INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('1-coffee-house','standard','cmr07ifqk0002q8xdhpwsuaew','1% Coffee House','## Top Reviews
> "Cute spot for a good coffee. Great for a coffee break and a little croissant snack. Would be nice if they had a breakfast, but this place is mostly coffee lovers oriented. Fresh good pastry though 🤗"
> **- kiddie garden (5/5/5)**

> "Really excellent coffee. If you like americano try the medium light roast. It is very flavorful. Nice acidity, the blueberry note really comes through.  The staff are very nice and obviously take pride in how they roast the coffee and prepare each drink.  The indoor area is very small and sunny even by mid-morning. The outside area has some shade but still a bit hot."
> **- Philip Smith (5/5/5)**

> "Great coffee with a good service and a very friendly young owner.  Coffee is roasted by the company itself. You have a few choices of coffeebeans and roasting levels.  Futher you can choose a sweet piece or a ham cheese filled croissant. Very big garden outside. This is a place were you dont need to hurry. Arrive and enjoy the good taste."
> **- Sven Fischer (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/1-coffee-house-1.jpg',NULL,'113/15 Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: Closed","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifpz0001q8xd0aml2ucx','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.700+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.700+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/1-coffee-house-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/1-coffee-house-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9551574239353936840',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('2-fishes','standard','cmr07ifr80004q8xd8ht65xxc','2 Fishes','## Top Reviews
> "Outstanding service, excellent food for reasonable (european) prices. Got there around 18 o‘clock, got seated perfectly and enjoyed the amazing sunset overlooking the beach. Awesome experience!  The food was outstanding: we ordered several starters, all where a 10/10. Local fish and the mushroom linguine as main, also 10/10. Desserts we’re a 11/10, heavenly.  Outstanding service as well! Staff super alert but not pushy, the 2 customer managers very kind and hanging around for some smalltalk.  It was as thoroughly rewarding experience. We will come again when we‘re back on Samui.  Thank you so much for that perfect evening and dining experience!"
> **- Steffen Rademacher (5/5/5)**

> "Nice spot on the water, great views. Lots of Italian inspo and the focus is on sea food. The thai dishes are great, steamed gold snapper was great. The lobster spaghetti also very good. Surprisingly excellent tacos for starters too, quite big too."
> **- Ben Smith (4/5/5)**

> "My boyfriend and I have been here many times, and we’ll definitely keep coming back—he absolutely loves the tacos here. The seafood is always fresh and really high quality, which makes every visit worth it. As someone who’s a big fan of pasta, I’ve tried three different pasta dishes here and never once regretted it. Each one has been delicious. The wine list is also impressive—they have pretty much everything you could be looking for. And the cocktails are soooo good. The staff are friendly and welcoming, though they don’t always pay much attention. I’m sure this is something they’ll improve over time 💕Still, the food and drinks make up for it, and we’ll definitely be back again. #The food look good but i don''t have still to take the food photo 😅"
> **- GG (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/2-fishes-1.jpg','099 281 9973','109,15, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.2fishessamui.com/','["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 5:00 – 10:30 PM","Wednesday: 5:00 – 10:30 PM","Thursday: 5:00 – 10:30 PM","Friday: 5:00 – 10:30 PM","Saturday: 5:00 – 10:30 PM","Sunday: 5:00 – 10:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.724+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.724+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/2-fishes-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/2-fishes-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4520277248498258278',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('20-stories-restaurant','standard','cmr07ifrh0006q8xdzqerbk7q','20 Stories Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "Beautiful location right on the beach front. I ordered a mojito which wasn''t the best, there was hardly any sugar and not enough lime. I also ordered seafood with rice, the seafood was well overcooked and the squid was rubbery and really chewy. There are lots of wait staff who were very friendly, and service was very fast."
> **- Dtown (3/5/5)**

> "We visited this restaurant twice during our stay and absolutely loved it. The tuna steak was fantastic — fresh, perfectly cooked, and honestly one of the best meals we had. What made it even more special was that it wasn’t even on the menu, but they still kindly prepared it for us when we asked. And for such great quality, the price was really excellent. That’s exactly why we came back a second time. Highly recommended!"
> **- Luisa Behrens (5/5/5)**

> "Stopped in for a bit to eat. I had the Ribs and the wife had Chi Ken cashew nut. Whilst the staff were exceptional the food was a little bland.. Maybe just an off day but wouldn''t make it a priority to return. Sorry guys."
> **- Steve Hampson (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/20-stories-restaurant-1.jpg','090 945 5888','65 Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 2:00 – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 2:00 – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 2:00 – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 2:00 – 11:00 PM","Friday: 2:00 – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 2:00 – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 2:00 – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.733+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.733+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/20-stories-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/20-stories-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16567821668983412629',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('3d-pest-control','standard','cmr07ifrq0009q8xdno6su6f3','3D Pest Control','## Top Reviews
> "3D Pest Control is the best and most affordable service! After 1 treatment, my house is free of ants and other various pests. Before getting their service, I couldn’t even have a dead fly in my house without 1000 ants swarming it, now I live stress free! I also have a dog and the treatment doesn’t harm him at all. 3D Pest Control comes every month, sends confirmation emails, and is willing to adjust for days if I need to. I highly recommend this service on Samui! 🙌🏼"
> **- Samantha Crosner (5/5/5)**

> "Since the initial consultation with 3D Pest Control, I have enjoyed nothing less than an excellent experience. The team conduct themselves in the most professional way, the communication is great and they are always sure to honour their appointments. All my concerns continue to be addressed in a friendly manner. When my contract came up for renewal, I had no hesitation in extending the same. With their expertise, I would highly recomnend them to address any pest control concerns."
> **- Mark Sangster (5/5/5)**

> "This is not the first company on Samui that we work with on issues of insects, rodents, etc. But this is the best company of all! Everything is always on time, the price is the best, information support is at a high level, and the Thai staff speaks English well. Manager Andrew is a model of professionalism. I recommend!"
> **- Dima Tereshko (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/3d-pest-control-1.jpg','+66636469004','100, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.3dpestcontrolsamui.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.742+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.742+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/3d-pest-control-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/3d-pest-control-2.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/3d-pest-control-3.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/3d-pest-control-4.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10674556416127440127',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('4-spices','standard','cmr07ifrx000bq8xd5u3x2561','4 Spices','## Top Reviews
> "My son found 4Spices while searching for sushi on Koh Samui and we’re very glad he did.  The restaurant is located high above Chaweng with fantastic views. The drive up is steep, but there is parking available and a buggy service takes you the final stretch to the restaurant.  We arrived around 8pm on a very rainy evening without a reservation and were seated immediately.  We ordered sea bass sashimi, salmon tempura, sea bass red curry, chicken fried rice, a 4Spices roll, salmon nigiri and tuna nigiri. Everything was beautifully presented and full of flavour. The sea bass sashimi, sushi and red curry were all excellent.  The salmon tempura wasn’t really to our taste because we prefer salmon served raw, but that was purely personal preference and not a reflection of the quality of the dish.  Service was friendly and attentive throughout, and the views over Chaweng are excellent, especially at night. I imagine arriving before sunset would make the experience even better.  Our bill came to just over THB 3,000 for three people, although we definitely ordered more food than we needed.  A great restaurant with excellent food, service and views. Well worth the trip up the hill."
> **- Mo Mayet (5/5/5)**

> "I had an absolutely unforgettable experience at 4 Spices in Koh Samui. The moment you arrive, you are greeted by a breathtaking panoramic view of Bangrak Bay that sets the tone for an exceptional evening. The open-air setting combines vibrant island energy with a relaxed, elegant atmosphere that makes it perfect for sunset dinners, romantic nights, or celebrations.  ￼  The menu is wonderfully diverse and reflects a creative fusion of Thai, Israeli, Japanese, and international flavors. Every dish we tried was beautifully presented and full of fresh, rich flavors — from the expertly crafted sushi to the bold fusion plates and signature Thai specialties. The balance of flavors was impressive, offering something exciting with every bite.  ￼  Drinks are equally delightful, with inventive cocktails that pair perfectly with the stunning ocean views. The service was friendly, attentive, and genuinely welcoming, which made the whole dining experience feel more personal and special.  ￼  Price-wise, 4 Spices offers excellent value for such high-quality cuisine and setting. The creative menu, gorgeous vistas, and impeccable service all come together to create a standout experience that anyone visiting Koh Samui should not miss.  ￼  I highly recommend 4 Spices for anyone seeking a memorable meal with a beautiful view and an international flair — this place truly deserves a 5-star rating in every way."
> **- Franz Heigemeir (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing experience at 4Spices – outstanding food & service!  We had a fantastic evening at 4Spices, and everything from the drinks to the main courses was top quality.  We started with two fresh coconuts – honestly the best and freshest we’ve had on the entire island of Koh Samui. Perfectly chilled and incredibly refreshing. Along with that, a Chang beer, ice-cold and just right.  For sushi, we ordered 8 tuna rolls and 8 salmon rolls, and they were absolutely fantastic. You could really taste the freshness of the fish, paired with a nice bit of crunch from the cucumber. The slightly thicker soy sauce was a real highlight — it elevated the sushi even more and rounded everything off perfectly.  As a starter, we had the crispy salmon. It was a bit different from what we expected, but still very good and enjoyable.  For the main course, the red curry sea bass was outstanding. The fish was perfectly tender, the coconut sauce was smooth and aromatic, and the curry flavor was simply top-level — rich, balanced, and incredibly delicious.  A special mention goes to our waiter Kyaw Tun. His service was exceptional: friendly, attentive, professional, and genuinely caring. He made us feel very welcome and truly enhanced our entire dining experience.  We would absolutely come back and highly recommend 4Spices — amazing food, great atmosphere, and first-class service."
> **- Shanna Generalao (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/4-spices-1.jpg','064 025 8290','8/100 4 Soi Blessing Village, bang rak Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.4spices-samui.com/','["Monday: 4:00 – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 4:00 – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 4:00 – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 4:00 – 11:00 PM","Friday: Closed","Saturday: 8:00 – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 4:00 – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.749+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.749+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/4-spices-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/4-spices-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10937680934952464171',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('4monkeys-coffee-bar','standard','cmr07ifs2000dq8xdls4a5fpn','4Monkeys Coffee & Bar','## Top Reviews
> "Beautiful views , exquisite food - really really good. We had a wrap, a chicken Caesar salad and a club sandwich - all super tasty . The smoothies were yum and the coffee was fabulous - try the caramel macchiato🥰"
> **- Darth sly (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing! Had a great dinner here, one of the best meals I had in Thailand. The chicken with garlic and pepper sauce, 5 stars. The staff was also incredible an very joyful! Great location too, right in front of the beach.  Would definitely recommend to go here"
> **- Teresa Oom V.S (5/5/5)**

> "We came here twice in April 2026…the first night of our holiday and the last…we wished it had been more.  An absolutely wonderful welcoming bar with incredibly relaxed beach vibes. The owner Nong is a lovely lady who cannot do enough for you…and she is an expert cocktail maker. Literally we had some of the best cocktails during our stay on the island.  4 Monkeys had an extensive cocktail list and my wife asked for one that was not on it. Nong checked but one of the ingredients  of the cocktail was not stocked (this was our fault for asking for something not listed!) however she got one of the team to check with a shop over the road for the ingredient..this way above and beyond what we expected!  The positioning the restaurant is incredible occupying an enviousn position overlooking the beach and sea…if you can try to get there for sunset and watch the fishing boat lights sparkle across the water as the waves lap against the sand…you cannot put a price on this!  Coming from the UK I cannot tell you how much we felt welcomed by Nong and her lovely staff..and if you appreciate a well crafted cocktail do not miss this place!"
> **- andrew owen (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/4monkeys-coffee-bar-1.jpg','094 746 4878','HWHR+7VR, 4169, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/share/1Hn3UGV9xv/?mibextid=wwXIfr','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: Closed","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifs1000cq8xdfo2aau32','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.754+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.754+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/4monkeys-coffee-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/4monkeys-coffee-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8221525031916299368',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('69-slam-lamai','standard','cmr07ifs6000fq8xdcjk1nuom','69 Slam','## Top Reviews
> "I purchased a sun protect jacket and shorts from their store and specifically asked for the receipt / form for claiming the VAT back when returning from Thailand, they asked me to come back the next day and gave me a normal invoice which when I clarified with the part time employee she mentioned that this would work and no previous customers had any problems. Unfortunately at the airport the claim was rejected since the shop had provided me the incorrect invoice with no proper form to claim my VAT back and I ended up loosing that money. The employees at the shop should be informed and educated since it’s in a prime touristic spot and from the looks of it have a lot of tourists coming in to buy their products."
> **- Amrita Gopinath (3/5/5)**

> "Very good place to buy surfer swim shorts that can be used for normal swim use as I don’t surf, they have for both men and women. Nice quality and good prices. Owner is a nice guy too and speaks perfect English"
> **- Allen M (5/5/5)**

> "Very good  material , great customer service ."
