INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('79-beach-club-resort','standard','cmr07ifsl000jq8xdzbhozvxn','79 Beach Club & Resort','## Top Reviews
> "I honestly have no words to describe how beautiful this resort is. The rooms were spotless, well organized, and every little detail in the sea-view room made me fall in love with the place. Waking up to that view was something special.  The service was excellent from the moment I arrived. The reception team was friendly, welcoming, and always happy to help. The food was also amazing, and overall my experience here was nearly perfect.  If you’re looking for a great place to stay and enjoy your vacation, I highly recommend it. The only thing worth mentioning is that you can hear music from the resort during the afternoon, especially if your room faces the entertainment area. If you’re a very light sleeper or looking for complete silence, this might not be ideal. Personally, even though I was tired and wanted to nap in the afternoon, I decided to enjoy the atmosphere, and when I needed to sleep, earplugs did the job perfectly.  A special thank you to Jennie, who was absolutely amazing throughout my stay. Also, thank you to the gentleman at reception whose name I unfortunately can’t remember. You both made my stay even more enjoyable. See u next time"
> **- Sara Ismail (5/5/5)**

> "Nim jj was a wonderful host. The pool and bar were amazing. The food is great and have different types to enjoy. We have been multiple times and we have a great time when we are here. The most friendly staff. Definitely recommend the beach club."
> **- April Pullen (5/5/5)**

> "Had an amazing experience at 79 Beach Club! From the atmosphere, to the food and the service, we had an absolute ball!! The swim up bar is awesome, so easily accessible and the staff are so friendly and accommodating. Our waitress JJ was amazing. Highly recommend for a day/night out! 🤍"
> **- Vivian Succar (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/79-beach-club-resort-1.jpg','077 427 799','79/79 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.79samui.com/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.773+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.773+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/79-beach-club-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/79-beach-club-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3077763131908594197',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('88-artisan-bread','standard','cmr07ifsp000lq8xdoizmxb3j','88% Artisan Bread','## Top Reviews
> "The sourdough bread is honestly the best I’ve ever eaten (and I love a good sourdough!)  we have enjoyed a wee coffee of an afternoon whilst staying at the beach and the setting is just beautiful. The staff are fab / supersonic service Going to miss this place!!  Must visit if you are in the area xx"
> **- May Woods (5/5/5)**

> "In my eyes the best bread, patisserie on the hole island. I especially recommend the Shashuka and Croissant.  They also have other Stores on Koh Samui but this is the best on in my eyes. However it can get busy, so some times you have to wait."
> **- Tim (5/5/5)**

> "Good vibes nice coffee and all the breads smell so good I have carrot cake and I love it. Next time I will try the breakfast for sure"
> **- MAGIC DUST (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/88-artisan-bread-1.jpg','081 539 2988','3, 25, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifso000kq8xdfe9gpaon','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.777+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.777+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/88-artisan-bread-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/88-artisan-bread-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1617467531592865316',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('8lements-spa','standard','cmr07ift2000oq8xdf23r2a05','8Lements Spa','## Top Reviews
> "Ok 8 ELEMENTS! Mai that massage was amazing. The ambiance is so relaxing and inviting you to tranquility.  Thank you for a great massage."
> **- Suzanne Fagins (5/5/5)**

> "Such a lovely place 🍃 Immediately felt welcomed walking in!  Thank you to all the lovely ladies at the spa for making us feel both very relaxed and comfortable! 🌸  Myself and my partner got both massages and facials and both overall experiences were amazing! The Facial was very calming and the products used were really high quality. Thank you,  Ti’e, Bad & Bassy for the amazing service we are very grateful 🙏🏼 (sorry if I spelt the names wrong)  The spa really made our hotel stay even better!  They do various services including scrubs, facials, massages, bath and more if you’re staying definitely check out the spa 😊"
> **- Chloe Lavell (5/5/5)**

> "The hotel is wonderful, with impeccable service and a very welcoming atmosphere. The spa is the true highlight, simply incredible! Extremely relaxing, well-maintained, and with excellent professionals. I left feeling completely renewed. A special thank you to the spa team, especially Bassy, Fern, and Mia who were amazing. Highly recommend!"
> **- Claudia Mori (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/8lements-spa-1.jpg','077 913 750','84, Tambon Bo Put, Suratthani, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.garrya.com/en/destinations/samui/spa','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifsv000nq8xdrwnu123q','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.790+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.790+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/8lements-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/8lements-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4304053997311952386',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('a-serene-beach-spa','standard','cmr07ift9000qq8xdmlfvknc7','A Serene Beach Spa','## Top Reviews
> "THE BEST MASSAGE 120min experience in THAILAND (we had more than 30 different) .We are stunned how skilled girls are and professional. Salon is very pretty and nicely furnished.A lot of small details makes salon look very cozy . Beautiful view from massage rooms. Easy to find salon it’s just next to the road with plenty parking around. Affordable price and lovely staff. We left salon impressed in every way.  Highly recommended!❤️"
> **- Honeymoon 365 (5/5/5)**

> "The atmosphere inside the shop is absolutely charming, and every therapist is warm and welcoming. I had one of the most relaxing massages I’ve ever experienced on Koh Samui. My therapist is Mintra she was exceptional,she even took the time to show me a few simple self massage techniques to help when I have migraines. She was incredibly kind, attentive, professional. I will definitely be returning here again next year! THANK YOU!"
> **- Ginny (5/5/5)**

> "An amazing massage experience.  Excellent list of services, reasonable prices, and a wonderful massage.  Apparently I fell asleep it was soooo relaxing.  Foot wash before, relaxing massage, and then delicious mango tea after.  Very accommodating with scheduling and no rush the entire time.  Loved the staff!!!"
> **- Jon Willoughby (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/a-serene-beach-spa-1.jpg','092 989 9069','76, Ban, 8, Thong Krut, Koh Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/Aserenebeachspa?mibextid=wwXIfr&mibextid=wwXIfr','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ift8000pq8xd7yujz20i','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.797+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.797+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/a-serene-beach-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/a-serene-beach-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16835422216768880941',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ab-samui-printing','standard','cmr07iftf000tq8xdhnxger1c','A&B Samui Printing','## Top Reviews
> "Chill and accommodating with service in mind at an unbeatable price. I know it sounds too good to be true, but they really helpes me out of a jam."
> **- Paravat Chantarakajon (5/5/5)**

> "Great services in one place for copying, scanning and printing. They also take visa and passport pictures and can help converting file format such as imagine to pdf,etc.. English speaking and very friendly place and also very reasonable prices"
> **- K C (5/5/5)**

> "Superb service and very professional . Great price and picture quality on the vinyl is  amazing . Very helpful and lovely couple who run it , they also give you great advice on design , I have used them twice now and it''s the place to go if you want quality and a great price 10/10"
> **- paul harrison (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ab-samui-printing-1.jpg','097 214 2745','17, 4 ตำบล แม่น้ำ Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.803+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.803+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ab-samui-printing-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ab-samui-printing-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6727679951176860085',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('about-cafe','standard','cmr07iftl000uq8xd1f7tpsbe','About Cafe','## Top Reviews
> "The cafe is cute and cosy. Service is functional but we experienced some raised voices and slamming of plates when questioning what an order was.  The coffee itself seems to be somewhat overextracted producing quite an unbalanced taste, and unfortunaly cant compete with some of the excellent specialist coffee in the area.  Like previous reviews, the generosity of the cafe must be questioned when the free drinking water comes out in thimble size cups, the smallest I have ever seen."
> **- Jo S (2/5/5)**

> "I don’t understand the hype about this café, except maybe for the waffle. The American breakfast was very light, apart from the bread – but what’s the point if you can’t put anything on it? The orange juice was ridiculously small, and the hot drink wasn’t even included. The "
> **- Audrey B (1/5/5)**

> "So, About cafe’ is one of the oldest coffee shop in town. Forget about those industrial, fancy, or modern style coffee shop that you can find every 200 m. this shop is all about a unique history with chilled vibe and reasonable price on menu.  They don’t have much seating so this might not be the place to come and work on your laptop, but this place is an ideal stop to have some breakfast and coffee before heading to the beach which is just a few steps away.  Recommended dishes ♥️Hot Cappuccino ♥️Scone ♥️Homemade yogurt with fruits  The alley itself is pretty cute, I like it a lot. I went there in the morning time so there are not many shop around here opened. From what I seen there are a few massage stores, a restaurant, and a small Chinese temple on the same street oh and also some cafe’ along the other side.  The road is oneway and pretty small, can find motorbike parking lot on the side of the road."
> **- Panshewa P. (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/about-cafe-1.jpg','077 938 167','160/1, Moo1, Ban Maenam, ตำบล แม่น้ำ อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 7:30 AM – 4:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:30 AM – 4:00 PM","Wednesday: Closed","Thursday: 7:30 AM – 4:00 PM","Friday: 7:30 AM – 4:00 PM","Saturday: 7:30 AM – 4:00 PM","Sunday: 7:30 AM – 4:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.809+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.809+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/about-cafe-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/about-cafe-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14475686974569981829',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('acacia-woods-furniture','standard','cmr07iftp000vq8xdpbzkmayd','Acacia Woods Furniture','## Top Reviews
> "The products themselves are good. But what was disappointing was that when the expensive shelves sagged and I contacted this company again for help, they even stopped answering me. That is, their goal is to sell to you, get money from you and forget about you. This is sad and not at all customer-oriented."
> **- Алексей Кошелев (1/5/5)**

> "I’ve worked with this team on several projects, and I can confidently say their quality is truly outstanding. The prices may be higher than your average wood shop, but the difference is clear — you’re paying for top-grade craftsmanship and premium materials, especially when it comes to their beautiful Acacia wood.  Whenever I need the highest quality pieces, this is my go-to place. I’ve had various custom works done, and every time the result has been exceptional — refined, durable, and visually stunning. You can really see the difference when compared to the everyday products on the market. It’s the kind of quality that stands out immediately and adds real value to any space.  If you''re looking for serious craftsmanship and timeless quality, I highly recommend them. Bravo to the whole team — keep up the great work!"
> **- Explorer X (5/5/5)**

> "Commissioned custom reclaimed wood floor standing mirror, dining table and home office desks. Khun Jib and her husband were super helpful. The workmanship is excellent and a high attention to detail. Highly recommended."
> **- Fayçal Sekkouah (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/acacia-woods-furniture-1.jpg','+66849442217','24/46 ม.5 บ้านใต้ Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.9,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.facebook.com/acaciawoodsfurniture','["Monday: 9:30 AM – 6:30 PM","Tuesday: 9:30 AM – 6:30 PM","Wednesday: 9:30 AM – 6:30 PM","Thursday: 9:30 AM – 6:30 PM","Friday: 9:30 AM – 6:30 PM","Saturday: 9:30 AM – 6:30 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ifso000kq8xdfe9gpaon','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.813+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.813+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/acacia-woods-furniture-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/acacia-woods-furniture-2.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/acacia-woods-furniture-3.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/acacia-woods-furniture-4.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14827552965756876236',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('adlib-cafe-vinyl','standard','cmr07iftu000wq8xdj3wbfgta','Adlib Cafe & Vinyl','## Top Reviews
> "The BEST Khao Soi Fusion Northern Style I have experience in Koh Samui. Rich curry flavor and on top of juicy Katsu Chicken. (Fried Chicken Japanese Style). I ordered that because it is the place signature’s menu, and was very very happy that I ordered it.  Definitely recommend a place for friends and family to come eat meet hangout in the day or late evenings. (so you can go to the fisherman village later around sunset).  The place is run by the owner himself so I ensure you its got his own style. Simple place that makes the environment very relaxing and friendly. Not only that this shop is also a restaurant but is also a vinyl bar as well. you can come check out the shop owner’s music Funk & Soul collection.  Amazing Taste Amazing Atmosphere Amazing Time"
> **- Athit Sumpunkulapak (5/5/5)**

> "We''re thrilled to have discovered this gem! Fantastic service and an unbeatable vibe make every visit special. Their coffee is outstanding, and the menu of authentic Thai dishes is truly tempting. We can''t wait to return, again and again!"
> **- Balanced Travel (5/5/5)**

> "Coolest place we''ve been to at Koh Samui! amazingly tasty and clean food. The Khao Soi is a must. The Katsu chicken is delicious. The bowls are also fresh and tasty. The Acai is the best we ate. The music here is top notch, fresh tunes from the owner''s vynil collection."
> **- David Troinin (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/adlib-cafe-vinyl-1.jpg','081 239 2319','17, district, 6, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.google.com/search?q=Adlib+Cafe+%26+Vinyl+Samui&stick=H4sIAAAAAAAA_-NgU1I1qDA2MDVJMzQwMDa0TDZLS02yMqgwMTIyskhOtjQ0SbJINTGyXMQq4ZiSk5mk4JyYlqqgphCWmVeZoxCcmFuaCQDfkDeJRAAAAA&hl=th&mat=CQfwKOZrdyW_ElcBTVDHnmVjP-xQoW33OP7S_pO9NqnprGnbKxByhXA7u4clA5R8vfIBAnANflyJ6_FgWXfssad0QOf_F0qqwU9vASPFZpfqEDW_AaDk2SeN21u_dWtrhHo&authuser=0&ved=2ahUKEwjh0b_XlYGUAxV41TQHHXXVMxYQ-MgIegQIDBAk','["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.818+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.818+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/adlib-cafe-vinyl-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/adlib-cafe-vinyl-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4765526150975382569',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('adrenaline-vibes-watersports','standard','cmr07iftz000yq8xdfeh8h9s8','Adrenaline Vibes Watersports','## Top Reviews
> "⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ An unforgettable tour w amazing team  We joined a 4-hour jet ski tour with four island stops, and the entire experience was absolutely fantastic from start to finish.  The staff were incredibly professional, attentive, and caring throughout the whole trip. Our guide led the group confidently, while another team member followed behind, making sure everyone was safe and comfortable at all times. The guide constantly checked in with us and made sure everyone was enjoying the ride.  They took beautiful photos and videos of everyone during the tour and on the islands, and brought us to stunning locations while also recommending great spots and activities at each stop. The sunset ride on the way back was truly magical and the perfect ending to an already amazing experience.  This was a perfectly organized tour with outstanding service and genuine care for the guests. Highly recommended to anyone visiting Koh Samui!💞"
> **- Liza Melkvi (5/5/5)**

> "I was on a 4-hour tour. I really liked Thomas''s friendliness and his attentiveness. The jet skis are of excellent quality 👍. While snorkeling, I managed to see a huge school of fish, and I also admired the beauty of Koh Phangan island and took many beautiful photos. I recommend it!"
> **- Evgenya Ponkratova (5/5/5)**

> "3 hour jet ski tour to Koh Phangan was everything we wanted. Good long ride at speed, private beaches and snorkeling. Guide eas very good, he even took our camera and got great pictures and videos"
> **- cheryl Terrillon (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/adrenaline-vibes-watersports-1.jpg','061 980 0910','67/61, ตำบล แม่น้ำ อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://adrenalinevibe.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 6:30 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.823+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.823+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/adrenaline-vibes-watersports-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/adrenaline-vibes-watersports-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4144128520143361477',NULL,NULL);
