INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('after-8-spa-nikki-beach','standard','cmr07ifuf0011q8xdt5x763u5','After 8 Spa Nikki Beach','## Top Reviews
> "Nikki Beach Koh Samui is a beautiful place to spend the day. We were there visiting friends and had a fantastic time. For us, it’s one of the nicest Nikki Beach locations.  The setting is stunning, the atmosphere relaxed yet stylish, and the service attentive. Great music, good food, and a perfect beach club vibe right by the ocean.  A wonderful spot to enjoy a sunny day with friends. Highly recommended."
> **- Oliver Kremers (5/5/5)**

> "We had an absolutely sensational stay! From the moment we arrived, everything was seamless and welcoming. The food was outstanding — every meal felt like a highlight — and the service was consistently attentive without ever being over the top.  The rooms were immaculate, beautifully presented, and clearly very well maintained. It made such a difference coming back each day to a space that felt fresh, clean, and comfortable. Honestly, we couldn’t fault a single thing throughout our stay.  A special shoutout to Nan and Care at the front — both were incredibly friendly, helpful, and always made us feel looked after. And a big thank you to our driver Noom as well, who was professional, reliable, and just an all-around great person to deal with. It’s staff like this that really elevate the whole experience.  The atmosphere across the resort was spot on — relaxed but still premium, with a great vibe whether you were unwinding or enjoying the beach club. Everything just felt easy, which is exactly what you want on a getaway.  This was our first time staying at a Nikki Beach, and it completely exceeded expectations. Safe to say it won’t be our last — already looking forward to coming back!"
> **- James Bimbilovski (5/5/5)**

> "i’ve had the best experience at this hotel, it’s been one of the best trips/stays of my life. everything made this trip perfect, i had the breakfast package and it was amazing!  One of the waitresses Fai Beer, was so lovely, she was very kind and helpful every morning and has such a lovely energy and smile! such an amazing member of staff. all the workers at the hotel are very helpful and kind and greet you everytime they see you. if you’re considering whether to come, definitely do so! thank you so much nikki beach it’s been amazing!!! only drawback was the location as it’s in a very quiet side of the island, if this is what you’re looking for then it’s perfect, but we’ve had to spend a lot of money on grabs whilst here."
> **- Zoe O''Sullivan (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/after-8-spa-nikki-beach-1.jpg','077 914 500','96, 3, Tambon Lipa Noi, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://nikkibeach.com/koh-samui/?utm_source=Google+Business+Profile',NULL,'cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.839+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.839+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/after-8-spa-nikki-beach-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/after-8-spa-nikki-beach-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9465511644152669761',NULL,NULL);
