INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('air-bar','standard','cmr07ifum0014q8xdh76noeiw','Air Bar','## Top Reviews
> "Drove from Chaweng to Air Bar to experience the famous sunset views. Unfortunately, heavy rain on the journey meant the drive took over an hour, and by the time we arrived the skies were still cloudy, so we didn’t get to see the sunset.  Despite that, we were still very impressed.  Parking is available at the InterContinental and the hotel provides buggy transport from the car park up to the bar, which is a nice touch.  The service was excellent throughout, exactly what you would expect from InterContinental. We sat near the edge and enjoyed the fantastic views across the sea.  My son had a fresh coconut, my daughter had a virgin strawberry daiquiri (which she said was excellent), and I had a Coke Zero. Total spend was around THB 800.  Even without the sunset, the atmosphere and views were great. I would definitely recommend visiting, but try to choose a clear evening if possible."
> **- Mo Mayet (5/5/5)**

> "Very good of a nice sunset the day we came is special. They have saxophone show feel so special love to see sunset"
> **- Nick Nissnile (5/5/5)**

> "The view from the Air Bar is absolutely stunning, truly breathtaking and unforgettable. The ambience is perfect for a relaxing evening or a special night out. What made the experience even better was the staff: incredibly friendly, respectful, kind, and attentive especially film she’s a gem of heart 💓☺️. Their warm hospitality added so much to the overall vibe. Highly recommended!"
> **- khin samui (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/air-bar-1.jpg','077 429 100','295, ตำบล ตลิ่งงาม Koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://samui.intercontinental.com/air-bar','["Monday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Friday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ift8000pq8xd7yujz20i','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.846+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.846+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/air-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/air-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7179602118476830801',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('airgym','standard','cmr07ifuq0016q8xd93oec65t','AirGym','## Top Reviews
> "I attended aerial sling class after X-mas before they closed for holidays. It was my first time on the sling, and the session was well organized.I learned positions and got confidence to continue. The teacher was very skilled and supportive, explaining clearly what to do, how to hold the back, chest, she knew when to help, when you’re ready for more difficult position. It was a pleasure to attend and I had a lot of fun as well. I highly recommend, the level of professionalism is high."
> **- Nadia Porubska (5/5/5)**

> "I gotta be honest, this is a truly world class studio with phenomenal professionals! 👏  I went multiple times for stretching with Kathi and pole dance classes with Faith and I was amazed with the level of their knowledge and approach. I’m sure all the other classes are fantastic as well!  I can’t wait to go back and take those classes regularly as it’s one of the best ones I’ve ever took! Studio is also very clean and with a lot of equipment, highly recommended! ✨"
> **- Karolina Parysz (5/5/5)**

> "I took several pole dance classes here and really enjoyed them! The absolute highlight for me, though, was the deep stretching class. Kathi’s approach to stretching was completely new to me — and incredibly effective. Highly recommend this lovely studio for both movement and mindful flexibility!"
> **- Karolina S. (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/airgym-1.jpg',NULL,'115/105, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://airgym.family/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 3:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifuo0015q8xdfahzrsp4','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.850+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.850+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/airgym-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/airgym-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16931753388119477924',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('all-clear-cleaning','standard','cmr07ifut0017q8xdyfenln6w','All Clear Cleaning','## Top Reviews
> "True 5-Star Service! Amazing service and easy, clear, effective communication! After submitting a video of our home to show the area to be cleaned, we received a quote (with and without windows) and chose deep cleaning, windows, and a sofa steam cleaning. We were able to get an appointment within the week. Andrew made it easy to understand the process and options. Khun Win and The All Clear Cleaning Samui team came to our home (with Khun Thet as cleaning lead) and within the span of 5 hours, windows were spotless, sills and fans dusted, fridge cleaned, inside and out, bathrooms sparkling, sofa steam cleaned and fresh! Our home was not wretched by any means, but having this deep cleaning done made a difference we could see and feel from the moment we stepped back inside. So clean it felt lighter and brighter throughout! My husband said, “The windows are so clean it looks like the glass isn’t even there!” The team was courteous and professional, communicating throughout the cleaning process by sending photos and videos showing their work. We will be repeat customers for sure."
> **- Autumn Lew (5/5/5)**

> "All Clear Cleaning has done approximately 1000 villa cleanings for us in the last 12 months.  We’ve entrusted them to clean our properties to a 5 star hotel level of quality, and they have exceeded our expectations.  The staff arrive on time, finish on time, and can handle anything.  We highly recommend All Clear Cleaning as the best cleaning service on the island"
> **- Nick Meylemans (5/5/5)**

> "We hired this company for a deep cleaning and they are very serious, they don''t mess around, they arrive with a very large and competent team, and they take their time. It''s a professional job. They are very hygienic and come with professional equipment. I recommend them."
> **- Yasmine O (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/all-clear-cleaning-1.jpg','+66962868487','67, Bophut, 7, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.all-clear-cleaning-samui.com/','["Monday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM","Thursday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM","Friday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM","Saturday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.853+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.853+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/all-clear-cleaning-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/all-clear-cleaning-2.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/all-clear-cleaning-3.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/all-clear-cleaning-4.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14892377111296581565',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('allegro','standard','cmr07ifux0019q8xdwudswsah','Allegro','## Top Reviews
> "Very delicious pizza… My kids love it… One of the best in the island for sure. The cesar also was yummy. Thank you so much 😌🙏🏾"
> **- Karina Perederii (5/5/5)**

> "Pizza, pasta and cold cut was yummy. All of the dishes not too salty. Many pizza place are too salty and oily. Pasta with pesto and ravioli stuff with mushrooms was really testy, not too oily and creamy. I love their ravioli. 😅 forgot to take ravioli photo. Staff was friendly. Recommend!!!"
> **- PeaPie (5/5/5)**

> "One of the best pizzas I had since quite some time and I’m half Italian so I don’t write it lightly! Awesome service, we received complimentary freshly baked Focaccia as appetizers, pizzas and salad were amazingly tasty, wet tissues after the meal and Mentos candies with the bill. What an amazing dining experience, would 100% recommend."
> **- Frederic Mauron (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/allegro-1.jpg','098 194 9707','G364+J32, Suan Uthit Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://allegrosamui.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.857+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.857+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/allegro-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/allegro-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4430265629466980641',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('allure-resort-beach-club','standard','cmr07ifv4001bq8xdhjlz43bq','Allure Resort & Beach Club','## Top Reviews
> "Great place and location. I am visiting for years now, unfortunately my last stay was just unacceptable. I stayed at Villa 6 and during the night I stepped out and left my slippers infront of my entrance. The slippers were gone. Next day I checked out and left my shades case and a clip with money in it in the kitchen. I returned one hour later from the Zaya restaurant and asked about it. The cleaning personnel and the receptionist manager just let me know - so sorryyyyy not have. Booking at a so called high profile resort like Zaya should come with some standards that are non negotiable. One is to trust that my belongings are safe within the premises. This is not the case here.  Update: one day after I posted my experience with Zaya, Doris reached out. She is representing the new Hungarian owner and is running Zaya as the new manager of operations. Doris expressed her surprise and asked for some background since she wasn’t aware of the whole situation. She welcomed me at her office at the Zaya restaurant and apologized for the whole experience I went through. She asked me to allow Zaya to prove their class and provide a solution. That was the first time I felt treated with respect and the level of professionalism and integrity I am expecting. I told Doris that I appreciate her conduct and that I am happy for her commitment since I am enjoying usually staying at Zaya including my loved ones. Doris told me she will see personally into the matter and will reimburse the money that has been stolen. Since I had no expectations  at alI I thanked her and left with a feeling that someone is really caring here at Zaya - which is important to me. One day later I got asked to validate the amount which was a weeks budget. After that - SILENCE.  Doris, the manager, decided to stay silent and ghosted me in the follow up and this is a reflection of my treatment throughout my stay. I have to say that I enjoyed my stays at Zaya and that Mercedes and her team were always caring and loving but staying at a place where I have to look over my shoulder and knowing that my belongings are not safe is not acceptable. Integrity and respect are the values that I expect and should be vital for an establishment like Zaya. Doris showed me personally that Zaya is lacking both.  Final update: The owner and Doris claim to be interested in finding a solution and are requesting a call. Truth is Zaya has all contact details including my number and the WhatsApp contact in order to clarify and mitigate this situation but are just not interested. Please stop playing games."
> **- Wassilios Tzouros (1/5/5)**

> "During my stay here everything was great. The rooms were clean. And everything was at my disposal. The staff was very kind and helpful. The food in the restaurant was very delicious and there was a lot to choose from. I would especially like to highlight that it is on the beach so the beach was very close and wonderfully beautiful. We will definitely come back"
> **- Doris Kiss (5/5/5)**

> "I’ve had lunch & chilled by the pool for the last two days. The food is great & a fair price compared to other hotels on the island. The view is amazing and a nice chilled vibe. Staff are great a special mention to Teddy, Co Co & Kiwi who have all been really nice & friendly. 100% recommend stopping in for lunch or staying in the Villas."
> **- Connor Moody (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/allure-resort-beach-club-1.jpg','077 247 956','7, 5 175/7 ปลายแหลม ซอย 1 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.zaya-samui.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifv2001aq8xdag7cvjgf','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.864+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.864+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/allure-resort-beach-club-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/allure-resort-beach-club-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9693207307817094991',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('aloha-resort','standard','cmr07ifv8001dq8xd12ir99t7','Aloha Resort','## Top Reviews
> "Loved this hotel! A great location close to shops and restaurants. Its right on a beautiful beach. The pool is lovely! Plenty of sunbeds around the pool and beach area with parasols and pool towels. There is also a small bar poolside. Watersports/massage available. The rooms were very spacious and clean, ours had a lovely terrace and a great view of pool area just a few steps away. The air conditioning worked well, beds were comfortable, water provided daily. Would definitely stay here again!"
> **- M C H (5/5/5)**

> "We only stayed at Aloha Resort for one night, but it was absolutely incredible. The rooms were very clean, spacious, and beautifully designed, making it hard to believe we were just passing through.  The breakfast area was stunning, with a serene atmosphere that made our morning feel extra special. The food was soooo good😍🧡🙏  One of the highlights was their outdoor massage setup—it’s open-air, without any air conditioning, which makes it perfectly relaxing for anyone who loves a natural, tropical vibe.  The pool was spotless and inviting, perfect for a refreshing dip. The staff were friendly and attentive, adding a warm, welcoming touch to our short stay.  Even in just one night, Aloha Resort left a lasting impression—we can’t wait to come back!❤️🧡🌴🌅🥥🩵"
> **- Anna Kálmán (5/5/5)**

> "Unprofessional Manager, Poor Hospitality Very bad experience at Aloha Resort, Lamai Beach, Koh Samui. We booked for 2 nights and wanted to extend for a 3rd night. The manager, Mr. Juan, repeatedly said the hotel was fully booked, even though rooms were clearly available online. We eventually booked the third night ourselves. Despite staying 3 consecutive nights, we were forced to change rooms every single day, even when rooms were available. No flexibility, no courtesy, no effort to accommodate us. Better-view rooms were available but never offered. The worst incident was on the day of our expensive day trip. Our tour pickup was between 7:15–7:30 AM. Breakfast starts at 7:00 AM, and I clearly informed Mr. Juan that we were going for breakfast and asked him to call us when the cab arrived. He said “okay.” The cab came, waited, and left — we were never informed. When confronted, the manager laughed, refused responsibility, and kept saying “it’s your fault, it’s not my job to call you. Guests must come to the hotel lobby” Because of this, we almost missed our paid day trip and had to rush to the pier on a scooty, which was stressful and unsafe. Amenities were shockingly poor: When asked for water during check in (which was taking time), they said water only provided in the room!! No shampoo No conditioner No body wash No dental kit No iron Only handwash provided This hotel does not deserve a 3-star rating. Even basic budget hotels provide these essentials. And I spend 3.5k baht a night on this non sense property! Also, while booking only a twin room was shown, our request for a double bed was bluntly refused despite availability. Overall: misleading information, zero hospitality, and extremely unprofessional behavior by the manager. Not recommended."
> **- Namrata Sharma (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/aloha-resort-1.jpg','095 474 4659','128 หมู่ที่ 3 Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.1,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.alohasamui.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.868+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.868+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/aloha-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/aloha-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17636117916902005532',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('alpha-gay-resort-spa','standard','cmr07ifvc001eq8xdf4pozmws','Alpha Gay Resort & Spa','## Top Reviews
> "We had a brilliant stay at the Alpha Resort! Jun was so helpful and arranged some fun activities for us during our stay. The staff go over and above to make your stay as comfortable as possible. The pool area is wonderful and so is the food and bar service. There is also a lovely bar called Whispers on the property which we enjoyed visiting.We also used the laundry service which again was great. Highly reommended and we will be back!"
> **- Simon Bush (5/5/5)**

> "Most excellent experience staying here for a week. Clean and orderly facilities. Sharp staff who were always on top of things. They arranged a pub crawl and show for guests. The friendly and polite and very well organise manager Jun was super flexible with checkout time, allowing me to finish some remote work before I departed. The food from the in house menu is delicious and from the new restaurant (Whisper Lounge) was top notch. Strongly recommend staying 👌 👌"
> **- Fred Holdt (5/5/5)**

> "Exceptional resort. Just perfect.   Jun, the manager hooked us up with the absolute best massage therapist for body scrubs and massages on site!  He set us up with drivers for a private tour of the island and rides to town.  He''s really the definition of customer service- above and beyond! We were there during a rainy week and he called in an awesome pedicure/manicurist to our suite, so nice after a three week hike in New Guinea."
> **- Charles McGrath (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/alpha-gay-resort-spa-1.jpg','062 167 1216','9/34, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.alphagayresort.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.872+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.872+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/alpha-gay-resort-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/alpha-gay-resort-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5790399261921531356',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('als-resort','standard','cmr07ifvf001fq8xdzdh7kxb5','Al''s Resort','## Top Reviews
> "We had an absolutely wonderful stay at this hotel. The beds were outstanding – incredibly comfortable and of exceptional quality. We slept amazingly well every single night, which made our entire trip even more enjoyable and relaxing. The location is simply perfect. It is extremely convenient and ideally situated, making it easy to explore the surrounding area and access everything we needed within a short distance. Overall, we couldn’t have been happier with our experience. The combination of superb comfort and an excellent location makes this hotel a place we would highly recommend and gladly return to."
> **- Nina E (5/5/5)**

> "Went here for drinks only, and it''s by far the best cocktails I''ve had during our two years in Thailand.  The young bartender Shwe is brilliant and very good service. Sure he''s fairly new to Thailand, and still has some learning to do but I''m sure that with the peak season. he will know the English by heart within short.  This is the first place in two years where cocktails were really good, and I''ve stayed at pretty descent hotels, tried numerous bars and restaurants and traveled a fair bit.  I only wished I''d found this place earlier than our fifth and final night in the area.  This is the bar to visit!"
> **- Htun Zaw (1/5/5)**

> "Stayed from 25th to 30th March 2026.  The resort benefits from a prime location and a generously sized property, both of which create strong first impressions. However, beyond this, the experience struggles to consistently meet the expectations associated with its pricing and positioning.  Our initial stay in the Deluxe Garden View room (3 nights) revealed dated interiors and a rather basic overall finish. The bathroom, in particular, felt below par for a property of this category. Additionally, the persistent mosquito issue across the resort was hard to overlook and detracted from overall comfort.  The breakfast offering lacked both variety and consistency. Replenishment was irregular, and the service, while courteous, lacked the attentiveness and energy one would expect. The omelette station was a rare bright spot.  Evenings felt noticeably underwhelming, especially in comparison to nearby venues such as Ark Bar Beach Club and Elephant Beach Club, which offer a far more engaging atmosphere.  Upgrading to a higher room category for the final two nights did enhance the stay, though it also highlighted the disparity in quality within the room categories.  Overall, while the location and scale are compelling, the product, service refinement, and experiential depth fall short of what one would expect at this price point."
> **- siddharth singh (2/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/als-resort-1.jpg','077 300 561','200 หาดเฉวง Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.2,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.alsresortsamui.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.875+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.875+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/als-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/als-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17201931595754603739',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('am-samui-resort','standard','cmr07ifvj001gq8xd6pcu8ko0','Am Samui Resort','## Top Reviews
> "The resort is located in a beautiful part of the island and offers a very relaxing atmosphere overall. It is spacious, with a nice swimming pool and a private beach. I stayed in both a beach house and one of the newly renovated rooms in the main building, and I definitely preferred the renovated room. However, the WiFi connection was very poor throughout my stay.  Another downside was the service. The staff did not seem particularly engaged or motivated, which was noticeable in their overall attitude. Unfortunately, I also forgot some clothes after checking out. I contacted the hotel about this, but they were unable to locate them, which was disappointing.  To end on a positive note: there is a cool muay thai gym around the corner :)"
> **- Caroline Krouwel (2/5/5)**

> "I really loved this hotel! The staff at the reception were super friendly and gave the best service. The food was amazing especially Pad Thai, it was so delicious! The whole place is quiet, peaceful, and surrounded by greenery. The beach and the sea are absolutely beautiful.  The only small downsides were that the room lock was a bit low and tricky to use, and the shower water pressure wasn’t very strong. If they fix these, it would be perfect.  Overall, I highly recommend this place if you’re looking for real peace and relaxation. 🌴✨"
> **- fridayclub (5/5/5)**

> "The best accommodation on Koh Samui! And that says a lot, because we’ve explored the whole island—we’ve stayed in Chaweng, Lamai, and other areas, but we always find ourselves happiest returning to Am Samui Resort. This was already our second year staying here, and I can only highly recommend it. Truly the best place we’ve ever stayed at!  We also had our wedding at the resort this year, and everything was absolutely beautiful and exactly as we imagined. A big thank you to Tracy for organizing everything so perfectly!❤️❤️❤️"
> **- Ivana Koleničová (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/am-samui-resort-1.jpg','084 440 6713','39 หมู่ที่ 3 Tambon Taling Ngam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/amsamuiresort',NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ift8000pq8xd7yujz20i','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.879+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.879+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/am-samui-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/am-samui-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3034042817881827198',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('amari','standard','cmr07ifvm001hq8xdv4re3rkj','Amari','## Top Reviews
> "The staff were genuinely friendly throughout my stay, and the breakfast was actually quite good. The pillows were also some of the most comfortable I’ve had in a hotel for a long time.  That being said, the room itself had several issues that I simply wouldn’t expect from a 5-star hotel, especially at around 7,500 THB for two nights.  I was staying in a ground floor room, and privacy was far from ideal. People were constantly walking past and could easily look into the room, which made it difficult to feel comfortable.  The balcony was full of mosquitoes, and I also found cockroaches inside the room. The hotel should really consider carrying out a proper pest control treatment, as this is not something guests should be dealing with.  The biggest issue for me was the air conditioning. The automatic mode kept switching on and off throughout the night, and every time it did, it was loud enough to wake me up. I barely slept during my first night because of it.  Another thing that stood out was the bathroom. The bum gun next to the toilet had almost no water pressure at all. This is not a hidden defect or something difficult to notice. Anyone cleaning the bathroom on a daily basis should immediately realise that it is barely working. It made me wonder how regularly rooms are being checked before guests arrive.  Overall, the staff were great and the breakfast was enjoyable, but the room quality, maintenance issues, and pest problems fell well below what I would expect from a hotel advertising itself as a 5-star property."
> **- Philipp Siemes (3/5/5)**

> "Myself and 14 friends just got back from a group trip here and we all want to go back already.  The staff were amazing and made a huge effort to get to know us, and make our stay more enjoyable.  Big thanks to Nanathawan who had a lot of patience for the needs of our large group. I think over 100 emails happened back and forth to organise this group trip and she was always happy to accommodate us and make suggestions that would improve our stay.  Big thanks to Penn who so warmly welcomed us to breakfast most mornings, learned my coffee order, and had an uncanny habit of appearing right near our group as soon as any of us had a desire for cocktails.  To Maysa for so expertly waiting on our beachside banquet and always stopping to talk with us like a good friend no matter where we saw her on the resort. Also the banquet was incredible, it even had fire twirlers make an appearance.  To Zeed for making sure we never had to lift a finger by the pool, making sure we were always relaxed, had fresh towels and for bringing funny banter.  Every staff member I saw no matter their job l always made an effort to smile or greet me. My friends even met the General Manager by chance and said he was lovely to them.  The resort as a whole exceeded all expectations I had. We stayed in both a pool view suite and a deluxe ocean view during our time, and also visited our friends rooms in a variety of locations and all carried a similar standard of luxury, function and tranquillity. Also had personalised hand written welcome cards, fruit and cute welcome messages written on the mirror.  The pool view suites are quite peaceful and though they are further away from the lobby, beach and restaurant, the walk is a lovely stroll. Plus you can often get a friendly staff member to drive you back on a golf cart.  Location is great. It''s in a part of Chaweng that is very close to, but not completely surrounded by all the liveliness and activity that Chaweng provides. So if you want a peaceful beach or poolside holiday one day, and want a busy night of eating, drinking and dancing the next, you can easily have both.  Breakfast buffet was incredible. There''s Thai and Indian sections, but also a huge section for stuff like, bacon, eggs, fruit, cereal, pancakes etc. Basically anything you associate with breakfast you will find. Cocktails were lovely. Be sure to follow happy hour around, it''s at different times at different pools.  I could say a lot more but would be here a while. But if you''re tossing up on whether or not you should come here, just trust me and do it. My only regret is that we didn''t stay longer."
> **- Jake Parker (5/5/5)**

> "If you want to stay right in the middle of the action yet wake up to pure beachfront bliss, Amari Koh Samui is hard to beat. Located in the heart of Chaweng Beach, you’re steps away from the vibrant, bustling energy of Chaweng — restaurants, nightlife, shopping — all within easy reach.  But the real star of the show? The private beach. And I say this confidently: it’s arguably the best stretch of sand in the entire Chaweng area. The sand is powdery, the water is clear and calm, and the beachfront setting feels exclusive and beautifully maintained. The sunbeds and beachside seating area are perfect for long, lazy afternoons, and the beachfront bar makes sunset time something to look forward to every day.  The arrival experience sets the tone immediately. The lobby is open, airy, and filled with natural daylight. As you walk in, you’re greeted by a sweeping view of the ocean — that instant “I’m officially on holiday” moment.  Dining is another highlight. Prego is widely regarded as one of the best Italian restaurants on the island — authentic flavors, excellent pasta, and a lively atmosphere. Amaya Café, the all-day dining venue, offers an impressive international spread, including strong Indian and vegetarian options.  Overall, Amari Samui delivers that perfect balance of location, beach quality, dining, and atmosphere. It was truly one of the most memorable holiday experiences we’ve had in Samui."
> **- Bharath S (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/amari-1.jpg','077 300 306','14, 3 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.amari.com/koh-samui?utm_source=google&utm_medium=gmb&utm_campaign=aps','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.882+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.882+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/amari-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/amari-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7806270392640567349',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('amarina-green-hotel','standard','cmr07ifvp001iq8xdsdd1v3ea','Amarina Green Hotel','## Top Reviews
> "We have very bad experiences with this place in my whole life. I don’t recommend you to go there at all. The owner and staff so RUDE!!!🔥🔥🔥 The staff can’t speak english at all. We come and want extend to stay there 3 days the staff say yes it’s available. And tomorrow she come to my room and tell me to go down to meet the cleaning lady and they tell me to check out directly at 12:30. Because another people already take our room and not available anymore. I am so surprised bcause at the time we don’t prepared at all to checkout and my boyfriend while working at our room and we don’t have place to go at the time. And when i arrived i see they offer laundry service and drop my stuff for loundry there and tell to them can we get it back tomorrow morning the staff and owner say yes. But when we want to checkout all my laundry still dirty and they don’t do the loundry. It’s so annoying bcause we need to hurry for checkout and nothing done at the time. And they don’t apologize at all until we go. You Owner and staff need to learning speak english so you can give clear information to your guest and don’t treat your guest so Rude!!!"
> **- diantinyy claraa (1/5/5)**

> "Room was Big and clean. Nice area to stay in, walking distance to beach and Lamai night market, but still in a quiet street. The staff is not good in English but it works. Clean bathroom and room."
> **- Emilie Rehn (5/5/5)**

> "The room was big n clean. Mattress was hard (ok for me) n pillow was on a high side for me. Lady at the front desk n the cleaning ladies were nice. The walls has no isolation so could hear everything.  Still, it was fairly quiet outside at night.  The only thing I dislike was the AC went off automatically about 3-4am so have to restart again.  It looks cheap to see hotel laundry hanging on the railing."
> **- Jaime Loh (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/amarina-green-hotel-1.jpg','081 797 6515','105, 60 Moo3, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'https://amarinagreen.top/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.885+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.885+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/amarina-green-hotel-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/amarina-green-hotel-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3137541462704115804',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('amazonas-beachwear-fishermans-village','standard','cmr07ifvu001jq8xd5dqt7u2l','Amazonas Beachwear','## Top Reviews
> "OMG!!! If you are in Koh Samui, you HAVE TO visit this place! Amazing collection of swimwear & bikinis especially for my plus size queens! The fit is so flattering to my curves, I''ve never looked so good in a bikini before! 100% recommend...so many beautiful colours & styles It was like candyland for beachwear!!!"
> **- Vandana Dhanak (5/5/5)**

> "Fantastic bikinis! Bought one & had to go back & buy more. Really lovely patterns & super thoughtfully designed to fit perfectly. Wish you could order these online! Get down there & check it out."
> **- Liza Bec (5/5/5)**

> "Great store! Helpful staff, excellent range, beautiful stuff, fair price."
> **- Frank Vitani (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/amazonas-beachwear-fishermans-village-1.jpg','088 684 6080','167, 46 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.890+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.890+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/amazonas-beachwear-fishermans-village-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/amazonas-beachwear-fishermans-village-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3267769851815155556',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('amazonas-beachwear','standard','cmr07ifvx001kq8xdgxh4jzfm','Amazonas Beachwear','## Top Reviews
> "OMG!!! If you are in Koh Samui, you HAVE TO visit this place! Amazing collection of swimwear & bikinis especially for my plus size queens! The fit is so flattering to my curves, I''ve never looked so good in a bikini before! 100% recommend...so many beautiful colours & styles It was like candyland for beachwear!!!"
> **- Vandana Dhanak (5/5/5)**

> "Fantastic bikinis! Bought one & had to go back & buy more. Really lovely patterns & super thoughtfully designed to fit perfectly. Wish you could order these online! Get down there & check it out."
> **- Liza Bec (5/5/5)**

> "Great store! Helpful staff, excellent range, beautiful stuff, fair price."
> **- Frank Vitani (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/amazonas-beachwear-1.jpg','088 684 6080','167, 46 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.893+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.893+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/amazonas-beachwear-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/amazonas-beachwear-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3267769851815155556',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('amba-health-club','standard','cmr07ifw0001lq8xd4lg6dp1i','Amba Health Club','## Top Reviews
> "Had a lovely lunch at Amba. The dining area is really nice - clean, calm, and tastefully done. Staff were friendly and attentive throughout the meal. I ordered the roasted Mediterranean pasta salad and a fruit juice. Both were delicious - fresh ingredients, well-balanced flavours, and beautifully presented!!  Prices are definitely on the higher end for Thailand (more like Western pricing), but the quality makes it feel worth it if you’re looking for clean, healthy food. Great spot if you’re craving something light and nutritious in a relaxed setting."
> **- Sibel (5/5/5)**

> "When I first came here, the receptionist wasn’t very friendly. She didn’t smile or make me feel welcome. Since it was at night, I thought maybe she had already had a long day, so I understood. Now I come here every week and even became a member, but unfortunately her attitude is still the same. She still asks if I’m a member with an unfriendly tone, even though she was the one who handled my membership. However, the other staff inside are super friendly and always welcome you with a smile. Everything else here is perfect — the steam room, sauna, and ice bath are always great. The price is also very reasonable. Overall, I really enjoy this place and keep coming back, but the experience at the front desk could definitely be improved."
> **- Gade (4/5/5)**

> "The saunas are fantastic, the ice bath is effective, and the steam room is spotless. The changing rooms are clean and well-equipped: towels, deodorant, shower gel, moisturizer—everything is provided. The staff is friendly, helpful, and attentive. A real gem in almost every way.  However, there is one drawback I must point out: bringing your own water bottle is prohibited. I understand that sodas and snacks aren''t allowed. But water is vital (especially in Thailand with temperatures around 30°C and in a 90°C sauna). This rule is a real problem. Taking advantage of dehydration to encourage on-site consumption by restricting access to water goes against the very philosophy of a spa. An exception should at least be made for water.  I hope management will reconsider this policy—it would be the only thing missing for this place to be perfect."
> **- J2F Team (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/amba-health-club-1.jpg','094 666 9985','135, 9 Bond Kai Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://ambasamui.com/','["Monday: 8:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 8:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 8:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 8:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 8:30 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.896+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.896+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/amba-health-club-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/amba-health-club-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14042869783124130031',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('amba-real-estate','standard','cmr07ifw4001nq8xd6t8heirz','Amba Real Estate','## Top Reviews
> "Absolutely recommend Amba Real Estate in Samui! Ladda and her team are true locals who know the island inside out — this isn’t just a business for them, it’s something they genuinely care about.  Their experience, strong local network, and excellent English make the whole process smooth and trustworthy. If you’re looking for professionals who really take the time to understand what you need and offer honest, knowledgeable advice, this is the team to go with."
> **- Olfa Djemal (5/5/5)**

> "I wish I had found the Amba team sooner! I had a few issues with other agencies, but Amba was by far the best. They helped me source and finalise the exact deal I was looking for. An amazing team that catered to my every need. Highly recommend!"
> **- toby wiltshire (5/5/5)**

> "Cannot speak highly enough of the team at Amba Real Estate. They are so welcoming, knowledgeable and quick to assist with any problem. Thank you very much to Ladda for going above and beyond to answer all questions, her kindness and professionalism is to be admired."
> **- Caitlin Lee (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/amba-real-estate-1.jpg','095 883 6196','90 3, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.ambasamui.com/real-estate/property-for-sale','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ifw3001mq8xdy3gf4igo','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.900+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.900+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/amba-real-estate-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/amba-real-estate-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16191667695549275591',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('amezcua-spa','standard','cmr07ifw6001oq8xdrm837ix8','Amezcua Spa','## Top Reviews
> "4.5/5! We had a lovely time at the spa! The service was so kind, and the ladies were incredibly gentle. My partner and I got the coffee scrub. The treatment and service itself was great. We felt very relaxed while taking care of and our bodies felt very soft. The ladies were also very attentive during the treatment, constantly asking us how we were and if we were comfortable. The facility is extremely clean and modern. The treatment room was stunning too. The only comment we have is that prior to the treatment we were offered a tea and cold towel however the towel was dirty with marks on it. Nothing to major, but just something to raise for future customers. Thank you so much to Som!"
> **- Gabrielle Nguyen (4/5/5)**

> "Amazing experience, very nice private room. I took coconut oil massage and it was super relaxing. I will come back"
> **- Morgan Morel (5/5/5)**

> "Such a lovely massage. Got the 60 minute Thai massage and it was super relaxing and thorough. We were greeted with tea and asked about our bodies/anything to avoid or concentrate on during massage. The room was lovely and very peaceful. My masseuse was very attentive and did not rush. Would highly recommend."
> **- Ruby Baird (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/amezcua-spa-1.jpg','077 246 362','14 T, 3, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://pranaresortsamui.com/amezcua-spa/','["Monday: 9:30 AM – 7:30 PM","Tuesday: 9:30 AM – 7:30 PM","Wednesday: 9:30 AM – 7:30 PM","Thursday: 9:30 AM – 7:30 PM","Friday: 9:30 AM – 7:30 PM","Saturday: 9:30 AM – 7:30 PM","Sunday: 9:30 AM – 7:30 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.902+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.902+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/amezcua-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/amezcua-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9811174688018085539',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ammatara-pura','standard','cmr07ifw8001pq8xdghchxiqc','Ammatara Pura','## Top Reviews
> "Ammatara Pura Pool Villas offers a very unique atmosphere compared to many modern resorts in Thailand. The architecture and design have a strong traditional Thai identity, which gives the property real character and makes it feel memorable rather than generic.  The villas are spacious, private, and peaceful, and the beachfront location in Lamai creates a calm and relaxing environment. The staff members are warm, welcoming, and genuinely try their best to make guests feel comfortable and well taken care of. The overall experience feels intimate and much more personal than large chain resorts.  One of the strongest points of the property is definitely its atmosphere — it feels more like staying in a private Thai residence than in a typical hotel.  The resort could benefit from some light renovation and modernization in certain areas, but at the same time this slight sense of age gives the property authenticity and charm that many newer luxury resorts simply do not have.  Overall, Ammatara Pura Pool Villas has something many modern luxury resorts are missing: soul, identity, and authentic character."
> **- Andrey S (5/5/5)**

> "A spectacular hotel  Architecturally beautiful  The villas are amazing. Book a Sea View villa for total privacy and amazing views  It really is an oasis of calm in a busy city  Easy walk to town and all the bars and restaurants  The hotel foo right on the beach is excellent too.  This is my second time visiting this hotel. This time for 12 days. Wish I could stay longer.  The service from the staff here is beyond any I have experienced anywhere else without it being intrusive.  Stephen the manager is a delight  And Anastasia the food and beverage manager is an absolute star!  Stay here Thank me later  😂👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻"
> **- Adrian Lima (5/5/5)**

> "Ammatara Pura completely exceeded our expectations and was even more beautiful than the pictures. My fiancée and I stayed in a pool villa with an ocean view, and the room was incredibly spacious, private, and luxurious. The size of the villa alone was impressive, and it felt like the perfect place to relax and enjoy a peaceful getaway. Our private pool was warm and refreshing, while the main resort pool was cooler and perfect for escaping the heat. The resort itself was quiet and serene, which made our stay feel even more special.  The service was absolutely worthy of 5 stars, and every part of the experience felt thoughtful and welcoming. The private beach access directly from the resort offered stunning views and added even more to the sense of exclusivity and relaxation. The food was also outstanding, and both breakfast and dinner at the resort were absolutely worth enjoying on site. We would definitely come back again and would highly recommend Ammatara Pura to anyone looking for a beautiful, peaceful, and unforgettable luxury resort experience."
> **- Alexander Bingham (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ammatara-pura-1.jpg','061 664 9545','128/75-76 Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.ammatarapura.com/','["Monday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.904+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.904+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ammatara-pura-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ammatara-pura-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10233853799588311931',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('amore-nail-spa','standard','cmr07ifwb001qq8xd4k3yiuej','Amore Nail Spa','## Top Reviews
> "Amore Nail Spa is hands down the best nail salon I’ve ever visited! From the moment you walk in, you’re greeted with a warm, welcoming atmosphere that instantly puts you at ease. The staff are incredibly friendly, professional, and talented—true experts in their craft.  I had a full manicure and pedicure, and I’m absolutely thrilled with the results. The attention to detail is impeccable, and they really take the time to make sure everything is perfect. The range of colors and designs is amazing, and the products they use feel luxurious.  The spa itself is spotless, stylish, and offers a relaxing vibe, making it the perfect escape from the hustle and bustle of Koh Samui. I even got a complimentary drink during my treatment, which was a nice touch!  Whether you’re looking for a quick polish or an indulgent spa day, Amore Nail Spa is THE place to go. I can’t recommend them enough—definitely worth the visit if you’re on the island!"
> **- Elio Giacomelli (5/5/5)**

> "I spontaneously discovered the salon today and as it looked very nice and modern, I had my nails done there with gel polish. The nail artist got the best out of my very short nails. Everything was very clean and she worked very accurately. I can recommend this salon to everyone. Thank you very much. :)"
> **- Lena Rau (5/5/5)**

> "I stumbled upon Amore Nail Spa while exploring Fisherman’s Village, and I’m so glad I did! The ambiance is so relaxing. The technicians are incredibly skilled, my nails have never looked better. I love that they use organic and pregnancy-friendly products, which makes the experience feel even more special. If you’re looking for a high-end nail spa with a conscience, this is the place to go!"
> **- วัชรภรณ์ เชวงวรกุล (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/amore-nail-spa-1.jpg','084 625 5899','79 7, 79, H25H+XW9, 7 ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.amorenailspa.com/','["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.907+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.907+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/amore-nail-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/amore-nail-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12396375602445393508',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('anahata-beachfront-retreat','standard','cmr07ifwd001rq8xdbd0rbnw6','Anahata Beachfront Retreat','## Top Reviews
> "This place is paradise on earth.  So chilled, beautiful beach,  great food and fantastic staff. Our cottage was really spacious and the kids loved every minute if it. The smoothies and juices were a fantastic boost in the morning to get us going for the day all made with the freshest of ingredients. We can''t thank you enough Anahata for looking after us this Christmas. We are going home full of energy and high on life,  all thanks to you."
> **- Andrea Mcmahon (5/5/5)**

> "I think the best time to write a review is a few weeks after the happening. It allows one to settle into a normal daily routine which highlights all things magical even more. Needless to say, MAGICAL is exactly the word that pops to mind when thinking of Anahata Resort. First, let''s talk about people. Our fearless leader/organizer Annabel was more than just a program coordinator, she helped with all things imaginable, including friendly chats, tweaks to events and appointments, and her constant reassuring presence. No question was too strange, no request impossible. The other person of note was Simon, the Reiki master extraordinaire. Never before have I been taken to such colourful journeys! The Reiki sessions left me floating an inch above ground, feeling light as a feather, without a worry in the world, and loving everyone and everything in equal measure. This, if I may, should be an integral part of your visit to Anahata. And then there were the incredible masseuses, the always helpful and kind restaurant staff, the knowledgeable and wise tea ceremony master, the fit and fabulous personal trainer (careful, ladies - bring a bib), the amazing and ageless aqua-fit trainer and a myriad of talented yoga teachers. I felt pampered, cared for, heard and cherished, every step of the way. As for the surroundings ... I am an early riser and found myself on the water''s edge very early in the morning, before the sunrise, often greeted by the resident voluntary guards (three fabulous doggies) who checked me out to make sure I was "
> **- Giia Weigel (5/5/5)**

> "Anahata! What a wonderful place to stay at. We planned on staying 2 nights, and it ended up to be a week. The staff was kind, the amenities were great, spacious rooms, sufficient selection in breakfast (with fresh coffee!). We enjoyed every activity which they offered: muay tai and yoga lessons, paddling board and kayak, sauna, well equipped gym and 2 pools. Best in my opinion for couples who seek a quiet place in the island. Thank you Rey and all the kind people we met."
> **- עדן לוי (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/anahata-beachfront-retreat-1.jpg','077 485 775','M2, 95/70, LIpanoi, ตำบล ลิปะน้อย อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.anahatasamui.com/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.909+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.909+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/anahata-beachfront-retreat-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/anahata-beachfront-retreat-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8696877396906265736',NULL,NULL);
