> **- Giia Weigel (5/5/5)**

> "Anahata! What a wonderful place to stay at. We planned on staying 2 nights, and it ended up to be a week. The staff was kind, the amenities were great, spacious rooms, sufficient selection in breakfast (with fresh coffee!). We enjoyed every activity which they offered: muay tai and yoga lessons, paddling board and kayak, sauna, well equipped gym and 2 pools. Best in my opinion for couples who seek a quiet place in the island. Thank you Rey and all the kind people we met."
> **- עדן לוי (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/anahata-wellness-1.jpg','077 485 775','M2, 95/70, LIpanoi, ตำบล ลิปะน้อย อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.anahatasamui.com/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.912+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.912+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/anahata-wellness-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/anahata-wellness-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8696877396906265736',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('andre-beach-bar-restaurant','standard','cmr07ifwi001tq8xdlt824hit','Andre Beach Bar & Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "We had an amazing evening dinner here. Service, atmosphere and service all five stars. The best Masaman curry I have had and my husband had the spagetti with meatballs which was also amazing. Highly recommended. We loved the setting right  on the beach."
> **- Pella Vee (5/5/5)**

> "Hands down the best restaurant on the island. Sa and Andre are so hospitable and the food is out of this world good. We try not to go to the same place twice when on holiday, but we went back three times to Andre’s. Every time as good as the last. The food is delicious and beautifully presented. It’s great value too. Tables are literally on the sand, an amazing place to have dinner."
> **- DJ 001 (5/5/5)**

> "Beautiful restaurant with lovely seating right on the beach — a perfect spot to relax. We had amazing spaghetti: one with lemon and shrimp, and the other with meatballs, both were excellent and full of flavor. If you’re looking for a change from Thai food, this place is definitely worth a visit. Highly recommended."
> **- Matúš Polakovič (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/andre-beach-bar-restaurant-1.jpg','081 677 4530','160 12, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.914+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.914+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/andre-beach-bar-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/andre-beach-bar-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13715466054909529701',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('animalia-pet-hospital','standard','cmr07ifwk001uq8xd59udmxuq','Animalia Pet Hospital','## Top Reviews
> "We went to this animal hospital for our dog''s treatment, and they quoted us 15,000 baht for stitches and care alone for the wound shown in the photo. When we realized the price was too high, they referred us elsewhere without even dressing the wound. Our dog was injured and in critical condition, but they did nothing."
> **- Mert Karakoç (1/5/5)**

> "Five days ago, we had our dog''s internal organs ultrasounded at Animalia Pet Hospital. The doctors and staff at this veterinary clinic provided us with excellent, attentive service, loving care for our dog, and a flawless examination. The ultrasound lasted an hour, and our dog tolerated it well. After the ultrasound, we were provided with all the materials (ultrasound screens) of each organ and the doctor''s report on each internal organ examined. The cost was completely justified for such a veterinary service. The doctor and staff are highly qualified, and the ultrasound equipment is excellent. We are very satisfied and grateful, and we highly recommend Animalia Pet Hospital. I give it 5 stars, but I would give it 10 if I could."
> **- Tatiana Samoilova (5/5/5)**

> "Avoid - they are incompetent and probably not trained veterinarians at all.  My cat was bitten by another cat - I brought her and they “found nothing” and sent us home.  Next day she has an abscess - if they just gave my cat antibiotics which would be NORMAL procedure … this wouldn’t have happened."
> **- Michael Gorodi (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/animalia-pet-hospital-1.jpg','095 257 7015','4169, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/Animaliavetsamui/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.916+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.916+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/animalia-pet-hospital-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/animalia-pet-hospital-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4951629449924204064',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('annie-eatery-sweetery-fishermans-village','standard','cmr07ifwn001vq8xda9wxqjf6','Annie Eatery & Sweetery','## Top Reviews
> "Sensational Flavours & Vibrant Vibes!  I’ve visited a few times now, and this spot never ceases to amaze me. If you eat with your eyes first, you’re in for a total feast—the food is consistently presented with such vibrant, juicy colours that it almost looks too good to eat.  The Raspberry Coffee: This was the absolute standout. I’ll be honest, I wasn’t sure the combination would work, but I was hooked after the first sip. It’s perfectly balanced and kept me coming back for more. A must-try for anyone looking for something unique!  The Fruit & Grain Bowls: Incredibly fresh. The dragon fruit and passion fruit were bursting with flavour, and the side servings of chia pudding and granola added the perfect crunch.  The Savoury Plates: The omelette with grilled asparagus and king oyster mushrooms was cooked to perfection—light, earthy, and very satisfying.  Sweet Treats:The banana toast drizzled with chocolate and peanut butter was the perfect indulgent-yet-healthy finish.  The atmosphere is bright and welcoming, making it the perfect place for a slow brunch. Whether you’re here for a caffeine kick or a full meal, the quality is top-notch."
> **- Victoria Gill (5/5/5)**

> "Great service and such a lovely experience! The staff were very friendly and welcoming. I ordered The eggs Benedict was rich and flavorful, and the matcha latte was smooth and perfectly balanced everything was so delicious. Loved it! 🍵✨I will definitely come back next time I visit Koh Samui and bring my family ❤️"
> **- Phonphan Misuek (5/5/5)**

> "Definitely a new favourite. The atmosphere was quiet and calm, the food was fantasy as always and the service was good. We always order the soups, and can definitely recommend them with a crispy baked bun."
> **- Alrike Coetzee (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/annie-eatery-sweetery-fishermans-village-1.jpg','063 625 9210','124 Thanon Had Lamai, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://annieeaterysweetery.app.link/ZxZyPeNH5Nb','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.919+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.919+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/annie-eatery-sweetery-fishermans-village-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/annie-eatery-sweetery-fishermans-village-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6523700234723286639',NULL,NULL);
