INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('anodas-spa-signature','standard','cmr07ifwx001yq8xdig5jv46t','Anodas Spa Signature','## Top Reviews
> "Me and my wife experience at Anodas Spa was nothing short of exceptional, thanks to the outstanding therapists Meena and Moni . Their work reflects a rare blend of deep expertise, intuitive understanding, and absolute professionalism.  Their couple Siam refreshing Package is a must try for those seeking to relieve their pent up stress.  From the very beginning, both Meena and Moni maintained a strictly professional approach, ensuring complete comfort and dignity throughout the session. Their conduct was impeccable—graceful, respectful, and focused entirely on delivering a high-quality therapeutic experience.  What truly sets them apart is their mastery over technique. Every movement was precise, well-paced, and clearly backed by strong training and experience. They seemed to instinctively understand pressure points and areas of tension, resulting in a massage that was not only relaxing but genuinely rejuvenating.  In an industry where professionalism and skill can vary, Meena and Moni stand out as exemplary practitioners. I would highly recommend them to anyone seeking a refined, authentic, and truly satisfying spa experience."
> **- BNI Rushabh Shah (5/5/5)**

> "Had a great experience, so much relaxing massage and also the ambiance and staff are really good.It was really nice to be here🥰"
> **- Gulalai Kifayat (5/5/5)**

> "We treated ourselves to a 2.30-hour couple’s package at Anodas Spa, and it was hands-down one of the best spa experiences we''ve ever had. We started with a Thai herbal steam, followed by a body scrub and a tailored facial. They use premium Phytomer products, and my skin felt absolutely glowing and rejuvenated afterward. The attention to detail here is unmatched-from the temperature of the room to the skill of the masseuses. It felt like a truly authentic Thai luxury experience. It''s incredibly convenient to just stroll over from your villa and melt into total relaxation. Highly, highly recommend!"
> **- Barun Singh (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/anodas-spa-signature-1.jpg','077 913 555','111 ม.5 เชิงมน Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.noraburiresort.com/spa-samui.html',NULL,'cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.929+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.929+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/anodas-spa-signature-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/anodas-spa-signature-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14381796185530809247',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('another-world-vr-arena','standard','cmr07ifx00020q8xdkcda9gvw','Another World VR Arena','## Top Reviews
> "We visited this VR place because of the great reviews, but our experience was mixed. We didn’t choose the hardest game, just a normal one, since an “easy” option felt more like something for kids. However, the game turned out to be much harder than expected. Instead of being advanced in a fun way, it was confusing and frustrating.  The staff knew it was only our second time playing VR. While setting us up with the controllers, they could see we needed explanations, but no proper guidance or better recommendation was given. A more professional approach would be to match the game to the customer’s experience so people can actually enjoy it.  We tried to continue, but when nothing worked, it stopped being fun and we finished much earlier. Afterward, we asked about a possible discount because the experience and price didn’t match. We were only told that we chose the wrong game and should try another time, which felt unprofessional.  With such a high rating, we expected more focus on creating a great experience, not just selling games."
> **- Sabína Cepka (1/5/5)**

> "They’ve got a huge selection of games to choose from, loads of space to move around, and the air conditioning is brilliant — especially on hot days. The seating is super comfortable too, which makes the whole experience even better. I often come here with my son and we always have a great time. Highly recommend it for families or anyone looking for something fun and different to do on the island!"
> **- George Willoughby (5/5/5)**

> "The horror game that we chose was completely not user-friendly and we stopped it in the first half of the time, we asked for another game to play and would pay additional money, but was not possible. Also, we needed to pay the full price, even if we just played half of the 45 minutes. Maybe it was just the game we chose, but we had a terrible experience. It was very frustrating and definitely not cheap.  ——— Edit after the answer from Another World Samui VR Club: We was not a team, we were 2 persons only and are really shocked how you lied in your answer. It shows again how unprofessional this place is run… i was even writing it in a nice way that probably because of the game we chose.  For all the people who are thinking about to go there,  go to the other VR place in Koh Samui also in Chaweng. The VR games are more user friendly für groups, couples and kids and in much more realistic VR Games"
> **- Joshua (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/another-world-vr-arena-1.jpg','097 270 5512','209, 2nd floor, Central Festival Mall, 209/1-2 หมู่ที่ 2 ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://samui.another-world.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.932+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.932+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/another-world-vr-arena-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/another-world-vr-arena-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16154609634280449159',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ant-pool-maintenance','standard','cmr07ifx30021q8xd84w6gww9','Ant Pool Maintenance','## Top Reviews
> "We had a crack in our pool filter multi port and asked ANT team to look at options. In the end, we replaced the filter and multi-port. ANT quoted, delivered and installed our new filter. Seamless from start to finish and the installation was efficient and super tidy workmanship. Highly recommend!"
> **- Tracey (5/5/5)**

> "I always get prompt service and fair prices for my pool supplies"
> **- Mai Thai (5/5/5)**

> "The staff provided excellent and friendly service. Delivery was fast."
> **- Dares Panpariyes (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ant-pool-maintenance-1.jpg','+6677961285','26 6, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.antpoolgroup.com/','["Monday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM","Thursday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM","Friday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM","Saturday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM","Sunday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.935+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.935+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ant-pool-maintenance-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ant-pool-maintenance-2.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ant-pool-maintenance-3.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7708538425984309966',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('antica-locanda','standard','cmr07ifx50022q8xdkphyjwnh','Antica Locanda','## Top Reviews
> "We had a fantastic dining experience at this Italian restaurant. From the very first bite, it was clear that everything was made with passion and high-quality ingredients. The pasta was perfectly cooked, the sauces were rich and flavourful, and the wood-fired dishes had that amazing authentic touch you can only get from true Italian cooking.  The ambiance was cozy and elegant, making it perfect for both a relaxed dinner and a special night out. The staff were attentive, friendly, and incredibly knowledgeable about the menu. They offered great recommendations and made us feel welcome throughout the entire meal.  Every dish was beautifully presented, and the desserts were absolutely unforgettable—especially the tiramisu, which was light, creamy, and simply perfect.  An outstanding restaurant from start to finish. Highly recommended for anyone looking to enjoy real Italian flavours with top-notch service. We definitely  return every week."
> **- GOLAN TACTICAL (5/5/5)**

> "Food is just amazing, the portions are generous, the ingredients fresh, I come to eat here at least few times a month since I discovered the place, 100% recommended."
> **- Luca Civi (5/5/5)**

> "Famous pizzeria in BangRak for many years but always a reference for Italian food and wood-fired pizzas with a great choice. The staff is very friendly"
> **- Jean-Marc Regamey (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/antica-locanda-1.jpg','077 960 803','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.937+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.937+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/antica-locanda-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/antica-locanda-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1565449604589966945',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('aquamaster','standard','cmr07ifx70023q8xd7v35b689','Aquamaster','## Top Reviews
> "Friendly, helpful staff and a really easy shopping experience. Fon took great care of us—answered all our questions and helped us find exactly what we needed without any upselling. Prices were reasonable too. Definitely recommend for scuba gear and supplies."
> **- Luke Randall (5/5/5)**

> "I had such a great experience working with Fon! She  was so professional and knowledgeable. As a newly certified diver she explained everything I need in detail. Highly recommend buying from Aquamaster!"
> **- Lauren Nardi (5/5/5)**

> "I bought swim fins at Aqua Master and I am absolutely satisfied. The products they offer seem very high-quality and professional. I would especially like to mention the great advice from Steve. He is a very friendly person with a lot of experience, takes time for his customers, and gives honest and competent recommendations. You immediately notice that he knows a lot about diving equipment, the local waters, and the diving areas. The customer service was excellent, friendly, and personal. I have now found the shop where I will buy my equipment in the future. Highly recommended!"
> **- A Kidis (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/aquamaster-1.jpg','077 430 360','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.aquamaster.net/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 1:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.939+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.939+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/aquamaster-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/aquamaster-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=284752604546947629',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('arkbar-beach-club-resort','standard','cmr07ifxb0025q8xd8x2akh47','ARKbar Beach Club & Resort','## Top Reviews
> "⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ Arkbar Hotel – An Amazing Experience!  I stayed at Arkbar Hotel in Thailand and had an incredible experience. The service was outstanding – the staff was friendly, professional, and always available for anything I needed.  The location is unbeatable – close to everything! Restaurants, nightlife, shops, and the beach are all within walking distance, making the stay extremely convenient and fun.  I booked the large room facing the pool – it was spacious, comfortable, and the view created an amazing vibe throughout the day.  The atmosphere is definitely the highlight – a DJ playing from 2:00 PM until 2:00 AM, with great music and an energetic vibe all day and night. The pool area also includes a pool table, and the pool itself is right by the beach – a perfect combination.  It’s important for me to mention that I had several rooms at the hotel, but none were registered under my name – so I did not receive any special or preferential treatment. This reflects a genuine and unbiased experience.  Overall – excellent service, perfect location, and an unforgettable atmosphere. Highly recommended, and I will definitely come back! 🔥🌴"
> **- Gil Carmi (5/5/5)**

> "While Ko Samui generally offers a quieter atmosphere compared to the more intense party scenes of Phuket, Pattaya, or Bangkok, there are places that provide a lively experience. One such spot is Ark Bar, known for bringing a different kind of energy to the island. Located right on the beach, Ark Bar creates a vibrant environment that contrasts with the usual tranquility of Ko Samui. It''s a popular choice for those looking for excitement after dark, transforming the peaceful beach setting into a dynamic party zone. The venue is known for its energetic atmosphere, featuring pulsating DJ sets and lively beach party vibes that blend with the serene ocean backdrop. The festivities often last into the early morning hours, typically concluding around 2 or 3 AM. For anyone on the island seeking a memorable late-night experience that combines a relaxed setting with an electric energy, Ark Bar stands out as a key destination."
> **- Nasir (4/5/5)**

> "ARKbar Beach Club on Koh Samui was very clean, spacious, and well maintained with a really nice overall setup. The music was good and created a relaxed but still lively atmosphere throughout the day. It was not overcrowded at all when we were there, which made it easy to enjoy everything without stress or noise. I spent the whole day chilling in the pool and just relaxing, which was exactly what I was looking for. The vibe is perfect if you like listening to music while you relax and enjoy the sun. If you prefer absolute silence and a very calm environment, then this might not be the right spot, but for a fun, easygoing beach club day it’s definitely a great choice."
> **- Stephan Z. (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/arkbar-beach-club-resort-1.jpg','077 413 333','4 1 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.ark-bar.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 2:00 AM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.943+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.943+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/arkbar-beach-club-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/arkbar-beach-club-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7146813543046316938',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('armandos','standard','cmr07ifxe0026q8xdktaayhgu','Armando''s','## Top Reviews
> "Such nice food, had the creamy mushroom pork with noodles(pasta) and sausage with onion, with fried grated potato... So delicious... And the mango smoothie was fresh and real flavour, not sweetened with sugar and syrup. And the fried banana with honey dip was amazing also"
> **- systemchris (5/5/5)**

> "We came here on the first day visiting Ko Samui, the owner was very kind and made sure we enjoyed our lunch. Everything was delicious, we recommend!"
> **- Sara Gomboc (5/5/5)**

> "Good food! And friendly owner from swiss"
> **- Matic Vrtačnik (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/armandos-1.jpg','080 536 7506','Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 10:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:30 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifs1000cq8xdfo2aau32','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.946+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.946+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/armandos-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/armandos-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2780787226668522873',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('aromi-diversi','standard','cmr07ifxi0028q8xdljwmhrk4','Aromi Diversi','## Top Reviews
> "Such a bad experience. We ordered burrata as a starter, but when it arrived, it was missing the olive oil and balsamic vinegar that normally come with it. When I asked the lady for them, she gave me an unpleasant look and brought them in a way that felt disrespectful. The service overall was terrible. We ordered and had to wait 1 hour for our food. A group who ordered after us got served first, even though they were 7 people while we were only 2. We still had to wait over an hour, and no one even apologized. On top of that, the food was disappointing — the fries were oily and not fresh, and the steak was way too salty. The prices weren’t cheap either, so we at least expected good service and a better experience."
> **- Doha Kassouri (1/5/5)**

> "Fine place, but food is average. Four cheese with just little bit Gorgonzola and SOMEHOW tomato paste. Little cheese in pesto pasta. Service could be better for the price."
> **- Nikita Gorokhov (4/5/5)**

> "We stumbled upon this place by accident and it turned out to be a really lovely surprise. The Italian food in Thailand honestly impressed us, food was tasty and well prepared. You can tell they pay attention to the little details. Big compliments to the whole team for a great experience."
> **- Ana Jurić (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/aromi-diversi-1.jpg','095 298 7851','37, 10, Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 11:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 11:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 11:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 11:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 11:30 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifxh0027q8xde6xqk8o6','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.950+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.950+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/aromi-diversi-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/aromi-diversi-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17278701257947431971',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('art-cafe-by-june','standard','cmr07ifxm0029q8xd6r8hk1rl','Art Cafe By June','## Top Reviews
> "I love Art cafe by June! I recommend it to anyone as the menu has more than plenty of options, the food is delicious and healthy. The carrot cake is amazing, the pumpkin soup too, the breakfast too and the vegetable spring rolls.. I’m sure the rest of the menu as well! The staff is impeccable and the atmosphere is perfect, you take off your shoes, get a glass of water to enjoy the thoughtful decoration and ambience. So much love to this place which is taken care of with so much love as well!"
> **- Maria Eugenia C e Russel (5/5/5)**

> "Wow, this Place is amazing if you want healthy, delicious food made with love. The carrot cake and pumpkin soup were the best ones I had in my life. All the food is sooo good and the vibe in this unique Place is calm, creative and inspiring. Thank you so much. I will come back for sure."
> **- Jennifer Attenberger (5/5/5)**

> "My favorite cafe In Samui. Khun June really created a perfect cafe. The food is amazing as ever and the vibes from this place are so peaceful. Staff is so kind and smiling always."
> **- sidharth singh (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/art-cafe-by-june-1.jpg','061 180 9995','Thailand, 4169 ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.954+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.954+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/art-cafe-by-june-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/art-cafe-by-june-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14909431523802050351',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('art-in-mind','standard','cmr07ifxq002aq8xdcdbocpge','Art In Mind','## Top Reviews
> "My daughter is studying at Art in Mind, and it has been such a wonderful experience. The school is truly amazing – she really enjoys her art classes and always looks forward to them. She has learned so many new things, not only about art but also about expressing her creativity with confidence. Thank you so much to the teachers for creating such a fun and inspiring environment!"
> **- Soink (5/5/5)**

> "Great place for kids on the island. Where they can show up their unlimited creativity and imagination. Plus, good coffee and beautiful people here . Good vibe! Highly recommended."
> **- Tonmai Wongtanaposil (5/5/5)**

> "Going to Art in Mind revitalized me in my soul. The space is absolutely breathtaking with lots of greenery, fresh air, and an amazing little cafe. Just these 3 elements are enough to inspire you to create in her space. Kru Gae is exceptional at what she does and her methods of teaching is catered differently to individualize the experience of the student. She allows me to create outside the box of “acceptable school trained art” and I appreciate her for letting me just play almost everyday there. We are like a community here. Come join us why don’t you? :)"
> **- Jaspreet Narang (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/art-in-mind-1.jpg','085 448 3020','42, 102 Chaweng Yai, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/artinmindsamui','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Wednesday: Closed","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.958+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.958+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/art-in-mind-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/art-in-mind-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8246970634845284775',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('art-in-paradise','standard','cmr07ifxu002bq8xd85jpw6eq','Art In Paradise','## Top Reviews
> "> This place is an absolute dream! > > The care, enthusiasm, professionalism, creativity, and innovative approach are beyond anything we could have hoped for. > > Our children can''t wait to come back every single day and are always sad when it''s time to leave. > > A heartfelt recommendation from our family — this place is truly something special. ❤️✨"
> **- MISHKA Designs (5/5/5)**

> "We stumbled across Ump on instagram and while home schooling was looking for an art class for our 4 year old! Thank GOODNESS for Art in Paradise! Our daughter was made to feel like home. She did an amazing art project and was so engaged! Love seeing her artistic side come out! So beautiful and can’t wait to go back!! Thanks again!"
> **- Carlie Cardle (5/5/5)**

> "Proud to be the part of this amazing art space. Always creative, modern, very child oriented and friendly. Thank you, teacher Um to be the best art teacher ever!"
> **- Kateryna Denysova (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/art-in-paradise-1.jpg','089 959 6691','Near Chaweng noi, Bo Phut, Surat Thani 84320 bophut Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.instagram.com/art.in.paradise.studio/','["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Saturday: 9:30 AM – 2:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.962+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.962+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/art-in-paradise-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/art-in-paradise-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6435350879122295263',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('art-lab-asia','standard','cmr07ifxx002cq8xd9oqjauzu','Art Lab Asia','## Top Reviews
> "I couldn''t be happier with my experience with Art Lab Asia. Hugo created a Memphis Milano-inspired Treetops Floor Lamp for me, and the result exceeded all expectations. The craftsmanship is fantastic, it looks incredible in person, and it''s clear a great deal of care went into every detail.  The lamp arrived in perfect condition to Amsterdam (Netherlands), professionally packaged, and everything worked flawlessly right out of the box. From communication to production and delivery, the entire process was smooth and reliable. I can wholeheartedly recommend Art Lab Asia to anyone looking for unique, high-quality custom pieces."
> **- Péter Dávid Kormányos (5/5/5)**

> "This company and its owner really deserve a 5 star review. After an accurate search online and on site for a particular sofa for our new home, we trusted Hugo and we ordered a Camaleonda sofa replica. Hugo was very professional, prepared and helpful since the first contact. We couldn’t be happier of our choice: the sofa is perfectly made, quality fabric and comfortable. Also the delivery package was very accurate and secure (we are in Italy). As we already did with our friends, we really recommend to buy your quality forniture from Hugo. We will definitely buy other design products from this company!"
> **- Marcella Devoto (5/5/5)**

> "I am writing this review because I, like you, was extremely concerned with the legitimacy of this company and whether or not I’d actually receive my order. I can confirm that not only is the company legitimate, I received my product, and Hugo was an absolute pleasure to work with. He truly held my hand through the entire process. I received my chair and it is in excellent condition! I am so happy!"
> **- alex faren (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/art-lab-asia-1.jpg','+66917426511','111, M3, Tambon Taling Ngam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.artlabasia.com/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ift8000pq8xd7yujz20i','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.965+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.965+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/art-lab-asia-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/art-lab-asia-2.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/art-lab-asia-3.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6443694333292004501',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('art-n-design','standard','cmr07ify1002dq8xdd8fyhyjh','Art ''n'' Design','## Top Reviews
> "I’ve had a lovely experience here! The lady that sews the dresses is really kind and helpful, she picked just the perfect dress for me that I would have missed. She helps with the colours, shape and size. She can also change the clothes a bit to fit you better! Definitely recommend. My dress was 950 THB which is not cheap, but I think it’s a fair price for an unique pair of clothing. PS: The dress on the picture is not the one I got, but it was really cute too so maybe it’ll your new dress :)"
> **- Julia Kadłubska (5/5/5)**

> "Lovely shop with incredibly kind owners. I came for the great selection of second-hand English books, and you can also donate your books here. The owner also creates beautiful, unique handmade clothes, accessories, and art — a truly talented lady! Definitely worth a visit."
> **- Sappie (5/5/5)**

> "This shop is a little haven to step into out of the heat. We had a lovely experience chatting with couple who own this shop. The very charming female owner is from generations of seamstresses and she makes beautiful clothing for the store. The owners offered us a refreshing herbal drink while we shopped. The inner sanctum of the store is a bookshop with many good English and German books so if you run out of reading material this is the place. The Couple both also produce artwork for the store. A great experience highly recommend!"
> **- Eleni Kypridis (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/art-n-design-1.jpg','088 017 3420','63 Plai Laem Soi 4, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://web.facebook.com/Art-n-Design-Samui-110322254977810','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifv2001aq8xdag7cvjgf','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.969+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.969+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/art-n-design-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/art-n-design-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=18175849042621368765',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('artzone-samui','standard','cmr07ify3002eq8xdcv6drcnh','Artzone Samui','## Top Reviews
> "My kids said the teacher was rather strict. My kids asked to leave early and this caused a problem with the teacher. He also let the kids use hot glue during the project and I thought this was a safety issue. My daughters friend got burned from the glue. I personally will not be going back"
> **- רחל אלמלח (1/5/5)**

> "The best place for kids on the island! Our girls are in love with this studio😍 Martin is amazing and can find a way to each kid’s heart. Kids alway spend very useful and creative time over there. Definitely recommend it! Must visit place for kids💯"
> **- Armen Decider (5/5/5)**

> "The best activities for kids on the island! Never boring, always fun and educational! Just remember to sign up beforehand 😅 there is an option for a sort of membership card which gives discount👍"
> **- Katya Dymshits (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/artzone-samui-1.jpg','082 697 8584','Unnamed Road, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.971+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.971+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/artzone-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/artzone-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16257589878392802933',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ash-tailors','standard','cmr07ify5002fq8xddqypahr3','Ash Tailors','## Top Reviews
> "I’m really happy with my new suit. Everything was done very quickly, and the quality is great for the price. The owner was very friendly and made the whole experience easy and enjoyable. The suit looks fantastic and fits very well. I would definitely recommend it."
> **- Noah Haschke (5/5/5)**

> "Very happy with this tailor. We stayed in Samui for 10 days, went around most of the tailors in the vicinity of the hotel. This one was the only one without an aggressive guy standing outside and wanting to sell. Went in, he seemed super calm and knowledgeable so I got a light linen suit made there. I couldn''t be happier, price was acceptable, Organisation and scheduling went easy and I never had to wait. Everything that was promised and agreed was delivered in full without any remarks on my end. Highly recommend this tailor compared to the other ones in fisherman village."
> **- Mathias Hoppe (5/5/5)**

> "I give a strong recomendation for ash tailor services. I ordered one 3 pieces suit, 5 shirts and 2 trousers. I asked for a specific design and I have received everything in great quality, perfect materials with great consultation and communication. Ash is not budget tailor. I would order wedding suit without hesitation from him... Prices are great too."
> **- Filip Beneš (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ash-tailors-1.jpg','094 807 2367','105, 111 Moo 1, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.ashtailorsamui.com/https://','["Monday: 10:30 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:30 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:30 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 10:30 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 10:30 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 10:30 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 3:00 – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.973+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.973+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ash-tailors-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ash-tailors-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17488118540422872338',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('asia-pool-security','standard','cmr07ifyb002gq8xdshx86t63','Asia Pool Security','Discover Asia Pool Security, a premier property and real estate located in Fisherman''s Village, Koh Samui. Find reviews, hours, and contact information.','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/asia-pool-security-1.jpg','080 685 3817','160/2 MOO1 1 er étage, porte 3 Building, Fisherman Massage ตำบล บ่อผุด BOPHUT, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,0.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.asiapoolsecurity.com/?utm_source=google&utm_medium=wix_google_business_profile&utm_campaign=7587742427362093213','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifw3001mq8xdy3gf4igo','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.979+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.979+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/asia-pool-security-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/asia-pool-security-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10020124506135683604',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('assure-thailand','standard','cmr07ifye002hq8xdkbj1894t','Assure Thailand','## Top Reviews
> "Within walking distance   Wonderful lady working the front desk speaks English very well and was a great help   Prices where close to online and happy to support the local economy"
> **- Jim Penrose (5/5/5)**

> "Excellent advice and a very warm welcome"
> **- Eric Pelle (5/5/5)**

> "Contrary to the reviews posted, I didn''t have a good experience with this particular agency. The group has three agencies, if I understand correctly, and I transferred my contract to another broker.  My main problem was the lack of information I received before signing. I asked as many questions as I could think of, but certain information specific to insurance rules wasn''t provided.  For example, after my initial insurance claim was denied, I asked to add the routine medical care option, and I was told it wasn''t possible during the contract term. Having this information before signing the contract would have made me think twice about adding this option from the start.  Following a second denied reimbursement, I emailed Ms. Bernet on November 3, 2023. I received her reply the next day stating that I don''t have general medical coverage and therefore I''m not entitled to reimbursement for my second hospital expense (an MRI of my ankle ligaments and a specialist consultation to check if I need surgery).  I replied the same day (November 4, 2023), and after she read my email 11 times, I still haven''t received a response.  Yes, they do know how many times an email has been read.  So I wanted to cancel the contract since it doesn''t suit my needs, but it''s impossible to cancel during the first year—another piece of information that wasn''t provided (perhaps it''s written in tiny print in the insurance policy, which I only received after payment).  I was hoping to reach an agreement with the agency, but with no response from them after 10 days, I decided to post this review.  Yours sincerely"
> **- Hugues Gerard (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/assure-thailand-1.jpg','063 083 0047','108/7 Moo 6 T.Maret T, ตำบล มะเร็ต อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.assurethailand.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.982+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.982+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/assure-thailand-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/assure-thailand-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2346951343999280783',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('astrococo','standard','cmr07ifyh002iq8xdq3fj0wzp','Astrococo','## Top Reviews
> "We only went this place to use the beach club. The beach was beautiful. There was Beach side lounge chairs, and bar available?. The place was clean and had a free parking lot"
> **- Kourosh Misaghi (4/5/5)**

> "If you’re thinking of booking, it’s worth checking in advance as the pool is currently empty and under construction.  This wasn’t mentioned when we booked online, and the pool was a big reason we chose this hotel. As a result, we decided to move hotels and didn’t stay, so can only comment on our booking experience. That said, we did receive a full refund, which we really appreciated."
> **- chloe (3/5/5)**

> "We have grown to enjoy our time here, the staff is very friendly both the cleaning service, the beach bar ❤️ and the reception. But there seems to be an issue in general in Thailand, and that is the matrasses. Why are they so hard?  I truly believe the mattress is what separates a hotel that sells out every season and earns repeat guests from one that doesnt.."
> **- Yasmin M (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/astrococo-1.jpg','077 458 274','124, on Lamai Beach behind Mcdonald 433 s Maret Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.coconutbeachsamui.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.985+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.985+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/astrococo-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/astrococo-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12491510779251313897',NULL,NULL);
