INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('au-bout-du-monde','standard','cmr07ifys002mq8xdm68n391d','Au Bout Du Monde','## Top Reviews
> "Truly magical. The entire experience is one of the best things I have done on Koh Samui and I have lived here now for many years. Erik and his wife are just the born hosts. But not only do they know how to make you feel comfortable, they also know their craft. The food looks and tastes absolutely delicious and Erik''s cocktails are truly a revelation. I was scared to get a juicy drink when I saw the amount of liquid. But it was an incredibly well balanced and very intense tasting cocktail and it looks fabulous on top. So much love for details. I cant wait to be back and bring more friends."
> **- Boris Lauser (5/5/5)**

> "My boyfriend and I went here in March and we absolutely loved it! The baths on the beach were amazing, as wel as the cocktails and the service. I would recommend everyone who is visiting Koh Samui to go here."
> **- Maud van Aerts (5/5/5)**

> "That experience was one of a kind, everything from start to finish. Gladys, Eric and their team truly knows how to host and make this time special. The food and wine pairing was fantastic. Cocktails were so strong, that everyone was laughing at the end. Also they went beyond when finding and returning my lost glasses on the island, which I am very grateful for. Thank you and hope to see you one more time"
> **- Joana Bataityte (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/au-bout-du-monde-1.jpg','096 356 8137','Tean Island, Koh Tan, Koh Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.auboutdumondekohtan.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifyr002lq8xdu4o1j1f1','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.996+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.996+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/au-bout-du-monde-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/au-bout-du-monde-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=613977032558170559',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('auayporn-resort','standard','cmr07ifyu002nq8xdvg9fx1g3','Auayporn Resort','## Top Reviews
> "Amazing, quiet, chill place with friendly staff. I extended my stay already 3x.  All the houses are in different colors and have their own parking spaces. There is a front and back balcony with a table and 2 chairs. Houses also have air-conditioning + kitchen equipment. There is also a big fridge which is nice because there is an outdoor kitchen. The resort also rents out pretty new scooters, 160click all in white.  Resort is clean and very well taken care of. Everyday staff is busy with keeping the roads clean, doing repares on the houses en they offer a neat cleaning service.  When you have any questions or issues. The contact on whatsapp is very good, and I fast reply back from the owner."
> **- Kelly Gorissen (5/5/5)**

> "Wonderful place and wonderful owners! I lived here for the best year on Koh Samui and I can say that the place is worthy of a rating of 6 out of 5. Incredible level of service and responsiveness ❤️ Thank you so much"
> **- Виктория Цыбулина (5/5/5)**

> "Rooms nice, everything you need, quite in the city. All staff members super friendly and helpful"
> **- ImKavi (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/auayporn-resort-1.jpg','098 382 5907','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'http://airbnb.com/h/a14apresort',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:10.998+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:10.998+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/auayporn-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/auayporn-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15404249369292711595',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('aurora-clinic','standard','cmr07ifyw002oq8xdw91h4nxv','Aurora Clinic','## Top Reviews
> "I did subbrow lift with Dr.Apiruk, plastic surgeon. I love the result with good and fast recovery. Doctor is very good and professional. You can go with your eyes close...I recieved a good care and professional treat by professional team. I will come back to do lower eyelid again next year ❤️❤️"
> **- Chantal Nossler (5/5/5)**

> "Had to remove filler that was placed in my chin and it looks absolutely horrible. It is not only over filled, but is crooked and uneven. There was also a small child in the room which is unsafe and completely unprofessional.  I would upload photos but its too embarassing.  Go somewhere else."
> **- Sara Jones (1/5/5)**

> "I did upper and lower eyelid surgery with Doctor Apiruk,plastic surgeon at the same time. I felt very well even it was a surgery. Great praise to the wonderful nurses holding my hands all the time so sweetly😘"
> **- Silvin Bruns (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/aurora-clinic-1.jpg','083 629 1446','Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.aurorahospital.co.th/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.000+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.000+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/aurora-clinic-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/aurora-clinic-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2518048971089089901',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('austrian-corner','standard','cmr07ifyz002pq8xd8sn0zg83','Austrian Corner','## Top Reviews
> "By far my favorite Restaurant in Koh Samui!!! Mario is a great host and his Team provides an excellent service! 🙏🏼👏🏼👏🏼👏🏼 Great Menu selection, especially if you are a Schnitzel lover like me🤤 Mario’s All-You-Can eat BBQ Saturday‘s & Wednesday‘s are also LEGENDARY and a must-experience event! Thanks Mario for being always a great host and even organizing for me a Beer from Switzerland…, good times! All the best and I will be back for sure👊🏼  Dominic 🫡"
> **- Dominic Frei (The Eagle) (5/5/5)**

> "Super BBQ food , cooked live on Wednesdays and Saturdays. Very very good value. Great place to meet. Mario is the best host . Highly recommend this place is you like hearty Austrian meat and salads."
> **- #A.J (5/5/5)**

> "First time was on a Wednesday. Had seats available. Third time was on a Saturday, no seats for about 15-20 min! Very popular weekend spot! Owner proudly walks around to each table offering a variety of meats from a platter. It''s not top quality but for the price... it''s a deal!!! Hot off the grill. The veggies are amazing! My fav is the cabbage and grilled hash potatoes. On Saturdays, later in the evening,  you get some fun karaoke. Oh... Did I mention the price... cheap!!! For such an amazing variety Austrian flavors!"
> **- EL NinJah (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/austrian-corner-1.jpg','080 579 0585','203/1 Maenam (Walkingstreet Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 12:00 – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 9:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.003+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.003+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/austrian-corner-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/austrian-corner-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2444431707893039991',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('avani-chaweng-samui-hotel','standard','cmr07ifz4002qq8xdjjbmtuk1','Avani Chaweng Samui Hotel','## Top Reviews
> "I stayed at Avani Chaweng for several nights during my trip through Thailand. While the hotel has a great location and the staff was generally friendly, my overall experience was mixed.  Unfortunately, the cleanliness of the room did not meet the standard I would expect for a hotel in this price range. I received stained towels on multiple occasions, the shower area was not properly maintained, and there were visible signs of mold on the ceiling.  I was also disappointed that access to parts of the pool and beach club area required additional payment, which was not clearly communicated beforehand. Furthermore, there was confusion regarding the included minibar and the promised 500 THB resort credit during check-out.  To the hotel''s credit, management responded professionally to my complaint and refunded the resort credit afterwards, which I appreciate.  Overall, the hotel has potential and a good location, but considering the price of over 4,000 THB per night, I expected a higher level of cleanliness and clearer communication."
> **- Joshua Horn (3/5/5)**

> "This was definitely one of the best hotels I have stayed in, in Thailand. The service was amazing, super friendly staff. The receptionist Fern was very nice and helpful. The only to downfalls are that the music from the seen beach club is very loud and the placement of the hotel is in the bottom of Chaweng so it’s kind of a long walk to centrum. But besides that would definitely recommend, especially if you’re a group of young people."
> **- Nora Page (4/5/5)**

> "I would like to give a special compliment to the hotel staff member Neng. He was extremely kind, professional, and always willing to help with a big smile. From the moment we arrived, he made us feel very welcome and taken care of. His service was excellent, and he went above and beyond to make our stay comfortable and enjoyable.  Employees like Neng truly make the difference in a hotel experience. Thank you for the great service!"
> **- יוסף מרגי (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/avani-chaweng-samui-hotel-1.jpg','077 956 808','209 Sala Koy Road Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.avanihotels.com/chaweng-samui?utm_source=GoogleMyBusiness&utm_medium=GMB&utm_term=ChawengSamui&utm_content=Home&utm_campaign=Google_GMB',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.008+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.008+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/avani-chaweng-samui-hotel-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/avani-chaweng-samui-hotel-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5869491587421542976',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('avani-samui-resort','standard','cmr07ifz7002rq8xdfch7bw80','Avani+ Samui Resort','## Top Reviews
> "We had a pleasant stay at Avani+ Samui Resort, and the true highlight of this hotel was definitely the staff. Every single person we interacted with was kind, welcoming, caring, and genuinely amazing. They really elevated the entire experience and made us feel very comfortable throughout our stay.  The room itself was beautiful, modern, and comfortable, with great amenities around the property. Since we stayed for 5 nights and unfortunately had rain almost nonstop for 4 of those days, we ended up spending a lot of time enjoying the pool, gym, and the pool/ping pong tables, which helped keep us entertained.  That said, there are definitely areas that need improvement, especially for a hotel that markets itself as a 5-star resort. The shower pressure was inconsistent and quite weak, making it difficult to properly wash shampoo and conditioner out of our hair. The fixed shower head was also leaking and spraying water everywhere, so we mostly relied on the detachable shower head instead.  The biggest disappointment was the food. We would strongly recommend skipping the breakfast, as it was very underwhelming the few times we tried it. The hotel restaurant in general was overpriced and unfortunately the food quality did not match the prices ( a bad cold cheeseburger and club sandwich were 1000 THB). After our first few meals, we ended up eating elsewhere for the rest of the trip. Do yourself a favor and drive 10–20 minutes to enjoy amazing local restaurants with far better food and prices.  Overall, this felt more like a solid 4-star hotel rather than a true 5-star experience, but the exceptional staff really made the stay worthwhile."
> **- Ana’s guide (4/5/5)**

> "We enjoyed the warm hospitality from reception to trainer to waiters for our stay in this beautiful resort. Special mention to K. Beam, K. Pekky, K, Panini, K. Diggy and K. Nick. Our heartfelt thanks for taking care of us during our stay here. You made our holiday even more memorable and we hope to see all of you soon.  Our room is beautiful but however one of the gate was damaged and drop off. Lucky no injury as the gate was quite heavy.  Location is definitely not that convenient but if you are looking to a quiet getaway with beautiful people to serve you and nice food, I would highly recommend this resort."
> **- Glan Lim (5/5/5)**

> "Our stay at Avani Samui was amazingly special. All of the staff do everything they can to make your stay perfect. My partner proposed to me during our stay and the restaurant manager khun Vivian helped him in secret to make everything perfect. Khun Vivian went above and beyond to help my boyfriend plan beforehand, helped him pick out the best spot on the beach for our engagement and stayed after her shift was finished to make sure the private dinner was amazing. We stayed in a pool villa room and it was exceptional. Every aspect of the hotel, from the friendly staff, to the unbelievable food and the beautiful setting is just fantastic and we can''t wait to return. Thank you!"
> **- Isabella Denn-White (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/avani-samui-resort-1.jpg','077 485 299','53/5 Moo 4, Phang Ka, ตำบล ตลิ่งงาม Koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.avanihotels.com/samui?utm_source=GoogleMyBusiness&utm_medium=GMB&utm_term=SunsetCoastSamui&utm_content=Home&utm_campaign=Google_GMB','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ift8000pq8xd7yujz20i','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.011+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.011+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/avani-samui-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/avani-samui-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10237117581360552614',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('azure-bar-grill','standard','cmr07ifzf002sq8xdu40utf3i','Azure Bar & Grill','## Top Reviews
> "We had veg khao sui, thai milk tea, and mango sticky rice. It was amazing, a must must try if you are in Koh samui"
> **- Nikita Vijay (5/5/5)**

> "The girl facing away come right up in my face as soon as I walk in and say ‘what you want’ very rudely. The woman looking at the camera was grabbing the menu out of my hands as I was still looking at it. Terrible service. I’ve been here past 2 nights spend over 1000 baht each time and tonight they just put me off with their behavior towards me. Awful experience."
> **- Joe (1/5/5)**

> "Love this place. Great cover music when I was there, which added to the lively and vibrant atmosphere. The staff were friendly and attentive, making sure we had everything we needed.  The menu offers a lot of variety, and everything we tried was delicious. I particularly enjoyed the Pineapple Fried Rice, which was served in a pineapple – it was both tasty and visually impressive. The ambiance is very modern and stylish, with comfortable seating and a relaxed vibe.  Overall, Hi Restaurant by ARKbar Beach Club is a fantastic spot for good food, great music, and a fun night out. Highly recommend if you’re in the area."
> **- Matt Cm (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/azure-bar-grill-1.jpg','097 925 3467','4, 1 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.3,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.ark-bar.com/hip-restaurant/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 2:00 AM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ift8000pq8xd7yujz20i','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.019+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.019+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/azure-bar-grill-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/azure-bar-grill-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3027004551481819899',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('baam','standard','cmr07ifzi002tq8xduvakth2y','Baam!','## Top Reviews
> "Really good gym and good price. Great selection of equipment, large airy building. No air con but I went in hot season and was fine as they have many fans. Definitely my favourite gym in Samui. Friendly staff too. I’m not sure why someone gave a bad review because of the state of equipment because it’s absolutely fine. The equipment is in good condition!"
> **- Tracey Wyatt (5/5/5)**

> "I regularly train here in badminton. During the hot season, it gets quite warm inside, but I’ve gotten used to it. I like the flooring, and the lights don’t glare into my eyes while playing. The court rental is 200 baht, and a personal training session with a coach costs between 700-1000 baht per hour. You can always buy drinks and snacks here, and there’s also a service for restringing racket strings.  Cons: The area in front of the building is full of potholes, and there’s no option to take a shower."
> **- Black Bird (4/5/5)**

> "Great gym. Very well equipped! You can do any type of training from functional to CrossFit to kettlebells. Dozens fans which is great for me but no AC, if that means something to you. Branded protein powder is very good and half the price of popular brands. Staff is pleasant. The lady “boss” not so much. But over all it’s one of the best gyms in Samui. No bro culture women feel comfortable here. Prices are reasonable."
> **- Caliph Herald (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baam-1.jpg','063 929 2622','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifuo0015q8xdfahzrsp4','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.022+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.022+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baam-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baam-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9372571535073062011',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('baan-bo-ran-village','standard','cmr07ifzm002vq8xdgolgxgp3','Baan Bo Ran Village','## Top Reviews
> "What a great place. Spotlessly clean and the food was fresh, very well presented and tasted fantastic. I went medium chilli and although quite hot it didn''t leave the mouth burning. However lips were tingling a bit😂. Lovely setting on a large pond. Gentle background music and the people serving us were very nice. If they were open tomorrow (Sunday) we would be back."
> **- Richard Walden (5/5/5)**

> "Wonderful atmosphere. The service is an 11. The food is very tasty. The portions are a bit on the small side but I get it because the prices are very reasonable."
> **- michael blanchard (5/5/5)**

> "April 2023 ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ 5 stars Thailand 🇹🇭 Koh Samui  Very nice and relaxing place. Good food with reasonable price. I am Thai and I found that the food was tasty and authentic Thai food. Dessert was yummy as well. Drinks were refreshing on a very hot day. I highly recommend. Thank you for your service 🙏"
> **- Onnida T (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baan-bo-ran-village-1.jpg','092 635 9745','7/2 Tambon Na Mueang, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/BaanBoranVillage/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifzl002uq8xdaadxjuc2','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.026+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.026+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baan-bo-ran-village-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baan-bo-ran-village-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5706907084662625530',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('baan-fah-resort','standard','cmr07ifzp002wq8xd52vdyxes','Baan Fah Resort','## Top Reviews
> "The hotel is located on the beachfront and is so lovely. The two ladies working on the reception were incredibly friendly and helpful.  We stayed in a beachfront room and a poolside room as we booked an extra night on Koh Samui, and both rooms were amazing. The AC was lovely, the bed was comfy and the bathroom was exceptionally clean.  We also had the breakfast which was tasty.  The only small issue is there are not many sunbeds and people do get up quite early to reserve them. But the beach and the view are gorgeous.  Highly recommend!"
> **- Jessica Steel (5/5/5)**

> "Such a nice hotel in a perfect location if you''re into a bit more peaceful environment. Still have 7-11, gym, thai massage spots, lots of restaurants and even a local night market at your convenience. 🤩 Staff is so helpful and breakfast is good. Rooms are kept clean and beach is enjoyable as well, with provided towels and sunbeds (usually reserved with towels/flipflops by other guests from 6:30 am onwards - nobody lying on them though.....). That''s the only downside but caused by other guests, not the hotel itself. Loved our stay and would stay there again!"
> **- Pipsa Ervasti (5/5/5)**

> "We stayed here for 3 nights and it was a lovely relaxing stay, very ideal if you’re wanting a relaxing few days on the beach. Ideal if you are wanting a quiet stay, not that many restaurant choices nearby but only a 10 minute taxi into busier more touristy areas. The rooms were spacious, simple and clean, and we loved our view to the beach. Beds were very comfy and bathroom had a good shower. Cafe food was basic but had everything you needed if you were hungry or thirsty. Staff were friendly. Only critique would be more beach beds, but isn’t a major issue. Would definitely stay here, great value."
> **- Beth Lyon (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baan-fah-resort-1.jpg','077 425 675','129/3-4 ตำบล แม่น้ำ Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://baanfahresort.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.029+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.029+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baan-fah-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baan-fah-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8403435968348362451',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('baan-haad-ngam','standard','cmr07ifzq002xq8xds8isx9nv','Baan Haad Ngam','## Top Reviews
> "What an amazing hotel - in a great location. It is close enough to action with a short ride to samui centre or chaweng road.  the beach was important for us and this has a really nice beach and a pool overlooking the beach. The attached restaurant Olivio has good quality and variety  A special shoutout to Rita and Pancake who made our stay very welcoming and were always supportive with our requests."
> **- Ayman Boulos (5/5/5)**

> "Wow...stunning hotel! The staff were friendly and could not do enough for you. The food was amazing. The rooms are all decorated to a very high standard. The grounds were beautiful, peaceful and chilled. This hotel is a definite  must, thouroghly recommend 👌 I will definitely be coming back"
> **- Leigh Foster (5/5/5)**

> "Enjoyable stay. Kind and friendly staff. Paid £75 for a standard room in semi low season - despite negative reviews about this grade room, I found it to be better than adequate with only a few tiny gripes which aren’t worth mentioning. Very nice location away from the noise. The Mediterranean restaurant is decent enough but it’s annoying when they add an unexpected 10% to the bill for taxes - IMO it’s better to be clear with the pricing. The hotel provide a free shuttle service twice a day into the heart of Chaweng. Would give 4.5 stars if possible."
> **- DSO Travels (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baan-haad-ngam-1.jpg','077 332 950','154, หาดเฉวง, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.baanhaadngam.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.031+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.031+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baan-haad-ngam-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baan-haad-ngam-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10175611632911633135',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('baan-hinlad-home-and-hostel','standard','cmr07ifzs002yq8xdaa7bgrzi','Baan Hinlad Home And Hostel','## Top Reviews
> "We only stayed one night here but if i could’ve chosen to stay longer, we would have. It was such a gorgeous spot right in the lush trees where you can sit peacefully in the garden. The room has a shutter door that opens up to the garden and this was my highlight. It’s so dreamy to sit here and chill away from loud busy areas. It’s about a 35 minute walk to the beach and shops but they have bikes here you can borrow anytime. It’s a 10 minute ride to a 7-eleven which was very convenient. The staff here are so friendly and welcoming too. If you’re considering booking this place honestly just do it- you can’t go wrong."
> **- Daisy Riley (5/5/5)**

> "The nicest and comfiest Hostel we stayed in since the beginning of our trip. It has a beautiful and quiet surrounding with a nice kitchen and backyard. Such a chill and lovely place. The owner is such a welcome, helpful and open guy that we instantly felt like at home."
> **- M. Drechsel (5/5/5)**

> "Beautiful place to stay on Koh Samui! The hosts are incredibly helpfull and kind and the place is very clean! The location is far away from most touristy things but the waterfall at the end of the street is fun to visit and there are some nice restaurants close by. There are also well maintained bicycles available that you can use for free and you can rent a scooter from them for a good price as well. We had an amazing stay and would highly recommend!"
> **- An-Sofie Merrie (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baan-hinlad-home-and-hostel-1.jpg','081 538 7237','72, Angthong, 6, Tambon Ang Thong, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.032+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.032+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baan-hinlad-home-and-hostel-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baan-hinlad-home-and-hostel-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1928330102441829898',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('baan-nai-rai-organic-farm-cafe','standard','cmr07ifzv002zq8xdzsrmua4p','Baan Nai Rai Organic Farm & Cafe','## Top Reviews
> "Baanairai Farm & Cafe is a hidden gem that perfectly blends nature, calm, and great taste. From the moment you arrive, you feel the peaceful atmosphere of the farm, green surroundings, open space, and a sense of slowing down that’s hard to find these days.  The coffee is excellent, made with care, and the food is fresh, flavorful, and thoughtfully prepared. Everything feels honest and high quality, without trying too hard.  What really makes this place special is the vibe: relaxed, welcoming, and authentic. It’s the kind of café where you can sit for hours, have meaningful conversations, work quietly, or just enjoy being present.  Highly recommended for anyone looking for great coffee, good food, and a refreshing break from the rush of everyday life."
> **- David Swissa (5/5/5)**

> "🩷🩷🩷 It felt like a little hidden world in the jungle 🥹🌿  Baannairai farm & cafe is so green, calm and cozy… you just sit and don’t want to leave.  Creamy mushroom pasta 🍝, papaya salad with shrimp 🥗 and a latte ☕️ everything simple and really delicious.  But what made it even more special… the girls working there 🥹 so kind, so warm, so genuinely sweet you feel taken care of in the nicest way.  Such a peaceful, happy place 🩷"
> **- Elvira (5/5/5)**

> "Lovely outdoor cafe set in a garden area. Delicious food and drinks. We are excited to come back and try more. We ordered the mushroom and avocado sourdough toast, spinach and mushrooms omelette, latte and tea."
> **- Nicole DiCristofaro (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baan-nai-rai-organic-farm-cafe-1.jpg','086 479 2559','Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: Closed","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.035+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.035+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baan-nai-rai-organic-farm-cafe-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baan-nai-rai-organic-farm-cafe-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8384531007492983616',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('baan-saitara-villas','standard','cmr07ig010030q8xd99a58k5a','Baan Saitara Villas','Discover Baan Saitara Villas, a premier accommodation located in Lamai, Koh Samui. Find reviews, hours, and contact information.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.041+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.041+00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('baanmharimlay-clinic-grooming','standard','cmr07ig030031q8xdw0idl1k2','Baanmharimlay Clinic & Grooming','## Top Reviews
> "Such a lovely vet clinic! The place is very clean and smells fresh. The vet is knowledgeable, skilled, and takes time to explain everything clearly. Communication in English is also excellent.  One thing I really love is the outdoor area behind the clinic where pets can walk and run around. Pet owners can sit back, relax, and enjoy the sea view while waiting. The overall vibe is calm, cozy, and very welcoming.  Highly recommend this place if you’re looking for great care and a beautiful, relaxing environment for your pet"
> **- TiKati W. (5/5/5)**

> "Extremely friendly and knowledgeable staff. We have always received the help we need for both our cat and our dog. They consistently provide excellent tips and advice, always delivered with a smile. The facilities are very clean and modern, and you always feel welcome there. They go the extra mile in ways you don’t expect, but that make such a big difference. I can highly recommend this clinic to anyone in need of a veterinarian. They are fantastic! 10/10"
> **- Förnamn Efternamn (5/5/5)**

> "Very caring and professional team. They gave great advice and took excellent care of my cat . Highly recommend!"
> **- Chonthicha Ruainin (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baanmharimlay-clinic-grooming-1.jpg','085 882 2334','Koh Samui, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.043+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.043+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baanmharimlay-clinic-grooming-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baanmharimlay-clinic-grooming-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14420489175039704648',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('babus-indian-restaurant','standard','cmr07ig060032q8xdk70d6yvm','Babu''s Indian Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "We visited Babu during the New Year''s holidays at the end of 2025. We attended the opening of his new restaurant. It was simply wonderful; he''s a wonderful person, a very caring owner. He put us up in his hotel first, which was a great honor for us. I remember his invitation to the restaurant opening, the food was delicious, and the atmosphere was lovely and homey. Babu is very sociable, we were a group of four, and he could keep up the conversation. The hotel and restaurant complex have a very convenient location, next to Mainam Beach, on a quiet street away from the busy road. We also used the car rental service. Thank you, Babu, for a fantastic vacation. We think of you often."
> **- Kirill Pechko (5/5/5)**

> "This was such a wholesome treat. After being in Thailand for 10 days we really started craving an Indian food & they delivered it so well. O had a chat with owner, his story. How he started the restaurant, man so much inspiring. Loved every part of his story & food at the same time.  Lovely hospitality, good food, good vibes! Next time we are in Koh samui surely will visit here again"
> **- Nilesh Sarswat (5/5/5)**

> "Delicious 😋 Fast friendly service 😁 and absolutely delicious.  Comfortable dining lounge with upbeat Indian music.  Did I mention the food was delicious.  Butter chicken and Allo Gobby with a garlic Nan and Papadams to start.  Perfect portions with medium spice as requested.  Highly recommend for residents and visitors to Koh Samui."
> **- OnlineFood Menus (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/babus-indian-restaurant-1.jpg','084 877 6034','44 Maenam 34, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/babusindianhot/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.046+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.046+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/babus-indian-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/babus-indian-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5902416356410494231',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('babysitter-samui','standard','cmr07ig080033q8xd4m406k3z','Babysitter Samui','## Top Reviews
> "Our 14-month-old twins found wonderful caregivers—and true friends—thanks to Rattana. Rattana and her assistants supported our family for three weeks during our stay in Ko Samui, and the experience was exceptional.  The boys genuinely loved spending time with them, which gave us complete peace of mind when leaving them in Rattana’s care. They enjoyed a wide variety of games and activities, all thoughtfully adapted to their interests and energy levels.  Rattana was consistently flexible and accommodating, readily adjusting to our changing schedule and needs. We are truly grateful to have met her and to have experienced such reliable, caring, and attentive childcare.  I highly recommend Rattana’s babysitting service to any family looking for a thoughtful, responsible, and trustworthy caregivers."
> **- Karina Collis (5/5/5)**

> "I had the service of Mam. The nanny service was for 8 days (8 hours/day) for my 11-month-old baby, and I couldn’t be happier. She was incredibly gentle, kind, and patient with my little one always positive and easygoing no matter the situation. My baby was in safe, loving hands. Highly recommend to any parent looking for a trustworthy and caring nanny! ❤️"
> **- Lienchi Lê (5/5/5)**

> "Exceptional Care from Samui Nanny Service - A Truly Heartfelt Experience  We had the most wonderful experience with Samui Nanny Service, entrusting our 1‑year‑old daughter to Nanny Mam. From the very first moment, we felt completely at ease. The entire process was smooth, professional, and incredibly kind.  Mam herself is a rare gem: warm, flexible, reliable, and deeply trustworthy. She cared for our daughter with genuine love, attention, and tenderness. It was clear every single day that she wasn’t just “doing a job” - she was giving her heart.  What touched us most was the emotional bond she built with our little girl."
> **- Friederike Rhein (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/babysitter-samui-1.jpg','093 962 6505','3, 88, Tambon Bo Put, Koh Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://samuinanny.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.048+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.048+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/babysitter-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/babysitter-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4237172628428763785',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('baci-italian-restaurant-bar-grill','standard','cmr07ig0b0034q8xdywnt7c3t','BACI Italian Restaurant Bar & Grill','## Top Reviews
> "We had the arrabbiata pasta and it was really flavorful, tiramisu was lovely and very well crafted. The ambience is beautiful, with tasteful decor and a very relaxing vibe. The service was excellent and the warmth of the owner really stood out.  We also tried the margherita pizza, which was good.  Overall, a top place for the service and the ambience. Highly recommended."
> **- Jai Sharma (5/5/5)**

> "I had the pleasure of dining at Baci Italian Restaurant in Koh Samui and also meeting the owner, Tiziana, a truly wonderful lady with 33 years of culinary experience and life on the island. Listening to her story and passion for Italian cuisine made the evening even more special. We started with a seafood salad, and it was outstanding. Every component was cooked perfectly tender, fresh and full of flavor. You can immediately tell that she knows exactly where to source the best fresh seafood in Thailand, which makes all the difference. The seafood spaghetti al cartoccio was another exceptional dish. The sauce was beautifully balanced, rich but not heavy, allowing the flavors of the seafood to shine. When I opened the bread crust of the cartoccio the aroma was incredible. I even used the bread to finish every drop of the sauce simply delicious. To finish the dinner we had a chocolate mousse, which ended the meal perfectly. The restaurant itself is beautiful, elegant and welcoming, with a lovely wood-fired oven that immediately shows the passion and professionalism behind this place. You can feel that this restaurant is built with experience, dedication and love for authentic Italian food. If you are looking for one of the best Italian restaurants in Koh Samui, Baci is absolutely a must visit. Highly recommended."
> **- Luca Foschi (5/5/5)**

> "In my opinion , this is the best Italian restaurant on the island . why ? This is the place where you can find other typical dishes than the classics ( which are also excellent ) . Portions are great , service is professional . Restaurant is very comfortable , with an A/C room too. Nice decoration . I had a pumpkin soup with shrimps and Gorgonzola and walnuts , it was so yummy . All dishes I’ve tasted there were amazing . They also improved their wine list , mostly Italian wines , but this time we had a Pouilly Fume. Will go again and again ."
> **- Sabai Glamping (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baci-italian-restaurant-bar-grill-1.jpg','065 032 3915','9, 287 Thanon Bond Kai, Bang Rak, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://baci-samui.com/','["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 6:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 6:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 6:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 6:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 6:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 6:00 PM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.051+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.051+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baci-italian-restaurant-bar-grill-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baci-italian-restaurant-bar-grill-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9650993114367595287',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('bad-ass-tattoo','standard','cmr07ig0e0035q8xdqjhiop7i','Bad Ass Tattoo','## Top Reviews
> "Last year when I was on Koh Samui, I got a tattoo at Bad Ass Tattoo Shop in Chaweng, and the experience was amazing. The artists were incredibly talented, the studio was super clean, and the whole vibe was just perfect.  This year I came back to Koh Samui again, but I’m staying on the other side of the island. Right in front of my hotel there was another tattoo shop, so at first I thought I’d just go there. But something didn’t feel quite right, and I kept thinking about the great experience I had at Bad Ass last year.  Then I found out that the shop in front of my hotel and Bad Ass Tattoo are actually owned by the same owner. At that moment it felt like a sign — like I was meant to get another tattoo here. I came to make right decisions again.  So I went back to Bad Ass Tattoo in Chaweng, and once again they absolutely nailed it. The artists are true professionals, they take their time, listen to your ideas, and the results are incredible. I couldn’t be happier with my new tattoo.  If you’re on Koh Samui and thinking about getting inked, I can’t recommend this place enough. Amazing artists, great atmosphere, and a team you can trust. Definitely a 5⭐ experience!"
> **- Premium PA (5/5/5)**

> "Great shop, A+! My girlfriend and I got a tattoo each. Great communication between us and the artists, with help of staff that speak great English. Shop is very professional and clean. Very fair price too! Excellent work and designs on our tattoos! Thanks for giving us so Great tattoo to remember our trip! Boss man, was very friendly and kind to us!  Also gave us a discount to their nicotine and weed shop next door."
> **- Kurt Schwarz (5/5/5)**

> "Very nice and inviting people. Studio also looks very nice and clean got free water and a beer to my tattoo! Tattoos are exactly as i wanted and they look stunning! These are my first tattoos and i''m so glad i chose this studio. I honestly really recommend these guys and hope they will have lots of customers."
> **- Matth Kühne (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bad-ass-tattoo-1.jpg','097 917 7111','13, 11 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://badasstattoo.shop/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 1:00 AM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 1:00 AM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 1:00 AM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 1:00 AM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 1:00 AM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 1:00 AM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 1:00 AM"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.054+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.054+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bad-ass-tattoo-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bad-ass-tattoo-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16037478671913592455',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('bad-monkey-hostel','standard','cmr07ig0h0036q8xdkiej3qsz','Bad Monkey Hostel','## Top Reviews
> "Planned to stay here for 3 nights extended to 4 as very very good hostel. Bathrooms are massive and lots of hairdryers to use. The staff are so lovely and kind and very attentive to what you need. Beds are very comfy. They offer a 50% wristband with the restaurant and bar below which is great and ended up going here 5 times! Would definitely stay again and recommend to others. Thank you to Lek who was so chatty and kind and made our stay great 10/10"
> **- Finley Webster (5/5/5)**

> "Great location right next to the mall, in a busy bar area and very close to the beach. The staff is lovely and welcoming. There’s a small outdoor sitting area, and the bathrooms are spacious  The rooms are a bit packed, and there was a slight damp, moldy smell. The mattresses are quite old and hard, and the bed makes noise with even small movements.  Overall, still a good budget option if you’re mainly there for the location"
> **- Benita Ahlf (4/5/5)**

> "Easily the best hostel in Samui, great location next to the beach and the nightlife.  Friendly staff and an amazing bar downstairs with the best food and drinks and pool tables and sports tv.  Ticks all the boxes and has a great vibe with sociable guests looking for a good time!  Defintely stay here"
> **- John (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bad-monkey-hostel-1.jpg','095 489 2140','90, 3, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://book-directonline.com/properties/badmonkeysamui',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.057+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.057+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bad-monkey-hostel-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bad-monkey-hostel-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=144547184881153620',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('baitong','standard','cmr07ig0j0037q8xd8phto3ss','Baitong','## Top Reviews
> "We had a very good experience during our stay at Banana Fan sea resort Hotel, especially the breakfast at Baitong Restaurant. The restaurant offered a wide variety of breakfast items on the buffet line, with many choices available for everyone to enjoy.  We especially enjoyed the Pad Thai, which was very delicious. The staff were friendly and attentive, and the atmosphere in the restaurant was pleasant and relaxing.  Overall, we had a wonderful stay and would be happy to recommend the hotel to others visiting Koh Samui."
> **- David Rashethie (5/5/5)**

> "Excellent food and service. Lot of vegetarian and vegan options. Aom, Van & Teng do a great job with the guests. They have live music, sea views and fire shows.  However, they should arrange “to go breakfast bags” for guests who are leaving early for airport or for excursions. You have to tell them 12 hours in advance which is not great."
> **- Abhishek Dubey (5/5/5)**

> "In the morning at Baitong Restaurant, there is a breakfast buffet with a wide variety of food all in one place. The highlight is the fresh juice corner, where juices are freshly squeezed every day, giving you a refreshing start to the morning."
> **- Thelover Cat (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baitong-1.jpg','077 413 483','201 หมู่ที่ 2 ถนน เฉวง, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.bananafansea.com/dining/','["Monday: 7:00 – 10:30 AM, 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 – 10:30 AM, 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 – 10:30 AM, 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 – 10:30 AM, 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 – 10:30 AM, 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 – 10:30 AM, 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 – 10:30 AM, 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.059+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.059+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baitong-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baitong-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10957101187729938354',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('bamboo-resort-samui','standard','cmr07ig0p0038q8xdhmuebqtf','Bamboo Resort Samui','## Top Reviews
> "Really nice jungle resort, human size, large commun pool, The rooms are large and give a sweet spot to relax !"
> **- Sebastien Hannoun (5/5/5)**

> "Very peaceful small resort. Highly recommended Joe the owner is very useful"
> **- Frederic Gimazane (5/5/5)**

> "Nice place. Beautiful garden Room and S pool super clean"
> **- Rosarin Jasmine (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bamboo-resort-samui-1.jpg','064 585 5967','108/10, soi 7, ตำบล แม่น้ำ อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://bamboo-resort-samui.webnode.fr/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 11:30 AM – 3:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.065+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.065+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bamboo-resort-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bamboo-resort-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=18196049141788797816',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ban-kao-tropical','standard','cmr07ig0s0039q8xdy5m2eb9y','Ban Kao Tropical','## Top Reviews
> "Just left the hotel after a month stay. I will mention the good points first: GM and owners’ son are really friendly and at ur disposal if u have any request. As we stayed a long time, a micro wave and a coffee machine were at our disposal in our room. Bankao area is quiet but that s what we liked, very rural. Hotel setting is very green in the middle of nature, very beautiful. Room size and design are nice. First night as we didn t have a scooter yet, they gave us a free ride to town to have Dinner. What I didn t like: cleaning of the room needs to be improved. Our room was cleaned every 4 days but after the cleaning, dust was visible on furnitures still and around bed area. We had loads of clothes moth at the beginning because of a traditional thai costume hanging in the room as decoration that probably was never vacumed and because of natural stones around the bath tub area that kept a lot of dust too. We asked the GM to remove this piece of decoration and it was done straight away. Bed was very unconfortable. Wifi is weak. There is no real « service » like you would expect a hotel to have, restaurant is closed most of the time. Our transfer from the hotel to the pier was supposed to be free, at least price was never mentionned and then driver charged us 500 thb which is kind of expensive due to the short distance."
> **- diana sotero (3/5/5)**

> "Staff is extremely helpful, they go above and beyond.  It is situated in the quiet area of Ban Kao, if you are looking for peace of mind, or looking for a cosy base this is perfect. Feels like a Great bachelor pad rather than a hotel.  Great value for money, I spent most of the day out and about, so this was perfect to return to and plan the next day and have a relaxing night.  You will definitely need transport to get to places from here."
> **- Amr Kamal (5/5/5)**

> "We stayed in one of the villa for one month and we had a great time. The driveway is rough but overall it’s great. It’s a complex of villas. I guess it would have the security if all villas were full. Our villa was big and cosy, 2b2b and we had a great time!"
> **- Karina & Martin (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ban-kao-tropical-1.jpg','077 920 035','69/6 Moo 4 T. Namuang, ตำบล หน้าเมือง อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.bankaotropical.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 9:30 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifzl002uq8xdaadxjuc2','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.068+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.068+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ban-kao-tropical-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ban-kao-tropical-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6768280809127062215',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ban-saket','standard','cmr07ig0z003bq8xd2nut7hsz','Ban Saket','Discover Ban Saket, a premier food and beverage located in Unknown, Koh Samui. Find reviews, hours, and contact information.',NULL,NULL,'Taling Ngam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,0.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.bluepillow.com/search/65c9e712671b07d23c684ad8?dest=bkng&cat=House&lat=9.47141&lng=99.93393&language=en',NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig0w003aq8xdfi0rydaw','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.075+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.075+00:00',NULL,'https://maps.google.com/?cid=17771171244386564736',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ban-suriya','standard','cmr07ig12003cq8xdse8vrra0','Ban Suriya','## Top Reviews
> "Ban Suriya was a spectacular wedding venue, and the location and scenery were absolutely amazing. The villa itself was kept very clean, and the amenities were perfect for our stay. We especially appreciated that there was plenty of room for everyone to have their own private areas when needed. The table tennis and pool tables were also a fantastic added bonus that our guests really enjoyed.  The staff were incredibly friendly and easy to deal with, and we loved that they were non-intrusive while still being attentive. Tik was wonderful, and nothing was ever too much for her to handle. She organized in-house massages for us very easily, which was a lovely touch. On top of the great service, we found all the charges to be very fair. It was a perfect experience from start to finish."
> **- Jena_ Vie (5/5/5)**

> "Ban Suriya is such a magical place! The minute I saw it I knew I had to have my wedding here and I couldn’t have been happier with everything! It was beyond perfect. The sunsets are STUNNING, the rooms are spacious and comfortable, the service was top notch and the villa manager Khun Tik was so helpful throughout our stay! She also makes her own yoghurt which was a surprising hangover cure for me and my friends :) The daily breakfast spread was also amazing each morning and the dinner they prepared for us was beautiful! Everything about this place was just such an incredible experience. We really appreciate all the efforts made by the Ban Suriya team to make our stay and our wedding event a truly exceptional one! Thank you so much! ❤️✨"
> **- Sarah Foo (5/5/5)**

> "Tik and the team have been amazing from beginning to end. The Villa is fantastic, it is very well maintained by the team at Villa Suriya who take pride in its overall upkeep. The location is paradise with direct beach access. We did notice we were the wrong side of the island for all the activities we wanted to do, though the cost of taxis are so reasonable that it didn’t matter. We plan to visit again in the future."
> **- Simon Rodd (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ban-suriya-1.jpg','02 544 0162','62/1 Moo 2, ตำบล ลิปะน้อย Koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.bansuriya.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.078+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.078+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ban-suriya-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ban-suriya-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16625836705177851947',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('banana-fan-sea-resort','standard','cmr07ig14003dq8xd3rrddwiq','Banana Fan Sea Resort','## Top Reviews
> "Stunning resort, I can’t fault any of it. We felt so lucky to be here! The entire place was beautiful and immaculately maintained, and we felt that the strip of beach outside the resort was some of the nicest along Chaweng. I don’t usually have high expectations for hotel food but the à la carte restaurant at Banana Fan Sea was actually good. Staff are thoughtful and kind. We’d often return to our room with a citronella candle lit in the bathroom which was such a lovely touch."
> **- Hazel Huang (5/5/5)**

> "In my opinion, this is one of the best hotels on the best part of Chaweng Beach. The resort has a beautiful boutique style — authentic yet modern — and the location right on the beach is fantastic.  The only downside is that such a great place sometimes attracts guests who unfortunately don’t know how to behave. But overall, it’s still a wonderful place to stay."
> **- Vilmos Kovacs (4/5/5)**

> "Fantastic hotel on a beautiful beach. Great rooms. Stand out is great staff who are helpful and friendly. The swim up bar is lovely. Twice a day happy hour is good. Food and the Thai buffet were great. Lovely touch was managers drinks reception early on evening. Cannot recommend the hotel, staff and facilities highly enough"
> **- lynn Wild (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/banana-fan-sea-resort-1.jpg','077 413 483','โรงแรมบานานา แฟน ซี รีสอร์ท, ตำบล บ่อผุด Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.bananafansea.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.080+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.080+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/banana-fan-sea-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/banana-fan-sea-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15015085332387458579',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('banana-it','standard','cmr07ig16003eq8xd4m4m1fz8','Banana IT','## Top Reviews
