INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('bandara-spa-resort','standard','cmr07ig19003fq8xd8fv3h5fx','Bandara Spa Resort','## Top Reviews
> "First time at Bandara, very welcoming & professional staff..Shout out & big Thankyou to Thirri. Always greeted with a smile as were all staff. Lovely 1st floor Canopy Bedroom with pool view. Breakfast very varied & fabulous Chicken & Cashew Stirfry. Lovely outlook from Bar & beautiful pools. We picked great weather, now back for our Winter. Thanks again.🇦🇺"
> **- Christine Redpath (5/5/5)**

> "We had an amazing stay at the Bandara Spa Resort & Pool Villas in Koh Samui.  It was a lovely place to relax with three pools and one of those was an adult only pool. The gardens are all well maintained and you are located right on the beach.  Our room was lovely, very clean and the bed was very comfortable.   All the staff are amazing and work really hard to make sure you enjoy your stay. All the food that we ate was amazing and very tasty.  Great location only 10 minutes walk from Fisherman''s Village with local shops and restaurants.  Would definitely recommend this hotel and visit again."
> **- tracy allen (5/5/5)**

> "⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️  We had such a wonderful stay at Bandara Spa & Resort. From the moment we arrived, the staff were genuine, incredibly friendly, and very helpful—nothing was ever too much trouble.  The room was spotless and very comfortable, and the entire property is beautifully maintained. The pools are especially well looked after and a great place to relax.  One of the highlights for us was the stunning view—watching the sunrise on the beach was absolutely beautiful. We also really enjoyed dining with those amazing views, which made the whole experience even more special.  It’s also within walking distance to Fisherman’s Village, which we absolutely loved visiting.  Overall, a fantastic stay and we would definitely come back. Highly recommend!"
> **- Dil Alim (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bandara-spa-resort-1.jpg','077 245 795','178, 2, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.bandarasamui.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.085+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.085+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bandara-spa-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bandara-spa-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10720622349565415892',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('bandon-international-hospital','standard','cmr07ig1f003hq8xd7j2z14ow','Bandon International Hospital','## Top Reviews
> "5/5, would break a bone again. Shattered my collarbone (ouch!), but the staff were absolute angels, making sure I felt safe and sound. Major shoutout to the X-ray guru who turned me into a human pretzel for the perfect shots."
> **- Sébastien Toursel (5/5/5)**

> "I called the Bandon hospital to get the quotation of an X-ray, price on the phone was 1500Thb, included doctors fees,  nurses, etc... And in fact I  been there got my X-ray and I paid exactly 1500.Thb  The 2 others hospital I called earlier did not have the same price on the phone and when I showed up.  And staff was nice too."
> **- Paul Falco (5/5/5)**

> "Had to have an abscess on my leg treated here. OPD. I feel they have done well with the wound and treatment. Compared to the other hospitals it''s priced fair, I feel. A fraction of what other hospitals charge.  I hope I don''t need their service again, but if I do, I would come confidently."
> **- Sören Dittrich (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bandon-international-hospital-1.jpg','077 332 706','123/1 หมู่ 1 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: 12:00 AM – 11:59 PM","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ig1d003gq8xdfxkqj28w','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.091+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.091+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bandon-international-hospital-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bandon-international-hospital-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6100907483152958930',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('bangjo-fishing-lure-shop','standard','cmr07ig1l003jq8xdg7c9cfka','Bang''Jo Fishing Lure Shop','## Top Reviews
> "Perfect service and a good choice for sea fishing. And the owner is really addicted to fishing. Love it 💚"
> **- Christoph Luecke (5/5/5)**

> "Very lovely little shop! The owner was very helpful and showed some new lures that came in for the type of fishery I wanted! Even got a free UV scarf."
> **- Sytze Van Der Wolk (5/5/5)**

> "Thank you so much for helping me assemble three fishing rods. It was so fast and you were so helpful.  I''ll definitely be using your shop again.  👍❤️🙏"
> **- Gitti Uafua (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bangjo-fishing-lure-shop-1.jpg','061 935 7118','105 หมู่3 ซอยกลาง Tambon Taling Ngam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:30 AM – 8:30 PM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 8:30 PM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 8:30 PM","Thursday: 8:30 AM – 8:30 PM","Friday: 8:30 AM – 8:30 PM","Saturday: 8:30 AM – 8:30 PM","Sunday: 8:30 AM – 8:30 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ig1h003iq8xdb1g9nifo','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.097+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.097+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bangjo-fishing-lure-shop-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bangjo-fishing-lure-shop-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9444398569889735',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('bangkok-airways','standard','cmr07ig1o003lq8xdk6uk54lg','Bangkok Airways','## Top Reviews
> "I honestly loved flying with Bangkok Airways. From start to finish, the experience was fantastic. The staff were incredibly friendly, attentive, and welcoming, which immediately set the tone for a great flight.  The plane was very clean, the seats were surprisingly comfortable, and everything felt well maintained. Even though it was a short flight, we were still offered a meal, which was such a nice touch and something you don’t see often anymore.  Boarding was smooth, the flight was on time, and overall it felt like a premium experience compared to many other airlines. I wouldn’t hesitate to fly with Bangkok Airways again and would highly recommend them to anyone traveling within Thailand or the region."
> **- Grace Chizawsky (5/5/5)**

> "Naiyana R Reservation & Ticketing. Bangkok Airways - Samui Station. Best of the best. Customer service keeps my heart melting. Thank you for your help!"
> **- Christina S (5/5/5)**

> "One of THE best Airlines I’ve ever traveled with. During a 50m flight from Bangkok to Koh Samui they managed to pull off full breakfast service with drinks and coffee. Never had this before. I was delighted. Very friendly staff. Airplanes are as expected (speaking from a European perspective)."
> **- Patrick Trübe (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bangkok-airways-1.jpg','077 422 520','ทางหลวงแผ่นดินหมายเลข 4169, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.1,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.bangkokair.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ig1n003kq8xd72v6yb3r','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.100+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.100+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bangkok-airways-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bangkok-airways-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12085779780996050043',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('bangkok-hospital','standard','cmr07ig1s003mq8xdl8wqwlhf','Bangkok Hospital','## Top Reviews
> "Review: Bangkok Hospital Koh Samui  From the moment you arrive at the entrance, you are well taken care of. Check-in is quick and efficient, and you are promptly directed to the appropriate department based on your health concerns. The hospital is very clean throughout, with a calm and pleasant ambiance that helps reduce stress during medical visits.  The doctors and staff were excellent. Across multiple visits — including X-rays, scans, and follow-up appointments — I felt well cared for and professionally handled. Everything is conveniently managed in one place, including consultations, diagnostics, and medication (though prescriptions are noticeably more expensive than at local pharmacies).  Payments and insurance handling went smoothly, and staff were generally helpful when clarifying billing and insurance matters.  However, there is one serious issue that negatively impacted my experience: access to medical documentation.  It was surprisingly difficult to obtain complete copies of my medical records. On several occasions, documents were either not handed over or only partially provided. When I requested full documentation related to my case, I felt uncomfortable — almost as if I was asking for something I was not entitled to. To be clear: any medical document written under my name is my legal right as a patient, and I expect to receive a full copy without resistance.  Despite paying a significant amount for comprehensive medical investigations, I received only partial documentation. This lack of transparency was unsettling and left me with the impression that the hospital could improve greatly in respecting patient rights and trust — rather than making patients feel like they are simply a source of revenue.  Overall, the medical care itself is very good, but the hospital must improve its procedures around record transparency and patient access to documentation."
> **- M. L. STARK (4/5/5)**

> "I would like to sincerely thank the team at Bangkok Hospital for the exceptional care provided to my 1.5 year old son during his stay. From the doctors and nurses to all supporting staff, everyone was incredibly kind, patient and attentive.  Caring for a toddler in the hospital can be stressful for parents, but the team made us feel reassured and supported every step of the way. The doctors explained his condition and treatment clearly, while the nurses were gentle, compassionate, and wonderful with children. The room was spacious, comfortable and exceptionally clean, making our stay much more pleasant. We were also impressed by the quality of the food, which was delicious and well-prepared.  We are truly grateful for the professionalism, dedication and genuine care shown to our son and our family. Thank you for making a difficult time much easier. We highly recommend Bangkok Hospital to any family seeking excellent pediatric care.❤️🏥🩺👩🏼‍⚕️"
> **- Pear Huijuan (5/5/5)**

> "I am very satisfied with my visit to Bangkok Hospital Samui. The entire team, including both the doctors and the nursing staff, is highly competent, professional, and friendly. I felt well taken care of from the very beginning.  I was especially impressed by the excellent service. From the moment I arrived, the registration at the reception was smooth and well organized. I would also like to highlight the German speaking customer service representative, Nisa. For an international hospital, this is truly remarkable. She took great care of me and made sure that my visit was comfortable and stress free. A big thank you as well to Dr. Phumiphat, who treated me. He was very professional, took his time and explained everything clearly, which made me feel very well cared for. I would also like to thank the two doctors who treated me in the emergency department. I can highly recommend Bangkok Hospital Samui, it is a place where high quality medical care meets outstanding service."
> **- Max Gelwich (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bangkok-hospital-1.jpg','077 429 500','57 หมู่ที่ 3 ถ. ทวีราษฎร์ภักดี Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://bangkokhospitalsamui.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ig1d003gq8xdfxkqj28w','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.104+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.104+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bangkok-hospital-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bangkok-hospital-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4267376762076882781',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('bangrak-tavern','standard','cmr07ig1u003nq8xdwowr7fxj','Bangrak Tavern','## Top Reviews
> "Gem of a bar in the heart of Bangrak.  One of the best pool tables I''ve ever played on, the owner Greg and staff genuinely care about everything and everyone in the bar and the drinks are reasonably priced. We had an awesome night there and wouldn''t hesitate to recommend it to anyone looking for a fun night out!"
> **- Marco Duarte (5/5/5)**

> "Great Sports Bar with plenty of high definition large Flat Screen TVs and a great sound system. Nice pool table. We had fun and will be back before we leave Samui. The owner and his staff are extremely welcoming and courteous. I highly recommend."
> **- imi mosaheb (5/5/5)**

> "Nice vibe, great drinks, and such a welcoming atmosphere. Huge shoutout to owner Greg and his partner — they were incredibly kind and even changed the music for us, which made the night feel extra special. Definitely a place to go to embrace the local community."
> **- Preeta Menon (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bangrak-tavern-1.jpg','083 502 7000','34/53, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 4:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Wednesday: 4:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Thursday: 4:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Friday: 4:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Saturday: 4:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Sunday: 4:00 PM – 2:00 AM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.106+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.106+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bangrak-tavern-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bangrak-tavern-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7193456709787482665',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('bantai-beauty-bar','standard','cmr07ig1x003oq8xdas5fn908','Bantai Beauty Bar','## Top Reviews
> "Booked myself in for a set of lashes and so happy I did. Had my first set done 10 years ago and vouched never again. However being on holiday and not wanting to wear mascara I bit the bullet. I made the appointment while still in Australia. Researched the area and found Bantai Beauty close to our resort.  The morning of I was met by Sophie who was so absolutely lovely and encouraging. I wasn’t sure what I wanted apart from something a little more natural. Sophie was so gentle and meticulous and I was so very happy with the outcome. I felt feminine and my lashes lasted 6 weeks. Sophie did warn to not swim too much and get oily products on them so I was super careful. Some did come off naturally but I still had quite a few left by the time I got back to Brisbane. Highly recommend Sophie and her salon for any beauty services."
> **- Annene Meere (5/5/5)**

> "I did my hard gel manicure there. It ended up looking nice. 1300 baht is a lot (European prices) but the quality was worth it. I preferred to pay for and get nice nails 💅 than cheaper and not be satisfied. The place is very clean, owner speaks perfect English so it’s easy to communicate. I highly recommend it. I also like the fact I could schedule the appointment earlier through the app."
> **- Veronica Bielik (5/5/5)**

> "⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️  Sophie is welcoming, professional, and very friendly, you can tell right away that she takes great pride in her work and the business. The space is clean, neat, cool, and relaxing from the moment you step in.  I booked in for a pedicure, gel polish, and foot scrub, and I could not be happier with the service, professionalism, and care Mary showed during my visit. Mary’s attention to detail was exceptional, the best pedicure I’ve ever had. The foot scrub was much needed, very relaxing, and has left my feet so smooth!  I only wish I lived closer so this could be my regular go to! I will absolutely return on my next trip to Koh Samui, and I cannot recommend Sophie and Mary highly enough be sure to book in, you won’t be disappointed."
> **- lisa stanch (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bantai-beauty-bar-1.jpg','095 548 0200','29, Maenam, 3, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.fresha.com/book-now/bantai-beautybar-j9rby9mk/all-offer?share&pId=1319107','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifso000kq8xdfe9gpaon','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.109+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.109+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bantai-beauty-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bantai-beauty-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7085856162710829397',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('bantai-padel','standard','cmr07ig20003pq8xdnv6f2b2t','Bantai Padel','## Top Reviews
> "Nice, laidback yet professional setup with fully equipped facilities for padel games and coaching. The reception is a nice spot to sit and relax before and after games but doesn''t accommodate large number of guests."
> **- Wunda Stone (5/5/5)**

> "Absolutely loved our time at Bantai Padel. The facilities are top tier, beautifully maintained, and genuinely some of the best we’ve played on. Everything feels considered, from the courts to the overall setup.  The service is exceptional. Huge shoutout to the entire team, especially Browny, Stefano, and Pie, who make the place feel welcoming, fun, and effortless from the moment you arrive.  Special mention to Marco for the padel lessons. Clear, patient, and next level coaching. Whether you’re new or experienced, the sessions are incredibly valuable and enjoyable.  And the pool… easily one of the best parts. Nothing beats jumping in for a swim after a solid game of padel. Such a perfect way to recover and reset.  An unreal spot with an amazing team. Highly recommend to anyone visiting or living nearby."
> **- Bill (5/5/5)**

> "I joined the padel camp  and had a great time. The coach is very good, patient, and explains everything clearly. The owner is super friendly and makes you feel welcome from the first moment. The atmosphere is relaxed,, and the courts are in good condition. I improved my game and enjoyed every session. Highly recommended"
> **- baris (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bantai-padel-1.jpg','061 307 8750','69, 42 Bantai Beach, Tambon Mae Nam, Maenam, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://bantaipadel.com/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifuo0015q8xdfahzrsp4','cmr07ifso000kq8xdfe9gpaon','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.112+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.112+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bantai-padel-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bantai-padel-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11420778028667277263',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('banyan-food-market','standard','cmr07ig23003qq8xdkp7eukxb','Banyan Food Market','## Top Reviews
> "We have been here about five times, tonight Khun Pui was playing Jazz with his band. We ate from the Grill and Sushi place and drinks for the bar. It is such a lovely setting there, great staff, so much food choice. Amazing host Gregory. Aways a happy space day or night."
> **- Natalie Kamolwattanasoontorn (5/5/5)**

> "A bit hidden but worth a visit. You get to choose from 6 to 8 different food stalls, sandwiches, burgers, Thai, Russian, veggie/ vegan  All catered to the farang customer mostly. Prices are fair but above average. Atmosphere is nice, especially after sunset.  Good place for a quick lunch / dinner or some drinks to start the night.  Recommended, will come back"
> **- Sören Dittrich (4/5/5)**

> "A wonderful small food market with a few types of tastey foods and dessert options. We had the Vegan sweetheart shake and the Eggoist egg sandwich and they were both delicious! Nice atmosphere 👌"
> **- i Travel (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/banyan-food-market-1.jpg','092 057 5557','25, 243, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'http://banyanmarket.com/','["Monday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.115+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.115+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/banyan-food-market-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/banyan-food-market-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17908294446998949520',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('banyan-tree','standard','cmr07ig25003rq8xdetqekof6','Banyan Tree','## Top Reviews
> "My stay at Banyan Tree was truly memorable, not just because of the beautiful property, but because of how exceptionally well I was taken care of throughout my visit. From the smallest requests to overall comfort and attention, everything was handled with warmth, efficiency, and genuine care.  A special mention to my villa host, Tak, who was absolutely wonderful. She was kind, thoughtful, and always available whenever needed. What stood out the most was her sincere hospitality — she never made anything feel like a formality. Every interaction was warm, personal, and reassuring, which made the entire stay incredibly comfortable and relaxing.  The level of follow-up and guest care at Banyan Tree is truly impressive. They pay attention to details, remember preferences, and make you feel genuinely valued rather than just another guest. It is rare to experience hospitality that feels this personal and effortless.  Grateful for such a fabulous experience and the wonderful memories created during my stay."
> **- Mir Mohammed (5/5/5)**

> "Had a great experience at Banyan tree, made my booking through my Chase Sapphire Reserve card. We were able to get early check in and a room upgrade at no extra cost! Big thanks to all the staff at the resort who were super friendly and helpful 24/7. Special thanks to our concierge MM which helped with all activity planning and made sure my girlfriend had a great experience on her birthday. Also, Ruang the Muay Thai coach which taught us so much about Muay Thai! I would recommend the private lesson with him. He was also very helpful and attentive anytime we were at the beach. Thank you all for a great stay!"
> **- Sebastian Nieto Blanco (5/5/5)**

> "An Exceptional Stay at Banyan Tree Samui Our stay at Banyan Tree Samui was absolutely outstanding from beginning to end. The entire resort is breathtakingly beautiful — stunning villas, incredible ocean views, perfect privacy, and an atmosphere that allows you to fully relax from the very first moment. Every detail throughout the property feels luxurious, elegant, and perfectly maintained. What truly makes this resort special, however, is the amazing staff. We have rarely experienced such genuine hospitality, warmth, and professionalism in a hotel. Every single team member throughout the resort was incredibly friendly, attentive, and always made us feel truly welcome. You can feel that exceptional service is deeply embedded in the culture of this resort. A very special thank you goes to Mr. Ta, who took wonderful care of us during our stay. He was always kind, professional, helpful, and incredibly attentive. His positive attitude and dedication truly elevated our experience and made our stay even more memorable. Employees like him are what transform a great hotel into an unforgettable one. We would also like to praise the fantastic breakfast team. Every morning was a wonderful experience thanks to their warm hospitality, attentiveness, and professionalism. The breakfast selection, quality of the food, and overall atmosphere were simply first-class — easily one of the best hotel breakfasts we have experienced. Banyan Tree Samui is truly one of the most beautiful resorts we have ever visited, and we will definitely return. Thank you to the entire team for creating such an unforgettable experience!"
> **- Ali Reza Tehranchi (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/banyan-tree-1.jpg','077 915 333','99, 9 ตำบล มะเร็ต อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.banyantree.com/thailand/samui','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.117+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.117+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/banyan-tree-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/banyan-tree-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3666235701569247855',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('bao-bao-asian-eatery','standard','cmr07ig28003sq8xdjutyakdk','Bao Bao - Asian Eatery','## Top Reviews
> "Popping into this restaurant on our last day in Koh Samui turned out to be such a great decision.  I hadn’t had proper Asian food (other than Thai cuisine) in quite a while, so the experience felt not only extra delicious but also genuinely interesting, finally getting to taste what these dishes are really supposed to taste like. And this place absolutely delivered.  Everything we ordered was made with fresh ingredients, and even the burger buns were special, they were soft, light, and moist, unlike regular buns. I believe they were made from rice, which made them even more unique and enjoyable.  The design of the restaurant deserves special mention too. It feels less like a restaurant and more like being welcomed into a friend’s beautiful and cozy living room. The atmosphere is warm, stylish, and very relaxing.  The staff were amazing as well, they helped us choose the dishes, the service was quick, and the presentation of the food deserves separate praise because everything looked beautiful.  Already looking forward to coming back to Samui and having more meals at this hidden gem ✨"
> **- Marietta (5/5/5)**

> "Loved the food. Delicious and fresh. The only thing was that sweet potato fries were little too oily - also the aubergine. Loved the buns and gyoza, edamame and homemade kimchi. Clean place, interior could have more searing because the space is huge."
> **- SuiYx23 (5/5/5)**

> "A very nice place, beautiful interior, and very friendly service. The cafe has tables in the back patio surrounded by plants under the open sky. If you''re going with a group, there are board games. I recommend getting the set of four bao for two. Be sure to try the mango with shrimp and the bao with tuna—my favorites. Overall, this place is a 10 out of 10. We went for both dinner and breakfast, and we loved it."
> **- Sergei Nesterov (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bao-bao-asian-eatery-1.jpg','098 831 7657','203, 4, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://baobao.cafe/','["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 11:30 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:30 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 11:30 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 11:30 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 11:30 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 11:30 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.120+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.120+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bao-bao-asian-eatery-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bao-bao-asian-eatery-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4718205791745946369',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('baobab','standard','cmr07ig2a003tq8xdgwl19pj9','Baobab','## Top Reviews
> "Beach vibes, fine taste & pure perfection at Baobab 🌴  Lunch by the beach doesn’t get better than this, perfectly cooked shrimp noodles packed with flavor 🍜🔥🍤 and a bottle of Ruinart Blanc de Blancs Champagne 🥂 to top it off. The combination of fine dining and tropical chill made it unforgettable.  The staff was friendly, the service was fast, and the sea breeze right by Lamai Beach made everything even more special ✨  👉 Highly recommend Baobab if you want that perfect mix of French elegance & island relaxation. We’ll definitely be back! 🇫🇷☀️"
> **- Attila Gönczöl (Tracy) (5/5/5)**

> "Great chilled beach and tropical vibe seashells hanging etc coconut shells... sandy floor. Pleasant friendly staff..all.about the beach vibe here..."
> **- Paul (5/5/5)**

> "Absolutely wonderful place to enjoy the breezy atmosphere and seafront views of the lovely Lamai beach; along with refreshing drinks and good foods. The setting is unique yet very spot on with its totally laid back decor. The cozy beachfront restaurant offers extensive sun lounging stations with umbrellas by the beach to enjoy the breeze and the sun. The food menu offers a plentiful selection of Thai and International dishes (and fresh pastries), and the portions I found them to be more than abundant and enjoyable. Owner and staff are incredibly pleasant and always come around to make sure everything is ok and enjoyed.  What I really like is that this place doesn''t seem to have chaotic energy of any sort with the patrons here, despite it always being filled and full of people. This place flourishes with people, yet it was so incredibly laidback and relaxed."
> **- Wunda Stone (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baobab-1.jpg','089 281 8598','127 64 Thanon Had Lamai, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.122+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.122+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baobab-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baobab-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14107396417349514984',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('bar-baguette-nathon','standard','cmr07ig2c003uq8xdricv1gfs','Bar Baguette','## Top Reviews
> "🌿🥑🍓⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ Review for Bar Baguette  What a fantastic place! If you''re looking for healthy, fresh, and delicious food in Fisherman''s Village, this is the place to be. From amazing smoothies, matcha, reboot juices, and vegan lattes to delicious breakfast dishes like the Egg Avo on Toast and Salmon Scrambled Eggs, they truly have it all! 🥑☕🍳  We also loved the Smoothie Bowl, which was fresh, colorful, and absolutely delicious. Everything is beautifully presented, made with quality ingredients, and served with a smile 🌸  The atmosphere is relaxed, the sea view is lovely, and the staff are incredibly friendly. We came back more than once during our stay because everything was just that good!  Highly recommended for breakfast, brunch, coffee, or a healthy lunch 💚✨  A must-visit in Koh Samui! 🌴🥭☀️"
> **- Colette (5/5/5)**

> "We were looking for a cafe while walking in Fishermans Village and came across Bar Baguette.  Crushed a great cappuccino with some cool art and a black tea.  On the walking street so a great patio to sit and chill on while enjoying a java."
> **- Team Sauce Travels (5/5/5)**

> "My absolute favorite cafe here in Fishermans Village. It has such a cute vibe and the cappuccino is amazing. Also one of the only cafes out here that is open early in the morning."
> **- Verena Visser (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bar-baguette-nathon-1.jpg','094 804 1221','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 9:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig1h003iq8xdb1g9nifo','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.124+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.124+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bar-baguette-nathon-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bar-baguette-nathon-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3367087805934782154',NULL,NULL);
