> "🌿🥑🍓⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ Review for Bar Baguette  What a fantastic place! If you''re looking for healthy, fresh, and delicious food in Fisherman''s Village, this is the place to be. From amazing smoothies, matcha, reboot juices, and vegan lattes to delicious breakfast dishes like the Egg Avo on Toast and Salmon Scrambled Eggs, they truly have it all! 🥑☕🍳  We also loved the Smoothie Bowl, which was fresh, colorful, and absolutely delicious. Everything is beautifully presented, made with quality ingredients, and served with a smile 🌸  The atmosphere is relaxed, the sea view is lovely, and the staff are incredibly friendly. We came back more than once during our stay because everything was just that good!  Highly recommended for breakfast, brunch, coffee, or a healthy lunch 💚✨  A must-visit in Koh Samui! 🌴🥭☀️"
> **- Colette (5/5/5)**

> "We were looking for a cafe while walking in Fishermans Village and came across Bar Baguette.  Crushed a great cappuccino with some cool art and a black tea.  On the walking street so a great patio to sit and chill on while enjoying a java."
> **- Team Sauce Travels (5/5/5)**

> "My absolute favorite cafe here in Fishermans Village. It has such a cute vibe and the cappuccino is amazing. Also one of the only cafes out here that is open early in the morning."
> **- Verena Visser (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bar-baguette-1.jpg','094 804 1221','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 9:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.127+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.127+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bar-baguette-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bar-baguette-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3367087805934782154',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('bar-bara','standard','cmr07ig2k003wq8xd41bgsvgz','Bar Bara','## Top Reviews
> "I also think this is one of the bests haircuts I had in some time. I asked for a fade and was impressed. The shop is small, simple, clean. Quality haircut, good price, excellent service, attention to detail. 10/10"
> **- Az (5/5/5)**

> "I visited this barber with my one-year-old child and also got my own haircut. Everything was excellent! The haircut was very well done, the service was outstanding he is super friendly and welcoming. I felt comfortable from start to finish. I will definitely be coming back and highly recommend this place!"
> **- Yve (5/5/5)**

> "Hands down one of the best fades I’ve had in a long time.  The attention to detail, patience, and overall service was seriously top level. The barber took his time properly and the result speaks for itself. Smooth fade, clean lines, and a relaxed atmosphere from start to finish.  Cost me 200 baht for hair cut and fade….and honestly worth every single baht. Gave a tip as well because the quality deserved it.  Already know this will be my regular barber every time I’m back in Koh Samui. Fully trusted 🙏🔥"
> **- Rafael Dàhl David (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bar-bara-1.jpg','061 441 2074','64 51, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.132+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.132+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bar-bara-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bar-bara-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7879870552404199991',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('bar-bohem','standard','cmr07ig2n003xq8xdesgqycz2','Bar Bohem','## Top Reviews
> "Authentic and original place with real character. Carson was there and welcomed us with open arms; genuine hospitality at its best. His Negroni is outstanding, perfectly balanced and truly unforgettable. A must-visit spot in Koh Samui for cocktail lovers. Cheers 🍸"
> **- PRISMA Consulting (5/5/5)**

> "A very cool bar that we happened to hear about through friends who live on the island — they took us there, and we’re so glad they did!  Honestly, I have no idea why this place doesn’t show up more in recommendations, because it’s definitely a must-visit if you enjoy cocktails.  We were two couples and ordered several cocktails — everyone loved everything we tried.  The atmosphere is fantastic, the bar is beautifully designed, and the lighting creates a really special vibe.  The staff were super professional, incredibly friendly, and made us feel genuinely welcome and comfortable throughout the evening.  Highly recommended — a great experience overall! 🍸✨"
> **- Gal Toronto (5/5/5)**

> "A cozy little bar with a great approach to cocktails. They don’t rely on a fixed menu—just tell them what you like, whether it’s sweet, sour, fruity, smoky, or even with a bit of spice, and they’ll create something for you. I asked for something fruity, fresh, and not too sweet, bitter, or smoky.  What they made was spot on—a beautifully balanced cocktail with a subtle hint of ginger that elevated the whole drink. Absolutely delicious. I’d definitely go back again."
> **- Lita Sekarnphicha (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bar-bohem-1.jpg','098 069 8871','58, 1 Bangrak Reach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100083606564372','["Monday: 7:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Tuesday: 7:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Wednesday: 7:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Thursday: 7:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Friday: 7:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Saturday: 7:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Sunday: 7:00 PM – 2:00 AM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.135+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.135+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bar-bohem-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bar-bohem-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11290108929017338912',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('baraca-mediterranean-restaurant','standard','cmr07ig2p003yq8xd6atv7s69','Baraca Mediterranean Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "Wow such an amazing restaurant!! The food,vibe and service was absolutely amazing. It tasted superb and the prices were really not bad. Also a big plus it’s in middle of fisherman’s village wow. It’s so beautiful and calm! The favours were vibrant and bursting with flavour. The service was exceptional and very fast."
> **- Yossi Shuchat (5/5/5)**

> "Usually don’t like spending extra for Kosher food but wanted some Hummus was totally worth it, tasty with nice extras and generous 3 pitas. Also tried the Koskos which was nice but would be nice to have more variety of veggies. My friend had the Hala Shnitzel and it was very tasty and big portion. Great vibe and design also"
> **- Liron Naor (5/5/5)**

> "We are a Jewish family that were looking for a kosher restaurant that we can enjoy a nice Sunday dinner. Wow!! It was absolutely amazing. The place is big, beautiful and clean. The food was delicious. We got different dishes and it did not disappoint. My kids are picky eaters and they enjoyed their food very much. They begged to come again. I highly recommend this place for clean, kosher yummy food."
> **- Maital David Katar (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baraca-mediterranean-restaurant-1.jpg','096 975 0534','43 moo1, Fisherman''s village, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 3:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.137+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.137+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baraca-mediterranean-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/baraca-mediterranean-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12882906013584944669',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('barathrum-computer-club','standard','cmr07ig2r003zq8xdxvp6hztd','Barathrum Computer Club','## Top Reviews
> "Extremely nice place! It''s impossible - to create such a cozy and comfortable place to play games! But 10pm closing time.. it is too early. 24/7 when?🔥"
> **- Vladyslav Strebkov (5/5/5)**

> "Best place in Samui if you''re passionate about video games. The room has several high-quality setups, making for an incredible experience. Everything has been designed for your comfort and optimal performance. And the staff is attentive to your every need. I 100% recommend this place 💯🙏"
> **- Philippe Dubois (5/5/5)**

> "Great place. They offer free hot drinks and free gaming on PS5. No other place like it in Samui for gaming."
> **- Frank Watson (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/barathrum-computer-club-1.jpg','061 650 3930','1, 76, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://linktr.ee/barathrum_club','["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 2:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 2:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 2:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 2:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 2:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 2:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.139+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.139+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/barathrum-computer-club-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/barathrum-computer-club-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=707273180885942792',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('barbershop-haircut-shave','standard','cmr07ig2t0040q8xdmdtob6uj','Barbershop Haircut & Shave','Discover Barbershop Haircut & Shave, a premier beauty and wellness located in Chaweng, Koh Samui. Find reviews, hours, and contact information.','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/barbershop-haircut-shave-1.jpg','091 815 5687','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,0.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.kohsamuibarbershop.com/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.141+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.141+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/barbershop-haircut-shave-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/barbershop-haircut-shave-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14316186951118819859',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('basic-mobile','standard','cmr07ig2v0041q8xdxm6oxykv','Basic Mobile','## Top Reviews
> "Unfortunately they didn''t had spare parts for changing the broken screen of my OnePlus OP 13  I bought a physical SIM card for Interner. They had multiple options, my choice was 299 bath with 55Gb network data for 15 days."
> **- Sandro Winkler (winklerrr) (4/5/5)**

> "RASISM! I came to sell my phone which I bought in Thailand, they told me they don’t “buy” but it says in their door they buy, I asked to charge to phone before showing them, they said they don’t have TYPE C, yeah phone store don’t have type c charger."
> **- Олеся Ворон (1/5/5)**

> "Screen was black.  Technician said all data lost and can''t be fixed.  Then sold us a cheap phone to use temporarily.  Took the phone to another shop in Lamai, they replaced the screen and it works and all data is still there.  So, I wonder how knowledgeable the technician really is."
> **- David Samui (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/basic-mobile-1.jpg','077 447 837','35/16 ม.6 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61553790521775','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.143+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.143+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/basic-mobile-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/basic-mobile-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8714898171828876810',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('basil','standard','cmr07ig2y0042q8xd0xxa3elm','Basil','## Top Reviews
> "Absolutely the best Indian I’ve ever had! Can’t recommend this place enough went there for a dinner a few times and everything was just so delicious. Tandoori Salmon and tandoori chicken is a must try! Staff were super nice and helpful, I really hope to eat there again in the future. Great value for the money!"
> **- Eleonora Pogany (5/5/5)**

> "I''ve tried pretty much every Indian restaurant in Samui, and to me this is the best by far. Their garlic naan bread is the best I''ve ever had, not just in samui. The chili prawn appetizer is so damn good, i want to lick the plate clean. And the curries are excellent.  Only complaint: food isn''t spicy enough for me, despite telling them i want proper firey chili.  But totally excellent both times i went. Will be back soon!  Update October 2024: I just returned from my first-ever trip to India, and I can honestly say that the food at Basil is as good or better than 80% of the restaurants I tried in India. It''s only the very, very top restaurants there that would outshine Basil, and that''s expected given how hard it is to find all the ingredients here in Thailand. We are truly lucky to have Basil here in Samui!"
> **- Yoel Lax (5/5/5)**

> "Pretty good dinner, recommended place! Good service and polite staff. Also, we could pay by card, we are super thankful!  Unfortunately I can''t give 5 stars because one of the plates was very bad. The hummus didn''t taste nice, and the bread they provided with it was very chewy. Don''t order it."
> **- Rubén (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/basil-1.jpg','089 499 4823','38/101, อำ เภ, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.146+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.146+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/basil-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/basil-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10221159342990634398',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('basilicom','standard','cmr07ig320043q8xd32t37881','Basilicom','## Top Reviews
> "Some will like the idea of having 100% israelis around them. We bit less. However the food here is absolutely amazing. By far the best Israeli food we had outside of Israel. Will recommend this place for everyone to eat here. Definitely a must!"
> **- Eddie (5/5/5)**

> "The best of the best. A staple in koh samui for all. Service is always with a smile. The food is fast, fresh and delicious. Big portions, not cheap at all on anything you ask or need. One of the best restaurants we ate all of the world. This place hold a big part of our vacation memories. We will definitely be back and recommend to everyone! Also delivery was awesome! God bless this place"
> **- Ariel Mizrahi (5/5/5)**

> "Probably one of the best Israeli food I’ve ever had outside of Israeli. Very big variety, generous portions, reasonable pricing, and the flavours are there!  I was expecting an Israeli tourist trap… it was actually a little piece of Israeli in a our plates 🙂"
> **- Sandy Zarka (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/basilicom-1.jpg','087 384 3789','166 6 ตำบล บ่อผุด Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://basilicomthailand.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.150+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.150+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/basilicom-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/basilicom-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4281251574172063404',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('bb-car-rent-taxi-service','standard','cmr07ig350044q8xdu0a6jz13','BB Car Rent & Taxi Service','## Top Reviews
> "Very good place to rent scooters and motorbike. They are very accommodating and the prices are in the best value for money. We rented here a couple of times and we also had sometimes small accident and they were always the best to accommodate everything and they are more then correct. Highly recommend !"
> **- Yohan Martini (5/5/5)**

> "Highly recommend BB moped and car rental. I rented a moped for 6 weeks and throughout they were there to assist whenever needed. Great customer service and reliable mopeds. Thanks again!🙏✌️💚 - Sheeny & Jess"
> **- jessica elsey (5/5/5)**

> "We came across BB rentals walking from our hotel. We rented the Honda click 160. This was perfect for two people. The bike was pretty much brand new with no problems and they delivered to the hotel for us. Deposit was 3000 baht and all communication was done through whatsapp easily."
> **- Ju Sadowski (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bb-car-rent-taxi-service-1.jpg',NULL,'9 74, Tambon Mae Nam, Maenam Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/BB-Car-Rent-BB-Service-744768588880100/?fref=ts','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07ifui0012q8xdzn158clv','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.153+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.153+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bb-car-rent-taxi-service-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bb-car-rent-taxi-service-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14032864610094889521',NULL,NULL);
