> "Lovely experience and hospitality. Highly recommend."
> **- Naveen (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/blue-voyage-yachting-1.jpg','086 424 4245','Unnamed Road, Tambon Lipa Noi, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.bluevoyagethailand.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.209+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.209+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/blue-voyage-yachting-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/blue-voyage-yachting-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5768930365035631732',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('blueblood-tattoo','standard','cmr07ig4s004tq8xdrddklnug','Blueblood Tattoo','## Top Reviews
> "I spent a long time looking for a tattoo studio and finally chose this one. One of the biggest advantages is that they can make a stencil beforehand, which was very important to me. The staff was very polite, listened to all my wishes and really tried their best. I’m very happy with the result and can definitely recommend this place 🤍"
> **- Svet Svet (5/5/5)**

> "Me and my girlfriend walked in without an appointment for two tattoos and they took us in straight away. The artist was incredibly welcoming and professional from the start, guiding us through the whole process with patience and expertise. Excellent technique, fast and precise, with great attention to cleanliness and hygiene. An amazing experience - highly recommend to anyone looking for quality ink in Koh Samui. We''ll definitely be back!"
> **- Ovidio Hincu (5/5/5)**

> "I‘ve had my small tattoo here and it was great! It didnt hurt and rabbit was so friendly and kind. Everything went so well. Thank you so much!"
> **- Sarah Brehmer (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/blueblood-tattoo-1.jpg','099 035 1971','147, 42, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://bluebloodtattookohsamui.com/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.212+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.212+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/blueblood-tattoo-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/blueblood-tattoo-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5823574384598250361',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('bm-grocery-lamai','standard','cmr07ig4u004uq8xd0p12h9bl','BM Grocery','## Top Reviews
> "Best hidden gem on Koh Samui! 🔥 Kombucha, masala chai, all kinds of dals and flours, yogurt, kefir, authentic Indian spices… you won’t find products like this anywhere else on the island.  So many unique and hard-to-find items, everything feels fresh and special. Some things are seriously addictive 😄  Simple place, but full of treasures. 100% worth a visit"
> **- Elvira (5/5/5)**

> "Half of the things we''ve bought today were rotten such as the mushrooms and watermelon. The yogurts were spoiled. And it''s the last time we will shop there. I recommend strongly to check everything you buying over there"
> **- gilad touchsher (1/5/5)**

> "The closest thing to a true expat store on the island! Has a great selection of items that the other grocery stores don''t carry. They also have homemade bread and deserts a very reasonable prices."
> **- Bobby Shaftoe (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bm-grocery-lamai-1.jpg','098 445 8084','Bangrakminimartsamui 30 2, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.214+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.214+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bm-grocery-lamai-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bm-grocery-lamai-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13714428659314267460',NULL,NULL);
