> **- Bobby Shaftoe (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bm-grocery-1.jpg','098 445 8084','Bangrakminimartsamui 30 2, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.217+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.217+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bm-grocery-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bm-grocery-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13714428659314267460',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('boat-bar','standard','cmr07ig50004wq8xd7f763200','Boat Bar','## Top Reviews
> "I recently visited Boat Bar at Bangrak Pier in Koh Samui, Tucked away set back off the main road, this little bar offers a peaceful escape from the usual tourist hustle. The location is perfect—right by the water with stunning views of the bay and bobbing boats, especially beautiful at sunset. It’s not loud at all; they keep the music low (or none at all during quieter times), making it ideal for a calm, enjoyable meal without any blasting speakers or crowds. The prices here are very reasonable—great value for the quality and setting. They have a well-balanced menu featuring both authentic Thai dishes and solid Western options, so there’s something for everyone.  We ordered a chicken burger, fried wings, a beef burger, pad krapow (spicy basil stir-fry), and Tom Yum soup with seafood. Everything was delicious: the burgers were juicy and perfectly cooked, the pad krapow packed with bold flavors, and the Tom Yum was rich, tangy, with fresh seafood. Portions were decent for the price. The wings were a stand out.  Super good tender and crispy.  Service was friendly and attentive without being overbearing. The only thing that stood out as “loud” was the owner himself—proudly calling himself “California Chris”, an American guy who’s clearly passionate about his place. He seems like a genuinely nice, welcoming character who chats with guests and makes everyone feel at home.  Overall, Boat Bar is a charming little spot with excellent prices, good service, delicious food, and that rare peaceful vibe overlooking the bay. Highly recommend if you’re looking for a relaxed meal away from the noise. 5 stars for the chill factor!"
> **- The Guy (5/5/5)**

> "Menu looked good. Read previous reviews. Ordered chicken taco''s and chicken burger. Chicken taco''s came with duck pancakes definately not taco''s were very bland no smokiness, spice or salsa. Chicken burger had a funny purple colour in it and the chips were terrible (old oil) tasted of gasoline. Daughters dinner arrived and was eaten before my chicken burger and fries arrived.Would not recommend or come back."
> **- Stephanie Mcgowan (1/5/5)**

> "Fun bamboo bar on the beach. Great sunsets and nice staff.  The beer is always cold and their food is the best around for the price"
> **- Kevin Foster (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/boat-bar-1.jpg',NULL,'H376+JQJ, 4171, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.220+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.220+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/boat-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/boat-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1696736919272836462',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('bondi-aussie-bar-grill-lamai','standard','cmr07ig52004xq8xd0qfh06ei','Bondi Aussie Bar & Grill','## Top Reviews
> "The food was great, even though I only tried one dish. I had the chicken tenders, and they were really good. They also offer a nice selection of drinks, including alcoholic options and milky beverages like an Oreo smoothie.  The service was quick and efficient.  The atmosphere felt clean, safe, and relaxed, with great live music adding to the vibe. They also have pool tables available at just 20 THB per round, which is a fun bonus."
> **- Monica’s Taste (5/5/5)**

> "absolutely fantastic food and great big draft beers! So very happy to see a business in Thailand not charge the 3 or sometimes 5% surcharge for credit card use! Just that within it self makes me want to come back but as a plus the food is great too! Thank you for a great lunch and great service! They also have access to tune into all the football games!"
> **- Joel Worsham (5/5/5)**

> "A really good place to eat whilst visiting Lamai.  They have a brilliant happy hour and the staff are fantastic!  I had the ribs and half chicken combo, and it was fantastic! Packed with flavour and the ribs fell right off the bone, and the chicken was juicy and had a good kick of heat behind it.  My partner had the burger and she said it was very juicy and a great burger!"
> **- Michael Witts (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bondi-aussie-bar-grill-lamai-1.jpg','098 218 8278','124/88 Thanon Had Lamai, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.2,0,0,0,NULL,'https://bondiasia.com/bondi-lamai/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 1:00 AM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 1:00 AM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 1:00 AM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 1:00 AM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 1:00 AM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 1:00 AM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 1:00 AM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.222+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.222+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bondi-aussie-bar-grill-lamai-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bondi-aussie-bar-grill-lamai-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10511807576409148574',NULL,NULL);
