INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('bophut-resort-spa','standard','cmr07ig570050q8xdkkqau3dn','Bophut Resort & Spa','## Top Reviews
> "We absolutely loved our stay at bo phut resort. We came for our honeymoon and stayed for 3 nights. The service is incredible especially the  attention to detail. Amenities are great, we enjoyed the pool and the gym and the beautiful gardens. The beach was not so good. Breakfast was ok, we have seen better in Thailandand. Really the service and staff where the best. Location is ok for fishermans village."
> **- Yaffa Matitya (4/5/5)**

> "Really nice hotel in great location. Staff all wonderful. Breakfast very good, you must try the Thai scrambled eggs, cooked fresh 😋 Our room was beautiful and cleaned to a high standard every day. Each night a staff member would come and plug in your mosquito 🦟 reppeler in your room!  Very short walk to lively fisherman''s village. Can''t fault this place. Beach not amazing but this has nothing to do with the Hotel."
> **- Ian gowland (5/5/5)**

> "We had an amazing stay at this hotel in Bo Phut and left very satisfied. The staff were genuinely kind, attentive, and welcoming throughout our stay. What impressed us the most was that they arranged a late check-out according to our flight time without us even asking — such a thoughtful gesture.  The food, the view, the atmosphere, and the rooms were all excellent. The rooms are very spacious, quiet, and everything feels new and well maintained. The location and overall experience were fantastic. Definitely a place I would highly recommend."
> **- Sinan Erbil (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bophut-resort-spa-1.jpg','077 245 777','12/12 หมู่ที่ 1 ตำบล บ่อผุด Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.bophutresort.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.227+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.227+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bophut-resort-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bophut-resort-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2679816920885853061',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('boujis-boutique-resort','standard','cmr07ig5d0052q8xdt72xz9y6','Boujis Boutique Resort','## Top Reviews
> "We stayed at Boujis in February 2026 and had such a comfortable and genuinely hospitable experience.  The views from the rooms are absolutely extraordinary, vast stretches of the moody, ever-changing ocean that feel almost cinematic. We woke up to some of the most spectacular sunrises right from our room. Those quiet early morning moments overlooking the sea will stay with us for a long time.  The property is located in Chaweng Noi, right along the main road. I would definitely recommend renting a bike so you can easily explore nearby cafes, beaches, and spots around the island. The rooms are perched on a hill, so be prepared for a bit of climbing each time you step out , but honestly, the views make it worth the extra steps.  The rooms themselves aren’t ultra-modern or luxurious, but they are clean, comfortable, and perfectly functional for a relaxed island stay.  What truly makes this place special, though, is the people. Ice, Noom, and Nee at the front office were outstanding ,incredibly responsive, thoughtful about guest comfort, and always willing to help with very genuine care. The housekeeping team was also wonderful and attentive as well. It’s the kind of place where the warmth of the staff elevates the entire experience.  We left feeling well looked after  and very grateful. Would highly recommend this place."
> **- Khyati S (5/5/5)**

> "Worth every Single second! The View in the Morning is awesome, the Staff is friendly and helpful and the room is clean and good located. Without a Motorbike it‘s a bit difficult because nothing is nearby but it‘s ok."
> **- Tanja Brungs (5/5/5)**

> "A home away from home. Our room was spacious, very close to the water so the view was breathtaking! Very clean, has all amenities, even Netflix. There’s a small kitchen where you could cook some basic dishes, big fridge to keep your food and drinks cool. There’s Dr Frogs restaurant next door so you can eat there - the food is very nice and service is very warm and friendly."
> **- Agne Radzevic (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/boujis-boutique-resort-1.jpg','077 448 544','103 หมู่ 3 ถ. ทวีราษฎร์ภักดี Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'http://boujisboutiqueresort.com/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ig5c0051q8xdykrbexft','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.233+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.233+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/boujis-boutique-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/boujis-boutique-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7054074147190620120',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('boutique-yachting','standard','cmr07ig5f0053q8xd7yj62q0c','Boutique Yachting','## Top Reviews
> "This was an amazing experience. The team was attentive, full of care and always on hand to assist with everything we needed. The arranged experiences were very nice and also gave us options to tailor it according to our needs, without it being too strict.  Even when the weather was uncooperative, they did their best to keep all of us engaged and happy.  Everyone should do this one, it’s a very comfortable way to explore the beauty of the islands."
> **- Musa Raibin (5/5/5)**

> "This was the absolute best excursion we could have done. We were a family of 8 with 3 kids under 6 years old. The staff was so accommodating and friendly. The food they cooked was fresh and delicious. The stops were engaging and fun with options for everyone in our family. I would recommend this boat and staff to anyone any day of the week. This was easily one of the most memorable days of my life. And a huge thanks and hug to the woman who took my fussy 2yr old under her wing and care with such love!"
> **- Brenna Toussaint (5/5/5)**

> "An absolutely fabulous day on the sail ship with Pko and crew. Very attentive staff. Boat not too crowded.  Really enjoyed time off the boat being taken to the viewpoint and beach. Then to the green lake within the mountain. The food is supplied and the drinks are available all day.  The lunchtime meal was not only ample but very well cooked. The masaman curry was my favourite. As far as value for money goes I would highly recommend as you get a quality experience. Seeing the sail ship and experiencing the sails out was a truly wonderful time that my wife and I will always remember especially as it''s our 40th wedding anniversary. Very impressed."
> **- Josh Sampays (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/boutique-yachting-1.jpg','065 420 7999','Bophut, 158, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://boutiqueyachting.com/','["Monday: 9:30 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:30 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:30 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 9:30 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 9:30 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 9:30 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 9:30 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.235+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.235+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/boutique-yachting-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/boutique-yachting-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3929538397753110507',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('bre-eze-restaurant-and-bar','standard','cmr07ig5h0054q8xdz76g83s9','Bre-Eze Restaurant And Bar','## Top Reviews
> "We just finished a 7 night stay at Fair house villas.  We had breakfast each morning and dined here every night.  The food quality was consistently excellent and was delicious, we loved the cocktails and the beers were nice and cold.  The staff were lovely, very attentive and always super friendly."
> **- Simon Deen (5/5/5)**

> "We stayed in fair house resort and this restaurant is part of this resort. Beautiful restaurant right on the view. Tasty food with wonderful views. Come here to enjoy serenity and have a wonderful dining experience. We tried the buffet, not sure about the ala carte though."
> **- Jitin Batra (5/5/5)**

> "We booked a pool villa for two weeks and enjoyed the very good and reasonable priced Thai food. We stayed in Thailand several times, rented houses, eat on the street as well as in nice restaurants. The restaurant Bre-Eze has an amazing variety of tasty dishes we enjoyed directly at the seafront. I can’t understand the bad recessions! What you get here is worth the money. I clearly can recommend it."
> **- Tango Lima (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bre-eze-restaurant-and-bar-1.jpg','077 429 000','H2F8+248, Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.9,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.fairhousevillas.com/','["Monday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.237+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.237+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bre-eze-restaurant-and-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bre-eze-restaurant-and-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14833143811438449942',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('breathflow-connection','standard','cmr07ig5k0055q8xdbkln8rbz','Breathflow Connection','## Top Reviews
> "We just finished the freediving level 1 course with Diego. It was a truly mesmerising experience, Diego did a great job at showing us the basics on land and practice in the ocean. He created a really safe environment for us to experience freediving. We’re more than happy to have reached 12m & 20m within only two days without prior experience. Lastly, to add a cherry on top we saw a whale shark and a marlin during our dives ! Thank you, Diego, keep up the good work :)"
> **- Glynnis Yap (5/5/5)**

> "Diego runs an incredible Free Diving course. I would recommend his free diving instruction or breathing classes to absolutely anyone. During our entry level free diving class we were lucky enough to have two instructors for just three students. The second instructor Ilias was quite skilled and did an amazing job of coaching me through my equalization challenges. I’m level one certified now and I can wait to return to these guys for advanced! Thank you!!"
> **- Travis Fair (5/5/5)**

> "Freediving with Diego from Breathflow connecting was an amazing experience: from the expert tuition to the beauty of the Thai gulf. As a complete beginner, Diego supported me with patience, knowledge, passion, and kindness to get me to new depths. I''ve gained a skill and memories that will last a lifetime."
> **- E Saunders (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/breathflow-connection-1.jpg','065 557 1148','174/34C, Lamai, ตำบล มะเร็ต อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.breathflowconnection.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.240+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.240+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/breathflow-connection-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/breathflow-connection-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3848646073049913501',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('bubale-chefs-sandwiches','standard','cmr07ig5m0056q8xd69pzo9hu','Bubale Chef''s Sandwiches','## Top Reviews
> "The food is delicious. The marinated meat is very delicious. I like the fried chicken. The chicken skin is delicious. It’s a warm restaurant. The owner is friendly. The service is like family. I recommend it. It‘s very delicious. The atmosphere is good. The sea view has a variety of menus. I am glad to know your family. Everyone is very good to me. My mother and I have time to go and support the food there and will refer our customers to your restaurant.🙏🌴🫶🏻🌴❤️🌴🫶🏻🌴🙏"
> **- พิทยาพร แซ่แต้ (5/5/5)**

> "Absolutely wonderful food! I had the kebab pita with fries and fried eggplant.  The FRIED EGGPLANT was some of the best I have ever tried. Truly. Definitely recommend.  It’s a small hole in the wall type place with kind staff."
> **- Nathan Piland (5/5/5)**

> "Stumbled across this place on Google Maps and decided to walk down from Fisherman’s Village. Outstanding selection of sandwiches in combinations I’ve never seen before. Both the sandwiches we had were fantastic along with the side of fries. Service was great and I think they were great value for money. Did get very warm in there however!"
> **- Jamie Willcock (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bubale-chefs-sandwiches-1.jpg','080 018 7787','15, Bangrak, 62, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 5:30 PM","Saturday: 6:00 – 11:30 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.242+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.242+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bubale-chefs-sandwiches-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/bubale-chefs-sandwiches-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8561075938735195847',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('buffalo-jungle-beach-club','standard','cmr07ig5p0057q8xdgx65tgj1','Buffalo Jungle Beach Club','## Top Reviews
> "Wonderful amazing place for parties and dancing on the sand.  Master is a big healer here and gonna help you with any problems in your body.  Big kitchen, gum for guys and couch from boxing.  Helpful people here. Highly recommended"
> **- Olga Dobrianska (5/5/5)**

> "Super good experience, friendly manager/staff, good shakes and food right on the beach. Fun machines for your workouts! Also: if you pay for the gym entry you can reenter all day long, meaning you can hit the gym in the morning and come back for some boxing in the evening!"
> **- Nemorino König (5/5/5)**

> "Nada, his brother and all the staff here were exceptionally helpful and really friendly. The gym has good quality equipment, a lovely bar area with lots of character and great shakes! Thank you guys :) - Charley and Zoe"
> **- Zoe Slough (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/buffalo-jungle-beach-club-1.jpg','0963 600 035','F22H+76, Koh Samui, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.buffalojunglesamui.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.245+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.245+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/buffalo-jungle-beach-club-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/buffalo-jungle-beach-club-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2143740793488241350',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('burger-king','standard','cmr07ig5r0058q8xdgaxtsotm','Burger King','## Top Reviews
> "Fast food in other countries is a bit of an experience. It’s always much nicer than in the states!  The sliding doors open with a single tap. (I now know this because I got trapped in the McDonalds.) 🤣  You order at the self-service kiosks and you can pay up front with baht after ordering!  Employees are quick to come and help with ordering at the kiosk and answering questions!  BK offers free WiFi. Most establishments print the WiFi code on the receipt but BK will provide it upon request.  One thing I’ve learned about fast food chains in Thailand is that they don’t typically have a public restroom.  The meal was prepared quickly with fresh ingredients and very good!"
> **- 405backpacker (5/5/5)**

> "There was us and one other customer in the restaurant and after 15 minutes of waiting they gave our order to the other guy waiting! Luckily he was decent enough to come over and ask if it was ours. I’m guessing our food had been waiting on the side for a few minutes as well as it was given to him immediately upon asking. The staff seemed more interested in looking out the windows at something on the street than working. After all this they then didn’t give us the sauce with the meal so I had to go back up and ask for it. No real apology either, pretty poor."
> **- Ethan Pegg (1/5/5)**

> "It was the worst Burger King experience. The burgers are definitely not flame grilled as advertised. Cardboard patties, and way over priced. I ask for the large size, they gave me small, then made me pay again for for a large drink."
> **- Scuba Tom (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/burger-king-1.jpg','063 226 7897','166 71-73 หมู 2 Tambon Bo Put, Koh Samui Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.burgerking.co.th/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.247+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.247+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/burger-king-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/burger-king-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15469540835478032141',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('burma-kitchen','standard','cmr07ig5u0059q8xdrzidx6s9','Burma Kitchen','## Top Reviews
> "Not sure where it earned the 4.8 star rating, Maybe they recently changed management, but I just went there and the menu was really poor in terms of options, basically every dish is chicken based and the dishes don’t look like the ones i saw online when I checked the restaurant out. I have lived in Asia for over 20 years so I am not new to south Asian cuisines and I had Burmese food a few times previously as I travelled to Myanmar a few times for work. This time I was disappointed at the quality of every dish I ordered. Sorry, not a nice experience by any standard."
> **- sergio Colombini (2/5/5)**

> "Came here for lunch and absolutely enjoyed every dishes here. The owner personally recommended the curry chicken, and it was such a treat - very well prepared, nicely braised and full of flavours. Other dishes I had were the samosa, mashed potato with pickles and pomelo salad; all were nothing short of delectable. Menus were extensive and their vegan dishes are clearly labelled - a nice, thoughtful touch. Beyond the food, the restaurant enjoys a nice spot atop the Dreamcatcher Hotel, overlooking Fisherman''s Village and the hills on the other side - surely nice for sundown drinks and chill. Lovely Burmese cuisine and ambiance!"
> **- Wunda Stone (5/5/5)**

> "We stopped here for a drink and to take in the view of Fisherman’s Village Street market. We ordered the spring rolls and they were absolutely delicious! They had curry in them which was a nice change of flavor from the usual spring rolls. The owner stopped over to say hello as well. Beautiful atmosphere too!"
> **- Desiree Lillo (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/burma-kitchen-1.jpg','081 723 6687','Dreamcatcher Hotel Rooftop, Fisherman''s Village, เลขที่ 88 6, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.250+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.250+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/burma-kitchen-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/burma-kitchen-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16135346674351800469',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('cabanas-beach-club','standard','cmr07ig5w005aq8xdiskovx4n','Cabanas Beach Club','## Top Reviews
> "Fantastic beach club, great facilities, music and atmosphere. We booked a day bed directly by the pool with sea view and it was absolutely worth it. Jenny took great care of us and showed fantastic service and hospitality. Highly recommend! Small note: we were originally told that the small pool was private and for exclusive use for the day bed guests and it turned out it wasn’t."
> **- Maria (5/5/5)**

> "A very chill place with a perfectly clean pool and well-maintained amenities. There’s a DJ playing throughout the day, which adds a great vibe.  They offer a wide variety of food options, and the cutest highlight of all is the ice cream bar by the beach. Overall, I truly loved the experience.  While seating space by the beach is a bit limited, the beach itself is beautiful. It’s a great spot for both friends and families, and they also have some really nice bars."
> **- Monica’s Taste (5/5/5)**

> "This is a very beautifully designed beach club and a nice sunny atmosphere. I ordered a salmon pizza and it was very delicious. The staff Nonny, were very friendly and always smiling nice photographer. Pass around like tropical fruit ice-cream that’s nice. Manager Aomie talked with me in a friend. I would like to come again next time."
> **- Gloy Thanyatip (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cabanas-beach-club-1.jpg','081 245 8493','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.cabanas.live/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.252+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.252+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cabanas-beach-club-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cabanas-beach-club-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4144623138640772875',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('cabaret-paris-follies','standard','cmr07ig5y005bq8xda0v0wg0g','Cabaret Paris Follies','## Top Reviews
> "Went and saw Paris Follies Cabaret Show last night!  It was awesome!! Outfits and make up were on point and stunning. Lots of energy! I love that they got the crowd to join in.  Was a fun night for sure."
> **- Bianca Katai (5/5/5)**

> "Very average in my opinion. Performers'' costumes were absolutely gorgeous but the energy, choreography and the atmosphere was just average. I do not regret checking it out but it definitely wasn''t a highlight of my trip to Koh Samoi."
> **- Adam Kaczmarek (3/5/5)**

> "Fantastic show, cheap entry (just buy one drink) and amazing costumes. Great way to start a night out in Central Samui/Chaweng on the way to the Ark Bar and beach fire shows."
> **- Jeff Emmerton (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cabaret-paris-follies-1.jpg','061 303 1000','166, 92 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'https://parisfolliescabaret.com/','["Monday: 7:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 7:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 7:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 7:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 7:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 7:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 7:00 PM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.254+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.254+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cabaret-paris-follies-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cabaret-paris-follies-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4203052624643223827',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('caf-color','standard','cmr07ig60005cq8xdpipwc5dk','Café Color','## Top Reviews
> "The pastry shop I had the pleasure of visiting truly deserves the highest praise! It’s a place that beautifully combines tradition with modernity, offering products at the highest European standards.  From the very first step inside, you can see the attention to detail – the elegant interior, the aesthetically displayed desserts, and the exceptionally friendly staff create an atmosphere you’ll want to return to again and again. Every pastry delights not only with its appearance but, above all, with its taste. The ingredients are clearly of the highest quality – fresh, natural, and carefully selected.  I was especially impressed by the cakes and individual desserts, which could easily compete with the finest patisseries in Europe. The textures are perfectly balanced, the sweetness is just right, and the flavor combinations are both creative and refined. The professionalism of the team is evident in every detail. You can truly see their commitment to quality, presentation, and hygiene – all maintained according to top European standards.  This place proves that excellence in pastry-making can reach world-class levels. If you’re looking for premium quality, exceptional taste, and outstanding service, this pastry shop is an absolute must-visit. Highly recommended! 🍰✨"
> **- Piotr Kawinski (5/5/5)**

> "The desserts are absolutely delicious! I’ve ordered from this shop twice already. The presentation is beautiful and really shows the care and attention put into each item. The cream cheese flavor is amazing!!  I especially love mayongchid (marian plum), and this shop does such a great job using seasonal fruits to create unique and tasty desserts😍🙏🏻  I haven’t visited the store in person yet, but I definitely plan to! I’d love to try their drinks and also check out their nail and eyelash services. The customer service is excellent🥰 very attentive and friendly, which makes me want to keep coming back🫶🏻  I’m always happy to support a great local Thai business like this. Highly recommended!  แปลไทยคืออร่อยค่ะ ชอบๆๆ"
> **- blue ncn (5/5/5)**

> "I have the best eyelash volumizing and bending. Suepr natural for male look. The staffs are the best part, very genuine, friendly and welcoming. Thier Banoffi pie is so delicious and also its specialty coffee. I could not recommend this place"
> **- Watt Hermann Ratanadechakorn (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/caf-color-1.jpg','065 854 8222','78, แม่น้ำ, 30, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61566084867838&mibextid=LQQJ4d','["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.256+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.256+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/caf-color-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/caf-color-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=62377536846485734',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('caf-flore','standard','cmr07ig62005dq8xdanl5iszq','Café Flore','## Top Reviews
> "Modern and "
> **- Drnatura Johny (5/5/5)**

> "If you''re a coffee lover, this place deserves a spot on your list. The coffee was expertly prepared, beautifully presented, and full of flavor, with latte art that showed real attention to detail.  The overall experience feels very much in line with the standards of some of the best specialty cafés in Europe: quality-focused, stylish, and welcoming. Highly recommended for breakfast, brunch, or simply enjoying an exceptional cup of coffee."
> **- Simona Horňáček (5/5/5)**

> "We’ve been to this coffee shop a few times now and absolutely love it! The food is delicious, the coffee is excellent, and the atmosphere is wonderfully relaxing. It''s also a fantastic place to get some work done on a laptop. Highly recommended!"
> **- Alida (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/caf-flore-1.jpg','098 186 2888','55, 7 Mu4, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.258+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.258+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/caf-flore-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/caf-flore-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15946899030121613831',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('caf-kob-by-the-sea','standard','cmr07ig67005eq8xd1ng7b7zt','Café K.O.B (By The Sea)','## Top Reviews
> "Great coffee and delicious pastries with a great sea view. They have both tables and lounges with views over the seaside. Staff were friendly. Welcoming for children we had a four month old and a 3 1/2 year-old and there was a small playground within the cafe."
> **- Nick Holzherr (5/5/5)**

> "Very good food and smiling welcoming staff. Its beach facing restaurant famous for breakfast and brunch. ✅ Recommendation: you can have great coffee here , bruschetta, fried rice with egg, pancake with strawberries, lemonade drinks  🛑Avoid: any matcha 🍵 drinks.  🛵 Parking for two wheelers is free and plenty of."
> **- Clear Viewer (5/5/5)**

> "I recently had brunch here and overall it was good, but not quite excellent. The food was definitely enjoyable — I had the avocado toast with poached eggs and smoked salmon, and everything was fresh and nicely presented. The flavors were good, but for the price, I was expecting something a bit more memorable or flavorful. It was tasty, just not particularly exceptional.  The setting itself is really nice. The place has a beautiful atmosphere, open space, and a relaxed vibe that makes it pleasant to sit and have brunch. That part was definitely a highlight.  However, the service could be improved. When I arrived, no one explained where to wait or how the seating worked. There seemed to be a list or a queue, but it wasn’t clear who was waiting for a table or how long the wait would be. I ended up standing around on my own without any guidance, and no one came to tell me roughly how long it would take or what I should do. It felt a bit confusing and unorganized.  Once seated, I also noticed that everything took quite a while. I understand that brunch places can be busy, but there was waiting for almost everything. The meal itself took around 30 minutes to prepare, and overall it ended up taking close to an hour just to have brunch. Again, not terrible, but a bit long.  When it came time to pay, the interaction felt a bit awkward too. I went to the counter to settle the bill and it wasn’t very smooth — I almost had to confirm myself that I wanted to pay, which felt a little strange. Nothing dramatic, just not the most attentive customer service.  So overall: good food, nice location, pleasant atmosphere — but the service and organization could definitely be improved, and for the price I expected a bit more flavor and efficiency. Still a good experience, just not an exceptional one."
> **- Mister Benz (4/5/5)**',NULL,'096 653 1925','33/105 Moo 4, Bangrak, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://kingofbread.co/find-us/bangrak-beach/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.263+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.263+00:00',NULL,'https://maps.google.com/?cid=12969787746799804231',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('caf-kob-homegrown','standard','cmr07ig6a005fq8xdn0ilufn8','Café K.O.B (Homegrown)','## Top Reviews
> "This place is supposed to be famous for its pastries, but in our opinion they were rather average. We tried a raspberry bun, which was fine, but nothing special. The Turkish eggs toast was also quite ordinary, with bread that felt a bit sponge-like. The English muffin was the worst – it tasted like something from a cheap supermarket. The club sandwich was very greasy. Everything was served separately, and the staff didn’t seem able to place the dishes properly on the table – instead, they handed them to us one by one, leaving us to figure it out ourselves. Overall, average service and a disappointing experience."
> **- Gaia Maluha (3/5/5)**

> "I love croissants and freshly squeezed carrot juice. It''s just perfect here!))) For some reason, the atmosphere here is a bit reminiscent of an Australian resort town.) The only thing missing is surfers."
> **- maybetomorrow (5/5/5)**

> "After two weeks of Thai cuisine, pleasant surprise in the form of full english breakfast. Sadly, my stomach was not ready for the portion and had to leave leftovers. Great coffee as well!"
> **- Vasil (5/5/5)**',NULL,'095 273 3652','207, ตำบล มะเร็ต อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://kingofbread.co/find-us/hua-thanon-beach/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifpz0001q8xd0aml2ucx','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.266+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.266+00:00',NULL,'https://maps.google.com/?cid=13859112496544514764',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('caf-kob-king-of-bread-caf','standard','cmr07ig6c005gq8xdhfjnth4u','Café K.O.B (King Of Bread Café)','## Top Reviews
> "Awesome for western-type breakfasts, bread eggs etc. The variety is fantastic and the food is really good, especially for the price. Ive shopped around for breakfast / brunch places in Bophut and I find KOB to draw the best balance between menu variety, price, and quality. My go-to is the breakfast hash with cheese, but I also really enjoy all of their sandwiches and burgers. Staff are really friendly, and another extra bonus is that you can pay with card, so you can save your cash for when you really need it."
> **- Radu Mustata (5/5/5)**

> "Nice and cozy breakfast spot! The food was very delicious and well prepared, and the atmosphere made it a great place. Friendly and welcoming crew too, which made the experience even better. Would definitely come back again!"
> **- Serene Chua (5/5/5)**

> "It may be a bit overhyped, but I still thought it was good. It’s a breakfast and brunch spot with a wide variety of food and drinks to choose from, offering both Thai and Western options a nice fusion overall. It’s also a great place to work or spend time casually. Overall, it was a good experience."
> **- Monica’s Taste (4/5/5)**',NULL,'081 829 9045','122/11 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://kingofbread.co/find-us/bophut-village/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.268+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.268+00:00',NULL,'https://maps.google.com/?cid=7411510909436988231',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('caf-kob-seaside','standard','cmr07ig6f005hq8xdana05tya','Café K.O.B (Seaside)','## Top Reviews
> "Really enjoyed my visit to King of Bread. The panini was perfectly toasted with fresh ingredients, and the bread quality is excellent. The coffee paired really well with it too. Great spot for a quick breakfast or lunch. Will definitely come back! ☕🥪"
> **- Ern Lim (5/5/5)**

> "We stayed on the island for 12 days and managed to come here 3 times. The ice coffees were always really well done, we recommend the caramel macchiato frappe or ice. I loved the cheese and ham croissant and the service was really good. It also has a lovely view and parking right in front of the store."
> **- Tiffanie Dumas (5/5/5)**

> "Just had a quick brekki be4 the ferry. Full breakfast. Lots of bacon.nice bread. Sausage ok, herbie( but I not a sausage fan). Good friendly service. I saw another customer have a brushetta with mashed avacado + chopped tomatoes. Looked good too."
> **- Ray Larkin (5/5/5)**',NULL,'084 184 2541','310/25, Café K.O.B Seaside, เทศบาลนครเกาะสมุย อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://kingofbread.co/find-us/nathon/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig1h003iq8xdb1g9nifo','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.271+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.271+00:00',NULL,'https://maps.google.com/?cid=578061564746426154',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('cafe-69','standard','cmr07ig6h005iq8xdzwk3z1tm','Cafe 69','## Top Reviews
> "If you’re traveling in Thailand with someone who has celiac disease, finding a place that truly understands gluten-free needs feels like winning the lottery. Cafe69 in Koh Samui is exactly that place, and we are so grateful we found it.  Our daughter has celiac, and the staff here were genuinely knowledgeable and attentive about her dietary needs – something that is incredibly rare to come across in Thailand. It meant the world to us as parents to be able to relax and enjoy a meal together without constant worry.  Now, the vibe of the place is… let’s say distinctive. Very Joe Exotic energy. But please, do not let that fool you for even a second, because the food is absolutely outstanding. Fresh, creative, full of flavor, and every dish has its own special twist that makes it memorable. This isn’t your standard tourist restaurant – the chef clearly puts real thought and passion into what comes out of that kitchen.  Highly recommend to anyone visiting Koh Samui, especially if you’re traveling gluten-free!"
> **- Dima Yarovinsky-Yahel (5/5/5)**

> "Cafe 69 was hands down one of the best meals we had in Koh Samui.  We started with the Green Curry Chicken Pie, Red Curry Dumplings and Tuna Tartare, and every dish was incredible. The Green Curry Pie in particular was something I’ve never had before and absolutely loved.  For mains, the Soft Shell Crab in Black Pepper Sauce was a standout, but the Kao Soi Grilled River Prawn stole the show. The flavours were unreal and the presentation was stunning.  What I loved most was how creative the menu is while still feeling authentic and packed with flavour. You can tell a lot of thought goes into every dish.  Great service, great atmosphere and food that genuinely lives up to the hype.  Easily a 10/10 meal."
> **- Bianka Dorman (5/5/5)**

> "Absolutely outstanding food. Creative yet still authentically Thai, and genuinely some of the best food we’ve had on our trip to Ko Samui.  The owner was incredibly friendly and attentive, clearly passionate about the menu. He took the time to walk us through recommendations and explain the dishes, which made the experience even better.  For starters we had the green curry chicken pie, tuna tartare, and duck red curry dumplings- all were exceptional, packed with flavour and beautifully presented. For mains, the stewed beef cheek with holy basil was tender and delicious, and the soft shell crab Pad Thai was fantastic. Every dish looked as good as it tasted.  The restaurant itself is cosy and quirky, with unique decor and presentation that really sets it apart. Portions are generous and the prices are very reasonable for the quality. The owner also recommended the lamb shank massaman, which we’ll definitely be back to try next time.  Highly recommend booking during busier times, although we were lucky to walk straight in as a table for two. We’ll absolutely be coming back if we’re ever in Ko Samui again."
> **- Tracey Stanbridge (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cafe-69-1.jpg','081 978 1945','157 52 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://m.facebook.com/Cafe69KohSamui/','["Monday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: Closed","Saturday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.273+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.273+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cafe-69-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cafe-69-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12629487907466767310',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('cafe-meow','standard','cmr07ig6j005jq8xdlbyj35mm','Cafe Meow','## Top Reviews
> "Cozy and clean cafe. Great coffee ☕️ , the pastries are really good. The croissants 🥐 had very good lamination, flaky and buttery. The blueberry danish pastry I had was really nice, flaky pastry, with velvety pastry cream and fresh, big, juicy blueberries baked onto it. My son had the Philly cheesesteak sandwich had generous amount of beef and cheese 🧀 sandwiched between freshly baked focaccia. An absolute hidden jem!"
> **- Siew Yee Tang (5/5/5)**

> "Super friendly staff. The Flat White coffee is outstanding, any Australian would have to agree on this. Definitely worth stopping in for a daily caffeine fix."
> **- David (5/5/5)**

> "Such great coffee, food and the service is always amazing. It’s such a great local spot with very reason prices. I love this place!"
> **- May Tan (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cafe-meow-1.jpg','063 125 1384','70, 36 Moo5, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://meowcoffeeandbakery.com/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 4:00 AM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 4:00 PM"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.275+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.275+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cafe-meow-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cafe-meow-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6011406031652022371',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('cafe-talay','standard','cmr07ig6l005kq8xdikkbdkot','Cafe Talay','## Top Reviews
> "Visited this restaurant multiple times for lunch and dinner twice as it was so lovely! The location is amazing, chill vibes and great food! One dinner with friends we had a couple starters, duck curry, pad kaprao and seafood curry. Seriously tasty! The whole group had a lovely evening. Cocktails are delicious too!"
> **- Anya H (5/5/5)**

> "By far the best barracuda fillet I have ever eaten! I can recommend this restaurant with a clear conscience.  It is a really beautiful location, a great price-performance ratio and very friendly staff!!  Thank you for this lovely evening... :)"
> **- Christian Fetzer (5/5/5)**

> "Definitely my favorite restaurant on Koh Samui. A big menu selection, authentic Thai food and very kind staff. Always locals around enjoying themselves and having a great time. Very calm beachside tables for relaxation, romance or getting some work done. I have never been disappointed by the food during the countless times I have eaten here. Strong and cheap drinks, fantastic food and beautiful views. I’m not sure what more you could ask for!"
> **- Carter Haggerty (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cafe-talay-1.jpg','092 465 5288','Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 12:00 – 9:30 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 9:30 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 9:30 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 9:30 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 9:30 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 9:30 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.277+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.277+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cafe-talay-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cafe-talay-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14671845102463478869',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('calis-caf-resto','standard','cmr07ig6n005lq8xd2j4kgjbi','Cali''s Café & Resto','## Top Reviews
> "I can’t recommend Callis Café on Koh Samui highly enough! This is our second year in a row visiting, and every single time the experience has been absolutely perfect.  The food quality is outstanding, every dish is prepared with real care and top ingredients. The chicken is made from proper chicken breast (you can truly taste the difference), and the pizza is honestly the best I’ve ever had. Even the cocktails are first-class and crafted to perfection.  The atmosphere is just as impressive as the food. The café combines a modern, cozy design with a stylish and welcoming vibe that makes you want to stay for hours.  On top of that, the service is exceptional. The staff are more than friendly, always welcoming, attentive, and genuinely caring, which makes the whole experience even more special.  If you’re on Koh Samui, Callis Café is an absolute must-visit. We’ll definitely keep coming back!  Thank u so much ☺️  Kind Regards  Philipp from Germany"
> **- P. K. (5/5/5)**

> "I absolutely loved this place! ❤️ It was my first evening in Thailand, and I couldn’t have picked a better spot. The food was honestly perfect—super tasty and beautifully prepared—and the location is just a dream.  What really made it special for me was the atmosphere. Everything felt so relaxed and welcoming. My personal highlight: they have a huge selection of games, which makes the whole experience even more fun and unique.  Such a cool concept, amazing food, and a beautiful setting—I’ll definitely come back!"
> **- Julia (5/5/5)**

> "I love it ! ❤️ Even for Koh Samui—and the island scene in General—I honestly didn’t expect this level of quality. We picked this place for a welcome dinner after picking up my girlfriend from the airport, and she was just as impressed as I was.  I wasn’t surprised—but still, this place exceeded my expectations once again. I’ve been on Koh Samui for two months now, and finding a restaurant with this level of ambiance and food quality is truly rare.  The owner is exactly what you’d hope for, and the entire team—from the kitchen to the service—deserves a solid 10/10. Everything felt genuine and well thought out.  I especially loved the concept of combining great food with a relaxed evening and board games—it’s such a cool and unique idea.  I’ve been working in gastronomy for 17 years as a restaurant manager, and I was genuinely impressed.  Thank you—and stay healthy. I’ll definitely be back!"
> **- Robin (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/calis-caf-resto-1.jpg','095 037 3453','Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 5:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 5:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 5:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 5:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 5:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 5:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.279+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.279+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/calis-caf-resto-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/calis-caf-resto-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=18083471368815131924',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('cape-away-beach-bar','standard','cmr07ig6p005mq8xdzb2hg4c3','Cape Away Beach Bar','## Top Reviews
> "I recently had lunch and drinks with my girls on a Samui trip. The staff, especially Bom, were very nice and provided great service. As someone in the hospitality industry, I can tell he did a really good job. The food and drinks are reasonably priced. You can chill here; I highly recommend it."
> **- JUJUBEE EWW (5/5/5)**

> "This restaurant offers a breathtaking sunset view, creating a tranquil and magical atmosphere. The gentle glow of the bonfire adds a cozy charm, making it a perfect place for a relaxing evening with great food and unforgettable views.  I am so happy, and I hope that I will get to come back here again."
> **- SORPOR WORMOR (5/5/5)**

> "Cape Away Beach Bar & Resort quickly became our favorite place. We ended up being there almost every day because it simply felt right. The food was amazing – real, proper Thai food, always freshly prepared, and always delicious. We truly loved it.  We stayed at the resort for five nights and were honestly overwhelmed by how kind and attentive the staff were. Every single person was warm, genuine, and incredibly caring. The whole team is just so sweet – you can really feel that they enjoy what they do.  Our villa was only a few steps away from the beach, which made everything feel easy and relaxed. Some days we had freshly cooked food brought to the pool, other times cocktails were delivered straight to the beach. Nothing ever felt like too much trouble.  It was one of those holidays that stays with you. We didn’t want to leave and already know that we’ll come back. Cape Away feels special, and we’re very grateful for the time we spent there."
> **- Kathrin Grabher (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cape-away-beach-bar-1.jpg','081 884 5321','78 after Mimosa Hotel, to the end of the road Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.capeawaysamui.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifso000kq8xdfe9gpaon','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.281+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.281+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cape-away-beach-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cape-away-beach-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2038645330029440731',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('cape-away-villas','standard','cmr07ig6r005nq8xdmyt2of4o','Cape Away Villas','## Top Reviews
> "Every now and then, you come across a place that reminds you what hospitality is supposed to feel like. Cape Beach Villas is one of those rare places.  Nestled in a quiet corner of Koh Samui, this well-designed property feels like a private sanctuary by the sea. With excellent snorkelling, swimming, paddleboarding, and kayaking right on its doorstep, it''s easy to spend entire days without leaving the hotel.  My husband and I attended a friend''s wedding here and were blown away by the team''s warmth, professionalism, and attention to detail. The event was beautifully executed, and nothing ever seemed too much trouble.  Cape Beach Villas is the kind of place that stays with you long after you''ve checked out. We can''t wait to come back."
> **- Crystal Chua (5/5/5)**

> "Our stay at Cape Beach Villa Resort in Koh Samui was truly unforgettable from the very first moment.  The entire property is beautifully designed, incredibly well maintained, and decorated with so much love for detail in a stunning boho style. As soon as we entered the resort, we immediately felt the open, peaceful, and welcoming atmosphere.  We received such a warm, professional, and friendly welcome, which made us feel comfortable right away. We stayed in the Villa Vanilla, located directly by the pool and close to the beach side, which was especially perfect and convenient for us as a family with children. The short walking distances made our holiday so much easier and more relaxing.  The rooms were spotless, beautifully maintained, and felt cozy and comfortable from the very beginning — almost like a second home.  Breakfast was absolutely outstanding with a wonderful à la carte selection, and every single dish tasted amazing.  The beach and the sea were simply beautiful. Visiting in May was perfect for us because it was very quiet and peaceful, exactly what we had hoped for in a relaxing family vacation.  But no matter how beautiful a hotel may be, what truly makes a stay special are the people. The staff at Cape Beach Villa Resort made our vacation exceptional. Everyone was incredibly kind, attentive, professional, helpful, and genuinely caring. Their warmth and hospitality made our stay absolutely perfect.  For everyone planning to visit Koh Samui and looking for a truly special place to stay: this is my personal heartfelt recommendation — definitely book Cape Beach Villa Resort!"
> **- Elisabeth Boettcher (5/5/5)**

> "We had an absolutely amazing stay here during our time in Koh Samui. From the moment we arrived, the staff went above and beyond to make us feel welcome. Their friendliness, professionalism, and attention to detail truly made the experience special. Nothing was ever too much trouble, and their exceptional service played a huge part in making our stay so enjoyable.  The accommodation itself was fantastic, comfortable and well maintained. It provided everything needed for a relaxing and memorable stay. The atmosphere created was perfect and it was clear that great care is taken to ensure guests have the best possible experience.  The beach was beautiful, quiet and not overcrowded making it the perfect place to relax and spend quality time with family and friends.  I would highly recommend this place to anyone visiting Koh Samui. If I ever return to the island, this will definitely be my first choice of place to stay. Thank you to Chrissy and the entire team for such a wonderful experience!"
> **- Mark (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cape-away-villas-1.jpg','081 884 5321','78, after Mimosa Hotel, to the end of the road, ตำบล แม่น้ำ Amphoe, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://capeawaysamui.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifso000kq8xdfe9gpaon','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.283+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.283+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cape-away-villas-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cape-away-villas-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17954837624763224457',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('cape-fahn','standard','cmr07ig6u005oq8xdpsx9i7q5','Cape Fahn','## Top Reviews
> "We had a mixed experience at Cape Fahn Hotel.  The good: The room was beautiful, very well maintained, and the private pool was large and really enjoyable. The breakfast was nice, and the spa massage was excellent and reasonably priced.  The less good: Getting to and from the hotel is quite complicated. There are boat transfers only until 11 PM, and if you return later than that you need to inform the reception in advance. Some staff members made us feel uncomfortable about this instead of handling it pleasantly. There was also a woman working at the pool who was rude and unfriendly, which really affected the atmosphere.  In general, throughout the stay there was often a feeling that guests were expected to keep spending more money, which made the experience feel less relaxed and welcoming.  We also asked for a late check-out. Of course we understand that this is never guaranteed, but the hotel seemed half empty and it felt like there was no real effort to accommodate the request.  The pool and facilities are nice, but not as impressive as we expected from this level of hotel.  Overall, if the hotel itself felt truly exceptional in every aspect, the complicated access might have been worth it. For us, unfortunately, it wasn’t, and we would not return."
> **- אילנית שפס (3/5/5)**

> "The best hotel we have ever stayed at by an absolute mile. We were incredibly excited for our trip to Cape Fahn, but nothing could have prepared us for just how special this place truly is. From start to finish, it was a flawless, unforgettable experience.  From the moment we arrived at the airport, we were warmly welcomed by Dima, which instantly set the tone for the entire stay. The service from that point on was simply exceptional — every member of staff went out of their way to make us feel relaxed, cared for, and completely at home. Nothing was ever too much trouble, and every small detail was handled perfectly.  The hotel itself is breathtaking. The villas are stunning, and immaculately maintained, offering complete privacy while still feeling luxurious and welcoming - each villa has their own private pool, so cool. The island and beach are absolutely magical - peaceful, pristine, and the perfect escape from the outside world. It genuinely feels like stepping into paradise.  A huge thank you must go to Dima and Neef especially, who were both amazing and truly made our stay even more special. They made the stay even better than it already would have been! If we could give this 100 stars, we would!!"
> **- Harry Heptonstall (5/5/5)**

> "We had the most incredible stay. From the moment we arrived, the team made us feel genuinely welcome and cared for. The property is stunning, the rooms are beautifully designed, and every detail feels thoughtful and intentional.  The property is absolutely stunning - beautifully designed, impeccably maintained, and set in the most breathtaking surroundings  What truly sets this hotel apart is the service - warm, attentive, and seamless without ever feeling intrusive. The entire experience felt special and memorable, and we will absolutely be returning. Thank you for such a flawless stay."
> **- Aarna Bedi (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cape-fahn-1.jpg','077 602 301','24/269, ตำบล บ่อผุด Koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.capefahnhotel.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifsv000nq8xdrwnu123q','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.286+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.286+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cape-fahn-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cape-fahn-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5235643638192039845',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('capybara-coffee','standard','cmr07ig6z005qq8xdjz3esap7','Capybara Coffee','## Top Reviews
> "Cute place. We got to feed the capybaras, they seem content with their space and do not distressed or anything. They also had meerkats, prairie dogs and Chinese bamboo rats. The staff let us hold a meerkat who seemed happy to be held. The meerkats were alert, playful and making happy noises. The rainbow soda was very good. The staff are pretty strict on the 30 minute time slot, just to be aware."
> **- Kiera Willis (4/5/5)**

> "Amazing experience! Really friendly welcoming staff. They have 2 older capybaras and have recently got 2 younger ones, as well as meerkats and other animals. You can feed the capybaras too. They looked very happy and were looked after well. Really cute items in the gift shop after too. So happy we got to experience this. Thank you"
> **- Charlie H (5/5/5)**

> "Entry fee plus you buy a drink. Handlers are quick to help you. A variety of animals. Based on pics, I thought they were all free roaming. Capyburas are free roaming but they mostly stayed in one area. The meerkats and mole rat are in glass front pens. Felt bad watching the handlers constantly disturbing them so people could hold them."
> **- Laura (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/capybara-coffee-1.jpg','095 591 0794','Ko Fan, Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.capybaracoffeethailand.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ig6y005pq8xd4jrvheih','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.291+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.291+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/capybara-coffee-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/capybara-coffee-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12112510251418567691',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('car-washing-wurth','standard','cmr07ig71005rq8xdfhtgs6cb','Car Washing Wurth','## Top Reviews
> "Two men were very meticulous in cleaning every area of the exterior of my truck. I was impressed with their detailing and time spent, and proud of the way my truck looked when finished. Price charged for cleaning the exterior (only) of my 4 door cab truck was 250 Baht."
> **- Brian Streb (5/5/5)**

> "Was not impressed. 900 for a clean inside and out for sale. Cane back with dirty mirrors and stains on the plastic still. You can definitely do better than this"
> **- Mike McNamee (3/5/5)**

> "Good service. Waiting room with aircon. Good for bikes and scooters too."
> **- Vadim Shevchenko (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/car-washing-wurth-1.jpg','086 479 3556','H282+MHH, Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifui0012q8xdzn158clv','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.293+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.293+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/car-washing-wurth-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/car-washing-wurth-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4398813671791386042',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('carnival-beach-village','standard','cmr07ig73005sq8xdkxk19ppi','Carnival Beach Village','## Top Reviews
> "We had such a great experience at this beach bar and honestly everything about the day was just perfect.  First of all, the location is amazing. You’re literally right in front of the sea with a beautiful view, comfortable sunbeds, and a super relaxed atmosphere. The beach itself is clean, the water is clear and very pleasant to swim in, and there are also nice pools available which were really well maintained. Being able to switch between the sea and the pools made the whole experience even better.  The food was a very pleasant surprise. I ordered the chicken pad thai and it was excellent — perfectly cooked, flavorful, and very generous in portion. You can tell it’s made fresh, with good quality ingredients and great balance of flavors. Definitely one of the best pad thais I’ve had at a beach bar.  The drinks were also fantastic. We tried a couple of fresh juices and they were delicious — refreshing, well prepared, and perfect for a hot beach day. Exactly what you want when you’re relaxing by the sea.  Service was friendly and efficient, the staff spoke good English which made everything easy, and the overall vibe of the place is just chill and enjoyable. It’s the kind of spot where you can spend the whole day: swim, eat, relax, have drinks, and just enjoy the beach.  Overall, a really great beach bar with good food, great drinks, nice pools, and a beautiful sea view. Highly recommend spending a day here if you’re in the area — we’ll definitely come back."
> **- Mister Benz (5/5/5)**

> "great family beach club. the staff is very friendly.  their food is ok. the location is 👍 👌 the pool and the place feel the weight of few years of tropical condition."
> **- aurelien mery (4/5/5)**

> "It''s a super cheap place right by the beach, the fruit shakes and pineapple fried rice are amazing!  The staff were so helpful and friendly, they even moved an umbrella to our chairs instead of just telling us where to sit.  Being 8 months pregnant, I was so relieved the food and drinks were safe – I could just relax and enjoy the ocean view.  They don''t have towels though, so bring your own. Everything was clean, especially the toilets."
> **- Syimah Beck (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/carnival-beach-village-1.jpg','095 282 4468','59/240, Carnival Beach Village, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://carnivalbeachvillage.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifsv000nq8xdrwnu123q','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.295+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.295+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/carnival-beach-village-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/carnival-beach-village-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11617275673949897599',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('casa-de-mar','standard','cmr07ig75005tq8xdywd5trdv','Casa De Mar','## Top Reviews
> "Great quiet hotel walking distance from the city center (~20 min). My room was very comfortable, I had everything I needed. Water was provided every two days (2 bottles 0.5l). Beach towels and cool beach bag offered. Small private beach terrace apart from the pool area (you can always find a sunchair there) with good access to the ocean (shallow, but with high tide you can even swim). Service was just amazing, I would rate the staff six out of five, if I could! So helpful and always sincerely friendly! I just did not like the resto that much but there is plenty of choice for the meals nearby."
> **- Tatiana Sergienia (5/5/5)**

> "Had a great stay at Casa De Mar. Beautiful beachfront hotel with a very convenient location. The staff were friendly and welcoming, and the service was excellent. Special thanks to Win and Min from housekeeping they were very professional and kept my room very clean. The breakfast buffet was also very good, and the staff in the breakfast restaurant were all really kind and attentive. Really happy with the hospitality and would definitely stay here again!"
> **- Nancy J (5/5/5)**

> "Lovely small beachfront hotel. The staff were all amazing! Jinny took daily care of the rooms in an excellent way. Location is good, on a quiet part of the beach. The busy town is about a 30 minute walk or 5 minutes by taxi/scooter. Ocean access is good and the beach chairs placed on a veranda near the pool. Pool has a perfect temperature and is swimmable. The ocean in front of the hotel has very low water for a big stretch, so safe for kids, but not ideal for swimming. Food and drinks quality is high standard. Breakfast has good variety and they make nice coffees."
> **- O W (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/casa-de-mar-1.jpg','088 760 4263','154/16 M.2 Chaweng Beach Tambon Bo Put, Suratthani, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.casademarsamui.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.297+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.297+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/casa-de-mar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/casa-de-mar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8073144725723387767',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('cascade-tara','standard','cmr07ig77005uq8xdf5yj6mq0','Cascade Tara','## Top Reviews
> "The perfect retreat! This hotel is truly lovely. Set away from the busyness of the more popular parts of the island, the hotel feels quiet and peaceful. The rooms are little villas which gives such a nice level of privacy away from the other guests. The staff are so kind and thoughtful and the restaurant has a good range of options."
> **- Martha Hind (5/5/5)**

> "Absolutely incredible hotel! 🫶🏼We planned to stay for only one night, but the experience was so exceptional that we are 100% coming back. Everything was beyond perfect — outstanding service, beautiful atmosphere, and top-level quality in every detail. This place truly exceeded all expectations. Highly, highly recommended! 🤩"
> **- Grieta Kirsteine (5/5/5)**

> "One of the cleanest hotels I have been to. Housekeeping was great and the reception staff are excellent. Kitchen staff went out of their way to provide my daughter with dumplings for breakfast everyday when we requested for it.  Shout out to Pan for going the extra mile in ensuring that we had a good supply of water and just being a generally hardworking and friendly guy.  Would love to stay here again if I was ever in Koh Samui again."
> **- Shamhaad Fahumee (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cascade-tara-1.jpg','098 822 9566','FX8P+69, Na Mueang, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.cascadetara.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ig4i004oq8xdv207xuh2','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.299+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.299+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cascade-tara-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cascade-tara-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7565702144161828449',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('cat-lover-hotel','standard','cmr07ig79005vq8xdjv52v3tu','Cat Lover Hotel','## Top Reviews
> "I had an amazing experience with Cat Lover Hotel Samui! Prae was incredibly kind, flexible, and accommodating with my schedule. She sent daily photos and videos, which gave me so much peace of mind while I was away.  The camera access and regular updates made it easy to see that my cat was happy, comfortable, and well cared for. It''s clear that Prae genuinely loves and understands cats. My cat came home relaxed and content, which says everything.  I highly recommend Cat Lover Hotel Samui to anyone looking for a safe, caring, and professional place for their cat to stay. I will definitely be bringing my cat back in the future 💖💛"
> **- Haley Ann Borgrud (5/5/5)**

> "So happy with my experience with this place. The owner is a lovely lady and takes very good care of the cats who stay with her. She sent us updates and pictures and we could also login to a camera to check out cats at any time while we were away. She provides excellent service, is friendly and very caring. Highly recommend!"
> **- Jack Boulevard (5/5/5)**

> "For wonderful care of your cats, these guys are the very best on Samui. Wonderfully caring people, and a safe, happy environment for your cats. Our 3 cats have been staying there whenever we travel for a number of years now. You cannot find a better, safer place for your kitties. Fantastic small business and they are so very helpful and caring. We know our cats will be incredibly well care for always. Simply the best cat care on the island. They love cats"
> **- todd “Cervelo” allan (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cat-lover-hotel-1.jpg','092 251 3938','102, Chaweng, 29 village 6, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.catloverhotelsamui.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.301+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.301+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cat-lover-hotel-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cat-lover-hotel-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3055622296244871300',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('celes','standard','cmr07ig7b005wq8xdgns08fbp','Celes','## Top Reviews
> "The hotel has two sections: an old wing and a new wing. The rooms in the new section are beautiful and comfortable, while the old section is at a much lower standard.  Breakfast starts closing even 5 minutes before the official end time, and the staff seem stressed and eager to shut everything down. This happened every morning and felt a bit unpleasant.  Housekeeping did not clear the used dishes from our room — cutlery, glasses, plates, etc. In addition, they did not provide enough towels and at times did not leave toilet paper. One day, the room was only cleaned late in the afternoon.  Overall, we stayed in a beachfront villa, so the room itself was amazing. However, the service experience is very much in line with a 4-star rating, or perhaps even less. The hotel restaurant is extremely expensive."
> **- Roei Elbaz (3/5/5)**

> "Mixed but enjoyable! The rooms are large and well kept. The service, while friendly, was painfully slow. We waited around half an hour for the pre-check in, then when we went back to finalise check in and pick up our room keys it took even longer. We were told to sit and wait while others checked in, with no queue management, so people who arrived later checked in before us. Quite frustrating, especially for a one night stay.  The pools are very nice and the bar/restaurant has a lovely view and good cocktails with a reasonable happy hour. Pizza was a little unusual but nice enough! Breakfast spread was very good.  The location is good. It’s on a very main road like many of the resorts in samui and so leaving the hotel wasn’t very pleasant. Inside the resort feels sufficiently insulated from the road though and the beachfront is beautiful."
> **- Mark Johnson (4/5/5)**

> "We had a wonderful stay here 🤍 Even though we had a small issue with the door during our stay, the staff handled everything incredibly quickly and professionally, without interfering with our trip at all. They made the whole process very easy and stress-free. The breakfasts were excellent every morning as well; so fresh and delicious! Thank you for such a lovely experience, we would happily stay again."
> **- Pilar Malah (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/celes-1.jpg','077 900 999','175/3 Moo1 Thaveerat-Pakdee Road, Bophut, ตำบล แม่น้ำ Koh Samui, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.celessamui.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.303+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.303+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/celes-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/celes-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4112121751357371804',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('centara-reserve','standard','cmr07ig7e005xq8xdt8dy3swx','Centara Reserve','## Top Reviews
> "I don''t have a bad word to say about this hotel!! Everything was perfect!! From the hotel itself which looks like heaven to the amazing employees who work there who always make sure that nothing is missing. Extremely high service awareness. Thanks to the amazing Michelle who took care of us from day one and to the stunning Sandy from the hotel''s steakhouse. Crazy breakfast - (for celiacs here there is a gluten-free stand of bread, cereals and cakes). Recommend!!"
> **- Eden Levi (5/5/5)**

> "From Stress to Pure Relaxation – 9.5/10! Centara Reserve Samui 🌼 is the perfect place to leave everyday life behind.  Here is our summary: • The Welcome: We arrived feeling very stressed but were welcomed with great warmth immediately. • Top Service by Mrs.Peach: A huge 🤗 thank you to Peach 🫶! Her professional skills and bright smile made us feel comfortable from the very first second. She perfectly represents the hotel''s great hospitality.🙏 • The Team: All staff members are extremely helpful and kind 🙏🌻, even though they work very hard. • Resort & Comfort: Top rooms, a "
> **- Lars Schniete (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing Vacation with Centara Reserve Samui!!!! The staff were incredibly warm and friendly, especially the breakfast team. Breakfast had so many delicious options that even after 4 nights we still couldn’t try everything! The room was beautiful, the view was stunning, and the hotel had a very natural and relaxing atmosphere. Also, the Thai restaurant “Sa-Nga” is a must try! We truly loved our stay and will definitely come back again!"
> **- Watiya Junniang (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/centara-reserve-1.jpg','077 230 500','38, Chaweng Beach, 2 Borpud, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.centarahotelsresorts.com/centarareserve/crs/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.306+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.306+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/centara-reserve-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/centara-reserve-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2840075739896870929',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('centara-villas','standard','cmr07ig7h005yq8xd0y45d55i','Centara Villas','## Top Reviews
> "Nice quiet location, perfect to relax. Anu and her team were excellent, taking care of us for 7 days at the bar and in the restaurant.  Lovely pool overlooking the beach and the rooms were nice too. Our room was a little dated, needing some maintenance while we were there but the team were very helpful and straight onto it. We stayed in the family suite which was very big so plenty of room for our family of 4 with a nice plunge pool. Perfect for when you want to kick back in the room to relax and the kids wanted to keep swimming.  Beautiful well kept gardens throughout the property and lots of stairs which didn’t bother us at all but something to consider if mobility is an issue.  Also an extra bonus was having an awesome little beach bar right next door “cool bar”, highly recommend that place too. Easy enough to get a Grab to/from Lamai and Chaweng."
> **- Ashley Durrington (4/5/5)**

> "We had a great time here. Everyone is super sweet and does his best to help the guests. The restaurant quality is top notch and not expensive, the view is absolutely incredible, it''s quiet and feels intimate. Great for couples, friends and family with many different activities for free during the stay. It''s a bit far away from the main city but buses are available and you can lend a scooter directly at the hotel (very easy to drive). The only thing is that the staff doesn''t al!us speak English so it can be hard to get your request through. Some mistakes will be made 🙂"
> **- mercier anika (5/5/5)**

> "Overall this is a good hotel for families, couples or traveling solo. They give you your own private villa. It’s perfectly self contained and you can eat all 3 meals. However breakfast there is only a buffet option, would have preferred to be able to eat à la cart since I don’t eat much. With the hotel being tucked away from town you will not have access unless you walk around 1 mile in or take a shuttle. The resort does offer a shuttle service but you have to sign up the day before. Overall a good option for travelers looking to unplug."
> **- Andrea Garcia (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/centara-villas-1.jpg','077 424 020','111 Moo 2, Maret Natien Beach, ตำบล หน้าเมือง อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.centarahotelsresorts.com/centara/csv','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ig3v004fq8xdw6q7afhh','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.309+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.309+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/centara-villas-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/centara-villas-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2953160265965932914',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('center-one-game-toys','standard','cmr07ig7j005zq8xdyi3knmwh','Center One Game & Toys','## Top Reviews
> "Great toy shop with a fantastic selection and friendly staff. Clean, well-organized, and reasonably priced. My child loved it—we’ll definitely be back! Perfect for gifts too"
> **- Jaya W (5/5/5)**

> "⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ Excellent Toy Shop on Koh Samui! What a fantastic little toy shop! A great selection of quality toys for kids of all ages — from educational games to fun beach toys and unique gifts you don’t find in the big stores. The staff were friendly, patient, and genuinely helpful. It’s clear they really care about their customers and love what they do. Prices were very reasonable too. Highly recommend stopping by if you’re on the island and looking for something special for the kids (or even the young at heart!)."
> **- Timothy MacDonald (5/5/5)**

> "Very helpful and friendly staff when looking for Christmas presents for my kids!"
> **- Victoria Chavez Harrington (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/center-one-game-toys-1.jpg','093 787 4800','128 1 ม.1, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/Center-one-game-toys-104759617660102/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.311+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.311+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/center-one-game-toys-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/center-one-game-toys-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9872569561917481838',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('central-samui','standard','cmr07ig7l0060q8xd50wzhs8o','Central Samui','## Top Reviews
> "This is a great shopping mall with a huge number of shops, as well as many cafés and restaurants. There is also a very nice children’s room, even for very young kids, with staff supervising them, which is a big plus.  The location is excellent, and it is especially nice that Chaweng night market is located nearby, making the area even more lively and convenient to visit. In addition, there are lots of entertainment options, so there is plenty to do besides shopping.  If you are traveling with children, this mall is definitely worth visiting."
> **- Yuliia Dudareva (5/5/5)**

> "Central Samui Mall - one of Koh Samui’s top shopping and lifestyle destinations, offering a mix of international and local brands, a vibrant food court, and a family-friendly atmosphere."
> **- Jitesh Purkait (The Nomadic Guy) (4/5/5)**

> "As a Thai person I really love open air malls they give a natural and relaxing vibe and make me want to keep walking around It feels unique and different from most malls คิดถึงสมุยจัง❤️❤️"
