> **- Rita Chiara Mele (5/5/5)**

> "Very cozy place and relaxing music with a nice staff and delicious food and drinks. We visit them many times to be on the sunbeds on this amazing beach and enjoy the meals and drinks.  We cant revies the rooms, because we didnt sleep there. Its really a worth to ve visited. We come back for sure next year. Kabkun Krhub"
> **- TOFI (5/5/5)**

> "Always eat here when in lipa Noi. Great place for drinks and food and all reasonably priced. It’s right on the beach so has sunset views to die for and chairs on the beach too. Service is mostly good but it does get busy so food sometimes takes a little longer. There is a limited menu but we have tried many things and they are all good, their milk shakes are brilliant too. Thai dishes are a great sized portion for the money. Highly recommended."
