INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('chom-dao-beach-club','standard','cmr07iga30071q8xdsy6xhw33','Chom Dao Beach Club','## Top Reviews
> "Top place in samui. If u want to be sure u get in , better make a reservation. This comes with a minimum spend of 2000 per adult. But yeah once u are there and u start ordering,  pretty sure u will use all the min spend. So it s reasonable.  I am not really into this kind of systems but ok... understandable that they need to do it as its a top place with top views. Food and drink were very good quality , good portions. Friendly staff. And very good atmosphere. It all fits together,  the music,  the food , the view , the place itself.... I would visit it again."
> **- steven work (4/5/5)**

> "First, the service was really nice and the atmosphere is perfect, but as for the food, I really don''t recommend it.  I ordered the steak sandwich cooked medium rare, but the first time they served it well done. However, the service was really nice, and they apologized and replaced it. The second steak sandwich, as shown in the picture, was almost well done, not medium rare.😅  If you want to come here, I recommend grabbing some drinks and just chilling with the atmosphere."
> **- Tanapoom Thanapura (2/5/5)**

> "Staff very friendly and view is amazing but food is average and expensive, drinks not good and overpriced, staff don’t know their menu and are disorganised.  It’s ok to sit enjoy one drink at the sunset but otherwise do not recommend at all"
> **- Dzina (2/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/chom-dao-beach-club-1.jpg','077 245 795','178 2, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/ChomDaoBeachClub','["Monday: 6:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 6:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 6:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 6:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 6:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 6:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 6:30 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.403+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.403+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/chom-dao-beach-club-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/chom-dao-beach-club-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5295880789542127018',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('chomtalay','standard','cmr07iga60072q8xdqwc4et47','Chomtalay','## Top Reviews
> "Very bad service, all food gone, very bad manage the menu and order. Waiting for very long, no steam rice, no spoon and fork beside asking. Terrible experience. It is located next to Guanwu statute. Will never come back again. Taking order without acknowledging. I ordered 2 bottles of water she resisted 4, ordered minced pork but servsed seafood fried with sweet basil, ordered 2 steamed rice come 3.  My headache with her communication."
> **- Qrius S (1/5/5)**

> "Really chill beach family restaurant! Nice view, nice owner, nice food, nice cocktails that pack a punch. Come and visit here if you are in the south of the island please come and visit them, they deserve it 😄"
> **- HZL (5/5/5)**

> "My wife and I are in Koh Samui for a month and we have been twice already! Twice because the Thai food is excellent, as is the price, as is the service, as is the atmosphere there as well. It is right on the beach, and is a very, very local and basic Thai restaurant. To find it, it is in the village of Hua Thanon on the left before the very sharp right-hand bend in the road. Look for the brightly lit-up lanterns and you''re there! The owner, a very friendly guy, and his very cute family live there. You might get a visit or two from the local  beach-dogs but they are nothing to stress about as they know if they upset any customers they will be chased off."
> **- Nick (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/chomtalay-1.jpg','089 874 3737','C2VF+QV4, Maret, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.406+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.406+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/chomtalay-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/chomtalay-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11260973425527851746',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('cielo-oriental-spa','standard','cmr07iga80073q8xd2dbf2jz3','Cielo Oriental Spa','## Top Reviews
> "Fantastic place and massage! I usually had very back aches and frozen shoulders. My masseuse Kungira did  such a wonderful job that I felt so Alive again after that! Nice place with a very welcoming lobby area. Very clean private room for me and my husband. Prices were so reasonable  as compared to other spas which cost twice as much. Will definitely visit here again given the chance!"
> **- Desiree Chua (5/5/5)**

> "The massage was very standard, costing three times more than what you can find on the street — 1,500 baht per hour. The towel I received had a hole in it. After the massage, when I was completely covered in oil, I took a shower for less than 10 minutes, and they rushed me so they could take the next booking. You should space out your appointments more and not rush guests in the middle of their shower. The receptionist was very kind and polite to me."
> **- Kobi Turgeman (3/5/5)**

> "Best massage i had in Thailand. Hands down. Little Thai girl had the strongest hands I''ve ever felt. Excellent and would highly recommend"
> **- tyler hiranaka (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cielo-oriental-spa-1.jpg','086 944 3838','เลขที่ 79/100 Tongsai Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://business.google.com/v/_/AKsrIN3mzwyiCysM4ea7pqb_PKcYj_XPPjfkJ9fmpXv2-6eZb8Znnvk/7c11/_?exp=1778401&myads=1','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifv2001aq8xdag7cvjgf','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.408+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.408+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cielo-oriental-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cielo-oriental-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8976663594416397739',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('cielo-samui-boutique-hotel-spa','standard','cmr07igaa0074q8xd76032exo','Cielo Samui Boutique Hotel & Spa','## Top Reviews
> "We truly loved our stay and felt extremely relaxed and at peace. We mostly spent our time by the restaurant and pool lounging and eating and drinking and watching the ocean. If you''re looking for a place to truly feel relaxed, this is it.  We came at a low season. We never had issues finding a day bed or feeling like we weren''t taken cared of at the restaurant. We also just missed the start of construction at the hotel next door.  Special thank you to Kat, the wonderful concierge who was welcoming and very helpful in helping my husband arrange secret surprises for me during our trip. Thank you to the staff at KohCo restaurant, Bia, Chuu, and Wut. You guys are incredibly hard-working and always happy to see and chat with us. Thank you for indulging our every whim!"
> **- Patricia (5/5/5)**

> "We had a fabulous stay at Cielo in Koh Samui. In booking ahead, they were super responsive, helped arranged taxi from the airport etc. the place is very boutique and would consider high end. The rooms are stylish and super comfy. Lovely touches like the bar fridge is all free on the first day. The pool is amazing and I have to say the pool beds are the best we have ever had. They have very comfy bed beanbags on the beach. The food like the place is high end too. Not typical Thai prices however once you’ve eaten there you understand why. Every meal we had there was superb, high quality ingredients, generous in portion and presented beautifully. And finally huge call out to all the staff who work there - they really make the place and super friendly and can’t do enough for you. Highly recommend this place and if I was here again, I would stay here again."
> **- Tash Farquhar (5/5/5)**

> "Little GEM on Koh Samui. We loved its intimate and cosy atmosphere. Check-I’m was smooth and the receptionist even accompanied to explained us to the room and hotel, which is more than appreciate. Each room is spacious, decorated with a lot of taste. All the staff was so kind and really professional. Breakfast was tasteful with an à la carte menu, what best than starting the day with a fresh coconut ;-). The location is great you can walk to the village on the beach or rent a scooter. There is many things to do nearby, we loved this place !!"
> **- Simon Glardon (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cielo-samui-boutique-hotel-spa-1.jpg','077 425 300','180/5 Moo 1 Bophut, H27C+HR5 ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.cielosamui.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.410+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.410+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cielo-samui-boutique-hotel-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cielo-samui-boutique-hotel-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6816072621544394003',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('cinnamon-beach-villas','standard','cmr07igad0075q8xdu35umo6l','Cinnamon Beach Villas','## Top Reviews
> "I only stayed for three nights, but it truly felt like I got to experience a real piece of paradise. The rooms are spacious and comfortable, and the entire property is beautifully maintained and set in stunning surroundings, with easy access to the beach - which was dreamy to walk along 💕  The service was excellent across the board - from reception to the kitchen staff and housekeeping. I really enjoyed the food and cocktails, and appreciated the convenience of being able to communicate via WhatsApp and order room service easily 👌  If I had to mention a couple of downsides, it would be the Wi-Fi (since I unfortunately had to work during my stay), and the occasional tiny ant in the room that seemed quite fond of my keyboard. There were also quite a few families around, which sometimes made it harder to fully relax by the pool 🫣  Even so, the place absolutely deserves full marks, and I would happily stay here again 🤗"
> **- Engva (5/5/5)**

> "We received a complimentary room upgrade, which was a lovely surprise. The room was very clean, spacious, and the bed was extremely comfortable. The sea view was beautiful and made our stay even more relaxing. The staff were friendly, helpful, and welcoming throughout our stay. Overall, a great experience and I would happily stay here again."
> **- Amornrut Ruangvilaisup (5/5/5)**

> "Nice place. The room we had was very spacious and had comfy pillows. It was very clean and well presented. The on-site restaurant had lots of options for food and drinks. The staff were friendly and helpful. Only downsides were that the aircon in the room was rather loud even on the low fan setting, and the room let in quite a lot of light at night through cracks in the door etc."
> **- Kiera Willis (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cinnamon-beach-villas-1.jpg','077 960 892','146, 6, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.413+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.413+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cinnamon-beach-villas-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cinnamon-beach-villas-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1890736842921160775',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('circus-school','standard','cmr07igaf0076q8xdrvidv5s8','Circus School','## Top Reviews
> "Genuinely one of the best accomodations we gave ever stayed in. The huts looked so cool.  It was perfectly clean, lots of storage, 2 fans, cold shower and all amenities provided. Location was perfect and close to the main street.  Ashley was a top bloke who talked us through basically everything about the island.  And to top it all off, they gave us a free lift to the pier to catch our boat. The accomodation was also a VERY good price for what we paid.  Overall, amazing experience. Highly highly highly reccomend."
> **- Elliott H (5/5/5)**

> "We had a great stay at samui circus!!! Rooms are clean,beds are comfortable, private bathrooms, 2 powerful fans, hot water down the hill, room is only equipped with cold water but that doesn''t bug us in the heat. The owner is a big sweetheart a fellow traveler picked up food poisoning the day before. When he checked in she knew he wasn''t well. She sent out one of the boys to get him some supplies. 100% would recommend She rents motor bikes aswell for a cheap price. Cheapest I saw in the 3 weeks we were on the island. Location is abit far from interest points but a scooter fixes that 5/5"
> **- Brock Taylor (5/5/5)**

> "I was surprised how good it was there. The rooms are cheap and nice. I only stayed 1 night to go to the airport the next day. A walk to the beautiful and restaurants. Very helpful host. Got a lift to the airport for 250 baht"
> **- Dave John (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/circus-school-1.jpg','092 905 5001','9, 240 Thanon Bond Kai, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.samuicircus.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.415+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.415+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/circus-school-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/circus-school-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1808310045319213939',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('classic-gym-fitness','standard','cmr07igah0077q8xdr6uks8ca','Classic Gym & Fitness','## Top Reviews
> "Name says it all! This is a Classic gym that has everything you need to get a great workout in. No need for headphone as they play great House Music all day long. Lots of space and equipment to use. Fantastic gym!!!"
> **- Orange Elephant (5/5/5)**

> "Good gym. I’m from the UK and trained here in the month of May. It’s a very large gym which has all the equipment you will need. They provide you with towels and have protein shakes available if needed. Very nice and friendly lady working at the gym who was very helpful. Good vibes there. Highly recommend."
> **- ɪᴏᴀɴ (5/5/5)**

> "I read bad reviews and decided to check it out for myself. The gym is very nice and has all the necessary equipment for training. However, it is very hot and unpleasant for training. Good service. Showers need improvement. There is another floor above and there is no pressure. I didn''t smell animals and even if I did I have no problem helping animals. Needs improvement but nice and has potential."
> **- משה שאשא (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/classic-gym-fitness-1.jpg','077 300 759','9/23, ตำบล บ่อผุด Koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 6:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 6:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 6:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 6:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 6:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 6:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 6:30 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifuo0015q8xdfahzrsp4','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.417+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.417+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/classic-gym-fitness-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/classic-gym-fitness-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12362730309793135251',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('clay-beach-samui','standard','cmr07igak0078q8xddr043w4l','Clay Beach Samui','## Top Reviews
> "An absolutely amazing villa in Thailand! The villa is incredibly spacious and beautifully designed, with great attention to detail in every room. Everything feels elegant, comfortable, and very well thought out. One of the highlights is the fact that the villa has four swimming pools, which gives plenty of space to relax and enjoy privacy at any time of day. The service deserves special praise — the staff are extremely kind, professional, and always ready to help with anything we needed. They prepared delicious breakfasts and lunches every day, using fresh ingredients and serving them with a smile. This villa is a perfect choice for a luxurious and relaxing stay in Thailand. Highly recommended — we would love to come back!"
> **- Mateusz Gruszka (5/5/5)**

> "We had a brilliant stay at Clay Beach Samui with our friends and their kids. Seamless airport transfer, introduction to the property, and a full service team who were incredibly kind, hard working, and exceptional.  Located right on the beach and walkable to Fisherman’s village. The zoning of the property allows for people to have some privacy while also being communal, and is aesthetically beautiful. There were four pools to enjoy throughout the day. Luxury amenities and design made the villa feel premium. Breakfasts selection and preparation was beautifully done. We ate a lot at the villa and the Thai food was great but would recommend exploring other restaurants. We organized massages one day which was lovely and also had a private boat organized to Pig Island(skip that one) and another island where we had drinks and a swim off the boat. Highly recommended and you won’t want to leave."
> **- Shawn Yip (5/5/5)**

> "Absolutely breathtaking villa! It’s even more stunning in real life than in the photos – the size, the design, and the atmosphere are simply incredible. Every detail is beautifully thought out, with amazing decor and a unique vibe throughout the space. The staff is outstanding – so kind, attentive, and always available to assist with anything you need, all day long. The location is perfect – very close to Fisherman’s Village and within walking distance to 7-Eleven. We will definitely come back and highly recommend this place to everyone!"
> **- Ofir Ben Dor (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/clay-beach-samui-1.jpg','080 086 6164','3, 16, Tambon Mae Nam, Maenam, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.claybeachsamui.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.420+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.420+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/clay-beach-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/clay-beach-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=18075491627725384588',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('clever-kids-playroom','standard','cmr07igan0079q8xd448mpv5z','Clever Kids Playroom','## Top Reviews
> "Great play area for kids up to 5 years. Beautiful toys and all is clean and new. My 2.5 year old had a great time! Costs 150 baht per hour. They also serve some drinks and snacks for kids (banana, apples and such). Would come again gladly if in the area"
> **- Inbar Safra Halavy (5/5/5)**

> "A perfect play area. The best on Samui so far cause all toys are in great condition and full sets. There ia place to run for my daughter and to play peacefully. Drinks are great too. Overall impression is 10/10, cant wait to come back next week 😻"
> **- Elena Pervova (5/5/5)**

> "Nice and relaxed children''s play area - gentle music playing, not too busy. Good selection of toys and activities, and some nice options for snacks and drinks available. We paid 200 baht an hour and stayed an hour and a half (300 baht). My partner was also able to use he space upstairs to work briefly (additional charge of 100 an hour)."
> **- Helen Aivazian (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/clever-kids-playroom-1.jpg','094 805 7801','9, 60 Moo. 1, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://instagram.com/samuicleverkids?igshid=YmMyMTA2M2Y=','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: Closed","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.423+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.423+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/clever-kids-playroom-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/clever-kids-playroom-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5850533932773808738',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('cobra-show-thailand','standard','cmr07igas007aq8xdjr626lli','Cobra Show Thailand','## Top Reviews
> "What an Incredible experience! You have to make sure you go when the shows are on, times are on the website. The experience was so immersive. I was truly terrified of snakes before this but touched a cobra! And held a python! Such a great place! And to whoever put the review saying for them to renovate … it’s Koh samui not London. This is a raw unfiltered experience like no other!"
> **- Sonny Poole (5/5/5)**

> "WOW!!! 🐍✨ One of the most unforgettable experiences in Koh Samui! At first I was nervous 😭 but the show is so exciting, interesting and surprisingly fun.  The host is AMAZING! So charismatic, funny and professional at the same time. He makes the whole show feel exciting instead of scary and tells so many interesting things about snake behavior and different cobras. You actually learn a lot while watching!  And yes… you can even take photos with the snakes after 🫣🐍 Such a crazy Thailand experience we will never forget.  The trainers are incredibly skilled and confident, and the whole show feels very well organized. Definitely something unique you should see at least once in Thailand 🇹🇭✨"
> **- Elvira (5/5/5)**

> "It was an exceptionally insightful and well-thought-out presentation. The ideas were expressed with clarity and depth, showing a strong understanding of the topic.  The speaker discussed the subject in a thoughtful, articulate, and engaging manner. He explained complex points clearly and spoke with confidence and respect, which made the discussion both informative and enjoyable to follow.  The people there were genuinely warm, kind, and welcoming. They treated everyone with consideration and friendliness, creating a pleasant and positive atmosphere throughout the experience."
> **- Dotan Egozi (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cobra-show-thailand-1.jpg','081 858 1852','6 181 หมู่2 Tambon Na Mueang, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://web.facebook.com/Cobra-Show-Thailand-962263957295206/?ref=bookmarks','["Monday: 10:30 AM – 4:30 PM","Tuesday: 10:30 AM – 4:30 PM","Wednesday: 10:30 AM – 4:30 PM","Thursday: 10:30 AM – 4:30 PM","Friday: 10:30 AM – 4:30 PM","Saturday: 10:30 AM – 4:30 PM","Sunday: 10:30 AM – 4:30 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ig4i004oq8xdv207xuh2','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.428+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.428+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cobra-show-thailand-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/cobra-show-thailand-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1277049231667301768',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('coco-palm-beach-resort','standard','cmr07igau007bq8xdll0ifn08','Coco Palm Beach Resort','## Top Reviews
> "We stayed in a cute little beach house #212 right by the sea and were really happy with it. Breakfast was included and it was perfectly fine. Just a short walk away is the pier for boats to Koh Phangan and Koh Tao – super convenient, as we spent a few days on Koh Tao. The boats were barely noticeable, so no issue at all. Honestly, this turned out to be the best beach on the whole island! We didn’t expect that, but there were almost no people, the water gets deep immediately (no rocks, no water shoes needed), and right next to the beach there’s a bar/restaurant with clean toilets. Perfect! We explored about half of Koh Samui, but this beach was easily our favorite. The area is nice and quiet – not many options around, but everything you need is within a 10–15 minute walk. Highly recommended! :)"
> **- adam šedovič (5/5/5)**

> "Nice accommodation offering a comfortable family vacation and great value for money. The location is excellent: right on a calm and clean beach with pristine waters, in a quiet area with plenty of good and inexpensive restaurants and bars nearby, as well as minimarts, massage parlors, and a laundry service. The beach overlooks the Pralarn Pier, but we did not find the ferry traffic bothersome for our enjoyment of the beach.  The property consists of many bungalows of different sizes and amenities. We stayed in the Bungalow Deluxe and although it was simple and not very large, it was sufficient for our purposes. Most importantly, the bungalow was clean, well appointed, and quite cozy. Complimentary coffee was a nice addition, and we also liked the spacious veranda.  The bungalows are surrounded by beautiful, well-maintained gardens and greenery. The property overall is styled in a pleasant traditional oriental setting. The pool was clean and sufficiently large, and there were plenty of sun loungers available both by the pool and on the beach.  Breakfast was served buffet-style and was plentiful and varied, with many traditional as well as local dishes on offer, including fruit salad, filtered coffee, and the option to order various styles of eggs.  Everything during our stay was perfect and we really enjoyed our time at this family-oriented hotel."
> **- Andrej Michal (5/5/5)**

> "I have stayed here for 10 nights. Location is very quiet, nice, but there is nothing to do in the vicinity. Except for a number of reasonable restaurants. Had a villa with private pool which is very spacious and good, but it needs a renovation. Houses are clean on the other side. Atmosphere is nice and personnel is friendly and nice. Breakfast is very simple and every day the same. Anyhow, interesting place for a reasonable price."
> **- Eric Bionova (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coco-palm-beach-resort-1.jpg','077 447 211','26/4 หมู่ 4 Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.cocopalmbeachresort.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.430+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.430+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coco-palm-beach-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coco-palm-beach-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15955570227878149155',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('coco-samui-riding-club','standard','cmr07igax007cq8xdnz4nyt33','Coco Samui Riding Club','## Top Reviews
> "We had a wonderful experience here. The horses look very healthy and are well cared for. The guides are super friendly and treat the horses with respect, which I really liked. We booked a one-hour guided ride on the beach for our two girls, and the price included lots of photos and videos, which the staff took with their own cell phones in a super friendly and courteous manner. A clear recommendation from us!"
> **- Mirko Ziegert (5/5/5)**

> "I had the best afternoon today riding with these guys. The horses are well looked after and the beach riding was just incredible. I was lucky enough to ride rainbow who was absolute angel, I fell in love with her. ❤️🤩🐎"
> **- Leanne Willars (5/5/5)**

> "I had the most amazing experience here. The staff were extremely friendly and took great care of the horses. The horses were happy and enjoyed being ridden. I booked a 1 hour beach ride and it has been one of my favourite experiences whilst staying in Thailand. Would 100% recommend this experience"
> **- Meggy Fisher (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coco-samui-riding-club-1.jpg','084 440 6713','ต Tambon Taling Ngam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 7:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 9:30 PM"]','cmr07ifuo0015q8xdfahzrsp4','cmr07ift8000pq8xd7yujz20i','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.433+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.433+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coco-samui-riding-club-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coco-samui-riding-club-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3097116861124999117',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('coco-smile-dentist-clinic','standard','cmr07igaz007dq8xdxr1n33ua','Coco Smile Dentist Clinic','## Top Reviews
> "I have been here on 2 occasions and found them very professional and helpful. Once to refix a crown and another to investigate tooth sensitivity. The dentist speaks good English and clean advice."
> **- Jan Griffiths (5/5/5)**

> "My partner and I came in for a routine cleaning. Got a next day appointment. Priced reasonably and literally the best dentist experience either of us have ever had. The least amount of pain from a cleaning. Very impressive 😇🙏🏽"
> **- Jessica Piff (5/5/5)**

> "Disappointed!!  I went there fix a front tooth filling that had come out. They did the job but the filling popped out again after only 2.5 months. I went back there to show them and ask to please fix it. They gave me my money back and said to go somewhere else and they will not do it. So I now I am left with a hole bigger than when I went there and they refuse to repair their own work and will hand it over to someone else to deal with. They probably assumed I was a tourist they will never see again. For this experience, I do not recommend to others."
> **- Kyle Smith (2/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coco-smile-dentist-clinic-1.jpg','099 095 5527','Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 10:00 AM – 4:30 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 4:30 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 4:30 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 4:30 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 4:30 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ig1d003gq8xdfxkqj28w','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.435+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.435+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coco-smile-dentist-clinic-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coco-smile-dentist-clinic-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9392040523070342673',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('coco-tams','standard','cmr07igb1007eq8xdlyv8m6h8','Coco Tam''s','## Top Reviews
> "Visited Coco Tam’s in Fisherman’s Village for dinner. By the time we arrived, most of the popular seats were already taken, so we could not get the exact spot we originally wanted. However, we ended up dining on the second floor, which actually turned out to be more comfortable and had an even better view.  The food quality was excellent. The menu seemed to lean toward Italian-style dishes, and everything we ordered, including the pasta and burrata cheese, was surprisingly good in both flavor and quality. The cocktails were also enjoyable, and they had the usual beer options as well. Overall, the food was definitely one of the highlights of the visit.  The atmosphere was another strong point. Arriving around sunset made the experience even better because the changing colors of the sky were beautiful. Later in the evening, there was also a fire show, which added a fun and memorable touch to the night. Since we were seated upstairs, the music was not overwhelmingly loud, which made the environment more relaxing.  One thing to note is that there is a minimum spending requirement of 2,000 baht. This could feel a bit expensive for lighter eaters, but for my wife and me, it was completely reasonable.  The only disappointing part was the service. Considering how large and busy the restaurant is, it is understandable that the staff are constantly occupied, but the overall attentiveness and quality of service felt a bit lacking at times."
> **- Dave (5/5/5)**

> "A place that’s absolutely worth visiting when you’re in Fisherman’s Village.  They offer incredible fire shows — honestly the best ones we saw in Thailand. The atmosphere is amazing, and it’s a great experience for all ages.  A few important things to know before you go:  1. If you don’t have a reservation, try to arrive at least 1–1.5 hours early to get a good spot. 2. They don’t always accept reservations for future dates — it seems to depend on availability and their own flexibility. 3. Fire shows don’t happen when it rains, so keep that in mind. 4. Smoking is allowed on the beach. 5. Payment is required immediately when ordering (not at the end). Credit cards are accepted. 6. Outside seating only offers the pizza menu.  Highly recommended — definitely one of those places you shouldn’t miss, and I think people of all ages will enjoy it. You won’t be disappointed!"
> **- Gal Toronto (5/5/5)**

> "We are many times here at coco tams and its the most interesting place on Koh Samui. The amazing Fireshow is two times every evening. And we love the Cocktails the Athmosphere and the Food is extremely high quality. We Staff is also very friendly. If you want to sit at the Roof Part of the Restaurant you have to  visit the Desk to the right in front of the Restaurant on the street. For the best tables for viewing the fireshow. You have to consume drinks and food for 2000 Baht. But this is worth it. We come back next year. Kabkun Khrub"
> **- TOFI (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coco-tams-1.jpg','091 915 5664','62 Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/CoCoTams','["Monday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.437+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.437+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coco-tams-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coco-tams-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2842089041934717843',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('coconut-grove-hotel','standard','cmr07igb3007fq8xd9toltarl','Coconut Grove Hotel','## Top Reviews
> "AVOID AVOID AVOID!!  The second we came into the room we saw that all of the bedding was dirty and had holes in it. We went down to the reception and asked them to kindly change our bedding on all of the beds and after some bickering they agreed. When we came back to the room after dinner we saw that only one of the beds had been changed. We also realized that the WiFi didn’t work in our room. So we went down to the reception and asked why only one of the beds were changed. She told me that I was wrong and they had changed everything. Only when I said that I had proof of the before did they even lift a finger and said that maybe they hadn’t changed the pillows and the blanket. When I asked them about the WiFi and that it didn’t work she just told me you have to stand ”by the door”. When I said that it was weird and if they have it in the listing they should have it in the rooms. Do you want to guess what she said to me? It is free so it is not a big deal. It was not free, I PAID for my stay here where WiFi is INCLUDED. Then she started to ”threaten” us that she would cancel the booking and that we would have to find another accommodation, who even does that?? Do you also want to guess what we find while they are changing our bedding, MOLD on the pillows. Is this a joke?? With this long review I just want to tell you that is you want the BAREMINIMUM in terms of costumer service and cleanliness you should avoid this place at all costs!!!!!"
> **- Liza Artemova (1/5/5)**

> "Coconut Grove  If you don’t mind a budget experience, this is your place as this is not the Taj Mahal. Sometimes I look at these reviews and wonder why people expect a 5 star experience when they only have a 1 star budget!  This place has a perfect location with a 1 minute walk to the strip and a 3 minute walk to the beach front. It is on the same property as a beach club(photo) in which you have access to(just order a mango smoothie) which will have 2 additional pools, a restaurant, live DJ, and an amazing beachfront. The rooms are basic and dated but huge and the beds are comfy. The staff are VERY friendly as well.  Make sure you ask for the rooms away from the main road as they can be a bit noisy at night. And yes, there are 3 stories so if you are disabled or out of shape to the point where you cannot walk 2 flights of stairs, this place is not for you. We will definitely be back!"
> **- Kokomojoe (5/5/5)**

> "I can said this hotel are not worth even a star. 3rd floor no lift 🛗 to go up with alot of luggage some more, and the staircase step are really dangerous when walk up and down with carrying luggage. Room area quite bad, no hair dryer, heater are broken all the way come out hot water only. Bedroom and Bathroom are very old, definitely not worth with the price. and one things is so unacceptable this kind of what such hotel getting deposit a 1000 bth collect.i know that''s refundable, but I feel..haiz....I leave in Koh Samui this trip with total 6 night in Lamai area and Chaweng. few hotel all very Nice and clean even 4-5star they also didn''t even collect the deposit. It is so funny this type of nothing hotel collect the deposit. Without hair dryer is my first meet in hotel. Unbelievable."
> **- May Tan (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coconut-grove-hotel-1.jpg','081 535 2335','159/72 Soi Ark Bar, ตำบล บ่อผุด Koh Samui, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.2,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.439+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.439+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coconut-grove-hotel-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coconut-grove-hotel-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=149429061187083761',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('coconuts-palm-resort','standard','cmr07igb5007gq8xdwomeean3','Coconuts Palm Resort','## Top Reviews
> "Very nice resort with friendly staff! Everything was clean and fresh. The breakfast was great with many options to choose from. The pool and the whole resort is relatively new. When we had any questions or problems the Rezeption was always able to help us."
> **- Lea Kreis (5/5/5)**

> "A bungalow resort with a nice layout, wich ensures the pool has warm and inviting water. The pool is deep and large enough for a good excercise swim. Next to the pool is a bar and restaurant with a large selection of tasty food. The staff is friendly and helpful. Any order can be put on the room tab, very convenient. Cozy and clean bungalows complete with a stocked minibar."
> **- Robert Hägg (5/5/5)**

> "Great value for money. We enjoyed our stay. Very quiet area with a lot of palms around 🌴 Bungalows are small, but really nice. We loved the bike rent service and the 24-hour working swimming pool. Hotel staff was friendly and welcoming."
> **- Anna Shkoropad (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coconuts-palm-resort-1.jpg','077 423 525','407/24 Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifpz0001q8xd0aml2ucx','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.441+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.441+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coconuts-palm-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coconuts-palm-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10920850101517055763',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('cocovolt','standard','cmr07igb6007hq8xdff4y7soe','Cocovolt','Discover Cocovolt, a premier transport located in Nathon, Koh Samui. Find reviews, hours, and contact information.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifui0012q8xdzn158clv','cmr07ig1h003iq8xdb1g9nifo','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.442+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.442+00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('code-hotel','standard','cmr07igb9007iq8xdj6qzpaey','Code Hotel','## Top Reviews
> "We stayed here with my boyfriend for a month and were absolutely satisfied.  What I must praise the most is the staff. Everyone is so friendly and kind! The cleaning ladies are very nice and do an excellent job. The bar and kitchen staff are just as great.  The hotel is beautiful and has an incredibly stunning view. We truly felt wonderful here and didn’t have a single problem during our stay. We will definitely remember this place for a long time, and we thank the entire team at Hotel Code for the wonderful stay they provided us. 😊"
> **- Hospoda Bitov (5/5/5)**

> "Had an amazing stay at this hotel! This was already our third time staying here, and every time it gets even better. We will definitely come back again in the future. The hotel is beautiful, clean, peaceful, and perfectly maintained. The atmosphere is so relaxing and makes every vacation feel special. The rooms are comfortable, the food is great, and everything feels high quality and well taken care of. What truly makes this place exceptional is the amazing staff. Everyone is so kind, welcoming, helpful, and genuinely caring. A very special thank you to Lay, Som, and Natty you made us feel at home from the very first moment. Your kindness, warm smiles, and exceptional service made our stay unforgettable. You can really feel how much the team cares about the guests, and that’s exactly why we keep coming back. Highly recommended for anyone visiting Koh Samui."
> **- רעות שוקרון (5/5/5)**

> "I have to say, this has been one of the best hotel experiences I have ever had in Thailand. The value for the rooms is incredible, and the views combined with the peaceful atmosphere make it truly special.  What stood out the most, though, was the team. Everyone working here was exceptionally kind and made me feel genuinely taken care of—almost like royalty.  Breakfast quickly became one of my favorite parts of the stay. I loved being able to sit down and order anything I wanted from the à la carte menu. It felt relaxed, generous, and thoughtfully done.  The guests here are also a delight. Because the hotel is set away from the busier areas of the island, it attracts a different kind of crowd—people who appreciate calm, beauty, and space.  Honestly, I almost hesitate to write this because part of me wants to keep this place a secret. But after seeing a few negative reviews, I feel compelled to say that they simply do not reflect my experience. I had a wonderful stay, and it is clear that this hotel is very well managed.I have to say, this has been one of the best hotel experiences I have ever had in Thailand. The value for the rooms is incredible, and the views combined with the peaceful atmosphere make it truly special."
> **- Chun Ku (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/code-hotel-1.jpg','062 245 0494','55, 13 Soi 4, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.samuicode.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifs1000cq8xdfo2aau32','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.445+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.445+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/code-hotel-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/code-hotel-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10755735408332491896',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('coffee-collective','standard','cmr07igbb007jq8xdgo4dynqx','Coffee Collective','## Top Reviews
> "I visited this coffee shop and tried several different coffees and dishes, and I absolutely loved everything. The quality of the coffee is truly high-grade, you can really taste the care and professionalism in every cup. The food was also excellent — especially the pumpkin soup with bacon, which was absolutely amazing and stood out the most for me. The service was outstanding: friendly, attentive, and welcoming. Thank you for such a great experience, I’ll definitely be happy to come back again!"
> **- Рааррр (5/5/5)**

> "I enjoyed the syrniki and buckwheat porridge. The honey cake was just okay. However, some of the prices felt unreasonable. A cappuccino costs 150 baht, which is far more expensive than at other places like Flo, To Be Sweet, and many others. The guacamole was also disappointing: 110 baht for a very small scoop that wasn’t particularly tasty."
> **- Epolina (4/5/5)**

> "The Basque cheesecake was absolutely amazing — rich, creamy, and incredibly smooth. You can really tell that high-quality ingredients are used, and it tasted like it was made with premium Philadelphia cream cheese.  The Americano was excellent as well. It was served hot and had a great flavor. As it cooled down, more of its pleasant acidity came through, making the coffee even more interesting and enjoyable.  Everything was delicious. Highly recommended!"
> **- Евгений Боровиков (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coffee-collective-1.jpg','098 563 8753','Moo1, 70/38 Maenam, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.instagram.com/coffeecollectivesamui?igsh=Y2VkMjViZ2FtdmVw&utm_source=qr','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.447+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.447+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coffee-collective-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coffee-collective-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12013864814078579038',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('coffee-joint-love','standard','cmr07igbc007kq8xdq2fwpr19','Coffee Joint Love','## Top Reviews
> "IMPORTANT: CASH ONLY Amazing place and an amazing vibe. You can tell the owner really knows what they’re doing. Every detail feels carefully thought out, and the atmosphere is one of the best I’ve experienced in Thailand. One thing I especially want to mention is the way they handle edibles. I live in California, where edibles are limited to 100 mg of THC per package. When you buy a cookie, brownie, gummy, or other edible, you know exactly how much THC you’re getting and how much you should take. In Thailand, I’ve visited several cannabis shops and almost none of them clearly showed the THC content of their edibles. In one shop, I even asked the staff how much THC was inside, and they simply said they didn’t know.  Then you see videos of tourists eating an entire brownie or cookie and having a terrible experience because they had no idea what they were taking. This shop does it right. Their edibles are clearly labeled with 100 mg THC, which makes it easy to divide into smaller portions and enjoy responsibly. Another huge plus is the coffee. This is actually the first cannabis shop I’ve visited where they make genuinely good coffee. Most places focus only on cannabis, but here they clearly care about the whole experience. The flower was great, the accessories selection was excellent, and everything felt professional. Special thanks to the owner as well. He came over, greeted me personally, and was very friendly and welcoming. Small things like that make a big difference. Highly recommended.  Вайб здесь просто отличный! Как будто приехал к кенту домой.Развалился на диване, бабушка принесла кофе с круассаном и оставила вас в покое. А дальше можно спокойно достать бонг и расслабиться так, будто завтра никуда не нужно)))"
> **- John Dutton (5/5/5)**

> "Exceptionally good weed I’ve been traveling in Thailand for 2 months this time, smoking every day, and the weed I got here got me really blown away 😸  Very friendly owner and buddies hanging out in the shop, great people  Recommend the Ape Grape strain, with a psychedelic touch"
> **- Cordelia Swift (5/5/5)**

> "Great little spot on the main street on Koh Samui. The Staff is helpful, the atmosphere is very chill. Superb Selection and daily Deals for all the stoners out there. Pay them a visit and relax ;)"
> **- Elektro Horst (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coffee-joint-love-1.jpg',NULL,'231/4 Meanam Koh Samui District Suratthani Province Meanam, ตำบล แม่น้ำ อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://glitchsamui.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 12:30 AM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 12:30 AM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 12:30 AM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 12:30 AM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 12:30 AM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 12:30 AM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 12:30 AM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.448+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.448+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coffee-joint-love-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coffee-joint-love-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13372227492718293624',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('colorize-boutique-hotel','standard','cmr07igbe007lq8xdbfr1l27l','Colorize Boutique Hotel','## Top Reviews
> "Stayed here for 1 week and had a great time. The place is in a great location, close to many markets and bars. The rooms were clean and spacious. The hotel has 3 cute cats which we loved.  The staff are super friendly and accommodating. They gave us a few recommendations for what to do and what to avoid.  As other reviews pointed out, the place is a little bit dated (the rooms) but in my opinion, so are many hotels in Thailand and the value for money is still fantastic.  Would stay again."
> **- Mateusz Jaworski (4/5/5)**

> "THE WORST EXPERIENCE EVER! This “hotel/hostel” does not look ANYTHING like the pictures. The pool was dirty and disgusting. When you threw something in the trash can, a lot of insects came out, and there were already insects in the room along the walls. The location was very far from the city center and from where things are happening, and you do not feel safe walking there at night. The people in the building were smoking marijuana all the time.  There were also cats in the lobby, so we were not even able to walk through it. The staff told us to walk around instead of removing the cats.  I would absolutely not recommend this place — choose another hotel."
> **- Mimmi Munther (5/5/5)**

> "We stayed at the hotel for a little over a week, and had a great experience. For the price we payed, it was good value for the money. Very helpful staff."
> **- Elias Magnussen (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/colorize-boutique-hotel-1.jpg','080 320 1910','118/4 Moo 4 T. Maret Lamai, Koh Samui, ตำบล มะเร็ต อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/colorizeboutiquehotel','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.450+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.450+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/colorize-boutique-hotel-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/colorize-boutique-hotel-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13446507475613405303',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('colts-horse-riding','standard','cmr07igbh007mq8xdb3ptv9iv','COLTS Horse Riding','## Top Reviews
> "Rides typically begin at base camp, lead through local jungle and gardens, and open onto Laem Yai Beach.  A major highlight for me and I daresay most people, is the opportunity to ride the horses into the clear ocean water.  We did the 0700 times lot which worked out great as we were the only two riding at the time so it felt like a personal horse riding tour. As this is situated on the western side of the island, sunsets here would be amazing riding the horses in the ocean with the sun setting.  Check time times. At high tide the water is right in but makes for no less a ride as it was such a wonderful experience riding the horses in the ocean. Low tides should provide a lot of extra riding space.  The stable caters to all levels. Beginners can be led by friendly staff, while advanced riders may be allowed to gallop if they demonstrate sufficient control.  Staff happily took high-quality photos and videos for us during the ride, and at no extra cost."
> **- Bourne Tour Guide (5/5/5)**

> "Went for an 8.30 morning ride. Was absolutely amazing for a beginner rider. They have riding of all levels but Zoe was a great teacher and made me feel completely at ease riding my horse Sky. We were explained the story of how the horses are actually rescues and saved from the slaughter house which made me feel even better about riding with Colts. The trail itself was beautiful and riding through the shallow sea was one of the prettiest sights I’ve ever seen. The Thai local instructor Nicky who was accompanying us was also great fun. Overall amazing experience. If you’re in Koh Samui this is the perfect horse riding experience."
> **- Tomay (5/5/5)**

> "Such an amazing experience! I had the 7:00 morning ride and I was the only one with the guide. As I am experienced it was a wonderful one hour ride full of trotting and cantering. The owner was very lovely and kind, when I asked if there is a chance for me to get a bigger horse as I am 180cm, he allowed me to get one. The horses were beautiful and clean, completely new equipment and it was really amazing! The guide Nicky was also very lovely, made the ride fun and exciting. Definitely a highlight of the trip! The horse Pawan was a sweetheart, very well behaved and I listened instantly to every signal I gave him. 🐴🫶🏼"
> **- Deni (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/colts-horse-riding-1.jpg','094 950 3306','Laem Yai Beach, Tambon Ang Thong, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.instagram.com/colts.horse.riding.kohsamui/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 6:30 PM"]','cmr07ifuo0015q8xdfahzrsp4','cmr07ifxh0027q8xde6xqk8o6','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.453+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.453+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/colts-horse-riding-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/colts-horse-riding-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17192690981508241103',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('como-bake-brunch','standard','cmr07igbk007nq8xdj6lax30f','Como Bake & Brunch','## Top Reviews
> "Amazing quality and fresh ingredients. You can really taste the difference in their artisanal bread. The glazed bacon with scrambled eggs was the highlight for me. Super chill atmosphere too. I’ll definitely be back!!"
> **- Kkay (5/5/5)**

> "Opened a year ago. Clean and hygienic. Cozy atmosphere. Fast and friendly service. The sourdough sandwich was tasty. Coffee was bold not bitter nor sour. Love it."
> **- Martlet (5/5/5)**

> "So I put 4 stars cause : the food, you wait ~10-15 minutes but the food is WORTH IT, very good sourdough bread, I highly recommend this place for a good toast. The service is okey not so much smile…but respectful. The vibes could be better if little music inside  and outside 🙏🏼 Thanks to welcome us."
> **- Lisa Pizzi (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/como-bake-brunch-1.jpg','081 734 0981','147/46-47, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61563205836665&mibextid=LQQJ4d','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: Closed","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.456+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.456+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/como-bake-brunch-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/como-bake-brunch-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16771032198052708982',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('complete-marine-services','standard','cmr07igbo007oq8xdhevy3u7f','Complete Marine Services','## Top Reviews
> "The best Marine Engineer I''ve ever had the pleasure to work with. David Lloyd  fixed my engine rapidly and efficiently, everything went as he said it would , his confidence and expertise achieved the repairs to a short timeframe,  and the outcome was totally to plan and successful. I cannot recommend Complete Marine Services more highly . David Lloyd is an extremely competent and professional marine engineer."
> **- Craig Murdoch (5/5/5)**

> "after a long period of unknown problems with our marine engine David was able to fix it quickly and efficient! He is highly skilled and can sort properly most technical hazards on boats and on land! Highly recommended company!"
> **- Kunta Samui (5/5/5)**

> "TOP! I had and issue with my suzuki outboard. Official Suzuki dealer  wasn''t able to fix it after several months, Suzuki came different times and try different solution until they suggested me to change engine (yeah really?) as they could not find the cause of the issue. Called CMS, he came, he checked he fixed! Now the boat is working perfectly! Thanks Robert!"
> **- Yannick Mancel (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/complete-marine-services-1.jpg','061 591 9777','36, 19 Choengmon, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifv2001aq8xdag7cvjgf','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.460+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.460+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/complete-marine-services-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/complete-marine-services-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7934464961449279850',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('conrad-hotel-resort','standard','cmr07igbq007pq8xdkt1fqwdr','Conrad Hotel & Resort','## Top Reviews
> "We had an amazing stay at Conrad Koh Samui. From the second we arrived, everything just felt right.  The villas are on another level — total privacy, insane ocean views, and sunsets that honestly don’t look real. Sitting in the infinity pool watching the sun go down was one of the highlights of our entire trip.  What really made the difference was the service. The staff were warm, genuine, and always happy to help without ever feeling over the top. You can tell they truly care about the experience they create.  Breakfast was excellent with plenty of options, and every meal we had was high quality. The whole property is peaceful, beautifully maintained, and perfect if you want to disconnect and relax.  We’ve stayed at quite a few luxury resorts, and this one stands out. Would absolutely come back."
> **- Idan Shchori (5/5/5)**

> "I stayed here for 3 nights and 4 days.  We came from Japan and spent a total of 6 nights in Koh Samui. Our first hotel was located in the city, while Conrad is far from the downtown area, so it was very quiet and perfect for my wife and me to relax.  The room was spacious, clean, and had a private pool, so we could spend the whole day comfortably in the room without needing to go anywhere. It perfectly suited what we were looking for.  The food was delicious, and the service was attentive and excellent. We would definitely love to come back again."
> **- Nori N (5/5/5)**

> "Our honeymoon stay at Conrad Koh Samui was truly magical and exceeded all our expectations. From the moment we arrived, we were captivated by the breathtaking views of the ocean and the stunning surroundings.  What made our stay especially memorable was the exceptional service. Every member of the staff went above and beyond to ensure that every need was attended to with genuine warmth and professionalism. Their attention to detail made us feel incredibly welcome and cared for throughout our stay.  The beautiful accommodations, world-class amenities, and unforgettable sunsets created the perfect setting for our honeymoon. We left with wonderful memories that we will cherish for a lifetime.  Thank you to the entire team at Conrad Koh Samui for making our honeymoon such a special and unforgettable experience. We can''t wait to return!"
> **- ahmed alzaid (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/conrad-hotel-resort-1.jpg','077 915 888','49/8-9 หมู่ที่ 4 Hillcrest Road Tambon Taling Ngam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.hilton.com/en/hotels/usmksci-conrad-koh-samui/?SEO_id=GMB-APAC-CI-USMKSCI',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ift8000pq8xd7yujz20i','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.462+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.462+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/conrad-hotel-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/conrad-hotel-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9694025048400092808',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('coral-cliff-beach-resort','standard','cmr07igbt007qq8xd3smetdi8','Coral Cliff Beach Resort','## Top Reviews
> "I was particularly impressed with the warm welcome from the staff at check in as they gave us a delicious complementary drink right when we sat down at the reservation desk. The porter was friendly helping us carry our suitcase down the stairs to our room showing us the room and reminding us to let them know if we needed help to take the suitcase back up when we check out…. Great service!  Going down to the beach you have a flight of stairs (for us old folks felt like 1 million steps 😂). You have a fantastic small beach with large boulders and great place to relax,swim and watch people out there snorkeling 🤿.  My husband and I visited Coral Cliff Beach Resort Restaurant for our first night here for dinner, and it was a wonderful experience from start to finish. The food was excellent. I’m still dreaming about the “Koh Samui Dream” cocktail the presentation was stunning, the unique flavors were unforgettable. A must-try! The staff were attentive without being intrusive and made us feel like VIPs. Highly recommended for anyone looking for a romantic dining experience!"
> **- Cheri Crickon (5/5/5)**

> "Overall a really beautiful spot. The room was neat, comfy and clean. The aircon a little noisy but effective and no musty smell, so that is good! Getting around is challenging if you have dodgy knees. The staff are friendly but English is something they battle with so at times frustrating. Breakfast is good and great value. Lamai Night Market and wider Lamai is pretty close and worth a visit. There is no Hotel shuttle, but you can book your own or ride (walking around here is possible but not recommended and I doubt much fun). Overall the hotel is a little tired but the value reflects that, so can’t complain!"
> **- Andrew A (4/5/5)**

> "About the Flat:⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ I liked it. It looks wery beautiful, and it’s also comfortable, the stuff is amazing, but ther are some disadvantages. In the number you can hear the motorbicycles on the road. It wasn’t horrible but I wish I couldn’t hear that. The second thing, it’s a flor. When you walk, it sounds wery loud 😬 But it’s not kritisch at all)  The Design looks good ) the view is fantastic You have everything you need for the nice holidays  Restaurant:⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ I liked the meal, cocktail, the stuff, but I was in Restaurant only 5 times, because the rest of times I visited restaurants in Chaweng or Lamai, and in the Fishing village there are a lot of fantastic restaurants )  The Staff:⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ Everyone was friendly with me, nice people.  Road: You have to rent the bike or take the taxi. I personally rented the bike for a nice price from hotel. It’s very comfortable and makes a lot of fun)  Everyone can find disadvantages everywhere, but in conclusion I’d like to say, that this place was magic for me, and I hope, will be also for you) 🇺🇦🇩🇪🇹🇭"
> **- Иван Вакуленко (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coral-cliff-beach-resort-1.jpg','077 448 500','210 หมู่ที่ 4 ตําบล, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.coralcliffbeachresort.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ig5c0051q8xdykrbexft','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.465+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.465+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coral-cliff-beach-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coral-cliff-beach-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12521637473336400114',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('coral-cliff-restaurant-bar','standard','cmr07igbv007rq8xd8cw8tets','Coral Cliff Restaurant & Bar','## Top Reviews
> "We were there on Christmas. The food was great and the view was absolutely stunning. The service was excellent my boyfriend said he felt truly spoiled as the staff always noticed when his drink was almost empty and refilled it for him before he even realized, even though it was a very busy night on Christmas.  We booked directly through the website which was very convenient and they reserved the best seats for us on Christmas. This place is one of our favorites and we will definitely come back."
> **- anw Anw (5/5/5)**

> "5-Star Service in a Stunning Location – Exceptional Management!  We had a memorable evening at The Cliff Bar and Grill. While the food was good, it was the outstanding service from the manager and the team that truly earned this 5-star rating. 1. Exceptional Management & Care: The manager was incredibly enthusiastic, attentive, and highly observant. We were dining with a small child, and the manager noticed our initial table near the kitchen was a bit noisy, so they immediately moved us to a quieter 2-person table further away. Even more impressive, while we were waiting for our main courses, the manager proactively moved us again to a more spacious 4-person table. They realized that having a toddler requires extra space, and this level of thoughtfulness and proactive care made our evening much more comfortable. A huge thank you to the manager for being so considerate! 2. Atmosphere & View: The location and the overall ambiance of the restaurant are stunning. It is the perfect spot for a beautiful evening out with a great view. 3. Food & Presentation: The food presentation was beautiful and very well-plated. Taste-wise, I would rate it around 3.5 stars given the price point—it was good, though perhaps not as extraordinary as the service.  I am giving this a 5-star review primarily because of the world-class service provided by the manager and the staff. If you value being well-taken care of in a beautiful setting, this is the place to be. We truly appreciated the hospitality! Rating: 5/5 Stars ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐"
> **- Vo Tung (5/5/5)**

> "The most amazing meal at the Cliff! Although a little expensive for Thailand, it was well worth it for the view alone and the food was even better! My partner is a coeliac and pescatarian. There were lots of options for her and the staff were very knowledgable about gluten-free food. She had a lovely gluten-free salmon pasta dish and I had a beautiful lasagna. We both got gorgeous gluten-free brownies for desert!"
> **- Mitchell Licata (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coral-cliff-restaurant-bar-1.jpg','077 448 508','124/2 Tambon Maret, Suratthani, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://thecliffsamui.com/','["Monday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig5c0051q8xdykrbexft','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.467+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.467+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coral-cliff-restaurant-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/coral-cliff-restaurant-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6648868876780039089',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('create-make-play','standard','cmr07igbz007sq8xdy9um6nt0','Create Make & Play','Discover Create Make & Play, a premier for kids located in Bophut, Koh Samui. Find reviews, hours, and contact information.','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/create-make-play-1.jpg',NULL,'G2MR+MQ6, Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,0.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.471+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.471+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/create-make-play-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/create-make-play-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13781633683024126100',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('creative-adventure','standard','cmr07igc2007tq8xdzdfh7kfq','Creative Adventure','## Top Reviews
> "A truly outstanding experience with Creative Aventure. Beautifully organized, and felt very exclusive. You can immediately tell they genuinely care about their guests. Highly recommended for anyone who appreciates high-quality service and unforgettable experiences."
> **- Kanokporn Chuayhom (5/5/5)**

> "Great tour by creative and well guided by Bernie in both French and English. Great food, snorkelling and island hopping."
> **- Rohan Watt (5/5/5)**

> "If you are looking for a great adventure this is the one, great vibes they have all you needs, I definitely do it again. Love it, thank you so much."
> **- The traveler (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/creative-adventure-1.jpg','096 648 7781','147, 41 Tambon, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.creative-aventure.com/',NULL,'cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.474+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.474+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/creative-adventure-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/creative-adventure-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7818447277626623067',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('crystal-bay-beach-club','standard','cmr07igc4007uq8xdup7k44jy','Crystal Bay Beach Club','## Top Reviews
> "Great place in this amazing setting straight on the beach away from hustle & bustle. Staff are very friendly and efficient. Tried pretty much every Thai dish on the menu — all of it was simply divine! The fire show was really fun as well!"
> **- Nara Toktoshova (5/5/5)**

> "Great dining experience. It gets better when you reserve for an evening supper at 7 p.m. They have a fire show that happens three times a week, and the food is almost “fine cuisine.” The show is very nice, set against a beautiful natural background: sand, sea, and rocks."
> **- Joe A (4/5/5)**

> "I have rarely witnessed such a lack of customer service. Late in the afternoon, a kind couple who had already paid for two sunbeds for the whole day offered them to us as they were leaving. The moment we sat down, the staff rushed over demanding that we pay the full day rate… as if the sunbeds magically went back up for rent at 4 p.m.  And the best part? They asked us for a receipt, even though everything here is paid in cash and no receipts are ever provided. Completely absurd, but above all revealing: the only thing that matters here is squeezing more money out of guests, not offering a good experience.  We walked away disgusted by the sheer lack of professionalism and the shameless money-driven mentality. This is not a beach club, it’s a cash-grab machine.  Silver Beach is stunning, but this place in particular should be avoided at all costs if you’re expecting even the slightest bit of respect or hospitality."
> **- Romy 31 (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/crystal-bay-beach-club-1.jpg','095 271 4472','209 Moo 4, Haad Thongtakian, Lamai,, Thanon Had Lamai, ตำบล มะเร็ต Koh Samui,, Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.2,0,0,0,NULL,'https://crystalbaybeachclub.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig5c0051q8xdykrbexft','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.476+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.476+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/crystal-bay-beach-club-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/crystal-bay-beach-club-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13381230927492371329',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('crystal-bay-resort','standard','cmr07igc7007vq8xdzbpe8p47','Crystal Bay Resort','## Top Reviews
> "Such a great experience for me and the family. The staff are incredible and we have to do a special shout out for Min and Bonnie who work there who were fantastic. The location was great being a short stroll to one of Thailands best beaches. The food at the restaurant was amazing. I can’t say enough good things about the place. Made our Thailand trip perfect. The fact you could be snorkeling one second and head back to the hotel to get a massage overlooking the ocean is just incredible. I highly recommend it. :)"
> **- jamie beaton (5/5/5)**

> "I stayed with my group for 3 days during our visit to Samui, the rooms were spotless and spacious. The staff was the sweetest, especially the guy at the restaurant that served amazing food(vegetarian as well). The view and the ocean-side massage space is the best thing about the resort! 10/10 recommend"
> **- Pragya Verma (5/5/5)**

> "We had the pleasure of staying here for two nights. The hotel''s setting is incredible and the view of the cove from our bedroom was second to none. The bed was super comfy, the air conditioning was quiet, the staff were really friendly and the breakfast was the best we''ve had on our trip. We absolutely loved our stay."
> **- Charlotte Auty (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/crystal-bay-resort-1.jpg','093 232 1718','205 Lamai Had Thongtakian Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://crystalbaysamui.com/crystal-bay-beach-resort/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ig5c0051q8xdykrbexft','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.479+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.479+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/crystal-bay-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/crystal-bay-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5534621413792232701',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('cu-club-restaurant','standard','cmr07igc9007wq8xd61shfj1a','Cu Club & Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "Great late night venue. Often doesn''t get busy until 4am but is open  to 8 or 9ish so be prepared to leave in the light!!  Pool played here. Nice cold chillout room.  Some food available. Very friendly. A lot of fun."
> **- Edmund Moriarty (5/5/5)**

> "This new club is absolutely fantastic! The atmosphere is vibrant and inviting, making it perfect for a great night out. The service is top-notch, with attentive staff ensuring you have everything you need. One standout feature is the convenience of parking and the after-party experience, which adds even more value to the visit. Highly recommend it for anyone looking for an unforgettable time!"
> **- Danudat (5/5/5)**

> "i like and i have happy all  on the time when i go in the pub 🍻😘"
