INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('d-smile-dental-clinic','standard','cmr07igcf007zq8xd7kq77y1l','D-Smile Dental Clinic','## Top Reviews
> "Terrible service, terrible communication.  My partner and I went in for a general checkup and clean a month ago, the experience was very poor. Charge $1500 Bhat for an xray she did not ask for. When it was delivered at the counter it had the wrong name on it and displayed as male not female. The dentist did not come and explain anything on the xray, it was left up to an unqualified receptionist to explain the details of the xray.  I was booked in for a month later, thought I would go back and give them a second chance. They had not sent the confirmation text message to the right place neither did they explain this when we were in there for the original appointment. Did not make an effort to contact me to see if I was coming in.  Turned up today, the receptionist explained that my appointment had not been confirmed when asked why I didn’t receive a text she said that it was sent on line to my partners number. Strange path of communication considering you had my details.  Highly do not recommend. Even when we explained our issues there was no assurance to make it right, just blank faces.  Do not recommend, save your self the time and money and go elsewhere."
> **- Liam Toohey (1/5/5)**

> "Dentist was okay. However they operate dual pricing and said “it’s like this, sorry”.  Two prices - 3000 baht for checkup and clean for foreigners, my wife paid 1800 for exactly the same thing.  Wouldn’t recommend."
> **- Adrian Fee (1/5/5)**

> "**I wanted to visit this place, but the admin service was very disappointing sarcastic and rude. As a local, I’d suggest considering other place instead**👎"
> **- khanichnett homklinkaew (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/d-smile-dental-clinic-1.jpg','088 762 1590','26 28 ม.3 ตำบล บ่อผุด Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.1,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ig1d003gq8xdfxkqj28w','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.487+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.487+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/d-smile-dental-clinic-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/d-smile-dental-clinic-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3404424684893470538',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('dan-auto','standard','cmr07igch0080q8xdu0jjdzda','Dan Auto','## Top Reviews
> "Lived in Samui for 14 years and never found a decent mechanic, and this ranges from main dealers to single operation businesses. THEN I came across Dan Autos!!! these guys gave me the best service experience I''ve had in Koh Samui, the owner speaks fluent English and he came out to the waiting area (great coffee shop) and explained every step that the engineers were carrying out on my Ford Ranger. truly fantastic service and value for money. Im now back with a second truck and receiving the same. THANKYOU DAN AUTO''s the very best on Koh Samui Island"
> **- scott cason (5/5/5)**

> "Best car service in Samui. Owner, Pete, has great english and mechanic skills :)"
> **- Anton Kovalenko (5/5/5)**

> "For vehicle service and repairs, also to get certificate for vehicles over 5 years old. (100 baht for bike).  Has Mobile Oil sign now,  Grey frontage. It used to be Castrol Oil."
> **- Jim P (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dan-auto-1.jpg','089 873 1292','18, 7, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.mobil.co.th/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifui0012q8xdzn158clv','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.489+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.489+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dan-auto-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dan-auto-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4666172982368634873',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('dara-samui-beach-resort','standard','cmr07igcj0081q8xdelgz4s56','Dara Samui Beach Resort','## Top Reviews
> "The Dara Samui Hotel is right at the entrance of the party area on Chaweng Beach, so you can be in the middle of the action in 5 to 10 minutes. The property is not the newest, but very well kept. Rooms are very clean, with big showers and large bathrooms. The staff is super friendly, always helpful, and cheerful. The beach is a bit small but still clean and with a nice view and invited you for long walks around the shore. The whole place is quiet, not noisy. The pool area is lovely, with a top  level ocean view from where you can look down at the beach area - extra plus for the nice wide view. One thing to know: it’s under a flight path, so you can hear planes maybe 6 to 12 times a day. But it starts in the morning and stops around 8 or 9 PM. Honestly, after a couple of days, we barely noticed, and it’s cool to watch them. Overall, we are super happy: great value for money, breakfast was good, had all we needed—we didn’t need 30 kinds of toast and Jogurts. Variety is on spot. It was perfect for us! We have been here from end april to first half of may 2026"
> **- Thorsten Lückemeier (4/5/5)**

> "I really have to say, I’ve already stayed in many hotels across different countries, but this was by far the best hotel in terms of service and food. I had one of the top three dishes I’ve ever eaten here — the Phat Thai with beef and chicken was absolutely incredible.  The hotel is located right at the beginning of the promenade and offers a beautiful atmosphere throughout the entire resort. The staff — especially at the pool bar — were outstanding: always friendly, attentive, and incredibly accommodating.  Every evening, there was a beautiful candlelight dinner setup directly on the beach, where you could enjoy dinner while listening to the sound of the sea beneath your feet — a truly unique experience. Chaweng Beach itself is also absolutely stunning.  I’m genuinely sad that I couldn’t stay longer, but I will definitely come back — that’s a promise!"
> **- Sascha Hartmann (5/5/5)**

> "An absolutely exceptional stay. The staff is incredibly helpful, attentive, and truly goes above and beyond to make every guest feel special. The quality of the services is outstanding.  A very special thank you to Are, who welcomed us so warmly and surprised us with a suite upgrade for our honeymoon — a gesture that meant a lot to us and made our stay even more memorable.  The hotel is stunning, full of authentic Thai charm, beautifully designed with great taste and attention to every detail. The atmosphere is elegant and luxurious without being over the top.  The breakfast is excellent, and the beachfront bars with their cocktails are amazing — everything is perfectly thought out for a dream stay.  The location is ideal: all shops nearby, right next to the lively party street yet perfectly quiet and peaceful.  I will definitely return every time I come back to Koh Samui, without hesitation."
> **- Ahmed.H (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dara-samui-beach-resort-1.jpg','077 231 323','162/2 2,, ถนน หาดเฉวง, ตำบล บ่อผุด Bophut, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.darasamui.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.491+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.491+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dara-samui-beach-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dara-samui-beach-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13839431996678493450',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('dara-samui-weddings','standard','cmr07igcl0082q8xd2i56qp2h','Dara Samui Weddings','## Top Reviews
> "Thank you so much to Chef Dara and her team for an amazing New Year''s Eve dinner in Koh Samui! They came to our rental villa and prepared a private dining experience that was lovely and incredibly delicious. Both the presentation and flavors of the meal were top notch. The service was friendly and professional. They took care of everything from start to finish. We highly recommend Siri Dara Samui Chef for an excellent dining experience in Koh Samui."
> **- Ariya Lapan (5/5/5)**

> "Chef Dara exceeded all of our expectations. Every single dish was presented so beautifully and tasted amazing. Our best meal in Thailand!! She and her team were also so friendly and she explained each of her dishes so well. Would definitely recommend and well worth the money!"
> **- Sandy (5/5/5)**

> "Our cooking class with Dara at Siri Dara Chef’s Table was an absolute highlight of our trip to Koh Samui! From start to finish, the experience was immersive, educational, and so much fun. Dara is not only an incredibly skilled chef but also a warm and engaging host who made us feel right at home in her beautiful kitchen.  We learned to cook authentic Thai dishes using fresh, local ingredients, and Dara guided us through every step with patience and expertise. She shared so many valuable cooking tips, cultural insights, and personal stories that made the experience even more special. The best part? Enjoying our delicious creations in a cozy, intimate setting!  If you’re looking for a hands-on, unforgettable culinary experience in Koh Samui, this is the class to take. Whether you’re a beginner or a seasoned cook, Dara will make sure you leave with new skills, amazing memories, and a happy (and very full) stomach. Highly recommend!"
> **- Donna Buonanno (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dara-samui-weddings-1.jpg','094 517 8916','28, 143 Moo1 Soi Maenam 1, Tambon Mae Nam, Koh Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://instagram.com/siridarasamui?igshid=YmMyMTA2M2Y=',NULL,'cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.493+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.493+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dara-samui-weddings-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dara-samui-weddings-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17451415552122429697',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('dara-serene','standard','cmr07igcn0083q8xdftiyeq1e','Dara Serene','## Top Reviews
> "We came here for a romantic dinner on the beach for my husband’s birthday and everything was absolutely perfect. The atmosphere was beautiful, the food was delicious, and the staff were incredibly kind and attentive.  They surprised my husband with a beautiful birthday dessert and even gave us the cake for free, which made the evening even more special. He absolutely loved it! Such a thoughtful gesture and amazing service.  Thank you for making his birthday unforgettable. We highly recommend this place for a special dinner in Thailand!"
> **- Carlota Corzo Álvarez (5/5/5)**

> "It was amazing! I ordered the “Happy Birthday” sign for my girlfriend’s birthday, and it did not disappoint! The tenderloin was fantastic, and they came with a free birthday cake and sang happy birthday to us after dinner. The table was right on the beach, with the waves in front of us, and live music. Service was excellent, and they took probably 100 photos of us 😅 Could not recommend more!"
> **- Lin_ Lei (5/5/5)**

> "We came over from a previous hotel at fisherman’s bay and were blown away by the hospitality and service here. The hotel is clean and beautiful but it is truly the staff that make this place, from the receptionist to the bar staff  and especially Jackson we were made to feel like royalty. Our honeymoon was truly made to feel special by the staff here and could not recommend it enough"
> **- Ross Miller (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dara-serene-1.jpg','077 231 323','162, 2, Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.darasamui.com/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.495+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.495+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dara-serene-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dara-serene-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17062186693085254001',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('david-luxe-jewelry','standard','cmr07igcp0084q8xd0z87a8g9','David Luxe Jewelry','## Top Reviews
> "David Luxe and his team are exceptional jewellers. The photos show a ring stack. One was lost and he made a replacement so good, you cannot tell which it is!  I went to many jewellers who refused to guarantee a match. The rings mean so much to me. My mother bought them for me nearly 40 years ago. The ring was lost on a crowded train the day we were sent home for the first COVID lockdown. The train operators could not find it. I contacted David a few weeks before we went to Ko Samui. We were there 6 days. He made the ring in 4. The cost saving we made compared to the UK, paid for our stay in beautiful Lamai. David updated me daily.  He is a true gentleman. You will not find better craftsmanship, value and customer care. David Luxe ❤️"
> **- Anita Sengupta (5/5/5)**

> "I got in touch with David to resize my fiancés engagement ring as it was too big but we only had a small amount of time left in Koh Samui however David made sure that it was not an issue and had the ring resized and returned all in under 24hrs. He was very responsive to any messages and answered all the questions and concerns I had, making sure to explain everything in great detail.  David made sure to take great care of the ring and has done a phenomenal job (you can not tell that the ring has had any alterations made whatsoever) & was very professional from start to finish. He also gave a very fair & competitive price for the service.  Me and my fiancé are both over the moon with how well the ring has come back and how smooth the whole process was. We both highly recommend David Luxe Jewellery."
> **- Jacob Thorp (5/5/5)**

> "I came to David with some opals that I purchased on my travels from Australia. A ring for my girlfriend and 2 necklaces as gifts. They all look amazing. David is a nice guy who helped us out with getting our custom designs close to our budget. I would recommend to anyone and would love to come back someday. Cheers David"
> **- George Mytton (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/david-luxe-jewelry-1.jpg','085 789 2598','124/529 M.3, ตำบล มะเร็ต Koh Samui, Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/jewelrysamui/','["Monday: 2:00 – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 2:00 – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 2:00 – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 2:00 – 8:00 PM","Friday: 2:00 – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 2:00 – 8:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.497+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.497+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/david-luxe-jewelry-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/david-luxe-jewelry-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17173186760692819657',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('dawn-korean-restaurant','standard','cmr07igcr0085q8xdiffq4w6z','Dawn Korean Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "Lovely Korean restaurant with fresh ingredients and produce. The warm hospitality and food here is fantastic. Thoroughly enjoyed my bowl of beef broth soup and rice."
> **- Wunda Stone (5/5/5)**

> "I recently had the pleasure of dining at Dawn, and it was an incredible experience! The food was authentically Korean, with rich flavors and dishes that truly transported me to Korea. The menu offered a great variety, and everything I tried was fresh, delicious, and prepared to perfection.  The prices were very reasonable, especially considering the quality of the food—it’s hard to find such authentic Korean cuisine at such good value. While the service was a bit slow, the staff were friendly and attentive once they arrived, making the wait worthwhile.  Overall, this is a fantastic spot for anyone looking to enjoy a genuine Korean dining experience without breaking the bank. I will definitely be coming back! Highly recommended."
> **- Aviram Gaon (5/5/5)**

> "As a foodie, I can definitely confirm that this restaurant is 100% authentic and tastes like Korean food. The food there is fantastic, everything is prepared very quickly and freshly. One of the best Korean restaurants I have eaten at abroad. I can only recommend it."
> **- Seraina Lopes (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dawn-korean-restaurant-1.jpg','084 850 1857','37/45, ตำบล บ่อผุด koh samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.499+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.499+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dawn-korean-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dawn-korean-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10486650346642920620',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('day-night','standard','cmr07igcs0086q8xd7cchg9ay','Day & Night','## Top Reviews
> "One of the best meals I had in Koh Samui. Every dish was delicious, especially the grilled Pork chop and creamy carbonara. The Caesar salad was fresh with plenty of parmesan and bacon, and the mushroom soup was rich and comforting. Great atmosphere, friendly staff, and beautiful presentation. Definitely worth visiting if you’re looking for a nice dinner spot in Samui. Will come back again! 🍽️✨"
> **- Jakkrit Timsawai (5/5/5)**

> "Lovely restaurant with a vintage vibe and plenty of photo spots. The upper floor is a rooftop, but it was fully booked when we visited. I’d recommend making a reservation in advance, especially before 7PM, as it gets quite busy.  We tried the Seafood Arrabbiata Spaghetti — you can choose the spice level. The flavor was good and the pasta was perfectly cooked al dente. The fried fish was also tasty, though a bit on the spicy side, so you might want to mention it if you prefer mild flavors.  Staff were friendly and attentive, which made the dining experience even better. Overall, a nice place for a relaxed meal in a great atmosphere."
> **- Cinderella Indie (5/5/5)**

> "Was recommended this restaurant by a relative and it was really good. An extensive food and drinks menu including beers and wines.  We ordered several dishes such as the watermelon with fish flakes, tom yum cashews but the Bai Liang Pad Kai (stir-fried Malindjo leaves with egg) was absolutely outstanding."
> **- Gursheel Dhillon (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/day-night-1.jpg','077 332 902','G3J7+P3, Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.dayandnight.co.th/koh-samui-2/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.500+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.500+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/day-night-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/day-night-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13447464197373982053',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('de-o-cafe','standard','cmr07igcv0087q8xd66v67gyo','De O Cafe','## Top Reviews
> "The servers are super friendly. The drinks are exquisite coming equipped with a golden spoon. We also have a stir rod. The bread was super fresh; it was cash money. The sandwiches were so yummy. There is even a garnish on the side of the sandwich. There is even a wonderful experience with a cute small cat. You can play with the kitchen while waiting for your food… if she chooses you."
> **- April VanKirk (5/5/5)**

> "We made this our regular spot on the island, and it never disappointed. Everything we tried—from fresh smoothies and coffees to a variety of Thai dishes—was incredibly flavorful, beautifully presented, and the price-to-quality ratio is unbeatable. The small team working there is also very warm and welcoming.  The restaurant is located on a busy main road, so it can get a bit noisy at times, but it didn’t bother us in the slightest. Highly recommend this spot for anyone looking for a delicious, casual meal"
> **- Sady S (5/5/5)**

> "Perfect Thai place with amazing food and smoothies! The family who owns the place are very welcoming and friendly, they cook very well and are very attentive to clients needs. The place is very cute. A bit noisy because it’s on the road but it’s common in the area."
> **- Keren Lipiec (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/de-o-cafe-1.jpg','091 896 3299','ถ. ทวีราษฎร์ภักดี Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: Closed","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifso000kq8xdfe9gpaon','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.503+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.503+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/de-o-cafe-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/de-o-cafe-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4542539085069568386',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('de-salon','standard','cmr07igcx0088q8xdm8v092x9','De'' Salon','## Top Reviews
> "If you want to have a perfect cut, highlights or dyed your hair, this hair salon is highly recommended. Simple, fashionable and professional hair stylists."
> **- Timea Ivančová (4/5/5)**

> "I came here to get my hair washed and dried after a day of snorkeling. I came in with very tangled and dry hair after being in the ocean all day. They washed it and blowed dried it for me, and my hair is so silky and soft. I would highly recommend if you’re staying in koh samui to come and get your hair washed here, especially if you need help detangling"
> **- Jade Taubman (5/5/5)**

> "If you’re having trouble with where to have your hair cut in Samui - this is the place!! Super fast and a good price for a decent haircut. Washing with a bit of head massage included. 450 ฿ for loooong hair! Felt like a princess with TWO hairdressers blow drying my hair!! ขอบคุณค่ะ⭐️"
> **- Ann-Catherine Thylin (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/de-salon-1.jpg','082 418 2233','64/38 Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: Closed","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.505+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.505+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/de-salon-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/de-salon-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=853378379961741390',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('deepawali','standard','cmr07igcz0089q8xdy8tje6d9','Deepawali','## Top Reviews
> "Delicious indian. Lamb rogan josh was tender.  Mixed yogurt was refreshing. Naan was tasty and cirspy and chewy in all the good ways. It was amazing.  659 bhat for 2 people."
> **- Lau G V (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing food! Tasted very authentic. Affordable and great atmosphere next to all the other food vendors. Service great very attentive staff. Would 100% recommend"
> **- Football Unite (5/5/5)**

> "•	“An exceptional dining experience! The flavors are rich and well-balanced, with every dish prepared to perfection. Great ambiance and excellent service make it a place worth returning to.” Lamb biryani,chicken tandoori, cheese naan & butter chicken masala very good…"
> **- Jasni (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/deepawali-1.jpg','063 804 5566','79, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 11:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 11:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 11:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 11:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 11:30 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.507+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.507+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/deepawali-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/deepawali-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9620712580317236973',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('delish-cafe-restaurant','standard','cmr07igd1008aq8xdoh81lm7s','Delish Cafe & Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "Homemade bread and blueberry fruit bowl was amazing! We also loved the Caramel Coffee and service! Comfortable and lovely spot for a late breakfast."
> **- Sara Fisher (5/5/5)**

> "We came for lunch and it was sooo delicious we came back for dinner and will definitely be coming lots over the next 5 days. Food really fresh and definitely the best food we have had in Thailand. So much flavour and staff absolutely lovely. Fully recommend coming here. Thank you so much for 2 lovely meals… so far!"
> **- Anna Coleman (5/5/5)**

> "Food is really good! Unfortunately, it seems that the place is understaffed.  - Took some time to get a waitresses anytime we needed something. No system for getting their attention. - We asked for the WiFi but got a half answer and we''re not really able to connect. I ended up sharing my own hotspot. - We had to ask for toothpick 3 times  Staff were also not too welcoming. Not at the same service level I have seen in other places in Koh Samurai."
> **- Emanuel Piza (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/delish-cafe-restaurant-1.jpg','098 584 6898','155/32,58,63, Chaweng Beach Rd, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.509+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.509+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/delish-cafe-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/delish-cafe-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4634085235820939594',NULL,NULL);
