INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('dental-design-clinic','standard','cmr07igd9008cq8xd0z8s25pz','Dental Design Clinic','## Top Reviews
> "I had my appointment about a week ago, so checking in to share my experience: I had a nerve inflammation of my wisdom tooth and I needed to get it removed urgently.  I called Dental design clinic, they offered the earliest time slot compared to other clinics and actually called me back to offer even earlier time. The tooth removal took just a couple of minutes , completely pain free. Great doctor and great crew around him. They did a detailed xray of my wisdom tooth too before removing it.  Provided me with antibiotics as well, very professional doctor. I read reviews before picking the clinic, and I am lucky I went with this clinic! Thank you guys"
> **- Vladimir Pavlov (5/5/5)**

> "This must be the best dentist in Koh Samui. I''ve been going to dentists for four decades and been a few in Thailand. The Doctor is so good and wanting to help me with my problem, While other dentists in the island wouldn''t even see me. He agreed to see me as an emergency patient. The staff are so nice and attentive, If I lived here this would definitely be my dentists, I want to thank Dr TEE and his staff again and let people know about my experience."
> **- G Candan (5/5/5)**

> "I had my wisdom tooth taken out by Dr Tee. Bear in mind I’m a very nervous patient. I was in and out in 20min. He was very gentle and his nurses helped me relax. I like their holistic approach. The whole process was painless. Thank you very much for your patience with me :)"
> **- Veronika Frankova (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dental-design-clinic-1.jpg','061 249 0228','11 7 ตำบล แม่น้ำ Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 AM – 12:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 12:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 12:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 12:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 12:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ig1d003gq8xdfxkqj28w','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.517+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.517+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dental-design-clinic-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dental-design-clinic-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1817787313147513471',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('design-brows-lash','standard','cmr07igdc008dq8xdrumidfv3','Design Brows & Lash','## Top Reviews
> "Got a manicure and pedicure and am super happy with the result. Friendly service, clean, attention to detail and a cute cat in the salon 😻"
> **- Katharina J (5/5/5)**

> "I stopped by spontaneously for a pedicure and luckily they had time right away. They worked with great care and everything was hygienic. I’m super happy with the result! :)  Thank you!"
> **- Kim Kierstn (5/5/5)**

> "Had a wonderful experience for both, lashes and nails. Highly recommend them to everyone!!!"
