INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('dining-the-beach-samui','standard','cmr07igdk008gq8xdnieyu8ts','Dining @ The Beach Samui','## Top Reviews
> "Our stay was really nice and especially thanks to TIME!! Time, you’re the heartbeat of the beach! Always spotting what we need before we even ask, taking care of everyone with a smile that lights up the sand. Super kind, super sharp—thanks for making our days epic! 🌴🍹"
> **- Josje Derijk (5/5/5)**

> "Talay Restaurant was amazing! Delicious menu, stunning beach views, and unforgettable cocktails. Boo, Buii, and Laii made the experience extra special with their warm, attentive service. Highly recommend for great food, great vibes, and truly memorable hospitality!"
> **- Trish Hannah (5/5/5)**

> "Big thanks for Mister Time!Smiling face ,full attention,lots of help! Mr.Time is fully customer oriented and I had the best service in years!Thank You gor everything,definitely going to come back!Food was fantastic !"
> **- Gabija Mostvilaitė (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dining-the-beach-samui-1.jpg','077 300 564','90 1, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.baanchawengbeachresort.com/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07igdj008fq8xdhc2mye6x','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.528+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.528+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dining-the-beach-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dining-the-beach-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1145235554569311191',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('discovery-dive-centre','standard','cmr07igdn008hq8xdmgup53pg','Discovery Dive Centre','## Top Reviews
> "I did my PADI Open Water Course with Discover Divers with OT as my Instructor. It was my first time diving and it was perfect. OT always made sure that im okay and I always felt safe. He has a lot of patience and explain things in a very nice way. All the other instructors and the crew on the boat were also very kind and fun. If you want a great diving experience and a great instructor, you should definetly dive with Discovery Divers."
> **- Ramona Hager (5/5/5)**

> "⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ Outstanding experience with Discovery Dive Centre, Koh Samui!  I had an excellent experience getting my PADI Open Water Certification with Discovery Dive Centre during my Thailand trip. From the very beginning, communication was effortless — quick replies, clear answers, and no ambiguity at any point. The transparency in pricing and transactions was refreshing, and the entire booking process was seamless and stress-free.  The e-learning system was easy to access, well structured, and perfectly paced, which made the in-water sessions far more productive. What really stood out was how cooperative and flexible the team was — even after completing my Open Water course, they smoothly helped me arrange a fun dive day without any hassle. And I chose Discovery again for my Fun Dive Trip BECAUSE of the genuinely unforgettable and enriching experience during my training dives.  A special mention to Margaux, my instructor — truly exceptional. Her training style was calm, efficient, and extremely thorough. The quality of education and skill development I received was top-notch, and I felt confident, safe, and well-prepared at every step. You can clearly tell you’re being trained by someone who genuinely cares about good diving and cares about the ocean, not just ticking certification boxes.  While on this journey with Discovery I got to interact with the other trainers too and I must say - the entire team consists of extremely passionate divers who does this more for their their love for the Ocean and Marine Ecosystems than anything else. Everyone is extremely knowledgeable and comes across as reliable sources for everything related to diving.  Thank you to the entire Discovery Dive Centre team for such a professional and enjoyable experience. I highly recommend Discovery to anyone interested in diving, whether you’re a beginner or continuing your dive journey — and I’ll definitely be back for more dives in the future!  PS - the boat rides to and from the dive sites with delicious and savory lunch spread and coolers packed with all-you-can-drink icy cold cans of Coca Cola needs to be acknowledged..! 🙏🌊"
> **- Jajabor Chronicles (5/5/5)**

> "It was our first time diving and we opted for the Discover Scuba one-day, two-dives package and went to Sail Rock. Our instructors Joe and Gustavo were absolutely fantastic. I didn’t know what to expect so I was really nervous but excited.  The crew were so friendly and knowledgeable, and from the minute they started briefing us when we walked in to the moment we were getting off the boat at the end, they were great company. I was genuinely so grateful to be in such capable hands.  They were so patient, explained everything in detail (as many times as I asked) and Joe brought me back up to the surface as many times as I needed till I was accustomed to the dive environment. Never made me feel rushed or pressured. I was worried at the start that this experience would maybe be one of those once-in-a-lifetime, one-and-done things, but no, not at all. Their passion and love for the sport was so evident and infectious I’m now itching to go back and am definitely going to look to get my certification next!  We were picked up and dropped off directly at our hotel. Food was included and lunch was quick, light, and very tasty. If you’re interested (but rightfully nervous) like me, I would say take the dive (excuse the pun). You may not like it, but you may also fall in love with it, and what you see under there isn’t comparable to anything I’ve seen in marine documentaries. You won’t know until you try, and there’s no better moment than this."
> **- Joelle Pasala (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/discovery-dive-centre-1.jpg','095 271 0017','14 3 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.discoverydivers.com/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.531+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.531+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/discovery-dive-centre-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/discovery-dive-centre-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7164649873546772550',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('diva-nail-studio','standard','cmr07igdp008iq8xd08tum0wo','Diva Nail Studio','## Top Reviews
> "Just had biab refill, and I''m extremely happy with the results. The technician was careful and took her time to ensure a stunning result.  Highly recommend."
> **- Iulita Staica (5/5/5)**

> "This is such a lovely salon! Me and my friend got our manicure and pedicure done😍😍 We loved it, soo pretty and pristine. They also do 3D nail art soo well! Highly skilled women! I wish I could’ve got those nails😍 The people are soo lovely and friendly. I would definitely recommend 💗"
> **- CEO of Henjoyment (5/5/5)**

> "Incredible design, I really love my new nails! Thank you 🙏🏻"
> **- Jade Wonders LDN (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/diva-nail-studio-1.jpg',NULL,'14, 6, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://divanailstudio.simplybook.asia/v2/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.533+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.533+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/diva-nail-studio-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/diva-nail-studio-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5632184872326166178',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('divas-cabaret-samui','standard','cmr07igds008jq8xdygngdgyc','Divas Cabaret Samui','## Top Reviews
> "This is a really fun night. I would highly recommend to visit this place whilst in Koh Samui.  The acts are great and very engaging. Little expensive but worth it."
> **- Becky Walker (5/5/5)**

> "A Mixed Bag: Fun Show, But Beware of the Tourist Traps!  We visited Divas Cabaret yesterday, July 13th, for their last show at 10:30 PM (they also have shows at 8:30 PM and 9:30 PM). Our experience was a real mix, and while some parts were enjoyable, it ultimately felt like a bit of a tourist trap. On the positive side, the show itself was kind of fun. It''s an hour long with upbeat music and the performers frequently change costumes, which keeps the energy up. However, there were several significant downsides. While the initial ticket prices seem reasonable (starting from 250 Baht without a drink, or around 380 Baht with a first drink), the price of additional drinks is absolutely outrageous. I paid 170 Baht for a single bottle of water, which is easily 10 times the standard price! This felt like a blatant rip-off. Another disappointment was the lip-syncing. Many of the performers seemed to just open and close their mouths without actually knowing the words, which really detracted from the performance. Finally, be prepared for the aggressive solicitation for photos at the end. Performers will approach you, but they don''t state a price and effectively won''t let you leave until you pay them for the opportunity. We ended up paying an extra 140 Baht for this, which felt forced and underhanded. In summary, if you go, be aware of the hidden costs and don''t expect a polished lip-sync performance. The show has its moments, but the high prices for drinks and the pushy photo tactics definitely left a sour taste."
> **- Ron Sher (2/5/5)**

> "Ordered Mojitos and it tastes good! The show is so nice, no regret watching it. You can see the performers take pride in their performance and are interactive with audience! Choice of music is great, really flow with crowd and everyone enjoyed the show. Do stay back for photo taking and give them some tips ;)"
> **- Audrey Says (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/divas-cabaret-samui-1.jpg','062 191 8602','60, 43, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:00 – 11:30 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 – 11:30 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 – 11:30 PM","Thursday: 8:00 – 11:30 PM","Friday: 8:00 – 11:30 PM","Saturday: 8:00 – 11:30 PM","Sunday: 8:00 – 11:30 PM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.536+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.536+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/divas-cabaret-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/divas-cabaret-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5352287028759630593',NULL,NULL);
