> "Ordered Mojitos and it tastes good! The show is so nice, no regret watching it. You can see the performers take pride in their performance and are interactive with audience! Choice of music is great, really flow with crowd and everyone enjoyed the show. Do stay back for photo taking and give them some tips ;)"
> **- Audrey Says (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/divas-cabaret-1.jpg','062 191 8602','60, 43, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:00 – 11:30 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 – 11:30 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 – 11:30 PM","Thursday: 8:00 – 11:30 PM","Friday: 8:00 – 11:30 PM","Saturday: 8:00 – 11:30 PM","Sunday: 8:00 – 11:30 PM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.540+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.540+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/divas-cabaret-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/divas-cabaret-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5352287028759630593',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('dk1-hostel','standard','cmr07igdx008lq8xdminc4ayu','DK1 Hostel','## Top Reviews
> "This is my second stay at DK1 Hostel, and once again, the past two weeks have been absolutely wonderful. Mama, the owner, is incredibly kind and makes you feel right at home. It’s easy to meet people there and spend time together. The staff do everything they can to keep the dorms, bathrooms, and common areas clean. I recommend this hostel 100%."
> **- Nicolas (5/5/5)**

> "If you’re looking for home away from home in Koh Samui then this is the place. DK mama maintains the place like her own house, greets and interacts with each and every guest. The location of the hostel is also quite close to popular Chaweng beach which is also Nightlife hub of Samui. Hostel also has very well equipped kitchen where you can cook your own meals. Meet really great folks in the hostel and was really amazing to hear their stories. Thank you for taking care mama and will see you soon."
> **- TEJAS KULKARNI (5/5/5)**

> "Out of all the hostels we’ve stayed in, DK1 will always have a special place in our hearts. The rooms and bathrooms are super spacious with everything you need. Facilities are perfect with as much coffee and water are you could want. Right around the corner from the beach/7 eleven/stadium, honestly the list goes on. That being said - nothing compares to our DK mama. A wonderful, beautiful soul that turns every stranger into family. My partner and I only stayed 2 nights, but even in such a short space of time, mama captured our hearts and gave us a home away from home. When we arrived, my partner had a foot injury and I had come down with the cold. Mama went above and beyond from helping us get ice and making sure we were safe, comfortable and happy to offering to go and get us dinner and bring it to us. She is incredibly hard working and tends to all hostel needs on her own. But was never too busy to have a yap and a giggle with us. We could not have asked for a more wonderful stay. (Not to mention meow meow the cat who is most loveable, sweet girl). Thank you so much for everything mama, your Scottish girls will never forget you ❤️"
> **- Julie Thomson (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dk1-hostel-1.jpg','089 329 9698','81/70 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61557757553659&mibextid=ZbWKwL','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.541+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.541+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dk1-hostel-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dk1-hostel-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17531111857866724533',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('dog-and-cat-pet-center','standard','cmr07ige0008mq8xdrnfxetaj','Dog And Cat Pet Center','## Top Reviews
> "I like the pets at the shop. There are a lot to see. They are well taken care of and the pets are healthy. The staff take good care of the animals and are very attentive to the pets. Give honest advice to customers."
> **- วสันต์ จุ้ยกลาง (5/5/5)**

> "Great shop. Very nice owner. We buy all our pet supplies here."
> **- J O (5/5/5)**

> "This shop is very big and nice. They have all products for pet. And they do pet care and grooming services too. I come here every month. I love here."
> **- ผลทอง (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dog-and-cat-pet-center-1.jpg','088 440 1304','25/219 moo 6 bophut Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/dogcatsamui?mibextid=LQQJ4d','["Monday: 9:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: Closed","Thursday: 9:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 9:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 9:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 9:30 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.544+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.544+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dog-and-cat-pet-center-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dog-and-cat-pet-center-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11049950937255987334',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('double-js','standard','cmr07ige3008nq8xdv0eqawmy','Double J''s','## Top Reviews
> "What a wonderful spot to stop at after a downpour. A nice tea, a warm friendly pet, a hospitable welcome from the staff and great music made my short time there just perfect. Sara is so sweet and even brought us something to help us dry off a little. Thank you for showing up on our path through Samui. Wishing you the best"
> **- Saranaz Mohammadi (5/5/5)**

> "Double Js is one of the best spots we discovered in Koh Samui, it has a bar, a great pool table and live music by Jesse. My boyfriend and I went here because it was right across the hotel we were staying at (ibis) and we ended up coming back almost every night. Not only did Double Js have very high-quality weed (we almost tried the entire menu!) But also the conversations and time we spent there was always relaxing, had a nice atmosphere with also great customer service. We always felt very welcomed, like we were meeting an old friend. Highly recommend to anyone visiting Koh Samui. We can''t wait to come back! :)"
> **- Gurman Grewal (5/5/5)**

> "Exceptionally friendly staff – you immediately feel welcome and part of the place. The owner is a gem of a person! Funny, animal-loving, and very personable. Everything here is just right: the quality, the advice, the prices, and the service.  The evenings with live music are especially worth mentioning! Whether it’s a band or a DJ, there’s always great music. It’s also important to highlight the excellent service from the bartenders.  Double J’s was where we felt most at home, and we’re looking forward to spending a few more evenings here on our next visit to the island."
> **- F M (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/double-js-1.jpg','064 227 8620','177 Plai Laem Soi 2, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.547+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.547+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/double-js-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/double-js-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14997007047997317097',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('dr-frogs-bar-grill','standard','cmr07ige7008oq8xduf9jngur','Dr. Frogs Bar & Grill','## Top Reviews
> "We came for a roast dinner on Christmas Eve and firstly, the views and design of the restaurant are beautiful. The food was good but we don’t think it was quite worth the price point (this was a Christmas set menu so appreciate there will be an uplift on the price). The staff were friendly but service was pretty slow. All in all a good place to come for a roast if you are willing to pay the price point."
> **- Kyah G (4/5/5)**

> "A perfect place to enjoy a meal with a view. We went for Sunday Roast. As it was our first visit, we both had the mix Roast, with every meat. Next time I think I will go for the porchetta. The plate was full and plenty of sauce on the side. The taste was really good, everything from the meat to the sauce and the vegetables was perfect! Tiramisu was also on point! Will definitely be back, both for Roast and to try the normal menu as well.  Recommend to book before as it was full when we were there."
> **- André Falkenhaug (5/5/5)**

> "One of the best meals we had in Koh Samui. Had to go back a second time to try their Roast Dinner which is one of the best I’ve ever had.  Only small gripe could possibly be the location as it is a bit isolated and hard to get a cab from.  Regardless, highly recommended!"
> **- Mark Gordon (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dr-frogs-bar-grill-1.jpg','077 448 505','103 B, Moo Bophut 3 Chaweng Noi Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.drfrogs.com/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig5c0051q8xdykrbexft','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.551+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.551+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dr-frogs-bar-grill-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dr-frogs-bar-grill-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10079008141449042014',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('dr-give-clinic','standard','cmr07igea008pq8xdes22ko2u','Dr. Give Clinic','## Top Reviews
> "I actually had a fine time here getting stitches removed and liked the doctor. I don’t like giving bad reviews but after taking bandages off I realized there were multiple stitches left in, including a full one - knot included. My husband had to cut to remove them and it was difficult as skin had started growing over them. They were not absorbable stitches and I asked multiple times to confirm they were all taken out so to me reflected a lack of attention to detail :("
> **- Julie (2/5/5)**

> "I didn’t book an appointment however the doctors welcomed me in from the rain and arranged to meet my aesthetic requests. I can not rate this clinic highly enough. First class treatment and equal to if not better than any clinic in Australia. The doctors spoke very well English and they even gave me medication at no cost for a cough I have picked up while travelling. If I could give 10 stars I would."
> **- Rhonda McDougall (5/5/5)**

> "Such a wonderful doctor and place. I got Botox and ultraformer skin treatment. I was a bit apprehensive getting this done in Thailand but Honestly couldn’t have asked for more very professional, gave great guidance and advice. Treatment was great needed small touch up in one area so went back in after a week and doctor fixed up for free. The service was amazing and great family clinic. Highly recommend"
> **- Fleur Montgomery (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dr-give-clinic-1.jpg','099 296 5225','132, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/dr.giveclinicsamui','["Monday: 5:00 – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 5:00 – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 5:00 – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 5:00 – 8:00 PM","Friday: 5:00 – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ig1d003gq8xdfxkqj28w','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.554+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.554+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dr-give-clinic-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/dr-give-clinic-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5752368613091319212',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('dr-health-clinic-samui','standard','cmr07igec008qq8xdjyjuoprk','Dr. Health Clinic Samui','## Top Reviews
> "Super clean, new, efficient clinic conveniently located fronting Chaweng Beach Rd. across from the Matcha Samui Resort even with the southern end of the water basin, open 9AM-10PM.  I had the bad misfortune of a dog bite on the DonSak mainland and needed a second round of a four-shot Rabies regimine while continuing on to Koh Samui. The friendly, confident well-English speaking staff, receptionist Asmin and nurses Belle & Im viewed my passport and prescription and then led me into their E.R. where I ''dropped my drawers'' for them to tend and re-dress my wound. Jokes by me about my lilly white farang ass had all laughing, but the ladies were most professional with their care.  I was in & out in under 25 minutes and the cost was fair, a little more than the 1275thb Provincial DonSak Hospital charged and 2000thb less than Samui Hospital. Happy, happy, my ''tail was wagging'' on the way out."
> **- GARY HIDU (5/5/5)**

> "Very good. Highly recommended! The staff were both friendly and professional and took my situation seriously. I explained the problem, and they handled it quickly and effectively. Very skilled professionals – 10/10. Fast response on tests and results, and excellent follow-up from the doctor."
> **- Hemeli “Primus” Aksn (5/5/5)**

> "Outstanding! Can’t thank the nurses enough, extremely thorough and caring. Compassionate and understanding, will treat you well. Be kind to them, they know what they’re doing very well. Would 10/10 recommend"
