INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('drip-indeed','standard','cmr07igef008rq8xdhjm3ozl1','Drip Indeed','## Top Reviews
> "Absolutely the best spot for specialty coffee on the entire island. We had the chance to meet the owner, Mimi, and it was clear right away how passionate she’s about coffee. Mimi understands the importance of working with small local roasters and continually experimenting with the extraction process to bring out the best characteristics of each bean. That dedication shows in every cup—exceptionally balanced, flavorful, and expertly prepared.  Beyond the coffee, the shop has an incredible vibe: welcoming, relaxed, and full of character. As an added bonus, there are two adorable resident dogs who make the experience even more memorable.  If you appreciate truly high-quality specialty coffee and the craftsmanship behind it, this place is a must-visit. A gem that sets the standard for coffee on Koh Samui."
> **- Ana Stasia (5/5/5)**

> "First iced pour over with Thai beans and it disappoint at all. Very chill atmosphere and the barista was really welcoming  I can definitely recommend this place especially if you are looking for local beans but also different roasts."
> **- Nino (5/5/5)**

> "Great place for a hot and a cold coffee with excellent service. The coffee beans are local great quality Thai beans! 👌🏻"
> **- Robin Lubbe (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/drip-indeed-1.jpg','064 927 3961','63 2 ปลายแหลม Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'http://facebook.com/dripindeed','["Monday: 8:30 AM – 4:30 PM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 4:30 PM","Wednesday: Closed","Thursday: 8:30 AM – 4:30 PM","Friday: 8:30 AM – 4:30 PM","Saturday: 8:30 AM – 4:30 PM","Sunday: 8:30 AM – 4:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig6y005pq8xd4jrvheih','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.559+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.559+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/drip-indeed-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/drip-indeed-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2665162365041692082',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('driving-school-samui','standard','cmr07igei008sq8xdz46yqt13','Driving School Samui','## Top Reviews
> "I took 10 hours of driving lessons here, I didn’t have any experience before. The instructor was very calm, relaxed and attentive, so I immediately felt reassured and encouraged to drive confidently. You can either choose manual or automatic transmission to learn. Highly recommended."
> **- Anna (5/5/5)**

> "If I had a god, I would be screaming ''OMG'' from the top of the island!! Tbh I am still coming to terms with it....  6 months I had been worrying about my international licence about to expire (just to realise I was allowed only 3 months on it anyway! Sweat!), little to no time to go back to school in Phuket where the queue is beyond and more!! Honestly. Phuketians will know what I mean. More sweat!  Right, I finally came to Samui. Contacted the 2 schools I could find online. ครูหมู (Teacher Moo) responded and ... turned this utter headache into a breeze! Honestly. Not enough 5 stars here to show my appreciation and relief!  He whisked me through all the tests, paperwork, wait, more tests... and I was done in a blink of an eye. 2 licences (car, motorsai). AND a very nice welcome from the team at Department of Transport in Lipa Noi. Kudos to them too; swift, professional, efficient.  Thank YOU, Teacher Moo!! ครูหมูครับ ขอบคุณมากมาาาาาากครับ จริงๆ มีกวาทสุขมากไปเลย!!  (Pictures are before the tests, and after I passed) 🙈🤣"
> **- Eddy BROSSE (5/5/5)**

> "The first time I got behind the wheel of a car! Hooray! Prior to that I drove a motorbike for several years. I really liked the teacher, very confident in driving and pleasant in communication in English. The price is confidential, I completed 10 hours of classes. I drove around the site, learned to park, and drove all over the island with the teacher"
> **- S P (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/driving-school-samui-1.jpg','086 945 7171','153/16 Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 7:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07ifui0012q8xdzn158clv','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.562+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.562+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/driving-school-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/driving-school-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8662767703060801426',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('duomo-italian-restaurant','standard','cmr07igek008tq8xd5ial66dz','Duomo Italian Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "Exceptional, traditional Italian cuisine. We tried a pasta dish and a pizza both were excellent and on the level of, if not better than, any restaurant in Italy. All staff members were extremely attentive and the host made us feel at home. Highly recommend to anyone after home made Italian food and hospitality in Koh samui."
> **- Spencer Duckmanton (5/5/5)**

> "From the moment we arrived, we were warmly welcomed and seated. All the waitstaff were attentive, kind, and made our evening very enjoyable. The food was excellent, and the overall atmosphere was delightful. Italian music played softly in the background, and paired with the amazing food, it really felt like we were in Italy rather than Thailand. This is an outstanding Italian restaurant. The tiramisu was one of the best I’ve ever had, absolutely delicious. Highly recommended!"
> **- Bohdana Kráľová (5/5/5)**

> "We spent a wonderful evening in Duomo. We had a pizza, salads (portions are enormous), and tiramisu. The dessert was the best of all tiramisus that I have tried in my life😍 our waitress Bobo was the person who made it. Bobo and the staff:it was awesome! We will come back on our next visit to Samui❤️"
> **- Maria Tolkacheva (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/duomo-italian-restaurant-1.jpg','077 300 504','60/33 Soi MontienHouse | Chaweng Beach, ตำบล บ่อผุด Koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 12:30 – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:30 – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:30 – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 12:30 – 11:00 PM","Friday: 12:30 – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 12:30 – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 12:30 – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.564+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.564+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/duomo-italian-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/duomo-italian-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6428392985328960007',NULL,NULL);
