> **- Дмитрий Рыбин (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/enjoy-samui-cleaner-1.jpg','+66992984251','H328+F37, Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100075908932516','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.608+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.608+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/enjoy-samui-cleaner-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/enjoy-samui-cleaner-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1366807606064760246',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ensure-insurance','standard','cmr07igfv009gq8xd08ckz3ky','Ensure Insurance','## Top Reviews
> "I’ve been a client of Stephen and his team for over 10 years, and their service has consistently exceeded my expectations. They are always prompt, responsive, and especially supportive during those unexpected moments when you need help the most.  The range of insurance options they offer is excellent. I’ve been particularly impressed with William Russell, who handle claims efficiently and without any hassle.  I highly recommend Stephen and his team to anyone seeking reliable, professional insurance services."
> **- Patrick O''Connor (5/5/5)**

> "Excellent service for all insurance needs. Very helpful and conscientious."
> **- Alex Armitage (5/5/5)**

> "Very helpful staff with great insurance options. Highly recommended."
> **- James Clements (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ensure-insurance-1.jpg','095 035 8569','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://ensureasia.com/','["Monday: 9:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifsv000nq8xdrwnu123q','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.611+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.611+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ensure-insurance-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ensure-insurance-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12374410670874904395',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('escape-beach-resort','standard','cmr07igfx009hq8xdhicum28a','Escape Beach Resort','## Top Reviews
> "This hotel is absolutely fantastic. The bungalows are modern, well equipped with very comfortable beds. We didn’t have a beach front bungalow, but the complex is small so this isn’t an issue. Cleanliness is very good, with housekeeping everyday.  The pool area is great with a good, but little pricey bar with good cocktails. The breakfast is a small buffet, but the food quality is good. Staff service is very good and they are friendly and polite.  The highlight here is the pool and views right on the beach. Location isn’t amazing if you don’t have a scooter and there is a HUGE hill to get to the hotel."
> **- Josh Wood (5/5/5)**

> "This place is definitely not a resort. The staff barely speaks to you, let alone English. They weren’t friendly, it felt like they don’t want to be there.  Our bungalows were more like camping, not like hotel. There was a barely any space inside and we had mould in the shower. The floor was rotten and puffed from the humidity which scratched our feet all the time.  When you lay by the pool there is constantly Ibiza-lounge music with bass overstimulating you.  The only positive aspects for us were the view of the sea and friendly ladies working at the cafe.  There are a lot of young families with kids who are very active and loud around the beach/pool area. So keep it in mind if this is not the environment you need.  The hotel is located quite far away from everything, so scooter is recommended as walking would take around 30 minutes to the main road."
> **- Anastasiya K (2/5/5)**

> "Dear Escape Hotel,  Your location is truely amazing. The views and the beach make it feel like your in paradise. The interior of room was nice, just a smaller room. But that was no problem for us. For the team working in Escape; you can make a big diffrence in the experience of the guest. It’s the first time in Thailand staff was this level of not interested and actually rude to us (If I read the reviews we are not the only ones). If this place is trying to make the experience a 10, try to laugh more. Communicate pro-active with your guest, and smile!!!! It’s not only worth it for the guest expierence, but also for your own working day. Try to make a little fun/enjoy. The working culture feels really down in this place. When fixing this issue the place has a lot of potention to make this a 5 star accomodation."
> **- Dina Vdq (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/escape-beach-resort-1.jpg','077 425 405','5, 1, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.1,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.1hotelrez.com/hotelbookings3/?MPage=0&HotelID=WBE-TH-2023-05-00006&ChainID=WBG-TH-2023-05-00002&fbclid=IwAR2H4quErwUjCHOjRwR1d_xD6LZDU3d_kFlIQSeJEF-TYvKVG0Zh7lTi0ls','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.613+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.613+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/escape-beach-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/escape-beach-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13763612263302874684',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('escape-by-nikki-beach','standard','cmr07igfy009iq8xdpg0qx8kj','Escape By Nikki Beach','## Top Reviews
> "Don’t be fooled: the food in the photo wasn’t taken at KFC, but at Escape by Nikki Beach — a fancy, expensive place. Yet somehow the wings tasted worse than KFC’s. As for the squid in the foreground, it felt like it died of old age, got washed ashore by a wave, and only then ended up on the grill and on my plate. Completely inedible. The quality doesn’t come close to what the prices suggest. I was genuinely concerned about getting food poisoning and was lucky not to get sick.  The vibe and cocktails were decent, which is why this place earns two stars. Other than that, it’s absolutely terrible."
> **- Ruslan I. (2/5/5)**

> "This restaurant is truly excellent — both in terms of food quality and service. The staff are polite, friendly, and very attentive to detail. I’ve been here many times and have been impressed every time. They consistently maintain a high standard. Highly commendable!"
> **- Thanchanok Ch (5/5/5)**

> "Very good food, prices are on the higher end, but very much not bad. This particular visit we had to pay cash because the credit machine was down, no big deal. Nikki Beach is very hip had great music, an actual DJ on duty, beautiful sunset view, worth a visit."
> **- Cuisine Quest (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/escape-by-nikki-beach-1.jpg','077 914 500','3, Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.2,0,0,0,NULL,'https://nikkibeach.com/koh-samui/dine-drink/escape/','["Monday: 6:00 – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 6:00 – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 6:00 – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 6:00 – 11:00 PM","Friday: 6:00 – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 6:00 – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 6:00 – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.614+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.614+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/escape-by-nikki-beach-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/escape-by-nikki-beach-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8004776466429283536',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('escape-spa','standard','cmr07igg3009jq8xdzbbcscpu','Escape Spa','## Top Reviews
> "A fabulous spa experience. We were greeted with a drink, there was no rushing, however it’s good to be a bit early to relax. The attention to detail was evident when you walk into the treatment room and exceptionally clean. I had the head neck and shoulders for 90 minutes and my daughter had the signature massage. The massage was very relaxing in-fact one of the best I have ever had ."
> **- Tanya Collins (5/5/5)**

> "I went to SALA Spa in Chaweng, Koh Samui, and it was honestly the best massage I’ve ever had. I did their signature massage, which was around 90 minutes, and even though it’s a bit on the pricey side, it was absolutely worth it.  From the moment you walk in, the smell and atmosphere hit you in the best way. Everything is calm, warm, and luxurious without feeling intimidating. It really feels like they’re trying to engage all your senses, not just rush you through a treatment. The space is beautiful, quiet, and incredibly relaxing.  The therapist was amazing and clearly knew exactly what she was doing. You can tell the staff actually care about their work and take pride in it. It didn’t feel robotic or rushed at all, it felt very intentional and well paced. The pressure, technique, and flow of the massage were perfect, and I left feeling genuinely relaxed instead of sore or overstimulated.  Yes, it’s more expensive than your average Thai massage place, but the quality, environment, and overall experience completely justify the price. This is the kind of spa you go to when you want something special, not just a quick massage.  If you’re in Koh Samui and want a high end, sensory, genuinely relaxing spa experience, I would 100 percent recommend SALA Spa Chaweng. I’d go back in a heartbeat."
> **- Alex (5/5/5)**

> "We had an incredible experience at SALA Spa Koh Samui, truly one of the best spas we’ve ever been to.  From the moment we arrived, we loved all the sweet details and thoughtful touches throughout the experience: fresh tea, a flower under the bed, beautiful treatment rooms with private shower and toilets, and amazing bedding, towels, and bathrobes.  We chose the milk bath and signature massage experience and absolutely loved every part of the ritual, the oils, the peaceful atmosphere, and the meditation moments. Everything felt perfectly smooth and relaxing.  A special thank you to Rose and Milky for the amazing massages. The whole experience was flawless, we highly recommend!"
> **- Charlotte de Saint Périer (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/escape-spa-1.jpg','077 905 888','99, Beach, 10 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.salahospitality.com/samui-chaweng/wellness/sala-chaweng-spa/?utm_source=Google&utm_medium=GoogleMyBusiness&utm_campaign=Web_Link','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.619+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.619+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/escape-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/escape-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10269388805225229904',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('eva-cafe','standard','cmr07igg8009kq8xdjf9xm4eq','Eva Cafe','## Top Reviews
> "Peaceful, green, and quietly charming. Excellent selection and presentation. The iced latte was spot on, my honey perfect, and the macadamia cake dangerously good. Great service too, a calm little gem, absolutely worth the walk💎💎💎"
> **- mikegreek2000 (5/5/5)**

> "Good place to sit and quiet for your lunch either dinner. Not too busy still has people continue coming and having lunch. Staff well trained.. Many Interesting foods & drinks menu and service charge will be included."
> **- Thitaphas K. (5/5/5)**

> "Delicious food, beautiful place, and a calm, relaxing atmosphere. Definitely worth visiting!"
> **- Mocodar (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/eva-cafe-1.jpg','093 328 5860','13/2 Garden of Eden อาคาร 1 Tambon Taling Ngam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.gardenofedenthailand.com/evacafe','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: Closed","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ift8000pq8xd7yujz20i','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.624+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.624+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/eva-cafe-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/eva-cafe-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8728796711052934825',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('expat-rentals','standard','cmr07igga009lq8xd0jax1x8e','Expat Rentals','## Top Reviews
> "We had a very good experience. The staff were friendly, helpful, and easy to deal with throughout the whole process. The service was reliable, everything was clearly explained, and the rental went smoothly from start to finish.  The bike was in good condition, the prices were fair, and everything worked out without any problems. We especially appreciated that they delivered the motorbike directly to our accommodation and also picked it up from there afterwards, which made everything even more convenient.  We would definitely rent here again and would choose this place again on our next visit to Koh Samui. Thank you!"
> **- EZ G (5/5/5)**

> "Excellent scooter rental experience. The scooter I received was practically brand new and in perfect condition. The staff were extremely welcoming, friendly, and helpful throughout the whole process.  Unlike many other rental companies, they did not ask to keep my passport, only a 2000 baht deposit, which is very reassuring. Their prices are also very attractive compared to other places.  They even delivered the scooter directly to my hotel and picked it up there at the end of the rental, which made everything very easy and convenient.  Everything was perfect from start to finish. I highly recommend this company if you want a smooth and trustworthy scooter rental experience. 👍"
> **- Stéphane Costa (5/5/5)**

> "Rented a bike for around a week from Expat Rentals. No passport needed just safety deposit. Unfortunately had a slight accident with the bike, told the owner and he was extremely understanding and helpful. He took me to the repair shop so I could see the price in person and pay for the repairs.  Would highly recommend hiring from this place as he was very upfront and honest."
> **- Adam (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/expat-rentals-1.jpg','087 107 6447','69, 172, Tambon Mae Nam, Maenam, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ifui0012q8xdzn158clv','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.626+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.626+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/expat-rentals-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/expat-rentals-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=980053152130105856',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('explorar-adults-only-resort-spa','standard','cmr07iggd009mq8xdmtw4b84k','Explorar - Adults Only Resort & Spa','## Top Reviews
> "I recently had the pleasure of staying at Explorar Kho Samui - Adults Resort and it was nothing short of exceptional. From the moment I arrived, the staff delivered service that was warm, intuitive, and flawlessly professional. Every detail—down to the personalized welcome and seamless check-in—reflected true five-star hospitality.  The room was immaculate, high floor-to-ceiling windows offered breathtaking views of the Samui - Thailand.  Dining at the hotel was an experience in itself. The cuisine was artfully presented and absolutely exquisite, showcasing both local flavors and refined international technique.  What truly sets this hotel apart is its unwavering commitment to excellence. The atmosphere is elegant yet calming, and every interaction feels genuine. I left feeling refreshed and valued. . An outstanding stay in every possible way."
> **- Sudha Jani (5/5/5)**

> "We had a wonderful stay at Explorar Koh Samui. The resort is beautiful, the pool area is fantastic, and the location is excellent. Everything you need is within easy reach, while the resort itself remains peaceful and relaxing.  The rooms were modern, clean, comfortable, and exactly what we were looking for. What truly sets this hotel apart is the staff and the overall guest experience. Everyone was friendly, professional, and genuinely willing to help with anything we needed. The food deserves special recognition. Breakfast was excellent, and dinner was an experience on its own. We follow a mostly vegan diet, and the kitchen was very accommodating, preparing vegan versions of several dishes for us. This level of care made us feel truly welcome. We also appreciated the personal approach when arranging our reservation directly with the hotel. Booking through their website came with additional benefits, and the team was responsive, flexible, and very guest-oriented throughout the process.  The best compliment we can give is that immediately after our stay, we booked another one-week stay for Christmas. That says everything about how much we enjoyed our experience here.  It is clear that the management genuinely cares about its guests. Highly recommended for anyone looking for a stylish adults-only resort with excellent service, outstanding food, and a relaxing atmosphere."
> **- Lukas (5/5/5)**

> "Rum Tasting Class at Explorar! Joey was amazing! He explained everything about the Koh Samui rums and guided us through the cocktail-making experience so well. He was informative, funny, polite, and always smiling, which made the whole experience even more enjoyable. Really appreciated the effort and energy he brought — highly recommend doing this with Joey at Explorar Resort!  The resort itself is amazing with great view, lovely pool & beach & amazing interior. Quiet & peaceful must visit if you are looking for a relaxed vacation. Also the staff is soo helpful and polite. Really felt good at heart."
> **- Shaveta Tolani (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/explorar-adults-only-resort-spa-1.jpg','077 953 035','44 133, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.explorarhotels.com/koh-samui/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.629+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.629+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/explorar-adults-only-resort-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/explorar-adults-only-resort-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2741145501479235286',NULL,NULL);
