> **- Shaveta Tolani (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/explorar-spa-1.jpg','077 953 035','44 133, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.explorarhotels.com/koh-samui/',NULL,'cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.631+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.631+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/explorar-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/explorar-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2741145501479235286',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('eyecare-optical','standard','cmr07iggh009oq8xdcg3ne017','Eyecare Optical','## Top Reviews
> "One of the best opticians I have experienced. I have a very complex eye condition and need to change glasses often and it''s always hard to find the right lenses. Gaysorn was so friendly and professional, extremely helpful."
> **- Elia Stupka (5/5/5)**

> "While on vacation, we went in with my husband’s pair of broken glasses. They were able to repair that pair in 36 hours. In the mean time , my glasses were stepped on. The owner was able to fix (re-mold) my frame in minutes. The service was so efficient that we purchased an additional pair of new prescription sunglasses which ready in a few hours. The owner was very friendly, personable and helpful. We would absolutely go back the next time we visit Koh Samui."
> **- Jennifer (5/5/5)**

> "Came here with my partner a few months ago for eye examinations. The technology used was very modern and the service was professional and friendly. Our new glasses suit us perfectly. We would highly recommend this optician and will definitely come back for future examinations."
> **- Margaret Green (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/eyecare-optical-1.jpg','077 426 972','105 205, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.633+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.633+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/eyecare-optical-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/eyecare-optical-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14453436938878626404',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ezra-beach-club','standard','cmr07iggj009pq8xdlmq66nfk','Ezra Beach Club','## Top Reviews
> "Great hotel with very friendly staff and central location. We upgraded to the villas and got a pool that was shared with other villas but was almost always empty so we had it to ourselves. The small private beach is nice and the hotel restaurant is right on it. Overall great stay"
> **- Maya Gal (5/5/5)**

> "If you are looking for a cool place that looks good in photos, then this is probably the spot for you. The bed was good and the room was nice, but really not much to offer in terms of service quality and amenities. There were a few not so friendly staff, and there seemed to be a new issue every hour we spent (there were also a few great and friendly staff, but the good usually gets hung down by the not so good).  The food and drinks were ok, but weren’t really worth sitting around for."
> **- Zachary Silva (3/5/5)**

> "Pros +location +nice infinity pool (long and narrow) +i really enjoyed opening my sliding glass door am being right on the pool deck.  Cons -music runs until 10pm, my mother in law didn’t love that. -not a lot of surfaces in rooms, I.e. no nightstands, no suitcase stand, so belongings had to be on floor. Good value, I would return."
> **- Pareen “PareenK.” Dholoo (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ezra-beach-club-1.jpg','077 954 094','5, Bangrak Beach T, 1, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'https://advance-booking.com/the-privilege-hotel-ezra-beach-club/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.635+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.635+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ezra-beach-club-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ezra-beach-club-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17562357606833473475',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('factory-world-jewels','standard','cmr07iggl009qq8xd0gscy2zi','Factory World Jewels','## Top Reviews
> "I never seen the shop like this in koh samui even in Asia . The shop is created with Moroccan decorations . All designs of jewels and pure silver 925 are touched my heart. The designs are unique ,original and limited editions. Necklaces, bracelets, ear rings and rings with precious and semi-precious stone come from many countries of the world. Just come only this shop you won’t miss anything. I confirmed!!!"
> **- sirinanth seangthong (5/5/5)**

> "The store is amazing! These are high quality jewelry and limited editions. Impressive necklaces with ancient stones. The store owners are very nice and give detailed information about each piece of jewelry. Strongly recommends!"
> **- אלה שוסטר (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing cool design of jewelry. The shop is chic owned by a Thai-French couple. Recommend to stop by and get a piece or two."
> **- Athip Nilkaeo (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/factory-world-jewels-1.jpg','092 625 7533','49 Thanon Had Lamai, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61565102364192',NULL,'cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.637+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.637+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/factory-world-jewels-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/factory-world-jewels-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12102588881038780243',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('fahthaweeporn-decor-maenam','standard','cmr07iggn009rq8xd3ezg7s4h','Fahthaweeporn Decor','## Top Reviews
> "They have a lot of tiles and bathroom fittings but this is all a facade. Actually this store is just a showroom for many things. Most things needs to be ordered, as most are not in stock. Furthermore, all the orders take at least 2 weeks, some up to a month. Many of the things you want are also out-of-production but still on-display.  The staff cannot be bothered to serve the customers. They don''t call you either when the stuff you ordered has arrived and I have to check back every so often if the things I ordered have arrived.  I gave up on ordering anything from here and ordered all my building materials and bathroom fittings from Bangkok and Surat Thani instead.  From Bangkok and Surat Thani the delivery only takes one week and they actually have what you need in-stock, and best of all, are willing to serve customers."
> **- Linn “ms-ats-cat” Ts (1/5/5)**

> "best tile, kitchen, bathroom appliance selection and show room on Samui."
> **- Paul McTaggart (5/5/5)**

> "Extensive stock of quality bathroom and toilet fittings as well as top quality tiles and wall covering."
