> **- Timothy M Butler (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/fair-house-weddings-1.jpg','077 429 000','39 ตำบล แม่น้ำ Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.fairhousevillas.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.648+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.648+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/fair-house-weddings-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/fair-house-weddings-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3148003970770869827',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('fairtex-pro-shop','standard','cmr07iggy009wq8xd1toyrl1h','Fairtex Pro Shop','## Top Reviews
> "Nicely kept store with a good range of boxing gloves and clothing for MMA and Muay Thai. Prices are excellent in comparison to where I''m from in the UK.  The woman serving me was helpful and friendly. They had lots of sizes available but could do with a larger range of accessories and other products such as muay thai ointments and such. They also didn''t have the size I wanted in the hoody but I bought another colour as it I love the Fairtex designs!"
> **- Rebecca l (4/5/5)**

> "Staff were 10/10 extremely knowledgeable and helpful surrounding questions about product and history. I had a great customer service experience at the store with the shop Lady. Very well kept store, clean and presented nicely. Items were priced at a fair price. Overall great experience and would recommend to anyone looking to buy gear with staff who have extensive knowledge."
> **- Shae D (5/5/5)**

> "Good staff, good advice, clean shop, many products to choose from."
> **- De Ne (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/fairtex-pro-shop-1.jpg','084 324 3882','Chumchon Chaweng Yai Soi 4 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.fairtex.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.650+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.650+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/fairtex-pro-shop-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/fairtex-pro-shop-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13868503180342455189',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('falafel-factory','standard','cmr07igh0009xq8xdzc0plkty','Falafel Factory','## Top Reviews
> "I decided to try their shawarma after seeing the positive reviews and because it was close to my hotel. Unfortunately, it was absolutely not worth it. It didn’t resemble any Middle Eastern shawarma I’ve ever had — from the bread to the veggies, meat, and sauces, nothing was even close. The taste was terrible, and I ended up throwing it away after just one bite."
> **- Mohamed Aslam (1/5/5)**

> "I was seriously craving some comfort street food, and since I don’t just eat anything, a good kebab wrap came to mind. But where to get it? Of course, from a trusted vendor. And as always.. a hit. Thank you so much — just mmm! 🫶🏼 Great people behind the counter 🙏🏼"
> **- Sonja Nova (5/5/5)**

> "Perfect falafel. I really enjoyed my wrap. I took the small one but it was totally perfect size for me. The ingredients were very fresh and I was pleasantly surprised that this place gets that a good wrap must have a good sauce!!! It is ESSENCE for a wrap to succeed. And this place offered various sauces which tasted really good, not cheap at all. I was pleasantly surprised, considering that the place looks very modest. Would order again and would recommend to others."
> **- Sandra Juhanson (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/falafel-factory-1.jpg','099 859 9035','Soi Green Mango - 195 Moo 2 Chaweng, ตำบล บ่อผุด Koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.facebook.com/falafelfactorysamui','["Monday: 12:00 PM – 5:00 AM","Tuesday: 12:00 PM – 5:00 AM","Wednesday: 12:00 PM – 5:00 AM","Thursday: 12:00 PM – 5:00 AM","Friday: 12:00 PM – 5:00 AM","Saturday: 12:00 PM – 5:00 AM","Sunday: 12:00 PM – 5:00 AM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.652+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.652+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/falafel-factory-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/falafel-factory-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16919341847114026613',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('fi-greek-restaurant-deli','standard','cmr07igh2009yq8xda2ioe4xr','Fi Greek Restaurant & Deli','## Top Reviews
> "I had a really great experience here! For being in Thailand, the food tastes surprisingly authentic Greek – very fresh, flavorful, and simply delicious. The portions are quite big, so you definitely leave the restaurant full and satisfied. Prices are a little higher but considering it’s a specialty cuisine, it’s absolutely fair and worth it.  The staff is very kind and welcoming, which makes the whole experience even better. The menu is clear and easy to understand, so ordering is simple  The only small downside is the atmosphere. It’s located on the busy main road. The place inside feels a bit empty and not really decorated with much detail. It comes across cold and plain. However, for me this wasn’t a big deal because the food itself was excellent and that’s what truly matters.  Highly recommended if you are craving authentic Greek food in Thailand!"
> **- Simon (5/5/5)**

> "Delicious food, excellent service and friendly people. Myself and my family eating often in this restaurant, in the center of koh Samui. Lamb oven, tzatziki, feta oven, pita bread, greek salad some of our favourite. They are makers of greek yogurt as well! This is the best yogurt I ever have. Thank you Fi Greek! See you on Friday!"
> **- Gle Gle (5/5/5)**

> "We went here for dinner with kids and parents. Cafe looks very simple; food is so so, portions small, very small for the price. We ordered 4 mains and 4 starters, and we were still hungry. In the end we ordered one more starter shrimps and this was the only good sized plate. Ipita bread not cooked well, when I informed waiter about it he just said, that it is a recipe. We are international family: Russian, Turkish and Greek and we never try such pita bread. There is no manager, just burmese staff working, so, don’t expect much from this place."
> **- Ekaterina Artigas (2/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/fi-greek-restaurant-deli-1.jpg','098 745 6809','125/9-10 Moo 1, T.Boput Taveeratpakdee Rd, ตำบล บ่อผุด koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.654+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.654+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/fi-greek-restaurant-deli-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/fi-greek-restaurant-deli-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4770174412054581451',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('first-samui-car-rental','standard','cmr07igh4009zq8xdblfxtzog','First Samui Car Rental','## Top Reviews
> "Very good and smooth experience: a few days before arriving at koh Samui, we were looking for a car, a few messages through whatsapp later and meeting was set for delivery of the car at our hotel. Since we were not so used to automatic car we were explained all the basics. Same easy experience for the car return at the airport. Good point is that basic assurance is included so that you can add additionnal assurance in top of it if wanted. Strongly recommanded!! Thank you"
> **- Muriel Grace (5/5/5)**

> "First Car Rental on the island of Samui is one of the finest — if not the very finest — car rental companies offering vehicles across a wide range of classes. The owners are educated, refined, and truly wonderful people, always ready to assist at a moment’s notice. The cars are fully insured, impeccably maintained, and of recent model years, having been operated with the utmost care and professionalism. All necessary insurance coverage is provided with the rental, ensuring complete peace of mind. For added convenience, your vehicle can be delivered directly to the airport and returned there just as easily. The pricing is entirely reasonable and fair. I wholeheartedly recommend that every traveler visiting Samui turn to this company. The owner, Khun Champ, is an absolute pleasure to deal with, and you can always rely on a smooth and agreeable experience in his care."
> **- Dimitry Luskin (5/5/5)**

> "We had a seamless experience with first Samui Car rental. The delivered the car to pier and picked up at the airport departures for the easiest exchange of the vehicle. I would highly recommend using them. The price was also very good. Thank you."
> **- Ashley Chen (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/first-samui-car-rental-1.jpg','093 578 2697','Sanam Bin Road, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifui0012q8xdzn158clv','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.656+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.656+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/first-samui-car-rental-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/first-samui-car-rental-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1294208670852828437',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('fishhouse-restaurant-bar','standard','cmr07igh600a0q8xdqwwqi6h6','FishHouse Restaurant & Bar','## Top Reviews
> "An Unforgettable Dining Experience by the Sea  One of the most memorable parts of dining at Fish House Restaurant—besides the beautiful seaside location and stunning atmosphere—was the exceptional service.  Special thanks to Khun Raven and Khun Apple, whose care and attention truly stood out. Their service was detail-oriented, attentive, professional, warm, and genuinely friendly. They explained the menu clearly, answered every question thoughtfully, and made us feel truly welcomed. Their dedication turned our meal into an unforgettable memory and a wonderful dining experience. The team here truly deserves recognition.  As for the food, we ordered a whole seabass (500 grams), which is perfect for 1–2 people. Guests can choose whether the fish is grilled dry or juicy, and the chef prepared it using a butterfly fillet technique, making it very easy and enjoyable to eat. The fish was fresh and delicious, served with a side of mixed vegetables that complemented it perfectly.  The homemade ice cream was another highlight — rich, well-balanced, and available in several interesting flavors. A lovely touch was the complimentary basket of warm baked bread, which immediately won our hearts.  The restaurant’s atmosphere is beautiful both during the day and in the evening, making it a perfect spot for a relaxed yet refined seaside meal.  Overall, Fish House is a place where great food meets outstanding service. The team truly makes the experience special, and they absolutely deserve all the appreciation for their hard work and passion."
> **- Cinderella Indie (5/5/5)**

> "We booked a table here as we were staying at the Melia hotel just down the beach. I was celebrating my birthday and the staff were so attentive and friendly. The beach setting was beautiful especially around Sunset. The menu had lots of options but we were recommended the steak. We also enjoyed some starters of oysters and seafood. It is very pricy but the quality and taste of the food definitely made up for this. We also got a tour of the hotel afterwards, would recommend."
> **- Kimberly Smith (5/5/5)**

> "I''m from Taiwan. This restaurant is fantastic, with a great atmosphere, beautiful decor, and very comfortable—it has a real resort feel, and the food is delicious. Ms. Pan''s hospitality, in particular, made me feel very comfortable."
> **- Yaochang Kuo (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/fishhouse-restaurant-bar-1.jpg','077 951 999','10/79 Moo 5 Bophut, Choeng Mon Beach, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.2,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.kimptonkitalaysamui.com/koh-samui-restaurants/fish-house-restaurant-and-bar/','["Monday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifsv000nq8xdrwnu123q','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.658+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.658+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/fishhouse-restaurant-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/fishhouse-restaurant-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9475085321580843473',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('flames','standard','cmr07igh800a1q8xdzvt8l9u0','Flames','## Top Reviews
> "We had the most incredible experience and couldn’t recommend this place more highly. We spent the entire day moving between the bar, poolside, and restaurant, and every single moment was made special thanks to the outstanding service. A huge thank you to Mui, Joam, Aton, Chon, Kong, Zix, and Pond, each of them went above and beyond to make sure we were comfortable, relaxed, and taken care of. Their attention to detail, warm personalities, and genuine hospitality did not go unnoticed. Whether it was quick service at the bar, thoughtful check-ins by the pool, or seamless service in the restaurant, everything felt effortless and welcoming. It’s rare to come across a team that is consistently attentive without ever feeling intrusive, but they absolutely nailed that balance. They truly made our day unforgettable. We’ll definitely be back and we’ll be recommending this place to everyone we know!"
> **- Imavi Alwis (5/5/5)**

> "We had a wonderful time at the pop-up bar at the private pier. The atmosphere was absolutely beautiful — a very chill vibe with a stunning sunset view that made the whole experience feel special and relaxing.  The drinks were well-crafted and very enjoyable, perfectly matching the laid-back seaside setting.  Special thanks to Khun Woody, who assisted us with the table arrangement and took great care of us throughout our visit — truly attentive and professional. We would also like to mention Khun Atom, who looked after us so well, assisting with service and serving the drinks with great care and friendliness.  Overall, a great experience with a lovely environment, good drinks, and excellent service. Highly recommended for a relaxed sunset moment by the sea."
> **- Vittawat Boonleang (5/5/5)**

> "Today, I had the pleasure of visiting a pop-up bar at the pier, and the experience was absolutely delightful. Mr. Woody kindly came over to greet us and personally helped select a table with a stunning view, which truly made the evening feel special.  The atmosphere was beautiful and relaxing, especially during sunset—perfect for unwinding and enjoying the moment. The drinks were refreshing and well-presented, adding to the overall charm of the setting.  I was also very impressed with the trainee staff. They were friendly, attentive, and always smiling, providing excellent service throughout the evening. Their positive attitude really enhanced the experience.  Overall, it was a memorable evening with great vibes, lovely service, and an amazing view. Highly recommended for anyone looking for a special and relaxing spot to enjoy a drink. 🍹✨"
> **- Vasunan (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/flames-1.jpg','077 429 100','Beach, 295 Moo3, Tambon Taling Ngam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://samui.intercontinental.com/flames','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 2:30 PM, 6:00 – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 2:30 PM, 6:00 – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 2:30 PM, 6:00 – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 2:30 PM, 6:00 – 11:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 2:30 PM, 6:00 – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 2:30 PM, 6:00 – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 2:30 PM, 6:00 – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ift8000pq8xd7yujz20i','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.660+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.660+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/flames-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/flames-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13507616809785682323',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('flavors-of-india','standard','cmr07ighb00a2q8xdrdjk0obs','Flavors Of India','## Top Reviews
> "🩷🩷🩷 🇮🇳Truly Indian Food With An Incredible View!  Such a beautiful place… you just sit, look at the view and don’t want to leave.  Food is really good. Aloo kulcha is so soft, ghobi paratha is amazing. Dhani kebab — never seen it anywhere else on the island, must try. Kadai paneer is super comforting.🍲  And the staff… so kind, so warm, really nice people.  Just a very nice place 💛"
> **- Elvira (5/5/5)**

> "Good place, great location! Came here twice and hands down the best dal tadka on the island. Their veg menu is more authentic than non-veg. The chicken almost all tasted same - sweet and generic. Order veg while you’re here. The paneer was also extremely fresh but cooked in a very canned purée with liquidy gravy. Can be visited for the location, though food is a hit or miss."
> **- Anshuman Singh (4/5/5)**

> "It is a beautiful location with a scenic view to the sea and overlooking Koh Phangan Island however the food is average. There are better Indian Food Restaurants on Koh Samui. You can try the food here once if you are traveling to this Island however if you stay on the Island and wants to have Indian food sometimes than this would not be the place you would want to come again and again."
> **- Ādi (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/flavors-of-india-1.jpg','064 024 1597','4169, Flavors Of India - Beachfront, Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'http://theflavorsofindia.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifs1000cq8xdfo2aau32','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.663+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.663+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/flavors-of-india-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/flavors-of-india-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10646927846399547004',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('floss-dental','standard','cmr07ighd00a3q8xdig0lqwhx','Floss Dental','## Top Reviews
> "Highly recommended. I had two teeth removed together with a crown, and honestly, I was very nervous before the procedure. However, everything went much faster and smoother than I expected. The doctor also performed bone smoothing and placed stitches. During the whole process, everything was explained very clearly: what I might feel, what I might hear, and what was happening at each stage. This made a huge difference and helped me feel much calmer. They took X-rays three times to make sure everything was perfectly done, and the X-ray was done right from the dental chair, which was very convenient. The doctor showed and explained everything in detail. I also received clear instructions for healing, aftercare, and the next steps for further treatment. The clinic is clean, cozy, and welcoming, and the staff are incredibly kind, attentive, and supportive. In the end, the price was also very reasonable. This was definitely the best dental experience we have had on Samui, and probably one of the best overall. We have now chosen this clinic as our family dental clinic and will definitely come back for any dental care in the future. Thank you so much to the whole team. I highly recommend this place to everyone 💚"
> **- Лия Шарова (Razmorozzzka) (5/5/5)**

> "The entire Floss-Team are very professional, very friendly and kind. 💜  They booked me in very fast, explained the entire process and have a very professional and clear communication. After my second treatment, my mouth felt completely back to normal. The gentle way of the team and Dr. New helped me overcome my big dentist fear and they never laughed at me, instead helped me throughout the process very calm and friendly. The pricing is absolute fair. Highly recommend his team for their skill and care. 🙏🏼 🙏🏼"
> **- J. C. (5/5/5)**

> "Excellent experience. Dr Poupee and her team are superior. Very efficient, professional and hospitable. Make you feel comfortable from the moment you walk in the door. High quality of dental work. I flew half way around the world for my services and I would do it again! Very happy and satisfied with cleaning, fillings and especially the whitening."
> **- Nicole Lewis (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/floss-dental-1.jpg','096 194 9791','25 240 ม.6, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 11:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ig1d003gq8xdfxkqj28w','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.665+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.665+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/floss-dental-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/floss-dental-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9458175723979909690',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('flow-restaurant','standard','cmr07ighg00a4q8xdpxt2nu28','Flow Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "We really loved this place — honestly had such a great stay ❤️ The hotel is small, quiet, and right by the sea, which was a huge plus for us. We stayed for 9 days and had a really good, relaxing time.  To be honest, we didn’t expect much from a 3-star hotel, but the service was surprisingly great — that was a very nice surprise. The overall atmosphere and staff made it even better.  The food was tasty, and even though breakfast was quite simple, we genuinely enjoyed it — it had everything we needed.  The beach was good too: right in front of the hotel the entry is a bit rocky, but if you walk a little to the right, there’s a much nicer spot to get into the water. The water isn’t super clear because of the sandy/muddy bottom, but there were almost no waves, so it was still really enjoyable to swim.  Since the hotel is small, the level of quiet really depends on the guests. Most of the time it was very peaceful, but on our last day a noisy group arrived, which was a bit annoying — luckily, it was already our last day.  So just a small note for future guests: please be mindful of others and respect the quiet atmosphere — this isn’t a party hotel.  Overall, definitely a place we’d come back to 🌿"
> **- Sofia Maksimova (5/5/5)**

> "The sea view here is absolutely beautiful, with a full panoramic view that feels incredibly relaxing. It’s the perfect place to sit back, unwind, and enjoy the atmosphere. The food is delicious and of great quality. The pasta, in particular, was rich and flavorful, with fresh, well-cooked shrimp. Paired with crispy garlic bread, it was a perfect combination. The drinks were refreshing and easy to enjoy, making them ideal for a laid-back afternoon by the sea. What truly stood out was the service. Special thanks to Khun Korn and the entire team for the warm welcome from the moment we arrived. Everyone was polite, friendly, and attentive, which made the whole dining experience even more enjoyable. This is definitely one of the must-visit spots in Koh Samui, whether for the view, the food, or the overall ambiance. I’ll definitely be coming back next time to enjoy the day pass by the pool and spend more time relaxing here. 🌊✨"
> **- Supaporn Jamlek (5/5/5)**

> "Just wow. I’ve been visiting maenam beach for 10years and always enviously looked into the place!! Anyway fast forward to my first stay there. Beautiful rooms, all backing onto a slick pool. Really good food, happy hour cocktails. The highlight is the infinity pool looking out over the vast blue calm sea. Oh and at night the pool has beautiful sparkling lights in it! Will be back."
> **- Claire England (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/flow-restaurant-1.jpg','077 426 000','49, 35, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'http://theflowsamui.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.668+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.668+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/flow-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/flow-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4638705485493830439',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('flower-paradise-bungalows','standard','cmr07ighi00a5q8xdguhfzj5o','Flower Paradise Bungalows','## Top Reviews
> "Perfect spot, right on the beach!! Nothing better than waking up and walking down to the beach and eating at their restaurant! The rooms are plenty big enough for two people. There were several clotheslines available to use, some inside and some outside. Very quiet area to stay, perfect spot to actually relax. Hot water was iffy, but as long as you limit how long your showers are, it''s not a concern."
> **- rose (5/5/5)**

> "It the worst experience I have ever had in Thailand. Please find a different hotel, stuff cheat on Booking and its clients with wrong photos. Dirty house, old furniture, spiders and tritons inside, their excrements everywhere. It''s awful!! We escaped to another hotel for the same money but much better quality"
> **- Pier (1/5/5)**

> "had the bungalow right at the beachfront. the beach directly in front of the property doesn’t get busy throughout the day and is the perfect place to relax a bit on your own. although the room was a bit run down, the air conditioning and the refrigerator worked really well. the owners were friendly and helpful, both beach bars in front had great music and nice staff."
> **- Ja Na (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/flower-paradise-bungalows-1.jpg','081 978 9123','127, 1, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.670+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.670+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/flower-paradise-bungalows-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/flower-paradise-bungalows-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9064058246984270824',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('flying-arrow-archery-center','standard','cmr07ighk00a6q8xdee2tncmw','Flying Arrow Archery Center','## Top Reviews
> "We had a blast as it''s not something you do every day!! Bows and gear were in good nick and different shooting ranges depending on your skill level & equipment used. We quickly got the hang of it with some tips and tricks from the owner. Would recommend if you are in the area."
> **- Vernon de Widt (5/5/5)**

> "Visited off peak so the outdoor range wasn''t open, but still had fun inside. Had a go at archery and with a cross bow. We were shown what to do by the helpful instructor and left to have fun."
> **- Colleen Simcock (5/5/5)**

> "My wife and I had a great time here learning how to properly shoot a bow and arrow. I also shot the competition cross bow at the 50 meter target. The owner helped me consistently improve my aim during every round. We would definitely go back again when we visit Samui in the future. Thank you!"
> **- Paul Michaels (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/flying-arrow-archery-center-1.jpg','083 045 8209','36/4, ตำบล แม่น้ำ อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.flying-arrow.net/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: Closed","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.672+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.672+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/flying-arrow-archery-center-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/flying-arrow-archery-center-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3406952364319498707',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('food-lab','standard','cmr07ighl00a7q8xdo9aerqgo','Food Lab','## Top Reviews
> "Amazing food and amazing host! My go to dinner place for my samui holiday! The prochetta is a true masterpiece, and the past gravy is so flavourful and creamy that  I could literally lick the plate until it shine!"
> **- Alexander (5/5/5)**

> "Food Lab is an Italian restaurant in Lamai, Koh Samui, specialized in authentic Roman cuisine and isbest known for its signature Porchetta (traditional Italian roast pork) and handmade pasta. Other favorites include Black Truffle Ravioli, Gnocchi, and authentic Pizza Alla Romana made with 48-hour aged dough for easy digestion. It us best described as a small, cozy, and casual "
> **- Kirk MacDonald (4/5/5)**

> "Lived on the island almost 2 years now, I’ve tried pizza in so many places and the dough is always off. This is the only spot with the perfect dough and crust. Roman style pizza and absolutely delicious. So it has my vote as best pizza in Samui. And I know my pizza, as a chef myself but also growing up outside of NYC. If you like it cheesy ask for extra cheese. Coming back soon for more pizza and to try their homemade pasta!! This restaurant deserves to be packed for their food and great service!!"
> **- Sasha Jarufe (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/food-lab-1.jpg','098 726 6385','139, 10, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/samuilab/','["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 5:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 5:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 5:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 5:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 5:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 5:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.673+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.673+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/food-lab-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/food-lab-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11892603426824906027',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('food-mafia','standard','cmr07ighn00a8q8xdivzbkiyi','Food Mafia','## Top Reviews
> "We enjoyed a nice Sunday brunch with various meats, cheeses & breads available in addition to eggs, beans, veggies, jams & other items. Service is excellent. We''ve since picked up our Thanksgiving ham, some buns, bagels, pretzels & salami. Pretty sure this will be our go to shop now. Impressive."
> **- Gerry Steiert (5/5/5)**

> "+ Tasty burger set with juicy meat. - Very uncomfortable tables and chairs 🪑 😵‍💫 Please, improve furniture  🙏🏼"
> **- Black Bird (3/5/5)**

> "Certainly not German standards of hygiene or quality. We ordered a baguette and a Ciabatta filled with some scrambled eggs, they arrived first complete with hair, then we got two baguette as the bakery! Didn''t have the ciabatta that''s on their breakfast menu! The baguettes were very chewy and seemed like old bread, my wife didnt like their special sauce as it had a strong flavour of mustard. She ordered a simple roll which came to the table extremely hot and once cooled it was so tough to eat, it had been microwaved to warm it!! Really disappointed with the quality here, when paying I was asked if everything was ok and I checked why the rolls had been microwaved, the guy seemed uninterested but confirmed it was microwaved , this shows they don''t care about quality or customer satisfaction. So many better places to have breakfast don''t waste your time here. I did tell the cashier I was unhappy but he wasn''t interested, the response below is nonsense"
> **- Jon (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/food-mafia-1.jpg','080 579 0585','Food Mafia 203, next to the, ตำบล แม่น้ำ อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.1,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 7:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 4:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.675+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.675+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/food-mafia-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/food-mafia-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4522794073956149693',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('forest-whisper-cafe','standard','cmr07ighq00a9q8xdtgwtjl2q','Forest Whisper Cafe','## Top Reviews
> "Extremely friendly and welcoming staff — truly some of the nicest people. I loved every part of the premises; it’s beautiful, peaceful, and very well designed in nature. The massage itself was very good and relaxing.  We booked a couple’s massage and also experienced the caves, natural spring areas, and body scrub treatments, which made the whole experience feel very complete and unique.  The only area I feel could be improved is hygiene standards in certain parts of the facility, which would make the experience perfect.  Overall, a wonderful experience and I would still recommend it for anyone looking for a relaxing spa day in nature."
> **- Ghada Mallah (4/5/5)**

> "We visited Tamarind Springs Samui as a wedding gift from our friends and chose the “Stoned on Samui” package — and it was absolutely worth it.  From start to finish, the experience was incredibly relaxing and thoughtfully curated. We really appreciated the no-phone policy, which allowed us to fully disconnect and enjoy the peaceful surroundings. It made the whole spa day feel even more special and immersive.  The treatments were amazing, and everything was beautifully set in nature. One thing to keep in mind is that there’s quite a bit of walking and stairs involved, so you do need to be reasonably fit. But honestly, it just adds to the charm of the place.  We loved every moment and would highly recommend it for a special occasion or a proper treat!"
> **- Zaza Meerveld (5/5/5)**

> "We had an absolutely wonderful experience at Tamarind Springs. We spent a beautiful afternoon immersed in nature, following a peaceful path through the forest that truly felt magical. The entire setting is unique, serene, and incredibly well integrated into the natural surroundings.  The spa itself is simply amazing and unlike anything we had ever seen before. The sauna carved directly into the rocks is something truly special – a one-of-a-kind experience that you won’t easily find elsewhere. It feels authentic, original, and perfectly in harmony with the forest. Without a doubt, the experience is worth every penny and absolutely justifies the price.  The massage was exceptional: deeply relaxing, professional, and perfectly executed. On top of that, all the staff were incredibly kind, welcoming, and attentive in every aspect, making us feel comfortable and well taken care of from start to finish.  This is not just a spa, but a complete experience in nature. Highly recommended for anyone looking for something unique, relaxing, and truly memorable.  Renato"
> **- Renato Rottmann (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/forest-whisper-cafe-1.jpg','085 926 4626','265, 1, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.tamarindsprings.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.678+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.678+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/forest-whisper-cafe-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/forest-whisper-cafe-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=363410939101283574',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('four-black-pizzeria-coffee-house','standard','cmr07ighs00aaq8xd5ut62s6v','Four Black Pizzeria & Coffee House','## Top Reviews
> "Best pizza I''ve had during my 3 weeks in Samui. Prices are also very fair for what you get. Paid around 330 baht for a pizza and an ice tea"
> **- Frederik Kiel (5/5/5)**

> "This is a really good italien restaurant. The Bruschetta with tomato and mozzarella was delicious and not too crunchy. The pizza was handmade and tasted amazing. The dough was perfect, not too crunchy and not too soft. I recommend going here if u want to eat italien food in thailand. The price was also really fair (~300 per pizza). The espresso was decent."
> **- Simon (5/5/5)**

> "Out of dosen pizzerias I visited on Samui this one is by far my favourite. Pizza is a matter of personal taste of course, but I was pleasantly surprised here: very tasty soft dough, stretchy cheese, top-notch ingredients. I really enjoyed every bite. Don''t bother with the delivery: go there and eat it straight from the oven. If you going to be dissapointed with this one, hell, I don''t know what kind of heavenly pizza you''ve been eating all your life, but I want a slice!"
> **- Andreas Flanco (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/four-black-pizzeria-coffee-house-1.jpg','061 917 8589','3 ตําบล บ่อผุด 160 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 4:30 – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 4:30 – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 4:30 – 11:00 PM","Friday: 4:30 – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 4:30 – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 4:30 – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.680+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.680+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/four-black-pizzeria-coffee-house-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/four-black-pizzeria-coffee-house-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3100195906120389715',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('four-seasons-resort','standard','cmr07ighw00abq8xdpcb1a9bf','Four Seasons Resort','## Top Reviews
> "Amazing stay, came here for a wedding and it was memorable  experience. The villas are spacious and beautiful, each with a private pool overlooking the resort and ocean. Food was top notch, and the infinity pool is incredible... I could’ve stayed there all day (and basically did).  The setting is stunning: secluded, peaceful, and a great escape from everything. The team was also excellent throughout, easy to communicate with and very attentive.  A couple minor things to note. It’s fairly remote, so getting off property takes some effort if you’re looking to explore. Because the resort is on a steep incline, you may need to request a cart to get around. Also, it is a jungle environment, bugs are part of the deal (I was fine, but my wife got a few bites).  The one real design gripe was the bathroom in our villa. Despite the size of the villa was overall, the toilet area felt oddly cramped with limited legroom, which seemed like a strange use of space."
> **- Luong H (5/5/5)**

> "The most beautiful resort in Koh Samui. So much care and effort goes into maintaining this resort and it really shows in every detail. The food was incredible and the staff truly could not do more to help.  The beach is stunning and the pool is large and the perfect temperature, such a dreamy place to spend the day. Every detail in the rooms is thoughtfully designed, super clean, and the views are beautiful. It is the ultimate luxury and comfort, exactly what you would expect from Four Seasons.  So happy I got to enjoy my White Lotus moment here."
> **- Alleah Facey (5/5/5)**

> "We traveled across the globe to stay here, expecting something special, but what we experienced was truly extraordinary. From the moment we arrived and were surprised with a villa upgrade and beautiful “Happy Anniversary” decorations, we knew this stay would be different. What we did not expect was how deeply personal and heartfelt the hospitality would feel.  For seven straight days, not a single thing went wrong. Every department, housekeeping, concierge, guest experience, pool team, dining, transportation, operated seamlessly. The service was intuitive and effortless. The team learned our preferences quickly and personalized our stay in ways that felt thoughtful rather than scripted.  The attention to detail was remarkable. When they noticed the books we were reading, they left us leather bookmarks. When they saw our tangle of electronic cords, they surprised us with leather cord organizers. On occasion, they even folded our clothes. After learning we were inspired to visit because of The White Lotus, Gift and Bee offered us a private tour of filming locations around the resort, such a thoughtful and fun surprise. Staying a full week allowed us to truly immerse ourselves in many of the resort’s special experiences, a Lunar New Year beach dinner with a fire show, private villa dinners, cultural activities, and a couples’ photoshoot. They even adjusted certain activities around our schedule so we would not miss out, a level of flexibility that meant so much.  Dining was exceptional throughout the stay...Michelin level at each restaurant. Chef Deepak went out of his way to create special Indian breakfast dishes after learning about my love for the cuisine, and spent time connecting with us at our table. That personal touch elevated an already world class experience.  One evening, I injured my toe at the pool, and within moments the entire team rushed to help. They stopped the bleeding, cared for me attentively, and even kept us laughing during the process. I did not feel like a guest, I felt like family.  I have never teared up leaving a hotel until this one. Saying goodbye truly felt like leaving home. The property is breathtaking, but it is the people who make it unforgettable.  Without question, this was the best experience of all our travels. The journey to get here was long, but we would do it again in a heartbeat. The entire team deserves the highest recognition possible for the flawless, heartfelt hospitality they deliver every single day.  P.S. Thank you to Juree for the beautiful hand painted card of us paddle boarding."
> **- Sebastian Sallot (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/four-seasons-resort-1.jpg','077 243 000','219, Tambon Mae Nam, Angthong, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.fourseasons.com/kohsamui/?utm_source=google&utm_medium=organicsearch&utm_campaign=tor-koh-hre-mid-seo-na&utm_content=na-na&utm_term=na',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifxh0027q8xde6xqk8o6','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.684+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.684+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/four-seasons-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/four-seasons-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4637702411135469681',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('four-seasons-spa-wellness','standard','cmr07ighz00acq8xdk3gnb6ad','Four Seasons Spa & Wellness','## Top Reviews
> "5 hidden private rooms in the natural hill makes this place unique from others. Walking path initially creates some relaxation , professional massages & outdoor bath elevate the place to be upscale with high price. No desserts or small bites after massage."
> **- Sumol (5/5/5)**

> "Wow. Wow. Wow. Spent the day here on my birthday and couldn’t be happier the views were incredible and the spa experience was the best massage and scrub we had in about 3 weeks of massages daily in Thailand. The homemade coconut jasmine scrub is to die for. I asked for the recipe. Wow thank you for making my birthday so special. The coconut bath after is a delight with a gorgeous view!"
> **- Dyana Camera (5/5/5)**

> "Thanks Wawa and Karn for the massage :) was great!"
> **- Alisa Matjuka (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/four-seasons-spa-wellness-1.jpg','077 243 000','219, Tambon Mae Nam, Angthong, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.fourseasons.com/kohsamui/spa/?utm_source=google&utm_medium=organicsearch&utm_campaign=tor-koh-spa-mid-seo-na&utm_content=na-na&utm_term=na','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifxh0027q8xde6xqk8o6','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.687+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.687+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/four-seasons-spa-wellness-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/four-seasons-spa-wellness-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12456727667928610708',NULL,NULL);
