> **- Sebastian Sallot (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/four-seasons-weddings-1.jpg','077 243 000','219, Tambon Mae Nam, Angthong, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.fourseasons.com/kohsamui/?utm_source=google&utm_medium=organicsearch&utm_campaign=tor-koh-hre-mid-seo-na&utm_content=na-na&utm_term=na',NULL,'cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifxh0027q8xde6xqk8o6','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.689+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.689+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/four-seasons-weddings-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/four-seasons-weddings-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4637702411135469681',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('foxtrot-bistro','standard','cmr07igi200aeq8xdc7tv0db8','Foxtrot Bistro','## Top Reviews
> "I absolutely fell in love with the food at Foxtrot Samui. Every dish I’ve tried has been consistently delicious, with great attention to flavor and presentation. It’s one of those places that really leaves a lasting impression.  I’ve actually gone back three times already—across both last year and this year—which says a lot about how much I enjoy it. Each visit has been just as good as the last, and I always find myself wanting to return for more.  If you’re looking for a restaurant in Samui that delivers both quality and a memorable dining experience, Foxtrot Samui is definitely worth visiting."
> **- Nattaly M. (5/5/5)**

> "The food was average, with a very international flavor profile. It’s better suited for those who prefer milder tastes rather than strong or bold flavors.  The service, however, was spectacular. The staff handled everything beautifully, especially how professionally they managed the sudden rain.  The atmosphere was absolutely breathtaking and truly elevated the overall experience.  The truffle dish stood out and was genuinely good."
> **- Monica’s Taste (4/5/5)**

> "Best restaurant on the island, hands down. From the moment you walk in, Martin, Beth and the whole team make you feel genuinely welcome.  The food is absolutely outstanding. Every dish is packed with flavour and clearly made with real care and quality ingredients. The atmosphere is perfect with incredible views of Bangrak bay.  We''ve eaten out a lot during our time here and nothing else comes close. If you''re visiting the island, do yourself a favour and make Foxtrot your first stop. You won''t regret it. ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐"
> **- J M (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/foxtrot-bistro-1.jpg','099 345 7696','16/13, เทศบาลนครเกาะสมุย อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://foxtrotsamui.com/','["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.690+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.690+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/foxtrot-bistro-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/foxtrot-bistro-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=953056323322850697',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('frank-legal-tax','standard','cmr07igi400afq8xdmudjbcfp','Frank Legal & Tax','## Top Reviews
> "Frank Legal & Tax is a highly regarded professional firm known for consistently delivering exceptional service. With a strong commitment to punctuality and efficiency, the team at Frank Legal & Tax ensures that all tasks are completed promptly and accurately. The staff members are not only polite and courteous but also possess a keen eye for detail, allowing them to handle complex legal and tax matters with ease.  At Frank Legal & Tax, the importance of professionalism in their interactions with clients is well understood. The team strives to maintain a high level of integrity and ethics in all aspects of their work, ensuring that clients receive the best possible service. The team is dedicated to providing personalized attention to each client, taking the time to understand their unique needs and goals.  One of Frank Legal & Tax''s key strengths lies in their ability to navigate the intricacies of the legal and tax landscape. The astute professionals stay up-to-date with the latest regulations and changes in the industry, allowing them to provide accurate and reliable advice to clients. The team takes pride in their ability to find innovative solutions to complex problems, ensuring that clients receive the best possible outcome.  In addition to their expertise, Frank Legal & Tax believes in maintaining a warm and welcoming environment for clients. The staff members are not only knowledgeable but also gracious and outgoing, ensuring that every interaction is pleasant and productive. Recognizing that dealing with legal and tax matters can be stressful, the team strives to create an atmosphere of trust and support.  In conclusion, Frank Legal & Tax is a professional firm that excels in providing exceptional service. With their punctuality, politeness, and astute professionals, they are able to deliver outstanding results for their clients. Frank Legal & Tax takes pride in their ability to navigate the complexities of the legal and tax landscape while maintaining a warm and welcoming environment. Clients can trust them to handle their legal and tax matters with the utmost professionalism and care."
> **- Gary Sakuma (5/5/5)**

> "I highly recommend Frank legal and tax services.  Their expertise is outstanding, providing quick and effective solutions to complex issues. They combine deep knowledge with exceptional client care, addressing every concern with precision and responsiveness. Working with Mr G and his team made the process smooth and stress-free.  If you need reliable legal or tax assistance, they are the go-to professionalism"
> **- Pm (5/5/5)**

> "Property can be a complicated issue for foreigners in Thailand as the rules may be quite different to where we come from. More so in places like Samui. Fortunately Frank Legal and Tax are very knowledgeable and able to deal with whatever is required such as registered leases, purchase/sale of a house (a house can be fully owned by a foreigner and ownership can be separate from ownership of the land), and the daunting myriad of paperwork needed for anything. Very efficient and thorough work with regular updates of progress. Having a good firm in Samui with local knowledge and contacts has made things a lot easier than having to use a Bangkok firm."
> **- Ismail Nasir (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/frank-legal-tax-1.jpg','061 469 7000','1/40 Moo 6, ตำบล บ่อผุด Koh Samui, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.samuilegaltax.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifu0000zq8xdvll5tv7z','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.692+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.692+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/frank-legal-tax-1.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16495378886471261924',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('freezy-cow','standard','cmr07igi700agq8xdga1j3tjm','Freezy Cow','## Top Reviews
> "The Ice Cream was indeed good, however for Foodies like me who transcended to strong flavours is limited by choice, they only have 2 options with pronounced flavours, Rum & Raisin and Snickers; the rest are actually light in flavour. Another likeability bonus is they give you sprinkles and Hershey syrups to enhanced the experience make the price now worth it. Service is good here. Toilet is clean. There limited parking (car & bike) here."
> **- Jimmy Chan (4/5/5)**

> "Iced Cappucino was really great, Chocolate Ice cream was okay. I would say 3 out of 5 but beautiful made. The location was clean and the service girls friendly. Would recommend for relaxing. Prices are a bit high for Thai standards."
> **- Ka Hiza (4/5/5)**

> "Friendly and polite service. Easy parking good prices. Nice relaxed vibe inside and some delcious looking snakcs and treats. Didn''t get any food but got coffees and cakes..people eating food outside..looked great. Lovely staff and would definitely return"
> **- Paul (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/freezy-cow-1.jpg','091 026 3576','108, 11 Moo1 (Ring Road, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.695+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.695+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/freezy-cow-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/freezy-cow-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15912582423619849114',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('friday-cutz-barber-shop','standard','cmr07igia00ahq8xdzvlhbm1b','Friday CUTZ Barber Shop','## Top Reviews
> "An absolutely exceptional experience—this place is truly on another level. I had the best shave and beard trim of my life, carried out with unmatched professionalism and flair. The attention to detail and sheer finesse were nothing short of extraordinary. Without a doubt, I’ll be returning, and this spot is now firmly marked as a go-to destination for outstanding, masterful grooming."
> **- Ruben Thomas (5/5/5)**

> "I just got a haircut at this barbershop, and I couldn’t be happier with the result. My barber, Fon, did an outstanding job. She is a true professional — attentive to detail, precise, and very confident in her craft. The haircut turned out exactly how I wanted: clean, stylish, and perfectly shaped. I highly recommend Fon to anyone looking for a top-quality haircut. Excellent service and truly professional skills!"
> **- Georgy G (5/5/5)**

> "Best one in all Thailand I like the way he work and the final results Very cheap - less the 10$"
> **- eitan shifffer (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/friday-cutz-barber-shop-1.jpg','062 524 9951','Friday CUTZ Barber Shop 100 45 หมู่ 1 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: Closed","Wednesday: 9:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 9:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 9:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 9:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 9:30 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.698+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.698+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/friday-cutz-barber-shop-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/friday-cutz-barber-shop-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9936180243395031398',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('frontline-beach-samui','standard','cmr07igic00aiq8xdsqo0f2q8','Frontline Beach Samui','## Top Reviews
> "Beautiful pristine and uncrowded beach to watch sunset. Shallow beach, nice for walking may be not for swimming. Towards the northern end of the beach is a small drinks stall under a big tree. The owner of the stall is friendly. He sells very chilled local beer and soft drinks."
> **- glyn sim (5/5/5)**

> "Great place to watch the sunset. You can swim in the morning until early afternoon but then the tide goes out. Park just off the road on the mud and grass near a big tree. Rope swim and hammock to chill on the beach. Some locals are there with cold beverages. 20 baht water 40 baht coke. They also had Chang beers and coconuts. Great people great place."
> **- Edward H (5/5/5)**

> "Perfect private (1EUR fee) beach for sunset chasing with a lovely staff!"
> **- Zrinka Antolović (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/frontline-beach-samui-1.jpg','+66994031426','Beach front, Unnamed Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.1,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.700+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.700+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/frontline-beach-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/frontline-beach-samui-2.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/frontline-beach-samui-3.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/frontline-beach-samui-4.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=18115884591521810020',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('fun-house-samui','standard','cmr07igie00ajq8xdwo7a6fdd','Fun House Samui','## Top Reviews
> "Great indoor playpark and restaurant close to big C. Park is nicely designed with slides and trampolines. Staff is supportive and taking care about safety of your kids. Restaurant has wide menu with drinks and snacks. Possibility to organize bday parties in the facility. All is good."
> **- Marek Horyl (5/5/5)**

> "very good playground for various ages. mine was 16 months old and had a lot of fun. prices are very reasonable and the staff is very friendly"
> **- aurelien mery (5/5/5)**

> "Great place, took my young girls for a couple of hours whilst I had an iced coffee and some snacks. Very reasonably priced at 100baht an hour per child. Staff are very friendly and seem engaged with the kids - playing with them and helping them with the slide, pushing them on the little trikes, etc. The iced latte was well presented and tasted good, as did the sliced green mango with Thai sauce, and the side of fries I got. Toilets didn’t have any toilet paper which could be improved and I didn’t see any water freely available for the kids but I may not have looked hard enough. Overall a nice break for kids and adults to do their own thing for a while."
> **- Stephen B (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/fun-house-samui-1.jpg','098 010 9432','Soi Bandon Hospital Road, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 10:30 AM – 8:30 PM","Tuesday: 10:30 AM – 8:30 PM","Wednesday: 10:30 AM – 8:30 PM","Thursday: 10:30 AM – 8:30 PM","Friday: 10:30 AM – 8:30 PM","Saturday: 10:30 AM – 8:30 PM","Sunday: 10:30 AM – 8:30 PM"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.702+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.702+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/fun-house-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/fun-house-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9611340670010229241',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('galanga','standard','cmr07igig00akq8xdqrt791fu','Galanga','## Top Reviews
> "The food was absolutely delicious and very high quality. It had been a long time since I’d had chicken that tender in Koh Samui honestly. I was a bit unsure about the lasagna because I thought it might not be their specialty, but in the end it was excellent too. The staff were also very attentive and professional. 10/10 thank u"
> **- M C (5/5/5)**

> "Great atmosphere with second-level seating that’s perfect for a bit of elevated people-watching. The space itself is beautiful — a thoughtful mix of old Thailand references woven into the interior design. It feels intentional, warm, and visually rich without being overdone.  The staff truly stands out here. Attentive, kind, and consistent with every interaction. You feel taken care of from the moment you walk in, and that kind of service makes a difference.  The starters were okay — perfectly fine, just missing that extra depth of flavor you hope for. The main dish landed similarly. Not bad by any means, just a bit underwhelming in terms of boldness and complexity. The presentation, though? Absolutely stunning. Every plate looked like it belonged in a feature spread.  There’s a decent wine selection and solid drink menu to round things out.  At the end of the day, the staff and location carry this place. If you walk in knowing the food is good but not groundbreaking, you’ll probably have a next-level experience simply because the ambiance and service elevate everything else.  A beautiful spot to spend an evening — just hoping for a bit more punch in the flavor next time."
> **- Ryan McGowan (3/5/5)**

> "We had a wonderful time at Galanga. The food is traditional Thai and the menu offers a lot of variety and options. The food was absolutely outstanding. The presentation and quality of the food was top notch, the drinks were fantastic, and the atmosphere of the restaurant was very chic and well done. The staff service was incredible and very friendly. We will absolutely be coming back here."
> **- Brent Kleinhenz (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/galanga-1.jpg','077 963 213','168/4 Moo2 Chaweng Beach Chaweng Tambol Bophut Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.galangasamui.com/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 11:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.704+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.704+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/galanga-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/galanga-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7862228525343923867',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('garden-of-eden','standard','cmr07igii00alq8xd2fg6baea','Garden Of Eden','## Top Reviews
> "Amazing place for private events. We chose this place for a private event for 50 people and couldn''t be more happy. The food, the location, the beautifully maintained venue but above all, the team that will go above and beyond to host their guests with a lot of care and make them feel at home  ❤️ Really can''t praise enough ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ Thank you 🙏"
> **- Shoresh (5/5/5)**

> "The great and largest venue for wedding in Koh Samui located 5 minutes to the beach with free shuttle services. The venue capacity up to 250 guests with in-house creative menus and drinks."
> **- Watcharapong Saikaew (5/5/5)**

> "The Garden of Eden in Samui is a dreamy wedding venue. With its lush landscapes and tranquil setting, it creates a picturesque backdrop for a memorable event. A truly top-notch choice for anyone planning a wedding in Samui. Highly recommended!"
> **- Zaza Meerveld (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/garden-of-eden-1.jpg','089 725 8010','13/2 Tambon Taling Ngam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.gardenofedenthailand.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ift8000pq8xd7yujz20i','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.706+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.706+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/garden-of-eden-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/garden-of-eden-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2047347239864754144',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('garnish','standard','cmr07igik00amq8xd2b5ilgk3','Garnish','## Top Reviews
> "first time here and it became my fav bar in samui :) The presentation of drinks has an interesting menu There is a clear price so easy to decide what you will order 💜  About staff there should get good good good review! The bartender is girl and she is so talented mak also the writer is another girl that can speak English and take care of us so well. I will definitely come back here for sunset or dinner again for sure"
> **- Honey bunny (5/5/5)**

> "Had an awesome experience at this place. Cocktails that uses local Thai ingredients such as Ants, Fish Sauce, Squid are the next level. Great job ! Delicious cocktails thats small batched so the menu changes often. Highly recommend the Chicken Consomme Cocktail and the Mango Sticky Rice Cocktail ! And did I tell you that the staff are super friendly and welcoming ??"
> **- JW INC (5/5/5)**

> "Pok was an amazing host and owner. He went over the drinks in great detail and let us know that nothing here is ordinary but rather has a creative twist which makes this bar, more of an experimental cocktail bar. We were also offered a complimentary shot, which made the birthday celebration even more special. He also provided us with a complimentary snack (bbq corn snacks) and they were phenomenal as well. We had the Slow Espresso Martini, Bee''s Knees, and shared the Miami Vice as a dessert cocktail. Overall, would highly recommend Garnish Bar."
> **- andrew white (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/garnish-1.jpg','083 150 0994','50 2nd floor, Moo1, Fisherman Village, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.garnishsamui.com/','["Monday: 4:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 4:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 4:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 4:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 4:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 4:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 4:00 PM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.708+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.708+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/garnish-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/garnish-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3747049963454963871',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('garrya-tongsai-bay','standard','cmr07igio00anq8xdaj7v2ul3','Garrya Tongsai Bay','## Top Reviews
> "If you are looking for a great experience during your holiday stay in Koh Samui, then this is the property to choose. From the moment you arrive, you feel genuinely welcomed at every step. The entire team—from the front office and restaurant staff to the buggy drivers and security personnel—goes out of their way to make your stay comfortable and memorable.  A special mention to the wonderful lady at the fruit salad counter every morning (fondly known as the “Chop Chop Lady”). She brought a smile to our faces every day and made breakfast a delightful experience.  The person who truly makes you feel special, valued, and treated like royalty is “KOOKIK”. Garrya is privileged to have a team member like her. Her warmth, professionalism, and genuine care for guests are exceptional and left a lasting impression on us.  We will definitely come back to Koh Samui, and this property will be one of the main reasons for our return.  Thank you to the entire team for making our stay so memorable. Highly recommended!"
> **- vikram sharma (5/5/5)**

> "We stayed here with our son and daughter in law for 10 days. Our stay at Garrya Tongsai Bay Samui was nothing short of exceptional. From the moment we arrived, we were made to feel genuinely welcome. The entire team was incredibly friendly, warm, and attentive throughout our stay — nothing ever felt like too much trouble, and every interaction came with a sincere smile. A special thank you to Kookik at breakfast, who remembered our names each morning. That personal touch truly made us feel valued and set such a lovely tone for the day. It’s these thoughtful details that make this hotel stand out. The food at FishTales was an absolute highlight. Every meal was delicious, beautifully presented, and full of fresh flavours. Dining there became something we looked forward to each day. We also have to give special mention to the wonderful staff around the pool. They went above and beyond to keep everyone comfortable — ensuring we were constantly hydrated, offering refreshing cold towels, and surprising us with little treats throughout the day. Their attentiveness really elevated the whole experience and made lounging by the pool feel effortlessly luxurious. Overall, Garrya Tongsai Bay delivers not only a stunning setting but truly outstanding service. We would highly recommend it and can’t wait to return! Many thanks Melanie, Brian(Melvyn),Tom and Cansu"
> **- Melvyn G (5/5/5)**

> "My husband and I spent four nights at Garrya Tongsai Bay after starting our Thailand holiday in Bangkok. We were welcomed with private transportation at the Koh Samui airport, complete with water and cold towels. The check-in process was relaxing and took place on a terrace overlooking the ocean.  We stayed in a seaview hillside pool suite. While not as large as some of the villas, it was extremely spacious and included a private pool with two lounge chairs. All the accommodations seem lovingly maintained and were clearly well-built to begin with. We''ve stayed in Four Seasons properties as well as The Standard Hua Hin (right after it was built) and this was our favorite. The resort isn''t super large, so the employees and our fellow guests quickly started to look familiar. We loved the friendly, intimate atmosphere, but if you want to blend in on a larger resort or prize anonymity, this one isn''t for you. We also liked how eco-friendly it was, things like delivering meal leftovers in real dishes rather than wasteful disposable packaging and daily educational nature walks stood out to us.  The service and dining punch well above their weight and are a large part of why we enjoyed our stay so much. Fish Tales offers nightly dinner, pool bar food service, and lunch. EVOL has healthier options, including multiple items for vegans. Rhoy Rhoy is a slightly more formal dinner option and is the site of the bountiful breakfast buffet each morning. The cocktail list available by the pool or via room service is excellent. We drank our way through most of it and nothing was a disappointment. I also want to give a special shout out to the lovely woman making fresh juices at breakfast each day. She is a real gem and we enjoyed seeing her!  Overall as we prepare to leave, we feel sad to go but grateful for our memorable and relaxing stay. Next time we''re in Koh Samui we will strongly consider returning. There are many outstanding resorts on the island, but this one blends service, approachable luxury, and care for the environment in a really lovely way. Thank you to the entire team!"
> **- Madeline Van Dolah (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/garrya-tongsai-bay-1.jpg','077 913 750','84, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.garrya.com/en/destinations/samui','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifsv000nq8xdrwnu123q','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.712+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.712+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/garrya-tongsai-bay-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/garrya-tongsai-bay-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2801370402233243531',NULL,NULL);
