INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('genesis-bakery-restaurant','standard','cmr07igiz00arq8xdch5owat2','Genesis Bakery & Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "If you’re looking for incredible, healthy food, a cozy environment, and an establishment that treats you like family - Genesis is the place to go. Their menu offers a wide variety, from Shakshuka to the most delicious cookies you’ll ever eat. The food leaves you feeling good and energised, giving you the perfect start to your day. 10/10 recommend trying anything and everything on the menu!🤩 P.S. if you like coffee, their Biscoff latte is to die for!!!!"
> **- Nikita Gibbs (5/5/5)**

> "The most amazing place in Koh Samui, they have the best home cooked breakfast, lunch and cakes!! First place I’ve been to on the island where everything tastes soooo good! I LOVE IT  The staff is so nice and friendly"
> **- Yasmine holmgren (5/5/5)**

> "loved the pan au chocolat they had to offer, they were absolutely delicious. however, the lady behind the counter was quite rude. the food was good though!"
> **- emma c (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/genesis-bakery-restaurant-1.jpg','081 476 6342','155, 28 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.723+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.723+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/genesis-bakery-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/genesis-bakery-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13333932191077543352',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('get-health-clinic','standard','cmr07igj100asq8xdmm2cm51p','Get Health Clinic','## Top Reviews
> "The clinic is centered around a talented and highly educated physician and surgeon who deeply understands their work and works closely with each patient. Despite the clinic''s high level of quality and cleanliness, the prices are reasonable, and the staff''s professionalism is based on the highest standards.  The doctor will help you resolve even the most delicate issues, if needed. Russian is also spoken at the clinic.  The quality of services here is on par with the most expensive hospitals, but Dr. Get''s clinic is the best choice; trust the locals.  Говорят по-русски!"
> **- We Ze (5/5/5)**

> "Did my surgery today , everything went smooth , DR. Get was super friendly , personally drove me to the Hospital where the surgery took place, also bought me a refreshing drink on the way home . Mr. Get thank you so much for what you’ve done , indeed recommend this place ! Also i’ve read a reviews for the clinic just right now , and there’s a guy who was waiting a little over his appointment and got frustrated, all i can say is , sometime we do t know what’s happening behind the scenes and maybe he was in the surgery which took a little more than planned , as far as i know Dr. Get is performing surgeries all over the hospitals on the Island so i would say a little understanding is a must . Thanks once again !!!"
> **- Pavel Cotogoi (5/5/5)**

> "I liked the clinic.  Very modern and cozy.  The wait (practical one hour) was a little disappointing.  I liked the ophthalmologist.  It''s a pity, our visit was absolutely useless.  The child’s vision could not be tested"
