INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('go-samui-catering','standard','cmr07igjk00axq8xdmvqakrmn','Go Samui Catering','## Top Reviews
> "Chef Don and his team are absolutely fantastic. Our wedding planner Juliette recommended Go Samui Catering and we booked them for our wedding in Koh Samui in February 2025. The food was a dream and our guests loved it. Don and his team are very professional and even at the rehearsal dinner a year before we knew we were in the best hands with Don. The bruschetta bar we booked was also very well received and praised by our guests. Once again a big thank you to the Go Samui Catering team for the delicious catering and we can highly recommend them."
> **- Anda Blume (5/5/5)**

> "Chef Don and his amazing team at Go Catering Samui catered multiple events across my 40th birthday extravaganza in beautiful Koh Samui - a pool party (canapes & bar), a private yacht 6-hour tour (grazing platter, canapes & bar), and a private cooking class covering some of the thai classics. Just, perfection.  Service - 5 stars! Food - 5 stars! (the flavours were amazing!) Ease of communication - 5 stars!  Cannot recommend the Go Catering team highly enough"
> **- Thomas Dunlop (5/5/5)**

> "We were amazed at what Chef Don and his team was able to put together for our two day wedding event. We wanted only local Thai cuisine and scheduled several calls with Don to go through our extensive list of requests. We appreciated his honesty when we were clearly ordering too much food and helped us curate the menu to give plenty of variety but staying within the theme. He was accommodating to the multiple dietary restrictions of our guests even with buffet style menu. Loved the recommendation of the flying style buffet as well so no one needs to wait in line for food. Everything ran seamlessly and the guests all raved about the food. Thanks Chef Don and team!"
> **- maia luke (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/go-samui-catering-1.jpg','087 473 2826','45/22, ตำบล บ่อผุด Koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.gosamuicatering.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifv2001aq8xdag7cvjgf','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.744+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.744+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/go-samui-catering-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/go-samui-catering-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12403256385073812593',NULL,NULL);
