INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('golden-studio','standard','cmr07igjt00b0q8xdq0x40kxo','Golden Studio','## Top Reviews
> "I had a pleasure experience with Golden from communicating the service I want till I booked the appointment and done the nail. They reply fast and clear information, fast appointment confirmation. Care understood exactly what I want, while the gel color I wanted was almost finished, not enough for my nail, we improvised and mixed the color, that was my highlight! Great job. She is very skilled, since I do nail monthly, so I can tell immediately. I will come back for her 100%. Highly recommended."
> **- Lin L (5/5/5)**

> "i got a manicure with gel + chrome + design and a pedicure with gel for 2200 THB (£50). the design was done meticulously, the nail artist was very patient with my changing my mind constantly and took 2 hours to complete my hands! the pedicure was done beautifully too. EDIT: my manicure chipped and came off after a day or two. Do not recommend unfortunately 🥲🥲🥲🥲🥲"
> **- Tegan Hurst (1/5/5)**

> "went to Golden Studio Nails & Eyelashes yesterday for gel nails and some nail art, and I couldn’t be happier! The staff were super kind and welcoming, they even offered me water and candy. The girl who did my nails was absolutely amazing! She did exactly what I asked for with so much precision and care. Honestly, I’ve never had nails this beautiful in my life! 💖 Plus, the studio itself is super cute and girly, such a lovely and relaxing atmosphere! 💅✨ I totally recommend this place!"
