INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('good-health-pharmacy','standard','cmr07igjv00b1q8xd6iw7kfnq','Good Health Pharmacy','## Top Reviews
> "This pharmacy and especially the pharmacist is really great! Everything is very clean and tidy, everything I wanted to buy is there! The prices are adequate. Special thanks to the pharmacist, he is always kind, polite, in a good mood and speaks English well — I appreciate it￼!"
> **- Андрей Панин (5/5/5)**

> "I had a disappointing experience at this pharmacy. When paying with a bank card, they charged an additional 3%, which was not clearly communicated upfront. Additionally, they applied a hidden conversion from THB to EUR with a markup fee of about 5.4%. This resulted in the price being increased by approximately 10% in total. I recommend being very cautious if you choose to shop here."
> **- Dmitry Tsvetkov (1/5/5)**

> "Had to go in with a persistent sore throat ( turned out to be a bacterial infection). The Pharmacist was very professional, helpful and friendly. He spoke perfect English and explained everything very clearly. I would 100% recommend going to this Thai gentleman if you are in the unfortunate position of needing medical advice."
