INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('grannys-samui','standard','cmr07igk000b3q8xdpnwdahek','Granny''s Samui','## Top Reviews
> "We have a sweet tooth and were looking for a place where we could enjoy coffee and dessert — and we found it. It’s a cozy, air-conditioned café with a wonderful selection of cakes. We tried the honey cake and the carrot cake. The taste was just as good as what you’d find in Europe, which pleasantly surprised us, since local desserts naturally tend to have their own distinct regional flavor. We will definitely come back again.😉"
> **- Olga * (5/5/5)**

> "Absolutely AMAZING!!! I love the atmosphere, I LOOVED the food, and the dessert (Honey Cake) was pure nostalgia to my mind. Just amazing."
> **- Edward Beebe (5/5/5)**

> "Nice and cozy place, delicious Russian food, not many vegan options but plenty of different drinks. Had the potato’s dumplings which were very great and well made. They are making rum infusion which was excellent (had the cream coconut)."
> **- Orel S (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/grannys-samui-1.jpg','063 119 0970','127 Moo 4, Mae Nam Subdistrict Maenam, ตำบล แม่น้ำ อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.instagram.com/grannys.samui/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.760+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.760+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/grannys-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/grannys-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5687119528113165753',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('green-beach-cafe','standard','cmr07igk200b4q8xdgbcosdz4','Green Beach Cafe','## Top Reviews
> "I love this place sooo much! I came here almost every day for two months The drinks are really good, same as the food. The view is amazing and they have lots of different options to sit, also options with shade. But the most amazing part is the staff. Everyone is soo friendly, they make such a good job every day. Especially Toom welcomed me within the first 3 seconds and made every day a little bit better with her smile🥰"
> **- Johanna Leitner (5/5/5)**

> "An absolute gem in Koh Samui!"
> **- Aleksandra Grajczyk (5/5/5)**

> "Great modern and clean little cafe alongside the beach. We had a coffee and smoothie and both were 👍 great. We placed ourselves outside overlooking the beach with the boats in view and a bent coconut tree. The staff were very friendly and efficient. The food coming out of the kitchen looked amazing. We will be back again to try a meal."
> **- Julie Sarafov (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/green-beach-cafe-1.jpg','082 105 6211','75, 3, Tambon Taling Ngam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/share/17ScWdZ6Tg/?mibextid=wwXIfr','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: Closed","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07igdj008fq8xdhc2mye6x','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.762+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.762+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/green-beach-cafe-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/green-beach-cafe-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3260022758799621499',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('green-bird-restaurant','standard','cmr07igk300b5q8xds9sv2ino','Green Bird Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "Green bird used to be a staple of our annual Samui trip. First found the place around 2012 after a Lonely Planet recommendation.  2026 was our first visit since COVID. And absolutely did not disappoint.  A little off the main track which is great to avoid crowds. The place is clean, airy and comfortable. The staff are always super friendly.  And the food… Best I can describe is mainland prices, and almost local price at that… almost.. 80THB for garlic pepper pork and rice as an example. Food is prompt, fresh and delicious.  And try their cocktails. Couldn’t tell you what is in it, but 2 time bombs let you know you are alive..  Highly recommend"
> **- James Earle (5/5/5)**

> "Highly recommend!!! You have to come here! We ordered a TON of dishes and honestly every single one was the best we’ve eaten in Thailand. Usually I can always find something that’s not quite enough for me, but here… everything was absolutely amazing.  What’s even crazier: I ate not far from here at a two Michelin star restaurant, and this place was better in every way taste, quality, portions, and overall vibe.  Even with the restaurant fully packed, the waiting time was super fast, portions were big, prices were really good, and the service? The best I’ve experienced in Thailand smiles, speed, everything on point. I’m 100% coming back. 🔥🇹🇭"
> **- Ataczkowski (5/5/5)**

> "Everything we tried was absolutely delicious! The prices are very reasonable, the place is well taken care of with a warm and cozy atmosphere, and the staff was extremely kind and welcoming. Definitely a place worth visiting!"
> **- George (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/green-bird-restaurant-1.jpg','086 906 4638','157 17 หมู่ที่ 2 ตำบล บ่อผุด Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://m.facebook.com/Pu.greenbird/','["Monday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.763+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.763+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/green-bird-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/green-bird-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=254676540208646793',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('green-flow-chill-bar-thai-food','standard','cmr07igk500b6q8xdx1iypgkq','Green Flow Chill Bar & Thai Food','## Top Reviews
> "What a wonderful place! Delicious food, friendly staff, a very varied menu, something for every taste. They also sell smoking devices! I highly recommend this place! We''ll be back again."
> **- Майя Макарадзе (5/5/5)**

> "Open place, very nice and well-kept, close to the beach. Family management, she speaks good English and her husband cooks. Everything really very good, well-groomed and clean. It''s worth a stop!!"
> **- Nicole Schiantarelli (5/5/5)**

> "Awesome food and friendly staff. We are papaya salad which was absolutely the best ! Frankly recomend this place"
> **- Maja Zeler (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/green-flow-chill-bar-thai-food-1.jpg','098 513 6862','37 30, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://greenflowsamui.com/','["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: Closed","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifso000kq8xdfe9gpaon','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.765+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.765+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/green-flow-chill-bar-thai-food-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/green-flow-chill-bar-thai-food-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3841873114365003781',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('green-garden-services','standard','cmr07igk700b7q8xdgzjv1dre','Green Garden Services','## Top Reviews
> "I bought an indoor plant and had a good talk and very good service with/by Nimma. She knows very well about plants and is super nice. I can recommend to go here. Also for big gardens and villas. They have a lot of big beautiful plants."
> **- Olli (5/5/5)**

> "This shop ordered plant seedlings from my store with cash on delivery, but the full payment was not made. They chose not to return the plants and instead planted them in pots. Although they mentioned that they could not resell the plants to foreign customers, the plants were still used. This situation was not handled transparently. In the end, the payment I received was less than the amount we agreed on, and the shipping cost was not covered, even though delivery to an island area is quite expensive.  The amount was small and not worth affecting your shop’s image."
> **- NUTTAMON EKKAMART (1/5/5)**

> "Very good advice, prices and selection of plants. Manager and staff very helpful and kind"
> **- Chris (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/green-garden-services-1.jpg','+66657428887','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/samuigreengarden/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.767+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.767+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/green-garden-services-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/green-garden-services-2.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/green-garden-services-3.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/green-garden-services-4.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6827396134070714957',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('green-mango-club','standard','cmr07igk900b8q8xdvs86mo4k','Green Mango Club','## Top Reviews
> "Came for some music, found excellent atmosphere, very good DJ, loved the music, drinks were ok priced and the crowd was multinational and it was beautiful seeing so many people just dancing and having fun. Highly recommend.  Hate to do this here but for me it was also a very hard time thinking of the Nova party where thousands of multinational young people came for the same peace of mind and harmony for dancing and never returned home."
> **- Zack Tzuk-Ramon (5/5/5)**

> "It''s hard to explain how much I love the Green Mango, out of all the places in the world I''ve visited.  I once got my ass kicked, for a week, by an angry Thai stripper (long story) and I ended up broke and barely able to scrape the money up to go home. The 4 girls at Green Mango, who were my friends already, picked me up, fed me, and took me to the airport on their scooters like the flight of the valkyries. Hands down one of the most unselfish, kindest, and most moving things anyone has ever done for me. And for that, I''ll always love the Green Mango, and my 4 guardian angels ♥️  (Jesus christ, that isnt the thai stripper in the picture. Its my chinese girlfriend, who the girls made feelat home!)"
> **- Jody Neil Ruth (5/5/5)**

> "Very quiet, not really a ‘club’. There was no atmosphere there. Was sat down listening to the music and I got approached by a person who groaped my crotch straight away. I pushed them away. I would not recommend this place, I’d recommend going to sound club which is a short walk around the corner. If you go here, be careful of the people there, keep an eye out."
> **- charlie Cooper 54 (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/green-mango-club-1.jpg','077 300 672','G3M7+399, Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.greenmangoclub.com/','["Monday: 9:00 PM – 4:00 AM","Tuesday: 9:00 PM – 4:00 AM","Wednesday: 9:00 PM – 4:00 AM","Thursday: 9:00 PM – 4:00 AM","Friday: 9:00 PM – 4:00 AM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 4:00 AM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 4:00 PM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.770+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.770+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/green-mango-club-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/green-mango-club-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5210391072111974194',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('greenacre-international-school','standard','cmr07igkb00b9q8xdtq1k0qbd','Greenacre International School','Discover Greenacre International School, a premier for kids located in Namueang, Koh Samui. Find reviews, hours, and contact information.','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/greenacre-international-school-1.jpg','077 430 729','108, Tambon Na Mueang, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,0.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.greenacre.ac.th/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ig4i004oq8xdv207xuh2','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.771+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.771+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/greenacre-international-school-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/greenacre-international-school-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1196480473571239725',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('greenlight-cafe-bar','standard','cmr07igkd00baq8xdspd6slzf','Greenlight Cafe & Bar','## Top Reviews
> "Green Light Village is an absolute gem in Koh Samui! Patrick, the owner, is incredibly kind and welcoming. Gun, the manager, is fantastic, and Nooky and the rest of the team are simply perfect. Everyone speaks excellent English, which makes everything easy and comfortable.  The value for money is unbeatable. It’s not a luxury hotel, but it truly doesn’t lack anything. The rooms are simple, very clean, and everything works perfectly. The pool is great, the atmosphere is peaceful and family-like, and you’re just a two-minute walk from the beach.  The bar serves simple food made with real care and amazing quality — you can really taste the love put into it.  In short: unbeatable quality-price ratio in a perfect location. We would definitely stay here again!"
> **- ABV (5/5/5)**

> "This is a review of the cafe. I had met Patrick earlier in the afternoon while strolling the street so we returned for supper that evening. We had a nice table by the pool; we were one of two tables being served. The ambiance and setting was very nice. Our server arrived to take our order with no extra words- no hello, no introduction, nothing to say about the menu or any specials (if there were any), pretty much just Flat. His mango shake was Thick(like pudding, he said) but it eventually thinned. The Chicken Salsa Wraps were tasty. Would have helped if the chicken chucks were cut smaller and distributed throughout vs a chunk here and there. His Teriyaki Salmon over Glass Soba noodles- he said the salmon was the tastiest he’s had in FV. The glass soba noodles had a kick to them that he wasn’t expecting so wasn’t really able to enjoy them. Overall the food, even though it took a bit to get to us, was Fresh and the presentation was  lovely. The server didn’t come to check on us, ask if we needed anything else, didn’t offer dessert. We actually had to get up and head to the front to pay while the five server staff watched us. Also, disappointing that Patrick who was at the front counter when we arrived, didn’t bother to stop at our table to even chat for a moment.  There was no one seated for supper when we left;  he was still at the front counter/bar talking to two seated people. Attitude...Small thing but a nice touch; they missed that. We had met people on the same afternoon who also talked with Patrick as he invited us to his Salsa lesson and dance. After a long day, they did make it back to say hello and check it out, but left disappointed as he didn''t even acknowledge their presence. We spent 600-800thb per person. They do take credit cards."
> **- Kele Coloma (3/5/5)**

> "I ONLY RECOMMEND THE RESTAURANT!! I WAS NOT A HOTEL GUEST  Very nice restaurant with many food options. My partner and I had a great experience, and they also have many tasty gluten-free choices. Thank you for the excellent service."
> **- Daniel Marsall (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/greenlight-cafe-bar-1.jpg','081 121 6955','3/28 Fisherman''s Village Bophut Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'https://greenlightsamui.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.773+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.773+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/greenlight-cafe-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/greenlight-cafe-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16492982901616896423',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('gringos-cantina','standard','cmr07igkf00bbq8xd9vw0e884','Gringo''s Cantina','## Top Reviews
> "Really good, been to so many Mexican restaurants throughout Thailand and this one is on my top 5. Definitely going to save this one for my Koh Samui trips. Food was great, and the frozen margaritas are great as well. We had the supreme nachos and buffalo wings to start. Both were great. Then of course we had the beef fajitas. Flavors and the sizzling hot plate were great. But I do think they should add more beef. More beef than pepper and onions are a must for that 10 outta 10 experience.  Still over all amazing and will be going back and sharing this place with my friends that pass through."
> **- lifestyle_googlemap -Instagram (5/5/5)**

> "WOW What amazing food! I expected generic Mexican but this was next level good. Friendly, off the strip, so quiet. Great food, great experience! Great staff! Highly recommended"
> **- Todd Engel (5/5/5)**

> "Absolutely incredible experience. The food was outstanding and the service was genuinely impeccable. Staff were friendly, attentive and the food came out impressively fast. We ordered a jug of frozen mango margaritas and loved that there were so many flavour options to choose from. The menu is fantastic and varied. We had the chicken fajitas served sizzling on a hot plate and the slow cooked beef burritos, and both were genuinely sensational. You can tell a lot of care goes into the food. Perfect location just off the busy strip and an easy choice for an amazing dinner. We will definitely be back.😍"
> **- Lottie Wilkinson (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/gringos-cantina-1.jpg','077 963 207','166, 99, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://gringoscantina.base44.app/','["Monday: 2:00 – 11:30 PM","Tuesday: 2:00 PM – 12:30 AM","Wednesday: 2:00 – 11:30 PM","Thursday: 2:00 – 11:30 PM","Friday: 2:00 – 11:30 PM","Saturday: 2:00 – 11:30 PM","Sunday: 2:00 – 11:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.775+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.775+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/gringos-cantina-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/gringos-cantina-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9209976388024374668',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('grow-high-maenam','standard','cmr07igkh00bcq8xdlviykxdp','Grow High','## Top Reviews
> "Such a nice place to chill. The owner is so friendly and helps you with everything! She also offers a range of different teas which taste really nice! Thanks for having us!! 🫶🏼"
> **- Jum Bo (5/5/5)**

> "Caro, the employee, is very sweet, accommodating, and friendly. The place is a nice ambiance. She explained the strains very well and recommend me based on what I wanted. Highly recommend to go!"
> **- Natalia Caballero (5/5/5)**

> "I recently visited a fantastic weed shop and I must say, I was blown away by the quality of their buds. The selection of strains was impressive, and each one was more delicious than the last. The staff was incredibly knowledgeable and helped me choose the perfect strain to suit my needs.  But that''s not all, they also had an extensive range of teas to choose from, which was a delightful surprise. I was able to sit back, relax, and enjoy a cup of their delicious tea while taking in the ambiance of the shop.  And to top it all off, their ice cream was simply divine. It was the perfect sweet treat to end my visit to the shop. Overall, I highly recommend this weed shop to anyone looking for high-quality buds, an impressive tea selection, and a sweet treat to top it all off. Trust me, you won''t be disappointed!"
> **- Liza Yazkova (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/grow-high-maenam-1.jpg','065 420 6000','100/5, ตำบล แม่น้ำ อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://growhighshop.com/','["Monday: 1:00 – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 1:00 – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 1:00 – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 1:00 – 11:00 PM","Friday: 1:00 – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 1:00 – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 1:00 – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.777+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.777+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/grow-high-maenam-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/grow-high-maenam-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12121983370312379220',NULL,NULL);
