> **- Natalia Caballero (5/5/5)**

> "I recently visited a fantastic weed shop and I must say, I was blown away by the quality of their buds. The selection of strains was impressive, and each one was more delicious than the last. The staff was incredibly knowledgeable and helped me choose the perfect strain to suit my needs.  But that''s not all, they also had an extensive range of teas to choose from, which was a delightful surprise. I was able to sit back, relax, and enjoy a cup of their delicious tea while taking in the ambiance of the shop.  And to top it all off, their ice cream was simply divine. It was the perfect sweet treat to end my visit to the shop. Overall, I highly recommend this weed shop to anyone looking for high-quality buds, an impressive tea selection, and a sweet treat to top it all off. Trust me, you won''t be disappointed!"
> **- Liza Yazkova (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/grow-high-1.jpg','065 420 6000','100/5, ตำบล แม่น้ำ อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://growhighshop.com/','["Monday: 1:00 – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 1:00 – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 1:00 – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 1:00 – 11:00 PM","Friday: 1:00 – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 1:00 – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 1:00 – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.779+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.779+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/grow-high-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/grow-high-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12121983370312379220',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('gusto-italiano','standard','cmr07igkl00beq8xdrt05asmx','Gusto Italiano','## Top Reviews
> "Gusto Italiano was a wonderful surprise with so many restaurants to choose from at Fisherman Village in Koh Samui we took a chance on this restaurant. We were seated at an open counter facing the beach.  The fettuccine Bolognese was excellent. The spicy salami pizza was flavorful and crust was cooked perfectly. It was the best pizza I''ve ever had here in Thailand.The fresh ingredients shine through in every bite.  Our server was attentive without being intrusive, all the staff were fantastic. Definitely will return."
> **- Cheri Crickon (5/5/5)**

> "I tried this italian restaurant because of the good reviews. We''ll, I was disapointed. The location on the beach and the ambiance is amazing. This is why you are paying the big price. The wine was excellent but the food had no taste at all. I was expecting flavorfull food for this price but it was not the case. I would not return. I paid 1500 baht for one person. It was one of the most expensive food and wine I bought so far in Thailand and probably the less memorable."
> **- Marie-Eve Parent (3/5/5)**

> "⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ We’ve eaten Italian food across Italy itself, so our standards are not easy to meet. Gusto Italiano met them — and then some. The setting alone is worth the visit. Fisherman’s Village is one of the most charming spots on Koh Samui, perfect for an evening stroll, and the restaurant sits right on the beach with tables at the water’s edge and an uninterrupted view of the sea. The kind of place you don’t want to leave. The pleasant sound of the sea and relaxing, pleasant jazz music plays in the background. Beautiful, stylish interior inside the restaurant. Perfect.  The food matches the atmosphere. The Seafood Risotto was flawless — properly mantecato, perfectly timed, generous with the seafood. Spaghetti alle vongole - aromatic, tasty sauce of perfect consistency, lots of shellfish without sand, spaghetti al dente, as requested. The pizza was just the way it should be. The pasta was thin, but the edges were fluffy, well-risen and airy, the most delicious ingredients, high-quality mozzarella and tomatoes. For dessert, we chose tiramisu. Classic, delicate, flavorful, delicious, pure delight.  And the wine: Argiolas Costamolino Vermentino DOC from Sardinia — order it without hesitation. Citrus, white flowers, Mediterranean herbs, and a mineral finish that belongs by the sea. A perfect pairing for every dish.  The service is very remarkable and worthy of attention, where Thai waiters try to speak Italian with you and manage your table responsibly.  A special mention to the owners, Marco and Roberta— true professionals in every sense, warm and genuinely welcoming. From the first moment you feel not just like a customer, but like a cherished guest. That kind of hospitality is rare. A truly authentic Italian experience on the shores of Koh Samui. We’ll be back."
> **- David Bach (David) (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/gusto-italiano-1.jpg','077 332 514','73/3 Moo 1 Fisherman Village, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.gustoitalianosamui.com/','["Monday: 1:30 – 10:30 PM","Tuesday: 1:30 – 10:30 PM","Wednesday: 1:30 – 10:30 PM","Thursday: 1:30 – 10:30 PM","Friday: 1:30 – 10:30 PM","Saturday: 1:30 – 10:30 PM","Sunday: 1:30 – 10:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.781+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.781+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/gusto-italiano-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/gusto-italiano-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6541608047941678519',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('h-bistro','standard','cmr07igkm00bfq8xd3wx8uw2f','H Bistro','## Top Reviews
> "We had dinner at HBistro for my husband’s birthday, and it was truly an exceptional experience.  From the moment of booking, the staff were very attentive to every detail. They asked about our preferences in advance and offered several menu options, including wine pairing. We chose the Mediterranean set menu with wine pairing on the beach. There was a chance of rain, and the team thoughtfully informed us about an indoor option — but luckily, we had perfect weather and could enjoy the beach setting.  For the occasion, they prepared a beautiful romantic gazebo decorated with flowers just for us, which made the evening feel very special. We also had a dedicated waitress who was incredibly attentive and responsive — we really felt like VIP guests.  The food deserves a special mention: everything was delicious, beautifully presented, and the wine pairing complemented the dishes perfectly. We were also surprised with a birthday cake, which was a lovely and thoughtful gesture.  Overall, it’s a great choice if you’re looking for a truly special dining experience — absolutely worth it."
> **- Nadiya Bondarenko (5/5/5)**

> "The food was delicious, all the staff were lovely – P''A, P''Ball, P''Noi, and everyone else as usual – and the music was great. It was a very warm and welcoming atmosphere, especially during my most frequent visits."
> **- wilasinee petchsuk (5/5/5)**

> "We We took the Mediterranean set and unfortunately it was really disappointing. It was very expensive, and still the food was honestly not good at all. It felt like they used expensive ingredients but without much attention to the actual flavors. The waiter was very nice and the atmosphere was good, but aside from that the food was poor, and we ended up with stomach aches throughout the night and the following day. Sadly, we wouldn’t recommend this place."
> **- Naama Tal (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/h-bistro-1.jpg','077 245 511','H26G+M8P, Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 7:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 10:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.782+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.782+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/h-bistro-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/h-bistro-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10719386228704853366',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('hachiya','standard','cmr07igko00bgq8xdmfbspaze','Hachiya','## Top Reviews
> "We stayed in Koh Samui for three weeks and came here almost every day. Amazing Japanese matcha and dirty coffees. Good desserts. Nice atmosphere and friendly staff. We bought beans for home brewing, too. Very happy with them."
> **- Lisa (5/5/5)**

> "Cute tiny roastery in Maenam. Valencia Latte was yum, I ended up bringing home some coffee beans from Chiang Rai. Staff was friendly and accomodating, was hoping to see the cat but perhaps it wasnt my lucky day!"
> **- TWNG (5/5/5)**

> "Came all the way to drink Matcha only, just to find it maybe they will get a restock next month. That was really disappointing. Also their Hokkaido milk was sold out as well so it was too many things at once. Cold brew was only decent, guess the beans were washed out too much, not much flavour and fat. It’s a cozy atmosphere but I didn’t like that the cat hair was flying around all the time on to the table and saw the cat inside the roastery so don’t want to imagine how much hair is inside."
> **- SuiYx23 (2/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hachiya-1.jpg','095 284 7090','93 1, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://instagram.com/hachiya_coffee?igshid=1vu7d9wa038og','["Monday: 8:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: Closed","Friday: 8:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 8:30 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.784+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.784+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hachiya-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hachiya-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=383788833119865948',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('hair-house-salon','standard','cmr07igkr00bhq8xd77az5m8y','Hair House Salon','## Top Reviews
> "I had a great experience at the salon yesterday. The hairstylist was very sweet and worked quickly. The place itself was clean, quiet, and pleasant. For only 300 baht, I got my hair washed, a relaxing head massage, a haircut, and a blow dry! Totally worth it!"
> **- Kris Yaskevich (5/5/5)**

> "I got highlights done here and I’m absolutely thrilled with the result! Kim is super lovely, very friendly, and truly professional. The highlights turned out absolutely beautiful and look really natural — exactly how I wanted them. You can tell she really understands how to match the tones perfectly, which makes such a difference. The prices are very fair too, not overpriced at all. I’ll definitely be coming back. Thank you so much, Kim!"
> **- M. Taylor (5/5/5)**

> "I had a super good experience at this salon. She gave me a really nice cut and was super sweet and the head massage was also great. She had a lot of time for me"
> **- elly elly (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hair-house-salon-1.jpg','081 846 7912','159 Soi 4, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/Hair-House-Salon-188973315350749/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.787+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.787+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hair-house-salon-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hair-house-salon-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11333273637779199398',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('hakuna-matata','standard','cmr07igku00biq8xdl4w6m72b','Hakuna Matata','## Top Reviews
> "They have a decent fleet of cars. The one I received was in great condition, clean and had no issues. My initial conversation with the team was good but I was disappointed with the delivery and pick up person. He wasn''t answering questions willingly during pickup and didn''t show me the exact fuel indicator. On the day of return, which was scheduled at 1 PM, the pickup team video called me twice while I was driving and the disapproval in their faces during video call was evident. I don''t understand what for - when despite all their follow ups, I reached at 12:55 PM to return the car. They also stated how the fuel was not the same and spoke in the local language, maybe they were joking, maybe trying to get something extra out, but regardless, I had given a 300 USD deposit and had a flight to catch. It''s not the best time to do this on return. It''s good I had sent a photo of the fuel during pickup and there were no issues. Its a good car rental service in Samui but there is need for improvement at the ground level."
> **- Virender Singh (4/5/5)**

> "Can recommend!  Great rental service! Easy and quick via WhatsApp. 3000thb deposit and a picture of passport. returned in full amount.  We rented for 9 days and extended by 1 day and had the scooter picked up at the pier. Worked flawlessly. The scooter was brand new with only 1800km on it. Competitive price for longer rentals."
> **- Marcus Lenker (5/5/5)**

> "I made a good experience with this scooter rental. Easy communication. I had to wait for 20 minutes when they brought me the scooter to the pier. It was in a good condition. They don''t take your passport just a 3000 ฿ (~80€) deposit. I brought the bike back and got my deposit back after a quick check. I would absolutely rent here again. 5 Stars. I''d advise you to order it in advance from their website."
> **- Cassius Cem Posthumus (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hakuna-matata-1.jpg',NULL,'31/26.สมุยแบดมินตัน, ต.บ่อผุด, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://rentcarsamui.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07ifui0012q8xdzn158clv','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.790+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.790+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hakuna-matata-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hakuna-matata-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12233419899243478733',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('halapua','standard','cmr07igkw00bjq8xd59fd8htu','Halapua','## Top Reviews
> "This wonderful open-air vegan restaurant is set within a plant-based resort in the hills of Samui with incredible views and a serene feel.  We reserved the tasting menu for ฿1000 each, which included an assigned appetizer, choice of starter and main course, chocolate cake dessert, and a glass of house wine. All of it was carefully and respectfully served.  Although expensive by Thai standards, it was quite inexpensive and great value by European and American standards.  The food was invariably beautifully presented and absolutely delicious, filling without being overwhelming.  If you’re able to spend that amount of money, there’s no reason not to go here. If you do, you will be amply rewarded.  Credit cards accepted without a fee, tax included in the price."
> **- Dan Brook (5/5/5)**

> "I am not vegan and i am in looove with this food! It’s fulfilling and never heavy for my stomach, no matter if I’ve eaten the whole menu list 😂 Cause it’s vegan, straight from their garden!  This sea view in unreal! And a salt-water swimming pool! I don’t know where else I can find one on the island. I can easily spend dayyyysss in here! The guys are just great at service, which is quite rare"
> **- Daria Trenina (5/5/5)**

> "Coming across authentic tasting vegan italian (sicilian) food is rare in SE Asia. But Halapua....wow! This is a MUST VISIT VEGAN RESTAURANT on Ko Samui. Whether you''re vegan or not, you will enjoy the food here. All of the staff were incredible, the atmosphere was great, and the sea view overlooking the pool was nothing short of stunning. Top that with some incredble tasting authentic sicialian food - A true 5 star experience."
> **- the1ZK (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/halapua-1.jpg','095 308 6978','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.kapuhalasamui.com/','["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 11:30 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:30 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 11:30 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 11:30 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 11:30 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 11:30 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig5c0051q8xdykrbexft','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.792+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.792+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/halapua-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/halapua-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5465206101078710641',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('hansar','standard','cmr07igky00bkq8xd1glf9ltp','Hansar','## Top Reviews
> "We stayed here during the first leg of our honeymoon trip in Thailand and we really enjoyed our time here. When we arrived, they had a honeymoon setup in the room with a rose petal-filled bath drawn. The resort is not too large so the staff was pretty attentive to our requests. It''s also conveniently located right next to Fisherman''s Village as well as the beach. A somewhat minor complaint is that some power outlets in the room seemed to be connected to the light switches, so turning off the lights at night would result in devices not charging."
> **- Zach M (5/5/5)**

> "The Hansar Samui was a great place to be. The rooms are nice, clean and modern with a lot of space. The Service is great too. Everyone was nice and helpful. Breakfast was good to. It was not The Biggest breakfast selection we had in thailand but you can easily find food that fits your taste.  The pool is insane. The biggest Infinitiv Pool i ever saw. And an Amazing view to Koh Pangan.  The hotel is on the main streat of the fishermans village, but even with this location quiet. Only one hotel closer you will hear the difference. If you like a more crouded place, the choice of many Restaurants on the street, but still a place to relax, hansar is the hotel for you!"
> **- Adrian Weber (5/5/5)**

> "Wow! What a great resort. We arrived mid morning and weren''t able to check in immediately however we are invited to use the resort facilities while we waited. The room itself was a beachfront room which was spacious and very nice. The facilities are fantastic and the Fishermans village markets are a 5min walk. If you are in Koh Samui I would recommend you look up Hansar as its absolutely fantastic."
> **- Dave Eri (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hansar-1.jpg','077 245 511','101, Bophut, 28 Moo1, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.hansarsamui.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.794+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.794+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hansar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hansar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6093724044617259049',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('happy-dog-day-care','standard','cmr07igl000blq8xdbpuv9ys6','Happy Dog Day Care','## Top Reviews
> "The owner and her brother are wonderful people. It is clear that they love animals very much and give them affection and love. We gave the dog away for 2 days and they sent us photos and videos of our dog several times a day and we were calm. Thanks again!We will contact you again!❤"
> **- Мария Прекрасная (5/5/5)**

> "Best dog care in Samui, using the service from this place several times and never regret. My dogs always happy to go there. The owner play with my dogs every time. Know the behavior of each of them.  Went beyond for grooming and taking care. Even spot some details that i missed.  Very recommend."
> **- jarodfah Sivayathorn (5/5/5)**

> "If you are remotely concerned about leaving your doggie here set your mind at ease. My wife and I cannot speak highly enough of the care and professionalism shown by the lady who owns Happy Dog Day Care. An example of this is our little Frenchie Billy sleeps with us and the first night there he was crying at bedtime so the lady called her brother over who spent 6 nights sleeping beside him which completely calmed him. She also made sure to watch Billy when he ate as he eats fast and can choke sometimes. Lots of photo and video updates. Highly recommend."
> **- Mikey Boy (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/happy-dog-day-care-1.jpg','081 198 1608','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/Tonaor2527/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.796+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.796+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/happy-dog-day-care-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/happy-dog-day-care-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1260814662464132206',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('happy-dog-maenam','standard','cmr07igl200bmq8xdn4852ube','Happy Dog Maenam','## Top Reviews
> "Khun Thidapa did a great job. Very nice bath, nails and haircut was done. Highly recommended."
> **- Blue Marina (5/5/5)**

> "Great service, super friendly owner"
> **- Vitaly Ivanov (5/5/5)**

> "I took my cat to the groomer, and they cleaned her up really well. She smells amazing!"
> **- Chanyanuch Pookonglee (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/happy-dog-maenam-1.jpg','084 979 5616','78, ติดกับแม่น้ำมวยไทย, 3 ถนนทวีราชภักดี, แม่น้ำ, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.798+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.798+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/happy-dog-maenam-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/happy-dog-maenam-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10208451166628950451',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('happy-elephant-restaurant','standard','cmr07igl300bnq8xd3iynqye3','Happy Elephant Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "This was an amazing find for my family and I. Oceanside, fantastic staff, and great food. As soon as we walked to the menu, we were met with instant hospitality. Our glasses were never empty, we received great recommendations from the staff, and they have something for everyone, from American, Italian, to authentic Thai food. The most notable for us was the unforgettable service we received from Zar, Nai, and Zaw. Their kindness was what led us to come again a second night; the best of the best. For the cost, we have no doubt that you will get your money’s worth!"
> **- Lydia Lynn (5/5/5)**

> "We have been at the Happy Elephant a number of times over a number of years now and have enjoyed the food, atmosphere and service every time. Tonight Nai was our server, he was polite and always aimed to do his best. Would thoroughly recommend"
> **- Britta Peters (5/5/5)**

> "Ordered a pink lady cocktail and Thai whisky. My partner confirmed the pink lady was a well made cocktail and I enjoyed the Thai whisky with coke. They also allowed me to sample the whisky before ordering.  Ordered the mussels in white wine and cream sauce for starters/appetiser, then lobster I panang curry and rare tenderloin steak with prawn, fries and peppercorn sauce. Mussels were 10-20 seconds over cooked as a little bit chewy but the sauce was fantastic.  Steak came more blue than rare but that made no difference to flavour, still melted In the mouth, just order one difference up for rarity.  Lobster was cooked beautifully and paired with the spicy panang curry, it was an excellent pairing. Tasty rice accompanied with it.  Ordered a date pudding with butterscotch sauce for desert. The desert was moist and a great imitation of a sticky toffee, served with both cream and ice cream.  The service from Nai was excellent and was very attentive when glasses or plates were empty.  We did spend a bit more due to our wedding anniversary which is to be expected.  Greta experience."
> **- Matthew Evans (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/happy-elephant-restaurant-1.jpg','077 427 222','79 9, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://happyelephantrestaurant.com/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.799+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.799+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/happy-elephant-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/happy-elephant-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13571840984909636365',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('happy-meaow-hotel','standard','cmr07igl500boq8xd6na6dn1z','Happy Meaow Hotel','## Top Reviews
> "We left our Appa & MoMo at happy meaow cat hotel for 7 nights. The care taker are so nice and reports about their every condition to us twice a day. We felt very safe and secure about our cat there. Thank you."
> **- May Thinzar Khine (5/5/5)**

> "Before our holiday we start to search options where we can leave our kitten 8 months old. It was a difficult decision because we never left her alone and we gonna be out about 23 days. After searching and asking friends, we chose the Happy Meaow Cat Hotel and never regretted it! The owner is a very nice lady who loves cats and knows how to take care of them. The hotel is clean and has a special play area where cats are played twice a day. here you can choose a room for your pet based on your budget. we received daily photo and video reports about our kitten, if necessary, you can also ask questions, the hostess answers everything very quickly. When we came back our kitten looked good, calm and happy to see us! Now we know where to leave our kitten for the next vacation. and I will recommend this place to others."
> **- ELENA TARATAEVA (5/5/5)**

> "“My cat Gigi adopted me while I was living in Koh Samui, and whenever I had to travel she became a regular guest at this wonderful cat hotel. The place is beautifully designed, super cat-friendly, clean, and fun — and it quickly became her second home. Not only did Gigi always enjoy her stays, she built a real bond with the caring staff. Recently, I had to move back to Los Angeles for business and personal reasons, and I asked the hotel owner if she could arrange for Gigi to travel all the way from Samui to LAX. Without hesitation, she took on the challenge with so much confidence and heart. She handled every single step — from paperwork and medical requirements to coordinating with pet friendly airlines — seamlessly. Since Gigi had to stay at the hotel for over a month before her journey, the owner kept me updated daily with photos, videos, and even vet checkups if she noticed anything less than perfect. As the travel date approached, she groomed Gigi beautifully, prepared travel goodies, wrote adorable notes for the airline crew to help take care of her, and even arranged pet-friendly hotels and the most suitable flights. She stayed by Gigi’s side right up until check-in at Bangkok airport. What touched me most was how much she truly cared — creating sweet Instagram clips of Gigi, adjusting her diet to healthier food with my permission, and treating her like family. When Gigi finally arrived at LAX, she was calm, healthy, and happy — which amazed us! She adjusted to her new home almost instantly, and we couldn’t believe how stress-free she was after such a big adventure. We are deeply grateful to the hotel owner for going above and beyond. Gigi is now with us in Los Angeles, safe and thriving, and it wouldn’t have been possible without the love and dedication she received from this cat hotel. If you are looking for a place that truly treats your cat as family, this is it."
> **- Dann Dun (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/happy-meaow-hotel-1.jpg','081 887 7491','66 อ่างทอง 11, Tambon Ang Thong, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ig1h003iq8xdb1g9nifo','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.801+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.801+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/happy-meaow-hotel-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/happy-meaow-hotel-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=126065978957503406',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('happy-samui-tours','standard','cmr07igl800bpq8xd767swa2t','Happy Samui Tours','## Top Reviews
> "We loved our experience with our Guide Tor and Driver Dominik! We had a 5 hour tour to tempels, viewpoints and waterfalls. We especially liked that the vehicle was comfortable and the information provided by Tor, who also made it not just informative but also with great humor and fun. This is what we want to have when booking “Happy Samui”! Thank you 🙏 would recommend it to anyone thinking about doing a tour on Samui!"
> **- Luis Gold (5/5/5)**

> "We had a blast on the Angthong Marine Park small group tour. The entire day was perfectly organized, with a modern fast boat and great quality equipment.  The itinerary was fantastic - exploring the islands and the national park followed by some of the most spectacular snorkeling we’ve ever experienced. Kayaking was also great.  A huge thank you to Alexander and the Boat 2 crew, whose tireless service and contagious energy really made the trip. If you want a professional, high-energy tour with the best crew, Happy Samui Tours is the way to go."
> **- T M (5/5/5)**

> "We really enjoyed our trip together with Ice, also known as "
> **- Frederic Bauer (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/happy-samui-tours-1.jpg','091 299 4642','airport road, ตำบล บ่อผุด koh samui, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.happysamuitours.com/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.804+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.804+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/happy-samui-tours-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/happy-samui-tours-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6029505985100847852',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('have-a-good-day-cafe','standard','cmr07igl900bqq8xdml9w5084','Have A Good Day Cafe','## Top Reviews
> "A beautiful beachside café with such a peaceful and relaxing vibe. 😍 The ocean view is amazing, and it’s a perfect place to chill by the beach in Koh Samui.  I tried the fries and sandwiches, and both were really great—fresh, tasty, and perfect with the beach atmosphere 🍟🥪.  Lovely ambience, good food, and calm vibes. Definitely a nice spot to relax and enjoy the sea view! ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐"
> **- Mehul Batra (5/5/5)**

> "Lovely cafe on the beach with a great selection of food and drinks and wonderful views. The fish and chips, spaghetti with pesto and calamari were absolutely delicious. You can also take your drinks to the beach seating. Very friendly staff and great atmosphere."
> **- Tereza Moníková (5/5/5)**

> "A wonderful restaurant with a wide selection of dishes – from breakfast to lunch and dinner, there’s something for everyone. The variety of shakes is a real highlight!  The staff is very friendly and attentive, and the beachfront setting is simply dreamy: with a view of the sea and surrounded by coconut palms, it’s the perfect place to relax. Absolutely recommended!"
> **- Johnny Flash (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/have-a-good-day-cafe-1.jpg','083 069 5065','Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/Have-a-good-day-111609494699988/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 7:30 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 7:30 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 7:30 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 7:30 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 7:30 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 7:30 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 7:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.805+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.805+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/have-a-good-day-cafe-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/have-a-good-day-cafe-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17235197895060509788',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('haven-samui-community-mall','standard','cmr07iglc00brq8xdg3yz72wz','Haven Samui Community Mall','## Top Reviews
> "Cozy mall in the heart of Chaweng with events almost every weekend. Good eateries in the mall including Thai, Italian, French, and Kosher. Plus a few clothing boutiques where you can shop too!  There''s also Tops Supermarket and upcoming bowling lane + arcade.  Lots of parking space."
> **- Peachy (5/5/5)**

> "A spacious, open area with a relaxed atmosphere, free from crowds. The design embraces nature, featuring plenty of wood, glass, and greenery. There are cafés and restaurants offering food and drinks, with cozy corners perfect for unwinding. Unlike large shopping malls, it remains peaceful and ideal for those who appreciate tranquility. Convenient parking makes it a great spot to spend quality time with family."
> **- Gavin Asavapatthasakul (5/5/5)**

> "Nicely located at Chaweng Beach Road, right across a very good hotel, Banana Fan Sea. It is very new and just had a soft opening on 11 Dec 2024. Not all the shops are open. On the day we went: Tops, Le Bistro a French restaurant, Quicksilver, Luxoptics, 69 Slam, an art gallery, money exchange booth, and a few more shops were open. The design of the mall is very nice and beautiful. I like the way they design the second floor and the 4 buildings weaving together nicely with a large open space in the middle. Very clever and inspiring design. Well done!"
> **- The Humble World Trotter (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/haven-samui-community-mall-1.jpg','082 898 1111','888 หมู่ 2 ถนนเลียบหาดเฉวง ตำบล บ่อผุด Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://havensamui.com/','["Monday: 7:30 AM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 7:30 AM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 7:30 AM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 7:30 AM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 7:30 AM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 7:30 AM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 7:30 AM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.808+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.808+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/haven-samui-community-mall-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/haven-samui-community-mall-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=580952170727855030',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('hd-visa','standard','cmr07iglg00bsq8xdi6cs5gk2','HD Visa','## Top Reviews
> "We were referred to Herbert and I''m very glad we were. He is a professional, straight talking gentleman that knows his stuff. His assistant Crystal is equally knowledgeable and both speak English, German and who knows how many other languages. A long standing business with excellent credentials."
> **- Mac Williams (5/5/5)**

> "UPDATE JUNE 2024  Another great journey from Herbert & Company.  A couple of points, for those who like to leave negative reviews.  1. HDVisa under Herbert’s leadership are trying to be as efficient as possible, dealing with and ultimately helping thousands of people. It may not be as convenient for us, but if he insists that coming to the office is the most effective way to serve/inform us, then that’s just the way it is. His house, his rules.  2. We should all learn to be quiet and patient. You are wasting his time, when you interrupt with questions. He has heard every question and scenario over the years. Let him say and do what he needs to, then ask at the end, after you have listened to and read all the provided information.  Yes, Herbert can be short and strict with people. If you are fussy about food, bring your own. If you can’t follow his instructions and rules, find another company.  At the end of the day, it’s the results that matter, not making friends and having a party.  I probably saved 2 hours and enjoyed a trip where there were no drunks, no addicts having medical emergencies, people rudely demanding additional washroom and cigarette breaks, a proper speed boat, not a slow long tail, fast track service and made a earlier ferry home.  We were never rushed, but we were on a precise and timed schedule, which is what so many people have a problem with.  Responding to group chats is crucial, not for “likes”, but acknowledgment of information, to ensure no one is left behind and if they are, it’s their own fault!  If you can’t handle Herbert, then this isn’t the service for you and I’m good with that, because it means I won’t be stuck next to you!🤣  I have used other services, so I can fairly compare, HDVisa is the premium service and always my first choice.  🙏  🇹🇭🇹🇭🇹🇭🇹🇭🇲🇾🇲🇾🇲🇾🇲🇾🇲🇲🇲🇲🇲🇲🇲🇲  I don’t know what some of the negative reviews are talking about. Herbert is experienced, knowledgeable and actually has a great sense of humour. What he doesn’t have a tolerance for, is stupidity, people that can’t, or won’t follow simple directions and jeopardize their fellow passengers and schedule.  A smooth operation, that completely took any stress out of the process.  Thank you Herbert, drivers and the rest of the staff, for one more reason to love and be able to stay in Thailand!  🙏"
> **- dollar bill (5/5/5)**

> "HORRIBLE SERVICE - УЖАСНЫЙ СЕРВИС  I just want to warn people about the HORRIBLE SERVICE I received from a guy with a ponytail.  The guy was rude, impatient and very angry. And THE ONLY REASON I SEE IS HIS DISLIKE OF RUSSIAN PEOPLE because I didn''t do anything wrong.  I always go the extra mile with my kindness and politeness knowing that Russians can be a bit challenging.  I was very polite and courteous: I greeted I smiled and I asked about the visa run service. He initially said they don''t have anything available, then he mentioned my nationality, then he dropped a paper in front of me to read, I didn''t even have time to read he increased his voice on me and I politely asked to be friendly.  I DID NOT USE RUDE WORDS, neither did I increased my voice or BEHAVE IN A WAY THAT COULD HURT ANYONE. It is my polite request that was his reason to tell the staff to not sell me anything.  Now, I understand that could have a bad day with a customer from Russia before me but that doesn''t give him the right to take it on me. I want people to beware of this business.  I highly recommend Samui Visa Run service as they are very kind, very polite and very helpful. I will use them from now on."
> **- Russ Svoboda (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hd-visa-1.jpg','077 420 747','359, B, 5, Tambon Taling Ngam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'https://hdvisa-thailand.com/','["Monday: 9:30 AM – 12:00 PM, 1:30 – 4:30 PM","Tuesday: 9:30 AM – 12:00 PM, 1:30 – 4:30 PM","Wednesday: 9:30 AM – 12:00 PM, 1:30 – 4:30 PM","Thursday: 9:30 AM – 12:00 PM","Friday: 9:30 AM – 12:00 PM, 1:30 – 4:30 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifu0000zq8xdvll5tv7z','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.812+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.812+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hd-visa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hd-visa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6490790128459058697',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('health-lab','standard','cmr07igll00btq8xd9tzgsh7s','Health Lab','## Top Reviews
> "Good facilities, nice staff and food at the cafe was great too. The space is a bit small and the cleanliness of the cold water pool could be improved."
> **- Frank KA (4/5/5)**

> "The herbal steam room is fantastic. The place is beautiful, shady, and has such a relaxing vibe. A perfect spot to unwind."
> **- Chanyanin Kasinakaunggoon (4/5/5)**

> "The sauna and ice bath were great. However, the music was trashy, and there was a noticeable smell of people smoking weed. The place also seems very anti-children. We went with our 2-year-old daughter, and it was clear she was not welcome. If you are parents looking to enjoy quality time focused on health and wellness, I suggest Luuma in Lamai."
> **- Issana (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/health-lab-1.jpg','063 073 7888','141, 251, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://healthlabthailand.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.817+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.817+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/health-lab-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/health-lab-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2551774100665599906',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('health-oasis-resort','standard','cmr07igln00buq8xdwpm82i1w','Health Oasis Resort','## Top Reviews
> "I’m completing my stay at Health Oasis Resort in Ko Samui, Thailand, and overall I had a very positive experience. The detox program was well structured, and from the beginning the staff explained each step clearly, so I always knew what to expect. They also provided a printed schedule with the hours and instructions, which made it easy to follow the program each day.  One thing I really appreciated was the level of support. If I needed anything, someone was always available to help, and the support staff were consistently kind, attentive, and encouraging. That made the whole experience feel much more comfortable and manageable.  The atmosphere was peaceful and ideal for anyone looking to focus on health, rest, and resetting both physically and mentally. I would recommend Health Oasis Resort to anyone looking for a supportive wellness and detox retreat in Ko Samui."
> **- Vic (5/5/5)**

> "My 28-Day Reset at Health Oasis – Koh Samui  Completing the 28-day program at Health Oasis was truly one of the best gifts I have ever given myself. From the moment I arrived, I felt completely supported. The staff were incredibly attentive, always checking in and making sure I was comfortable and cared for throughout the entire journey.  The setting itself is simply breathtaking. Waking up to the beach right on your doorstep, watching the most spectacular sunsets each evening, and being surrounded by such tranquility created the perfect environment to truly reset both body and mind.  This retreat gave me the rest I didn’t even realise I needed. Being able to slow down, focus on my health, and allow my body to cleanse and recover was an incredible experience. Over the 28 days I lost 7 kilos, but more importantly I feel clean, rejuvenated, and reconnected with myself.  Health Oasis is more than just a retreat — it’s a place where you can step away from the noise of everyday life and give your body and mind the reset they deserve.  I’m deeply grateful for the care, the peaceful environment, and the transformation I experienced during my stay."
> **- Private (5/5/5)**

> "I recently completed a 20-day detox here.  It was a transformative experience. The beachfront setting is beautiful and calming, perfect for focusing on health. The detox program was well-structured, with vitamins and nutrients that kept hunger away, making the process manageable, though not without challenges. Detox can leave you feeling tired and affect your mood or sleep, so it’s not exactly a vacation, but the results are worth it—I lost 12 kg! The staff were fantastic—professional, supportive, and always approachable. Nicola and Eva, the health managers, were incredibly caring and attentive, ensuring I felt secure throughout. The hotel manager, Tik, and the entire team were very kind, always ready to help with a smile. Many guests I met were returning customers, which speaks about the quality of this place. I recommend it to anyone looking to prioritize their health. After the detox, I’d suggest taking time to explore Thailand—it’s an amazing place."
> **- Daniel Cohen (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/health-oasis-resort-1.jpg','077 602 096','26/4 Moo 6, ตำบล แม่น้ำ Maenam, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.healthoasisresort.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifs1000cq8xdfo2aau32','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.819+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.819+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/health-oasis-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/health-oasis-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3387265984902459974',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('health-retreat-samui','standard','cmr07iglp00bvq8xd2pn70pi3','Health Retreat Samui','## Top Reviews
> "I have just finished an 8 day detox health cleanse and I am feeling fantastic. Under the knowledgeable, caring, skilled, guidance of Dr Manta, this is a brilliant program. Dr Manta brings many years of education and experience and has created a program that has loads of health benefits. I will be back next year for this health and energy boost. Thanks Dr Manta"
> **- Susan G (5/5/5)**

> "As an acupuncturist on vacation, I was looking for TCM practitioner for self-care, and I’m so grateful my friend referred me to Dr. Manta! She and her Thai health massage colleague Lek were both very caring and knowledgeable therapists, treating my neck and back stiffness during my week on Samui (I stayed nearby, not on-site). I highly recommend them for anyone looking for expert holistic healthcare. I’ll certainly be back next time I visit!"
> **- W L (5/5/5)**

> "It was a great experience to make the detox 5 days Massage was really good. Detox Not easy to do . The room have to be better. Lot of things are broken or not OK in the bungalow. Beach not far but the Programm is really hard when you make it for the first time. For my body it s was enough 5 days... I wait for feeling all the benefits beacuse I a m really..... Empty and tired"
> **- Sophie Lecoq (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/health-retreat-samui-1.jpg','081 891 8607','32, 10 Moo 6 Soi 3, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.healthretreatsamui.com/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifs1000cq8xdfo2aau32','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.821+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.821+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/health-retreat-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/health-retreat-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16815280335366523772',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('heart-shape-mountain-seaview','standard','cmr07iglr00bwq8xdklbt7z5m','Heart Shape Mountain Seaview','## Top Reviews
> "Excellent place, abit remote, you need to take right route, follow heart shape view signage on the road and it will take you to the location. Once you reach there, the view and ambiance will take your breath away! The owner is friendly and food there was good. A must try is their fresh coconut, its chilled and coconut water is just amazing. I highly recommend to visit in noon time. Kids friendly place, swings, tents, place to run and have fun."
> **- Purav Desai (5/5/5)**

> "Woow! Just go! Beatiful!"
> **- Nina Rönn (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing Views. Less touristy then other view points. Probably because its up a windy road. 100 Baht entry, but you get a free soft drink. Very enjoyable."
> **- Robbie McCann (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/heart-shape-mountain-seaview-1.jpg','099 496 1888','Unnamed Road Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/heartshapesamui/','["Monday: 10:30 AM – 6:30 PM","Tuesday: 10:30 AM – 6:30 PM","Wednesday: 10:30 AM – 6:30 PM","Thursday: 10:30 AM – 6:30 PM","Friday: 10:30 AM – 6:30 PM","Saturday: 10:30 AM – 6:30 PM","Sunday: 10:30 AM – 6:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig5c0051q8xdykrbexft','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.823+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.823+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/heart-shape-mountain-seaview-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/heart-shape-mountain-seaview-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4611596908646851573',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('heaven-samui','standard','cmr07iglt00bxq8xdhfu2wbb4','Heaven Samui','## Top Reviews
> "Today''s very enjoyable HEAVEN tour. Snorkeling and diving are a must-do course. Jet ski and sofa board are also very good."
> **- samui koh (5/5/5)**

> "Samui Island''s Best Pleasure. It''s like a must-see tour before you die. Skin scuba diving is so fun and the island is so beautiful. Be careful not to get bitten by a pig on pig island. Heaven Floating Tour is the best. Fighting!!"
> **- 김종진 (5/5/5)**

> "Very nice to see the happy elephants around while i am eating. Very beautiful place so relaxing"
> **- Jum cox (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/heaven-samui-1.jpg','099 360 3222','717, 19 Tambon, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.heavensamui.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.825+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.825+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/heaven-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/heaven-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16334665958421251826',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('here-slow-bar-coffee','standard','cmr07iglv00byq8xdipo2rmrw','HERE Slow Bar Coffee','## Top Reviews
> "Had a wonderful breakfast experience at Here Coffee and Eatery. The food was fresh, beautifully presented, and absolutely delicious.  If you''re looking for a great coffee spot and breakfast destination in Ko Samui, this place is definitely worth a visit.  Highly recommended for anyone who appreciates quality coffee, delicious food, and a thoughtfully designed space.  Will definitely be back."
> **- Simona Horňáček (5/5/5)**

> "The menu was very complete, had various options to pick from. The service was amazing they were very kind and helpful. We come a lot to samui and we have never had a better place. They served the coffee really fast and was delicious. We were very satisfied and will come again for sure! 🧙🏼🪄🔮 ขอบคุณค่ะ"
> **- Patri B. (5/5/5)**

> "Had a perfect breakfast, nothing to be desired. Food, drink incredibly delicious. The boss and the staff are all extremely nice and attentive. I eat there every day. The food actually looks like the pictures on the menu. Warm recommendation!"
> **- Pia (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/here-slow-bar-coffee-1.jpg','062 414 4488','4169, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/share/1F1ZHWqPvL/?mibextid=wwXIfr','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.827+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.827+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/here-slow-bar-coffee-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/here-slow-bar-coffee-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10781977240941600937',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('hi-samui-hostel','standard','cmr07iglx00bzq8xdt9shjhuv','Hi Samui Hostel','## Top Reviews
> "Loved this place! Bagged a bed in a dorm for an incredibly affordable price (less than £6 a night!) and was amazed by the cleanliness and anemeties on offer. The workers here are fabulous and very accommodating, especially the intern who was working there. He was so friendly and attentive and was able to help me despite the language barrier. Really impressed!"
> **- Nepheli K (5/5/5)**

> "Peaceful, well-equipped place with the option to eat on-site; located in Choeng Mon near restaurants and the beach. The staff is lovely and attentive. I will gladly return."
> **- Dominique Veron (5/5/5)**

> "I had a lovely time here! I wish I stayed for longer. A very chill hostel and location, but great vibes! I loved the free pool table and really great food and cocktails too! Lovely staff and just all round great place to stay! Short walk to beach, as well as other restaurants and massage spas."
> **- Lara Smith (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hi-samui-hostel-1.jpg','094 201 0264','Hi Samui Hostel 10/20-21 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'http://hisamuihostel.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifsv000nq8xdrwnu123q','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.829+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.829+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hi-samui-hostel-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hi-samui-hostel-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=463367882877490865',NULL,NULL);
