> "Come the authentic Thai coffee shop open tomorrow HIGH SIAM"
> **- koh Ai Solution (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/high-siam-1.jpg','062 898 6646','80 29 หมู่ที่ 1 ซอย ลานทอง Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/share/15cBzUrwh6/?mibextid=wwXIfr','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 4:00 PM, 5:00 – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 4:00 PM, 5:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 4:00 PM, 5:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 4:00 PM, 5:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 4:00 PM, 5:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 4:00 PM, 5:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.831+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.831+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/high-siam-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/high-siam-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7664115535992281012',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('highland-paradise','standard','cmr07igm100c1q8xdyfphjpj2','Highland Paradise','## Top Reviews
> "It''s an amazing place with friendly staff and the best view we''ve come across on the entire island. The food was very tasty and there is a lot of dishes to choose from. You can also veganize some dishes if you ask (e.g. replace meat with tofu). The price performance ratio is also very good. We ordered like half a dozen dishes so of course that adds up :-)"
> **- Not Sure (5/5/5)**

> "This is the best dinner we had on Koh Samui, hands down. The food was so so delicious and at typical local prices. But on top of that, the service was so attentive and the view was spectacular. There''s also a giant swing onsite, chickens, parrots. So much to see! Treat yourself to the delight of dining here."
> **- Falina Stack (5/5/5)**

> "Wow, what a view. Food was amazing and so was the cocktails. The restaurant wasn’t over crowded but not empty either. Very good place if you want to eat and enjoy a beautiful view without it being over priced and over crowded."
> **- Nicolai Olesen (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/highland-paradise-1.jpg','061 502 0498','55/60, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/highlandparadisekohsamui?mibextid=LQQJ4d','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig5c0051q8xdykrbexft','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.833+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.833+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/highland-paradise-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/highland-paradise-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=102746918726122163',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('hippos-gym','standard','cmr07igm300c2q8xd0x3q34gu','Hippo''s Gym','## Top Reviews
> "Pros: - Equipped with all the machines you need, surpassing the typical hotel gym. - Cool vibes and affordable prices, plus it''s not crowded.  Cons: - The heat can be intense; best to train in the morning. - Uneven flooring can be noticeable during heavy squat or deadlift sessions. - Machines and weights often have grease on them; a warning sign or notification would be helpful. While greasing machines is understandable for an open-air gym, a heads-up would have been appreciated."
> **- Alberto Centioni (4/5/5)**

> "Lovely, authentic and special gym with open walls and fans. Friendly personnel, you get a towel and price is only 100 baht. Applied a little and was able to do all the moves in my training program. I definitely recommend this place. Must experience."
> **- Marjo Heikka (5/5/5)**

> "Very nice gym, affordable (100 baht per day), with good equipment and great vibes. I definitely recommend it.  Keep in mind that it’s an outdoor gym, so you should definitely wear insect repellent."
> **- Vladimir Miletic (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hippos-gym-1.jpg','084 119 8049','HXFR+892, Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/p/Hippos-Gym-100054480459577/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifuo0015q8xdfahzrsp4','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.835+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.835+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hippos-gym-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hippos-gym-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3919298688605126481',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('hl-rent-cars-bikes','standard','cmr07igm500c3q8xdil68zyl8','HL Rent Cars & Bikes','## Top Reviews
> "We rented a 125cc scooter for five days. Everything went smoothly, quickly, and easily. Unfortunately, I fell once while starting off and caused some minor damage. No problem, I was happy to pay for the damage in a reasonable manner, as I am ultimately responsible. However, I disagree with the final damage bill. They are charging me for replacing parts that I''m quite certain will never be replaced. Additionally, they charged me 200 baht for delivery, which never took place. We picked up and returned the scooter ourselves on foot. All in all, I feel cheated and ripped off at the end of the rental period. There''s no way this repair is worth 1300 baht. See attached photos. The scooter itself was in good condition and didn''t let us down. The staff is reserved and seems very bored and not very friendly."
> **- Alexandros Orfanidis (3/5/5)**

> "Hello, I would like to express my complete dissatisfaction with the experience of renting three motorbikes from your shop.  From the very first day, we faced serious and dangerous problems: 1.	On my motorbike, the screws on the exhaust were missing, causing the exhaust to constantly bounce up and down during every ride. Besides being extremely annoying, it was also very unsafe. 2.	My friend’s motorbike had a dead battery, which you fixed once, but the very next day it failed again and left him stranded in the middle of the road. This clearly shows a lack of proper maintenance and technical inspection. 3.	The third motorbike was missing a screw from the axle, which caused my friend to slip and fall. This is not just negligence — it is a serious safety issue and could have resulted in a much worse accident.  Additionally, your overall behavior was disappointing. You did not respond promptly, you did not show willingness to help, and you insisted that the motorbikes were “new”, while in reality they were in terrible and dangerous condition.  Such an experience is unacceptable, especially when dealing with vehicles used by tourists who rely on your professionalism and reliability. I hope you take our feedback seriously so that no one else has to go through a similar situation."
> **- Manolis Alimanis (1/5/5)**

> "The best rental place and experience I had in Thailand. Brand new, well maintained motorcycles. I had a brand new 300cc Yamaha Zeus with LED headlights. Great service, free helmet choice, very good prices! I would 100% recommend."
> **- Lorenz (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hl-rent-cars-bikes-1.jpg','080 692 4740','10/80 Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://hl-rent.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifui0012q8xdzn158clv','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.837+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.837+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hl-rent-cars-bikes-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hl-rent-cars-bikes-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16248739367297789959',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('hm','standard','cmr07igm700c4q8xd6n9qmiod','H&M','## Top Reviews
> "I used to visit H&M at least once every month, and every experience before today was smooth and pleasant. But what I faced today was honestly shocking and extremely disappointing because of one lady staff member named Ploy, whose shift started around 3:30 PM.  When I was paying for my items, she asked whether I had a membership card. I said yes and immediately showed the barcode from my phone, but she completely ignored it and only asked for my phone number. Without properly checking anything, she quickly printed the receipt and handed me the change.  After that, I asked about my birthday discount because this month is my birthday month, and according to the membership benefits explained during registration — as well as the advertisement shown in my H&M app — I should receive a 15% discount.  However, she looked like she had absolutely no idea about it and did not even try to listen to my explanation. Her attitude was very rude and disrespectful. While I was talking to her, she kept turning to chat with her colleagues instead of paying attention to me as a customer.  A few minutes later, one of her colleagues told me that I needed to wait 15 minutes for a refund process. So we stood there in front of the counter waiting, but nobody cared, nobody updated us, and not a single person apologized for the inconvenience even they are not busy, not many customers just me and my friend stood in front of counter . It honestly felt like we were invisible.  I have been a loyal customer of H&M for a long time, which is why this experience hurt even more. I never expected to be treated with such disrespect and carelessness. Today’s experience was not only inconvenient, but also extremely upsetting and disappointing.Finally, she didn’t say total amount and total me that look at this amount at scan with (her own language). Even I’m not Thai. That why I believe that she just assists EUROPE people happily😂😂😂. #one star for this kind of staff ."
> **- Wai Zin Phyo (1/5/5)**

> "I am extremely disappointed with my experience at H&M Central Chaweng.  The day before my purchase, I clearly saw a promotion for 10 pieces of underwear for 500 THB, displayed together as a set. When I returned the next day to buy the last remaining set, the display had become messy and the items had been separated into groups of 8 and 2, with no clear indication that they were no longer part of the same promotion.  I selected all 10 pieces based on the promotion and went to the cashier, only to be told that the total was around 1,400 THB. When I asked for an explanation, I was told that only 8 pieces were included in the promotion and that the other 2 pieces cost an additional 500 THB. This made no sense, especially when the receipt still showed the items grouped as a 10-piece set.  What disappointed me most was not just the price difference, but the lack of clear organization and communication. Customers should not have to discover hidden conditions only at the checkout after spending time shopping. If promotional items can be mixed up so easily, staff should ensure that displays are checked regularly and clearly labeled.  This experience was frustrating, confusing, and left me feeling misled. I expected much better from H&M."
> **- Dena Rose (1/5/5)**

> "Suggest double checking your bill after paying. With multiple reminders to the cashier to check on my item prices, she pretended to check (obviously did not want to go through the proper process & hassle, and hoping that I would not check my receipt). I did check right after she handed me my items, and surprise, the prices were wrong. It took my nerve and my 30 mins to cancel the entire transaction, and another cashier had to re-scan everything and re-do everything from the start. What I don’t understand is, why just not do it once properly? I have a small child and my husband waiting, why go the extra mile to cause inconvenience? Just mind blowing. To the cashier with curly hair, if you are reading this please respect people’s time and money, do a proper job for your future customers. Thanks"
> **- Haku Nam (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hm-1.jpg',NULL,'1st Floor, No.209,209/1-209/2, Borpud Sub-district, อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.hm.com/th?utm_source=google_location&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=TH0011','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.839+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.839+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hm-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hm-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=122337507918559196',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('holiday-inn-essence-bar-lounge','standard','cmr07igm900c5q8xdce175vxc','Holiday Inn Essence Bar & Lounge','## Top Reviews
> "I want to start off saying how incredible the welcoming hospitality was of the breakfast host! Het name is Som O, and her warm smile first thing in the morning really made my day. Incredibly sweet and professional, a real asset for the hotel! The food was really good, lots of choices for everyone and also largely catered to the little ones. Maybe to keep the flavour palette open to kids, the flavours were less bold and prominent than you would expect in Thailand but I totally understand they don’t want to set the kid’s mouth on fire. The atmosphere is really good, beautiful new style of the Holiday Inn. However, there are a lot of kids. Which we could’ve expected it being a kids paradise, but for a couple without kids it was a little overwhelming at times. For the  Holiday Inn formula this was definitely the best breakfast we ever had."
> **- Damy Kok (5/5/5)**

> "Nana and Pao and Natty and Thata serving us in the restaurant  were amazing. We loved them so much. They are so friendly and feel like family. X is the best bar tender and makes AMAZING thai tea. Nong and Pom and Mike make such tasty food. The best in Ko Samui! We can''t wait to come back here. 11 stars! ❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️"
> **- Lola Jitendra (5/5/5)**

> "Food takes wayyy too long here. Tried it 1 time not coming back."
> **- Anoer Ilahi (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/holiday-inn-essence-bar-lounge-1.jpg','077 951 777','8888 Moo.1 Bophut Sub-District, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/essencesamui/','["Monday: 7:00 – 10:00 AM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.841+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.841+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/holiday-inn-essence-bar-lounge-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/holiday-inn-essence-bar-lounge-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12059285358589811135',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('holiday-inn-family-fun','standard','cmr07igmc00c6q8xd87slbcfg','Holiday Inn Family Fun','## Top Reviews
> "We had the most wonderful one-week stay at this fantastic family resort, and we truly couldn’t have asked for a better experience.  What impressed us the most was the Kids Club. The entire team was incredibly warm, professional, and genuinely dedicated. A special thank you goes to Annie and Namfon, who took exceptional care of our little one (1y). We always felt completely comfortable and confident knowing she was in such loving and capable hands. The daily program was creative, engaging, and varied — there was something exciting happening every single day. We also really appreciated that the Kids Club was cleaned thoroughly for an hour every day, which gave us great peace of mind.  The hotel grounds and rooms are beautiful, modern, and extremely well maintained. Everything was spotless and thoughtfully designed. The pools are fantastic and perfect for families, and the breakfast was good with plenty of choice to start the day right. All staff members throughout the hotel were exceptionally friendly, attentive, and always eager to help.  For us, the week truly could not have been more perfect. We wholeheartedly recommend this hotel to any family with little kids looking for a relaxing and joyful vacation experience. We would return without hesitation!"
> **- Sibylle Z (5/5/5)**

> "Where should I start? I have never seen such a disappointing hotel as the Holiday Inn Bophut.  We arrived at the hotel around 10:00 AM and, of course, we understood that check-in would only be available from 3:00 PM. My mother wanted to drink some water, which is something that is normally available in a hotel lobby. However, she was told to go to the nearby 7-Eleven and buy some water herself.  Nevertheless, we were able to check in around 12:00 PM.  The rooms are extremely noisy. Guests were playing loud music in their rooms until around 11:00 PM, and there were even people playing football nearby. It was impossible to get a peaceful night’s sleep.  The breakfast service was an absolute disaster. The staff seemed overwhelmed all the time, especially the lady standing at the entrance every day, asking for room numbers. She has a long ponytail and wears a headset. Every single day, only we were told at 10:30 AM that we should go to the buffet because it was about to close. The buffet officially closes at 11:00 AM. It felt like they simply wanted to clean everything up early and get rid of the guests.  The breakfast selection was exactly the same every day, with very little variety.  The pool is far too small for the number of guests staying at the hotel. There are also far too few sunbeds both around the pool and on the beach. There are only eight beach loungers available in total.  So think carefully before spending this much money on this hotel. There are much better hotels in Chaweng, and Chaweng Beach is also far more beautiful.  The beach in Bophut is very unattractive, full of seaweed and algae. The stones are large and rough, making it uncomfortable and even painful to walk into the water.  The only positive thing about this hotel is the Fisherman’s Village right next door.  Overall, this hotel is definitely not worth the price we paid, and I would not stay here ."
> **- Matrushka Sawoya (1/5/5)**

> "Recently stayed for 6 nights. Amazing hotel for adults and kids. The kids club, pools, slides, gym are all amazing. We went to the Circus one night which the kids loved. Our room was amazing, and the cleaners were 11/10. The only thing we would change is the location of the pilates / yoga. It is on the grass outside where people are eating breakfast, so not the best spot for quietness. Other than this, we couldn''t fault the Holiday Inn at Koh Samui. Lots of great restaurants nearby, and the night markets are great too."
> **- Elliot Lynch (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/holiday-inn-family-fun-1.jpg','077 951 777','ตำบล บ่อผุด Bophut สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.ihg.com/holidayinnresorts/hotels/us/en/koh-samui/usmrt/hoteldetail?cm_mmc=GoogleMaps-_-RS-_-TH-_-USMRT',NULL,'cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.844+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.844+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/holiday-inn-family-fun-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/holiday-inn-family-fun-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9021251202137941484',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('holiday-inn-lazy-coconut','standard','cmr07igme00c7q8xdqommxovm','Holiday Inn Lazy Coconut','## Top Reviews
> "We had great time enjoying this bar Many drinks and food with fair prices The team is very nice and always smiling The managers are always asking you if everything is good Thank you for Rum,Sam,Fresh,Nat for everything"
> **- idan (5/5/5)**

> "Ordered pizza to eat by the pool with the family. About a 20 minute wait but we were lying by the pool anyway.  The fried food and pizzas were great quality and worth the price and convinence"
> **- Johnny Nguyen (5/5/5)**

> "This is a great bar if you’re a guest at the hotel, especially happy hour. They are very heavy handed with the alcohol. We stayed at the hotel for two nights and had a great time at this bar. Will return for sure."
> **- Shivangi Ganatra (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/holiday-inn-lazy-coconut-1.jpg','077 951 777','8888 Beach Road, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.4,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.846+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.846+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/holiday-inn-lazy-coconut-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/holiday-inn-lazy-coconut-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16140048862798447370',NULL,NULL);
