INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('home-art-tattoo','standard','cmr07igmi00c9q8xdatp6tbeq','Home Art Tattoo','## Top Reviews
> "Mr.Kit is lovely and single man. I recommend a good tattoo shop in Lamai Beach... Well done. tattoo work and massage. Both services I am impressed."
> **- Alan McCready (5/5/5)**

> "Messaged Mr Kit before I arrived in Koh Samui and then again when I arrived each time I got a prompt response. Arranged a meeting to discuss the tattoo I wanted and expressed that I would like a Bamboo tattoo rather than a machine. Having booked in I then had the most amazing experience. Mr Kit is a very humble, personable, friendly and talented artist. I couldn’t have wished for a more professional and fantastic tattoo all done in a traditional style. It is an experience that I will never forget and a permanent reminder of a wonderful trip and a fantastic artist. Thank you Mr Kit for the memories made and if you are here on the island and need a tattoo then this is the place to go!"
> **- Jonny ''Dynamite'' Maynard (5/5/5)**

> "20/12/2025- I spent 3 days exploring different types of meditation working on breath work and being still. Very good experience. Amazing meditations & massage. Was even taken out to the waterfall to practice some of the breathwork we had explored the days before. Thank you for your guidance. Has helped with pain, posture and my breathwork. Thank you for your blessing and taking me to the temple. Definitely come check out MR Kit shop you will not be disappointed by the tailored experience! See you again soon :)"
> **- lukki lashley (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/home-art-tattoo-1.jpg','062 829 8889','124, 530 M.3 Thanon Had Lamai, Tambon Maret, Koh Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/Home-Art-Tattoo-Lamai-Beach-952065144951207/','["Monday: 5:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 5:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 5:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 5:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 5:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 5:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 5:00 PM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.850+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.850+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/home-art-tattoo-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/home-art-tattoo-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4754997726434113680',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('homemade-burgers-sandwiches','standard','cmr07igml00caq8xdcbjutj9b','Homemade Burgers & Sandwiches','## Top Reviews
> "Really good food! Can especially recommend their iced mocha coffee, so delicious.  The staff are very friendly."
> **- Patrick Kongsbak (5/5/5)**

> "Such a vibey atmosphere with the music. The burger was delicious. The bun was so fresh. The vegetarian and the meat burger perfectly cooked. The vegetarian burger had so much flavour. I love how the menu gives the option of having fries the the burger for more money or without fries for less money. The servers were super friendly and the food came out fast. There are also so many drinks available."
> **- April VanKirk (5/5/5)**

> "Homemade Burgers & Sandwiches is one of our must-visit places, while on Koh Samui. The food is terrific, staff is extremely nice and attentive and the ambience with all the little huts with tables in the garden is great! We have tried more or less everything on the menu - from starters to main courses and Thai dishes. Everything is great, an experience!"
> **- Silvio Wolf (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/homemade-burgers-sandwiches-1.jpg','085 788 4162','34/3 แม่น้ำ หมู่ที่ 5, ตำบล แม่น้ำ อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://restaurantsnapshot.com/Homemade_Burgers_and_Sandwiches/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 9:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifso000kq8xdfe9gpaon','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.853+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.853+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/homemade-burgers-sandwiches-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/homemade-burgers-sandwiches-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16297529583035141315',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('homestay-samui','standard','cmr07igmm00cbq8xdy17lz9wc','Homestay Samui','## Top Reviews
> "Homestay Samui is really one of the most  unique accommodations i’ve ever had the chance to experience. It’s a slightly remote location, in the heart of nature. The bamboo cottage is very clean and has everything that you need for your stay and it’s surrounded by plants, but also very well protected against mosquitoes and other small visitors 😀. The hosts are so friendly, helpful and try to cater to your needs as much as possible. The garden is also so beautiful, especially the back area where you can see the river. I really enjoyed our time here and I think it’s definitely a lovely experience to have on the busy island of Koh Samui. Thank you to the lovely hosts for making our stay so enjoyable! 🤩"
> **- Raluca Cozma (5/5/5)**

> "Tip top"
> **- Ingo Germer (5/5/5)**

> "Good food, cool staff...🤣🤣"
> **- Roger Champoud (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/homestay-samui-1.jpg','098 049 5956','1, 1, Tambon Na Mueang, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.homestaysamui.com/?fbclid=PAQ0xDSwMADfxleHRuA2FlbQIxMQABp9e1yjWUPcCM0ZiJCZW6njD2BcgiA656BYc1-sPnq1P1NniVn4NWkRfDudUQ_aem_hBZW24Y635bNAiQf5Pv9gQ',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ig4i004oq8xdv207xuh2','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.854+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.854+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/homestay-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/homestay-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10040147746453476655',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('homm-chura','standard','cmr07igmo00ccq8xd0yev9o83','Homm Chura','## Top Reviews
> "Our stay at the hotel was fantastic and we truly enjoyed the entire experience. The level of service was excellent, and the staff were always friendly, helpful, and professional.  The food was very good with a nice selection of dishes, and everything we tried was fresh and tasty. The hotel facilities were also impressive and well maintained, making it easy to enjoy everything the hotel has to offer.  The rooms were great – very clean, comfortable, and well designed. It was clear that a lot of care goes into keeping the rooms in excellent condition.  We also had a great experience when one of our friends arrived before check-in time. Even though he came early, the staff did their best to accommodate him and were able to give him the room earlier, which was a really nice gesture.  We had a very pleasant stay and would definitely recommend this hotel to others."
> **- Dudu מתתיהו (5/5/5)**

> "The entire hotel experience was incredible, starting with the amazing staff and all the facilities. Highly recommended! I would especially like to thank Kitty for keeping my room on point, extremely clean, and all her kindness. And also Pope, who is lovely and very kind. She has an easy smile. People like these make the whole experience even more special. Thank you for everything and for providing me with the best experience this week. A big thank you from the Azores Islands (Portugal)."
> **- Rodrigo Lopes (5/5/5)**

> "Best hotel I’ve ever stayed in. Never had a pool that close to the beach before. Very tranquil. Rooms are lovely, I love the traditional feeling and the concrete bathrooms. Me and my husband absolutely adore Kitty, who cleaned our room and looked after us during our stay. Close to a 711 and easy walk to all amenities. Highly recommend!"
> **- Lewis Hickman (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/homm-chura-1.jpg','077 915 100','99, 9, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.hommhotels.com/hotels/homm-chura-samui',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.856+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.856+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/homm-chura-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/homm-chura-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11392917854263115938',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('honda-motorcycle-dealer','standard','cmr07igmq00cdq8xd6iq5mxg3','Honda Motorcycle Dealer','## Top Reviews
> "I’ve always had great service from here. I speak Thai, so maybe I can explain my requirements a little better. It is a Thai business primarily for Thai people, not a holiday rental store, so maybe don’t expect Disneyland if you rock up with no shirt and a bottle of Chang beer 😂"
> **- Malcolm Swaine (5/5/5)**

> "Try to get service is impossible. Attitude absolutely disrespectful to foreign person. Gave my bike away to Thai friend. Will never buy Honda again in Thailand. Hard to believe Honda company allows this type of thing to happen."
> **- Rocko (1/5/5)**

> "The service guys really need to pay more attention to what they are doing, got my 12k service on my ADV 160 and left with more warning lights on than when I arrived."
> **- Michael F (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/honda-motorcycle-dealer-1.jpg','086 954 4739','163/2 ถ. ทวีราษฎร์ภักดี Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:00 AM – 5:30 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 5:30 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 5:30 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 5:30 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:30 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 5:30 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifui0012q8xdzn158clv','cmr07ig1h003iq8xdb1g9nifo','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.858+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.858+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/honda-motorcycle-dealer-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/honda-motorcycle-dealer-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10118368947798397435',NULL,NULL);
