INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('honey-tara-restaurant-bar','standard','cmr07igmu00cfq8xdvb0ruyia','Honey Tara Restaurant & Bar','## Top Reviews
> "Absolutely and amazing and quite place to enjoy your dinner. Most vegetables are organic from their own garden. Huge portion of food, tasty and well prepared. Staff really friendly and the atmosphere is like a family."
> **- M. L. STARK (5/5/5)**

> "Tara Bistro is a real little gem on Koh Samui. The atmosphere is relaxed and welcoming – the kind of place where you immediately feel like you’re exactly where you’re supposed to be.  The prawns were absolutely delicious: fresh, juicy, and full of flavor without any unnecessary fuss. You can really taste the quality. It’s simple food done exactly right – which, in my opinion, is much harder to find than fancy dishes. The rest of the menu also looked amazing, but honestly… after those prawns, it was hard to think about anything else!  The service was friendly and professional, with just the right balance between being attentive and giving you space to enjoy your evening. I had a great time and will definitely be coming back. If you’re looking for a place to enjoy great seafood in a relaxed setting, Tara Bistro should be high on your list.  And a little tip: order the prawns. Trust me – your future self will thank you!"
> **- Batty On Tour (5/5/5)**

> "Beautiful location in the hills. The grounds are quiet and peaceful. Great spot to have a lunch and cocktail."
> **- Timothy Murtland (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/honey-tara-restaurant-bar-1.jpg','098 822 9566','FX8P+69, Na Mueang, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.tarabistrosamui.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 8:30 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 8:30 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 8:30 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 8:30 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 8:30 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 8:30 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 8:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifv2001aq8xdag7cvjgf','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.862+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.862+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/honey-tara-restaurant-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/honey-tara-restaurant-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13234099709279400223',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('hot-point-express','standard','cmr07igmw00cgq8xdhaw3sz0f','Hot Point Express','## Top Reviews
> "First time in Koh Samui, I was trying to find a bike to rent and some middle eastern food, Found this place through social media and as the first place to come to I already know I''ve made the best choice, now I have a great strong bike and a full stomach, the service, food and location just makes this place an easy choice, was lucky to meet the owner he welcomed me and my wife very nicely, recommended on meals and every meal was a hit, next move was obvious... Saving this spot on my Google Maps as a favourite and my next gaol is to try every single meal in this menu!  Thanks for having me and giving an amazing service along with great food.  Highly recommended for anyone needing bikes & food!"
> **- Ronald Wisznia (5/5/5)**

> "Always very smiling staff, always very tasty food, as well as for dine in options as for delivery and self pick up. Come here really OFTEN. One of the best places opened till late. A lot of balanced and healthy options 💗 also best shawarma on island"
> **- Ana (5/5/5)**

> "I like how we can choose our own vegetables inside. Good service. Good atmosphere.  I also take out food once in a while and order it on food panda."
> **- Christie (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hot-point-express-1.jpg','091 034 4847','3 114 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://hotpointsamui.com/','["Monday: 1:00 PM – 3:00 AM","Tuesday: 1:00 PM – 3:00 AM","Wednesday: 1:00 PM – 3:00 AM","Thursday: 1:00 PM – 3:00 AM","Friday: 1:00 PM – 3:00 AM","Saturday: 1:00 PM – 3:00 AM","Sunday: 1:00 PM – 3:00 AM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.864+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.864+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hot-point-express-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hot-point-express-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10859222910474087416',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('house-of-lucie','standard','cmr07igmx00chq8xdwfbqbvhm','House Of Lucie','## Top Reviews
> "House of Lucie Samui has two floors with 3 artists’ works are being exhibited. Especially Steve Mccurry and James Nachtwey’s photography works are worth to visit to experience."
> **- Htoo Tay Zar (5/5/5)**

> "A stunning two-story art gallery set by a serene lotus lake.  The exhibitions change regularly, featuring both national masters and contemporary artists. On the second floor, you’ll find works by recent Lucie Awards honorees — world-renowned photographers.  They also host engaging and inspiring workshops. The staff are exceptionally attentive, and the owner is wonderfully friendly and welcoming! 🙏  A true hidden gem — definitely worth a visit!"
> **- Mark Avvakumov (5/5/5)**

> "Wonderful art gallery and craftwork The vibes is so peaceful, there you can unfold your creativity"
> **- Sebastien Hannoun (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/house-of-lucie-1.jpg','095 478 9987','2 23 หมู่ 2 Proo Na Mueang Rd, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://houseoflucie.org/','["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: Closed","Wednesday: 1:00 – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 1:00 – 6:00 PM","Friday: 1:00 – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 1:00 – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 1:00 – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ig4i004oq8xdv207xuh2','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.865+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.865+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/house-of-lucie-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/house-of-lucie-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6867801451999626101',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('house-of-suzy','standard','cmr07ign100ciq8xd850hxx0e','House Of Suzy','## Top Reviews
> "House of Suzy in Lamai is easily one of our favorite spots in Samui. This speakeasy-style bar has such a unique vibe, and every visit feels like a great night out waiting to happen.  The tapas are delicious, the cocktails are creative and perfectly crafted, and the overall atmosphere just pulls you in. We love coming here to eat, drink, and dance—it’s the kind of place where you can spend the whole evening without realizing how fast time flies.  The Chinese Deco interior is stunning and adds so much character to the space. The music is always on point, and they often have live performances that make the experience even more special.  If you’re in Samui and looking for somewhere with amazing food, drinks, and energy, this place is a must-visit. We’ll definitely keep coming back!"
> **- Zaza Meerveld (5/5/5)**

> "This is a great cocktail bar in Lamai that I highly recommend. They have a wide variety of cocktails, and I can tell you they''re delicious.👌"
> **- Me Coffee Slow bar (5/5/5)**

> "This is an absolute gem in the center of Lamai. Beautifully crafted cocktails? Check. Wonderful staff and people? Check. Top notch ambience? Check.  A little bit off the tourist track - which is great...! Perfect for those evenings where you want a bit of a chill and catch up with friends.  Hope they bring in live music at some point. :)"
> **- Jonathan Cheng (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/house-of-suzy-1.jpg',NULL,'Baan Lamai, 144, 24 ตำบล มะเร็ต อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.houseofsuzylamai.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.869+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.869+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/house-of-suzy-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/house-of-suzy-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1832531727962605057',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('hua-kati-cafe','standard','cmr07ign300cjq8xdtgzg6j1c','Hua Kati Cafe','## Top Reviews
> "We came across this place by chance and are so glad we did! The food was exceptional! When we first saw how nice the furniture and ambiance was, we expected the prices to be higher than they were! The portions were large, service was quick and friendly, and the vibe of the restaurant is very chill and quiet in the best way. Definitely worth coming to, especially if you’re headed to/from the pier. It was only about a 5-7 minute walk from the pier."
> **- Veronica West (5/5/5)**

> "Beautiful Location, amazing food & top service. Highly recommended, we''re very happy after dinner with fresh baracuda and and enjoyed it a lot! Thank you so much. Greez Mel & Jaz"
> **- Medusa Coconut (5/5/5)**

> "Stellar dining experience, our best on Samui. Lovely place with art and geckos decorating the walls. The food was delicious and well presented. The white snapper was barbequed perfectly and our pad se aw was bursting with chill and fresh vegetables. The owner was a lovely person, explained all the dishes and happy to change some set menu options for dietary needs. Definitely one to return to! ขอบคุณครับ🙏"
> **- David Aitch (tekrah) (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hua-kati-cafe-1.jpg','091 526 7213','แม่น้ำ Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://m.facebook.com/Hua-Kati-cafe-beach-bar-restaurant-636751243425029/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.871+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.871+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hua-kati-cafe-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hua-kati-cafe-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16187412886007485120',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('hug-samui','standard','cmr07ign500ckq8xd6sjkqdov','Hug Samui','## Top Reviews
> "Right on the beach with a lovely pool and restaurant. It doesn’t get more tranquil than being tucked into a humble villa amidst the luscious plant life just steps from the beach.  Friendly staff. Great service. Tasty food. Right by the pool or beach. Doesn’t get better than that. Enjoying my time with Hug Samui so much."
> **- jordan lento (5/5/5)**

> "Stopped by on our scooter for lunch! Everything was delicious! We had margarita pizza and some seafood apps next to the beach. The view was amazing We also tried the deep fried banana & pineapple with icecream and it so yummy! Our server Dear was great! Loved this place!"
> **- Alyssa Kelley (5/5/5)**

> "Excellent traditional oil massage in a beautiful beachfront location. Old-fashioned, authentic Thai massage performed with great skill and care. The therapist was very professional and the massage deeply relaxing. What makes this place special is the setting: a lovely swimming pool right by the sea, a calm atmosphere and a restaurant where you can relax before or after the treatment. A perfect spot to unwind and enjoy a complete wellness experience in Samui. Highly recommended."
> **- Luca Foschi (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hug-samui-1.jpg','064 362 4942','Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifs1000cq8xdfo2aau32','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.873+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.873+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hug-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hug-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1514567756706436346',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('hummus-yossef','standard','cmr07ign700clq8xd3u66z61g','Hummus Yossef','## Top Reviews
> "Nice casual place with a fast-food style vibe. The hummus was fantastic, really well made and full of flavor. The asado burger was ok, good quality but it didn’t really impress me. Service and atmosphere are pleasant and relaxed. One small note: the menu shows photos of some dishes that were not actually available. Overall a good spot for casual food, with some excellent items and room for improvement."
> **- Luca Foschi (4/5/5)**

> "The food was so fresh and delicious! The humus was very good, but we loved the most all the veggies and salads that were truly amazing. It’s a nice break from pad Thais and curries 😆 A great address for vegetarians!"
> **- thefrench gal (5/5/5)**

> "We had really good hummus with eggplant and mushrooms and as a side falafel with tahini Also the cappuccino with oat milk and the hot matcha oatlatte were sooo good (literally the best matcha we had so far in thailand) Staff was so lovely, we really had the perfect experience"
> **- Anna S (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hummus-yossef-1.jpg','061 301 9747','155, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 4:00 PM","Saturday: 7:30 PM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.875+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.875+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hummus-yossef-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hummus-yossef-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4930008142151311627',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('hustlers-beer-garden-pool-hall','standard','cmr07ign900cmq8xdwtb2bjts','Hustlers Beer Garden & Pool Hall','## Top Reviews
> "If you’re English and missing a Sunday roast then this is the place to come!! 565B for chicken, beef & lamb with all the trimmings. Everything was absolutely delicious. Highly recommend!!"
> **- Liz Newcombe (5/5/5)**

> "Good vibes pool tables and darts, lovely staff and very good foood was tasty! If your staying at bad monkey right below, free drink for ladies on Tuesday and different events every day"
> **- Hope Foster (5/5/5)**

> "I had avocado and poached eggs on toast here and it was absolutely amazing (as you can see in the picture). I would highly recommend this place to have breakfast, lunch or dinner. Great service from the staff, atmosphere and they have so many pool tables too. You can even get 25% off food and drinks if you’re staying at the Bad Monkey hostel upstairs."
> **- Matt Fishlock (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hustlers-beer-garden-pool-hall-1.jpg','080 478 0206','185 หมู 2 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://linktr.ee/hustlers.samui','["Monday: 12:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Tuesday: 12:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Wednesday: 12:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Thursday: 12:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Friday: 12:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Saturday: 12:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Sunday: 12:00 PM – 2:00 AM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.877+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.877+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hustlers-beer-garden-pool-hall-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hustlers-beer-garden-pool-hall-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16299860301541533340',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('hyatt-regency','standard','cmr07ignb00cnq8xdjmooq3ib','Hyatt Regency','## Top Reviews
> "We had quite a good time in this hotel with the beautiful view and convenient location with excellent food, but I want to say that this hotel is good for families with kids as there are several opportunities for the children to enjoy, but I don''t recommend it to couples or solo travelers as It is quite noisy seeing children all around. The pool was not super clean at some hours. We stayed in this hotel for 5 nights but the room was running down, every day we had a problem, one day with the electricity, one day with the water, one day with the sink. The breakfast was amazing but the service was sometimes slow."
> **- raheleh roohianfard (3/5/5)**

> "We stayed at Hyatt Koh Samui for our honeymoon and overall had a pleasant experience, but there were a few important issues that need attention.  We had specifically booked and fully paid for an ocean view room, however upon arrival we were given a partial ocean view. After raising this with the team, they shifted us to a better room the next day, which we appreciated—but it was still not a full ocean view as originally booked.  On our second night, we returned to our room to find a baby cot placed inside, which was quite surprising considering we were on our honeymoon. This felt like a clear oversight from the hotel staff.  We were also informed that dosa could be prepared for us as Indian vegetarians, however this was never arranged during our stay, which was disappointing.  That said, apart from these issues, the property itself is beautiful, and the overall stay was comfortable. With better attention to guest preferences and room allocations, the experience could have been excellent."
> **- bijal sheth (3/5/5)**

> "The staff were professional, friendly, kind and helpful. The room service was impressive and massages were one of the best I’ve received. I really enjoyed my stay here but found that it was lacking in vegetarian food options. The overall guest atmosphere felt informal and standoffish but that wouldn’t stop me from returning."
> **- Sahur Geereh (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hyatt-regency-1.jpg','077 448 777','99/11 หมู่ที่ 5, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.hyatt.com/hyatt-regency/en-US/usmrk-hyatt-regency-koh-samui?src=corp_lclb_google_seo_usmrk&utm_source=google&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=lmr',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifsv000nq8xdrwnu123q','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.879+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.879+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hyatt-regency-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/hyatt-regency-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17799768823587566622',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('i-talay-resort','standard','cmr07ignd00coq8xdt205g5az','I -Talay Resort','## Top Reviews
> "Bungalows are small and basic, but it''s all about the location: right on the beach, very peaceful. We had a wonderful stay, if you really want to appreciate it get a moped (owner is more than happy to arrange one for you). Plus points for the lovely black cat that sits by the till!"
> **- Silvia Mariani (5/5/5)**

> "We very much enjoyed our meal here. Great breeze on the beach with a beautiful view. Good food with a full page of vegetarian options available, and crispy bacon.  Excellent service.  We look forward to coming back."
> **- Kiki Dee (5/5/5)**

> "I don''t know how I have missed going to this gem location before. Located on the south west coast of Samui, it''s a stunning location for watching sunsets with wonderful views out to the nearby islands. At the entrance there''s a wooden bridge that spans across a lake with colourful lotus flowers. The restaurant serves amazing food and cocktails to sip while watching sunset. The restaurant also has beach bungalows for hire. Certainly a highlight of this trip"
> **- Rob S (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/i-talay-resort-1.jpg','081 721 3683','164 19, Tambon Taling Ngam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://italay.top/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ift8000pq8xd7yujz20i','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.881+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.881+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/i-talay-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/i-talay-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5284526427089748366',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ibis','standard','cmr07igng00cpq8xd7ot1ufr2','Ibis','## Top Reviews
> "As soon as we arrived and checked in, we were warmly welcomed by Molly and K. Sanook. Their hospitality immediately made us feel comfortable  at home. The service was beyond words — warm, thoughtful, and genuinely caring. They also gave us many great recommendations for places to visit and delicious food around Samui. We were truly impressed and not disappointed at all. Already looking forward to our next trip and staying at ibis Samui again!❤️"
> **- อินท์กัลญา ทัศน์บวรรัตน์ (5/5/5)**

> "If you’re in Koh Samui, this is one of the most comfortable places to stay. 10/10 for real. The beach is right in front, so mornings feel peaceful, and it’s close to Fisherman’s Village with plenty of great cafés and bars. A 7/11 and pharmacy nearby also make everything easier. My friend and I planned to stay one night and ended up extending because we genuinely loved the place.  The rooms are clean and modern with beautiful sunrise views. There’s a gym, a pool table, a nice pool area, and the hospitality felt warm throughout. The breakfast buffet had a good range of options, and overall the stay felt like great value for money. I’d definitely come back."
> **- priyam sharma (5/5/5)**

> "Great location and lovely spot at the beach. Pool area is nice with snacks a bar and a restaurant. The breakfast buffet is also fine. Rooms are a bit on the small side but for that price you won''t find much better. Staff is extremely friendly and helpful. The place offers games you can borrow, a pool table in the lobby, a small gym and a diy laundry room."
> **- Marc Lenzke (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ibis-1.jpg','077 914 888','Bophut Beach, ตำบล แม่น้ำ อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.2,0,0,0,NULL,'http://ibis-samui-bophut.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.884+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.884+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ibis-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ibis-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=283941004960797677',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ice-bar','standard','cmr07igni00cqq8xdh0nc6gv1','Ice Bar','## Top Reviews
> "I visited an ice bar in Samui with my friends, and it was such a unique and fun experience! The bar is on the smaller side, but it has an incredibly cool and distinctive vibe inside. Upon arrival, they ask for an entrance fee, which includes one drink. The drink is served in a glass made entirely of ice, which is super cool and adds to the experience. They also provide you with warm clothes and accessories to help you get the best photos.  The overall experience was fantastic – we had a great time taking fun photos, enjoying the ice-cold drinks, and just soaking in the unique atmosphere. The staff were friendly and made sure we were comfortable throughout our visit.  The location is perfect, right in the heart of Chaweng''s party area. It’s a great spot to check out before heading out for a big night out. Highly recommend it for anyone looking for something fun and different to do in Samui!"
> **- Ella Benchan (5/5/5)**

> "Awesome icebar and experience in Samui. This place is seriously cold. They do give you jackets and hats to wear before going in. We bought entry for 280 baht which included a flavored vodka shot. Even the shot glasses are made of ice. You can chill in the bar and take photos and there’s even a polar bear head to wear. Friendly staff and great experience."
> **- City of Angels (5/5/5)**

> "What a great experience ! Imagine enjoying 30 degrees celcius Samui night Life and all of the sudden being transfered into a minus 30 degrees all Ice bar environment enjoying a vodka flavored shot dressed in a glass made of Ice as well. This for Only 280bath. Definetely recommend. We had so much fun with my Friends !"
> **- Xavier ARRUEGO (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ice-bar-1.jpg','085 783 3091','162 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.886+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.886+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ice-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ice-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5374489079494241917',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ida-b','standard','cmr07ignk00crq8xdbxii0gl6','Ida B','## Top Reviews
> "I really enjoyed staying at this resort. The rooms are beautiful, spacious, and the bathrooms are outstanding. I stayed in the Junior Plus room and was very pleasantly surprised by how amazing the room looked and felt.  The staff is truly 10/10 — very punctual, kind, and always ready to help with anything you need. The cleanliness of the rooms is exemplary. The sea view is stunning, as the resort is located high on the hill.  The food is also delicious. I wholeheartedly recommend this resort and I would like to congratulate the staff for doing such an excellent job."
> **- Iuga Daniel (5/5/5)**

> "My stay at Ida B Hotel on Koh Samui was absolutely exceptional.  The view from my room was sumptuous and the hotel offers breathtaking scenery.  The service was outstanding : meticulously attentive and thorough in every detail.  Every member of the team was incredibly kind, friendly, and always readily available to help with anything I needed.  This hotel genuinely deserves its 5-star rating and meets European 5-star standards in every way.  From the luxurious accommodations to the impeccable service, everything exceeded my expectations.  I highly recommend Ida B Hotel to anyone visiting Koh Samui who wants a truly premium experience."
> **- Sach (5/5/5)**

> "The property itself is beautiful, however 5* means attention to detail. The room itself really gorgeous with a stunning view.  The staff was very friendly. The boutique hotel has 12 rooms of which 3 were occupied (including mine). We did love the backgammon and chess boards in the lobby.  Then why three stars only? Being an avid traveler I dislike bashing a place but the experience here was not 5*. We reached after it was dark. The path is off the main road, on an extremely steep hill. You need an SUV cab to reach there, or the hotel has a pick up and drop service between 8am and 10pm daily.  (They accommodate earlier and later times if you inform them). This information should be findable on booking.com  so one can make an informed decision on whether i want to be in a secluded or busier place.  The lobby lights and air conditioning should be turned on at all times if not at least till midnight. No early cut-offs. (10pm for everything). It feels like we are being told when to call it a night.  The breakfast was very limited. Day 1 we were told two eggs per person only. One of us being a body builder in the competitive league, 2 is not enough! We finally did get more after talking to the hotel manager. On the last morning they ran out of yoghurt. Someone went to fetch it and it arrived within 5minutes but that really shouldn’t happen.  The hotel Manager Phee, manages the guests and fulfills your wishes to his best ability. I’ll add, missing warm water on day 1, the room safe wasn’t working (they had to replace the battery) and even then it didn’t work, dog poo in front of the gym at 10pm, lights turned off, aircon turned off (allowed to turn on oneself but that is not 5* for a gym).  I’ll conclude by adding the property has great potential, the owners seemed nice, we exchanged brief greetings."
> **- Payal J. (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ida-b-1.jpg','098 016 0389','49, 13 หมู่ที่ 5 Phitakthong Rd, Tambon Lipa Noi, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://idab-domain.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.888+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.888+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ida-b-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ida-b-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10094341594926190949',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ilas-world-dog-hotel','standard','cmr07ignm00csq8xdopxmoe97','Ila''s World Dog Hotel','## Top Reviews
> "Pistachio stayed at Ila’s for 5 nights. It was her first time at a dog hotel and I did a lot of research before choosing where to send her. She is a rescue who has been in a shelter for 8 years and is extremely nervous and unless me and my husband are there she doesn’t let anyone touch her. Pistachio did stay in her kennel the whole time because she was so nervous but Ila really took the time to make her feel comfortable. Pistachio woke her up every morning at 5 am whining and Ila got up to see to her and reassure her every morning, giving her extra treats and really being patient with her. Recommend to anyone!"
> **- Emily Willmot (5/5/5)**

> "My dog stayed with Ila for a week and I’m very satisfied. She is professional, attentive, and clearly experienced with dogs. My dog came back calm and well cared for. I would trust her again without hesitation!"
> **- Marine Méric (5/5/5)**

> "We’ve chosen to leave our sweet dog Johnny at Ila’s World Dog Hotel several times, and every time it’s been a great experience. The hotel is not too large, and each dog has plenty of personal space. The care is attentive, professional, and clearly given with love. Johnny truly enjoys being there, and we feel completely at ease knowing he’s in good hands. Ila regularly sends videos and updates, and Johnny always looks happy and relaxed. Highly recommended!"
> **- Avital Kaufman (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ilas-world-dog-hotel-1.jpg','084 308 5316','78/12 Moo 4, ตำบล ลิปะน้อย Koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.ilasworld.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 12:00 PM, 2:00 – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 12:00 PM, 2:00 – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 12:00 PM, 2:00 – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 12:00 PM, 2:00 – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 12:00 PM, 2:00 – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 12:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.891+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.891+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ilas-world-dog-hotel-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ilas-world-dog-hotel-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8398162721875833138',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('impiana','standard','cmr07igno00ctq8xdnttu9p2l','Impiana','## Top Reviews
> "Excellent resort with private beach.  If you''re looking for a relaxing place in Koh Samui Impiana is a beautifully kept resort including buffet breakfast.  Staff go out of their way to be hospitable. Especially Guitar - she was super helpful at check-in as I arrived too early she was very kind and allowed me to enjoy the resort while my room was being cleaned.  and Aung helped me change my room to one that suited my needs more.  I highly recommend staying here as it has everything you need to relax and enjoy your holiday without having yk leave the resort.  The beach is the added bonus - crystal clear turquoise"
> **- Margo Colombana (5/5/5)**

> "I had a wonderful stay at Hotel Impiana. The location is fantastic, offering easy access to the beach and nearby attractions. The rooms were clean, comfortable, and well-maintained, with all the amenities you need for a relaxing stay. The atmosphere of the hotel is calm and inviting, perfect for both short getaways and longer vacations.  The staff was consistently friendly and professional, always ready to help with a smile. Breakfast was varied and delicious, and the overall service exceeded my expectations. I would definitely recommend this hotel to anyone looking for a pleasant and stress-free stay.  I would especially like to highlight Sun at the reception. She was incredibly kind, helpful, and professional throughout my stay. From the moment I arrived, she made me feel welcome and took the time to answer all my questions with patience and a genuine smile.  Sun went above and beyond to ensure everything was perfect, whether it was assisting with check-in, giving recommendations, or helping with any requests. Her positive attitude and excellent service truly made a difference in my experience. Thank you, Sun!"
> **- kiki lashes (5/5/5)**

> "The beachfront location is beautiful and great for relaxing by the sea. The breakfast was amazing and definitely one of the highlights of our stay.  However, the rooms are not very luxurious and don’t really feel like a 4-star standard. We booked two rooms, and unfortunately one of them had a smelly bathroom. We politely asked to change the room, but were told the hotel was fully booked and it wasn’t possible.  The location is good for the beach, but not ideal for shops or getting around. Outside the hotel you’re directly on the road, the area isn’t walkable, and the nearest shops are about 1–2 km away, so a motorbike or transport is needed.  For the price we paid, we would probably choose a different place to stay next time."
> **- Tarek Sinjer (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/impiana-1.jpg','077 448 994','91/2-3, Moo 3, Chaweng Noi Beach, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.1,0,0,0,NULL,'https://samuihotels.impiana.com.my/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ig5c0051q8xdykrbexft','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.892+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.892+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/impiana-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/impiana-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8642933657747280109',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('infinity-accounting','standard','cmr07ignr00cuq8xdaimhr2rb','Infinity Accounting','## Top Reviews
> "Excellent helpful staff and Khun Jee knows how to get things done. We wish the Infinity team good luck at their new location. Highly recommended."
> **- EGMC (5/5/5)**

> "Great service, Friendly and very Helpful. Professional and knowledgeable. Highly recommend"
> **- Jay Gee (5/5/5)**

> "The staff were very helpful and friendly. You could ask them anything you wanted; they were very approachable."
> **- Chayada Petcharat (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/infinity-accounting-1.jpg','082 352 2823','108, 14, Tambon Bo Put, District, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://infinity-samui.com/','["Monday: 9:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 9:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 9:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifu0000zq8xdvll5tv7z','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.895+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.895+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/infinity-accounting-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/infinity-accounting-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=18342949141706524780',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ingon-accurate-accounting-services','standard','cmr07ignt00cvq8xdurwrkcsj','Ingon Accurate Accounting Services','## Top Reviews
> "All of our team is using Ingon Accounting Services for their visa, work permit and tax payments.  We can easily say that they are the best. The staff is very kind and attentive. You can truly trust to them.  We strongly recommend them. Thank you."
> **- LotusFriendlyHotel KohSamui (5/5/5)**

> "Been here for 14 years and I know most of the accountants on the island. I can easily say Ingon Accounting is one of the best. They track your visa days, your work permit schedules and gives you a warning to not to forget about it. Highly recommended. Thank you Mrs. Ingon and her professional staff."
> **- Cumhur Seyhoglu (5/5/5)**

> "I have been using Ingon accounting for over 10 years and very happy with the service. Special thanks to Khun Nit and Khun Nam for looking after our accounting. Thank you Khun Ingon and team."
> **- Chris (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ingon-accurate-accounting-services-1.jpg','077 430 556','H24M+6PH, Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:30 AM – 12:00 PM, 1:00 – 5:30 PM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 12:00 PM, 1:00 – 5:30 PM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 12:00 PM, 1:00 – 5:30 PM","Thursday: 8:30 AM – 12:00 PM, 1:00 – 5:30 PM","Friday: 8:30 AM – 12:00 PM, 1:00 – 5:30 PM","Saturday: 8:30 AM – 12:00 PM, 1:00 – 5:30 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifu0000zq8xdvll5tv7z','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.897+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.897+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ingon-accurate-accounting-services-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ingon-accurate-accounting-services-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16445279468636843166',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('inkinc','standard','cmr07ignv00cwq8xdx86b9o73','Ink.inc','## Top Reviews
> "I was at the studio today to cover up two older tattoos. With the result I couldn''t be more happy!! Excellent!  From the first contact and booking to the appointment today, the service was outstanding.  The team is super friendly and helpful, the artists do an incredible job and the result is really good! Pricing is more than fair and the team is really looking to keep hygiene up.  They also make sure that you clearly understand the aftercare.  All in all I would come back anytime without hesitation and recommend this studio above all other.  Result pictures follow as soon as fully healed."
> **- Jan Hangarter (5/5/5)**

> "I researched this place before leaving Sydney and it stood out straight away. The booking process overseas when I decided I wanted a tattoo was very easy and accommodating. I got a traditional boxer piece to match my style and the guys at Ink.inc absolutely smashed the piece, some of the best work I’ve ever had done. The gang were so nice, the place is clean and very hygienic, and the aftercare method comes with a free balm and a step by step guide for looking after your piece. Highly recommend these guys and I’ll be back for another piece this year."
> **- Roger Claymore (5/5/5)**

> "Great, clean studio. Very clean and efficient with their work. I came in with an idea and they started that day and finished with no problems on the second day. Couldn’t be happier with the end product. Highly recommend and will definitely be back."
> **- Caleb Rapley (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/inkinc-1.jpg','096 534 1731','14, Subdistrict, 38 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, District, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://ink.inc/?utm_source=google&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=gmb_koh_samui_profile','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.899+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.899+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/inkinc-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/inkinc-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12527850223191430085',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('insens','standard','cmr07igny00cxq8xd9tvmerfq','IN’SENS','## Top Reviews
> "If you’re looking for amazing furnitures in Koh Samui and a pleasure to design your interior, go for it ! This shop is incredible.. great personal and they are taking really care of your order until you will be delivered.. highly recommended .."
> **- David Lambert (5/5/5)**

> "Gigi was so very helpful at this store with many lovely items with Bali influence. Much handmade, lovely pillows and throws as well as teak floor lamps. We had driven by 100 times and finally stopped. I’m so glad we did!"
> **- Autumn Lew (5/5/5)**

> "Really nice shop with friendly, helpful staff! We bougth different stuff for our new villa ☺️"
