INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ipc-green','standard','cmr07igo800d1q8xdcdrfec5x','IPC Green','## Top Reviews
> "We visited IPC Green Samui to explore options for our two young children.  The facilities look nice at first glance, but the overall experience raised several concerns.  Before even properly touring the place, we were immediately presented with a price list. The system is very rigid: full-week attendance (Monday to Friday, full day only), with no flexibility for shorter days or fewer days per week.  Enrollment requires committing to a full semester (around 4 months), even if you only need a short-term solution. This creates a significant financial risk — if you realize after a few days that it is not the right environment for your child, you are still locked in and have already paid a substantial amount.  We also asked about trial days and were told they would follow up, but we never received any response.  Overall, this might suit families looking for a strict, long-term program, but we would not recommend it for families who value flexibility or want to ease their children into a new environment first."
> **- Siamak Davoudi (2/5/5)**

> ""
> **- Irada Jantana (5/5/5)**

> ""
> **- ปลิตา มะมัย (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ipc-green-1.jpg','094 787 6539','166, 9, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.ipcgreen.com/','["Monday: 8:30 AM – 4:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 4:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 4:00 PM","Thursday: 8:30 AM – 4:00 PM","Friday: 8:30 AM – 4:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.912+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.912+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ipc-green-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ipc-green-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2171117330149581024',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('island-organics','standard','cmr07igob00d2q8xddaw1nbo0','Island Organics','## Top Reviews
> "Chef Lat was an absolute gem during our cooking class. What made this experience special was the location being on her own private organic farm. We made a total of 4 dishes and a local herb drink with butterfly pea flower tea. She also gave us a tour of her whole organic farm in which she talked about the processes of maintaining her farm, and also the time it took to develop. Highly recommend this local hands-on experience."
> **- andrew white (5/5/5)**

> "Highly recommend! Learnt so much about cooking authentic popular Thai dishes and even making coconut milk! Chef Lat was a wonderful teacher, very bubbly, friendly and funny! We even had a garden tour where Chef Lat showed how the different herbs are grown as well as gardening tips! 10/10 experience!"
> **- Hemal Shah (5/5/5)**

> "Chef Lat is absolutely amazing. What a joyful and fun experience. She is super welcoming and hilarious throughout. A really passionate teacher and happy soul. The food was incredibly delicious. Chef Lat will walk you through every step and show you around the garden where she grows fresh produce. I highly recommend this course! We will come back! Thank you Chef Lat 🙏 kop kun krap 🙏"
> **- West Stow Pods (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/island-organics-1.jpg','062 526 6210','24/1 Moo 4, Bangrak / Chaweng Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.islandorganicssamui.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.915+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.915+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/island-organics-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/island-organics-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13865446169081172385',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('issara-clinic','standard','cmr07igoc00d3q8xdf8f143hi','Issara Clinic','## Top Reviews
> "I had a great experience at this clinic! I just came for a mole removal, but was in and out within 20 minutes, very fast service, kind staff and doctor. They were very gentle with the anesthesia and the laser, I didn''t feel a thing! They also gave me bandages and antibiotic ointment for aftercare, all within the quoted price given over Facebook. Would recommend to others for this service as well as others!"
> **- Care (5/5/5)**

> "I went there for Botox and lip filler end of April 2022. The procedure was overly painful! I have had this done many times before. It should never be this painful. Even with numbing cream! My lips and eyes was bruised for a week! The Botox has worn off already after only 1. Month! I asked for my lips to have a small amount as they were already full. They insisted I have 1 instead of half. They just want to make money! My top lip after a month looks awfully! I look like a duck as they put in too much. DON’T GO HERE! I’m thinking of getting an inspector out to look at their products. This practice should not be open!"
> **- Ann Masters (1/5/5)**

> "This is the best Dermatological Skin Clinic in Koh Samui! The Doctor was really great, and the staff really took care of me. Their products are also advanced. On top of Issara clinic being so POSH. Their clinic is also so clean too. Plus, they don''t over charge their patients. I can''t wait to be back."
> **- Mishy Co (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/issara-clinic-1.jpg','077 300 242','4/135 M.2 Bophut Suratthani, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.916+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.916+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/issara-clinic-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/issara-clinic-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=113722121631161437',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('isuma-samui-floating-club','standard','cmr07igof00d4q8xd66nn39kk','Isuma Samui Floating Club','## Top Reviews
> "I had a fantastic experience at this café! The sunset view and overall atmosphere were absolutely beautiful. They provide fishing equipment, and if you''re lucky enough to catch something, they''ll cook it for you! The café itself is spacious, with comfortable sandbag seating that makes it the perfect spot to relax. The food and drinks were delicious and reasonably priced. The staff were incredibly friendly and provided excellent service. They were very helpful throughout the visit. I’ll definitely be coming back again!"
> **- Ella Benchan (5/5/5)**

> "Isuma Samui Floating Club offers an unparalleled dining experience on the tranquil waters of Koh Samui. This floating restaurant combines exquisite cuisine with the serene ambiance of the sea, making it a must-visit destination for both locals and tourists. ￼  Ambiance and Setting: ★★★★★  Nestled off the coast of Bang Por Beach, Isuma Samui provides a unique setting where guests can dine while gently floating on the ocean. The establishment’s design harmoniously blends traditional Thai elements with modern aesthetics, creating a cozy and elegant atmosphere. As the sun sets, the panoramic views of the horizon offer a breathtaking backdrop, enhancing the overall dining experience.  ￼  Cuisine: ★★★★★  The culinary offerings at Isuma Samui are both diverse and delectable. Specializing in fresh seafood, the restaurant ensures that each dish is prepared with the utmost attention to quality and flavor. A standout feature is the squid fishing activity, where guests can catch their own squid and have it prepared on the spot as sashimi or grilled to perfection. This interactive experience adds a unique twist to the dining journey, allowing patrons to connect with their food in an intimate way.  ￼ ￼  Service: ★★★★★  The staff at Isuma Samui Floating Club are renowned for their warm hospitality and attentiveness. From the moment guests arrive, they are greeted with genuine smiles and a willingness to accommodate special requests. The team’s knowledge of the menu and their dedication to providing a memorable experience contribute significantly to the restaurant’s stellar reputation. ￼  Activities and Entertainment: ★★★★★  Beyond the exquisite dining, Isuma Samui offers engaging activities such as squid fishing, allowing guests to immerse themselves in local traditions. Additionally, the venue occasionally features live music performances, enhancing the ambiance and providing entertainment that complements the serene surroundings.  ￼  Overall Experience: ★★★★★  Isuma Samui Floating Club seamlessly combines gourmet dining with unique experiences, all set against the stunning backdrop of Koh Samui’s waters. Whether you’re seeking a romantic dinner, a family outing, or a solo adventure, this floating restaurant promises an unforgettable experience that delights all the senses. ￼"
> **- koh Ai Solution (5/5/5)**

> "Such a special experience. Staff were super lovely, gave us lots of tips on how to fish and they were really nice and funny. Great atmosphere. 100% recommend for a family or a date night :)"
> **- Emily Henshaw (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/isuma-samui-floating-club-1.jpg','098 815 8884','24, แม่น้ำ, 7, Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.isumasamui.com/','["Monday: 3:00 – 10:30 PM","Tuesday: 3:00 – 10:30 PM","Wednesday: 3:30 – 10:30 PM","Thursday: 3:00 – 10:30 PM","Friday: 3:00 – 10:30 PM","Saturday: 3:00 – 10:30 PM","Sunday: 3:00 – 10:30 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifs1000cq8xdfo2aau32','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.919+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.919+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/isuma-samui-floating-club-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/isuma-samui-floating-club-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12663636770487703428',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('isuzu-car-dealership','standard','cmr07igoh00d5q8xd187faqal','ISUZU Car Dealership','## Top Reviews
