> **- ตุ้ยพา เที่ยวใต้ (5/5/5)**

> "Absolutely an EXCELLENT dealership! I bought a new Isuzu VCross from them — luxurious and beautiful — the best vehicle I have ever owned. I am very impressed with the quality of the service provided. A first-rate dealership 😍⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️"
> **- Jamie Knapp (5/5/5)**

> "Very poor customer service in the service department. Isuzu is one of the best car I own but this centre service is useless even you make an appointment."
> **- Charlie Tong (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/isuzu-car-dealership-1.jpg','077 002 989','57 48, Tambon Taling Ngam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.1,0,0,0,NULL,'https://sites.google.com/isuzusurat.co.th/isuzusurat','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifui0012q8xdzn158clv','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.921+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.921+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/isuzu-car-dealership-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/isuzu-car-dealership-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8939306119854119999',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('jade-cottages','standard','cmr07igoj00d6q8xdm36yhv5s','Jade Cottages','## Top Reviews
> "Beautiful accommodation set in a stunning garden with a swimming pool. It is about a 20-minute walk from Fisherman’s Village. They can arrange a scooter rental directly on-site. Breakfast was great, with a choice of three options. The French owners are very pleasant and more than happy to help with anything. We would love to come back sometime. Merci!"
> **- Jiří Majer (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing weekend escape! The pool and outdoor lounge were perfect for our group; great poolside area, comfy sunbeds, and plenty of space to hang out. Staff were friendly and helped arrange a taxi and late check-in. Close enough to Chaweng nightlife but still super private. Highly recommend for groups."
> **- Leander Davies (5/5/5)**

> "Beautiful stay and lovely hosts. Nicely located in a residential area, 20min walk from Fisherman''s Village (5min by Scooter). Nice cold AC in the rooms, Pool is beautiful and clean, nights are quiet. would definitely recommend. :)"
> **- Samuel Unterrieder (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jade-cottages-1.jpg','095 850 0668','167, 28 Soi 1, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.923+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.923+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jade-cottages-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jade-cottages-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13046468508606069481',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('jahn-restaurant','standard','cmr07igol00d7q8xdubkxcddf','Jahn Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "Jahn restaurant is simply divine and easily one of the best on the entire island. It is a grill restaurant, and while we mainly had fish and seafood, it was fantastic and prepared to an incredible standard. There is also a great choice of wines to accompany the meal. We almost want to keep it a secret from people outside the resort so it doesn''t get too crowded, but absolutely hats off to all the chefs; the food is incredible and the experience was flawless. During my birthday, we had the most delicious chocolate mousse cake there which was the perfect end to the evening. It truly is a culinary masterpiece."
> **- Beatrice (5/5/5)**

> "Jahn might have one of best locations on the island. It has one of the most incredible views which sets the scene for a great dinner. The space itself is very intimate. There are only a couple of tables and booths in the restaurant. The design is very relaxing and smooth. The wagyu itself was actually underwhelming and I didn''t enjoy it as much as I thought I would. The entrees and sides were fantastic though. The service was impeccable and I am annoyed I didnt remember our hostesses names as they did an amazing job."
> **- Dave Eri (4/5/5)**

> "Our dining experience was excellent from start to finish. Our server, Ming, and the chef, Fon, were outstanding. We chose the tasting menu with wine pairings, and every course was incredible. The food paired beautifully with the wines.  The staff truly personalized the experience and made us feel very well taken care of as hotel guests. The ambiance was unforgettable: being so high up and watching the sunset behind the five islands was absolutely stunning.  Highly recommend this restaurant for a special dining experience."
> **- Keaton Wlaz (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jahn-restaurant-1.jpg','077 915 888','49/8 9 Hillcrest Road Tambon Taling Ngam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.hilton.com/en/hotels/usmksci-conrad-koh-samui/dining','["Monday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Friday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ift8000pq8xd7yujz20i','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.925+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.925+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jahn-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jahn-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12797350509111258426',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('jai-spa','standard','cmr07igon00d8q8xdi52ejleo','Jai Spa','## Top Reviews
> "Great massage ladies, very strong Thai massages, very clean."
> **- Sophie Wong (5/5/5)**

> "Hands down the best massage experience in Thailand. From the first session, we knew this place was special — the ladies here understand your body so well and know exactly where to apply pressure without you saying a word.  We ended up visiting every two days because the massages were consistently perfect. Even after we changed hotels and moved 30 minutes away, we still rode back just to get our massage here. We tried another place closer to our new hotel, and it just wasn’t the same.  If you want a truly skilled, professional, and healing massage, this is the place to go. Highly recommend!"
> **- chalalai chaiwongkhot (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing specialists! When we visit Koh Samui, we always go to them, even if we are far away. Highly recommend this wellness salon"
> **- Alexandr Wigrovski (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jai-spa-1.jpg','062 132 8549','45 แม่น้ำ 13, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.927+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.927+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jai-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jai-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11952661191802986297',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('jalmin','standard','cmr07igop00d9q8xdrfmlspem','Jalmin','## Top Reviews
> "Perfect boutique hotel with a wonderful restaurant and extremely friendly staff. Expect high levels of service and rooms cleaned twice a day here. I stay here every time I come to Samui. Close to the downtown tourist area but far enough away to keep away from the noise. See you soon Jalmin and friends!"
> **- Mike Hurrell (5/5/5)**

> "I had a very pleasant stay at Jalmin hotel. The room was clean, comfortable, and well maintained. The staff were friendly, polite, and always willing to help. The location is convenient, close to shops and restaurants, which made traveling very easy. The facilities were good and met my expectations. Overall, it was a great experience, I highly recommend this hotel to anyone visiting Koh Samui."
> **- Onuma Polwik (5/5/5)**

> "6-star hotel 😍 quality bed, so comfortable I didn''t want to wake up. The room was clean and smelled nice. The staff were lovely, smiling, and provided prompt service.  The area around the hotel is lush and has plenty of seating, plus there''s a restaurant in front of the hotel serving delicious, high-quality food. I highly recommend this place; you won''t be disappointed. 🥰"
> **- Tharnitarat Intajit (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jalmin-1.jpg','077 423 789','101 Chaweng Beach Rd, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320 Chaweng, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://jalmin.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.929+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.929+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jalmin-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jalmin-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12341303895722100067',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('james-bike-shop','standard','cmr07igor00daq8xdlvejtjim','James Bike Shop','## Top Reviews
> "I had a great experience with this motorbike rental place! I rented two bikes, and both were in excellent condition—you can trust them completely. The owner was super helpful throughout the entire process. Anytime I had a problem or question, I could just call him, and he’d take care of it right away. I really felt like I was in safe hands. Highly recommend this trustworthy, professional place!”"
> **- Eren Koprulu (5/5/5)**

> "Great place and great service! It’s a rental, repair and the shop! James speaks good English. If there is any issue with a bike, they fix it and provide you with replacement without any problem 👌 Also great choice, good price and communication! It’s close to the Nathon Pier and they drive you to the pier, once you return the bike, if you are taking ferry! I’m motorcycle driver and lover myself, I highly recommended this place!  Renting here again and sending my friends! 🙏🙏🙏"
> **- F M (5/5/5)**

> "We just returned our scooter after 4 days. It wasn’t in the best shape when we got it, but it was functional. There were some loud noises coming from the brakes, so we messaged James to ask if we could return it and get a replacement. Instead, he offered to change the brake pads, and everything was done in about 10 minutes, so we were back on the road.  James was also very responsive on WhatsApp, and when we requested to return the bike an hour later than planned, it was no problem at all.  The bike almost didn’t have any shock absorbers, but let’s be honest, that seems to be the case with many scooters on these rough roads in Thailand 😅  The shop is about a 15-minute walk from the pier. We went there because during the high season, all the scooters near the pier were already rented out, and only electric options were left, which aren’t suitable for driving on the higher points of the island.  They also have a friendly dog who loves cuddles while you wait for the paperwork 🥰  Overall, this rental worked out fine for us, and we would recommend it 🛵"
> **- Klara Novak (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/james-bike-shop-1.jpg','062 419 8666','GWGQ+X8G 308/19 อ่างทอง Tambon Ang Thong, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://m.facebook.com/James-Bike-Shop-110448918274582/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifui0012q8xdzn158clv','cmr07ig1h003iq8xdb1g9nifo','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.931+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.931+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/james-bike-shop-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/james-bike-shop-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13482322828985296640',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('jamminz-beach-bar','standard','cmr07igos00dbq8xdf8pesip5','Jamminz Beach Bar','## Top Reviews
> "We did not eat but drink and the rock smashed music was unbelievable. Mainly the female rock singer…she is really talented and has got “deep rock voice”…We did dance at the end of the show almost all the bar guests…and come back again next evenings, really great athmosphere and even karaoke bar, if you like classical rock, you will rock it🤘"
> **- Radoslav Mahut (5/5/5)**

> "Great drinks, awesome service by Jack and the team and the band is really impressive. There’s atleast 5 band members on stage. Taking wishes!  We had so much fun"
> **- Nico (5/5/5)**

> "Came here again tonight because the band was fabulous, the beer was cold and the service was fantastic. It’s a great little set up in the Lamai night market. This is a busy spot and they allow you to bring food over from the other vendors. Def must stop by and sing along. (Band starts at 8pm)"
> **- Aimee Sasaki (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jamminz-beach-bar-1.jpg',NULL,'Maret, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/jamminz.jamminz','["Monday: 6:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Tuesday: 6:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Wednesday: 6:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Thursday: 6:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Friday: 6:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Saturday: 6:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Sunday: 6:00 PM – 1:00 AM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.932+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.932+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jamminz-beach-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jamminz-beach-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3079053829744188752',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('jardin-restaurant','standard','cmr07igou00dcq8xdgihn48qi','Jardin Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "We didn’t expect the restaurant to be so wonderful. Calm romantic atmosphere and tasty menu. We had fresh fish carpaccio and duck totallini as starter. Then had the grilled snapper and roasted chicken. Both expertly prepared. Finished it off with nice dessert. All in all very tasty experience and I would recommend if you are looking for high level French cuisine. Thanks to passionate chef and his wife?  Wil make time to go back."
> **- Charles P (5/5/5)**

> "We didn’t expect the restaurant to be this wonderful. The atmosphere was calm, romantic, and beautifully designed, making the whole dining experience feel very special from the moment we arrived. We started with the fresh fish carpaccio and duck tortellini, both absolutely delicious and full of flavor. For the main course, I had the lamb and my wife ordered the beef, both expertly prepared and cooked to perfection. We finished the evening with a lovely dessert that completed the meal perfectly. The food was truly outstanding, and you can really feel the passion and dedication of the chef in every dish. A special thanks as well to the chef’s wife and the staff for their warm hospitality and welcoming service throughout the evening. Overall, it was an incredible and memorable experience, and we would highly recommend this place to anyone looking for high level French cuisine. We will definitely make time to come back again."
> **- Leo Rodriguez (5/5/5)**

> "Absolutely wonderful dinner! My wife and I were thoroughly impressed. The pan-seared seabream filet was cooked to perfection—crispy skin, flaky flesh. The raster grouper was a flavorful and unique delight. To start, the mozzarella salad was so fresh and creamy. A truly memorable meal in a lovely atmosphere. We can''t wait to return!"
> **- Виталий Воробьев (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jardin-restaurant-1.jpg','083 151 6582','Mae Nam maenam, soi 7, ตำบล แม่น้ำ Koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61560795846167&mibextid=ZbWKwL','["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 12:00 – 2:30 PM, 6:30 – 10:30 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 2:30 PM, 6:30 – 10:30 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 2:30 PM, 6:30 – 10:30 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 2:30 PM, 6:30 – 10:30 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 2:30 PM, 6:30 – 10:30 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 2:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.934+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.934+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jardin-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jardin-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10141751647615908025',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('jasmine-resort','standard','cmr07igox00ddq8xdgvdab5ow','Jasmine Resort','## Top Reviews
> "The room was extremely outdated, nothing like what is shown in the photos online. There were blood stains on the sheets. That was unacceptable. You’ll see it in my pictures. The pictures make the hotel look modern and stylish, but in reality they are very misleading. When I booked, the room was advertised as having a garden view, but the actual view was a wall, completely blocked. The air conditioning when set on low or medium, it made constant loud noise, making it impossible to sleep. I was forced to either turn it off, which made the room uncomfortably hot, or set it on the highest setting, which made the room freezing. There was no comfortable or quiet option. I also tried several items at the restaurant, and the food was barely average. Nothing stood out, especially considering the price point. Overall, there was no value for the money paid. I would definitely not stay here again and would not recommend this hotel to others."
> **- Maryam (2/5/5)**

> "We had a wonderful experience staying over the Christmas holiday. Our room was comfortable and private. I enjoyed the walk to the dining area and pool that overlooks the beach. The service and food was great and reasonably priced. We got massages in a room by the beach and had quick access to the beach and shoreline. Overall, a great experience we will always remember!"
> **- John Majeski (5/5/5)**

> "Stayed there for 3 nights at the Sea View rooms on the 2nd floor. The room is very big, you control the lightning and the ac in the room with a remote control that is located next to the bed which is very comfortable. The view is amazing, the beach is great, breakfast is very good with a lot of options. Staff is very helpful and always positive and smiling. Good experience!"
> **- Roi Hay (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jasmine-resort-1.jpg','077 232 446','Maret, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.samuijasmineresort.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.937+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.937+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jasmine-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jasmine-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8296243747663980936',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('jasmine-rice-restaurant','standard','cmr07igoz00deq8xd2fadrvct','Jasmine Rice Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "Jasmine Rice Restaurant is a popular beachfront dining spot located at the Samui Jasmine Resort in Lamai Beach, Koh Samui, known for serving authentic Thai, seafood, and international cuisine. The restaurant offers a romantic, laid-back atmosphere with tables on the sand, live music, and a focus on fresh, local ingredients. Not a better way to finish a beautiful day on the beach than to have a great meal on the beach. We ordered Khao Soi and Tom Yum with noodle and a couple glasses of wine...fantastic. Congratulations Chef"
> **- Kirk MacDonald (5/5/5)**

> "Jasmine Rice is a wonderful beachfront restaurant with a super friendly service and an unbeatable location right on the beach. The relaxed atmosphere is made even better by live music, which creates the perfect setting for a laid-back dinner by the sea.  The dishes are excellent, especially the Pad Thai, the refreshing Papaya Salad, and the flavorful Beef Curry. While the prices are higher compared to nearby food markets or smaller local places, the quality, setting, and overall experience make it absolutely worth it.  A great spot for anyone looking to enjoy delicious Thai food with stunning beach views and warm hospitality."
> **- Bernhard R. (5/5/5)**

> "Absolutely wonderful food! Staff is very friendly and if you are looking for tasty Thai food this is the place! Highly recommend the seafood barbecue menu!  So fresh and cooked to perfection."
> **- lofgren1992 (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jasmine-rice-restaurant-1.jpg',NULL,'F28X+J36, Maret, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.939+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.939+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jasmine-rice-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jasmine-rice-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8364341274050373809',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('javanese-furniture-decoration-design','standard','cmr07igp000dfq8xdy7a973mj','Javanese Furniture & Decoration Design','## Top Reviews
> "Large offer, very beautiful products, fair prices. This is the best shop in Samui for wood furniture."
> **- Sebastien Bertrand (5/5/5)**

> "Everything you can find to decorate with taste your home is there. Nice choices of interior items, exotic freshness.."
> **- gerard Armand Marie (5/5/5)**

> "Great choice and prices are attractive as well. It''s a nice place to find decoration ideas"
> **- Gert Lehmann (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/javanese-furniture-decoration-design-1.jpg','+66935654661','HXHG+6W7, Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://javanese-samui.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.940+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.940+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/javanese-furniture-decoration-design-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/javanese-furniture-decoration-design-2.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/javanese-furniture-decoration-design-3.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/javanese-furniture-decoration-design-4.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16640860118782548219',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('jaymart','standard','cmr07igp500dgq8xd9ye3a5o2','Jaymart','## Top Reviews
> "I initially stopped by JAYMART in Central Samui looking for an electrical component, but I’ve also been in the market for a sound system upgrade. That’s when I spotted the JBL speaker I had my eye on—one that the Lamai location no longer carried. It wasn’t until then that I realized I had walked into the same store brand, just in a different location.  The store manager, Nan, who has been with the company for 19 years, spoke excellent English and was incredibly helpful throughout my purchase. She let me test the speaker in-store, allowing me to turn up the volume and experience its full range. The JBL system performed exceptionally well, passing my test with ease.  What truly stood out was Nan’s dedication to customer service. Since this was an impulse buy and I was on my motorcycle, I had no way of getting the speaker home. Without hesitation, Nan suggested taking one of the taxis downstairs, even offering a clever tip—telling them the manager referred me, which might help secure a better rate.  I was genuinely impressed by her professionalism, friendly demeanor, and problem-solving skills. Even after nearly two decades in the business, she still brings the kind of attentive and engaging service that makes you want to return. The rest of the staff were equally polite and curious, making the experience even more enjoyable.  For anyone looking to upgrade their sound system or make any electronics purchase, I highly recommend checking out JAYMART in Central Samui. The quality of service, expertise, and care they provide is truly exceptional."
> **- Nomadic Lotus (5/5/5)**

> "Protective glass for 290 baht and excellent service.  They even offered me something to drink."
> **- Mighty Karpador (5/5/5)**

> "I went to buy a Super VOOC charger but received a Vooc charger instead. When they were selling it, they said it worked, and they charged 990 baht, claiming I needed to buy an original cable to use it for Super VOOC functionality. But when I tried to exchange it, they said it wasn''t possible. I consider myself ripped off by the salesperson. From a customer''s perspective, I''m very disappointed."
> **- Mr.scream satanic (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jaymart-1.jpg',NULL,'209,209/1 หมู่ 2 ชั้น 1 2 ห้อง 117 216, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.945+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.945+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jaymart-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jaymart-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13195855154640927387',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('jazz-up-music-school-studio','standard','cmr07igp800dhq8xdjqd46sw9','Jazz Up Music School & Studio','## Top Reviews
> "Practiced piano at Jazz Up for 3 weeks now, daily, on my Samui stay. They have two very fine upright acoustic pianos, each in a separate room. The owner is very approachable and welcoming. I highly recommend it for any amateur or professional pianist looking for a practice studio while on the island!"
> **- Omri Tal (5/5/5)**

> "My son has been doing drum lessons with Jazz Up for over a year now.   He loves it and his teacher is amazing.  He’s very passionate and enthusiastic in the lessons that he teaches.   All the teachers here are dedicated musicians and they seem to produce great little music makers!   I would definitely recommend this school for anyone looking."
> **- Bonnie Maclean (5/5/5)**

> "Such a great place!!! Teachers are very kind, smiling and always creating warming sweet atmosphere for learning! Great prices and easy to learn. I never knew anything about music and during first lesson already started to play. After 2d lesson I already could play very small part of 15 different songs. If you dream all your life to try musical instruments like me but never have time give it a try and you will discover completely new world for yourself! Definitely Best School on the island!"
> **- JJ K (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jazz-up-music-school-studio-1.jpg','090 910 0010','23 484 ถนน บางรัก-บ่อนไก่ Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 12:00 – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 7:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 9:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 9:30 AM – 4:00 PM"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.948+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.948+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jazz-up-music-school-studio-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jazz-up-music-school-studio-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12773124769651795986',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('jennifer-mentor-co-ltd','standard','cmr07igpa00diq8xd84k22m8y','Jennifer Mentor Co, Ltd.','## Top Reviews
> "We had the most amazing afternoon at Koh Samui Elephant Haven. We chose to visit the Haven specifically, after extensive research found it to be the most ethical sanctuary available. It’s clear that all the staff care deeply for the beautiful rescue elephants. Our guide, Mr Thai, was a fine example of this. He was knowledgeable, humorous and gentle mannered. He helped to elevate our already brilliant experience! At Samui Elephant Haven, they  practise showing the elephants the upmost respect and encourage guests to do the same- not to encroach on the elephants freedom.  We were able to prepare food and feed the elephants, have a tour around the sanctuary learning some fascinating facts about elephants as well as the sad stories that lead the elephants to be rescued. The tour was followed with the provision of a delicious, authentic vegetarian Thai meal including starter, main and dessert. We would highly recommend this experience and support of the sanctuary so that they can continue the important work that they do. Thanks, Ella & Luke (England)"
> **- Ella Saunders (5/5/5)**

> "We had the most heartwarming and unforgettable day at Samui Elephant Haven. From the moment we arrived, it was clear how deeply the staff care — not only about the elephants, but about sharing their stories with respect and compassion.  This is truly an ethical sanctuary. You can see how well the elephants are looked after and how much thought goes into their care, enrichment, and wellbeing. Hearing each elephant’s history was incredibly moving and gave us a deeper appreciation for the work this sanctuary is doing.  The tour was very informative and included plenty of hands-on experiences, all done in a way that clearly prioritizes the elephants’ comfort and dignity. The guides were knowledgeable, patient, and genuinely passionate.  For anyone with mobility issues, there is a bit of a hill to walk, but it felt very manageable. There were always shaded areas to wait, and at almost every stop where information was shared, there was also a place to sit and rest, which was really appreciated.  Lunch was absolutely delicious and thoughtfully prepared. One of the biggest highlights of the day was celebrating our friend’s birthday — we brought a birthday “cake” that was fed to the five girls (the elephants!) at the end of our visit, and it was such a joyful, unforgettable moment.  This experience was educational, emotional, and deeply uplifting. If you’re looking for an ethical, caring, and meaningful elephant experience in Koh Samui, Samui Elephant Haven is a must-visit. We left with full hearts and so much gratitude for the work they do.  🐘💚"
> **- Jessi Nessi (5/5/5)**

> "I highly recommend this Sanctuary for everyone wanting to meet an elephant but not knowing how to without exploiting them. The caregivers are amazing, the place is vast and it''s very clean. The elephants are all rescues and can''t live in the wild. Sanctuary is really ethical - you can''t touch them. You can feed them from a safe distance and the staff makes sure animals are well taken care of. Mr Thai was the best guide, with a kind heart and nice jokes 😄 he helped us learn about the rescued elephant''s, their history and hardships. While very sad, you can rest knowing they will never endure anything like this again ❤️"
> **- Anita N (kita051) (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jennifer-mentor-co-ltd-1.jpg','095 628 6160','137/31 Tambon Bo Put, Koh Samui Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://samuielephanthaven.org/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.950+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.950+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jennifer-mentor-co-ltd-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jennifer-mentor-co-ltd-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=18219655523928613364',NULL,NULL);
