INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('jib-computer-group','standard','cmr07igph00dlq8xdy097z2q0','JiB Computer Group','## Top Reviews
> "Mixed Experience at JIB – Central Samui  Consistency in customer service is key, but unfortunately, not every visit delivers the same experience.  I first visited JIB to upgrade my video card and was met with a knowledgeable, friendly, and accommodating staff member who made the process smooth and enjoyable. Their assistance left a positive impression, making me confident in returning for future purchases.  However, on a recent visit to look for a Fire Stick or a Xiaomi streaming stick, my experience was quite different. The staff member on duty was curt and unwelcoming, making me feel as though my inquiry was an inconvenience. Instead of helping me explore potential options available in Thailand, they abruptly walked away when another customer entered. I then stood waiting while they slowly typed at the keyboard, seemingly looking something up, though there was no communication. The lack of engagement and dismissive attitude made the experience frustrating.  While I may return for specific computer components, I sincerely hope to be assisted by a more professional and attentive representative next time."
> **- Nomadic Lotus (3/5/5)**

> "This shop provided excellent service when I purchased two monitors. Despite encountering an installation issue, their team addressed and resolved the problem. Their commitment to customer satisfaction made the entire process smooth and hassle-free."
> **- Nomad Li (5/5/5)**

> "Fantastic service, Great attitude, Friendly staff and most important the genuine concern to give you value-for-money. In a day and age where most people want to sell more or cheat you, these guys gave me what was best for my money. I highly recommend them especially the manager who made sure I was taken care off. Loy Machedo"
> **- Loy Machedo (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jib-computer-group-1.jpg','090 678 7816','เลขที่ 209, 209/1 ศูนย์การค้าเซ็นทรัลเฟสติวัล สมุย ห้องเลขที่ 204 ชั้น 2 2 หมู 2 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.jib.co.th/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.957+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.957+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jib-computer-group-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jib-computer-group-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7483693302849530876',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('jimmy-woos','standard','cmr07igpk00dmq8xdfi60hj0n','Jimmy Woo''s','## Top Reviews
> "Great place, good service, great prices. The band that plays is so good!! We had such a great time we ended up here every night."
> **- Isabel Cejudo (5/5/5)**

> "Absolutely fantastic bar. Great for Australian and English guests. Tourist price for drinks but not too high. Band is great and so many great songs. Less than 4000 baht for 4 ppl for 4 hrs including cocktail and shots."
> **- Heather Morris (5/5/5)**

> "AMAZING LIVE MUSIC, the best entertainment. I had a lot of fun! Incredible guitarist, the quality is above the clouds! Also, good price drinks"
> **- Tania Lozano Guzman (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jimmy-woos-1.jpg',NULL,'91, Chaweng, Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.jimmywoos.com/','["Monday: 7:00 PM – 3:00 AM","Tuesday: 7:00 PM – 3:00 AM","Wednesday: 7:00 PM – 3:00 AM","Thursday: 7:00 PM – 3:00 AM","Friday: 7:00 PM – 3:00 AM","Saturday: 7:00 PM – 3:00 AM","Sunday: 7:00 PM – 3:00 AM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.960+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.960+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jimmy-woos-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jimmy-woos-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11208710406306829238',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('jins-bar-and-restaurant','standard','cmr07igpm00dnq8xdv0qfm4ef','Jin''s Bar And Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "Fantastic food and cocktails available Jins. We walked to it from our nearby hotel, Adarin Beach. Seating area is covered so is rain proof. Lots of lovely plants make it look lush. They provided mosquito spray which we used, did not get bitten, generally it seems just a good idea to use mosquito prevention in Thailand. Friendly staff. There is parking outside the front, there is a toilet."
> **- Adrian Everest (5/5/5)**

> "Really enjoyed the food and atmosphere. Met the lovely owner here. I liked that they had mosquito spray on the table for guests."
> **- Lisa Kao (5/5/5)**

> "Perfekt Food, Ambient and Service. They are super friendly and the food is one of the best and authentic that we had on Koh Samui. The prices are really affordable and the cocktails are more than amazing. I would recommend everyone to come here to enjoy food and atmosphere ❤️ Most of everything everyone should come to meet Restaurant owner Jin, that makes sure that everyone is satisfied and enjoys every moment🫶🏻"
> **- Azra Imamovic (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jins-bar-and-restaurant-1.jpg','095 296 5205','3 ตำบล แม่น้ำ Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/jinbarandrestaurant/','["Monday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.962+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.962+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jins-bar-and-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jins-bar-and-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3235923810114519312',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('joon-hostel','standard','cmr07igpp00doq8xd1hkfz04s','Joon Hostel','## Top Reviews
> "Such a good meal at Joon, a Persian restaurant near Choeng Mon.  We shared the "
> **- Tammy Wade (5/5/5)**

> "Such a hidden gem in Koh Samui! As someone who’s been travelling, finding this Persian restaurant honestly felt like a taste of home. The food was exceptional — rich, authentic flavours and clearly made with so much care. The staff were absolutely amazing, so welcoming and genuinely friendly, which made the whole experience even better. If you’re in Koh Samui and want incredible food and warm hospitality, this place is a must-visit. Highly recommend!"
> **- Lana Ahmad (5/5/5)**

> "Loved everything in this restaurant. All the food is authentically home cooked. You could taste that with every single dish. They have incredibly good black tea Persian style. The lamb is incredibly soft and delicious. Ghormeh sabzi was out of this world for me.. thank you Davud for your incredible hospitality and kindness. Loved your playlist and service. Absolutely one of the best Persian restaurants ever. Prices are on the higher side, but you get an amazing quality."
> **- SuiYx23 (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/joon-hostel-1.jpg','095 248 4837','63, 127-129 Chaweng-Choengmon Road Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://joonhouse.com/','["Monday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: Closed","Thursday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifsv000nq8xdrwnu123q','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.965+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.965+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/joon-hostel-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/joon-hostel-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15175431929230152492',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('jr-bicycle-shop','standard','cmr07igpr00dpq8xdvg8da1zp','JR Bicycle Shop','## Top Reviews
> "You can truly feel the love for cycling here – this bike shop clearly lives and breathes the sport. I brought my gravel bike in for a full inspection and got it back in absolutely perfect condition. Every detail was taken care of with great precision and care. A huge compliment to the team for the fast, highly professional, and extremely competent service. It’s rare to find a place where the passion for cycling is so genuine and noticeable. I am more than happy to be a customer and a guest of this outstanding bike shop on Koh Samui. Highly recommended."
> **- Jens (5/5/5)**

> "I contacted the store to get information about renting a bike for the day. I received a very warm welcome. I got advice and had the bike adjusted to my liking. The owner is a cycling enthusiast. I will continue to visit and I recommend you do the same if you need to have your bikes serviced."
> **- Emmanuel Rodriguez (5/5/5)**

> "Great bike mechanic who works on anything from kids bikes to top end road and triathlon bikes. I have used Khun Ming for the last 3 years and have always been impressed. 🙏"
> **- Jonathan Haworth (Jono) (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jr-bicycle-shop-1.jpg','084 625 4404','เลขที่ 110/50 หมู่ 6 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifui0012q8xdzn158clv','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.967+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.967+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jr-bicycle-shop-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jr-bicycle-shop-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6673483834836509382',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('js-beauty-center','standard','cmr07igpt00dqq8xddb00xv5o','J''S Beauty Center','## Top Reviews
> "We had such an amazing experience thanks to Marissa! She took incredibly good care of us from beginning to end. The treatment was absolutely incredible and our skin is glowing afterwards.  She really took her time to do everything properly and made sure we were comfortable throughout the whole session. You can truly feel how much she cares about giving the best experience possible to her clients. She guided us so well and paid attention to every detail.  It was our first time doing this treatment, and my wife and I are absolutely delighted with the result. We had a wonderful moment and would highly recommend this place especially Marissa. Thank you again for such a great experience!"
> **- nordine hadouch (5/5/5)**

> "Highly recommend J''s Beauty Center. I had the facial with extraction and the beautician was very friendly, professional, and took great care to make the treatment comfortable. In hindsight, I probably should have told her not to worry so much about hurting me during the extractions so she could be more thorough!  I visited with a group of friends and we all came away with glowing reviews. I''m already looking forward to coming back to try the ear spa.  A tip for others: book ahead, as they seem to be very popular."
> **- Jeeves-Julian “JJ” Stephens (5/5/5)**

> "I found this salon online and read a lot of good reviews which prompted me to book. I could not be more happy with the service I received and for the price, I had a facial which is the best I’ve had and my skin is so clean and sculpted! This wasn’t just a facial it was skincare based and I left with the glass skin look 🥰I brought my teenage son with me who wasn’t feeling great and they let him lie on the bed next to me and put a blanket over him. 100% would recommend❤️"
> **- Jade Bell (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/js-beauty-center-1.jpg','063 220 1817','108/28, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/JS-Beauty-Center-109936551657619/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.969+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.969+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/js-beauty-center-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/js-beauty-center-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5014604360890231367',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('jungle-safari-tours','standard','cmr07igpv00drq8xd0bcqo4ry','Jungle Safari Tours','## Top Reviews
> "Great Tour to hidden gems of Koh Samui. Knowledgeable guides, punctual pick ups and scheduling. Great support outside of Tour."
> **- Lisa Heitmann (5/5/5)**

> "What a fantastic day! The tour was simply amazing, with a great selection of sightseeing stops. The guides were absolutely fantastic - professional, friendly, and made the whole experience so much fun. Excellent hospitality and organization from start to finish. Highly recommended this tour!"
> **- Dominik Harmuth (5/5/5)**

> "Jungle tour was amazing!! Nan was such a good tour guide! We did a waterfall hike, which wasn’t too much to see because it was dry season, we learned about the different fruit that grows, lunch on the top of the hill was delicious, the views were spectacular. The ride on the safari trucks were fun too! Highly recommend!"
> **- Agata O''Neil (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jungle-safari-tours-1.jpg','065 619 6549','26, 3, Tambon Ang Thong, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.junglesafaritourskohsamui.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifxh0027q8xde6xqk8o6','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.971+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.971+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jungle-safari-tours-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jungle-safari-tours-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12291252612512916643',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('jungle-wheels','standard','cmr07igpx00dsq8xduw39hhqj','Jungle Wheels','## Top Reviews
> "I rented a scooter here for one full month in February, and the experience was absolutely excellent.  I rented an XDV for a little under 300 baht per day for the whole month, which is a very good price considering the condition of the bike. The scooter was in very good shape, clean, well maintained, and ran perfectly throughout the entire month.  What really stood out to me was the service. They even delivered the scooter directly to my hotel, which made everything super easy and convenient. The staff is extremely kind, professional, and truly customer-oriented. You can really feel that they care about providing good service.  At the end of my rental, I returned the scooter two days earlier than planned. I didn’t ask for anything, but they still refunded me for those two unused days without hesitation. That level of honesty and fairness is rare and very much appreciated.  I highly recommend this place to anyone looking to rent a scooter. Great prices, great bikes, and outstanding service. I would definitely rent from them again."
> **- Mister Benz (5/5/5)**

> "Big thankyou to the jungle wheels crew , I arrived in samui a day earlier than my original booking and they still sorted us out with a bike with no problems. There seems to be a lot of bike rental companies in samui but these guys are top of the bunch .if you want to see what the island has to offer and be free from the organised tours get a bike from these guys , they also give you an ebook with everything to do on the island . We will be getting our bikes from them when we come back ."
> **- Lee Burgess (5/5/5)**

> "Jungle Wheels are the best, they delivered & collected the Scooter on time, the scooter - Honda ADV 160cc was nearly new, only 3000km, & in excellent condition, the hire was made so easy, photo of documents sent via whats-app, & they delivered as promised. Good handover with them explaining how things work, open, & steering lock/alarm. Fuel in tank & returned the same. They also sent a booklet via whats-app with links to places & things of interest. We used the scooter over 4 days, up & down both sides of Koh Samui. With two onboard & she done it well."
> **- Phil Allen (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jungle-wheels-1.jpg','061 286 7362','4171, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.junglewheels-samui.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifui0012q8xdzn158clv','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.973+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.973+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jungle-wheels-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jungle-wheels-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14402642228171797682',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('juno','standard','cmr07igq000dtq8xdz1kk1gdp','Juno','## Top Reviews
> "One of my favourite bars on the island. You''ll always get a warm welcome from Orly & her team. Service is excellent. Lovely selection of food on the menu & often have weekly specials (Shakshuka!!). Beautiful sunset views - views of Big Buddha. Always a great play list & dont miss the live DJ nights. Thank you Orly for always making us welcome xx"
> **- Karen MC (5/5/5)**

> "Such amazing cafe and more really very kind and very friendly staff especially that lady helped us alot thanks again And highly recommended"
> **- Peshawa Zedbagi (5/5/5)**

> "This place has something that stand out of many other places. It is somehow crazy and electric. And the Owner, a fantastic and cheerfull lady, keeps the atmosphere at the highest level. Lot of drinks being consumed and good food if you are chemically hungry. Great music played and "
> **- Michele Annoni (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/juno-1.jpg','095 256 0121','14, 51, Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.junosamui.com/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig6y005pq8xd4jrvheih','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.976+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.976+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/juno-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/juno-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16943507305984397319',NULL,NULL);
