> **- B property (Bob) (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jw-pest-control-service-1.jpg','+66945859870','Maret, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.979+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.979+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jw-pest-control-service-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jw-pest-control-service-2.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jw-pest-control-service-3.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/jw-pest-control-service-4.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5704506509459523489',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('kabuki-tattoo','standard','cmr07igq600dvq8xdyb1gh3j0','Kabuki Tattoo','## Top Reviews
> "We recently got our tattoos done at this salon — and we are absolutely thrilled! The artists not only work flawlessly with their technique but also pay great attention to every detail and request. Everything is sterile and neat. Our tattoos turned out exactly as we imagined — clean lines and stunning detail. Huge thanks for your creativity and heartfelt approach! Now we have not just drawings on our skin, but little works of art. We’ll definitely be coming back for more! 🙌✨"
> **- Наталия Лабунская (5/5/5)**

> "An unforgettable experience — the best tattoo studio ever! My husband got a very personal and detailed forearm tattoo here, and we are beyond happy with how everything turned out. From the very beginning, both Lee (the artist) and “Kick” (the owner) put their heart and soul into making sure my husband ended up with exactly the tattoo he dreamed of. Their effort and dedication were truly exceptional.  “Kick” took her time to sit down with us, carefully noting every single idea and detail my husband had in mind. She even gathered reference photos to help explain everything clearly to Lee. Her preparation was impeccable. She made the whole process so smooth and enjoyable, always with a warm smile and such a friendly attitude — you instantly feel at home in their studio.  The tattoo took two full days, just before we returned from vacation, and I stayed with them the entire time. I never once felt bored or uncomfortable — quite the opposite! The studio is cozy, welcoming, they offer a great price and well-located, so I could easily go out to grab some food and bring it back for my husband.  The tattoo itself was incredibly complex and full of fine details, but Lee handled it with amazing patience, skill, and positive energy. You could truly feel that both he and “Kick” were doing this with love and joy — and that makes all the difference.  We’re so deeply grateful to both of them. This wasn’t just a tattoo — it was a full experience, filled with care, passion, and professionalism. 100% recommended. If you want a tattoo that’s done with heart and incredible attention to detail, this is the place to go."
> **- Leyre Sides (5/5/5)**

> "It was a very nice experience! The studio was very clean and the artist did a great job 😇 They are also very hygenic! And they were soo nice!!"
> **- Laura Ledl (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kabuki-tattoo-1.jpg','063 842 1015','159/43 ตำบล บ่อผุด Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.instagram.com/kabukitattoosamui?igsh=ZjJxeGE0ZDBwNTRu','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 11:30 PM"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.982+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.982+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kabuki-tattoo-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kabuki-tattoo-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5737787603592820434',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('kachatan','standard','cmr07igqa00dwq8xdppmcd3s5','Kachatan','Discover Kachatan, a premier food and beverage located in Chaweng Noi, Koh Samui. Find reviews, hours, and contact information.',NULL,'077 951 999','10, 79, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,1200,0,0,NULL,'http://www.kimptonkitalaysamui.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig5c0051q8xdykrbexft','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.986+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.986+00:00',NULL,'https://maps.google.com/?cid=1792967035450585232&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('kalamari-beach-villa','standard','cmr07igqd00dxq8xd3poxx4xo','Kalamari Beach Villa','## Top Reviews
> "Fantastic beach house, conveniently located nearby some great beachside restaurants and coffee shops. Davide and team looked after us very well. Daily breakfasts and the staff can prepare lunch and dinner if needed. Magnificent beachside deck and kitchen/diner/pool room where we ended up spending most of the time. There is a separate living room with large TV.    Good sized swimming pool with a jacuzzi function at one end but we mostly swam in the sea."
> **- Fergus Evans (5/5/5)**

> "I have traveled to many places around the world, and as a mother of seven children, I have extensive experience with all kinds of accommodations. However, this home truly exceeded all my expectations – it is absolutely at the very top.  The house is even more beautiful than in the photos. It is luxurious, thoughtfully designed, and finished with stunning details. Everything was perfectly clean, and we didn’t encounter any insects at all (only a few small lizards, which is completely normal here). The level of cleanliness and maintenance was exceptional.  David’s team is absolutely outstanding. Every single person who took care of us was professional, kind, and attentive – I didn’t have a single complaint. The food was incredible. They prepared anything we wished for, and we had breakfast, lunch, and dinner for an entire week for seven children – who are quite picky eaters – and everything was consistently delicious.  In all my previous stays around the world, there has always been at least a small issue – whether it was water pressure, air conditioning, or something minor not working properly. Here, everything functioned perfectly. Not a single flaw.  David himself is a truly wonderful host – kind, generous, and always willing to help, even beyond what is expected. It was always a pleasure to see him, smiling and full of great recommendations on how to enjoy our time and who to contact for anything we needed.  We even had massage therapists come directly to the house, which was amazing, and the staff helped take care of our baby so that I could enjoy meals in peace. This level of care is something I have rarely experienced.  During our stay over New Year’s, there was an unexpected accident – a car crashed into the wall of the house, damaging part of the property and the water system. The team handled it with incredible professionalism. Everything was fixed almost immediately, and we didn’t even notice any disruption. They continued working on repairs throughout the week, yet our comfort was never affected.  This experience only highlights how professional and well-organized David’s team truly is. I am beyond satisfied, and I genuinely believe that we will be returning here with our family again and again.  Marketa"
> **- Marketa Pokorna (5/5/5)**

> "Absolutely fantastic, beautiful beach location with coastal breeze. Private and exactly like a luxury resort. Wonderful holiday atmosphere, perfect for tranquil and relaxing days. Davide the host and onsite staff just amazing and made our stay unforgettable, would recommend getting the chef each day, food just amazing!!!"
> **- IULIIA PESKOVA (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kalamari-beach-villa-1.jpg','061 270 4376','39/4 แม่น้ำ Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://kalamaribeachvilla.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifs1000cq8xdfo2aau32','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.989+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.989+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kalamari-beach-villa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kalamari-beach-villa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17984764188397683680',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('kalimantan','standard','cmr07igqg00dyq8xdo0qekqtp','Kalimantan','## Top Reviews
> "We stayed at Briza for 4 days and used to have breakfast here.. it was breezy , open, clean and the BF choice was sufficient and satisfactory. Although, I am vegetarians but we had our fill everyday with fresh fruits, eggs, breads and some other stuff. They serve lunch as well which can be provided right at there beachfront also."
> **- Pairinmas Buasomboon (5/5/5)**

> "awesome restaurant serving both local food and European dishes at a reasonable price"
> **- Id Goh (5/5/5)**

> "I don''t understand the lack of reviews? Maybe because it''s located on a resort? But this was one of the best restaurants we ate at on Koh Samui. The service was super friendly and fast. The beachfront view was beautiful, and there was even live music when we were there. The food was delicious (although the raw onion on the burger wasn''t quite to my liking) and it arrived quickly. It is on the pricey side, but that''s par for the course. Highly recommended."
> **- Wouter van Os (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kalimantan-1.jpg',NULL,'G3RC+5R9, Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.992+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.992+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kalimantan-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kalimantan-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5250818436684985563',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('kamalaya','standard','cmr07igqj00dzq8xdem87w0w4','Kamalaya','## Top Reviews
> "If you are looking for a life-changing experience, this is the place. I spent 10 beautiful days at Kamalaya in May 2026 — a place I will never forget. An extraordinary longevity and wellness oases. A high-end retreat offering life-changing coaching, spiritual guidance, beautiful treatments, meditation, and healthy nourishing food. Everything is designed to help you truly slow down, reset, and reconnect with yourself. I highly recommend this place to anyone looking to take a real break from everyday life and discover true inner treasures. Thank you great team.  Sharon"
> **- Sharon Schaveet (5/5/5)**

> "Special Place with Special People that inspire you to reach your full wellness and fitness potential. Kamalaya is magical…it’s built in the jungle surrounded by the sea. It is more amazing than the website photos. Book it don’t think twice."
> **- Beth Taylor (5/5/5)**

> "Stayed during Loy Krathong, such a beautiful time to be here. Everyone is incredibly kind and attentive; they genuinely care about you feeling relaxed the whole time. The massages and all the services are super professional. Truly an incredible experience."
> **- Julian Jaramillo (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kamalaya-1.jpg','077 429 800','102 9 Laem-Set Rd, Tambon Na Mueang, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.kamalaya.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ig4i004oq8xdv207xuh2','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:11.995+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:11.995+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kamalaya-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kamalaya-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3862845952768714283',NULL,NULL);
