> **- Barbara Dietrich (4/5/5)**

> "In February 2026 we held my daughter and son in law''s wedding at the Karma Resort. Family and friends travelled from Australia, South Africa, the USA, etc. to attend the wedding. The families and many of the guests stayed at the Karma Resort. The wedding itself was magical, with the Karma staff doing everything possible to work with the wedding planner to make not only the wedding but our entire stay at Karma memorable. The rooms were beautiful, especially with the outdoor showers. The staff were extremely friendly and helpful, the restaurant food was excellent and the location, within walking distance of Fisherman''s Village was very convenient. Overall, we were extremely happy that we chose the Karma Resort as the venue to host the wedding and the place for us to stay over the wedding period. Thank you to Yulia and the amazing staff."
> **- Sharon Lessing (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/karma-resort-spa-1.jpg','077 427 111','182, 3, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.karma-resort.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.024+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.024+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/karma-resort-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/karma-resort-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6304578270572845880',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('karma-sutra-bar-and-kitchen','standard','cmr07igrf00e9q8xdqosvh3y4','Karma Sutra Bar And Kitchen','## Top Reviews
> "I loved the vibe, music and atmosphere of this place. Cocktails were outstanding. I wish I had the capacity to try more of what they had to offer. But, the service was horrible. The lady on the top floor was eyeing my wife''s phone since she was checking for vegan options nearby. This place didn''t have good vegetarian/vegan options. We still waited for 20 mins for someone to come and take our order but no one did. By the time we walked downstairs, our bill was already ready. Sorry but that one lady kind of killed the vibe of the place for me."
> **- Virender Singh (3/5/5)**

> "I ordered a glass of red Côtes du Rhône wine and the bottle clearly turned bad or was oxydized. The wine tasted like burned caramel and the color was brownish similar to à bad Porto. I told the waitress and she argued the wine was good. However she changed the glass but it was the same disgusting taste, really not normal for this type of wine and all the staff were just staring at me and I felt so unconfortable that I left. I do not recommand this place."
> **- Marie-Eve Parent (1/5/5)**

> "Great food, great service. Live music every night. The perfect place to take in great cocktails, great view, and watch all the people walk by. Situated on the busiest corner of Fisherman''s Village, with it''s sister bistro across the street, it is the perfect location. All of the staff are friendly and attentive. The food is excellent, as are the cocktails. The beer, wine, and liquor selection are top notch. Not the lowest prices around, but not the priciest, either. It is the perfect range to be surrounded by a nice class of diners and drinkers."
> **- Collin Kinnear (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/karma-sutra-bar-and-kitchen-1.jpg','088 751 8674','37, หมู่บ้าน ฟิชเชอร์แมน, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.karmasutrasamui.com/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.027+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.027+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/karma-sutra-bar-and-kitchen-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/karma-sutra-bar-and-kitchen-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10038953073723238658',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('kawins-kitchen','standard','cmr07igrh00eaq8xdfbpymc8m','Kawin''s Kitchen','## Top Reviews
> "We are visiting on holidays from Canada and we were out for a walk looking for a cute dinner restaurant that was between our hotel and not in fisherman’s village. At first glance it reminded me of a small bistro chain restaurant but I was pleasantly surprised to find out it was small beautiful, relaxed and delicious!!  There was chicken strips and fries for our picky children, delicious drinks and my husband and I both had meals from the specials board.  The attention to detail and presentation of the plates was gorgeous and full of flavour! Don’t overlook this place it’s definitely a must visit in Koh Samui! We stayed at Zazen boutique and it was about a 7-10 min walk to get there.  5 Stars!!"
> **- Reagan O’Dea (5/5/5)**

> "This was the best tasting morish food I''ve had for my whole stay in my Thailand trip in Koh Samui Bo Phut area. Sadly only found on my last night. My mum and me shared Khao Soi (creamy gorgeous sauce with noodles and chicken) and Budda Bowl. We finished every last bit. Then we''re treated to complimentry coconut icecream. The Mai Tai cocktails were great to, would definitely recommend to anyone."
> **- Danielle Ruan (5/5/5)**

> "What a wonderful restaurant :-)  Amazing food!  Such good value! (with plenty of gluten free options for me - knowledgeable and kind staff, including Kawin the owner who was so helpful.  A genuine warm welcome and true hospitality and caring - excellent fresh food, served with such care and attention to detail.  Thank you very much - we will be back :-)"
> **- Lizzie T (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kawins-kitchen-1.jpg','086 444 9226','157, Fisherman''s Village, 2 ถ. ทวีราษฎร์ภักดี Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://kawinskitchen.net/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: Closed","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.029+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.029+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kawins-kitchen-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kawins-kitchen-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6205316037475362875',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('kba-kiteboarding-school','standard','cmr07igrj00ebq8xdbyhz804n','KBA - Kiteboarding School','## Top Reviews
> "I would recommend this type of sport to everyone one who likes to challenge himself or to learn something new.  I and my wife, we had unforgettable experiences with Mike 🪁He made everything to learn us how to control the Kite, how to stay on the board. It was my dream, and it came true I wold definitely come beck to Koh Samui and I will visit this kiteschool again, and I understood, that I will continue to exercise this sport.  Thank you Mike, thanks for your passion  Ivan & Elaina 🇺🇦🇩🇪"
> **- Иван Вакуленко (5/5/5)**

> "Super friendly and swift contact by whatsapp by the kba owner .  Nice spot. Unfortunately did not get to do kiting caus of no wind today. But spot looks perfect with shallow  water ."
> **- Jakub Regieli (5/5/5)**

> "This is the place ! rather you are absolutely new to kite or a pro, they had it all. I actually had some gear with me but the super friendly KBA staff helped me out to adjust it for local weather, they rented us what we needed without any questions asked so we won’t miss a single second of wind to catch. We had an amazing season, surprisingly they have everything , kites , foil, twintip, surf, boards, wing, Sup, skate you name it - they got it 😃. They have great IKO licensed instructors , insurance and super friendly and helpful staff. 5 starts from me guys , thank you 🙏🏻 for all your help and guidance you just made our trip more awesome and safer ☝️ Till next time 🫶🏻"
> **- Philipp Anufriev (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kba-kiteboarding-school-1.jpg','083 643 1627','Ang Thong, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.kiteboardingasia.com/locations/koh-samui/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07ifuo0015q8xdfahzrsp4','cmr07ig1h003iq8xdb1g9nifo','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.031+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.031+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kba-kiteboarding-school-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kba-kiteboarding-school-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=18326560500622940396',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('kc-beach-club-pool-villas','standard','cmr07igrl00ecq8xdtcepylf1','KC Beach Club & Pool Villas','## Top Reviews
> "We had the most incredible time at KC Resort. Everything was amazing—the staff, the atmosphere, and the facilities. The team went above and beyond, keeping our room spotless and always making sure we had everything we needed.  A special shout-out to Bum, Mint, Prae, and Ji for making our stay even more memorable—we truly appreciated your care and attention!  This was our second time staying here, and it definitely won’t be our last. We’ll absolutely be back! It’s a big, beautiful resort and truly an amazing place to stay. Highly recommend to anyone considering it."
> **- Chavi Block (5/5/5)**

> "We had an absolutely wonderful stay at KC Beach Club & Pool Villas in Chaweng. The hotel has a perfect location right on the beach, with beautiful views, a relaxing atmosphere, great food, and very comfortable rooms.  What truly made our stay special, however, was the incredible service from the staff. A special thank you to A Ji Kee and Tawan — they were all exceptionally kind, welcoming, and always smiling. They made us feel genuinely cared for from the moment we arrived until we left.  The entire team went above and beyond to make sure we had the best holiday possible, and we truly appreciated every moment. We would highly recommend this hotel to anyone visiting Koh Samui, and we will definitely come back again"
> **- natalie kudsk (5/5/5)**

> "This place exceeded my expectations. The restaurant has a very warm and relaxing atmosphere, making it a perfect place to enjoy a meal with family or friends. The environment was clean, beautifully arranged, and very comfortable.  Excellent service from the staff. Everyone was polite, attentive, and genuinely caring throughout the entire experience.  I would especially like to recognize:  * Khun A * Khun Koi * Khun Bum * Khun Kee  They provided outstanding hospitality and made us feel very welcome. Their professionalism, friendliness, and attention to detail truly made the visit memorable.  I highly recommend this place to anyone looking for great food, a wonderful atmosphere, and exceptional service. I will definitely come back again."
> **- Sumrit Chinna (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kc-beach-club-pool-villas-1.jpg','077 915 155','11 9 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.kchotelsresorts.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.033+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.033+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kc-beach-club-pool-villas-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kc-beach-club-pool-villas-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17229807046270654674',NULL,NULL);
