INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('koh-samui-fitness-center','standard','cmr07igt000etq8xd0ywlssjb','Koh Samui Fitness Center','## Top Reviews
> "This is my favorite gym in the world! It has all equipment you could need for only 1000 baht for the month. The manager is incredibly kind and caring, and it lit up my day every time I saw her. This gym felt so positive and enjoyable to be in. The atmosphere and clientele are humble and pleasant, which is not always the case in gyms, and I highly recommend this gym and supporting the owners!"
> **- Hannah Greene (5/5/5)**

> "Really great Gym ! Staff are fantastic and very helpful , great prices, very fair!"
> **- Laurent Harper (5/5/5)**

> "While it might not have the newest equipment, it does have everything you need for any type of workout, friendly people and the best membership price I could find on the island. I❤️this gym!"
