INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('koh-samui-laser-tag','standard','cmr07igt300euq8xde0rshj08','Koh Samui Laser Tag','## Top Reviews
> "We had an incredible experience at this laser tag and laser room! The place is clean, well-organized, and perfectly designed for kids. The staff were super friendly, patient, and made sure all the kids understood the rules and felt safe the entire time.  The laser tag arena is exciting without being scary, and the laser room challenge was a huge hit — the kids were laughing, running, and fully engaged from start to finish. It’s a perfect mix of fun, teamwork, and energy-burning activity.  Great atmosphere, professional setup, and happy kids (which means happy parents!). Highly recommended for birthdays, playdates, or just a fun outing. We’ll definitely be back! 🎯✨"
> **- yarden gilboa (5/5/5)**

> "We celebrated my daughter’s 11th birthday here and it was a great experience! The kids had so much fun and were really excited about the laser tag games. The staff were very kind, friendly, and helpful throughout the whole event. They made sure everything went smoothly and helped the children feel comfortable and enjoy the game. Thank you for making the birthday celebration so special!"
> **- Yulia Adieva (5/5/5)**

> "Fantastic service. Clean and good environment. Recommended!"
> **- Aaron Aw (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/koh-samui-laser-tag-1.jpg','082 619 9009','99, 5 Suan Utid Road, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://lasertagkohsamui.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.087+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.087+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/koh-samui-laser-tag-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/koh-samui-laser-tag-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11937597420728752041',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('koh-samui-taxis','standard','cmr07igt500evq8xdpl77iluj','Koh Samui Taxis','## Top Reviews
> "Highly recommended. Good communication. Easy to book and deal with. We contacted Tap to take us to a few places around Koh Samui that we wanted to see. He was on time, helpful and informative. He drove us around over four hours, for a good rate, in a good air conditioned van. Thanks for a great day Tap."
> **- Cass Goldie (5/5/5)**

> "Excellent taxi company. Polite, well priced, safe and friendly respectful drivers. Highly recommend Mr Tap and his company for getting around in Koh Samui."
> **- Alexis Day (5/5/5)**

> "Mr. TAP is a top notch 👌🏽 During our stay in Samui and Koh Tao, my family used his services a several times. He is a polite man and always on time . The price is very reasonable too . I highly recommend. Thank you once again and see you when we get back to Thailand 🇹🇭 🙏🏽 Kob Kun Ka ."
> **- Lokkie Lokkie (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/koh-samui-taxis-1.jpg','083 509 6577','142, 1, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ig1n003kq8xd72v6yb3r','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.089+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.089+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/koh-samui-taxis-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/koh-samui-taxis-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12360847065267078829',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('koh-samui-tennis-club','standard','cmr07igt700ewq8xd22m1py14','Koh Samui Tennis Club','## Top Reviews
> "Enjoyed a one hour coaching session with Sasha, he was friendly and professional.  The courts are now refreshed and good surface to play on."
