> "Just recently on the way to tennis club passage has been finally fixed, now it''s easy for bikes, cars, and bicycles to get to. tennis court, toilet, shower rooms are always clean, there is gym as well, small shop  at entrance you can purchase soft drinks and alcohol beverages, staff are always welcome and friendly :)"
