INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('kumon-samui','standard','cmr07igu900f9q8xd4b9k5nq2','Kumon Samui','## Top Reviews
> "It''s efficient, conveniently located, and very affordable, as it caters to local residents. A well-thought-out math methodology. There are stages, incentives, prizes, awards, certificates, trophies, and a performance scale throughout Thailand, making it easy to track your child''s progress. The children love it. Attentive manager. Comfortable sofas for parents. Flexible visiting hours. Opportunities to take a break from classes. With consistent attendance and homework, the results are amazing."
> **- Art Myname (5/5/5)**

> "Children become more enthusiastic and expressive, gaining more self-confidence. Schoolwork becomes easier, and they consistently achieve good grades. Importantly, parents don''t have to constantly nag them about school homework; they can do it immediately upon seeing it."
> **- Phathip Thongsree (5/5/5)**

> "I have 120 pages of homework at home, which is causing me a lot of stress because of my mother and my terrible tutoring."
> **- Nam Mon (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kumon-samui-1.jpg','090 963 0630','คุมองสมุย (โลตัสเฉวง) อาคารอยู่กลางลานจอดรถ ด้านหน้า โลตัสเฉวง ถัดจาก ร้านนวด My friend, 1, bophut, 7 ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://kumonsamui.my.canva.site/','["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 3:00 – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 3:00 – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 3:00 – 7:00 PM","Friday: 3:00 – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.129+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.129+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kumon-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kumon-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4459455133959242643',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('kya-beach-house','standard','cmr07igub00faq8xdgj2yeq34','Kya Beach House','## Top Reviews
> "We have just returned from the most incredible family holiday staying at Kya Beach House & already dreaming of when we can return! It’s such an incredible place & had everything we needed.  Location is on a very quiet beautiful clean beach, but there are also great thai restaurants and shops within a few minutes walk if needed. The staff Jeab & Dao are super friendly & helpful & the service & food they offer is amazing.  Breakfast while looking out to sea is the best way to start the day!   We did a good mix of total relaxation days spent by the pool and sunset paddle boarding (boards available at the house). On the days you want to do more they offer everything from massages at the house to visits to the elephant sanctuary, amazing boat trips & so much more to help you explore the island. Every detail has been thought of to make your stay so memorable.  We’ve stayed all over the island and this is our favourite!"
> **- Victoria (5/5/5)**

> "What an incredible family holiday ! It is our third trip to Thailand and I can honestly say it was the best yet.!  Kya Beach house has absolutely everything to offer for a family travelling with children. There was a little bit for everyone from an idyllic beach with hardly anybody on it, so the most perfect location with privacy and yet just a short walk away along the beach are restaurants, shops and massage, parlours all beachfront, it’s incredible.  The villa itself is exactly as you see on the pictures but the spaces particularly the outside area is huge and spacious !  The children could play on the private beach or in the pool all within eye shot of us whether we were relaxing on the sunbeds or under the chilled outdoor lounge it was super easy.  The house itself is perfectly set up and very clean and the staff cannot do enough for you. It was like being in a second home, it was such an amazing visit.  We have already booked to come back next year and we can’t recommend it enough."
> **- Kai N’Daw (5/5/5)**

> "Kya Beach House exceeded all our expectations. The location is breathtaking, the house beautifully designed, and the atmosphere peaceful and truly relaxing.  What made the experience exceptional was the service: the team was warm, thoughtful, and incredibly professional. They struck the perfect balance between attentiveness and privacy, making us feel completely cared for without ever being intrusive.  Every detail was just right – it felt more like being welcomed than simply hosted. We’re already looking forward to coming back."
> **- _ usinpictures (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kya-beach-house-1.jpg','081 597 6772','39/1 Moo 6, เทศบาลนครเกาะสมุย อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.kyabeachhouse.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifs1000cq8xdfo2aau32','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.131+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.131+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kya-beach-house-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/kya-beach-house-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14780058505383389238',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('la-bodega','standard','cmr07igud00fbq8xdwr4i6yko','La Bodega','## Top Reviews
> "Delicious and filling! We had pineapple fried rice with prawns and pad kra pao with chicken and a fried egg on top of the rice.  Both meals came quicky and were absolutely delicious! We had to force ourselves to finish them as they were very filling.  We both had a bottle of water and the total came to 520 baht.  Very reasonable.   Will definitely come back to try something else."
> **- Dianne Wilson (5/5/5)**

> "The steak was delicious and perfectly cooked. Portion size is good as well, but it’s a bit pricier than advertised. I checked the posted menu before coming but the one I got had almost double prices. Still fair for the value."
> **- MH (4/5/5)**

> "We had breakfast here. I ordered the American breakfast and she had the basic breakfast, both of which came with orange juice. After placing the order, we were told there was no orange juice available and were given water instead. No offer of another juice or any kind of discount on the breakfast sets.  I was genuinely lost for words when my American breakfast arrived. I am not sure what kind of bacon they used, but it looked terrible. I thought maybe the taste would make up for it, but it was just as bad. Honestly not sure if it was even bacon or just pure fat. I have attached a photo of the bacon for reference. The sausage was okayish, but the rest of the breakfast was poor, and for the price, the portion was very small.  This was easily the worst breakfast we have had so far in Lamai. I am currently sitting at Café KOB and the bacon here is proper.  Gave two stars instead of one because the basic breakfast was not too bad.  This place might be better suited for lunch or dinner plus drinks, but our experience with breakfast was very poor."
> **- John (2/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-bodega-1.jpg','096 053 5838','124, 20 Had Lama Rd, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84130, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://linktr.ee/labodegasamui','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.133+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.133+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-bodega-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-bodega-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3483009122661839231',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('la-cantina','standard','cmr07iguh00fcq8xdjqk27vzc','La Cantina','## Top Reviews
> "This place is really nice, we had a great dinner for 5 people and enjoyed it. Rib eyes were great, the Mexican food was great we enjoyed everything. The owner came to check up on us, and so did several from the staff. The view to the ocean and beachfront is great. Only minor inconvenience was that one of the waiters was “to eager” to clean off. And was almost on standby looking over our table. Everything else spot on, and yes it cost some money but to us it seems worth it."
> **- Nicklas Krog (5/5/5)**

> "Great central location. We been at lunch time, very quiet, beautiful beach views. Food was fresh, well cooked and presented. Long wait for food. Tourist prices."
> **- Dylan Ddl (5/5/5)**

> "Come here if you’d like to vomit the night of, and the morning after you’ve eaten here!!! the quality of food certainly is not on par with what the prices are.  Birria tacos tasted worse than taco bell. Consume was mediocre. Overall 1-10: at most a 1 Pasta was saltier than the ocean. 1-10, pasta would get a score of 0. Basically inedible. And the fried fish (fish and chips) was somewhat edible. 1-10: around a 3  Food wasn’t even digestible. I threw up the 1,600 baht meal within 10 hours of eating it.  Don’t recommend going here whatsoever!! Can find cheaper food with better quality and taste. Just cause it’s in fisherman’s village doesn’t mean it’s going to be good!! Beware!!! Hopefully this restaurant can use this feedback and do something good of it. Totally disappointed. Night and morning ruined with stomach pain and rounds of vomiting."
> **- Lukas Williams (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-cantina-1.jpg','077 310 742','Fisherman Village, 54, 2 2, ตำบล บ่อผุด Koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/lacantinafishermanvillage/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 1:00 AM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 1:00 AM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 1:00 AM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 1:00 AM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 1:00 AM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 1:00 AM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 1:00 AM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.137+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.137+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-cantina-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-cantina-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7363956716021887800',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('la-cte-de-boeuf','standard','cmr07iguj00fdq8xd4wadl00w','La Côte De Boeuf','## Top Reviews
> "I really loved this place. The food was delicious, especially the steak. The atmosphere is lovely, with a well-designed layout that separates the bar area from the dining area, making it comfortable and relaxing. The owner is very friendly, and the staff are nice and attentive."
> **- rapatr matinrat (4/5/5)**

> "For a little variety and if you''re really in the mood for good French cuisine, this restaurant is a great tip! We went there twice because it was so delicious. The staff were very professional and friendly, and they had a great wine list! Thank you for the lovely evenings!"
> **- Sa Je (5/5/5)**

> "This is the highest level of service quality I have experienced in Samui. The staff was unbelievably well trained, and the entrecôte was simply perfect, served with bone marrow and homeade french fries. Amazing selection of wines at very fair prices. If I could give more than 5 stars I would!"
> **- Cyril Vallotton (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-cte-de-boeuf-1.jpg','098 990 0217','30/26, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.lacotedeboeufsamui.com/','["Monday: 6:30 – 10:30 PM","Tuesday: 6:30 – 10:30 PM","Wednesday: Closed","Thursday: 6:30 – 10:30 PM","Friday: 6:30 – 10:30 PM","Saturday: 6:30 – 10:30 PM","Sunday: 6:30 – 10:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.139+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.139+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-cte-de-boeuf-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-cte-de-boeuf-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17251536869949378500',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('la-fourchette','standard','cmr07igul00feq8xdz8xl6lcm','La Fourchette','## Top Reviews
> "Laurent and Mama are adorable. The products are high-quality and you can even find good French wine. For a French moment in Koh Samui, I recommend it 100%. Thanks again for the fondue. Looking forward to seeing you again"
> **- Francois Bluteau (5/5/5)**

> "It is our second time here. One of the best restaurants in Lamai. We ordered tartar and snails, everything was top notch. Will definitely return next year Approved"
> **- Volodymyr Kostyrko (5/5/5)**

> "We went there for fondue 🫕 and it was amazing. So, we went again to see if the second time experience will match the love at first sight type of experience, so ordered the cheese fondue again. Turned out to be even better and yum. Cant wait to go back again and try other items from the menu. And the homemade desserts were top. Wow wow wow thank you chef"
> **- Roshani Bajracharya (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-fourchette-1.jpg','081 382 1280','Had Lamai 1 84/46 Moo 3, ตำบล มะเร็ต Koh Samaui, Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100063710466636','["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Friday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.141+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.141+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-fourchette-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-fourchette-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=519280679159652284',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('la-lanterna','standard','cmr07iguo00ffq8xd28xjzjrh','La Lanterna','## Top Reviews
> "This is an amazing place, I rarely write reviews, but I wanted to write one. The pizza is the most delicious I''ve ever had, and the tiramisu is a delicate paradise. The only minor downside is the smell of cleaning products at first, but the pizza acts as a magic pill, eliminating it. It''s also reassuring to know that the place is clean."
> **- Владимир Сильнычий (5/5/5)**

> "I wish it was acceptable to eat Italian every night on our Thai holiday. This food was to die for. Like many other reviews were staying at the Sheraton and wanted something outside the resort but close by. I needed gluten free because my husband saw the gnocchi and was set in going to La Lanterna. Not even mad that there was only one pasta option for me because it was THAT good. Service includes free bread."
> **- LB M (5/5/5)**

> "At Nello’s, quality is immediately clear! I had the Pizza Nello and it was simply outstanding – light and crispy crust, the freshest ingredients, and authentic flavors that take you straight to Italy with the first bite. Friendly and attentive service, cozy atmosphere. A true landmark for great pizza in Koh Samui. Compliments to Nello and his team!"
> **- Luca Foschi (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-lanterna-1.jpg','098 681 7477','82/19, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://lalanternasamui.com/','["Monday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig5c0051q8xdykrbexft','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.144+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.144+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-lanterna-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-lanterna-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2656602838517423070',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('la-marine-lakeside','standard','cmr07igus00fgq8xdiicgs7av','La Marine Lakeside','## Top Reviews
> "Restaurant by the lake.  We visited regularly trying out different dishes and desserts.  Meat quality was very good, lean and tender. The sides of green salad and fried potatoes were stars.  The operators were friendly. Staff were polite and attentive. A very pleasant place to dine.  Highly recommended."
> **- Martlet (5/5/5)**

> "Absolutely wonderful. Gorgeous setting down by the lake and such a lovely atmosphere. The service was fantastic, never a glass left empty or feeling like you needed to call for someone''s attention. The food was awesome, can''t express enough. Wonderful cuts of beef from the North of Thailand. Absolutely delightful experience and we will definitely be back!! Fantastic from entry to exit 🙌❤"
> **- Zoe Thomas (5/5/5)**

> "We had a fantastic evening here. Everybody’s food was absolutely delicious. The karaoke was amazing and created such a fun atmosphere, and the staff were incredibly attentive throughout the night. A special mention to the owner Manalow who was wonderful and made sure everything ran smoothly. Great food, great service, and a brilliant vibe, we’ll definitely be back!"
> **- NICHOLAS EDWARDS (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-marine-lakeside-1.jpg','080 246 0173','83/76 Moo2, Chaweng Beach Rd, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.148+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.148+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-marine-lakeside-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-marine-lakeside-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12392489884611657058',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('la-perle-resort','standard','cmr07iguv00fhq8xdivr9y0zt','La Perle Resort','## Top Reviews
> "Located on Koh Samui’s north coast, we stayed in one of two beachfront villas with a private pool. We were picked up at our arrival pier by taxi arranged by the hotel, we rented a vehicle for our time which was also arranged by the hotel staff, as was our onward travel upon leaving so can’t fault their helpfulness. Location was great too - quiet enough to feel relaxed by the beach and our pool but also close enough to the busy hustle and bustle of central Koh Samui. Reception is open from 8am-9pm so any queries outwith those hours has to be done via WhatsApp and the kitchen/bar closes at 4pm which was disappointingly early because there aren’t many eating places nearby so without a vehicle we would have struggled for food and had to order via Grab. The villa itself was good, very spacious and comfortable but there were issues. Firstly the door to the villa was a nightmare to lock - it’s a sliding door and the two panels didn’t seem like they fit together properly unless you physically forced them together. Even while pushing the panels together it didn’t lock easily at all - it took us a good 5-10 mins on our first try and really it shouldn’t be that hard to lock a door. Secondly, the interior needs refreshing, there were plaster marks and stains on some walls which again was very disappointing given its advertisement as a ‘luxury boutique hotel’. The private pool was great, especially being right on the beach but it had a lot of leaves and debris in it which I had to remove myself, I don’t think we saw the pool being cleaned once during our stay. There were rust marks around the edge as well and one of the lights in the pool didn’t work either so that area could also do with a refresh. Each morning I felt my throat sore and dry after leaving the air conditioning on, something I haven’t noticed in any other of our stays on our trip so I wonder when it was last cleaned/serviced. The shower was also a let down, it was lukewarm at best and wasn’t very powerful. We were also charged for a broken plate that wasn’t our fault which we felt very unfair given it wasn’t broken prior to us leaving for the day but after we returned in the evening and our room had been cleaned it was laying broken. Despite protesting, the receptionist insisted we pay and we felt we had no choice. Not the worst stay but certainly not the best and don’t believe it should be advertised as a ‘4 star luxury boutique hotel’."
> **- Lauren Methven (3/5/5)**

> "Food:  Excellent restaurant located at the hotel. Tasty food and very good shakes.  Service 5/5  Overall I would definitely recommend this place for a beach day. We would have stayed for dinner, but unfortunately the restaurant closes after sunset."
> **- Сергей Х (5/5/5)**

> "We spent 10 days at La Perle. The location is beautiful, beach with white sand. The area is peaceful, perfect for relaxing. The staff is super friendly and helpful. The food is good, you can rent a motorbike to discover the island or book an island tour at the reception. (Or other activities) There are a couple other restaurants and two supermarkets in 10 min. walk."
> **- József Pitzinger (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-perle-resort-1.jpg','077 447 127','78/20 5 Bantai, เทศบาลนครเกาะสมุย Maenam, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.2,0,0,0,NULL,'https://laperlesamui.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifso000kq8xdfe9gpaon','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.151+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.151+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-perle-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-perle-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12575403377930594579',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('la-rhumerie-de-koh-samui','standard','cmr07igux00fiq8xd6lrc019m','La Rhumerie De Koh Samui','## Top Reviews
> "Introduced to me by my friend Tony. This place is incredibly nice and pleasant. The setting is relaxing with a bohemian lifestyle. We were greeted warmly by the owner Fanny. She introduced me to their own made Rum. It was very flavourful. Highly recommended! We ordered the mixed plate, pizza Regina and ending with Ba Ba au Rhum, a desert. The pictures below says it all...delicious! Don''t miss this place when in Samui."
> **- Lee Soon Guan (5/5/5)**

> "Great hidden gem. The rum and home-made syrup was really good. Lovely location, with friendly staff. Recommend the pizza"
> **- Alrike Coetzee (5/5/5)**

> "Rhum and Islands -- a good fit! This is a great stop if you''re in the south end of this island. The pizza was excellent, and the staff were lovely folks who walked us through the whole rum tasting thing :) If it''s a hot day and you''ve ridden all the way from the North end, I believe you can also take a dip in their pool."
> **- Chrys Fernandez (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-rhumerie-de-koh-samui-1.jpg','099 275 9284','44, Namuang, 5, Tambon Na Mueang, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/larhumeriedesamui','["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifzl002uq8xdaadxjuc2','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.153+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.153+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-rhumerie-de-koh-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-rhumerie-de-koh-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16317939151692199159',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('la-vida','standard','cmr07igv000fjq8xda4pzpzmo','La Vida','## Top Reviews
> "An Absolute Gem in the Heart of Chaweng! ​An amazing hotel that is perfectly suited for couples looking for a romantic getaway. ​The location is unbeatable—right in the heart of Chaweng, yet surprisingly quiet and peaceful. We stayed in a Sea View Suite, which was incredibly spacious and offered stunning views. ​Highlights of our stay: ​The Beach: Pristine, very clean, and fully equipped with everything you might need. ​Facilities: The pools are fantastic and well-maintained. ​Service: Exceptional service across the board. When we had a minor issue with a clogged toilet, the maintenance team fixed it immediately. ​Cleanliness: Housekeeping did a great job cleaning the room every single day. ​Dining: A very good breakfast with a nice variety. ​The staff is incredible and truly service-oriented. Bottom line: This hotel is highly recommended and definitely worth it!"
> **- Arie Derzie (5/5/5)**

> "Hotel was generally ok. Our check in wasn''t the smoothest process (despite arriving a day late) as we were taken to the wrong room. Resulting in a walk back up to the reception whilst they sorted this out. This meant our room wasn''t ready and we had to wait around 20 mins for them to prepare it. Being in the only premium room in the hotel we expected a little extra treatment from the hotel but this wasn''t the case. The only difference between this and the other rooms is the private pool- which wasn''t that big or deep enough to really enjoy. There was no turn down service either which we expected for a 4 star hotel. Meaning that you were left with only 4 bottles of water each day to last until the next room clean. If you wanted more this was extra (as per the sign in the mini bar fridge). Breakfast is basic, with a range of pastries, fruit etc. Easy to walk to the town - around 15 mins and a 7 eleven pretty much across the road. Check out process again wasn''t smooth, as they forgot which room we were in, making this unnecessarily longer than it should have been. We were a little disappointed in the price of the room and what we got. Advice if you''re thinking of going here - just book a standard room and save your money"
> **- Rebecca (3/5/5)**

> "Grounds are lovely.  Bar and kitchen staff are friendly and helpful.  For the price AUD $300 per night ( and we stayed 7 nights), the accommodation would best be described as average. There is nowhere to put your clothes besides 7 coat hangers.  I was advised we could put our clothes on the rack above the toilet???  There is cable tv only (not all channels work) and tvs do not allow you to connect to your B own streaming accounts.  Over the last 3 days I was unwell with a cold and when I requested some for my tea, was advised could not be obtained from kitchen that time of night …8pm  Basic to average at best"
> **- Jo Clunes (2/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-vida-1.jpg','077 234 000','101 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.lavidasamui.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.156+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.156+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-vida-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-vida-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4687994866798418720',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('la-villa-luna','standard','cmr07igv200fkq8xd6uu9jm94','La Villa Luna','## Top Reviews
> "This French restaurant offers a truly unique dining experience right by the beach. Visiting during sunset is absolutely magical—watching the sun dip into the ocean while enjoying your meal creates a romantic and unforgettable atmosphere. 🌅✨ The interior reflects a classic French elegance, while the outdoor seating is the real highlight, allowing you to enjoy the cool ocean breeze and stunning sea views. The food is exceptional. Each dish is beautifully presented, with rich and well-balanced flavors that capture the essence of authentic French cuisine. Service is equally impressive, with friendly and attentive staff who make the entire experience even more enjoyable. Overall, this is the perfect spot for a date night, anniversary, or any special occasion. Great food, breathtaking sunset views, and a relaxing beach atmosphere—all in one place. Definitely a hidden gem worth visiting."
> **- Htoo Lay (5/5/5)**

> "We were craving something different from Thai food and decided to visit this place for dinner. Samui food scene keeps impressing me! Even the restaurant is not at a central location, it has a lot of customers, which is always a good sign. The menu is diverse with choices of meet, fish and pizzas.  I was absolutely impressed by truffle Camembert. I also tried Thai style tartar, which was also interesting twist on a traditional tartar dish, and the only downside is my husband ordered a steak to be medium but it came “well done”, he nevertheless thoroughly enjoyed it, especially with the mushroom sauce that was with it. You can see that people here like what they do and pay great attention to everything from service to the atmosphere. Great place to visit for a couple or family dinner."
> **- Daria Zhuravleva (5/5/5)**

> "Big potential but I had the poorest and saddest panacotta of my life and paid  200thb for it. The burger was ok . Employees are not thai and boss neither. Explications about the menu not really clear still don''t know what is the Mediterranean burger. I am a local and have been around , there is some work and improvement needed. Nice spot on the beach easy to park and quiet and clean place. Restaurant well decorated and music not loud."
> **- Houss Ni (2/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-villa-luna-1.jpg','063 084 0170','4169, Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: Closed","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifs1000cq8xdfo2aau32','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.158+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.158+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-villa-luna-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/la-villa-luna-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15000639914121098221',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('lago','standard','cmr07igv400flq8xd3x3k7c38','Lago','## Top Reviews
> "A precious public space, close to Chaweng''s main street. It''s great for jogging and walking, though the concrete walkway is a tad too ugly and the land along much of the pathway has been flattened for some development of sorts. It would be nice if a lot more trees and bushes were planted along the periphery of the lake to provide shade and keep the area cool. I noticed bird trappers in the area, sadly, trapping spotted doves, and people in the area use the walkway for their scooters, endangering themselves and the joggers/walkers. The Lake is at its best in the evening when a cool breeze makes the whole area pleasant. There are clean, free toilets and an outdoor gym, as well. The lake on the Chaweng side has been beautified with flowering plants and several large trees provide roosting for a variety of birds. Would be great if they make this into a bird sanctuary."
> **- Saurabh (4/5/5)**

> "nice lake with concrete walk way around & a dirt road/path too. was to lazy to walk around so i motorbiked..). met some kids around there that were popping wheelies with their bikes. few locals fishing & having a picnic. recommended"
> **- SICILIAN-AMERICAN (4/5/5)**

> "The Lake is a very popular running / jogging spot, and it even has some exercise equipment on the southeastern end.  One full lap of the lake is approximately 6.8km.  I would suggest running in at sunrise or late afternoon before dusk or the sun will bake you. Secondly: there are no lights illuminating the walkway.  At certain days, there is a night market and on holiday even bigger events.  Lots of parking options for your scooter or car. Red taxi also frequently pass by.  Sadly, no boats or something available. Swimming is out of the question as well. Water is rather murky."
> **- Sören Dittrich (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lago-1.jpg',NULL,'Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.160+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.160+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lago-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lago-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13806579599407789197',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('lai-thai','standard','cmr07igv600fmq8xdukc8hnge','Lai Thai','## Top Reviews
> "Many strong points.  1. Nice View. Beautiful scene. 2. Good Price. 3. Kindness  If you have a chance to visit there You can see the heaven in there. Whatever You must visit there."
> **- YOUNGJO YOON (5/5/5)**

> "This is a family run restaurant Inexpensive, great view+ sunset. All the food is freshly prepared(never frozen or packet) Traditional Thai but with European choices they lunderstand English. Friendly staff"
> **- Louise Innocent (4/5/5)**

> "Very friendly owner! Tasty food with an breathtaking view! And so cheap, you won''t belive... :)"
> **- Dominik J. Becker (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lai-thai-1.jpg',NULL,'Taling Ngam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifso000kq8xdfe9gpaon','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.162+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.162+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lai-thai-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lai-thai-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=523483407446382220',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('lajava-beach-lounge','standard','cmr07igv800fnq8xdd1idew6n','Lajava Beach Lounge','## Top Reviews
> "The most authentic french menu I can find in Samui. Set in a very very "
> **- Leena Chanvirach (5/5/5)**

> "A beautiful place, a hidden gem with a selection of European and Thai dishes. I found this place by looking for restaurants near me.. seen the photo of the fish dish and thought I have to try this, let’s go! Phillip let me know that the fish may take a little while as it requires preparation and I was happy with that as we were there for sunset and not in a hurry - we are on holiday right.. it was worth the wait indeed! My husband and I shared the dish and the crumbed pork also. Everything was fresh and cooked aldente. I tried Phillips selection of French wine and bought a bottle of Chandon which was also a reasonable price and his chocolate desert - a perfect balance of ingredients. This place really felt homely.. was lovely to spend the time here, we walked out on the waterfront and chatted with Phillip. Food is really 5 stars, we’re looking forward to having another meal here! I’d come back to Samui to spend time here again. Thank you Phillip, Nit and Daisy for your beautiful food and hospitality xo"
> **- Mike Schoers (5/5/5)**

> "Discovered by chance. Such a charming restaurant in a very simple idyllic setting by the sea and rustic road to get to. The owner is French together with his Thai wife. She does the cooking and the food is superb and authentic."
> **- Lee Soon Guan (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lajava-beach-lounge-1.jpg','087 271 5533','26/2 Ban Thongkrut, Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 12:00 – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: Closed","Thursday: 12:00 – 8:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 8:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07igdj008fq8xdhc2mye6x','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.164+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.164+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lajava-beach-lounge-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lajava-beach-lounge-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3498841208391434623',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('lamai-buri-resort','standard','cmr07igva00foq8xdjsunfywz','Lamai Buri Resort','## Top Reviews
> "I really liked to stay here, we extended our stay. After we made some bad experience in Lamai with different Hotels we were scared of booking more then one night, but this was our favorite Hotel in our price range. We paid 55€ for our Room. This Hotel got a really nice pool area and insane kind staff, the way to the beach isn''t too long."
> **- Stiefen (5/5/5)**

> "Good location.. beautiful pool area. Modern clean..nice gardens..service really friendly and helpful. Car parking. For me the rooms were very basic and uncomfortable so wouldn''t stay again..well.worth it if not going to spend long jn room as pool is really nice but bed uncomfortable and really didn''t want to stay any longer... gorgeous pool. Staff great. Everything clean"
> **- Paul (4/5/5)**

> "Really nice hotel extended my stay for a few days. Staff was amazing would go back"
> **- gemma harvey (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lamai-buri-resort-1.jpg',NULL,'Maret, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.2,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.hotelssuratthani.com/lamai-buri-resort/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.166+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.166+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lamai-buri-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lamai-buri-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11469977378459168802',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('lamai-chalet-resort','standard','cmr07igve00fpq8xdrn7v6odu','Lamai Chalet Resort','## Top Reviews
> "We really enjoyed our stay. The house is right by the sea — just a few steps and you’re on the beach. Waking up to the sound of waves was very nice. The place is clean and well maintained. Cleaning was regular, with fresh towels and clean bed linen. The area is quiet and calm, good for resting and sleeping. No noise, just the sea. The host was friendly and easy to communicate with, always replied quickly. Good place if you want a calm stay by the sea. We would stay here again."
> **- Elnikov Semyon (5/5/5)**

> "**risk to health** pillows are covered in black mould, mattress even worse, cockroaches everywhere and not small ones while over 2 inches, can''t walk down the road to hotel at night as down 400 metres unlight dirt track, no security or anybody on reception at night so hotel totally unsecure via road or beach. I booked in for 4 nights but lasted less than 48 hours explained to manager why leaving and got a smile and told very good Don''t think cleaning staff even cleaned room properly before given to us and handed air freshener when entering"
> **- Rebekah Dawson (1/5/5)**

> "HIGHLY NOT RECOMMENDED 🤬🤬🤬 Disappointing Experience  I would like to share my unsatisfactory experience at this chalet. I made a reservation six months in advance and was shocked upon arrival to find that my room had been replaced with a very poor-quality one. Despite requesting a room with two single beds, I was given a large bed.  Furthermore, the bathroom was extremely dirty, and the overall condition of the hotel was unsatisfactory. I also observed similar issues experienced by other travelers, where reservations and payments had been made, but upon check-in, the chalet was already full.  This experience is highly discouraging and reflects poor management. The reservation system should guarantee the desired room and maintain the cleanliness of the hotel. I hope the management can improve their services and ensure a more positive stay for future customers."
> **- Mohd Saad (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lamai-chalet-resort-1.jpg','094 949 0916','127 127/9 Thanon Had Lamai, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/lamaichalets/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.170+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.170+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lamai-chalet-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lamai-chalet-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1835261223487552243',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('lamai-coconut-beach-resort','standard','cmr07igvo00fqq8xdsaltgmhx','Lamai Coconut Beach Resort','## Top Reviews
> "Perfect. Bungalow close to the beach and close to lamai beach road. Everything clean, awesome breakfast. Small nice Pool and space at the beach. Coming here since 3 years."
> **- Nico S (5/5/5)**

> "A lot of weed people(resort guests and visitors ) coming to smoke on this resort beach chairs/bed and resort common area. Even you sit on your balcony bangalow, smoke is coming your way ... Most of guests need to leave their beach chairs to be somewhere else to avoid the smoke. No rules no signs in the area or anywhere ... According to front desk staffs, it''s not prohibited to smoke weeds around the resort common area. The resort has no restrictions (even it''s against the law to smoke in opened area where it can disturb people ) and other resorts have big signs No smoking and No weed on the beach and common area but this resort seems to be happy to entertain these weed smokers) Babies, kids and families try to enjoy their holiday, they need to inhale the weed smoke or not able to enjoy on the beach even they are the resort guests. What a big disappointment.!!!! The resort itself is not too bad, just don''t understand why they don''t want to try to make their resort free from bad behaviors and even illegal doing while other resorts in the area put very big no smoking, no weed signs."
> **- LL Ac (1/5/5)**

> "I booked a bungalow and was very satisfied with my stay. The hotel is located directly on Lamai beach. The hotel grounds are very clean and have a pool. The bungalow was also good, and the hotel staff were very friendly and accommodating."
> **- Marco B. (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lamai-coconut-beach-resort-1.jpg','077 332 589','124, 4, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.lamaicoconutbeachresort.com/','["Monday: 6:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 6:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 6:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 6:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 6:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 6:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 6:00 AM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.180+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.180+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lamai-coconut-beach-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lamai-coconut-beach-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1233653002526126314',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('lamai-fitness-retreat','standard','cmr07igw200frq8xd2cu6iom7','Lamai Fitness Retreat','## Top Reviews
> "I had a wonderful stay and an amazing time at the Lamai Fitness Retreat, and I highly recommend it to everyone—it was an extraordinary experience. The atmosphere at the retreat is incredible, and I felt right at home from the very beginning, even though I went there alone.  I was there for two and a half weeks and did the weight loss program. They’ve thought of everything—from the beautiful accommodations and three delicious, healthy meals a day to a personal trainer, great facilities, a super varied class schedule, and so much more.  The personal training sessions with Lewis were the highlight; he pushed me to my limits, and I learned a lot about training and nutrition. Everyone else on the team was also very friendly, motivating, and always helpful.  Now that some time has passed, I can say with pride and continued motivation that the stay has had a lasting impact on me. I’ve been able to transfer some of what I learned into my daily life and am once again giving exercise and nutrition a much higher priority."
> **- Jonas Glaser (5/5/5)**

> "I spent 4+ weeks training at Lamai Fitness. They provide great variety of classes, well-equipped facilities, and delicious balanced meals. But what truly made the difference were the coaches — their professional, personalized approach helped me improve my physique and build confidence.  Huge thanks to: Andy – breathwork classes are a must, especially if focus and calm don’t come naturally. Baikey – mobility sessions saved my body during intense training, and the gentle motivation and professional advice helped me run my first 10k. Eve – always there to help with anything practical which saved me a headache. Love the sound healing as well.  Also, you’ll always know when Eve and Baikey are around — their laughter fills the gym and creates the best atmosphere.  What could improve : 30 min PT session is not enough. I assumed it’s 50 min. The food could have a bit more variety on weightless programme."
> **- Anna Zoltek (5/5/5)**

> "You can search and search to find a retreat as good as Lamai Fitness Retreat. If you feel Big, small, strong or needing to get there, this is the perfect place for YOU!! I loved every session with my PT Laura! Very knowledgeable and we had lots of laughs and fun! Everything you need is right here. Accommodation onsite or nearby. Fully set up gym Onsite cafe (Harry is my favourite barista and smoothie maker, I miss you Harry🤗 Fabulous, caring Personal Trainers Daily PT sessions Massages daily if you want Access to resort pool, spas and sauna Breath work sessions Sound healing sessions Yoga Their success is in.your success! Thank you dearest beautiful people! William, Laura, Eve, Pikey, Harry, Lewis, Bo and everyone else that made me feel more than welcome! ❤️"
> **- Suzanna Palombi (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lamai-fitness-retreat-1.jpg','096 983 8394','136/74 Moo 4 Thanon Had Lamai, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.lamaifitnessretreat.com/','["Monday: 6:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 6:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 6:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 6:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 6:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 3:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 3:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.194+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.194+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lamai-fitness-retreat-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lamai-fitness-retreat-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13342504931350799644',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('lamai-football-club','standard','cmr07igw400fsq8xdubf4vbvr','Lamai Football Club','## Top Reviews
> "Lamai football Club is a great place for kids of all ages, to come and develop new skills and meet new friends. The coaches are professional, kind and work diligently with every student to help them reach bigger and better goals. If you like football, why not come along and give it a try."
> **- Russell Shinnie (5/5/5)**

> "Very happy with my child’s progress and development while being at LFC. Coach has great interaction skills to keep the kids interested and progressing. Everything has been very clear and professional from management, definitely recommend it to anyone thinking of joining."
> **- Rob Deans (5/5/5)**

> "Excellent football club with great coaches and facilities. Welcomes children of  a range of ages and abilities, with both male and female made to feel part off the Lamai football family."
> **- Steven Christy (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lamai-football-club-1.jpg','096 983 8394','136 Lamai, 74 Thanon Had Lamai, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.lamaifootballclub.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.196+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.196+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lamai-football-club-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lamai-football-club-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4276158787608821355',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('lamai-inn-99','standard','cmr07igw600ftq8xdu3c6ig6s','Lamai Inn 99','## Top Reviews
> "The room is average, nothing special. The lighting is terrible, and the electrical system is faulty; if you turn off the light, the phone charger disconnects.  The bathroom doesn''t have an extractor fan and the internet is terrible.  The good thing is that it has parking and is close to the beach."
> **- Chris “Chris” Diaz (3/5/5)**

> "The hotel is in an amazing location just walk across the road to the beach and restaurants. The grounds are nice and pool area is great. We got two rooms and although very dated they were neat tidy, aircon worked, comfortable. We stayed for 5 nights and had no issues enjoyed the stay and would recommend on location alone!"
> **- christian howard (4/5/5)**

> "Good room, however if you dont like Bugs then DO NOT stay here as there are loads of cicadas bugs in the trees which make loud screeching sounds.  Around 10pm they fall onto the stairs of the room…  Beds sheets are clean but the walls not so clean. They need a refurbishment on the rooms."
> **- Zubair Amini (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lamai-inn-99-1.jpg','077 424 212','109/11 หมู่3 Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.2,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.lamaiinn.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.198+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.198+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lamai-inn-99-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lamai-inn-99-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13569773221897412525',NULL,NULL);
