INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('lamphu-kitchen','standard','cmr07igwe00fwq8xd4gmow19s','Lamphu Kitchen','## Top Reviews
> "This restaurant offers healthy vegan food with great taste. The dishes are flavorful and well-prepared, making it a perfect choice for anyone looking for nutritious options. The place is beautifully decorated in a loft style, creating a relaxing and cozy atmosphere inside. The prices are reasonable for the quality and experience. Highly recommended!"
> **- VenusKK (5/5/5)**

> "Beautifully stunning food. Funny how healthy and energizing all dishes I tried were tasting.  Unfortunately I forgot to take a photo of the seabass, which was top notch. Coffee is great. Assortment of kombucha probably the only place on the island to get such a variety. Keep doing what you’re doing! Khop khun krap"
> **- Michael Grillhösl (5/5/5)**

> "Cosy health food cafe in Lamai that caters well for vegans which is always a positive! I recommend the tofu salad and the sweet potato tonkatsu sauce. The Go Green Juice is also elite."
