INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('lananas-restaurant','standard','cmr07igwh00fxq8xdce5t841k','L’Ananas Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "🩷🩷🩷L’Ananas Restaurant  Perfect place for a sunset cocktail 🥹🌅 you sit right by the sea, soft light, calm atmosphere… just pure bliss  you don’t come here for the food — you come for the feeling 💛"
> **- Elvira (5/5/5)**

> "Excellent restaurant with authentic Thai food prepared by Thai chefs. The food is outstanding, and the staff are very kind and helpful. Highly recommended."
> **- Cédric T (5/5/5)**

> "L''Ananas restaurant is located in The Sunset Beach Resort, just next to the Intercontinental Resort. I''ve been past many times and never quite know whether the restaurant is open.  It was open today, so I decided to come in for lunch.  The restaurant has very stylish and modern decor, and it''s beautifully located on Taling Ngam beach. A really relaxing atmosphere with a very refreshing breeze today.  The menu is a bit limited,  but they do have several popular Thai dishes. I had gaprow gai (chicken) which was very nicely presented and vegetable spring rolls.  Both tasted fine.  The prices were good for a hotel restaurant.  They don''t have scan, so I paid in cash.  I hope the restaurant continues to be open."
> **- Paul Glickman (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lananas-restaurant-1.jpg','077 428 200','126/9, The Sunset Beach Resort, ตำบล ตลิ่งงาม อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.thesunsetbeachresort.com/restaurants','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ift8000pq8xd7yujz20i','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.209+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.209+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lananas-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lananas-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13125120198074607627',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('lavaled','standard','cmr07igwj00fyq8xd3mr52991','LAVALED','## Top Reviews
> "Fun experience My boys had a blast and even the dad participated and sweated. Fun experience My boys had a blast and even the dad participated and sweated. חוויה מהנה הבנים שלי נהנו מאוד ואפילו האבא השתתף והזיע.  The owner of the place is very nice and agreed that the little girl would also participate at no extra charge, made her feel welcome. Highly recommend! You also get a bottle of drink at the end;) We will be back soon!"
> **- Shanni Zohar (5/5/5)**

> "We recently celebrated a birthday at Lava Land Koh Samui, and it was honestly such a wonderful experience. 🎉 From the moment we arrived, the team made us feel incredibly welcome. They had beautifully decorated the space for the celebration and truly took care of every little detail so we could just relax and enjoy the moment. The place itself is amazing colorful, fun, and full of great energy. The kids had an absolute blast, and the whole atmosphere made the celebration feel really special. What stood out the most was the kindness of the staff. Everyone was so friendly, attentive, and genuinely happy to help. It’s rare to find a place where the team puts so much heart into making sure families have a great time. Thank you, Lava Land, for helping us create such a joyful birthday celebration and beautiful memories. We’ll definitely be back! 💛  Highly recommended for families looking for a fun and magical place to celebrate."
> **- ליאל אלנקוה (5/5/5)**

> "Great fun, did a game for 2, we had a blast! I recommend 100% for original fun also protected from the blazing sun!"
> **- Eva Noub (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lavaled-1.jpg','080 746 2360','162, 161 moo2, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.thelavaled.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.211+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.211+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lavaled-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lavaled-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5710908304558470806',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('lay-lagom','standard','cmr07igwk00fzq8xdqb4v9shj','Lay Lagom','## Top Reviews
> "Wonderful beachside cafe in koh samui. Really loved the vibe & ambience. Went there to have breakfast, pancakes were amazing. Staffs were very friendly. A perfect place to spend quality time with family/friends/alone. Also ideal for remote working. Must visit😋❤️"
> **- Shouvik Mukherjee (5/5/5)**

> "Really nice location and atmosphere. The café is pet-friendly and even provided a water bowl for our dog, which was a nice touch. However, there are three big dogs at the restaurant, so we had to keep an eye on our surroundings.  The coffee is good, and the pasta was really delicious. I finished the whole plate. The chicken cashew nut was a bit unusual though, as it mostly tasted like tomato sauce."
> **- Doenpen Surapong (4/5/5)**

> "Nothing beats the feeling of having meal overseeing the ocean, listening to the sea breeze....and accompanied by chillax acoustic songs.  Everything I had here was good. The staff are very nice and hospitable.  I came here after reading positive reviews and it didn''t disappoint.  Come here if you are really hungry and want to unwind at the same time."
> **- Cathy Nelson (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lay-lagom-1.jpg','062 456 6900','73/23 Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/laylagom.cafe.bar','["Monday: 8:30 AM – 1:00 AM","Tuesday: 4:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 1:00 AM","Thursday: 8:30 AM – 1:00 AM","Friday: 8:30 AM – 1:00 AM","Saturday: 8:30 AM – 1:00 AM","Sunday: 8:30 AM – 10:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifs1000cq8xdfo2aau32','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.212+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.212+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lay-lagom-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lay-lagom-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13623928821862400684',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('le-bistro','standard','cmr07igwm00g0q8xd8jfbbt9h','Le Bistro','## Top Reviews
> "Well the food was really good! If you are looking for an early morning place to have breakfast, then this is a very good option.  The breakfast menu is solid gold and quite a lot of variety you can choose from.  The staff was very kind and helpful.  The atmosphere was a bit hot and they dont have indoor seating or air conditioning. So, it gets pretty intense lol.  Also, price could have been a bit less, believe!  All in all, a quite good experience!"
> **- Fahiim Shahriar Shovon (4/5/5)**

> "I wanted a clean simple yet satisfying meal to stay on track with fitness goals. I saw ale Bistro and I was not disappointed. The service was a bit slow but then I saw there was one lady in the kitchen cheffing it up. It was well worth the wait!The chicken was juicy, sauce was light, vegetables were grilled, fries were PERFECT!"
> **- Lexi (5/5/5)**

> "I came like 1 hour before it''s closed, But the staff was still nice to me but little bit too close to me because they wanted to go back home, I guess. But They were still friendly and were ready to serve.  The steak was cooked to what I desired, And the French fries was nice.  I think my only issue is that it was very hot. Even though it was night, And the fans Don''t make the place more chill to stay in."
> **- taz mazia (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/le-bistro-1.jpg','064 017 3803','Haven Samui Community Mall, 888 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61566745734873&mibextid=ZbWKwL','["Monday: 8:30 AM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 8:30 AM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 8:30 AM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 8:30 AM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 8:30 AM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.214+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.214+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/le-bistro-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/le-bistro-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8854404316067340987',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('le-blocks','standard','cmr07igwo00g1q8xdjp14bvpj','Le Blocks','## Top Reviews
> "Best place for kids activities in the beautiful Samui island.  Many different choice of play for children of different ages and keep them busy with creative art work like beads and Lego.  Shop staff is also very attentive and understanding to requests to ensure children enjoy their time in Le Block.  A must go place if you are here."
> **- Tan Hock Meng (5/5/5)**

> "A great place for kids to have an awesome time. They can be creative and have fun while being watched by very nice and friendly staff. The service is absolutely worth the money. If you want to go shopping or spend some time without kids while knowing your little angels are in good hands,  this is the place for you."
> **- Chris Gentleman (5/5/5)**

> "Best place for kids. The main reason we come to big C Spending here at least 3-4 hours a week Kids love it Very peaceful, quiet and the kids enjoying every activity they choose. The owner is very friendly and all workers are nice . Highly recommended"
> **- lior levi (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/le-blocks-1.jpg','098 203 3089','129/19 ม.1 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.216+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.216+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/le-blocks-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/le-blocks-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11596508615471178329',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('le-burger-shack-maenam','standard','cmr07igws00g2q8xdhr30b7fo','Le Burger Shack','## Top Reviews
> "We ordered two burgers: the Le Caesar for me and the Le Gourmand for my partner. The Le Caesar was honestly great — the chicken was super fresh, juicy, and the sauce was really good. The Le Gourmand was also delicious, well put together and full of flavor.  We also had the Aspen Fries. They were good, although I personally would’ve liked a bit more truffle and a stronger parmesan flavor. Still, overall pretty solid.  In general, everything was super good. Great taste, good service, and definitely a place we’d come back to. 🍔✨"
> **- Daniela Pardo (5/5/5)**

> "Really good burger and the fries are to die for. I''m used to good fries (because I''m Belgian) but these were incredible! The girl who works there was so sweet and friendly!!"
> **- Nini Michalak (5/5/5)**

> "Very good Burgers and fries! Mint lemonade was very fresh and the sauces were on point."
> **- Celin Karaarslan (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/le-burger-shack-maenam-1.jpg',NULL,'9/9, Subdistrict, ตำบล แม่น้ำ อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.instagram.com/leburgershack/','["Monday: 4:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Tuesday: 4:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Wednesday: 4:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Thursday: 4:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Friday: 4:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Saturday: 4:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Sunday: 4:00 PM – 1:00 AM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.220+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.220+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/le-burger-shack-maenam-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/le-burger-shack-maenam-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4384848109694335368',NULL,NULL);
