INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('le-fournil','standard','cmr07igwx00g4q8xd5aijj8kp','Le Fournil','## Top Reviews
> "Le Fournil French Bakery — A Little Piece of France in Koh Samui!  If you’re looking for an authentic French bakery experience on the island, look no further than Le Fournil. This charming gem in Maenam has been delighting locals and travelers alike since 2011 — and it’s easy to see why!  The coffee here is absolutely divine. Whether you go for a classic Espresso, a velvety Cappuccino, or a refreshing Iced Americano, every cup is crafted with care and passion. The flat white and macchiato are simply perfection — smooth, rich, and full of character.  The menu is unpretentious yet thoughtfully curated — great quality at very reasonable prices. You get real French bakery vibes without the Paris price tag!  The atmosphere is warm and welcoming — a perfect spot to start your morning, catch up with friends, or simply slow down and enjoy life island-style. ☕🥐  Le Fournil is not just a bakery — it’s a daily ritual for anyone lucky enough to discover it. A must-visit on Koh Samui — don’t leave the island without stopping by! 🇫✨"
> **- Denis Yumatov (5/5/5)**

> "French bakery in Thailand. We had the English breakfast which was huge & delicious! The bacon was personally smoked by chief/owner with coconut wood. The croissants were lovely! The orange juice was freshly squeezed and the coffee latte was perfect. Oh the cat was an added bonus."
> **- Cynthia Spilman (5/5/5)**

> "Perfect breakfast in Maenam. French bakery concept with a limited variety of options to select from an each is excellent.  Most remarkable is the sweetest owner/manager of the restaurant who personally takes your order and brings an elegant sweetness to your morning to start the day.  Relax with a coffee and a croissant or have a full English breakfast.  Whatever best fuels your day.  See you again soon."
> **- Frank Taravella (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/le-fournil-1.jpg','085 446 1439','16, Soi 4, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 7:00 AM – 2:00 PM","Tuesday: Closed","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 2:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 2:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 2:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 2:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 2:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.225+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.225+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/le-fournil-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/le-fournil-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13946233386278065144',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('le-relais','standard','cmr07igwz00g5q8xdluir7436','Le Relais','## Top Reviews
> "Tried two pizzas, chicken salad and chocolate mousse. The carnivore pizza was flavorful with generous toppings. The dessert was airy and tasty. Recommended."
> **- Martlet (4/5/5)**

> "We came with kids for Karting and find amazing place with delicious food , Very kind staff and owner. Kids are are happy and parents too ☺️"
> **- Jenny Erez (5/5/5)**

> "Absolutely terrible experience. We waited for 2 full hours, only for the place to suddenly close without telling us anything. When we came at the exact time they told us to, they said they had given our slot to other people! The staff was completely unprofessional and rude, and the whole place is just poorly managed. This karting track is a joke — don''t waste your time or money here. I would give zero stars if I could."
> **- misha zonuk (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/le-relais-1.jpg','080 012 7149','101, 2, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://samuikarting.com/restaurant-bar/',NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.227+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.227+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/le-relais-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/le-relais-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12721176028184071283',NULL,NULL);
