INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('lee-eyelash','standard','cmr07igx300g7q8xdvw6y2spe','Lee Eyelash','## Top Reviews
> "Had the best experience here. Normally stick with my lash girl in the UK but as I’m travelling needed someone great before Christmas. I was not disappointed at all and I’m very picky with high standards! She fit me in at such short notice and was so nice and comforting when I came in. Shes kind, friendly and so skilled! She recommended what would be best for me and honestly my lashes are now stunning!! Thank you so much, if I’m ever in Koh samui again I’ll be back! 10/10 recommend! I never leave reviews so trust me she’s brilliant!!"
> **- Tee Josephine (5/5/5)**

> "Hello girls! I’m on samui for long term and tried find good master but always was no.. I try this and it was my good luck! I loved how quickly she did my lashes. They lasted for a month, beautifully and evenly. Plus, I brought my own lashes from Russia, and she''s a true professional. She has a lot of experience, and it''s immediately obvious.🫶🏾 I tried several salons on Koh Samui and everything was unsuccessful, no one could do my complicated eyelashes.. but she did it 👍🫶🏾"
> **- ANNA Dudanova (5/5/5)**

> "Mali is an incredibly kind person and really knows her craft. Whenever I''m in Koh Samui, I just make an appointment with her, and the lash results are amazing!"
> **- Barbara Edelmann (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lee-eyelash-1.jpg','063 158 8524','21 Bangrak, 5, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.leelashesxxx.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.231+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.231+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lee-eyelash-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lee-eyelash-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13998571528674623023',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('legacy-muscle-universe','standard','cmr07igx600g8q8xdt7xkxvpb','Legacy Muscle Universe','## Top Reviews
> "I recently trained at Legacy Muscle Universe and bought a 10-session pass. Honestly, this is the best gym in Koh Samui and probably even one of the top 10 bodybuilding gyms in Thailand. In terms of equipment and overall bodybuilding setup, I honestly think it’s the best-equipped gym on the island.  Like many other reviews mention, this is a very bodybuilding-oriented gym with a huge amount of machines, which is great if you train seriously. You can tell a lot of people here are passionate about fitness and bodybuilding. There are many experienced lifters and bodybuilders training here, and the atmosphere feels focused and motivating.  There are also a lot of foreigners and tourists, but that’s normal for Koh Samui. Even during the mornings the gym can get quite busy, which shows how popular the place is. I came in low season and I  never saw the gym empty.  The staff are also excellent — very friendly, smiling, professional, and constantly re-racking weights and keeping the gym clean and organized. For me, that makes a huge difference in the overall experience.  The price is a little expensive honestly, but considering this is Koh Samui, I still think the pricing remains fair for the quality of the gym and equipment.  I’ve been living in Bangkok for years, and honestly, even in Bangkok it is extremely rare to find a gym with this level of equipment and overall quality for this kind of price. I can count them on one hand. That’s something they should absolutely keep because it’s one of the gym’s biggest strengths.  Overall, a very serious gym with excellent bodybuilding machines, a good atmosphere, and probably one of the best training environments on the island."
> **- Mathieu Chaumont (5/5/5)**

> "Hands down the best gym on Koh Samui. The space is huge, spotless, and fully air-conditioned — high ceilings, tons of room, and you never have to wait for a machine. The equipment is next-level: it’s kitted out with high-end Bench Fitness gear (the Australian brand), including plate-loaded machines and custom pieces you genuinely won’t find anywhere else in Thailand. Everything is new and maintained constantly.  It’s so much more than a gym, too — there’s a proper podcast and photo studio, group classes (Power Pump, spin, BODYCOMBAT, yoga) led by great coaches, and a spa for recovery. Open 6 AM to 11 PM daily, which makes it easy to fit in around anything.  But the thing that really sets Legacy apart is the staff. Genuinely warm, attentive, and welcoming — you’re treated like family every single time MAKE THE BEST PROTEIN SHAKE ON THE ISLAND 🏝️ The crowd is a healthy mix of beginners and serious lifters, so it’s motivating without ever feeling intimidating. If you’re on Samui and you actually want to train, this is the place. Highly recommend!"
> **- Ben Urquhart (5/5/5)**

> "This gym has everything you need in one place! The equipment is modern, clean, and well-maintained, with plenty of machines and free weights for all workout styles. I also love the variety of classes available — from yoga and Pilates to HIIT and strength training. The instructors are friendly, motivating, and make every class enjoyable. The atmosphere is welcoming, energetic, and perfect for both beginners and experienced gym-goers. Definitely one of the best gyms I’ve been to!"
> **- จุติมาพร สุขสกุล (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/legacy-muscle-universe-1.jpg','082 446 2445','H38M+99H, Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://legacymuscleuniverse.com/','["Monday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifuo0015q8xdfahzrsp4','cmr07ifv2001aq8xdag7cvjgf','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.234+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.234+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/legacy-muscle-universe-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/legacy-muscle-universe-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7496669182087488152',NULL,NULL);
