> "This is a lovely cafe, especially if you want to break from the Thai food. But it does have also several Thai bowls. Portions are decent and tasty. Would definitely come back."
> **- Yaman Akdeniz (4/5/5)**

> "Loved the place! The atmosphere of the interior is nice, the staff are kind, the food is delicious, price is reasonable. I ordered the “two way on toast” and my husband got “salmon avocado toast”, both tasted really yummy and refreshing. My husband also had a cappuccino and said the coffee tastes great. They have rooms for rent on the upper floor even."
> **- Al-Ghalya Al-Mahrooqy (5/5/5)**

> "Awesome breakfast or lunch spot in koh samui !! Every dish we tried was fresh and had a good portion size. The fried calamari is a must try - as well as one of there lovely drinks. Would definitely recommend trying it out !"
> **- Emma Olm (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/little-green-cafe-nathon-1.jpg','062 239 6517','157, 11 ถ. ทวีราษฎร์ภักดี Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'http://facebook.com/littlegreensamui','["Monday: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig1h003iq8xdb1g9nifo','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.263+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.263+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/little-green-cafe-nathon-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/little-green-cafe-nathon-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15588618269184276828',NULL,NULL);
