INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('liv-clinic','standard','cmr07igy200glq8xdm362fl4f','LIV Clinic','## Top Reviews
> "1000/10❤️ Khun Ma’am(คุณแหม่ม) is very professional. She spoke nicely, was very gentle, and always asked if it hurt or felt uncomfortable. The Diode laser is also reasonably priced. The reception staff gave good recommendations and did not push any upselling, which made me feel comfortable. Overall, I’m very impressed"
> **- ปุญญิศา ชะนะ (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing experience from start to finish. The team were incredibly informative, with outstanding attention to detail and genuine care throughout the entire process. The products used were brilliant and the results speak for themselves. I’ve had many procedures done over the years, and this was by far a true five-star experience. Highly recommend! Thank You Dr Naam and Nurse Noona"
> **- Tammy Johnson (5/5/5)**

> "I booked and travelled specifically for a HIFU treatment, with extensive WhatsApp communication prior to the appointment confirming the treatment, pricing, and booking details. Everything was booked, confirmed, and ready to go.  After spending over an hour each way and 1,400 baht on taxis, I arrived expecting to proceed with the treatment I had clearly booked.  Instead, a non-medical staff member pushed a brochure in front of me and told me I “needed” Oligio, priced at around four times the cost, with no explanation as to why the treatment I booked was suddenly unsuitable.  When I asked for a doctor’s explanation or medical opinion, I was told I would need to pay an additional 1,000 baht just to speak to the doctor — effectively charging me to justify an upsell that the clinic itself initiated.  At no point did anyone: •	Explain the clinical reasoning for changing the booked treatment •	Offer a medical consultation as part of that decision •	Acknowledge or apologise for the wasted time and travel costs •	Attempt to resolve the situation  The follow-up communication avoided addressing these issues entirely.  Despite clear pre-booking communication and confirmation, this experience felt like a bait-and-switch and cash-grab, not a patient-first medical consultation. Informed consent and transparent medical advice should come before sales tactics — not behind a paywall.  I would strongly advise others to clarify in writing whether: •	The booked treatment will actually be honoured •	A doctor consultation is required to proceed •	And whether additional fees apply simply to receive an explanation"
> **- Katie Allan (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/liv-clinic-1.jpg','065 996 4242','LIV CLINIC เลขที่ 1/63 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://liv.clinic/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: Closed","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.266+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.266+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/liv-clinic-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/liv-clinic-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4416482180324489338',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('live-india','standard','cmr07igy500gmq8xd4n66atxv','Live India','## Top Reviews
> "A good Indian restaurant. The service was excellent. The food tasted really good. You get great value for money here. Highly recommended!"
> **- Jaan R9 (5/5/5)**

> "It’s April so that might explain how quiet it is, so there is little by way of atmosphere. However, the food is really good and great vegetarian dishes too. The service is great; very friendly, helpful staff. The mango lassi is absolutely delicious. A must if you come here. I’ll be back for sure. Well worth a visit."
> **- Brian Bergin (4/5/5)**

> "Food 5/5 Service 3/5 Interior 2/5  The BEST Indian food i had maybe even in my life. Phenomenal flavors, even just the rice with cumin tasted so good! You know when with every bite you do the "
> **- Vladimir Klempa (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/live-india-1.jpg','080 584 8698','124, 175 Thanon Had Lamai, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://r.grab.com/o/nquIzyU3','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: Closed","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.269+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.269+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/live-india-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/live-india-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=18441814547012875745',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('lkrin','standard','cmr07igy800gnq8xd7nmc149y','L’Ékrin','## Top Reviews
> "A hidden gem! I am usually the kind of person that likes to explore and try different cuisines and restaurants. So it was really unexpected for me to eat every single night for a week at L''eKrin - and all thanks to the talented chef David. It really is hard to describe this place and the food, just because the words won''t do it justice. Right after lunch, David goes to the local market to select fresh fish, which he brings back to the restaurant, and makes a new menu each night. He goes around to every table explaining each fish and the different ways that he can prepare it. I am not a big seafood person, I can eat it once in a while, but I don''t go crazy over it. Here - completely different. The way he prepares it... absolutely amazing. No fish smell, no bones, soft, tender, juicy. The way he plays around with the flavors and the contrasts is... well beyond me. Despite the fact that there are managers, and of course, the wait staff, he still comes out of the kitchen to check up on you, to see how you like the food, to chat. He adds a real personal touch. And after a few lunches and dinners he starts understanding your tastes even better - and caters to them. David is definitely a great chef! And not only is every dish delicious, but it is also beautifully decorated. The wine and drink selection at the restaurant is good, and you can find a good pairing for each dish. The only thing that can be improved at this restaurant, and this is something that is barely noticeable because everything else is amazing - is the wait staff. They need to be trained a bit better, especially with how they present and pour the wine. But again, this is such a minor detail, that it almost doesn''t matter. If I ever visit Koh Samui again, I will definitely eat here again!"
> **- Alexei Kourinov (5/5/5)**

> "We were a group of 5 and have been eating here 3 times. The cook is a very friendly guy and the food is soo delicious. We also had lobster which was fished by the cook himself!!! We ordered the day before and the next day he showed us a picture where he caught the lobster. We totally have to come back to this place!"
> **- Patrick Pi (5/5/5)**

> "Very nice place, tasty food and very friendly staff. Recommend it!"
> **- mihail mihov (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lkrin-1.jpg','077 447 127','HXM8+3PR, Koh Samui, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifso000kq8xdfe9gpaon','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.272+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.272+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lkrin-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lkrin-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16360523203161839177',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ln-spa','standard','cmr07igya00goq8xdkwcvbvws','Lèn Spa','## Top Reviews
> "Everything is the best! There is a lot of attention to details, tea and hot/cold towels before and after massage, everybody is so nice! The massage is perfect too! Definitely must visit place  The prices is 100% affordable for such quality"
> **- Ekaterina Vasileva (5/5/5)**

> "An absolutely wonderful spa experience from start to finish! The facility is spotlessly clean, and the calming décor instantly puts you at ease the moment you walk in. The staff are professional, friendly, and communicate excellently in English ;)  The massage was top-notch skilled, professional, and exactly what I needed. We booked the private room for two, which was beautifully maintained, comfortable, and very relaxing. Perfect for a couples'' treat!  What really stood out was the complimentary drinks and snacks upon departure a thoughtful and well-presented touch that left us feeling truly pampered.  Highly recommend this gem to anyone looking for a quality spa experience. Will definitely be coming back!"
> **- Preeditha Nitisakul (5/5/5)**

> "I have mixed feelings about this salon because some services were excellent, while others were disappointing.  First, the pedicure was outstanding. The technician was very thorough, took great care of my skin and cuticles, and applied the gel polish beautifully. It has been almost two weeks since my pedicure and it still looks great.  The salon itself is beautiful, clean, and very professional. The hospitality is exceptional – guests are offered drinks and small snacks before and after the treatment. The overall atmosphere feels comparable to a high-quality European salon.  My husband also had a Thai massage and was very satisfied. According to him, it was above average compared to many other Thai massages he has experienced.  Unfortunately, my manicure was a major disappointment.  My cuticles were not properly treated, and the manicure already looked grown out on the same day because the product was applied too far from the cuticle area. The nail shapes and lengths were inconsistent, and even after I asked for corrections, the final result was still uneven.  The biggest issue was the nail preparation. I only had gel polish previously, but the technician treated my nails as if they had hard gel and over-filed them significantly. During the procedure I repeatedly indicated that it was painful, but the filing continued. My natural nails are now extremely thin, sensitive, and feel almost like paper. Even simple daily activities are uncomfortable.  The gel polish application itself was also below expectations. The product is uneven in several places, with visible bumps and thickness inconsistencies. Some edges were not properly finished, and the polish was applied untidily around the sides of the nails. Overall, the manicure does not look like a freshly completed professional service.  It is a shame because the salon, pedicure, hospitality, and massage were all excellent. However, due to the poor manicure quality and the damage caused to my natural nails, I cannot recommend the manicure service and would not choose it again."
> **- Alexandra Becková (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ln-spa-1.jpg','099 015 2604','17/9, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.lekarnspa.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifsv000nq8xdrwnu123q','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.274+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.274+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ln-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ln-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14716619286851048269',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('lobster-bar','standard','cmr07igyc00gpq8xdnj0u8q4s','Lobster Bar','## Top Reviews
> "We ate here all weekend. The lasagna, grilled fish, pasta, and soups were delicious! We made a custom pizza for my vegetarian husband. They saved us from the bizarre Thai food. The ice cream at the entrance was delicious.🥰 The restaurant is quiet and there is no blaring music, unlike other places"
> **- Daria Kostyuk (5/5/5)**

> "Really good food. Had the glass noodle soup which was surburd and Pad Thai. The pad Thai on the little sweet side but good. The portions sizing was perfect. Service was excellent"
> **- J White (5/5/5)**

> "Great place with good Thai food for avery good price. Staff is super friendly and helpful. Food is just delicious,cocktails are good as well. A must for everyone who wants to enjoy authentic thai food"
> **- Leen Maegh (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lobster-bar-1.jpg',NULL,'162/157,159 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.276+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.276+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lobster-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lobster-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17639766773276241758',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('locean','standard','cmr07igyf00gqq8xduylbccq4','L''Ocean','## Top Reviews
> "Got 2 pizzas for 3 people, pepperoni, and seafood (around 350 and 450 baht respectively before taxes and service). Seafood was bland. Pepperoni was good. Pizza size is medium. Had to ask for plates (and even then we were given only 2). Prices are exclusive of vat and service charge with add up to a hefty 17%. Not good enough service for an asked price."
> **- Alex (3/5/5)**

> "We enjoyed a romantic dinner at the L’Ocean with the dishes served both fresh and flavoursome. Only downside was that the fish was rather small and the drinks were a little pricey when factoring in the near 20% tax and service charge to the cost. Two drinks cost over 700 baht so if you fancy a few it will be a relatively expensive evening by Thai standards. The table setting was beautiful with views out to the sea. The wait staff were attentive without being overbearing and all in all we had a very enjoyable evening. Highly recommended if you are looking for a romantic setting with a warm, laid-back ambience."
> **- Alfred Romeo (4/5/5)**

> "Average food with a nice view. The service is wonderful, however the quality and presentation of the food is lacklustre. I would suggest trying the pomelo salad."
> **- Gobind Thind (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/locean-1.jpg','089 074 8488','12/12, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.bophutresort.com/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 10:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.279+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.279+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/locean-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/locean-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14528924682335233956',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('lolamui-cafe','standard','cmr07igyi00grq8xdpvd781v7','Lolamui Cafe','## Top Reviews
> "We ordered a few pieces of cake at this place, and every single one was truly delicious! If you’re looking for a spot to enjoy exceptional and fresh made desserts, this is a must-visit.  The service was attentive, and the facilities are charming, surrounded by beautiful natural scenery that adds to the overall experience. Highly recommended."
> **- Joagat (5/5/5)**

> "This is my first cafe in Thailand Koh Samui The coconut cake is wonderful!!! A must try here!!! The air conditioner is working very well, u might feel cold when u come in but after a while u''ll just feel cool, dry and comfy. I tried taro coconut cake bc they ran out of normal coconut cake today. Bueno!!! The Raspberry cappuccino is sweet. Be careful if u r not a fan of sweet coffee. Although I''m not into sweet coffee, the cappuccino was still nice. Why isn''t anyone here??? (Friday) This can be my work cafe so nice♥️ They also have Japanese seat which you can lay on the floor. Great choice for tourist👍 I won''t say it''s cheap. 85 THB for taro coconut cake 80 THB for Raspberry cappuccino But affordable. Slightly cheaper than Japan(?)"
> **- うる (5/5/5)**

> "there is parking, you place an order and pay at the cash register, and then choose a place, there are places near the cash register, as well as in a separate house or on a cute little terrace. Inside the cafe there is a lot of visual space and very cozy. we ordered a drink and desserts. the desserts were light and tasty, without the bad butter flavor that most Thai bakeries use. strawberry earl gray cake - conveyed the bright taste of tea. the coffee was delicious."
> **- А. (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lolamui-cafe-1.jpg','077 601 607','F26Q+8X7, Maret, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/lolamuicafe','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: Closed","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.282+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.282+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lolamui-cafe-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lolamui-cafe-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6850383171118623415',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('lomprayah-catamaran','standard','cmr07igyk00gsq8xdy5y09d74','Lomprayah Catamaran','## Top Reviews
> "We had a nice relaxing day with our family (a baby and a 4 years old). We skipped snorkeling and went directly to the view point (got very crowded right after) and then to the beach to pick a nice spot renting some beach chairs. The place has amazing views and swimming within colorful fish was amazing. The tour guides were always passing by to check on us and gave nice tips."
> **- Louise ferreira (5/5/5)**

> "We did a daily trip to Koh Tao and Koh Nangyuan. We stopped for snorkeling one hour once at Mango Bay in Koh Tao, and for around 3 hours at Koh Nangyuan, snorkeling around Japanese garden. For a short daily trip from Koh Phagan, this tour was convenient as we don’t need to take another ferry or stay in Koh Tao. Our guide Kik was very helpful and friendly. Thanks for guiding us towards beautiful coral reefs!"
> **- Önder Ceylan (5/5/5)**

> "Namyen was absolutely perfect, and Nang Yuan Island was even more beautiful than I imagined.  Thanks to the guide’s clear instructions and great snorkeling spot recommendations, it was the best snorkeling experience I had in Koh Samui.  If you visit Koh Samui, this place is a must-see!"
> **- 김연정 (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lomprayah-catamaran-1.jpg','089 873 0005','Bontji Moo 4 Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.lomprayah.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ig1n003kq8xd72v6yb3r','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.284+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.284+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lomprayah-catamaran-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lomprayah-catamaran-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13434509386704531722',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('long-dtai','standard','cmr07igyn00gtq8xd1epzxhwi','Long Dtai','## Top Reviews
> "Long Dtai by David Thompson is a must-visit restaurant, offering an unforgettable dining experience. I am fortunate to be spending my holiday at Cape Fahn in Samui, where we will enjoy dinner at this acclaimed establishment.  Long Dtai''s cuisine emphasizes local ingredients to create extraordinary, authentic southern Thai dishes. Featured in the Michelin Guide, the restaurant guarantees a delectable dining experience.  My favorite dishes from the menu include:  - **Aromatic Beef Skewers with Cumin and Turmeric:** The beef is incredibly juicy, and the aroma of fresh Thai herbs is delightful. 480 baht - **Coconut and Turmeric Curry with Blue Swimmer Crab:** Typically a favorite of mine, this dish here is exceptional, with incredibly fresh crab. 980 baht - **Palm Sugar Dumplings in Coconut Cream (Dessert):** Easy to eat, with the perfect sweetness from the palm sugar. 270 baht  The restaurant operates from 18:00 to 21:30. If you arrive early, you can visit the bar, open from 17:00 to 22:00. Please note that the restaurant is closed every Wednesday.  Guests from outside the hotel are welcome, but it is advisable to make a reservation in advance. Additionally, allow extra time for the hotel''s transit boat to reach the restaurant.  If it''s not the rainy season, I recommend sitting outside to enjoy the island view.  Overall, I believe this restaurant is likely to receive a Michelin award next year, thanks to its impressive flavors, ambiance, and service. Thank you for providing me with such wonderful memories."
> **- Mandy P. (5/5/5)**

> "Hard to beat location and view. The food was excellent. We had the turmeric salad, which was the highlight, really a superb dish. The red snapper curry was also amazing! It is a bit pricy, but the flavors deliver in an area that has a lot of reduced spice due to the western tourists."
> **- Jacob Boland (5/5/5)**

> "Long Dtai means traveling in the south defines our dining experience at the restaurant very much. My curiosity as a fan of David Thompson from many places in London & Bangkok, we decided to dine there. We found the authentic southern Thai cuisine with locally & sustainability products took us to the culinary journey of the beautiful South of Thailand. We love the fresh crabs in the yellow curry soup. The harmony of fresh ingredients & spices are excellent. The location, the service are simply elegant."
> **- Cher Fontaine (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/long-dtai-1.jpg','077 602 301','24/269 Moo 5 T, ตำบล บ่อผุด A.Koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.2,0,0,0,NULL,'https://longdtai.com/','["Monday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: Closed","Thursday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Friday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifsv000nq8xdrwnu123q','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.287+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.287+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/long-dtai-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/long-dtai-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3883663245141751130',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('longlae-samui-tour-travel','standard','cmr07igyp00guq8xd3944653w','Longlae ​​Samui Tour & Travel','## Top Reviews
> "I would recommend this company to anyone!! Absolutely fabulous. They were easy to communicate with over WhatsApp message. We booked with them back in November for a tour around pig beach and snorkelling and this is still one of our top and favourite memories of the entire holiday in Thailand. From the transport to the boats and the whole trip they were phenomenal. Trust the process as the docks are nothing like we are used to in the uk. The boat driver was absolutely lovely and helpful and was more than happy to assist and evolve the day around us. We cannot wait to book back with this company in may when we come back!"
> **- JH E (5/5/5)**

> "Highly recommend this agency. We took a private trip to the Pig island with a long tail boat, it was by far the cheaper price (half from all agencies across the island). It was very easy to book, everything was smooth and on time. Make it in private allow us to manage our tour and decide how much time we want spend on each part of the tour."
> **- Sagi Wainberg (5/5/5)**

> "Thanks a lot for this great moment! That was amazing  😍"
> **- Brice MRLT (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/longlae-samui-tour-travel-1.jpg','099 161 8215','53 Angthong 6 Tambon Ang Thong, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.longlaesamui.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifxh0027q8xde6xqk8o6','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.289+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.289+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/longlae-samui-tour-travel-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/longlae-samui-tour-travel-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4028116309712814984',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('lotus-samui','standard','cmr07igys00gvq8xdhoejqc7p','Lotus Samui','## Top Reviews
> "My family and I (grandparents, parents, 3 grandchildren) spent a delightful 10 days at Villa Chi Samui in early April. Having experienced Bangkok and Chiang Mai, we were eager for some beachside relaxation and water sports for the children. The villa itself is superbly presented and immaculately maintained with many areas cool and sheltered from the hot April sun. Consequently we were able to eat outside every evening and enjoy the awesome range of Thai food, expertly prepared by Nahm, the villa chef. If I have one small criticism of the villa layout, the pool by the beach is really no more than a plunge pool and the long main pool by the side of the house is somewhat awkwardly positioned. The “twin” villa next door with its beachside pool might be better for families with children. We made several trips to Fisherman’s Village for the beach, water sports and night market, including the Thai New Year celebrations. All the transportation was flawlessly arranged by our excellent host, Jenny, often at short notice. We were treated like royalty by Jenny and her team -I can’t speak highly enough of the care and attention we received from them. It was very humbling. Jenny even got up at 4am on our last morning to ensure the taxi to the airport had arrived on time. We were captivated by the people of this lovely country and all agreed it would be great to return one day with so much of Thailand still to explore."
> **- Nigel Allsop (5/5/5)**

> "Love the villa and the staff. Khun Jenny and Khun Nam were excellent at taking care of us. Khun Nam is a wonderful chef too. I fully recommend this wonderful resort which also has an excellent view to add."
> **- Wilfred Ong (5/5/5)**

> "We had an amazing stay at this beautiful and perfectly maintained property. The private beach is absolutely stunning — clean, peaceful, and ideal for relaxing. What truly makes this place exceptional, however, is the staff: always available, efficient, and genuinely attentive to every need. As frequent travelers, we can confidently say this hotel stands out for its quality and service. Highly recommended for both couples and families looking for a refined and comfortable experience."
> **- Cristiano Abbate (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lotus-samui-1.jpg','089 972 3043','12/61 Moo 5, เทศบาลนครเกาะสมุย อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.lotussamui.com/','["Monday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM","Thursday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM","Friday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM","Saturday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM","Sunday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifs1000cq8xdfo2aau32','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.292+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.292+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lotus-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lotus-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12218322522034685050',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('lou-lou-eatery-bar','standard','cmr07igyv00gwq8xddswb77ig','Lou Lou Eatery & Bar','## Top Reviews
> "Fantastic restaurant. I ate here multiple times and was never disappointed. Both the Thai and non-Thai dishes were very good. The cocktails were always very well made (and strong!) The service and staff are excellent, very attentive and helpful. I would highly recommend."
> **- Dtown (5/5/5)**

> "Lovely new restaurant on the way to BanTai beach.  Just opened a few days ago in the soft-opening stage, and I have been 3 times.  An excellent caesar and chopped salad,  chicken green curry and spring rolls.   Once they get up and running with a full menu and staff, I suspect this will be packed and difficult to get a seat. The food quality and taste was excellent with generous portion , the staff very caring , and the relaxing atmosphere felt very high quality for this neighborhood.  Definitely keep an eye on Lou Lou''s as a great new spot.  The Boutique resort is looking fantastic as well.  You can tell the pride of new ownership here !"
> **- Jim Anthony (5/5/5)**

> "Sad we did not have the time to enjoy it more! What a lovely place, all the staff is nice, the food is delicious, we ate dinner 3 nights in a row and also breakfast. Great burger, the strips and the chopped salad, lovely mix! Good cocktails, Good cappuccino, we loved it. The music, the vibe, everything! Thank you!"
> **- The Misses (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lou-lou-eatery-bar-1.jpg','095 310 0353','7, 7 Bantai Soi 4, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.mooreasamui.com/lou-lou','["Monday: 7:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 7:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 7:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 7:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 7:30 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifso000kq8xdfe9gpaon','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.295+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.295+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lou-lou-eatery-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lou-lou-eatery-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11839435557820043347',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('lub-d','standard','cmr07igyx00gxq8xd1u5015y2','Lub D','## Top Reviews
> "Amazing experience at Lub d! Everything was great, from the rooms to the overall vibe. A special thank you to Jar and Oli, who were incredibly kind, attentive, and professional throughout my stay. Their positive energy and outstanding service made a big difference. I’ll definitely be back. Highly recommended!"
> **- Jaccob (5/5/5)**

> "Bento, Ann, Wine, Keng, King, Tony and too many more to name, made this trip extremely memorable. Initially was supposed to stay for 3 nights but ended up staying close to two weeks. Stayed both in dorms and private rooms, both were amazing. Food was excellent, happy hours all the time, events every day and overall a good vibe. Highly recommend."
> **- Ariz N (5/5/5)**

> "We are having the best time at Lub D Koh Samui Chaweng! The location is absolutely perfect right on the beach, sun glaring and the property itself is gorgeous.  A huge thanks to the reception team for being so welcoming and taking the time to walk us through everything when we arrived. We got the included breakfast and it was deliciously fresh. And a special shoutout to Mod—you are a rockstar! Thanks for always hooking us up with such tasty drinks and for being so kind and accommodating throughout our stay. You really made our trip extra special! 💛"
> **- Matt Blouin (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lub-d-1.jpg','077 230 326','159 99 ตำบล บ่อผุด Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.lubd.com/destination/koh-samui/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.297+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.297+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lub-d-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lub-d-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3468817549019914630',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('lucky-restaurant','standard','cmr07igz100gyq8xdn9ryw6yu','Lucky Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "Went here twice as we had to go back for some more sweet and sour chicken as it''s delicious.  Service is friendly and efficient, prices are very reasonable and there''s parking right outside.  Not to be missed.  Edit - we went there for a third time for breakfast before catching the car ferry to Don Sak. Breakfast was good too."
> **- Richard Williams (5/5/5)**

> "The Food is delicious. Nit the Owner, and here Daughter in the Kitchen and Nit’s Husband Steve, and also Nit’s sons in the restaurant is a perfect family team.  We are many years guest at the Lucky Restaurant as guest and we are glad to come so often we can, for dinner. Our family and friends dinner last tuesday was phenomenal. Thank you very much to Nit and here Team 🙏🏻"
> **- Just4 FunTH84 (5/5/5)**

> "I had an amazing dining experience at Lucky Restaurant! The fried fish and shrimp with rice were absolutely delicious—perfectly cooked, crispy, and full of flavor. The steak was another standout—tender, juicy, and cooked to perfection. Each dish was served hot and fresh, making every bite a real treat. The service was excellent, and the owner was incredibly kind and welcoming, which made the experience even more special. I highly recommend Luckey Restaurant for anyone looking for incredible food and a warm, friendly atmosphere. I can’t wait to come back for more!"
> **- Maryam Choubineh (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lucky-restaurant-1.jpg','084 855 3844','310/22 Moo 3, Angthong, Koh Samui, อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig1h003iq8xdb1g9nifo','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.301+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.301+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lucky-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lucky-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17437206868623788952',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('lucky-to-be-alive','standard','cmr07igz400gzq8xdpx0zq3fu','Lucky To Be Alive','## Top Reviews
> "Excellent selection of Thai craft beers with 7 on a rotating tap and more in cans.  Superb service by the bar woman Trina who is very polite and always smiling.  The first night I tried 2 different hazy IPA’s and 1 IPA, all draft, super tasty and very fresh.  We went back the second night and they had all already changed one of the drafts and I was able to try 3 entirely different draft IPA’s, again of great quality.  It isn’t cheap, but then again I haven’t come across cheap craft beer anywhere in South East Asia. We didn’t eat at any of the street food stalls, but other people were bringing food back to the bar area and it looked very tasty. If you like craft beer and fancy a change from the usual; Chang, Singha & Leo I’d highly recommend this place."
> **- Mark Wilson (5/5/5)**

> "Small but excellent – highly recommended! They have 7 fantastic beers on tap and many more great craft beers from Thai microbreweries in the fridge. The staff member was incredibly friendly, and we discovered some amazing new craft beers while feeling completely at home. Thanks for this wonderful little gem! 🍻"
> **- S. Mayar (5/5/5)**

> "Superb range of craft beers in an area awash with Singha etc. Sours, Lagers, IPAs and a decent DIPA on the 7 taps, plus cans and bottles in the fridge (cider and stouts too) Really friendly service, would strongly recommend a visit."
> **- Russ Wyld (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lucky-to-be-alive-1.jpg','098 345 2490','79, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/craftbeerkohsamui','["Monday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: Closed","Wednesday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Friday: 4:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 5:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.304+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.304+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lucky-to-be-alive-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/lucky-to-be-alive-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14826029868452148831',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('luggage-storage-setada','standard','cmr07igz600h0q8xddgu3h1g3','Luggage Storage Setada','## Top Reviews
> "So happy that this place exists. Made my life so easy to travel to the islands for a week. I celebrated while I relaxed only having what I needed for my trip. Too easy! They''ll pick up before you leave and reunite you on your return to whichever Samui hotel you land at. 10/10 😁"
> **- dom hayden (5/5/5)**

> "The owners are super friendly and helpful. I left my things there for over 1 year, it’s super clean, air conditioned, very safe, if you want to leave your belongings in a safe place that does not have mold and is ideally air conditioned, this is the right place to go. They were very flexible with my contract, and even when I picked up my belongings 2 months after the contract finished, they kept my things safe and did not give me any pressure. The owner even helped me to sell my things on facebook, when I came back to pick up the leftovers and had only a few hours time on the island and didn’t have time to put an advertisement online at all. This storage place also has a coworking space upstairs. It’s an amazing location with amazing owners, 5 stars"
> **- Cupoftea Withouthoney (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing service! Extremely communicative with great prices. I was able to explore the islands without the hassle of dragging my large suitcase around. They offer pick up and drop off service as well. Made my traveling much easier and relaxing. Thank you so much!"
> **- Erin (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/luggage-storage-setada-1.jpg','083 449 7940','10, 81 Maenam, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.306+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.306+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/luggage-storage-setada-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/luggage-storage-setada-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2924460923563705147',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('luk-khai-lek-cafe-restaurant','standard','cmr07igza00h1q8xdfs9y2sxs','Luk Khai Lek Cafe & Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "A truly peaceful and beautiful spot to unwind. Sitting by the river with a cold drink, surrounded by lush greenery and the sound of nature, made the whole experience feel calm and refreshing. The setting is very relaxing, with cozy seating areas and a lovely view of the small red bridge and flowing water. It’s the perfect place to slow down, enjoy the atmosphere, and escape from busy city life. Great for a quiet coffee, a chat with friends, or simply enjoying the scenery. Would definitely come back."
> **- Mister Benz (5/5/5)**

> "A true hidden gem of Samui 🌿✨ So much green, so much beauty and such a peaceful atmosphere everywhere 🥹  The staff were incredibly kind and warm, and they even made a special vegetarian vegetable dish just for me 💚 Everything tasted so fresh and comforting!  The shrimp pad thai was absolutely delicious, the orange coffee was amazing, strawberry Thai tea was so good and refreshing  and of course STRAWBERRY match🥰🍓☕️  One of those places that feels cozy and beautiful from the first minute ♥️"
> **- Elvira (5/5/5)**

> "Lovely setting away from the tourist crowd beautiful riverside restaurant with gardens , indoor and outdoor seating, delicious thai food and good coffee The pad thai gung, mussaman chicken and pad kapraw moo all delicious  Relax under the trees or next to the mountain stream - this rainy season is ideal. The neighbours are buffalo and egrets Plenty of parking ... location is on the cross island road"
> **- Coconut Emma (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/luk-khai-lek-cafe-restaurant-1.jpg','090 164 5402','65 แม่น้ำ Maenam 9, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.310+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.310+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/luk-khai-lek-cafe-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/luk-khai-lek-cafe-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6362846757983325892',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('luna-hut-garden','standard','cmr07igzm00h2q8xduqobhs9o','Luna Hut Garden','## Top Reviews
> "We really liked this place we went there 4 times in the 5 days we were there. Great for a lunch place. Can recommend the pad Thai! The last night we ordered the lobster (order one day in advance). We got really good service and got too see them fresh early in the day. The meal was amazing and the vibe really nice plus super service. A definitely recommendation."
> **- Trine Nielsen (4/5/5)**

> "Got here randomly when bypassing and we were pleasantly surprised. The staff and the owner is very kind. Its a traditional thai restaurant that never disappoints. We had 2 drinks, 2 cocktails, 1 appetizer, 2 main dishes and 2 desserts and the receipt was only 820baht! The portion itself may be a bit small but that is a good thing so you can try many different things in one go. Every single dish and cocktail was delicious. Recommend!"
> **- Sara Gomboc (5/5/5)**

> "Base on Google reviews decided to visit since it was a short drive from my hotel and Google was not wrong! Good food, decent prices which hopefully they continue to maintain the price and quality and even the locals visit for their meals. Will be happy to return should I be back in Samui"
> **- Nathanael Tan (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/luna-hut-garden-1.jpg','062 064 1199','26 5 ถ. ทวีราษฎร์ภักดี Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 10:30 AM – 9:30 PM","Tuesday: 10:30 AM – 9:30 PM","Wednesday: 10:30 AM – 9:30 PM","Thursday: 10:30 AM – 9:30 PM","Friday: 10:30 AM – 9:30 PM","Saturday: 10:30 AM – 9:30 PM","Sunday: 10:30 AM – 9:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifs1000cq8xdfo2aau32','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.322+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.322+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/luna-hut-garden-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/luna-hut-garden-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7963590997681740116',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('luuma-sauna','standard','cmr07ih0200h3q8xdj8uethff','Luuma Sauna','## Top Reviews
> "Best spa in Samui. For 380 bahts, you get a day pass and access to a swimming pool outside, a sauna, hammam, a cold plunge, an ice bath with actual ice in it, and a very warm little pool.  You can relax in sunbeds, work on a desk, and the food here is also amazing !! 10/10 experience.  When i went it was a rainy day, that made the experience even more cosy.  Will definitely come back again :)"
> **- Nastasya (5/5/5)**

> "I had a very pleasant stay at Luuma in Koh Samui, Thailand. From the moment I arrived, the staff were extremely friendly, kind, and always ready to help with anything I needed. Their genuine hospitality made me feel truly welcome and comfortable throughout my stay.  The atmosphere at Luuma is peaceful and relaxing — perfect for anyone who wants to unwind and recharge. All facilities are clean, beautifully designed, and well-maintained, creating a calm and cozy environment.  Luuma also offers excellent facilities including a sauna, steam room, massage services, bain glace, and ice bath — all of which made my stay even more enjoyable. The on-site restaurant is also great, with delicious food and a lovely setting to relax.  The location is convenient, close to local attractions and beaches, but still quiet enough to enjoy a sense of privacy and peace.  Overall, Luuma was wonderful. I truly appreciated the helpful and friendly staff, the relaxing environment, and the great facilities. I would highly recommend Luuma to anyone visiting Koh Samui."
> **- Rick Hein (5/5/5)**

> "It''s only 390 baht per day and the place is clean and really relaxing.  After going to the sauna, I felt like my body and mind were relaxed.  I would really recommend it to anyone who wants to relax and take a break from work.  The price is reasonable and the service is good, so I''m willing to go again.  It''s a really good place for those who want to relax 👍"
> **- MyoThwe Khing85 (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/luuma-sauna-1.jpg','065 538 6193','124, T, 7, Tambon Maret, lamai, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://mysmartqr.com/luuma-samui','["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.338+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.338+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/luuma-sauna-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/luuma-sauna-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15155783725831788549',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('luxsa','standard','cmr07ih0700h4q8xdz94d4kq5','Luxsa','## Top Reviews
> "A true hidden gem for massage and relaxation. My partner and I enjoyed the coconut oil Thai massage, and it was exactly the recharge we needed during our trip. The environment is incredibly peaceful, and the decor fully immerses you in Thai culture.  The staff, from reception to the therapists, are exceptionally warm, welcoming, and attentive. The snacks served before and after the massage were a delightful touch — refreshing, tasty, and a small highlight of the overall experience.  For the quality of service and ambiance, the price is more than worth it. Highly recommended!"
> **- Josh Cheng (5/5/5)**

> "This spa is absolutely beautiful and offers a truly tranquil atmosphere. Every visit leaves me feeling deeply relaxed, refreshed, and at peace. The massage oil is outstanding, featuring a distinctive and delightful fragrance that sets it apart from others. I genuinely love this place and look forward to returning whenever I am in Koh Samui.🤍"
> **- Phatchara Thammasiri (5/5/5)**

> "I had an eastern blend deep tissue massage with Poonim and it was amazing. Strong, full-body treatment and exactly what I needed. She is highly skilled and professional  highly recommended!✨🌹🤍"
> **- Alkida Jaupi (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/luxsa-1.jpg','077 245 511','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.hansarsamui.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.345+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.345+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/luxsa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/luxsa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1937620234918390516',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ma-ha-tea','standard','cmr07ih0d00h5q8xd5dzffvgs','Ma-Ha-Tea','## Top Reviews
> "You guys need to improve the live music band, before MHT had much better singers specially 2 girls (see photo attached), one very short and slim with an amazing voice she used to sing in Old School and also kongsiam and another one that likes to colour her hair pink or sometimes yellow. Give them a call, bring them back to HO, they were much better than the guys you have now. If you bring those female singers I will give 5 stars and tip accordingly to the quality of the singers and service ! If you have the best club you need the best singers!"
> **- Teng Mo (3/5/5)**

> "This is quite a cool little venue, staff are very welcome and friendly, I would say it''s more for Thia people or people who enjoy Thia music.  But I enjoyed my time"
> **- Stevo Success (4/5/5)**

> "I love to listen thai live music, yesterday I went there but unfortunately they didn''t let me entry saying "
> **- ALESSANDRO Fontana (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ma-ha-tea-1.jpg','092 516 8555','3, 226 หมู่ที่ 2 ตำบล บ่อผุด Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 PM – 3:30 AM","Tuesday: 9:00 PM – 3:30 AM","Wednesday: 9:00 PM – 3:30 AM","Thursday: 9:00 PM – 3:30 AM","Friday: 9:00 PM – 3:30 AM","Saturday: 9:00 PM – 3:30 AM","Sunday: 9:00 PM – 3:30 AM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.349+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.349+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ma-ha-tea-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ma-ha-tea-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15284105721333187316',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('maenam-pet-clinic','standard','cmr07ih0s00h6q8xdw3ddz9xj','Maenam Pet Clinic','## Top Reviews
> "Found three stray kittens, I brought them here the next day. The Vet and nurse are super lovely and professional! The medical checkup and cleaning was very thorough. I definitely recommend as a base vet for your pet, they will definitely be for my new kitties!"
> **- Ayala Jackson (5/5/5)**

> "My girlfriend likes this place. Do not expect too much information if you can''t speak thai, especially the vet herself didn''t even talk to me at all. Rest of the staff was nice, even on a busy day."
> **- most404 (3/5/5)**

> "My cat is 17 years old and we travel a lot. I have been to clinics in different countries and nowhere have I seen such attention, expertise and professionalism.  I have been a client of this clinic for several months and can recommend it with all responsibility.  Here you don''t have to worry about your pet. Great clinic. Great doctor. Highly recommended and appreciated for everything you''ve done"
> **- Aleksandr (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/maenam-pet-clinic-1.jpg','089 737 8782','80/8 ม.1 แม่น้ำ Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 9:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: Closed","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 4:00 PM"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.364+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.364+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/maenam-pet-clinic-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/maenam-pet-clinic-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10259224116601730918',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('magic-resort','standard','cmr07ih1600h7q8xd6wrk3hn7','Magic Resort','## Top Reviews
> "Located in Lamai Beach. Just a few steps from the sea. The location it’s perfect, dipend on the weather and tides from the color of the sea. It’s absolutely more quite then the biggest Cheweg but also here you can find all the services, pub and bar. The staff at Magic Resort are really kind and gently, especially the Boss that manage the bungalows. We’ve rent there also the scooter, and they’ve some brochures for the near excursion. The rooms are cleaned every days, clean towels provided. Also the bathroom is okay, enough water for the shower time. Outside each bungalows have a small terrace, so cute. The atmosphere is perfect, very quite and your just a few steps from the main Lamai road."
> **- Giop Pi (5/5/5)**

> "Very lovely family resort. I definely come again. Location is awesome. You can rent motorbike from resort. They have restaurant and it offer very delicious food. Laundry service also working well."
> **- Tomi i (5/5/5)**

> "Wonderful resort run by a very nice and service-minded family. They offer massage, food, rental of motorbikes and jetskis etc. After asking if I could extend my stay for more days, the lady managed to fit me in even though during busy Christmas times. She also helped me book transfer and ticket to the ferry to Koh Tao. My only complaint is that my bungalow was located at the opposite of their bike shop so a lot noise during morning and day."
> **- Oskar Ryberg (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/magic-resort-1.jpg','089 289 4291','130 Thanon Had Lamai, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.magicresortlamai.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.378+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.378+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/magic-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/magic-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16628890691814819599',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mahalo-efoil-kite-surfing-lessons','standard','cmr07ih1b00h8q8xdblohx5fs','Mahalo - Efoil Kite Surfing Lessons','## Top Reviews
> "Awesome spot to learn kitesurfing. Our instructors were super nice and tailored their teaching to each person. I totally recommend it for beginners and anyone looking to improve. My 8 and 12-year-old sons started here and now they love it! Thanks a lot !!!"
> **- Patrick Lucereau (5/5/5)**

> "Outstanding experience from start to finish. Communication with Pavel via WhatsApp was flawless — we always checked an hour in advance if conditions and timing were right, and he replied promptly and professionally every time. All instructors were excellent, calm and highly professional, with perfect English. Both my husband and I were standing on the board after just a few hours and enjoyed an adrenaline-filled ride right at the beginning of 2026. We even saw a ten-year-old child starting kitesurfing — safely, confidently and with great instruction. The conditions were among the best we’ve ever experienced. Highly recommended. 🌬️✨"
> **- Karina Svoboda Tochtarová (IG karinaprague) (5/5/5)**

> "I had a great expérience with the school. My instructor Philip (not sure if I spell his name right) is  patient and encouraging. I managed to have some rides in my second class. Highly recommended!"
> **- tang yun (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mahalo-efoil-kite-surfing-lessons-1.jpg','096 803 5296','62, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'http://mahalo.center/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07ifuo0015q8xdfahzrsp4','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.383+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.383+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mahalo-efoil-kite-surfing-lessons-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mahalo-efoil-kite-surfing-lessons-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13530900996536310453',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mai-samui-beach-resort','standard','cmr07ih1e00h9q8xdd2xz3et9','Mai Samui Beach Resort','## Top Reviews
> "Very disappointing and unsafe experience - stay away  This hotel is extremely run down and dirty. We booked 5 rooms. When we arrived, we were given rooms and then moved to other rooms due to the smell of mold and renovations - and in the new rooms each room had a different serious problem.  In one room there were exposed electrical wires. In another room, there was no hot water. In one room the toilet wouldn''t flush. In another room, there were termites on the bed and their droppings fell on the mattress, which caused me to develop a rash on my chest and shoulders.  The towels smelled bad. The swimming pool looked like a frog pond. The dining room was very dirty. The entire hotel is poorly maintained - everything is broken and outdated.  The beach bar was the dirtiest I have seen in all 7 times I have visited Thailand. The mattress had brown stains on it. The curtains were stained. The balcony door wouldn''t lock.  The food was hostel standard at best.  There were cobwebs on the ceiling. The water dispenser/path near the dining area was full of garbage.  Everything is broken, old and not maintained at all. I highly recommend staying away from this hotel."
> **- Guy Ben Zion (1/5/5)**

> "- Architectural a very nice place where our room is situated at the poolside. - Nice big rooms with a lot of space. - As always in Thailand very polite and helpful service both at reception, restaurants and cleaning. - The beach was actually quite a disappointment with a lot of dead corals making it very hard to go into the ocean for a swim and the tide made the beach dissappear. The ocean was on the other hand very warm. - The breakfast restaurant was a bit too small and often we had to wait for a table."
> **- Trond Birk (4/5/5)**

> "The hotel is located quite far from town and feels a bit isolated, so having your own car or transportation is necessary. Upon arrival, there were no security guards to guide us to the parking area, so we had to figure it out ourselves. When entering the lobby, there was only one staff member sitting there, but no greeting or acknowledgment. I had to approach and inform them that I was checking in, and they seemed unsure about the process. I had to wait until another staff member came to assist.  The hotel itself is very beautiful, with a lovely landscape. The room is nicely decorated with a good layout, but it feels a bit outdated and could benefit from renovation in the future. Also regret that the beach is not friendly to swim as a lot of scree.  Cleanliness needs improvement. Ex. Swimming pool is look green! There was quite a lot of dust in the room, no slippers were provided, and the floor felt sticky when walking. Coffee and tea bags were provided, but there was no kettle. I would also avoid using the bathtub, as there was sand and dirt, and the water turned brown.  Breakfast was good, with a variety of options. The Thai food section was especially delicious. Restaurant staff were average, but it’s best to avoid peak times as there are limited tables and the area feels too small for a resort of this size. When we arrived, there were no staff to check our room number or guide us. It felt like a self-service setup, and we had to stand and figure out what to do next or where to sit. I even had to ask other guests if I could share a table.  Luckily, I only stayed for one night at this price. I would highly recommend that the management team review and improve the operations, service, and staff training. It’s quite unfortunate because the hotel itself has a beautiful beach and landscape, but overall, it does not meet expected standards.  06/03/2026"
> **- THXX KAEW (2/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mai-samui-beach-resort-1.jpg','077 914 600','2 6, Tambon Ang Thong, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.9,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.maisamui.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifxh0027q8xde6xqk8o6','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.386+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.386+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mai-samui-beach-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mai-samui-beach-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12954441231366362348',NULL,NULL);
