> **- THXX KAEW (2/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mai-samunprai-spa-1.jpg','077 914 600','2 6, Tambon Ang Thong, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.9,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.maisamui.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifxh0027q8xde6xqk8o6','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.389+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.389+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mai-samunprai-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mai-samunprai-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12954441231366362348',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('maison-tonka','standard','cmr07ih1k00hbq8xd3geuz74b','Maison Tonka','## Top Reviews
> "Visited this café today with my husband and infant to escape the heat and enjoy something a little different.  The waitress was friendly and attentive. She brought over iced water while I waited for my husband to arrive and kindly accommodated my request for some plain bread for my infant. My smoothie was also very nice.  Unfortunately, the experience was overshadowed by the quality of the bread that was served. When it arrived, it was extremely dry and stale, to the point that I initially thought it had been toasted. Upon closer inspection, I noticed several blue-green specks within the bread that appeared consistent with mould.  When I raised my concerns with staff, I was told that the colouring was simply a characteristic of the “leavened bread.” However, the specks were blue-green in colour rather than the beige, white, or brown tones typically seen in sourdough or other artisan breads. This explanation did not address my concerns.  What was most disappointing was that the bread had been served for an infant. A simple replacement with a fresh slice would have gone a long way towards resolving the situation and reassuring us that food safety was being taken seriously.  My husband owns and operates two successful cafés, so we understand the importance of quality control and handling customer concerns appropriately. For that reason, we found this situation particularly disappointing and unacceptable.  I hope this feedback is taken constructively and helps prevent a similar experience for future customers."
> **- Rebecca (1/5/5)**

> "After seeing the reviews we had to go for breakfast. Arrived 9.30am. So ordered 2 orange juices, salmon croissant and as a French patisserie wanted to try the quiche? 10 minutes after order the waiter comes with a coconut? We said we didn''t order that and he just laughed and walked off? 5 minutes later comes with 1 orange juice? And says they have run out? 9.30am and no orange juice? Salmon croissant came for my wife and that was good! However my quiche was terrible! So dry and inedible! At 300bhat you would expect the service and quality of food to be the best? The second quiche came and was a little better but not worth 3 bhat let alone 300! The whole experience was terrible, service, food, and we clearly were very lucky with other reviews! Never will return 2 stars for the Salmon croissant!Warning avoid the quiche"
> **- john hollands (2/5/5)**

> "A huge thank you to the wonderful team at Maison Tonka! We are celebrating a friend’s 40th birthday on Koh Samui and I was given the job to arrange the cake. I’m a bit of a foodie and baker so I took this job very seriously.  Well I couldn’t have chosen better! From the first contact via Insta, the team has been extremely responsive and accomodating. They designed a custom creation for us with my friend’s favourite flavours, dark chocolate and pistachio.  On our arrival on the island, we came to pay for the cake and enjoyed an amazing breakfast. All the pastries and sweets on display looked so good too!  On the party day, the cake was delivered to our villa at the arranged time, arrived in perfect condition and looked stunning. And most importantly it was so delicious! Everyone commented on the quality and flavour of the cake. Luckily there was plenty of cake for everyone to have second servings as well 😅  Thank you again for helping to make our event so special! We will visit again on our next trip to Samui!"
> **- Andrea MacDougall (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/maison-tonka-1.jpg','065 807 6205','105, Boputh, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://maison-tonka.com/','["Monday: 7:30 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:30 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:30 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 7:30 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 7:30 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 7:30 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 7:30 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.392+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.392+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/maison-tonka-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/maison-tonka-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11361762085219819858',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('maithy-pool-lounge-restaurant','standard','cmr07ih1m00hcq8xd5667b3j3','Maithy Pool Lounge & Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "The views are amazing and unique with the planes coming in. The food is great. The staff are amazing they are first class and make you feel great. The staff are the best. Its a bit pricey but for the quality and view and amazing staff its wort it. We will come back. Its a steep drive up though but its ok. I loved the experince and wont forget it."
> **- Joseph Marraffa (5/5/5)**

> "Absolutely lovely evening at Maithy. Perfect sunset views, perfect service, great food (I am officially in love with the Tom Kha soup!). Reasonable pieces considering the upmarket location. Staff were top level, efficient and friendly. Kudos to the DJ for the great chillout music. Will certainly go again next time we''re in Samui"
> **- Adrian Cardona (5/5/5)**

> "Wow, since I arrived at the restaurant because the restaurant has a very beautiful view. You can see the temple view and the view of the pier. It is very suitable for taking a photo to keep  the atmosphere, especially at sunset. It is very beautiful sunset 🌄 As for the food, the foods are very delicious. The plate is beautiful. There are both Thai and international food And the price of food is not expensive either. And in the evening, there will be music to listen. You can sit and watch the atmosphere at night while eating For the road is quite steep. Be careful when driving. And the restaurant has a parking.  I recommend this shop and I will definitely come back again"
> **- Sugar Pattie (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/maithy-pool-lounge-restaurant-1.jpg','064 917 5174','30 123, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.uniquekohsamui.com/dining/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.394+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.394+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/maithy-pool-lounge-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/maithy-pool-lounge-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1670013688467128144',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('majesty-tailor','standard','cmr07ih1p00hdq8xd5curhzx9','Majesty Tailor','## Top Reviews
> "I am definitely recommending Ron and his services for everybody to try. As somebody being 6"
> **- Thomas Påbøl (5/5/5)**

> "My new international suit, Connection.  Came to Koh Samui Thailand for a week for a birthday celebration with plans to get a custom suit in Bangkok the week after. I  stumbled across Majesty Taylor and met Ron the owner, who is the perfect balance of knowledgeable about quality suits and a personable tailor. Not only are they knowledgeable about the current trends and fashions, they were more than accommodating with my busy schedule. They provided quality service and an extremely quality suit. As someone who routinely buys quality suits in the past, the quality of his suits match those. I’d highly recommend if in Ko Samui. I was able to get two custom suits and 4 phenomenally sized shirts!!!"
> **- Corey Nicholas Collins (5/5/5)**

> "The BEST experience I’ve had on Koh Samui. Walked into Majesty Tailor on our second day, and met the owner Ron. I had some ideas for maybe a new suit, and after careful guidance from Ron, I walked away with 2 full suits and 4 shirts. Even my girlfriend but a full suit. All custom tailored to fit perfectly, with all our small quirks and details fitted in. I will definitely order more from here, the craftsmanship is impeccable, and to top it off, not only was Ron enjoyable and a great man to be around, he personally delivered the suit to our hotel.  If you’re in the area, and consider a new shirt or suit, there is only one man to visit!"
> **- Simon Haubjerg (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/majesty-tailor-1.jpg','089 725 5657','30/5 Moo 4, Bangrak, Bophut, Koh Samui, Bophut, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61552655108905&mibextid=JRoKGi','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.397+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.397+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/majesty-tailor-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/majesty-tailor-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12366495988086664275',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('make-my-nails','standard','cmr07ih1s00heq8xd6n7kwpfl','Make My Nails','## Top Reviews
> "Absolutely amazing service! Her work is detailed and she is so kind! I had sent her multiple photos of what I wanted to do and we combined some to achieve the design I wanted. The studio is lovely, clean and there is ac. I have honestly never had someone work on my nails with such care and enthusiasm! ❤️ She also has an instagram @makemynails.kohsamui  I highly recommend doing something new to your nails if you are visiting. There are rearly talented nail technicians like her that can make what you see in pictures possible!"
> **- Diana Petrova (5/5/5)**

> "I had a lovely time and got beautiful nails in this salon. The studio has a nice atmosphere - free wifi 🥳 - and the nail artist is really a sweet person. I also had a gel pedicure here and she did an excellent job. (Small side note: If you want to have the hard skin removed from your feet, you need to pay a small extra fee - as it is not included in the basic pedicure.) The price for the service is fair, I also appreciated the clear communication on the costs beforehand."
> **- Gréta Gärtner-Uszkai (5/5/5)**

> "I got the best nails I’ve had in a very, very long time. It’s kind of perfection. She does an amazing job and is also so friendly and lovely. I’m really glad I found her and would recommend her to everyone. I will definitely come back again as long as I’m on Koh Samui. If I could, I would give 10 stars."
> **- Ece Ertas (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/make-my-nails-1.jpg','087 891 8491','215/1 แม่น้ำ Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100090806123078&mibextid=ZbWKwL','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 2:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.400+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.400+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/make-my-nails-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/make-my-nails-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3485561272205844029',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('maleny-baby-club','standard','cmr07ih1w00hfq8xdzwqy8qeu','Maleny Baby Club','Discover Maleny Baby Club, a premier for kids located in Namueang, Koh Samui. Find reviews, hours, and contact information.','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/maleny-baby-club-1.jpg','083 664 6697','6/179, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,0.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://m.facebook.com/malenybabyclub/',NULL,'cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ig4i004oq8xdv207xuh2','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.404+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.404+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/maleny-baby-club-1.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9780267422090433887',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('malibu-resort','standard','cmr07ih1z00hgq8xdg6uz2vai','Malibu Resort','## Top Reviews
> "Everything is fine Until you’ve left some value things when you checked out. Put that into your mind, you’ll never get it or them back.  Front of house is fine though but not sure how genuine the house keeping are.  Sometime, the thing wasn’t that expensive but it’s meaningful for the owner."
> **- Py A INPANG (1/5/5)**

> "I felt so sad to have spent my vacation here. The hotel is not at all like the pictures - I’m guessing they were taken a long time ago or enhanced. This resort is very dirty and rundown. The first room I stayed in was horrible, so I asked to change. Second room, same problems. I then asked to leave and get a refund for the remaining nights but they refused and were very rude about it. I ended up leaving early anyway. I could barely sleep because there were lots of mosquitoes and bed bugs, as well as very thin walls so you can hear everything. Terrible sewer smell in the room too. Very run down room. The breakfast was horrible and very limited. The only good thing about this resort is it’s next to the beach. The hotel is very expensive for what you get - you can spend the same amount of money on a much better resort."
> **- Adam Smith (1/5/5)**

> "Nice experience Pool is clean and great access to the beach ⛱️. Also central to bars,  supermarkets and food markets. Rooms are aged, but everything works,  lots of mosquitoes 🦟. Breckfast is basic, fresh fruit and juice went down a treat. Hotel staff are very attentive  and friendly"
> **- Jonathan (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/malibu-resort-1.jpg','077 332 855','15/2 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.2,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.malibukohsamui.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.407+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.407+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/malibu-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/malibu-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16738135670741120313',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('malika-beach-club','standard','cmr07ih2300hhq8xd3kyt3v04','Malika Beach Club','## Top Reviews
> "Perfect Beach Club for Families! 🌴☀️  An absolutely family-friendly beach club that leaves nothing to be desired! Parking is super easy, making arrival stress-free. The staff is incredibly welcoming, and with plenty of seating, you’ll always find a great spot.  The kids'' area is fantastic, featuring a children’s pool, playground, and even a supervised kids'' club. There are three pools in total, as well as treehouses, great live DJ music, and a relaxed, vibrant atmosphere.  Everything is extremely clean and well-maintained, with complimentary towels, a climate-controlled massage area, and a beauty salon. The food and drinks are delicious and reasonably priced for the quality and service provided.  The absolute highlight: an incredible fire show every Friday at around 7:30 PM! 🔥 Definitely highly recommended, and we will be back for sure! 😊"
> **- Katharina Zahn (5/5/5)**

> "Beautiful beach club with recreational and relaxation outlets such as salon, steam rooms and massage pavilion. Nicely landscaped and thoughtfully designed. Sundown hours is especially picturesque with beautiful views of Bangrak beach and the distant Koh Phangan. Great to enjoy over refreshing drinks and food."
> **- Wunda Stone (5/5/5)**

> "Locate in Bangrak, awesome new beach front multi function venue with restaurant , sun deck, massage… everything we need to relax. Natural design that combine with rocks, trees; creating ambience that is so unique. Definitely a must-go venue. Will come back to check out its hamburger next time, should be very juicy, tender, and tasty😀"
> **- don hsi (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/malika-beach-club-1.jpg','080 285 9854','147, 25, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.malikabeachclub.com/','["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.411+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.411+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/malika-beach-club-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/malika-beach-club-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4213644220587416317',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mamba-beach-lounge-restaurant','standard','cmr07ih2a00hiq8xdvb6dilgz','Mamba Beach Lounge & Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "Such a wonderful Restaurant with live music and amazing staff. My kids played volleyball with some residents while we chilled drinking cocktails listening to live reggae. One of the highlights of our tour around the islands. The owners are lovely and we wish them the very best with their business and life in Thailand. Can’t wait to come back.  Andy & Vicky"
> **- Vicky Rees (5/5/5)**

> "Unfortunately, the waiters and staff are not Thai and don''t speak English very well, so is quite difficult to communicate in either Thai or English.  There are quite a lot of communication problems in trying to get your order through and ask any questions."
> **- Jo S (3/5/5)**

> "So the waiter was friendly but they can not understand english they dont know what’s on the menu. The menu was also a little bit weird you get 3 cards with the menu printed on both sides it is very confusing! Also for the waitress . The food was okay the pizzas were dry on the outside but it was okay. The owner said after all that, that the cocktails were on the house so we ordered another round for us 3 persons, but then when the bill came the waiter did not know about anything, so we told her that. Then the manager came again and told us that she only meant one cocktail but thats not true."
> **- Rafael _K (2/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mamba-beach-lounge-restaurant-1.jpg','092 980 0936','F24R+RQV ThailandF24R+RQV, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:30 AM – 11:30 PM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 11:30 PM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 11:30 PM","Thursday: 8:30 AM – 11:30 PM","Friday: 8:30 AM – 11:30 PM","Saturday: 8:30 AM – 11:30 PM","Sunday: 8:30 AM – 11:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.418+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.418+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mamba-beach-lounge-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mamba-beach-lounge-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7643489222151779347',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mammamia-coffee','standard','cmr07ih2f00hjq8xdwoo5uxao','Mammamia Coffee','## Top Reviews
> "Average rating. Stifling heat (the fans weren''t enough). The hand burger for lunch was just average. Small portions of fries and beer. Meh."
> **- Laurent Gennerat (3/5/5)**

> "From the Heart. Great atmosphere and food."
> **- Илья Левашов (5/5/5)**',NULL,NULL,'HX9W+JPR, Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifs1000cq8xdfo2aau32','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.423+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.423+00:00',NULL,'https://maps.google.com/?cid=13156598710944389809',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('manga-sushi','standard','cmr07ih2j00hkq8xdk3hobgjn','Manga Sushi','## Top Reviews
> "If you’re looking for high-quality sushi, Manga Sushi is the place to go. You might find the prices a bit high at first glance, but once you taste the food, you’ll realize you’re paying for premium quality. The fish is fresh, the flavors are balanced, and the service is warm and welcoming. Great food and great vibes!"
> **- Aung ChanThar (5/5/5)**

> "Not bad at all..enjoyed this. Great service and seating areas. Food could of been better. Pretty expensive and not the best for price. Unlikely to return but not bad place"
> **- Paul (3/5/5)**

> "Thank you so much for delicious sushi, size is big, ingredients are super fresh 8 pieces in the roll. Nice place to come with a big group of people. They have different teas in pots. 🫖 if you enjoy your hot tea… Love the art on the walls ❤️🔥👌🏼"
> **- Anna Denysenko (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/manga-sushi-1.jpg','096 776 3542','127, Beach, 8 Thanon Had Lamai, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.mangasushisamui.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.427+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.427+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/manga-sushi-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/manga-sushi-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5350589250306699375',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mango-tree-house-rent','standard','cmr07ih2m00hlq8xdkjhfhoz2','Mango Tree House Rent','## Top Reviews
> "This mango tree house is an absolute gem! Nestled among lush greenery, it offers a peaceful stay.  The craftsmanship of the house is impressive, blending seamlessly with the natural surroundings. The interior is cozy yet well-equipped, providing a comfortable stay while maintaining a rustic charm.  Overall, this mango tree house is a perfect escape from city life. Highly recommend it for nature lovers, couples, or anyone looking for a unique and memorable stay!"
> **- Sarah J (5/5/5)**

> "Stunning property with high end features. Obviously well loved and cared for by its owners. It’s like a gallery house with lots of classy artwork, but it’s also got more of an industrial feel, so very modern. The pool is community shared but very quiet. It’s close to the large supermarkets, the famous “Fisherman’s Village” and also the elephant sanctuary."
> **- michael allen (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mango-tree-house-rent-1.jpg','+66816938381','Mango Tree House, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.mangotreehousesamui.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.430+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.430+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mango-tree-house-rent-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mango-tree-house-rent-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17177076552922098179',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mango-tree','standard','cmr07ih2o00hmq8xd733vr5zq','Mango Tree','## Top Reviews
> "Visited Mango Tree right after arriving at Koh Samui through the Lipa Noi ferry port and decided to have lunch here. The restaurant atmosphere was nice and relaxing, suitable for a first meal after the journey.  We ordered the pineapple fried rice. The taste was decent, but it was slightly different from what we expected, as it was not served in the usual half-cut pineapple presentation. Unfortunately, the prawns in the dish were undercooked, which was disappointing and affected the overall experience.  Service was acceptable and the location is convenient if you are arriving from the ferry port, but the kitchen definitely needs to pay more attention to food preparation quality."
> **- Gan SB (4/5/5)**

> "Definitely worth stopping by for the coconut combo dessert – a true poetry of flavors. The kra prao is also very good. Prices are reasonable and portions are generous for local standards. The owners are always attentive and regularly check on the tables, which makes the experience even better."
> **- Grzegorz Mikulski (5/5/5)**

> "The best food we have experienced whilst here in Thailand. Not only was the food incredible but the service was superb too. Very attentive from start to finish. Provided fans to keep us cool and even mosquito repellent too. The cocktails were amazing."
> **- avrodamo (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mango-tree-1.jpg','081 693 8381','123/8 Tambon Lipa Noi, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/MangoTreeRestaurantBarSamui','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.432+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.432+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mango-tree-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mango-tree-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3863783830685738897',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mantra-samui-resort','standard','cmr07ih2t00hnq8xdqr2ne60h','Mantra Samui Resort','## Top Reviews
> "An absolutely perfect stay from the beginning to the end! This hotel exceeded all our expectations in every possible way. Everything was spotless and beautifully maintained you could truly feel the high standards everywhere.  The food was outstanding, with a huge variety of delicious options every day. Every meal felt special! The pool area was stunning and relaxing, the gym was modern and very well equipped, and the view was simply breathtaking something you never get tired of.  The laundry service was unbelievably fast and so convenient. We also loved the many extra services offered, especially the bike rental, which made our stay even more enjoyable and fun.  But what truly made this experience unforgettable was the staff. They are without a doubt the friendliest, warmest, and most helpful team we have ever encountered. We never had to ask twice for anything everything was handled immediately with a smile. They made us feel not just like guests, but like family.  In my 10 years of traveling, this has honestly been the best hotel experience I have ever had. We are already looking forward to coming back next year!  Thank you for making our stay so special and unforgettable!"
> **- Salem Mechani (5/5/5)**

> "My stay at Mantra Resort was definitely memorable, and what I liked most about the place was the excellent service. They treat you incredibly well and really take care of you - I even got a free room upgrade! The uphill infinity pool is stunning, offering incredible views over the gulf. They have two room types available: Studio Style: This is their signature room. They are really lovely, modern, and have a beautiful decor and vibe. Apartments: Located near the pool. While the apartments themselves are good, the location can be a bit sketchy. When it rains, it gets very slippery up there so be very careful. That being said, a few things bothered me during my stay, namely the constant AC issues and power cuts. To their credit, they get fixed very quickly. But there was a night where the issue lasted quite a while and I was even given a replacement room for the night when it rained heavily and the generator went out, which I really appreciated. However, I wish I didn''t have to ask for the room change myself; I would have preferred if management recognized the issue quickly and offered it upfront. Overall, I’d give it a solid rating for the staff''s attention, care, and quick fixes. But the power cuts and AC issues need a full audit and permanent fix so future guests don''t have to deal with them."
> **- Nader Alqalaa (4/5/5)**

> "We had a great stay at the Mantra Samui Resort and would definitely recommend it.  The staff were without exception incredibly friendly, helpful, and welcoming.  The room very spacious, we had an ocean view with a private terrace, sun loungers, and a beautiful sea view.  The pool area is lovely and looks just like the pictures. The pool is very large, there are plenty of sun loungers, and we never had trouble finding a free one. Pool towels are provided.  The restaurant is also nice, with good food and drinks. Breakfast, however, has some room for improvement. It felt a bit uninspired at times. The quality was okay, partly à la carte and partly buffet. The coffee was very good, but overall breakfast does not quite reach a 5-star standard.  Regarding the location: the hotel is logically situated higher up the hill. With a scooter, everything is easily reachable, and for us the location worked very well. Scooters can be rented directly at the hotel. The road up to the hotel is quite steep, so you should already have experience riding a scooter.  Overall, a clear recommendation."
> **- Selina Schneider (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mantra-samui-resort-1.jpg','077 951 600','9/123-124, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.mantrasamui.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.437+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.437+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mantra-samui-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mantra-samui-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7329438674503136020',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('maraleina-sports-resort','standard','cmr07ih2z00hoq8xd9s02ra44','Maraleina Sports Resort','## Top Reviews
> "Wow—what an incredible place. I don’t even know where to begin. The facilities are world-class, the staff and trainers are genuinely welcoming, and the range of classes and equipment is exceptional. From HYROX to Pilates to Yoga, everything is top-of-the-line, making this one of the best all-rounder gyms and truly amazing value for money.  From Sand and the team at reception to Moo, Marta, and the rest of the training crew, it’s been 5 stars again and again. Thank you for making us feel so welcome and for helping us work toward our goals, even if just for a short time. We’ll honestly miss you all once our stay is over."
> **- Chanté Venter (5/5/5)**

> "My girlfriend and I came for a 5Day fitness retreat, and truly enjoyed our time here. The various fitness classes were challenging yet fun - with each of the coaches showcasing a good level of professionalism and competency (even though they might teach different unrelated classes).  During our short time, we did yoga, body sculpt, Muay Thai, TRX, Hyrox-based, and even squash - all the classes were good and pushed us quite a bit, even though we exercised quite regularly.  The top notch gym was certainly a highlight as well, with high quality equipment that was never crowded. We could tell that many external guests dropped by for the gym as well.  The sauna and ice baths were something we took daily advantage of to recover. Although it was a bit of a shame that we had to be split up as it was gender specific and within the locker rooms.  While our experience was great, there were a few areas that we felt was a little shame. Firstly the accommodations are located 5mins drive away and required shuttle bus to pick up (which was usually quite fast). But we heard there’s a new hotel that is aimed to be open by May 2026, which will make things a lot more convenient.  Secondly, the breakfast could do with a little more variety, and a little more protein rich options- considering that it’s a sports resort. (There are also some secret menu items that’s available but not on the menu!)  Forthly, we felt the class programming could have a little more options in timings, as there’s usually only 2-3 classes in the morning, and 2 at 4/5pm. Which means it will be a bit of a rush to head out after the morning sessions + a meal, and return before the first afternoon class.  Lastly, there isn’t really much around the resort area, so you’d have to travel out for more restaurants and shops. The free bike rental was also good as it opens up a handful of options at the beach nearby, but don’t expect a lot from it.  That said it’s still an amazing experience and we’d recommend for anyone looking to get away for a couple of days and get fit!"
> **- Jason Lee (5/5/5)**

> "I went to Maraleina to try the new facilities and it did not disappoint. The place is beautiful, very clean, with brand new equipment. Everything you need is there, from ergs to weights (perfect to train for Hyrox!). Will definitely go back on my next trip to Samui."
> **- Al (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/maraleina-sports-resort-1.jpg','080 169 4276','123/9 Moo 4 Tambol Namuang, ตำบล หน้าเมือง Koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.maraleina.com/','["Monday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifzl002uq8xdaadxjuc2','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.443+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.443+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/maraleina-sports-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/maraleina-sports-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=18071624545827231997',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('marasca','standard','cmr07ih3300hpq8xdpgr9numf','Marasca','## Top Reviews
> "My stay at Marasca Samui was absolutely exceptional and exceeded all expectations. From the very first moment, the level of service stood out — genuinely warm, attentive, and professional at every step.  As a Hilton Honors status guest, I truly felt recognized and valued. The team clearly understands what premium hospitality means: personalized approach, proactive care, and sincere attention to detail that makes you feel special rather than just accommodated.  The views are simply stunning — beautiful sea panoramas that create a sense of calm and luxury throughout the stay. Whether enjoying the morning or watching the sunset, the surroundings are unforgettable.  The cuisine deserves special praise. The food was consistently excellent, beautifully presented, and full of flavor. Dining at the hotel was a real pleasure and an important part of the overall experience.  What impressed me most was the care provided at every step — nothing felt forced or scripted. The staff was always one step ahead, ready to help, advise, and make the stay effortless and relaxing.  Marasca Samui is a place where high standards meet genuine hospitality. I would gladly return and wholeheartedly recommend it to anyone looking for comfort, great service, and a truly memorable stay."
> **- Klaudiusz Kott (5/5/5)**

> "The best staff I have ever encountered! Everyone was so kind, welcoming, and genuinely friendly throughout my stay. The rooms were exceptionally clean and very well maintained. The food was incredible, with a wide variety of delicious options to choose from. I highly recommend this hotel and would definitely stay here again!"
> **- Sara Fahm (5/5/5)**

> "I stayed at Marasca with my family and had a wonderful experience from the moment we arrived. The staff were very friendly, welcoming, and even recognized my son, which made us feel very special. The welcome ritual was thoughtful and beautifully connected to the story and culture of Koh Samui.  Our room was extremely comfortable, and the super king-size bed was perfect for the family. I also appreciated the turndown service, where they provided sleep amenities to help us rest better, so I didn’t even need to request an extra bed.  Since we arrived on a Saturday, we enjoyed the pop-up food station offering burgers and hot dogs. The Afro house music created a great atmosphere that blended perfectly with the beach club vibe.  Another thing I really liked was the hotel app. It made it very easy to communicate with the staff and borrow items from Marasca by U. It was very convenient and efficient.  I would especially like to highlight the breakfast. There was a great variety of options, including a buffet and an unlimited à la carte menu. I loved that I could order freshly prepared dishes while still enjoying the buffet selection.  Thank you to all the staff for such a warm welcome and a wonderful experience. I will definitely come back again and highly recommend your place. It’s a great spot on Koh Samui! 😊"
> **- Natheera Panmas (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/marasca-1.jpg','077 953 555','789, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.marasca.live/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.447+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.447+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/marasca-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/marasca-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=311937183386341805',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('march-samui-resort','standard','cmr07ih3800hqq8xdh36vhcyv','March Samui Resort','## Top Reviews
> "We took superior king room,enough space,very clean,they cleen rooms every day,you have small safe in your room,pool is clean,outside is very calm. Location is great,you have cheap supermarket just outside,and beach is nice with lot of restoraunts. Service is great,you can book various trips at the reception with 10% discount You can rent scooter."
> **- Djordje Ivanovski (5/5/5)**

> "Comfy bed. big bathroom. opposite a lovely big beach. The pool is so nice! all rooms had a terrace outside that was very private. staff were lovely. they offer moped rental and Muay Thai sessions"
> **- Eva J (5/5/5)**

> "DO NOT book this place. They cancel our booking reservation without telling us, we arrived at the hotel and they told us it’s fully booked. Our money from booking got blocked for 12 days to wait for refund - that we have to call and ask for, because hotel doesn’t inform booking directly. So it cost us lots of stress and money"
> **- katarzyna lukasik (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/march-samui-resort-1.jpg','092 526 4598','73/10 Moo6 Tambon Mae Nam, Koh Samui Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://marchsamuiresort.top/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifs1000cq8xdfo2aau32','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.452+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.452+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/march-samui-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/march-samui-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14458820214854383098',NULL,NULL);
