> "Good shop,  all you need for a good catch, nice owners,"
> **- Island Man (5/5/5)**

> "Compact store loaded with most (possibly all) the fishing gear you need for casual sport fishing around Samui.  Decently impressive variety of hooks, weights, lures, floating jigs, rods, reels, line (most types, including cable).."
