INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('marea-pizza-focaccioni','standard','cmr07ih3e00hsq8xdxpij75s5','MAREA Pizza & Focaccioni','## Top Reviews
> "ust had the Pizza Margherita and Greek Salad . perfetto! The Margherita is the real deal, wood-fired, thin, and blistered just right. San Marzano tomatoes, fresh mozzarella, and basil that pops with flavor. Simple, but executed flawlessly , you can taste the quality in every bite. Paired it with the Greek Salad , crisp lettuce, juicy tomatoes, red onion, olives, and a generous block of creamy feta, all dressed in a light, zesty vinaigrette. Super fresh and the perfect cool contrast to the hot pizza. Service was friendly and fast, even on a busy evening. Loved the retro vibe and open-air seating , great spot to unwind after a beach day. Highly recommend for anyone craving authentic Italian flavors on the island. We’ll be back! 🍕🥗"
> **- shay yakobi (5/5/5)**

> "Extremely kind staff, I hope they are getting paid enough for how good they attend customers! The food was delicious! Big portions! The restaurant is really elegant and nice, it’s very clean and its placed in the perfect location! You can get great pics! Good spot to see the airplanes landing 🛬 Definitely recommended and would come back again!"
> **- Dafhne Karina (5/5/5)**

> "Very friendly staff! 🤗 Gorgeous view of the sea, beautiful at sunset 🌅 I loved the margarita pizza, it’s delicious 🍕"
> **- maika m (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/marea-pizza-focaccioni-1.jpg','080 005 5677','4171 16 Bangrak 6, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.mareasamui.com/','["Monday: 1:00 – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 1:00 – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 1:00 – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 1:00 – 9:00 PM","Friday: 1:00 – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 1:00 – 9:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.458+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.458+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/marea-pizza-focaccioni-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/marea-pizza-focaccioni-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17057203037359178036',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('marzano','standard','cmr07ih3h00htq8xdutxzikxm','Marzano','## Top Reviews
> "Great little restaurant right on the beach. I love coming there for a coffee. I think they have the best one, at least the best I found in Chaweng. The whole team is very friendly and easy-going. Special thank you to the barista named Pop. He is always super friendly and attentive, and makes amazing coffee. ☕️ This place has also very decent food, especially compared to many other beach restaurants in Chaweng beach, where quality tends to be on the lower end. I especially like their pizza, very yummy and served fast. Thank you for amazing service. 🙏💜"
> **- Marie L. (5/5/5)**

> "Stayed at Malibu resort and this was onsite. I remembered eating the pizza at this place  years ago when it first opened. This time again I went for its pizza. The margarita was just enough for 1 . No wastage. Crust was good. Slightly fluffy . Naples style. Eat it by the pool or beach fron. Perfecto! Hotel guests with room numbers  get to enjoy 10% off . There were passersby who walked along the beach and came in for food. Nice centralised location along busy Chaweng beach."
> **- Anne C (4/5/5)**

> "Great service and awesome location. Unfortunately the quality of the pizzas didn’t meet my expectations. Regarding the name and the prices for the pizzas I was expecting a better quality."
> **- Pizza is Love (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/marzano-1.jpg','077 332 855','ตำบล บ่อผุด Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.2,0,0,0,NULL,'https://malibukohsamui.com/italian-restaurant-chaweng','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.461+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.461+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/marzano-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/marzano-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8358569466478215340',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('matcha-samui-resort','standard','cmr07ih3j00huq8xdv5quenn0','Matcha Samui Resort','## Top Reviews
> "Very nice stay in a great location directly on Chaweng Beach. At first, the two separate hotel buildings felt a little confusing, but after the first day it became very easy to understand and move around.  The room service and housekeeping worked perfectly throughout the stay. I was especially impressed by the shower water pressure and the stable water temperature, which was honestly one of the best experiences compared to several other places I have stayed in Thailand.  The pool area and beach area were both very relaxing and well maintained. The staff were friendly, helpful, and professional. The location is also excellent, with many restaurants, shops, massage places, and nightlife within walking distance."
> **- Jan Erikson (5/5/5)**

> "This stay was a complete disappointment and far below acceptable standards. The hotel was under major renovations, causing constant and unbearable noise throughout our stay. There was absolutely no disclosure of these renovations anywhere at the time of booking. Had this been clearly stated, we would never have booked this hotel.  The elevator was not working, creating serious inconvenience. The rooms smelled strongly of sewage, making them unpleasant and unacceptable to stay in.  The breakfast was poor, very limited, and lacked any variety. The rooms themselves are old, outdated, and in urgent need of renovation.  Despite all these serious issues, the hotel refused to cancel our reservation or offer any refund, which we found highly unprofessional and unacceptable.  Overall, this hotel failed on every level. We strongly advise others to avoid booking until all renovations are completed and the hotel meets basic hospitality standards."
> **- Leah (1/5/5)**

> "I had a wonderful stay at this hotel. Everything exceeded my expectations—from the cleanliness of the room to the friendliness of the staff. The location is very convenient, making it easy to get around. The atmosphere was comfortable and relaxing, and I truly felt welcomed throughout my stay. I would definitely come back again and highly recommend this hotel to others."
> **- Phakdi wagner (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/matcha-samui-resort-1.jpg','098 519 6297','19 Moo2 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.2,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.matchasamuiresort.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.463+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.463+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/matcha-samui-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/matcha-samui-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9510053998817252064',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mazda-samui-mitrthae','standard','cmr07ih3m00hvq8xd5u6hfox1','Mazda Samui Mitrthae','## Top Reviews
> "The mechanics'' service was a complete disaster, absolutely appalling. I had an appointment at 8:30, arrived at 8:20, and was greeted by a girl who didn''t speak English, so naturally she couldn''t understand what I was saying. At 8:45, the so-called mechanics manager arrived, but he also didn''t speak English. I waited in the waiting room, and at 8:50, the mechanics finally appeared. At 9:00, they came to have me sign a work order for a service including an oil change. I had come for an estimate (the appointment was made 15 days prior) because of a warning light on the dashboard. A third man who spoke three words of English tried to converse with me and finally understood what I wanted (at last). After waiting for over an hour, they told me that my vehicle had several problems, okay, but most importantly, that the front brake pads were very worn and needed replacing. I said okay, but the worst part is that my car was already back on the lift, ready to be returned to me. They never even asked me if I wanted them to change them right away—how is that even possible?! They''re safety-critical parts.  I had my brake pads changed elsewhere, and this proves once again (it''s not the first time I''ve been disappointed) that this service is incredibly incompetent. They have no respect for schedules, no one speaks proper English, and the mechanics seem more interested in chatting amongst themselves than taking good care of the vehicles and customers. Seriously, if you''re thinking of buying a Mazda, be aware that the service department is completely inadequate."
> **- lady jersey (1/5/5)**

> "Very poor service, technical people are not technically fit for the cars. They include other services of MG cars. Before the service for pathetic now become more pathetic  Service Mazda of Bangkok is best but for Samui very poor. Good car Good customer steering place but for car it''s not good for service. I have so many cars of Mazda but it''s look like the service are not good and upto marks.  I hope company Mazda will do something on this. Others wise soon this things come into market and custom avoid to purchase Mazda. Try to understand service is also a part of company."
> **- Pramod Dubey (1/5/5)**

> "We had the good fortune to meet dealer customer relation expert Patcharawan Sootmuang who understood our requests & spoke impressive English. We needed to make an appointment for 3 days later. Fortunately the required parts were in stock. We were amazed by the comfort of the waiting room. Spacious, comfortable & a variety of snacks & drinks available. Again, very impressive. We''re glad we made the decision to have our car serviced here & we''ll definitely continue to come here. Very efficient service."
> **- Gerry Steiert (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mazda-samui-mitrthae-1.jpg','077 415 700','Na Mueang, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/mazdakohsamuimitrthae/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifui0012q8xdzn158clv','cmr07ig4i004oq8xdv207xuh2','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.466+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.466+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mazda-samui-mitrthae-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mazda-samui-mitrthae-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16094307576628267550',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('meal-prep-lamai','standard','cmr07ih3o00hwq8xda772g83t','Meal Prep','## Top Reviews
> "One of the best healthy spots I’ve tried in Bo put. The concept is really well done: every meal includes the calories and macros (protein, carbs, fats), which is super convenient if you train or simply want to eat clean without guessing everything.  What I liked most is that the food is actually very healthy BUT still tastes really good, often “healthy food” is bland, but not here. Portions are also generous and filling, while still feeling light and balanced afterwards.  The wraps and bowls were fresh, high in protein, and very satisfying. Service was fast.  Another big plus: they’re open almost all day, including mornings from 9am, which is perfect for breakfast, post-workout meals, or just a healthy lunch during the day.  Prices are fair and not overpriced considering the quality, ingredients, and portion sizes.  You can tell this place is made for people who care about fitness, health, or simply eating better without sacrificing taste. I’ll definitely come back 👍"
> **- Mathieu Chaumont (5/5/5)**

> "A wonderful place for lunch or coffee! The food is delicious and well-balanced, excellent value for money! You never feel heavy afterwards, just satisfied and full. It''s especially nice and convenient that the calories, fats, and carbohydrates are already calculated, so if you''re tracking your diet in detail, there''s no better place. The desserts deserve a special round of applause, and the coffee is excellent! I''ve been eating here 5-6 times a week for a month or more—that says a lot!  Thank you, meal prep ❤️🙏🏽"
> **- Alina Izotova (5/5/5)**

> "Meal prep samui in chaweng is the best place on the island, maybe in the whole of thailand for affordable clean macro calculated food. Theyre quality and dedicated to heavy scrans is unparalleled. Me and my friends have been coming here nearly everyday for over a year and they are always consist with high quality food aswell as providing a great atmosphere for good craic. Shout out my home girl Rona for always providing a warm welcome everyday!"
> **- Ethan Kelly (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/meal-prep-lamai-1.jpg','095 558 0350','1, 18, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'http://mealprepsamui.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.468+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.468+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/meal-prep-lamai-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/meal-prep-lamai-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10244534174004091875',NULL,NULL);
