INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('meeting-bar','standard','cmr07ih3s00hyq8xdada1oypy','Meeting Bar','## Top Reviews
> "Really cool spot. On the road about halfway between Bophut and Maenam. Good food, beers, cocktails, live music open session every night. Pan the owner is an amazing guitar player and singer and a great host. I got up and sang a few songs. Bar only reopened last year, definitely worth calling into. Also some really cute dogs live there too!"
> **- Donal Scullion (5/5/5)**

> "A Hidden Gem in Mae Nam with Authentic Vibes and Great Entertainment Meeting Bar Samui is an exceptional spot that truly deserves its 5-star rating. Located in Mae Nam, this bar-restaurant offers a unique atmosphere with its tropical garden setting and colorful decoration.[tripadvisor +2] Atmosphere and Entertainment The venue stands out for its live music performances that create a warm and festive ambiance. The space is comfortable and airy, featuring free pool tables for customers. The atmosphere strikes the perfect balance between relaxed and lively, making it ideal for an enjoyable evening with friends.[wanderlog +3] Food and Drinks The authentic Thai cuisine is delicious and highly appreciated by visitors. The menu features Thai and Isan specialties with reasonable prices starting at 80 baht. Cocktails are available from 99 baht, and the beer promotions at 299 baht with complimentary ice offer excellent value for money."
> **- koh Ai Solution (5/5/5)**

> "A wonderful place for dinner! The staff is kind, polite, and exceptionally friendly. The food is outstanding—whatever you order, you can expect high-quality ingredients and delicious flavors. I highly recommend this restaurant, even during quieter hours. A great dining experience!"
> **- Jennifer Ciotti (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/meeting-bar-1.jpg','093 956 0710','177/53 หมู่1 Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.meetingbarsamui.com/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 11:30 PM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.472+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.472+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/meeting-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/meeting-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11476906318880130809',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mekong-fusion-restaurant-lounge','standard','cmr07ih3v00hzq8xdcv3qhwmy','Mekong Fusion Restaurant & Lounge','## Top Reviews
> "We were introduced to this restaurant by Pink House, and we are incredibly grateful for the recommendation. The location is simply stunning: beautiful, tucked away from the hustle and bustle, and set in the middle of a true jungle oasis that instantly makes you feel relaxed.  The service was exceptionally friendly, warm, and attentive without ever feeling forced. The food was outstanding — creative fusion cuisine at a very high level, perfectly balanced and full of flavor.  This is one of those places you don’t discover by chance but will definitely remember. Highly recommended — we will most certainly be back."
> **- Leyla (5/5/5)**

> "I came to this restaurant on a Wednesday late afternoon around 5pm. It was very quiet just a few people around the pool.  I had such a lovely experience. The space has a beautiful relaxed lounge vibe — warm lighting, natural wood and bamboo details, and a really calm, welcoming atmosphere. It feels very comfortable.  I read a few negative reviews about the service, that was not my experience at all the service was excellent — attentive without being intrusive, and genuinely friendly.  The menu has great variety, both thai and Vietnamese dishes and a large drinks menu and full bar. I went with the special pho which was especially good — rich broth, fresh herbs, and perfectly balanced.  Definitely recommend if you’re looking for a relaxed but quality dining experience in Koh Samui. I will happily return."
> **- Dtown (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing Viet food at Mekong Fusion! The tea leaf salad (in rice sheet), the fried spring rolls and Cashew nut curry were fantastic! Great variety of dishes and delicious vegetarian/vegan options too! We had a great chat with the French manager as well who was very nice and friendly! Easily one of the best restaurants in Koh Samui, we definitely recommend - would be getting a lot more attention if it was on one of the busier neighbourhoods of the island!"
> **- Tony Lao (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mekong-fusion-restaurant-lounge-1.jpg','080 525 3172','91/11, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.samui-baan-sukreep.com/','["Monday: 12:00 – 10:30 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 10:30 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 10:30 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 10:30 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 10:30 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 10:30 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 10:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig5c0051q8xdykrbexft','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.475+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.475+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mekong-fusion-restaurant-lounge-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mekong-fusion-restaurant-lounge-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10469758651923398215',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('melati-resort','standard','cmr07ih3z00i0q8xdsv7jrwx0','Melati Resort','## Top Reviews
> "I surprised my wonderful partner with a belated Valentine''s romantic getaway. The resort is absolutely stunning, with lush tropical gardens, and we took lots of memorable photos during our short 5-minute walk to the beach. After waiting a few minutes, our beachfront romantic dinner was ready, and it was an incredible experience to watch the sunset. The team members were friendly, attentive, and even took lovely photos of us. The meal was delicious—a beautifully arranged 7-course set menu with many other options. The variety of food was tempting, and the wine paired perfectly with the dishes! The candles, flowers, and open pergola created a truly breathtaking setting. We loved every moment of this special evening, and it’s a memory we will cherish forever. Thank you again for such a wonderful experience!"
> **- Vanessa Bruce (5/5/5)**

> "We stayed at Melati Resort for 4 nights with our 2 kids and we absolutely loved it. From the moment we arrived, it felt like a little tropical escape. The resort is set on a quiet stretch of beach that feels almost private, which made it incredibly peaceful and relaxing. The whole place is beautifully designed, surrounded by lush gardens and with a real sense of space and calm. We stayed in a spacious villa with a private pool which is perfect for families and such a luxury to have your own space to unwind. One of the highlights was the option for a private dinner on the beach, which felt really special. The spa was also amazing, we had one of the best massages there. What really stood out to us was how genuinely kind and warm everyone is, the staff made us feel so welcome throughout our stay. There’s a small but lovely kids club right by the pool, which made it easy to combine relaxing and keeping the kids entertained. The pool area at he beach is beautiful, with a swim-up bar, and we really enjoyed the different dinner themes in the evenings. If you feel like exploring, Choeng Mon Beach is just a short scooter or taxi ride away with some great beach restaurants. Right next to the resort there’s also a small local spot on the beach where you can enjoy simple Thai dishes, grab an ice cream, or even get a massage. Overall, a beautiful, luxurious and very family-friendly place, perfect if you’re looking for a peaceful stay with a bit of everything."
> **- Sarah Reinhoudt (5/5/5)**

> "What a wonderful experience from stepping out of the taxi until checking out. As a person who has traveled in different countries around the world I would highly recommend this hotel if you visiting Koh Samui. All staff are so helpful and nice. You feel more like a part of the family than just a guest with a room number. The breakfast were really good, they had something for everyone, they also changed some of the courses from day to day which was fun. The caramel sauce and bread and much more were homemade which gave that “little extra”. Excellent food, from Thai cuisine to English fish and chips. The rooms had everything you can ask for. Spacious environment, bathroom facilities, board games and wardrobes and cabinets. A lovely experience. A bit pricier than other hotels, but you don’t mind while you get to enjoy everything I wrote above. After a couple of days after checking out of this hotel we came back to enjoy a stunning dinner and the staff remembers us and was very welcoming. Thank you!"
> **- Florencia Macsad (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/melati-resort-1.jpg','077 913 400','9 Thongson Bay 99, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'http://melatiresort.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifv2001aq8xdag7cvjgf','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.479+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.479+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/melati-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/melati-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8695544763221050333',NULL,NULL);
