> "What a wonderful experience from stepping out of the taxi until checking out. As a person who has traveled in different countries around the world I would highly recommend this hotel if you visiting Koh Samui. All staff are so helpful and nice. You feel more like a part of the family than just a guest with a room number. The breakfast were really good, they had something for everyone, they also changed some of the courses from day to day which was fun. The caramel sauce and bread and much more were homemade which gave that “little extra”. Excellent food, from Thai cuisine to English fish and chips. The rooms had everything you can ask for. Spacious environment, bathroom facilities, board games and wardrobes and cabinets. A lovely experience. A bit pricier than other hotels, but you don’t mind while you get to enjoy everything I wrote above. After a couple of days after checking out of this hotel we came back to enjoy a stunning dinner and the staff remembers us and was very welcoming. Thank you!"
> **- Florencia Macsad (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/melati-spa-1.jpg','077 913 400','9 Thongson Bay 99, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'http://melatiresort.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifv2001aq8xdag7cvjgf','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.481+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.481+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/melati-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/melati-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8695544763221050333',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('melia-hotel-resorts','standard','cmr07ih4400i2q8xd23jfq939','Melia Hotel & Resorts','## Top Reviews
> "I stayed at this hotel with my sister and had a wonderful experience. The staff were incredibly attentive, always checking in to make sure we were comfortable and helping us with transportation around the resort. Their friendliness and hospitality made our stay even more enjoyable.  The room was clean and well maintained, and the entire resort was spotless and beautifully surrounded by nature. The beach was stunning, with crystal-clear water and a relaxing atmosphere.  The food was delicious, especially the Spanish dishes, which were some of the best we have ever tasted. Overall, we had a fantastic stay and would highly recommend this hotel to anyone looking for a relaxing and memora"
> **- ปิยรัตน์ สุดรัก (5/5/5)**

> "I just wanted to share how absolutely incredible my stay was at your hotel. I truly loved every moment of it. The hotel itself was amazing, but what really made the experience unforgettable was the level of service and kindness from your team.  They kindly offered us compensation due to the inconvenience caused by the temporary closure of the swimming pool, and the way everything was handled exceeded our expectations. The team immediately accommodated us and made sure we felt comfortable and well taken care of without any delay or hassle.  A very special thank you goes to Siri ❤️🥰, the manager, as well as the receptionist K and Miu 🥰who assisted us during our stay. They were both absolutely wonderful so kind, attentive, and genuinely caring. Their friendliness and willingness to help made such a difference and really elevated our entire experience.  We are used to staying in high-end hotels, but this was honestly one of the best hotel experiences we have ever had. The level of hospitality, warmth, and professionalism was exceptional from start to finish.  Thank you again for such a memorable stay. We will definitely be coming back and recommending your hotel to others without hesitation. We wish you the best Amelle"
> **- Amelle HADOUCH (5/5/5)**

> "This was one of the best ever resorts. The location is fab - right on the beach. The beach is one of the best I have been to. The resort has 5 pools and lagoons. The loungers and sea beds are aplenty. The restaurant on the pool side serves very tasty dishes perfect for the location. From the pool you can walk over to the beach and spend hours on the sand and water. The rooms are huge and very well designed. They even have amenities like table tennis, kids movies,activities to keep everyone busy I literally had tears when I left. Looking forward to going back soon"
> **- nidhi sinha (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/melia-hotel-resorts-1.jpg','077 938 899','H3CM+PJ9, 4171, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.melia.com/en/hotels/thailand/koh-samui/melia-koh-samui?utm_campaign=google&utm_content=5770&utm_medium=organic&utm_source=directories',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifsv000nq8xdrwnu123q','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.484+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.484+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/melia-hotel-resorts-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/melia-hotel-resorts-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17594174498697079847',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('merit-life-cafe-restaurant','standard','cmr07ih4700i3q8xduq25t9aq','Merit Life Cafe & Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "We just had breakfast at Mer Fresh & Full Cafe and Restaurant Samui, and it was absolutely delicious and fresh. Our sandwiches were freshly made and tasted great.  The staff provided excellent service — when we ordered one mango smoothie for our children to share, they thoughtfully split it into three without us even asking. That small gesture made our experience calmer and more enjoyable.  Highly recommended!"
> **- Daniel Toft (5/5/5)**

> "We visited MER Fresh & Full Coffee in Bophut and really enjoyed the experience. The space is large and beautifully decorated, especially at this time of year with its Christmas-inspired decor. The service was friendly and welcoming. We ordered two drinks, accompanied by an almond croissant and pancakes. The food was tasty, soft, and well presented, making it a great spot for a relaxed coffee break. Definitely worth a visit."
> **- Soraia Horta (5/5/5)**

> "We absolutely love  food and bakery! Everything is so delicious, high-quality, and made with care.The owner is so kind for us.Thank you for the inspiration and amazing taste!"
> **- Poy Rose (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/merit-life-cafe-restaurant-1.jpg','095 440 1441','175 5, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://openmapth.com/breakfast-samui-mer-fresh-full-cafe/','["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifs1000cq8xdfo2aau32','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.487+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.487+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/merit-life-cafe-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/merit-life-cafe-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7107849110573000183',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('metal-tattoo','standard','cmr07ih4900i4q8xdt4rqmxbw','Metal Tattoo','## Top Reviews
> "Amazing artists. Friendly people. Awards hard to count. Best place I''ve seen in Thailand. Worth every dollar. I''m from Canada and didn''t know where to go, but these guys are awesome. My wife who used to train Muay Thai on the island had work done here. And now I am too. So impressive. Can''t say enough. Come here if you want clean high quality and style."
> **- Devin Popowezki (5/5/5)**

> "While I am a grown woman, I have an intense needle phobia and decided to face it dead on at Metal Tattoo while my friend got a tattoo. I advised the technician, Taa, of my fear and found that I could not have been in better hands. She is an absolute Rockstar! She was understanding, patient and kind. She froze my ears before piercing so expertly that I literally did not feel anything. Had I known what I would experience in this studio, I would not have spent the few days prior freaking out about my decision! If you are looking for next level technical expertise as well as patience and kindness, Taa is the one for you. I would highly recommend her for chickens like me and, even more so, to parents looking to get their children''s ears pierced."
> **- Suzanne C (5/5/5)**

> "It is the best tattoo studio in Koh Samui! I went there with my friends. It’s clean, very good customer service. I recommend this to everyone. Zofia Harhaj"
> **- Zofia Harhaj (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/metal-tattoo-1.jpg','088 751 8330','Lamai beach, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.metaltattoosamui.com/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.489+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.489+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/metal-tattoo-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/metal-tattoo-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=86607589275485352',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mikes-tailor','standard','cmr07ih4b00i5q8xdsyn7cfrg','Mike''s Tailor','## Top Reviews
> "We had an amazing experience with Mike. He tailored these custom suits perfectly and we could not be happier with them. Mike''s customer service is top notch too. He delivered the final product to our resort + came to our resort for a 2nd fitting to confirm the sizing too. Super high quality cloth for a great price and excellent tailoring skills. Mike is amazing!"
> **- Curran Anderson (5/5/5)**

> "I had a suit tailor-made here and I’m really happy with the result. The work was professional and very clean from start to finish. The suit fits perfectly, and the quality is simply outstanding.  What stood out the most was how friendly and attentive everyone was. They took the time to make sure everything matched exactly what I wanted, and you can tell they genuinely care about their craft and their customers.  I was also pleasantly surprised by how affordable it was. The value for money is excellent considering the quality and service you receive.  I would definitely recommend them and would gladly come back again! 👌🏻"
> **- Luis Barth (5/5/5)**

> "Here’s a polished version of your review:  We recently had a suit, shirts, and blazer tailored by Mike after reading the excellent reviews, and the experience certainly did not disappoint.  From the initial consultation through to the fitting appointments and final collection, Mike and his team were professional, courteous, and attentive to every detail. Their service went above and beyond, even delivering our garments back to our hotel so we could get ready for dinner without any hassle.  The quality, craftsmanship, and customer service were outstanding. If you’re looking for a skilled tailor who takes pride in their work, I highly recommend Mike and his team. 5 stars !!!"
> **- Rebecca Towns (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mikes-tailor-1.jpg','063 395 9327','19, Fisherman village, moo1, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://mikestailorsamui.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.491+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.491+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mikes-tailor-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mikes-tailor-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13378656990221767771',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('minairal','standard','cmr07ih4d00i6q8xdbv513xe6','Minairal','## Top Reviews
> "After one week of daily use, we were genuinely impressed by this air-to-water machine. From the very beginning, the installation process was simple and intuitive. The design is sleek and modern, blending perfectly into both indoor and outdoor living spaces. The water quality is excellent—fresh, clean, and pleasant to drink, with no aftertaste. Producing potable water directly from the air is both fascinating and reassuring, especially in a context where reducing plastic waste and increasing water independence are becoming increasingly important. In just one week, our daily habits have completely changed: no more buying bottled water, no more storage issues, and no more plastic waste. It’s a solution that is environmentally responsible, highly practical, and cost-effective over time. An innovative and well-designed technology that truly delivers on its promises. We would confidently recommend this machine to anyone looking for a clean, sustainable, and modern water solution."
> **- Etienne Tallard (5/5/5)**

> "This machine quickly becomes indispensible. Tasty water... no plastic waste or microplastics... no more lugging water around. Different size machines available. Purchase or rent options and Minairal handles service and filter changes. Friendly english speaking staff Easy 🙂"
> **- Coconut Emma (5/5/5)**

> "Great machine - even more excellent people supporting it. We had to position the unit to make sure it gets enough humidity. Once we got that right the unit generates a ton of water. It physically tastes better to any bottled mineral water you buy from the store. I have 2 units - one for my home and business and highly recommend Minairal. 5 stars."
> **- Ryan Cartier (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/minairal-1.jpg','082 113 0501','151, 35 ม.1, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://shop.minairal.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.493+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.493+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/minairal-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/minairal-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17679298912110818553',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mind-your-language','standard','cmr07ih4f00i7q8xd318hdnl3','Mind Your Language','## Top Reviews
> "I attended the beginner 2 week intensive language course to try and improve what little thai I knew. It was fantastic, Pi Joms teaching methods had us speaking a lot in a very short period. He was supportive and patient while also creating an environment that made the brain work and remover phrases. I now feel confident to go out and order food, describe objects/places and hold small conversations in thai while also having the confidence to ask what someone is saying in thai with the useful phrases Pi Jom taught us. I would reccomend this course to anyone looking to learn thai and will be forever grateful to Pi Jom and his colleagues for helping me 🙏🏽"
> **- Garfield Brown (5/5/5)**

> "I had been trying to speak some basic Thai for over a year but was stuck at just a few words, despite hours spent listeniing to Comprehensible Thai and trying to learn the script. Joining the 2-week, 40-hour intensive course was the best decision I made.  It unlocked my willingness to try to speak. The course is well structured, the teacher dynamic, and attentive to our individual levels within the group. Absolutely worth it."
> **- Claude Montpetit (5/5/5)**

> "Some places stay with you long after you leave them. For us, Mind Your Language School is one of those places  What started as “just an English school” became a warm and meaningful part of our life on Koh Samui. There is something very special about this place - the calm atmosphere, the friendly energy, the bright space hidden in a small quiet street. Every time we came there, we felt welcomed  We are very grateful to Jom, Lee, and the whole staff for their support, kindness, and help with all the practical things and documents. And special thanks to our amazing teachers Ivan and Haley Ann. Their lessons were professional, engaging, and genuinely inspiring. They made learning English feel alive and enjoyable  Thank you for creating not only a school, but a place with heart. We will remember it with warmth and gratitude  Artem and Natalia ❤️❤️"
> **- Артем Б. (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mind-your-language-1.jpg','087 284 6582','142, Bophut, 7 Soi Khao Phra, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.mindyourlanguagethailand.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 2:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.495+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.495+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mind-your-language-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mind-your-language-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2578391436713248264',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mira-mare-resort','standard','cmr07ih4h00i8q8xdzspu68mz','Mira Mare Resort','## Top Reviews
> "I highly recommend it. The service is excellent, the people are friendly and helpful. The rooms are clean and comfortable, but most of the time you''re outside anyway. The food there is also great, especially the Thai food. As for the location, in my opinion it''s simply perfect. The beach is beautiful and you''re quite centrally located. Lamai Beach gets deep quickly, even after just a few meters, and you can sometimes find some nice high waves. However, the water can also be very calm quite often. If you''re looking for a good meal, there are many excellent restaurants in both directions, some less than a minute away. For activities like clubs or parties, you only have to walk 2-7 minutes. The travel agency is right next to the resort at the entrance, where you can book even better activities, such as island tours. Jet skis and other water sports are also just a 2-minute walk from the resort. If you get injured or anything happens, there''s a doctor directly across the street from the resort, and if you need to do some quick shopping, there''s also a 7-Eleven right there. And for massages there are enough places around too. Overall, I can highly recommend it and had absolutely no complaints."
> **- Nino (5/5/5)**

> "An absolutely wonderful stay! The bungalows are brand new, modern, and exceptionally spacious – you immediately feel comfortable and at home. It’s clear that great attention has been paid to quality and comfort. The entire property has an idyllic, almost paradise-like atmosphere. The direct beach access is priceless – waking up with an ocean view and being just a few steps away from the water is simply amazing. The staff is incredibly friendly, warm, and attentive, making you feel truly welcome and well taken care of. The beachfront restaurant perfectly completes the experience, serving delicious and authentic Thai food in a stunning setting. This is a place where you can completely unwind and relax. Highly recommended – we will definitely be back!"
> **- Uli Sonnenburg (5/5/5)**

> "Had a two-night stay there in bungalow A06 which was pretty close to the sea and thus it was nice to hear the crashing waves to go to bed. The hospitality was great, the owner (Mira) is a wonderful person. The room was simple but comfortable enough. The bathroom had two hand-held showers, one warm and one not but with more pressure which was good when rinsing off after a swim in the sea. The Wifi worked well, which isn''t always a given even these days. A good location in busy Lamai beach and still very quiet at night. I didn''t eat at the restaurant, but the Americano that I had was good. A great value stay on Ko Samui!"
> **- Stefen Fangmeier (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mira-mare-resort-1.jpg','077 424 262','124 16 Thanon Had Lamai, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.miramare-samui.com/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 8:30 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 8:30 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 8:30 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 8:30 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 8:30 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 8:30 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 8:30 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.497+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.497+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mira-mare-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mira-mare-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16379567159519182416',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mira-serene','standard','cmr07ih4k00i9q8xddwkikvyp','Mira Serene','## Top Reviews
> "The food quality was absolutely excellent! Every dish was flavorful, fresh, and clearly made with care. I also ordered a very simple and very healthy dish, and it tasted amazing — proof that even the most basic ingredients can shine when prepared well. We love how the restaurant is setting up with a good beach vibe . Khun charm helping as a lot with the food  every  dish  come out perfectly.. this place is  really make our night to be special. High recommend!"
> **- Bunpithak Sadsatean (5/5/5)**

> "I had one of my best meals in Thailand here, such a pleasant surprise. Lovely ambience, surroundings, live music was beautiful. Food excellent and the service was superb. Couldn’t recommend highly enough"
> **- Graham T (5/5/5)**

> "Outstanding! We held our 2 year anniversary of the Dinner Party Gang here and Mira Serene did an amazing job. Food. Service. Music and even a fire show. Thanks to your team for a great job!"
> **- Shar Moore (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mira-serene-1.jpg','081 666 4492','59 128, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifsv000nq8xdrwnu123q','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.500+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.500+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mira-serene-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mira-serene-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16282708105774651146',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('miskawaan-beachfront-villas','standard','cmr07ih4m00iaq8xd3c05587c','Miskawaan Beachfront Villas','## Top Reviews
> "It was an absolute pleasure staying at Miskawaan Beachfront Villas. From the very first moment we arrived, we felt sincerely welcomed and cared for. The villa itself was stunning — beautifully designed, impeccably maintained, and offering the perfect blend of luxury and comfort. Every room was spotless and inviting, creating a peaceful retreat where we could truly unwind.  The food was delicious and thoughtfully prepared, adding to the overall experience, while the professional spa team provided treatments that were both rejuvenating and deeply relaxing. Every detail of our stay was handled with warmth and genuine hospitality, making our visit not only relaxing but truly memorable.  Please extend our heartfelt appreciation to the entire wonderful team. We would also like to express a very special thanks to Dada and Zin — their exceptional care, kindness, and thoughtful attention to every detail truly made all the difference. Their warmth and dedication meant so much to us and elevated our stay in the most meaningful way.  We leave with the fondest memories and a deep sense of gratitude. We very much hope to return again soon.  With our warmest thanks and best regards,  Thida and Robert"
> **- robert dwyer (5/5/5)**

> "Staying in a private villa always comes with high expectations — and I can honestly say that Miskawaan Villas is a place I would recommend without hesitation.  The villa manager was exceptional, with a rare sense of timing and attentiveness. Everything was taken care of quietly and naturally, often before we even realized we needed something, while always respecting our privacy.  The private chef was another highlight. The food was consistently excellent, and I loved how open and flexible she was in creating dishes exactly the way we wished. Every meal felt personal and thoughtful.  The Lotus Villa itself is beautiful. Even though it is directly on the beach, it offers a wonderful sense of privacy. The layout is spacious yet intimate, making it easy to relax and truly settle in.  We also enjoyed several in-villa treatments and facials, which were outstanding. Having this level of wellness in the privacy of the villa added a very special dimension to the stay.  I have experienced many luxury villas around the world, and this is one I would gladly return to — and recommend to anyone looking for something truly special."
> **- Romika Fazeli (5/5/5)**

> "Our group of 16 stayed in Villa Champak and Villa Bougainvillea for a special birthday celebration, and it was exceptional. Lilly, Alice, and the amazing staff took care of every detail, making our three-night stay truly memorable. The service was outstanding, the food was incredible, and the team’s warmth made us feel completely at home. Highly recommended for anyone looking for an unforgettable villa experience.... Looking forward to our next visit"
> **- SF F (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/miskawaan-beachfront-villas-1.jpg','083 390 2992','67 28 ตำบล แม่น้ำ Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://miskawaanvillas.com/','["Monday: 8:30 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 8:30 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 8:30 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 8:30 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 8:30 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.502+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.502+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/miskawaan-beachfront-villas-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/miskawaan-beachfront-villas-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11823279257892912108',NULL,NULL);
