> **- SF F (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/miskawaan-weddings-1.jpg','083 390 2992','67 28 ตำบล แม่น้ำ Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://miskawaanvillas.com/','["Monday: 8:30 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 8:30 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 8:30 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 8:30 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 8:30 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.504+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.504+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/miskawaan-weddings-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/miskawaan-weddings-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11823279257892912108',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('miss-olive-oyl','standard','cmr07ih4q00icq8xdo06woyt0','Miss Olive Oyl','## Top Reviews
> "Nice restaurant with nice setting. The Tom Yum was tasty and very nice, came with rice. My wife had the vegetarian tacos which she enjoyed.  Value is the only gripe, especially when you can get food for much better value at the same quality.  To be expected from a busy tourist hotel."
> **- Glenn Wilkinson (4/5/5)**

> "The staff is very nice. The foods and drinks are great to try 💖✨😚"
> **- Bunyawee Kusapan (MIA) (5/5/5)**

> "The best food we’ve had while travelling Thailand. Highly recommend the beef massaman and pad thai but so far everything we’ve tried has been amazing! Lovely staff and great views over the beach"
> **- Melanie Walker (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/miss-olive-oyl-1.jpg','077 914 700','63 182 ตําบล Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.saiihotels.com/kohsamui-villas/dining/miss-olive-oyl/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 – 10:30 AM, 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 – 10:30 AM, 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 – 10:30 AM, 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 – 10:30 AM, 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 – 10:30 AM, 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 – 10:30 AM, 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifsv000nq8xdrwnu123q','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.506+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.506+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/miss-olive-oyl-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/miss-olive-oyl-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2318427151493034014',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('miss-real-estate-agent','standard','cmr07ih4t00ieq8xdi9gzu5bk','M.I.S.S. Real Estate Agent','Discover M.I.S.S. Real Estate Agent, a premier Property Services located in Na Mueang, Koh Samui. Find reviews, hours, and contact information.','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/miss-real-estate-agent-1.jpg','+66921240962',NULL,NULL,NULL,0.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ih4s00idq8xdbhwjttn6','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.509+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.509+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/miss-real-estate-agent-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/miss-real-estate-agent-2.jpg"]',NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mitan-design-fine-furnishings','standard','cmr07ih4u00ifq8xdrfvcjs6m','Mitan Design & Fine Furnishings','## Top Reviews
> "Today I discovered this wonderfull design furniture shop in Maenam, Koh Samui😍You''ll find truly stunning table vases, pillowcases, small sculptures, and beautiful indoor and outdoor furniture here. There''s also a small but exquisite menu featuring lovingly prepared dishes, coffee, and homemade pastries. I highly recommend this shop to anyone looking for something unusual outside the mainstream."
> **- Claudia K. (5/5/5)**

> "Can’t fault these people so friendly can do enough for us well recommend excellent prices too 🫥*****"
> **- Gareth Mitchell (5/5/5)**

> "Bought some stuff from Mitan Design Shop, and I loved them. The shop offers variety of furniture and unique decoration for different occasions that I cannot see from other shops on the island. Mike and Tania are very helpful!"
> **- Bautista Richellyn (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mitan-design-fine-furnishings-1.jpg','+66641031000','163 10, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.510+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.510+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mitan-design-fine-furnishings-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mitan-design-fine-furnishings-2.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mitan-design-fine-furnishings-3.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mitan-design-fine-furnishings-4.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15699813023837594163',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mk-ultra-art','standard','cmr07ih4w00igq8xdseqe0k6a','MK Ultra Art','## Top Reviews
> "We had a fantastic experience at MK Ultra Pottery doing a wheel throwing class as a family with kids ages 8–12. It was a great couple of hours learning the basics of throwing in a relaxed, welcoming environment. Morgan was an excellent instructor — patient, personable, and very encouraging with both adults and kids. She explained everything clearly, gave hands-on help when needed, and made the experience genuinely fun for everyone. Highly recommend this as a family activity or for anyone curious about trying pottery for the first time."
> **- Kraemer Lovelace (5/5/5)**

> "We had the best time being creative as a family. We enjoyed focused and gentle, easy to follow, instruction on how to throw clay on a wheel. It was perfect for beginners but they also offer advanced instruction as you improve. Check it out, Morgan and Kalvin were fantastic owners/instructors. Perfect for visitors to Koh Samui and folks that are lucky enough to live here."
> **- natalie heitman (5/5/5)**

> "What a wonderful experience! My husband and I came for a practice wheel throwing class and experienced pottery for the very first time. Morgan was just great, super professional and nice and we made 2 pieces each with her guidance. I highly recommend you to come to the studio and enjoy this amazing class."
> **- Tal Sharon (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mk-ultra-art-1.jpg','080 709 1726','16, 41, Tambon Bo Put, Boh Put, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.mkultraart.com/','["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 12:00 – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 6:00 PM","Friday: Closed","Saturday: 12:00 – 4:00 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.512+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.512+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mk-ultra-art-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mk-ultra-art-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17041788376624173113',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mollusca-japanese-oyster','standard','cmr07ih4y00ihq8xdpbxri85s','Mollusca Japanese &Oyster','## Top Reviews
> "A must have in Koh Samui.  It’s a cozy place, the service amazing, and the food is super fresh and delicious!  Had a few rolls, and the wagyu steak.  Prices were definitely reasonable.  This will be a go to for us when we are wanting Japanese!"
> **- Michael LaGuardia (5/5/5)**

> "The salmon salad comes with two really great sauces and there is quite a variety of noodles and sushi  It’s not as cost effective as K2 in the central shopping mall (they have a buffet) but I highly recommend this restraunt"
> **- Bruce Blacklaws (5/5/5)**

> "Even there’s a little bit less of choices but the restaurant served me good taste and fresh ingredients dishes. Especially oysters!!!🦪  Staffs are full of service minded and eager to please your meal genuinely. Recommend for Chawaeng’s dinner lists for group of friends or even soloists."
> **- Sucharee R. Thada (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mollusca-japanese-oyster-1.jpg','099 469 6969','60/42, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.514+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.514+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mollusca-japanese-oyster-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mollusca-japanese-oyster-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3119748323669459325',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mom-to-be','standard','cmr07ih5000iiq8xdrz0ivulg','Mom To Be','## Top Reviews
> "The price shown on social media and the price asked at the clinic after the injection is different. When I asked if the price had changed, she replied that the price changed because I didn''t tell the doctor beforehand. I have already booked the clinic from Oct16. How do I know not only to book, but also to tell the doctor in advance???  I said It''s okay and i go back home but very disappointed"
> **- Awada Kwdafra (1/5/5)**

> "I recently visited the Samui Woman and Mom Clinic for an ultrasound, and I’m so glad I took my boss’s recommendation. From start to finish, the experience was exceptional. The ultrasound cost was very reasonable, which is always a plus. The doctor was incredibly detailed, kind, and genuinely caring, making sure I felt comfortable and informed throughout the entire process. The staff was also wonderful, with pleasant personalities and excellent English, which made communication smooth and stress-free. I highly recommend this clinic to any woman or mom looking for professional and compassionate care."
> **- Kimberlye Toledo Sartorio (5/5/5)**

> "I came here for my first prenatal appointment which included an ultrasound. The doctor was lovely and although the clinic was busy, I did not feel rushed at all during the appointment. The fees are also very reasonable when compared to the hospital prices."
> **- Kaylo (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mom-to-be-1.jpg','097 473 0157','9 175 หมู่1 ตำบล แม่น้ำ Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: Closed","Wednesday: Closed","Thursday: Closed","Friday: Closed","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.516+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.516+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mom-to-be-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mom-to-be-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5387435846748986121',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('monkey-bar','standard','cmr07ih5300ijq8xdv9luwxln','Monkey Bar','## Top Reviews
> "Beachfront bar at Sheraton hotel. Fire show at 8pm, lasts 20-30 minutes. Smaller show than at bigger/busier parts of the island. The food selection is a mix of Thai and western food. Quality is fine, but not high. I’d search elsewhere for higher quality food and better atmosphere. Location is convenient if you like this beach or are staying nearby. Service was friendly and prompt."
> **- M Bean (4/5/5)**

> "Amazing location! We enjoyed delicious beach bar food, ice cold beers and happy hour cocktails. Staff were friendly and helpful. Highly recommended!"
> **- Nicola Davies (5/5/5)**

> "We absolutely love this bar. We stayed at the Sheraton for two weeks and had the best time here. The food is great and the drinks are top class but I have to say that it’s the staff who make the bar extra special. Everyone is so welcoming and friendly. We will miss our evening cocktail looking at the sea and sharing a story or two with our new found friends at the Blue Monkey. A must visit if you’re in Samui."
> **- Lydia Griffiths (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/monkey-bar-1.jpg','077 422 020','86 Moo 3 Chaweng Noi Beach, Tambon Bo Put, Koh Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.marriott.com/en-us/dining/restaurant-bar/usmss-sheraton-samui-resort/6074676-blue-monkey.mi','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.519+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.519+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/monkey-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/monkey-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13531138629748196791',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('monkey-samui-hostel','standard','cmr07ih5700ikq8xdvqe9mu5c','Monkey Samui Hostel','## Top Reviews
> "The dorm stay was okay overall. There were no basic amenities like soap or towels, and the cleanliness was average. However, the staff was super friendly and welcoming, which really made a difference. I still liked the place for its simplicity — it’s very economical, and the presence of the dog and cat made the stay even more pleasant and homely."
> **- Sagar Turkar (4/5/5)**

> "Cheapest place in Koh Samui what more can you ask for amazing host amazing dog hippo I am traveling on a budget and this place made my stay in Koh Samui !"
> **- Dhillion (5/5/5)**

> "🌟 Monkey Samui – Best Budget Stay for Solo Travelers! 🏝️  If you’re looking for the cheapest accommodation on Koh Samui, Monkey Samui is the perfect spot! This place is ideal for solo travelers who want a simple, affordable stay without unnecessary luxuries.  One of the best parts? You’re greeted by a friendly dog and cat when you arrive, which instantly makes the place feel warm and welcoming. 🐶🐱  Yes, it’s a budget hostel, so don’t expect five-star luxury—but for the price, it’s 100% worth it. You get a clean bed, chill vibes, and a chance to meet fellow travelers without breaking the bank.  Ignore the bad reviews—some people expect way too much for such a small fee. If you’re looking for a social, affordable, and laid-back stay in Koh Samui, Monkey Samui is a great choice! 🏠💙"
> **- KP (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/monkey-samui-hostel-1.jpg','02 935 3520','H38F+G4V, Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.2,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.monkeysamui.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifv2001aq8xdag7cvjgf','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.523+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.523+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/monkey-samui-hostel-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/monkey-samui-hostel-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3756714282020631722',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('moon-restaurant','standard','cmr07ih5d00ilq8xd83jkqza6','Moon Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "Food is very tastey ! & service is amazing."
> **- Jason Maldonado (5/5/5)**

> "Highly recommend this restaurant, the food was extremely high quality yet very reasonably priced, the same as many surrounding restaurants yet it felt so much more luxury. Atmosphere and environment was gorgeous with chandeliers and lovely decor. The service was excellent and staff very attentive, friendly and accommodating. We had the mussels to start which were incredible some of the nicest Iv ever had, main we had tom yum soup with prawns, chicken cashew nuts and fried rice. Food was delicious and well presented. There were many small details which really made a difference, for example complimentary breadsticks, pretty lamp, ashtray and toothpick holder on the table. A special mention to our waiter Niko who was very helpful and friendly. We came on our last night in Koh Samui which is a shame as we would have definitely come back if we had found it sooner!"
> **- Ashleigh (5/5/5)**

> "The food very tasty, nice and clean good service and fair prices first time I’m here for sure I coming back again"
> **- Avi Erev (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/moon-restaurant-1.jpg','098 484 5188','14 5 ตำบล บ่อผุด Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://moonchaweng.com/en','["Monday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.529+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.529+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/moon-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/moon-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11963155921299364528',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('moorea-boutique-resort','standard','cmr07ih5g00imq8xd4ryx5tct','Moorea Boutique Resort','## Top Reviews
> "Moorea Boutique is a lovely place to spend your time in Koh Samui. A little bit outside of main island, it’s perfect distance to get anywhere with a rented scooter.  The hotel itself is great, with a small but relaxing pool, attentive staff and a friendly owner, who is there to suggest interesting sights to see. What is more you can see that they are expanding of the campus, with new buildings being prepared to accomodate more facilities, I can only see the resort to be better with time.  The breakfast are huge and tasty, although if I were to give one small con - a bit on the pricier side. Nothing you cannot try once in a while.  All in all, great place to stay in order to cruise around Koh Samui!"
> **- Andrzej B (5/5/5)**

> "Everything about this small boutique hotel is wonderful. The grounds are gorgeous, with lights in the trees that make the whole place feel almost enchanted at night. The pool is beautiful, and the rooms are peaceful and comfortable, with good AC, cozy bedding, and excellent water pressure. Fresh towels (including beach towels) and drinking water are provided daily. The restaurant is beautifully decorated, serving a good mix of Thai and Western food, and often features live music. The service throughout the hotel is impeccable, everyone is friendly, attentive, and speaks good English. It’s also just a short walk to a quiet, pristine beach with several restaurants and massage spots nearby. The only downside is occasional power outages in this part of the island, which can mean a few hours without AC or running water since the system runs on a pump. It happened a few times during our nine-night stay, though the candle-lit restaurant makes it surprisingly romantic while you wait."
> **- Gilly & Noga Nativ (5/5/5)**

> "Wow wow wow!  We attended a wedding at this special gem, and it was one of the most special experiences I’ve had.  I highly recommend this property for private events, entertainment , and chef inspired cuisine.  The property is family owned and operated, and they’re incredibly friendly, engaging, and attractive.  The food was a big highlight.  Easy walk to the beach, massage/nail places, and cute beach bars.  Very clean, inspired decor, and attentive service.  I can’t wait to go back."
> **- Brian Melton (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/moorea-boutique-resort-1.jpg','095 310 0353','7, 7, Tambon Mae Nam, Koh Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.mooreasamui.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifso000kq8xdfe9gpaon','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.532+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.532+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/moorea-boutique-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/moorea-boutique-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11740228784328629910',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('moringa-spa','standard','cmr07ih5l00inq8xdu57hh0f2','Moringa Spa','## Top Reviews
> "I had a wonderful experience at the spa. The receptionist, Khun Yui, provided excellent service with great attention to detail and made me feel very welcome.  Additionally, Khun Praew was very friendly and attentive. She focused on the specific areas I needed and ensured I felt comfortable throughout the session.  Overall, I am very impressed with the service and would highly recommend this spa."
> **- กนกพร สินธุพาชี (5/5/5)**

> "This afternoon had the pleasure of experiencing a 90-minute aromatherapy massage at Santiburi Koh Samui, and I cannot recommend it enough! Therapists Cream and Mook were exceptional. From the moment I arrived, the serene ambiance set the perfect tone for relaxation. Yui at reception was warm and friendly welcoming us with a beautiful smile and explaining all the options available to us  Cream''s technique was incredible, expertly addressing my tension points while ensuring I felt comfortable throughout the session. Mook complemented this beautifully with a soothing touch, creating a harmonious balance that left me feeling rejuvenated. The choice of essential oils was delightful, enhancing the overall experience with calming scents that lingered pleasantly.  Both therapists were professional, attentive, and genuinely caring, making this one of the best spa experiences I''ve ever had. If you''re looking for a tranquil escape and top-notch service, definitely book with Cream and Mook at Santiburi!"
> **- Viila Sēcūra (5/5/5)**

> "I ordered elixir of love for me and my husband for his birthday! Saying good or even wonderful is nothing to tell you how it was! Really recommended to enjoy your life, your body and the man you love ❤️"
> **- Инна Якшина (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/moringa-spa-1.jpg','077 425 031','12, Maenam Beach, 12, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://santiburispa.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.537+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.537+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/moringa-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/moringa-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12822812824313179268',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('morya-pharmacy','standard','cmr07ih5n00ioq8xd2x284co1','Morya Pharmacy','## Top Reviews
> "Unfortunately, I am disappointed with the service at this pharmacy. The staff did not seem very knowledgeable about the medications and gave conflicting information. When I asked for a probiotic to take with antibiotics, I was offered a very expensive dietary supplement and told it was the only option. I also received incorrect information about the medication and possible side effects. In addition, the antibiotic was dispensed without any dosage instructions or the usual label explaining how to take it. I expected more professional advice and assistance."
> **- Karolina K (1/5/5)**

> "Friendly, professional and knowledgeable pharmacist called Jazz who gives very good advise on what to use. Highly recommended!"
> **- Chezburgr (5/5/5)**

> "Very good service best pharmacy chain on Samui with many branches"
