INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mr-chicken-taxi-van-service','standard','cmr07ih5u00iqq8xdsw3pb6og','Mr. Chicken Taxi & Van Service','## Top Reviews
> "Highly recommended. Good communication. Easy to book and deal with. We contacted Tap to take us to a few places around Koh Samui that we wanted to see. He was on time, helpful and informative. He drove us around over four hours, for a good rate, in a good air conditioned van. Thanks for a great day Tap."
> **- Cass Goldie (5/5/5)**

> "Excellent taxi company. Polite, well priced, safe and friendly respectful drivers. Highly recommend Mr Tap and his company for getting around in Koh Samui."
> **- Alexis Day (5/5/5)**

> "Mr. TAP is a top notch 👌🏽 During our stay in Samui and Koh Tao, my family used his services a several times. He is a polite man and always on time . The price is very reasonable too . I highly recommend. Thank you once again and see you when we get back to Thailand 🇹🇭 🙏🏽 Kob Kun Ka ."
