> **- Deepti Sapare (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mr-diy-1.jpg','+6621367401','No. 46, 4 Moo. 4 Maenam, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.mrdiy.co.th/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.551+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.551+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mr-diy-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mr-diy-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6072851734759243060',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mr-ocean-samui','standard','cmr07ih6200itq8xdstajj20o','Mr. Ocean Samui','## Top Reviews
> "Highly recommended! The boat was beautiful, very clean, and well maintained. The crew was honestly one of the best we’ve ever experienced. From the moment we checked in, they took such great care of us and made everyone feel comfortable and welcome. Everyone in our group said this sunset trip was one of the highlights of our entire holiday. Truly a wonderful experience."
> **- Jill Kittinuttakul (5/5/5)**

> "Living on the island for over 20 years, I can honestly say this is one of the most beautiful yet authentic boat tours there is. We had such a great experience with MR Ocean Boat Tours, the boat was clean and comfortable, the team was incredibly friendly, and everything felt well organized and relaxed. They truly took care of us and made the whole day effortless and enjoyable. Beautiful spots, great vibes, and a genuinely special experience. Highly recommend."
> **- Chilly prasertsri (5/5/5)**

> "Myself and my family took a half day boat tour last week with Mr Ocean, and it was absolutely fantastic. Our guide Ko (apologies if misspelt!) was friendly, warm and knowledgeable. He provided us with lots of information about the area, as well as taking interest in our home as well! My 5 year old daughter absolutely loved pig island, and I particularly enjoyed the snorkeling (where Ko was able to point out different fish and showed me a puffer fish which was so interesting!). Also helped in recommending food at a local interest which was great as allowed us to experience authentic thai cooking and food! A great trip for all of the family, would highly recommend to anyone looking into boat tours in the area!"
> **- Rachael Caldwell (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mr-ocean-samui-1.jpg','097 426 2391','2, 14, Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://tantulika12.wixsite.com/travel/42','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifzl002uq8xdaadxjuc2','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.554+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.554+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mr-ocean-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mr-ocean-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1647561991972561279',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mr-samui-property-management','standard','cmr07ih6400iuq8xdv0f19ylg','Mr. Samui Property Management','## Top Reviews
> "We had a really great experience with Mr. Property Siam. Jordi,Paul and Thura were amazing and took great care of us the entire time. Communication was always clear and quick — they answered every question we had and explained everything in a way that was easy to understand. They made sure Ilwe had all the information and support needed, which made the whole process feel stress-free.  The airport transfer was smooth and well organized, so arriving was easy and comfortable. Overall, everything was handled professionally but in a very friendly, personal way. We felt well looked after from start to finish. We would definitely recommend Mr. Property Siam to anyone visiting Koh Samui!"
> **- Khadija Guseynova (5/5/5)**

> "We had a fantastic stay with Zizo and his team. We were throughly looked after throughout the length of our stay.  The views were fantastic, house was clean, tidy and comfortable. We will definitely be coming back again."
> **- Tyler Mason (5/5/5)**

> "Mr Property Siam has been an excellent property management partner.  They have a great team—Jordi, Paul, Yankee, Thura, Phyo, Nye, Adam, and the rest of the staff—who are truly committed not only to taking great care of the villa, but also to treating every guest with kindness and creating lasting experiences. In a short period, they helped our property achieve Guest Favorite status through their professionalism and dedication.  Communication is always clear, proactive, and transparent, and it’s evident they are continuously investing in smarter marketing, stronger online visibility, and long-term growth for the entire portfolio.  They are dedicated to improving performance for owners while maintaining high standards for guests. Highly recommend!"
> **- i Datar (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mr-samui-property-management-1.jpg','+66890606440','115, 26, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.mrpropertysiam.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 8:30 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 7:30 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 7:30 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 7:30 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 7:30 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 7:30 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 7:30 PM"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.556+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.556+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mr-samui-property-management-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mr-samui-property-management-2.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mr-samui-property-management-3.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12325939142592060649',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mr-tappo-van-and-taxi-samui','standard','cmr07ih6500ivq8xdasi3glpf','Mr. Tappo Van And Taxi Samui','## Top Reviews
> "Highly recommended. Good communication. Easy to book and deal with. We contacted Tap to take us to a few places around Koh Samui that we wanted to see. He was on time, helpful and informative. He drove us around over four hours, for a good rate, in a good air conditioned van. Thanks for a great day Tap."
> **- Cass Goldie (5/5/5)**

> "Excellent taxi company. Polite, well priced, safe and friendly respectful drivers. Highly recommend Mr Tap and his company for getting around in Koh Samui."
> **- Alexis Day (5/5/5)**

> "Mr. TAP is a top notch 👌🏽 During our stay in Samui and Koh Tao, my family used his services a several times. He is a polite man and always on time . The price is very reasonable too . I highly recommend. Thank you once again and see you when we get back to Thailand 🇹🇭 🙏🏽 Kob Kun Ka ."
> **- Lokkie Lokkie (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mr-tappo-van-and-taxi-samui-1.jpg','083 509 6577','142, 1, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ig1n003kq8xd72v6yb3r','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.557+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.557+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mr-tappo-van-and-taxi-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mr-tappo-van-and-taxi-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12360847065267078829',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mr-tee-lawyer','standard','cmr07ih6800iwq8xdd44hemwn','Mr. Tee Lawyer','## Top Reviews
> "Great, friendly and very responsive lawyer who did a perfect job. Thank you lawyer tee 🙏"
> **- Thomas B (5/5/5)**

> "We trusted Lawyer Tee with handling the legal matters for a complicated villa purchase and were absolutely impressed and pleased with his service. From his attention to detail to outstanding communications and client care, we noted time and time again that we made the right choice in trusting him. There’s a lot that can go wrong with a real estate transaction and we always felt like he was looking out for us and ensuring good decision making and legal protection. Highly recommended."
> **- Jeff Grant (5/5/5)**

> "Lawyer Khun Tee is the best. He’s helped us out multiple times and is such a decent person. I highly regard him as not only a great lawyer but also a great friend. I would highly recommend him to anyone. Thank you."
> **- May Tan (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mr-tee-lawyer-1.jpg','090 945 2871','Taling Ngam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://countryislandlawyer.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 4:00 PM"]','cmr07ifu0000zq8xdvll5tv7z','cmr07ift8000pq8xd7yujz20i','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.560+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.560+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mr-tee-lawyer-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mr-tee-lawyer-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17964542440351475039',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mrkais-kitchen','standard','cmr07ih6a00ixq8xdjclzm68w','Mr.Kai’s Kitchen','## Top Reviews
> "I came here 2 times and everything I tried was really tasty and fresh. I would recommend it to everyone who wants to eat happily without scaring food poisoning etc. All the servers are very friendly and kind. Tasty, affordable, healthy!"
> **- Çağla (5/5/5)**

> "This was probably the best meal and service of our entire 3 weeks in Thailand. Jom was our waiter and she answered every question and was very knowledgeable and attentive. There is a great selection of dishes and all cooked fresh in front of you. The seafood was the freshest We’ve tasted and the beef in the massaman was big chunks rather than the tiny slivers normally found. We couldn’t rate this place highly enough and our only regret is that we discovered it on our last night. Otherwise we would have been back."
> **- Aidan Blunt (5/5/5)**

> "Delicious food! We are vegetarian so always look out for places with good vegetarian options and Mr Kai Kitchen certainly delivers! Pretty much all noodle and curry options on the menu have a tofu or vegetable option which amazing! I had a tofu massaman and my wife had a tofu red curry with yellow noodles and we had a tofu satay to start! The food was honestly so delicious and on top of that, presentation was excellent! The staff are also extremely lovely and attentive- highly recommend for great veggie options!"
> **- Johnny Cavanagh (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mrkais-kitchen-1.jpg','080 264 5254','17 28, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100063754172671','["Monday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.562+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.562+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mrkais-kitchen-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mrkais-kitchen-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5474461744936294437',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mrloizo','standard','cmr07ih6d00iyq8xdln02jbw7','Mr.Loizo','## Top Reviews
> "Absolutely outstanding.  After hearing great things about ZOI, we decided to give it a try for a date night, and it exceeded every expectation. From the moment we arrived, the atmosphere was elegant, welcoming, and perfectly suited for a special evening.  The food was simply incredible. Every dish was beautifully presented, full of flavor, and prepared with obvious attention to detail. It''s rare to find a restaurant where every plate that arrives at the table impresses, but ZOI managed exactly that. The quality of the ingredients, the creativity of the menu, and the execution were all exceptional.  The service was equally impressive—professional, attentive, and genuinely friendly without ever feeling intrusive. The staff made us feel welcome throughout the evening and added to the overall experience.  What impressed us even more was the value for money. The quality of the food, presentation, ingredients, and overall dining experience easily matched restaurants charging significantly more. Every dish felt carefully crafted, yet the prices remained very reasonable. It''s rare to leave a restaurant feeling that you''ve received more than what you paid for, but that''s exactly how we felt at ZOI. Thank you to the entire ZOI team for an unforgettable evening."
> **- MA LA (5/5/5)**

> "We visited this restaurant last night and had a wonderful experience. It is designed to give the feel of a Greek taverna by the sea and it delivers. Service was good. Food stole the show! Everything was delicious. Loved it! If visiting Fisherman’s Village and fancy something a little different do not hesitate."
> **- Karen Scott (5/5/5)**

> "From the moment you step through the doors, you are instantly transported to Mykonos. The atmosphere and decor are so authentic that I forgot I wasn''t actually on a Greek island.  The food was, quite literally, finger-licking good. Every dish was bursting with fresh, vibrant flavors. But what truly made the evening special was the hospitality. The chef was incredibly kind and went out of his way to chat with us, even bringing over a few extra dishes for us to sample that we hadn''t even ordered! It’s rare to find that level of personal touch!"
> **- Olga Martí García (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mrloizo-1.jpg','064 113 5419','73/1 Moo 1 Fisherman''s Village, ตำบล บ่อผุด Koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.instagram.com/zoi.samui?igsh=MW84dG4wcTd1OWZwMg==','["Monday: 2:00 – 11:30 PM","Tuesday: 2:00 – 11:30 PM","Wednesday: 2:00 – 11:30 PM","Thursday: 2:00 – 11:30 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 4:30 PM","Saturday: 7:00 – 11:30 PM","Sunday: 2:00 – 11:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.565+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.565+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mrloizo-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mrloizo-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3768142631349964262',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mrungs-safari-tours','standard','cmr07ih6g00izq8xd718eugmu','Mr.Ung’s Safari Tours','## Top Reviews
> "Very well planned outing. The drivers are safe and knowledgeable. Great lunch served. The water fight was a lot of fun."
> **- Louis C (5/5/5)**

> "Had such a fun day with Mr. Ung’s Safari Tour in Koh Samui! We visited beaches, waterfalls, elephants, Magic Park, and more. The highlight for me was the water splash play at the end of the hot day,such a perfect and fun way to cool down! The staff were also super kind and friendly. Highly recommend if you want to explore Koh Samui in one day!"
> **- Praew Issara (5/5/5)**

> "In 2023 I took my family to Koh Samui and we had an amazing time doing fun activities. We booked a day trip with Mr. Ung''s Jungle Safari and they took us to awesome temples, jungle roads, mountain views, and waterfalls! I will book with them again hopefully this year!"
> **- Ian W. (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mrungs-safari-tours-1.jpg','081 737 5427','55, 93, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.mrungtourskohsamui.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 10:30 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.568+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.568+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mrungs-safari-tours-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mrungs-safari-tours-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11567246848484989922',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mui-dim-sum','standard','cmr07ih6i00j0q8xd7nhaqc7h','Mui Dim Sum','## Top Reviews
> "A local dim sum gem! Everything tasted fresh with a great variety to choose from. The highlight for me was their Thai Tea—extremely creamy and rich, whether you have it hot or cold. It’s absolutely delicious! Quick service and a cozy vibe. Highly recommended for a morning treat!"
> **- Wariz Game (5/5/5)**

> "This place is amazing! Great food, service and more! We live nearby and eat here regularly."
> **- Ruth Brock (5/5/5)**

> "We have breakfast here twice and we like the food here. The parking was big enough we did not have any problem finding parking spot. We loved pork poridge with added salty egg, soft boiled egg, and thousand year old egg. We put them all in the bolw. My other favorites includes Chinese donut (Pro Tong Ko) and hot Thai Tea with condense milk! The only con for us were no air condition room so I need to have my towel with me to wipe my sweat. The service from the waiters were excellent! Overall, I would recommend this place for breakfast."
> **- Nick Tessalee (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mui-dim-sum-1.jpg','084 264 4289','166/1 ม.5 ต.ลิปน้อย​ อ​เกาะสมุย​ จ.สุ​ราษฏร​์​ธานี Tambon Lipa Noi, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/pg/MUI.DIMSUM','["Monday: 6:00 AM – 1:30 PM","Tuesday: 6:00 AM – 1:30 PM","Wednesday: 6:00 AM – 1:30 PM","Thursday: 6:00 AM – 1:30 PM","Friday: 6:00 AM – 1:30 PM","Saturday: 6:00 AM – 1:30 PM","Sunday: 6:00 AM – 1:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig0w003aq8xdfi0rydaw','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.570+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.570+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mui-dim-sum-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mui-dim-sum-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15455284561119463731',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('mui-mui','standard','cmr07ih6l00j1q8xdw33zd21s','Mui Mui','## Top Reviews
> "The breakfast options are quite varied ranging from rice and noodle dishes. You have the option to choose your style of eggs to customise to your preference. They also do English options like bakes beans, hash browns and sausages. The fruits are of course delicious, which include dragon fruit, water melon, papaya, pineapple etc.overall very satisfactory."
> **- Hendricks (5/5/5)**

> "We didn''t stay at the resort; we just stopped here for breakfast after reading great Google reviews. However, the place didn''t live up to the hype. The sautéed tomato was just one small cherry tomato cut in half, and the apple pancakes had no apple in them. The side of spinach was overly creamy. Three of us ordered the Ur Breakfast dish, but it was confusing to understand what was included. It mainly consisted of eggs (any style) on some bread, with the rest being optional and needing to be ordered as an add-on. The poached eggs were served cold and on the hard-boiled side. The highlight of the meal was the fresh coconut. Our total bill for five people, including some drinks, was 2,118 Baht."
> **- K.G. C-W (3/5/5)**

> "We had a little family reunion of 18 people at Culture! Siri, Pom, Daw, Tee, Fluke & Warn were so fantastic! Rooms are great, pool is wonderful. The food is okay. The hotel is located in a very central area which is great! I will say - the pool villas are beautiful but the bathroom is WIDE open! No privacy at all! Do consider when booking!"
> **- Riddhima Shamji (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mui-mui-1.jpg','077 238 828','86 Moo4 1st Floor Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.theculturesamui.com/dine','["Monday: 6:30 AM – 10:30 PM","Tuesday: 6:30 AM – 10:30 PM","Wednesday: 6:30 AM – 10:30 PM","Thursday: 6:30 AM – 10:30 PM","Friday: 6:30 AM – 10:30 PM","Saturday: 6:30 AM – 10:30 PM","Sunday: 6:30 AM – 10:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.573+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.573+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mui-mui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/mui-mui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8459257695229369602',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('munchies','standard','cmr07ih6n00j2q8xdr7gyoqvy','Munchies','## Top Reviews
> "One of the best Weed Shops in whole Samui. They got hash, edibles and everything else."
> **- Vito Frey (5/5/5)**

> "Beautiful place, super helpful and friendly employee. He helped us in our choice and we are very satisfied. 100% recommend"
> **- Serena Ferli (5/5/5)**

> "Jane was very sweet and welcoming. She introduced me to a good flavour. You get good quality for good money"
