INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('nahm-restaurant-bar','standard','cmr07ih6w00j6q8xd0akt8t0e','Nahm Restaurant & Bar','## Top Reviews
> "Restaurant with great food and a nice view.  Booking the reservation through WhatsApp went smooth. When we arrived they gave us a nice table inside but soon moved us all the way to the front with a better view over the water. We didn’t asked for it but the proposed this themselves which we found attentive.  The staff is really alert and professional, they asked if we wanted to have a photo taken, were quick with refilling the wine and took the plates away at the perfect moment.  Food was quick and more importantly; delicious. The portions are not too big so I recommend ordering more than usual."
> **- Tycho Klein Severt (5/5/5)**

> "We had a stunning meal here, was my favourite in Koh samui. Highly recommend, amazing food and the view and atmosphere is lovely! Staff very attentive and polite too. Highly recommend!"
> **- Ben Pearson (5/5/5)**

> "We went to Nahm for dinner and would highly recommend arriving before sunset so you can sit by the water and enjoy the view.  The food was excellent, and the drinks were just as good. Overall, it was a really lovely experience. I went with one of my girlfriends for a night out, and we left having a great, memorable time.  Definitely a spot I’d recommend."
> **- Erika Gudnason (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nahm-restaurant-bar-1.jpg','063 198 8778','16/9, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 1:00 – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: Closed","Wednesday: 1:00 – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 1:00 – 9:00 PM","Friday: 1:00 – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 1:00 – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 1:00 – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.584+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.584+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nahm-restaurant-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nahm-restaurant-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12058936730494811999',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('nail-story','standard','cmr07ih6y00j7q8xddygvaj6f','Nail Story','## Top Reviews
> "This was the first time that i cried after a studio visit. At the beginning they told me 1900 bath for tips and colour. I was shocked about the price, so I decided just to do french. The result is really bad. I said that I would like to have it really natural. Now I have pink nails with an asymmetric white. It took a very long time and I am so unhappy and paid 900 bath."
> **- Charly Schumacher (1/5/5)**

> "The technician “OB” can barely speak any English. I had to use google translate to communicate with her. One of my fingers on the edge of the cuticle was bleeding. I am no expert in manicures but I think some nails are not very nicely done -weird shape+a little uneven  On the positive side, the place was pretty clean."
> **- Miss Bonita Lee (3/5/5)**

> "The salon is very well maintained and everything is clean. The owner and the staff are super nice and you immediately feel welcome. The prices are a bit higher. I didn''t know the technique used to fill my acrylic nails before. I really like the result except for a few unevenness. The work was carried out very carefully. Unfortunately, the French drawing is not very straightforward. However, a simple service would definitely be recommended."
