INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('nailstudiosamui','standard','cmr07ih7100j8q8xdv789v9k9','NailStudio.samui','## Top Reviews
> "Needed an appointment for a fresh BIAB set and needed an extension on one of my nails that had snapped - was given a time for the next day which I was super happy with! Was seen by a super friendly nail tech and was given probably the best set of nails I’ve ever had! Affordable, neat and pretty😁 Would definitely recommend 💗💕"
> **- Grace Breach-Cannon (5/5/5)**

> "Woahhh so happy with my mani-pedi! For my muslim sisters, this is your go to for a russian/japanese like manicure and pedicure. My cuticles are neat and nails are super shiny! She spend 1.5 hours in total for just the cuticles, shaping and nail bed. Would highly recommed!"
> **- Meagan Simon (5/5/5)**

> "Best manicure ever – professional, fast, and flawless! A must-visit for perfect nails.  I had the best manicure I''ve ever had here! The nail technician was incredibly focused and professional, working with great attention to detail while still being quick. Everything was spotless, and the atmosphere felt welcoming and relaxing. Even though I’m just visiting the area, I wish I could come back regularly — the result is perfect! If you’re in town and looking for top-quality nails, this is the place to go."
