> "For two weeks, my husband and I visited the Nakee salon. We have tried various massages, and the service is always very polite and attentive. Our backs said "
> **- Дарья Дьякова (5/5/5)**

> "This is definitely the next massage shop on the island. 100000%. 1 year already coming here and I recommend for anyone. My favorite therapists are Risa, Vas and Noy. But I didn’t try all therapists. I really think any person working in this shop is good: girls are always presentable, nice, highly highly professional! See you soon again! You are the best"
> **- Marina Pustokhod (5/5/5)**

> "I had an absolutely exceptional experience at this massage studio in Koh Samui. From the moment I walked in, the atmosphere was calm, clean, and incredibly welcoming. The entire space is designed to help you relax instantly — soft music, pleasant scents, and a very professional setup.  A special thank you goes to Vas, my massage therapist. She is truly outstanding at what she does. You can immediately tell that she has a deep understanding of the body and knows exactly how to release tension. Her technique is both strong and precise, yet very intuitive. She adjusted the pressure perfectly throughout the session and focused exactly on the areas that needed attention.  What really stood out to me was her attention to detail and genuine care. This was not just a standard massage — it felt personalized and thoughtfully executed from start to finish.  After the session, I felt completely relaxed, re-energized, and free of tension. It was honestly one of the best massages I’ve ever had.  If you’re in Koh Samui and looking for a high-quality, professional massage, I highly recommend this place — and especially Vas. I will definitely come back!"
> **- Kevin R. (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nakee-thai-massage-spa-1.jpg','083 126 7882','17 8, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.nakee.spa/online-reservation/book-appointment-at-bo-phut-beach/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.606+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.606+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nakee-thai-massage-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nakee-thai-massage-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7856497652224734851',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('namaste-samui-indian-restaurant','standard','cmr07ih7l00jgq8xdy2uwqexf','Namaste Samui Indian Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "Place was really busy but we were lucky enough yo get a table. Staff were really friendly and efficient despite how busy it was. Ordered chicken and vegetable pakoras to start then spicy chicken curry with rice and a chilli nan. Good size portion of both pakoras and they were delicious, 4 jars of sauces already on the table to have with them. Curry and nan were also great. Food took a little time to come out but that’s ok as it’s fresh and the place was so busy. No idea why this place is not higher rated as it was so good and great value. Highly recommend."
> **- Glasgow girl (5/5/5)**

> "Excellent , flavoursome curry. We had the Kadai Paneer and Lamb Bhuna - asked for spicy and they delivered! The garlic and butter naan is nice too. One bonus was the sundries for the popadoms that were all super tasty. The only let down was that the popadoms themselves been a bit better - they don’t seem to be the freshly fried, bubbly ones. The staff are lovely 🥰"
> **- Kieran Humphries (5/5/5)**

> "This is our favorite place for dinner. We come here every evening, no matter which part of the island we’re staying in. The tandoor BBQ sets are absolutely delicious, served with a variety of sauces to suit every taste. The prices are very reasonable, and the staff are always polite, attentive, and welcoming. Highly recommended!"
> **- Nik Nikitin (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/namaste-samui-indian-restaurant-1.jpg','062 778 6490','หมู่ที่ 3, Thanon Had Lamai, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.609+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.609+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/namaste-samui-indian-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/namaste-samui-indian-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13726723553774760355',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('namwa-painting','standard','cmr07ih7o00jhq8xd2u1hz6sd','NAMWA Painting','## Top Reviews
> "Such a cute place offering arts and crafts ranging from all sorts of DIY crafts (canvas bag painting, teddy pours, bracelet making, canvases, pottery painting +) The owner is really kind and helpful in setting you up with whatever craft you choose. She also offers DIY classes like basket making on certain days. Unique if you’re looking to do something outside of beach activities and a fun place to bring your kids or have a date. For 420 baht we got 2 iced coffees and a canvas bag craft. Worth the time and perfect way to take a memorable souvenir 🌴🎨"
> **- JJ (5/5/5)**

> "Nice little artist café right by the road. It offers workshops for making dreamcatchers and for painting, DIY necklaces and rings. The owner is also very skilled in crafts and makes all kinds of products out of bananas. Lovingly decorated in a shabby-chic style. They also offer food. Affordable prices on the way to the beach."
> **- F M (4/5/5)**

> "Such a cute little shop for an afternoon of being creative. Painting cute jewellery holders, canvas bags, plant pots... they have so many items to get creative with. They also offer workshops for children & embroidery classes/ideas. The owners are so friendly & helpful. Highly recommend to anyone who wants to have a relaxing afternoon, in a lovely setting.  They also have a small Thai food menu & fruit juices/soft drinks."
> **- Lauren Fowler (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/namwa-painting-1.jpg',NULL,'44 31 ตำบล แม่น้ำ Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.612+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.612+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/namwa-painting-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/namwa-painting-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15548906710568071264',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('nana-beach','standard','cmr07ih7r00jiq8xdpl606m19','Nana Beach','## Top Reviews
> "we just wanted to lay down on a sunbed which we did then we got a smoothie for 130thb which was pretty good. the view is beautiful the sunbeds are in the shade. then after a while we went to eat lunch which was also good but quite expensive we took thai dishes since they were cheaper and water. the view is beautiful. the dogs are also super cute but i dont think they''re their dogs. Also the staff was super nice and friendly. all in all we paid 752thb"
> **- Maya Stuffer (5/5/5)**

> "This place is nice - the morning glory was really excellent, and the veggie fried rice was really nice. We also had vegan thai basil tofu which wasn''t to my taste but my partner liked it. We asked for things to be vegan."
> **- Charlotte Owen (4/5/5)**

> "Nice beach restaurant with a lovely see view and you can even catch the glimpse of sunset at evening. The staff goes above and beyond to please you. Quality Thai food but also some European menu. Very good pizza and Sangria was lovely. The Fire Show which we couldn''t book in famous for this Coco Tam’s maybe wasn''t as magnificent but was very very good. Would definitely recommend."
> **- Maryna Ryan (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nana-beach-1.jpg','095 028 1818','127 M1, ตำบล แม่น้ำ อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/nanabeachsamui','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.615+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.615+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nana-beach-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nana-beach-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11811657468525085145',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('nanny-samui','standard','cmr07ih7t00jjq8xduih187sm','Nanny Samui','## Top Reviews
> "Our 14-month-old twins found wonderful caregivers—and true friends—thanks to Rattana. Rattana and her assistants supported our family for three weeks during our stay in Ko Samui, and the experience was exceptional.  The boys genuinely loved spending time with them, which gave us complete peace of mind when leaving them in Rattana’s care. They enjoyed a wide variety of games and activities, all thoughtfully adapted to their interests and energy levels.  Rattana was consistently flexible and accommodating, readily adjusting to our changing schedule and needs. We are truly grateful to have met her and to have experienced such reliable, caring, and attentive childcare.  I highly recommend Rattana’s babysitting service to any family looking for a thoughtful, responsible, and trustworthy caregivers."
> **- Karina Collis (5/5/5)**

> "I had the service of Mam. The nanny service was for 8 days (8 hours/day) for my 11-month-old baby, and I couldn’t be happier. She was incredibly gentle, kind, and patient with my little one always positive and easygoing no matter the situation. My baby was in safe, loving hands. Highly recommend to any parent looking for a trustworthy and caring nanny! ❤️"
> **- Lienchi Lê (5/5/5)**

> "Exceptional Care from Samui Nanny Service - A Truly Heartfelt Experience  We had the most wonderful experience with Samui Nanny Service, entrusting our 1‑year‑old daughter to Nanny Mam. From the very first moment, we felt completely at ease. The entire process was smooth, professional, and incredibly kind.  Mam herself is a rare gem: warm, flexible, reliable, and deeply trustworthy. She cared for our daughter with genuine love, attention, and tenderness. It was clear every single day that she wasn’t just “doing a job” - she was giving her heart.  What touched us most was the emotional bond she built with our little girl."
> **- Friederike Rhein (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nanny-samui-1.jpg','093 962 6505','3, 88, Tambon Bo Put, Koh Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://samuinanny.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.617+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.617+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nanny-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nanny-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4237172628428763785',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('nanny-service-koh-samui','standard','cmr07ih7w00jkq8xdvzeef8wo','Nanny Service Koh Samui','Discover Nanny Service Koh Samui, a premier for kids located in Bophut, Koh Samui. Find reviews, hours, and contact information.',NULL,'087 355 7151','114, 10 MOO5, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,0.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.nannyservicekohsamui.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.620+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.620+00:00',NULL,'https://maps.google.com/?cid=3430768068143544976',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('nanus-restaurant','standard','cmr07ih7y00jlq8xd54ak30zw','Nanus Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️  We came here for dinner and I can honestly say the pizza is the best I’ve ever had. The dough was absolute perfection – beautifully crusty around the edges yet soft and fluffy inside. Every bite was full of flavour and cooked just right. Truly authentic and unforgettable – highly recommend!"
> **- Jon Kononowicz (5/5/5)**

> "Fantastic place with one of the best possible views.Food is excellent.Italian owner leads restaurant in very kind and high quality standard. We was shocked how beautiful place such as this can be hidden . We left restaurant very happy with food ,service and. Ambience. Highly recommended.  Very affordable as well 👌❤️"
> **- Honeymoon 365 (5/5/5)**

> "Best Italien Food in samui … The Spaghetti Bolognese 🍝 Are cooked for 8 hrs like in Italy …. The Pizza is outstanding… the incredients are superb…. Would love to give 6stars"
> **- bernie lengauer (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nanus-restaurant-1.jpg','099 410 0261','Lipa Noi, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://app.tableo.com/r/bs4GN-J','["Monday: 5:00 – 9:30 PM","Tuesday: 5:00 – 9:30 PM","Wednesday: 5:00 – 9:30 PM","Thursday: 5:00 – 9:30 PM","Friday: 5:00 – 9:30 PM","Saturday: 5:00 – 9:30 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.622+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.622+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nanus-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nanus-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12437879874052619430',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('napasai-the-spa','standard','cmr07ih8100jmq8xdqzsvctcj','Napasai The Spa','## Top Reviews
> "One of the best places I have visited abroad. Very nice area, completely quiet. The service offers you evertything what you want. Great breakfast (Thai & western) with direct view on the beach, fresh and organic ingredients. Very nice pool and beach area. People from the hotel very friendly and helpful. Bikes to rent for free to go to a massage or pickup some food in area nearby."
> **- christoph ewerth (5/5/5)**

> "Our family’s annual spring getaway!! How does one describe paradise—true, effortless perfection? The truth is, you don’t. You simply find yourself returning, year after year, drawn back by a place that feels more like a private world than a destination.  Our deepest gratitude to dear Alla and the extraordinary team at Napasai, whose warmth and intuitive hospitality elevate every moment into something truly special. Every detail is executed with quiet precision—from the pristine, secluded residences to the flawless in-villa dining, and the ever-attentive team who anticipate your every need before you even realise it.  What began as a week-long birthday escape effortlessly unfolded into ten blissful days—and still, it wasn’t enough. Time moves differently here.  The oceanfront residences are in a league of their own—especially the five-bedroom villas. Expansive yet intimate, they offer complete privacy, stunning infinity pools that melt into the horizon, elegant lounging spaces, and an atmosphere of serene exclusivity at the far end of the resort. It feels less like a stay, and more like having your own slice of paradise.  Quite simply, this is not just a destination—it’s a tradition, a feeling, and our family’s most cherished escape.!! Can’t wait to be back next spring 🤗"
> **- Chinka .Dhir (5/5/5)**

> "Paradise, and hospitality with heart  Our stay at Napasai Samui was nothing short of exceptional.  Before our arrival, we were confronted with a sudden and distressing medical emergency involving close friends in Bangkok. We reached out to the hotel to explore whether any flexibility might be possible with our dates.  Initially, the situation was complex due to third-party booking policies and availability constraints. However, what truly sets Napasai apart is what happened next.  The team, particularly Khun Ohm, reconsidered our request, reviewed availability again, and came back with a thoughtful, humane solution. They offered flexibility without penalties and even provided a complimentary upgrade for the first two nights. It was handled swiftly, elegantly, and with genuine empathy.  In a moment of emotional stress, that kind of response matters enormously.  And then we arrived. Paradise on earth.  The setting is breathtaking: a peaceful private beach lined with palms, calm waters, space, privacy, and an atmosphere of understated luxury. No mass tourism feeling. No noise. Just serenity.  Travelling with our 7-month-old son, we were welcomed warmly and allowed to use the facilities upon early arrival. The staff were consistently kind, attentive and sincere. Never forced, always authentic.  Service throughout the stay was impeccable. The villas are beautiful and spacious. The food was excellent. The overall feeling was one of calm, privacy and genuine Thai hospitality.  We understand the resort will close for extensive renovations in April/May 2026. We sincerely hope that whatever changes are made, the soul of Napasai — its tranquillity, elegance and human warmth — remains untouched.  We wholeheartedly recommend anyone considering Koh Samui to book Napasai. It is rare to find a place that combines physical beauty with emotional intelligence in service.  We will absolutely return."
> **- M.I. ten Bosch (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/napasai-the-spa-1.jpg','077 429 200','65 10 Maenam Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://napasaisamui.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifso000kq8xdfe9gpaon','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.625+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.625+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/napasai-the-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/napasai-the-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16149481287430848524',NULL,NULL);
