> **- Lauren Fowler (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nartanas-paint-classes-1.jpg',NULL,'44 31 ตำบล แม่น้ำ Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.630+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.630+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nartanas-paint-classes-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nartanas-paint-classes-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15548906710568071264',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('naruemon-pearl','standard','cmr07ih8800jpq8xdj7tc3u3r','Naruemon Pearl','## Top Reviews
> "Beautiful and affordable jewelry. I bought a necklace and earrings but came back later for more:)"
> **- Patrycja Renes (5/5/5)**

> "Best place in Samui if you are knowledgeable about pearls. The owner creates beautiful pearl jewelry. Her family has been running this store for 20+ years.  I have bought many times here. They are all beautiful!"
> **- Ming M. (5/5/5)**

> "We went to the store today.  We made a great discovery, a well-maintained shop with a choice of jewelry and above all a very pleasant person who does not push you to buy who shows you all the products and very professional, we bought a necklace and a ring which took very  reasonable plus a small gift offered by the very kind lady.  I highly recommend the store"
> **- seboos (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/naruemon-pearl-1.jpg','093 429 9449','126/16 ถ. ทวีราษฎร์ภักดี Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://m.facebook.com/naruemonpearlsamui/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 8:30 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 8:30 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 8:30 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 8:30 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 8:30 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 8:30 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 8:30 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.632+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.632+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/naruemon-pearl-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/naruemon-pearl-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=128373677546099137',NULL,NULL);
