> ""
> **- MANU C (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nataya-villa-development-1.jpg','+66986860245','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ig5c0051q8xdykrbexft','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.634+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.634+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nataya-villa-development-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nataya-villa-development-2.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nataya-villa-development-3.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nataya-villa-development-4.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=65688888204127595',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('nature-jewelry','standard','cmr07ih8d00jrq8xdwlfgl26a','Nature Jewelry','## Top Reviews
> "All their pieces are gorgeous, wish i could buy them all! Staff at the fisherman’s village shop were really helpful and knowledgeable. We bought a few bits of jewellery all real silver and some containing precious stones. Would highly recommend as we have been looking for good jewellery on our travels across thailand."
> **- Zahra Fontenelle (5/5/5)**

> "I am surprised this shop has only 4 stars. This place is a PARADISE for all ladies who love natural stone silver jewellery. I love it especially since I wear silver, not gold and they have plenty of beautiful 925 silver items ♥️ the “Nature” in the shop name is ideal, designs are allowing you to feel like a nature fairy :) I spent over 1 hour there, trying countless pieces and bought 1 pair of earrings. Staff was very friendly, no one seemed to be bothered with my endless “tryons”, although I was very careful putting it back into place :) the prices are quite high for Thailand but still around ~60% of the price one would pay for similar items in Europe. I’d only invest in the silver cleaning machine, cause some items are darkened and it’s hard to see their beauty because of it :) but still - Highly recommend!"
> **- Olga Chr (5/5/5)**

> "Adore this store. Affordable good quality pieces"
> **- Michelle (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nature-jewelry-1.jpg','077 422 594','200, 9 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.2,0,0,0,NULL,'http://thailand-jewelry.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.637+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.637+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nature-jewelry-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nature-jewelry-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1796334867448804136',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('net-tours-asia','standard','cmr07ih8g00jsq8xdvivq2dby','Net Tours Asia','## Top Reviews
> "Amazing tour “3 in 1 Bamboo rafting”☺️ My friend recommended this tour for me and it was really good. We spent time with family. Tour was pretty intense and balanced. Turtles, bamboo rafting was amazing - incredible views. Temple was full of crazy monkeys (please don’t feed them), temple in the cave was cool. My family was happy to see elephants and ride on atv - and that’s all in one day! Phang Gha province is different from Phuket. Want to visit it again one day :)  I didn’t have a PayPal account and paid by cash (you should ask about it in WhatsApp)"
> **- Марита Атакова (5/5/5)**

> "We decided to buy half day tour to know what the boat tour is in general. I looked through local offices and compared prices on the web. Net tours Asia offered the best price. However I was a bit hesitating because their office places on the opposite part of Thailand and I had to communicate with agents via WhatsApp only. Next day we had a free transfer to to the bay where the tour starts where the workers offered us a light breakfast: tea/coffee, toasts with jam and sweets. It is possible to buy necessary equipment there but it is expected more expensive then buying same goods in markets or marketplaces. After half an hour the group was ready to start. The speed boat seemed to be in a good condition and we offered cold water during the tour. The snorkeling places were good but the islands were brilliant! Wonderful views, clean beaches, bright fishes, white sand and transparent water 😍 I didn''t regret a second about spending money, it is totally cost every baht! Probably the best way to spend money in Thailand for new emotions is to go to a boat trip to islands. I highly recommend you to try The bad side is that  I felt symptomes of heatstroke next day however I live in Thailand a few months, I was in a cap all tour long except diving part and I had never felt it before. But this is my fault😊 So pick something to cover your head, neck and shoulders, don''t repeat my mistakes 😉 After that we had a free transfer to our place As a summary: -the prices here are reasonable -Pick what is written on net tour website -add a hat and a t-shirt or something to cover neck and shoulders even for half day tour -you also can pick an individual tube for snorkeling -enjoy your time😁"
> **- Konstantin (5/5/5)**

> "Good Staff very kindness give all informations with honestly , good service and good price also"
> **- Polypoly Thelittlebear (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/net-tours-asia-1.jpg','064 162 4212','8, 15 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.nettoursasia.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.640+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.640+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/net-tours-asia-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/net-tours-asia-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2355773754888388662',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('new-body-and-mind','standard','cmr07ih8l00jtq8xdsxvpwyib','New Body And Mind','## Top Reviews
> "I finished a 14‑day cleansing at New Body and Mind (Feb 2026) in Koh Samui, and it was a truly wonderful experience. From the moment I arrived, the staff made me feel genuinely cared for. Everyone was kind, attentive, and incredibly supportive throughout the entire process. During the fast, everything was thoughtfully prepared for us—fresh juices, mineral drinks, and broth—and the daily schedules were clearly laid out so we always knew what to expect. The staff was very attentive and accommodating, and you could really feel that customer care is a top priority here. One staff, member, Anchalee, even went above and beyond by helping me change a flight, which I truly appreciated. I came primarily for the fasting experience, but I ended up losing 20 lbs as well, which was a pleasant bonus (though not my main goal). Beyond the fasting, I really enjoyed the yoga sessions, morning walks, and massages—they added so much balance and calm to the experience. While I was there, I spoke with someone who had attended a different retreat in the same area and didn’t feel well taken care of. That conversation made me even more grateful for the level of attention and care at New Body and Mind. The director clearly emphasizes excellent customer service, and it shows in every interaction with the staff. Overall, this was a very pleasant, well-organized, and supportive retreat. I would absolutely return and would love to bring friends here one day to help them experience it as well. Highly recommend."
> **- C F (5/5/5)**

> "I recently completed the New Body & Mind 10-day detox program, and it has been a truly refreshing experience.  Before starting, I was feeling heavy, low on energy, and mentally tired. After completing the program, I feel much lighter, more active, and mentally clear. My energy levels have improved, and the overall heaviness in my body is gone.  What makes this experience even better is the professionalism of the team. The staff is highly disciplined, very supportive, and always attentive. The place is neat, clean, and maintains excellent hygiene standards, which makes you feel comfortable and confident throughout the program.  This is not just a detox — it’s a complete reset for both body and mind. Highly recommended for anyone looking to improve their health, energy, and overall well-being."
> **- Shams Bawany (5/5/5)**

> "★★★★★  I try to visit Body & Mind at least once a year, and it’s always an incredible experience. It’s the perfect place to detox, rejuvenate, and truly reset both body and mind.  The exercise sessions with Dah are fantastic and very motivating. The staff are extremely warm, friendly, and always helpful. The food and fresh juices are excellent—healthy and delicious.  What I love most is the beautiful location and the amazing effect the program has on my body. I always leave feeling lighter, healthier, and completely refreshed. Highly recommended!"
> **- Nandita Palshetkar (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/new-body-and-mind-1.jpg','077 423 189','41 1 Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://newbodyandmind.com/','["Monday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.645+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.645+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/new-body-and-mind-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/new-body-and-mind-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2596744068046438186',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('new-leaf-detox-resort','standard','cmr07ih8o00juq8xdyc5vz8iu','New Leaf Detox Resort','## Top Reviews
> "My husband and I spent 10 days at New Leaf in January and we again left impressed by the program and the New Leaf Wellness team members. The staff are excellent and always go above and beyond to ensure our stay is as enjoyable as possible. This program is a wonderful  ‘reset’ and an excellent way to start a new year! Thank you New Leaf💞"
> **- sophia (5/5/5)**

> "Just had the most wonderful 14 days at New Leaf. The staff are wonderful and absolutely there to assist on my journey. I needed a life reset and I feel it has happened and along the way met lovely people from all over the world. Quite a special place plus lost weight feel lighter more clarity and joyous. What fun! Thank you New Leaf and I hope to be back."
> **- Sally Margan (5/5/5)**

> "A Life-Changing Experience – More Than Just a Detox  This was my first ever detox program, and I can honestly say it was a transformative experience—one that healed not only my body, but also my soul.  I joined  program for 10 days, not fully knowing what to expect. By the end of it, I had not only lost significant weight and centimeters from my waist, but I had also gained something far more important: a sense of renewed energy, clarity, and inner peace. My fitness improved, my mental health took a noticeable turn for the better, and I left feeling like a stronger, more balanced version of myself.  Everything—from the care of the staff to the structure of the program—was thoughtfully designed to support real, lasting change. This wasn''t just a break from routine; it was a reset on every level.  If you''re looking for more than just relaxation, and you''re truly ready to reconnect with yourself, I cannot recommend this experience highly enough"
> **- Olga Sameliuk (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/new-leaf-detox-resort-1.jpg','077 955 156','Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.2,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.newleafwellness.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.648+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.648+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/new-leaf-detox-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/new-leaf-detox-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10968163780692019627',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('new-star-beach-resort','standard','cmr07ih8q00jvq8xdqt13fvz6','New Star Beach Resort','## Top Reviews
> "A hidden gem!  Would recommend for sure. The room was spacious with very high celling. And there was quite a creative bathroom with open shower.  The area is quiet, there weren''t many guests when we stayed. There are a lot of greens, from lobby to beach bar goes a stream. The hotel has a good access to the beach.  As always I am pleasantly surprised with amazing staff, they know what they do and they do it well."
> **- Мария Бурнашова (5/5/5)**

> "if you want peace and rest just in the beach,this place is perfect for it! they have wonderful people working in the hotel,thank you all for such a hospitality! definitely worth to book place including breakfast,it was one of the best breakfast in all island so far. hotel located in peaceful area,far away from crowds,not so much things to do around,but 7/11 and pharmacy is just across the street.In general this hotel is  for couples and families,no party vibe,so just take your book and enjoy your holiday! looking forward to come back !p.s. i stayed in ocean view villa,highly recommended!"
> **- Gabija Mostvilaitė (5/5/5)**

> "The Room I have has high ceiling and large bathroom with extra outdoor shower.  The price was about US$350 per night.  Very big infinity pool by the beach front.  Breakfast restaurant is not very big and has few patio tables.  The food doesn''t match up to the price I paid for the stay.  The USM airport lounge has much better food than here.  Services also need to be improved as their staffs were not well trained in the hospitality industry."
> **- Benny Kwong (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/new-star-beach-resort-1.jpg','077 414 500','83 Moo 3, ตำบล บ่อผุด Koh Samui, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.newstarresort.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ig5c0051q8xdykrbexft','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.650+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.650+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/new-star-beach-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/new-star-beach-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17116287316201449039',NULL,NULL);
