> **- Benny Kwong (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/new-star-weddings-1.jpg','077 414 500','83 Moo 3, ตำบล บ่อผุด Koh Samui, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.newstarresort.com/',NULL,'cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ig5c0051q8xdykrbexft','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.653+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.653+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/new-star-weddings-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/new-star-weddings-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17116287316201449039',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('nh-collection-peace-resort','standard','cmr07ih8w00jxq8xdbcouzgsi','NH Collection Peace Resort','## Top Reviews
> "This is our second time at Peace. Came about 3 years ago before the up graded deck and it being bought out by NH Collection  I was a little bit  worried it would have lost a bit of its laid back atmosphere.  I shouldn''t have. The up grades have been the cherry on top. Some of the staff from last visit are still here. Shout out to Patrick who remembered us! The staff are the key to Peace. They are so genuinely friendly and go out of there way to make your stay as perfect as possible . Patrick, Arr ,Rainbow and Creamy are the stoundouts so far after our first 2 days. I''m sure I will have add more names to this review.  Breakfast is amazing and its enough to keep us going till a light snack at lunch. The chefs do fantastic dinner specials as well . Being right on the beach at BhoPhat makes it nice and quite. Lots of couples and families here but if you want some night-life Chawang is only 20.min  away. Fishermans village is a 5 min walk down the beach and it has plenty of restaurants and bars . The markets on Monday, Wednesday and Friday nights are the best on the island."
> **- Matthew Spence (5/5/5)**

> "really is a peace resort. it’s wonderful, the staff is lovely, you feel like you’re in paradise. we stayed in a superior villa for 4 nights, and was truly amazing. the beach is quite, there are a lot of sun beds, the breakfast is excellent, and the view is breathtaking. the hotel area is beautiful, very green, like a movie. one more thing to highlight is their spa. we went several times and Kong, one of the massage specialists is the best specialist I’ve ever met. we’ve been several massage places all over Thailand, and this place, especially Kong was the best one. this hotel is highly recommended if you would like to experience something special."
> **- Dora Papp-Biro (5/5/5)**

> "We had a wonderful stay at NH Collection Samui Peace Resort.  The hotel is beautifully maintained, peaceful, and perfectly located. The swimming pool area is especially pleasant and relaxing, creating a lovely atmosphere throughout the day.  The food was excellent, the cuisine at the restaurant was delicious, refined, and consistently well presented. We truly enjoyed every meal. The breakfast buffet is generous and of a great quality.  The service was impeccable from start to finish: warm, attentive, and highly professional.  We highly recommend this hotel and would gladly return."
> **- Gerondeau Fabienne (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nh-collection-peace-resort-1.jpg','077 425 357','178, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://world.nh-hotels.com/en/nh-collection-samui-peace?utm_source=GoogleMyBusiness&utm_medium=GMB&utm_term=PeaceSamui&utm_content=Home&utm_campaign=Google_GMB',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.656+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.656+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nh-collection-peace-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nh-collection-peace-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5311285538712838144',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('nh-collection-sea-wrap','standard','cmr07ih8y00jyq8xdr81zhli5','NH Collection Sea Wrap','## Top Reviews
> "This is our second time at Peace. Came about 3 years ago before the up graded deck and it being bought out by NH Collection  I was a little bit  worried it would have lost a bit of its laid back atmosphere.  I shouldn''t have. The up grades have been the cherry on top. Some of the staff from last visit are still here. Shout out to Patrick who remembered us! The staff are the key to Peace. They are so genuinely friendly and go out of there way to make your stay as perfect as possible . Patrick, Arr ,Rainbow and Creamy are the stoundouts so far after our first 2 days. I''m sure I will have add more names to this review.  Breakfast is amazing and its enough to keep us going till a light snack at lunch. The chefs do fantastic dinner specials as well . Being right on the beach at BhoPhat makes it nice and quite. Lots of couples and families here but if you want some night-life Chawang is only 20.min  away. Fishermans village is a 5 min walk down the beach and it has plenty of restaurants and bars . The markets on Monday, Wednesday and Friday nights are the best on the island."
> **- Matthew Spence (5/5/5)**

> "really is a peace resort. it’s wonderful, the staff is lovely, you feel like you’re in paradise. we stayed in a superior villa for 4 nights, and was truly amazing. the beach is quite, there are a lot of sun beds, the breakfast is excellent, and the view is breathtaking. the hotel area is beautiful, very green, like a movie. one more thing to highlight is their spa. we went several times and Kong, one of the massage specialists is the best specialist I’ve ever met. we’ve been several massage places all over Thailand, and this place, especially Kong was the best one. this hotel is highly recommended if you would like to experience something special."
> **- Dora Papp-Biro (5/5/5)**

> "We had a wonderful stay at NH Collection Samui Peace Resort.  The hotel is beautifully maintained, peaceful, and perfectly located. The swimming pool area is especially pleasant and relaxing, creating a lovely atmosphere throughout the day.  The food was excellent, the cuisine at the restaurant was delicious, refined, and consistently well presented. We truly enjoyed every meal. The breakfast buffet is generous and of a great quality.  The service was impeccable from start to finish: warm, attentive, and highly professional.  We highly recommend this hotel and would gladly return."
> **- Gerondeau Fabienne (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nh-collection-sea-wrap-1.jpg','077 425 357','178, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://world.nh-hotels.com/en/nh-collection-samui-peace?utm_source=GoogleMyBusiness&utm_medium=GMB&utm_term=PeaceSamui&utm_content=Home&utm_campaign=Google_GMB',NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.658+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.658+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nh-collection-sea-wrap-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nh-collection-sea-wrap-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5311285538712838144',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('nicolazi-design','standard','cmr07ih8z00jzq8xdswqm6l0n','Nicolazi Design','## Top Reviews
> "Nicolazi design is wonderful, I’ve used the products I bought for two months pre writing this review. The design is stylish and more importantly the usage is comfortable, sturdy and feels genuinely quality (function before form!). As for the customer service, it’s up level, from the storeroom visit to delivery to installation, my hand was held, clockwork service.  I’m also the fool who found a loose bolt on the floor and assumed it was from one of my Nicolazi sun loungers, Nicolazi sent a technician the next day, and then I learned the bolt was unrelated, kudos to Nicolazi Design having excellent after purchase care."
> **- Kirtes Bharti (5/5/5)**

> "Nicolazi Design Samui is the best outdoor furniture store on Koh Samui. The store staff is very nice and very helpful, but the most important thing is that the furniture they sell is beautifully designed and of very high quality. I bought two sunbeds which I am incredibly happy with, they are simply fantastic. So I recommend this store because it is certainly the best store on the island and one of the best in Thailand. Thank you for your help and making my purchase a pleasure."
> **- Maciej Brzezicki (5/5/5)**

> "Exclusive furniture, definitely worth the price! Great customer service."
> **- Sir Peedeeseen (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nicolazi-design-1.jpg','+66652721262','123, 189, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.nicolazi-design.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.659+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.659+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nicolazi-design-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nicolazi-design-2.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nicolazi-design-3.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nicolazi-design-4.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3257393690729435972',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('nikki-beach-beach-club','standard','cmr07ih9200k0q8xdyoqkxfrl','Nikki Beach Beach Club','## Top Reviews
> "Nikki Beach Koh Samui is a beautiful place to spend the day. We were there visiting friends and had a fantastic time. For us, it’s one of the nicest Nikki Beach locations.  The setting is stunning, the atmosphere relaxed yet stylish, and the service attentive. Great music, good food, and a perfect beach club vibe right by the ocean.  A wonderful spot to enjoy a sunny day with friends. Highly recommended."
> **- Oliver Kremers (5/5/5)**

> "We had an absolutely sensational stay! From the moment we arrived, everything was seamless and welcoming. The food was outstanding — every meal felt like a highlight — and the service was consistently attentive without ever being over the top.  The rooms were immaculate, beautifully presented, and clearly very well maintained. It made such a difference coming back each day to a space that felt fresh, clean, and comfortable. Honestly, we couldn’t fault a single thing throughout our stay.  A special shoutout to Nan and Care at the front — both were incredibly friendly, helpful, and always made us feel looked after. And a big thank you to our driver Noom as well, who was professional, reliable, and just an all-around great person to deal with. It’s staff like this that really elevate the whole experience.  The atmosphere across the resort was spot on — relaxed but still premium, with a great vibe whether you were unwinding or enjoying the beach club. Everything just felt easy, which is exactly what you want on a getaway.  This was our first time staying at a Nikki Beach, and it completely exceeded expectations. Safe to say it won’t be our last — already looking forward to coming back!"
> **- James Bimbilovski (5/5/5)**

> "i’ve had the best experience at this hotel, it’s been one of the best trips/stays of my life. everything made this trip perfect, i had the breakfast package and it was amazing!  One of the waitresses Fai Beer, was so lovely, she was very kind and helpful every morning and has such a lovely energy and smile! such an amazing member of staff. all the workers at the hotel are very helpful and kind and greet you everytime they see you. if you’re considering whether to come, definitely do so! thank you so much nikki beach it’s been amazing!!! only drawback was the location as it’s in a very quiet side of the island, if this is what you’re looking for then it’s perfect, but we’ve had to spend a lot of money on grabs whilst here."
> **- Zoe O''Sullivan (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nikki-beach-beach-club-1.jpg','077 914 500','96, 3, Tambon Lipa Noi, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://nikkibeach.com/koh-samui/?utm_source=Google+Business+Profile',NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.662+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.662+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nikki-beach-beach-club-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nikki-beach-beach-club-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9465511644152669761',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('nikki-beach-resort','standard','cmr07ih9500k1q8xdk3dpqud0','Nikki Beach Resort','## Top Reviews
