> **- Zoe O''Sullivan (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nikki-beach-resort-1.jpg','077 914 500','96, 3, Tambon Lipa Noi, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://nikkibeach.com/koh-samui/?utm_source=Google+Business+Profile',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.665+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.665+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nikki-beach-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nikki-beach-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9465511644152669761',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ninja-water-park','standard','cmr07ih9700k2q8xdc1zpwjex','Ninja Water Park','## Top Reviews
> "It was one of my children''s favorite resorts and places in Koh Samui, my children really enjoyed the many attractions they have to offer. The staff is very attentive and professional, so I felt safe when my children enjoyed the attractions at sea. The restaurant and the rooms are clean :) And I got to know the owner when I was there and he is a charming man who is always ready and wants to help. I recommend and will definitely go back there again in the future with my kids"
> **- dekel dahari (5/5/5)**

> "The Ninja Water Park on Bangrak beach is a thrilling aquatic playground for all ages. With its vibrant colors and various inflatable obstacles, it offers endless fun and excitement. Children can splash and climb freely, while adults can join in the adventure or relax on nearby loungers. The park''s convenient location on the beach allows for stunning ocean views and easy access to amenities. Safety measures are well in place, ensuring a worry-free experience for families. Whether diving off the slides, navigating through obstacles, or simply basking in the sun, this water park promises a memorable and enjoyable day for everyone."
> **- Adi Nagar (5/5/5)**

> "We were here as my daughter requested to play with the inflatable park. Actually, I was first worried as there were quite a lot of negative reviews, but it was OK. My daughter was very happy and enjoyed the park very much. Staff were always monitoring the park to ensure safety. I will recommend to wear sandals or some kind of footwear as there might be a possibility of having stones or shells on the ocean floor. Also don''t recommend jumping and diving from a high position as the water is very shallow. We also had lunch here and it was very good! Not only Thai food but there were wide range of food. My daughter enjoyed fish and chips which was one of the kids menu. Enjoyed that last half day in Samui before heading back to Nathon pier. Looks like we cannot catch GRAB from this place, thus we used taxi."
> **- 中山雄介 (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ninja-water-park-1.jpg','081 978 9085','30/5 Moo 4 baphout Bangrak Reach Road, อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://samuipier.com/','["Monday: 10:30 AM – 6:30 PM","Tuesday: 10:30 AM – 6:30 PM","Wednesday: 10:30 AM – 6:30 PM","Thursday: 10:30 AM – 6:30 PM","Friday: 10:30 AM – 6:30 PM","Saturday: 10:30 AM – 6:30 PM","Sunday: 10:30 AM – 6:30 PM"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.667+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.667+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ninja-water-park-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ninja-water-park-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14040911582667506756',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('niramai-spa','standard','cmr07ih9b00k3q8xd9frpmltk','Niramai Spa','## Top Reviews
> "Relaxing massages, especially with the aromatic oils."
> **- Nacho CK (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing massages, wonderful stuff ! Recommended!!"
> **- Noam (5/5/5)**

> "Incredibly delicious spa & massage clinic. It is worth all the money, as it is a very relaxing and extremely professional experience, while having the sweetest staff. I got a massage from Jeab, and I can definitely recommend her, as she was really skilled and very attentive"
> **- Caroline Abrahamsen (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/niramai-spa-1.jpg','091 035 1987','26/1-3, ตำบล มะเร็ต อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.thaifighthotel.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.671+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.671+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/niramai-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/niramai-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10655331727939837578',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('nm-motorbike','standard','cmr07ih9d00k4q8xdblfjpshs','N&M Motorbike','## Top Reviews
> "Very nice and helpful people, easy to communicate with. We took two Yamaha NMax bikes - the bikes are in excellent technical and visual condition. 10/10 🙏"
> **- Jakub Kot (5/5/5)**

> "Excellent experience from start to finish. The motorbike was in perfect condition, clean and very reliable throughout our trip. Communication was easy, the pick-up and return process was smooth, and the staff were friendly and helpful. Everything went exactly as agreed. Highly recommended, and I would definitely rent from them again when visiting the island. Thank you!"
> **- Alvaro Miguel Rosa Salces (5/5/5)**

> "I rented nmax for 6 days. The condition was perfect. Everything was smooth. They even came and took back the bike from where i was living while i was checking out. They are so helpful and nice people. Thank you for your valuable service. I recommend n&m motorbike to everybody. Thank you guys"
> **- Alpay Burak (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nm-motorbike-1.jpg','099 406 1612','102 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://nm-samuimotorbikerental.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ifui0012q8xdzn158clv','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.673+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.673+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nm-motorbike-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nm-motorbike-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3754722836929473378',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('no-stress-lamai','standard','cmr07ih9f00k5q8xdy9u8oxnq','No Stress Lamai','## Top Reviews
> "I honestly can’t recommend NO STRESS enough — this place completely lives up to its name 🌴✨  From the moment we arrived, the owner (such a genuinely kind and welcoming lady!) made us feel right at home. The whole team is incredibly friendly and attentive, which just adds to the relaxed, happy vibe of the place.  The food is delicious — fresh, flavorful, and exactly what you want when you’re by the beach. And don’t even get me started on the coconut… SO good 🥥💛  What really makes this place special are all the little extras: free WiFi, free sunbeds, and even free stand-up paddle boards, which made the whole experience feel extra fun and carefree.  The beach itself is stunning — soft white sand, crystal-clear water, and a beautiful view that makes you want to stay all day (which we basically did 😌).  If you’re looking for a place to relax, eat well, and just enjoy life by the sea… No Stress is absolutely it. Can’t wait to come back!"
> **- Anna Kálmán (5/5/5)**

> "I wouldn''t recommend the Tom Yum. It was too clear and sour, and I didn''t enjoy the flavor at all. It’s the worst version of this soup I''ve tried. We also tried the Pad Thai, which was nothing special, and the coconut drink was disappointing as well. Interestingly, all dishes were a flat price of 180 baht, which is quite unusual for this type of food."
> **- Anislav Atanasov (3/5/5)**

> "The place lives up to its name. The staff is very friendly and attentive, making you feel welcome right away. The food is delicious, and there’s a great selection of drinks. One of the best perks is that you can use the sunbeds for free as long as you order something. All of this is set on a beautiful beach, which makes the experience even better. We would definitely come back!"
> **- K (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/no-stress-lamai-1.jpg','084 119 0182','Maret, LAMAI, Surat Thani 84000, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://fr-fr.facebook.com/no.stress.restaurant.koh.samui/','["Monday: 8:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 8:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 8:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 8:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 8:30 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.675+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.675+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/no-stress-lamai-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/no-stress-lamai-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8549656011934748786',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('nomad-brunch-and-brew','standard','cmr07ih9j00k6q8xd1wzlrunl','Nomad Brunch And Brew','## Top Reviews
> "We had an amazing brunch here, everything was honestly top-tier. The place itself is beautiful: very clean, minimal, and tropical, with a super relaxing atmosphere. Sitting outside surrounded by greenery made it even better — calm, sunny, and perfect for a slow brunch.  The food was excellent. The eggs were perfectly cooked, creamy and full of flavor, served on great quality bread with fresh ingredients. The balance between the richness of the dish and the fresh salad on the side was spot on. You can really tell that attention is paid to both taste and presentation.  Drinks were also great, especially the iced coffee — refreshing, well-balanced, and ideal for a warm day. Everything came out well presented and appetizing.  Service was friendly and smooth, not rushed, which really adds to the experience. Overall, it was a very enjoyable brunch, great food, great vibe, and a place I’d definitely come back to and recommend without hesitation."
> **- Mister Benz (5/5/5)**

> "A hidden gem. The coffee was delicious and I loved that I got to choose which beans I could have for my espresso.  Naturally I went for the dark roast and that was divine. Full of rich chocolate and hazelnuts notes, yet balanced and never overwhelming.  My wife went for the medium roast americano and that was joy in a cup.  The pancakes with fruit and the the eggs Benedict were sumptuous.  I went keto with eggs, bacon and spinach — the surprise was the very well spiced spinach.  Don’t miss it.  P.s The service especially from the entire team was warm, welcoming and friendly. Traditional Thai hospitality (which isn’t always the case in the busy high season) mixed with modern charm.  P.s.s yes, almost empty cup photo - was so good 😊"
> **- Chirag Singapuri (5/5/5)**

> "A really nice place setback off the main road so it’s got a good vibe. They have both inside & outside seating. I’ve eaten twice at this place and both times the grilled chicken has been amazing. Worth a visit if in the area."
> **- Connor Moody (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nomad-brunch-and-brew-1.jpg','097 998 1933','Choengmon, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://linktr.ee/nomad.kohsamui?utm_source=linktree_profile_share&ltsid=b8abe3c4-0b37-4761-b589-26f67fbde62e','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifsv000nq8xdrwnu123q','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.679+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.679+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nomad-brunch-and-brew-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nomad-brunch-and-brew-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4499641718585820769',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('nonna-son','standard','cmr07ih9l00k7q8xdb312u8zd','Nonna & Son','## Top Reviews
> "The pasta was absolutely delicious and full of flavor. The staff were very friendly and provided great service throughout the meal. We chose to sit on the outdoor balcony, which had an amazing view of airplanes taking off and landing — such a unique atmosphere. The restaurant is conveniently located at Chaweng Beach, easy to get to, and the food arrived very quickly without a long wait.  The only small downside was that we asked for extra sauce and received only a little portion, plus there was an additional charge for it. Other than that, it was a very enjoyable dining experience and definitely worth visiting."
> **- Peacezy Wirinya (5/5/5)**

> "Really enjoyed my visit here. I had the Wagyu pasta, and I can definitely recommend it,  it was full of flavor and cooked perfectly. We also tried the tiramisu, which was delicious.  The service was great as well. Everyone was friendly, attentive, and made us feel welcome throughout the evening.  Overall, a very good dining experience with great food and a nice atmosphere. I would happily come back and definitely recommend this place to others."
> **- Angelina (5/5/5)**

> "What a lovely place! The food is amazing and the staff is very attentive. We’ve eaten here 3 times already and the food has been delicious every time. Highly recommend!"
> **- Dagmara Samko (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nonna-son-1.jpg','093 647 0809','168/1 168/55 ตำบล บ่อผุด Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.instagram.com/nonnaandson_samui/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.681+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.681+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nonna-son-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nonna-son-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3192350338837190039',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('noori-india-indian-restaurant','standard','cmr07ih9n00k8q8xdcbop95r5','Noori India Indian Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "We were looking for an Indian restaurant near Central Samui and came across this place after seeing the photos and reviews. It looked promising, so we decided to give it a try.  When we arrived, the owner welcomed us and brought some complimentary crackers while we waited for the food, which was a nice touch. We ordered several dishes and everything was excellent. The portions were very generous and the prices felt fair for the quality and quantity.  The chicken tikka masala was definitely the highlight, full of flavor and perfectly cooked. The garlic naan was also fantastic and went really well with the curries. Overall, everything we tried was very satisfying.  If I stayed longer in Koh Samui and felt like having Indian food again, I would definitely come back."
> **- Alexander Cillan (5/5/5)**

> "Noori Indian Restaurant in Chaweng, Koh Samui, is an absolute gem for anyone craving authentic Indian flavors on the island. From the moment we stepped in, the nice atmosphere welcomed us—vibrant yet cozy, with friendly staff greeting us warmly and making us feel right at home. The location couldn’t be better, right on Chaweng Beach Road, easy to reach and perfect for a meal after beach time. The food was excellent, bursting with delicious spices and perfectly balanced flavors. We started with the cheese naan—hands down one of the best I’ve ever had, soft, fluffy, and loaded with gooey cheese. The garlic naan was equally addictive, with just the right amount of buttery garlic kick. For mains, the chicken tikka masala was rich and creamy, the butter chicken indulgent and comforting, and the vegetable creamy curry was a standout for its fresh veggies and smooth sauce. The vegetarian biryani was fragrant and packed with layers of flavor—wonderful vegetarian options all around, catering beautifully to non-meat eaters. What truly surprised us were the French fries—seriously the best French fries I’ve ever had in Thailand! Crispy on the outside, fluffy inside, perfectly seasoned, they were an unexpected highlight. Service was good throughout—attentive, smiling staff who were quick to refill drinks and check in without hovering. Prices are reasonable for the quality and portion sizes, offering great value in touristy Chaweng. Overall, Noori delivers top-notch Indian cuisine in a welcoming spot. We left full, happy, and already planning our next visit. Highly recommended—5 stars!"
> **- The Guy (5/5/5)**

> "The food was good. The prawn biryani and prawn tandoori were excellent. For the first time in a long time, I actually finished the whole masala dish, it was so good I just couldn''t stop eating! I also noticed that they don''t add food coloring, which is a plus. The service is good, and the ambience is okay—suitable for a local, authentic spot"
> **- Abrar Amer (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/noori-india-indian-restaurant-1.jpg','083 968 7912','17 1 ถนน หาดเฉวง, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://nooriindia.com/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.683+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.683+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/noori-india-indian-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/noori-india-indian-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7423716319219735552',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('nora-beach-resort','standard','cmr07ih9q00k9q8xdqvdhp0h3','Nora Beach Resort','## Top Reviews
> "This resort is gorgeous with all its lush plant and tree life everywhere. The resort is a little bit outdated compared to the photos they post. This resort has the best staff we have ever had at a hotel and we''re warm and helpful the entire time even with our baby and when my wife hurt her leg. The resort is pretty steep with the lobby being at the top and the beach pool and restaurant being at the bottom but they offer golf cart rides everywhere. The resort is unfortunately hard to leave by foot because of the tight busy road outside with no sidewalk to the shops and restaurants so we took lots of short taxi rides which they call for you at least. The beach is a bit underwhelming but its calm and quiet. The pool is really nice to make up for the beach luckily. The restaurant had a very very good breakfast buffet but the food and drinks at the resort were way overpriced (294 baht for a cocktail with tax and automatic 10% tip). The food also has an automatic tip of 10%. We stopped eating at the resort after the second night and found much cheaper options elsewhere and limited our drinks at the pool due to poor value. The beds are also really hard and we found them uncomfortable. Other than that we had an incredible time at this wonderful place and enjoyed spending time with all the amazing staff. Thank you Nora Beach for a wonderful family vacation!"
> **- Brock50 (4/5/5)**

> "We went only for a lunch and drinks during Samui Regetta event. We didn’t get to see any boats but we loved the restaurant set up facing the beach. It was lovely.  There were tiny bums during the service but, the professionalism after little communication about the discomfort during the food service  were exceptional. They shone ⭐ Honestly, I appreciate it.  The communication was incredible and efficient.  The manager Mr. Joe and other guy,  the chef (I believe) and FB teams and other team members were exceptional.  We haven’t stayed there but for the food, especially dessert 🍨 and Iced Caramel Latte was amazing.  I absolutely recommend.  We would like to stop by again in the future for the dessert when we have family visits.  It was lovely."
> **- Roshani Bajracharya (5/5/5)**

> "A big thank you to Michelle and the team for the warm Thai hospitality. This is my second time staying at this property and they have been phenomenal through and through. I would love to see a small refresh for some of the towels, pool linens and bathroom fixtures which are starting to show wear. Otherwise, my experience both stays was nothing short of world class which a lot of bigger, higher end hotels lack these days. The little things like a smile and the team making an effort to remember coffee orders at breakfast, asking about the activity you were telling them you were going to was. It’s these little touches which make it feel so much like home. Thanks again to the whole team at Nora for making me feel so welcome."
> **- Gal Gross (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nora-beach-resort-1.jpg','077 429 400','222, Chaweng Beach, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.norabeachresort.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.686+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.686+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nora-beach-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nora-beach-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2196044647886695773',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('nora-weddings','standard','cmr07ih9t00kaq8xd7dvgpajn','Nora Weddings','## Top Reviews
> "We’ve just returned from the most amazing trip to Thailand, where we spent a week in Koh Samui staying at the Nora Buri Resort & Spa, and we were so impressed from start to finish.  From the moment we arrived, the staff were incredibly friendly and helpful. Nothing was ever too much trouble. The rooms are set on a hillside, but you can request a buggy at any time to take you up to your room, which was always quick and easy.  We had breakfast included, and the variety each morning was excellent - plenty of options to suit everyone. Even though we booked a standard double room, it was big, spacious, and very comfortable.  One of the standout touches for us was the service around the pool. The waiters were so friendly and even remembered our usual order - it’s those little personal touches that really make a difference and elevate the whole experience.  The hotel is about a 10 minute taxi ride from the main area with restaurants and nightlife. It’s not really within walking distance, but that wasn’t an issue for us as taxis were always readily available outside the hotel. There are a few restaurants nearby, but we preferred heading into the main area for a bit more atmosphere and buzz.  Overall, we would highly recommend this hotel and wouldn’t hesitate to return. It made our time in Koh Samui truly special."
> **- P Lynn (5/5/5)**

> "Loved every minute! We have been at Nora Buri for two weeks and the entire time my partner and I have just been able to relax  We booked a pool villa on the hill. Great space to spread out and the pool was beautiful.  Great restaurants - we booked with luxury escapes so had meals included. We were never bored of the food. Fantastic selection!  I have to say hats off to the staff. Made my partner and I feel at home the entire time.  I’d say again and I will be recommending to friends."
> **- Lachlan McKillop (5/5/5)**

> "We had an absolutely incredible stay at Nora Buri Resort & Spa in Koh Samui!  We booked the Ocean View Pool Villa, and it not only lived up to the photos, it completely surpassed our expectations. The villa was stunning, the private pool was beautiful, and the views were truly breathtaking. Every morning felt like waking up in paradise.  What made the experience even better was the staff. From the moment we arrived, everyone was incredibly welcoming, friendly, and eager to help. The resort is spread across different areas, and the staff were always quick to assist with transportation around the property whenever we needed it. Their hospitality made us feel genuinely cared for throughout our stay.  The combination of luxurious accommodations, amazing views, and exceptional service made this one of our favorite hotel experiences. We would absolutely recommend Nora Buri to friends and family and hope to return again soon.  Thank you to the entire team for such a memorable stay!"
> **- Leigh Hauser (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nora-weddings-1.jpg','077 913 555','111, Moo 5, Chaweng Beach, Bophut, Koh Samui, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.noraburiresort.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.689+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.689+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nora-weddings-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nora-weddings-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9635277104675490676',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('nordenfeld','standard','cmr07ih9v00kbq8xd0ev8sgi8','Nordenfeld','## Top Reviews
> "I highly recommend this shop. The clothes are cute and the prices are reasonable. The staff are lovely and give great advice.👏🏻✨"
> **- R. Mice (5/5/5)**

> "The shop is cutely decorated. Clothes are arranged in sets, making them easy to choose and match. The staff are very good at giving advice"
> **- Didier (5/5/5)**

> "Beautiful shop in ko samui! Walked past and had to stop and have a look inside! Left with several new outfits! Beautiful materials and many options to choose from. Staff polite and helpful 🤩"
> **- Alec Thorp (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nordenfeld-1.jpg',NULL,'14, 102 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Koh Samui, Surat Thani 84320 Bophut, ตำบล บ่อผุด Koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.nordenfeld.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.691+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.691+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nordenfeld-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nordenfeld-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9139319415002219353',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('nutchaya-driving-school','standard','cmr07ih9z00kcq8xdf3u16me4','Nutchaya Driving School','## Top Reviews
> "Very good experience!  Real lessons, instructor''s English is limited yet instructions were very clear and communication was efficient. Administration was very friendly, patient and accommodating. I came in with a lot of fear and zero knowledge but left with confidence and necessary foundation. Highly recommended!"
> **- Alina Bondarenko (5/5/5)**

> "This is the best driving school and the only real driving school in Samui. The teacher is very professional and caring. The workers are also friendly and helpful. I got my driver license after good practice. Thanks for all your great effort."
> **- Catherine Liu (5/5/5)**

> "very good driving school. staff speak english. i went to get my motorbike drivinglicense with a friend. it was not very hard. and if you have problems they help you till the end. thank you staff for another great expierence in thailand. kapkoonkub 🙏🏽🇹🇭"
> **- SushiBapau040 (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nutchaya-driving-school-1.jpg','062 394 9464','22/12 ม.5 ต Tambon Na Mueang, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifui0012q8xdzn158clv','cmr07ig4i004oq8xdv207xuh2','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.695+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.695+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nutchaya-driving-school-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/nutchaya-driving-school-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=18407454159679678663',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ocean-air-maintenance','standard','cmr07iha100kdq8xd9ri1q7wc','Ocean Air & Maintenance','Discover Ocean Air & Maintenance, a premier Property Services located in Big Buddha, Koh Samui. Find reviews, hours, and contact information.','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ocean-air-maintenance-1.jpg','+66947158888','79 91, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,0.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 5:15 PM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 5:15 PM","Thursday: 8:30 AM – 5:15 PM","Friday: 8:30 AM – 5:15 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: 8:30 AM – 5:15 PM"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ig6y005pq8xd4jrvheih','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.697+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.697+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ocean-air-maintenance-1.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=466164170461937978',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('oceans-elite-yacht-charters','standard','cmr07iha300keq8xdagb9r96k','Oceans Elite Yacht Charters','## Top Reviews
> "We had the best time in Ang Thong National Marine Park.  Tik picked us up right at the entrance of our cruise boat tender, so we waisted no time and headed straight on our adventures.  May and his boat crew were super attentive throughout the trip getting us drinks, pointing out sites, went snorkeling with us through the caves.  Then he showed us a wonderful time at a pristine private beach with a sandbar where we relaxed and soaked in the sunshine.  Lastly. we had our best meal at Puluay Island for blue crab in curry sauce, giant prawns, deep fried fish and Tom Yum soup.  Hair blowing against the breeze, electric beats vibrating through the sound system, vibrant scenery, and smiles all around.  It was pure magic.  Highly recommend the crew!"
> **- Krysti Sam & Dave Dang (5/5/5)**

> "I’ve just completed two consecutive private tours with Oceans Elite, and I can honestly say the experience was extremely positive.  Tik’s service was exceptional — she was clear, responsive, and very confident in addressing all my questions. There was an unexpected issue the day before the first tour, as the boat’s engine had a problem and I had to switch to another boat. Naturally, that caused a bit of stress at first, but she handled the situation professionally and efficiently. In the end, everything turned out even better than expected.  A special thank you to our guide, Dome. He was not only incredibly attentive but also genuinely fun to be around. I specifically requested him to be our guide for both Ang Thong Marine Park and Koh Prangham, and I’m very glad I did.  I highly recommend them. From start to finish, I felt confident and well taken care of. Considering these were two private tours — and therefore a significant investment — at no point did I feel I had made the wrong choice."
> **- Juliano Yamakawa (5/5/5)**

> "⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ We’re on a two-week holiday in Koh Samui and booking Ocean Elite with the boat Gigi has been one of the highlights of the trip. The boat was absolutely beautiful, very clean and comfortable, and felt really luxurious without being over the top.  The crew were amazing – so friendly, helpful and professional, and they really made the day special for our group. Everything ran smoothly and we could just relax, swim, and enjoy the stunning scenery.  If you’re visiting Samui and thinking about a private boat day, I’d 100% recommend Ocean Elite and Gigi. A perfect way to spend a day on the water and make great memories"
> **- Chloe Ferry (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/oceans-elite-yacht-charters-1.jpg','089 288 6404','41/21, ตำบล แม่น้ำ อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://oceanselitecharters.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.699+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.699+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/oceans-elite-yacht-charters-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/oceans-elite-yacht-charters-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14827324527417767892',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('odyssey','standard','cmr07iha500kfq8xd57f1cp3f','Odyssey','## Top Reviews
> "I recently had the pleasure of staying at a stunning villa in Koh Samui, and it exceeded all my expectations. The villa is beautifully designed, showcasing some of the most exquisite architecture I''ve ever encountered. Every room is spacious and well-appointed, with a focus on cleanliness that made my stay incredibly comfortable.  The facilities are top-notch, offering everything you could need for a relaxing vacation. From the private pool to the outdoor lounging areas, every detail has been thoughtfully crafted.  The energy of the place is uplifting, largely thanks to the amazing staff. Lea, the property manager, is simply outstanding. Her attentiveness and genuine kindness made a significant difference in my experience. The entire staff was exceptionally welcoming and eager to assist, enhancing the overall atmosphere.  Location-wise, the villa is perfectly situated, allowing easy access to local attractions while still providing a serene retreat. This property truly offers a perfect blend of luxury and comfort. I highly recommend it to anyone looking for an unforgettable getaway in Koh Samui!"
> **- hamzah nabulsi (5/5/5)**

> "We had the absolute pleasure of getting married at Odyssey. After months of searching for the perfect venue, we stumbled upon this hidden gem—and it truly exceeded all our expectations. The villa embodies quiet luxury, with its beachfront setting, stunning design, and impeccable attention to detail. Every room was immaculate and beautifully unique, with no element overlooked.  Nathalie and her team were beyond amazing—warm, welcoming, and always available. Their dedication and care made us feel completely at ease, and it was clear that nothing was ever too much trouble.  The villa offers exceptional privacy—it truly feels like you have the entire place to yourselves. On the rare occasions people passed by, they would often pause, clearly impressed by the stunning property.  We felt completely safe and secure throughout our stay, which made it even more relaxing.  The location is ideal, with Fisherman’s Village, the pier, and the airport all close by, making it easy to get around.  Our stay at the Odyssey was unforgettable. While it was made even more special by our wedding, the experience itself—both the accommodation and the service—was the best we’ve ever had. Our friends and family felt exactly the same. Leaving was genuinely emotional, and I was brought to tears when it became time for our departure. I can only hope to return one day. Thank you for helping us create such incredible memories that we will cherish forever."
> **- Bell Jacobs (5/5/5)**

> "We stayed here a week in April 2026 to celebrate my birthday with a group of 16 people (and a few birthday guests from other places) and honestly, I could not have chosen a better location for it!  From the moment we arrived, it was clear that everything there is done to a very high standard. A beautiful, very well maintained property, lovingly designed bungalows, some with a pool, others with a garden area, exceptionally friendly and attentive staff, and all set in surroundings to die for.  Also, the event management arranged through the villa manager for organizing the celebration was exceptional. Everything ran smoothly, the team took care of everything and I was able to fully focus on my guests and enjoy the evening. Exactly how you would want it to be.  A special and big thank you to Léa, one of our villa managers, who kept everything organized and made the whole stay feel effortless.  All in all, a perfect place for groups and special occasions. We’ll very likely be back.  Kind regards Timo and friends"
> **- Timo Kloy (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/odyssey-1.jpg','092 270 4600','58, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://odyssey-samui.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.701+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.701+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/odyssey-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/odyssey-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11319519601418133388',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ohm-auto-maenam','standard','cmr07iha800kgq8xdit5mzf3h','OHM AUTO','## Top Reviews
> "Ordered tyres online and brought here for a change. Efficient and professional service. Done in an hour with excellence. Friendly staff offering free coffee and muffin during the wait."
> **- Martlet (5/5/5)**

> "An absolute fantastic garage that got me out of a lot of trouble!  I cannot recommend this garage enough. On Christmas Eve, I drove my 4x4 to Fisherman’s Village for dinner and noticed a tire was going soft. By the time I went to collect the car the next day (Christmas Day), it was completely flat.  I searched Google Maps for a nearby garage and found OHM Auto. I gave them a call and spoke to a gentleman—I believe he was the manager—who spoke English, which was a huge relief. He told me not to worry and just asked me to send my location via WhatsApp. Within less than an hour, he had a technician sent out to me.  They fixed the puncture right there on-site, and I was back up and running in no time. I was genuinely surprised by the repair cost; it was so cheap, especially considering it was Christmas Day!  If you need help, definitely give them a call. Highly recommend!  ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️"
> **- Anthony (5/5/5)**

> "BYD display kept warning me that 1 tire pressure was too low. Even after refilling, it went down again after a few days. Went to this shop: in very short order they found a nail, removed it, sealed the hole (without needing to remove tire), refilled the air. All within less than 10min at a fair price.  Highly recommended"
> **- Miguel Jaun (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ohm-auto-maenam-1.jpg','089 590 4109','Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifui0012q8xdzn158clv','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.704+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.704+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ohm-auto-maenam-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ohm-auto-maenam-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1166762940643860655',NULL,NULL);
