INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ok-fitness','standard','cmr07ihad00kiq8xd5eg58aj2','Ok Fitness','## Top Reviews
> "Solid gym for 140 THB per pass! Honestly, it’s not bad at all for that price on the island where everything is overpriced. you have everything you need for a full workout. It would be nice to see a few more kettlebells and dumbbells added to the functional area, but overall, it’s excellent value for money. Definitely a good spot if you’re looking for a budget-friendly session!"
> **- Olga Martí García (4/5/5)**

> "One of the best local gyms you’ll find! OK Fitness Samui is a hidden gem for anyone who loves a no-nonsense, old-school gym vibe. No aircon – and that’s actually a big plus. You sweat it out properly, just the way it should be in Thailand. It’s raw, honest training in a tropical setting. The equipment covers all the basics, and everything you need for a solid workout is there. Best part? Only 120 baht per day – unbeatable value for money. Highly recommend for anyone looking to stay fit without the frills."
> **- medium_nice (5/5/5)**

> "Decent gym with decent equipment! Has everything you could possibly need for a good workout.  Whilst there is no air con, the fans kept the place cool enough when working out.  120 baht entry for 1 time! Well worth the price! Definitely recommended if visiting or moving here as the price and equipment are both decent"
> **- Curtis James Fountain (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ok-fitness-1.jpg','082 420 9527','HXH2+4XG, Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifuo0015q8xdfahzrsp4','cmr07ifs1000cq8xdfo2aau32','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.709+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.709+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ok-fitness-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ok-fitness-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10497800527778198683',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('old-school-bar','standard','cmr07ihaf00kjq8xdafsyi8x9','Old School Bar','## Top Reviews
> "Real Thai vibes! One of the most authentic Thai bars I’ve ever been to! No fancy cocktails – just cold beer with ice, good vibes, and amazing live Thai music. Mostly locals, which makes the atmosphere even more special. I speak a bit of Thai, and they actually invited me on stage to sing a Thai song with the band – such an unforgettable moment! 🎤🇹🇭 The staff is super sweet and welcoming, and the energy is just pure joy. If you''re looking for a real, fun Thai night out (and maybe a chance to sing on stage 😄) – this is the place."
> **- Lital Levitin (5/5/5)**

> "Great little local hangout next to the lake. Excellent hip hop and rock music playing while band setting up. Once band set up the music was fantastic from both groups that played when we were there. Food overall was great with a few dishes missing the mark slightly. If you want to experience a typical local social hangout, this is one of the better ones."
> **- Peej (4/5/5)**

> "so much fun! Thai live music, good vibes, and a great local feel."
> **- Jessi Heifets (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/old-school-bar-1.jpg','063 080 5408','G3G5+8FF, Unnamed Road, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 6:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Tuesday: 6:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Wednesday: 6:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Thursday: 6:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Friday: 6:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Saturday: 6:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Sunday: 6:00 PM – 2:00 AM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.711+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.711+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/old-school-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/old-school-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17424146254468623617',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('olivers-steakhouse-bar-grill','standard','cmr07ihai00kkq8xd3a0uj2my','Oliver''s Steakhouse Bar & Grill','## Top Reviews
> "Overall it was just a visit that didn’t meet the expectations I guess. The restaurant itself is just normal, nothing astonishing about it. I think the prices were pretty high for being Thailand.  But the thing is, we can live with higher cost, and that the restaurant is not astonishing - but SERVICE is very important, which this placed really lacked. The staff didn’t welcome us, they didn’t seem happy to have customers. It felt like we were just a problem there to be honest…"
> **- Alexander Schützler (1/5/5)**

> "We have eaten at Oliver''s Steakhouse half a dozen times over the last two weeks. Everything we have eaten has been cooked to perfection, I recommend the ribeye, or just the beef patties, which if you are on a carnivore diet are a great choice. The staff are attentive, and the chef is very accommodating. Price is reasonable compared to a couple of steak houses at Fisherman''s Village."
> **- Scott Griffiths (5/5/5)**

> "The steaks were mediocre compared to other places on the island. The set up is too open so the smoke from the grill overpowered the dining area. The owner is very nice. Overall, it''s not on top of our return to spot."
> **- Jenna Carroll (2/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/olivers-steakhouse-bar-grill-1.jpg','084 203 5646','Bangrak, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: Closed","Wednesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.714+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.714+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/olivers-steakhouse-bar-grill-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/olivers-steakhouse-bar-grill-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5466207505586666150',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('olivio','standard','cmr07ihal00klq8xdd2jxae92','Olivio','## Top Reviews
> "We had the most amazing time at this hotel. The room was perfect and clean, the pool and view was beautiful, and the food at the restaurant was delicious every time. I am coeliac and every member of staff made sure I was looked after, catered to my allergy’s and made sure I had gluten free bread every morning at breakfast. If I ever come back to Ko Samui, I will be coming back here! Thank you so much!"
> **- Olivia Humphreys (5/5/5)**

> "I wad not impressed by the food: the starter (potato slices with truffle) was overfried in a too big amount of oil. The main course (risotto with baby octopus) was a bit overcooked, wine should have been evaporated better. Overall it looked better than tasted. However, the place is located in a beautiful spot where you can enjoy amazing sunset and ocean"
> **- Tatiana Sergienia (2/5/5)**

> "We stayed at the accommodation at the same premises so we frequented Olivio’s throughout our stay and we cannot fault anything. The staff were great, all meals including the two for one pizzas, the breakfast and the menu items were delicious. The restaurant was always immaculately clean and well presented and the background music added to the ambience of the restaurant. The service was prompt, professional and efficient and it was an added bonus which kept us from going elsewhere. I have no hesitation in recommending Olivio’s."
> **- Patty (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/olivio-1.jpg','093 576 4842','154/14-15, 154/14-15 หมู่ 2 เทศบาลนครเกาะสมุย อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.oliviosamui.com/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.717+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.717+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/olivio-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/olivio-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12679919096728586975',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('omart-liquor','standard','cmr07ihao00kmq8xdppr7nllw','O''Mart Liquor','## Top Reviews
> "Great vibes, premium drinks, and a place you’ll love coming back to 🍷🍸🍺From fine wines and premium spirits to ice-cold beers and so much more,there’s something perfect for every mood and every night.  Relaxing atmosphere, friendly service, and great music — the perfect spot to unwind with friends 🥰"
> **- Wani (5/5/5)**

> "My favorite liquor store in the island, all staffs are super friendly and nice 😍 and I found this soft-dried mango (low sugar) from TAI GUO PIN, the best of the best in Thailand 😋 Definitely come back again :)"
> **- Jennifer Mabangkru (5/5/5)**

> "Step into a world of premium beverages and discover one of the most diverse drink selections in town. Our store offers a wide variety of wines, spirits, champagne, whiskey, sake, and specialty beverages from many countries around the world. Whether you are looking for something classic, luxurious, or unique, you’ll find the perfect bottle for every occasion.  We carefully select high-quality products at great prices so our customers can enjoy the best value without compromising on taste and authenticity. From fine wines and imported liquors to refreshing mixers and rare collections, there is something here for everyone — beginners, collectors, and beverage lovers alike.  Our shelves are always stocked with quality products, friendly service, and exciting new arrivals waiting to be discovered. We warmly invite you to stop by, explore our wide selection, and enjoy a premium shopping experience.  Visit us today and find your next favorite drink at a price you’ll love!"
> **- Apitchaya Anuvet (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/omart-liquor-1.jpg','065 623 2698','23 ตำบล บ่อผุด Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.720+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.720+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/omart-liquor-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/omart-liquor-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16175200126636113617',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('on-street-bar-samui','standard','cmr07ihar00knq8xd33nwntm7','On Street Bar Samui','## Top Reviews
> "If you are looking for nice place with BEST cocktails in Koh Samui, then this is it! Just secret pearl middle of Banana Market with best cocktails!"
> **- Sabīne Belova (5/5/5)**

> "The bar is amazing. The cocktails are excellent. Very good atmosphere! Good prices."
> **- Idan Prigal (5/5/5)**

> "Very good Cocktail very good Owner and staff"
> **- Savatang tattoo samui (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/on-street-bar-samui-1.jpg','087 552 3524','Banana Market ติดกับห้าง Haven ตรงข้าม โรงแรม Banana Fan Sea Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.onstreetbar.com/','["Monday: 7:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Tuesday: 7:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Wednesday: 7:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Thursday: 7:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Friday: 7:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Saturday: 7:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.723+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.723+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/on-street-bar-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/on-street-bar-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11864842198897237953',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('onaka-sushi-bar','standard','cmr07ihau00koq8xdvx19iks7','Onaka Sushi Bar','## Top Reviews
> "Fresh delicious Japanese in Koh Samui what more could you want! Loved this restaurant from the decor to lovely staff. An absolute must if you love sushi 🍣 All made fresh with care and detail - Sooo good!"
> **- melanie kirkpatrick-cross (5/5/5)**

> "Best sushi we''ve had in a long time! Salmon sashimi was so fresh and the portion is triple what we get in London. Double salmon roll was really good too. Definitely coming back again! Service was slightly slow but it was busy on the day."
> **- Lon Lon (5/5/5)**

> "This is a great little sushi bar located on the main beach road in Lamai, Koh Samui. Overall the food was great. A couple of dishes that didn''t have much taste but they were fried dishes. The Sushi and Nigiri was all very fresh and tasty. We will be going back to try more dishes. Definitely worth a try if your craving sushi."
> **- Simon Walker (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/onaka-sushi-bar-1.jpg','065 660 6777','124, 669, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 2:00 – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 2:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 2:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: Closed","Friday: 2:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 2:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 2:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.726+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.726+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/onaka-sushi-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/onaka-sushi-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=510643726015019274',NULL,NULL);
