INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ook-ook-social-beach-club','standard','cmr07ihaz00kqq8xdpyz6oiy7','OOK OOK Social Beach Club','## Top Reviews
> "I stumbled across this place walking down the beach. You can’t miss it, on a good day, there’s huge inflatable beanbags in the shape of bananas.  I was blown away with the quality of both the drinks and the food, combined with the price.  The Pad Thai (pictured) was 150bht and the coconut and rosemary iced smoothie was 120bht.  Yes, I know somebody will say that “that’s expensive” for Thailand, and, what I know you can get similar items for 80bht and 40bht respectively, they won’t taste as good as these and have this view.  The staff are all lovely, and, this was my go to lunch spot on at least five occasions.  You can access it from the beach, or off of the main road (just look for their sign, next to a hotel called The Stay).  Trust me, you won’t regret it. 👊🏼🔥"
> **- Adam Toctan (5/5/5)**

> "Unfortunately when we visited the water was shallow at the beach ... made the place look dirty and unpleasant to look at. We came for breakfast before going for a swim and we were told that the restaurant is offering a buffet for breakfast.  The breakfast buffet was small and it was 350 tb per person."
> **- Reem Mohamed (3/5/5)**

> "Went there just to ride the yellow water trike with our kids. The kids had a blast! The restaurant is air conditioned, so we can take a break, get away from the heat and enjoyed cool smoothies / light snacks. The staff is super nice and service is above standard. Love it!"
> **- Bangkok Stray dog (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ook-ook-social-beach-club-1.jpg','077 415 200','162/5 หมู่ที่ 2 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'https://web.facebook.com/ookooksocialbeachclub','["Monday: 8:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 8:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 8:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 8:30 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 8:30 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.731+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.731+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ook-ook-social-beach-club-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ook-ook-social-beach-club-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7465507315050587067',NULL,NULL);
