INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('orchid-spa','standard','cmr07ihb400ksq8xd5az6x7qe','Orchid Spa','## Top Reviews
> "My partner and I went for a Thai massage with Thai herbal oil. Very strong massage, it felt great afterwards and a free drink of water afterwards."
> **- Beanie Wintringham (5/5/5)**

> "Came in for a traditional Thai massage and loved it. The place is clean, with soft music. They give you a little towel to rest your head on with a slight mint scent. The masseuse was very professional and kind. Left the place feeling relaxed and grateful for the service. Thank you!"
> **- Marina González Álvarez (5/5/5)**

> "Very good foot massage. For us was very comfortable temperature inside: not to hot not to cold."
> **- Rimvydas Baltrusevicius (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/orchid-spa-1.jpg','083 596 5393','130 จ.สุราษฎาร์นี 1, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.736+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.736+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/orchid-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/orchid-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16788027780416550816',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('organic-farm-coffee-shop','standard','cmr07ihb600ktq8xduu044fh5','Organic Farm & Coffee Shop','## Top Reviews
> "Organic Farm & Coffee Shop in Koh Samui is a wonderful place to visit. Located in the hills, it offers a beautiful view overlooking the sea, creating a very relaxing atmosphere.  The menu has a great selection of Thai dishes, all fresh and very tasty. The service is also very friendly and welcoming.  A lovely spot to enjoy good food and one of the best views on the island. Highly recommended."
> **- Oliver Kremers (5/5/5)**

> "The atmosphere is amazing, the food is delicious, and the prices are very reasonable. The staff are friendly and provide excellent service.  If you plan to visit, I highly recommend coming by car. It is not advisable to ride a motorcycle because the road is quite steep. Going uphill is fine, but going downhill can be very dangerous.  Only very experienced riders with good riding skills and high-quality motorcycles might manage safely. However, for safety reasons, it is best to avoid using a motorcycle altogether."
> **- Netnapa Tanyongthong (5/5/5)**

> "The food is fresh and delicious. I know I’m eating healthy when I eat here. The views are amazing and the atmosphere is wonderful. The air is clean up there and I always enjoy the respite from the smoke filled streets of Samui. They have a variety of dishes, desserts, and drinks to choose from. They have places to relax and lay back while taking in the surrounding countryside and spectacular views"
> **- Shirden (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/organic-farm-coffee-shop-1.jpg','087 889 9914','GXJ2+PF, Ang Thong, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/samuiorganiccoffeeshop/','["Monday: 9:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: Closed","Thursday: 9:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 9:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 9:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 9:30 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifxh0027q8xde6xqk8o6','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.738+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.738+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/organic-farm-coffee-shop-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/organic-farm-coffee-shop-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16992661688990381583',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('oriental-living','standard','cmr07ihb800kuq8xdev61y7io','Oriental Living','## Top Reviews
> "My experience with Oriental Living was nothing short of exceptional. I needed to furnish my newly built house in Krabi while living in Spain, and Somporn helped me choose the furniture with a level of professionalism and dedication that was truly unmatched. The delivery date was met with incredible punctuality, and the furniture is perfect, of the highest quality, and beyond all expectations. I recommend Oriental Living to anyone looking to tastefully furnish their apartment or villa. Special thanks to Somporn for his professionalism."
> **- adelchi mancusi (5/5/5)**

> "I visited the Oriental Living Samui showroom yesterday and had a great experience. The staff were very friendly and professional, and they took excellent care of me. Seeing the showroom in person really gave me confidence in the quality of the products. After the visit, I arranged delivery through Oriental Living Samui, and everything went smoothly and professionally. Highly recommended!"
> **- Wannaporn Wongwit (5/5/5)**

> "I have known Oriental Living since I arrived on Koh Samui, but somehow never made it into their showroom, The Loft, across from Big C in Bophut. I finally stopped by recently, and it was absolutely worth it.  The furniture and interior pieces are beautifully curated, with a strong Bali-style influence that feels warm, natural, and very well put together. Seeing everything in person makes a huge difference compared to photos.  They offer full interior design solutions, but also smaller pieces if you are just looking for details or accents. The staff was relaxed, approachable, and happy to answer even the most complicated questions without any pressure.  Definitely worth a visit if you are into interior design or quality furniture on the island."
> **- Patrick Kollitsch (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/oriental-living-1.jpg','+6677423877','125, T, 17, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.oriental-living.net/','["Monday: 9:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 9:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 9:30 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 9:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.740+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.740+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/oriental-living-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/oriental-living-2.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/oriental-living-3.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=511764003921609694',NULL,NULL);
