INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('oscars-fashion','standard','cmr07ihbe00kwq8xds01unirf','Oscars Fashion','## Top Reviews
> "Oscars Fashion is THE place to go for suits in Koh Samui. I came to his shop in need of a 3 day turnaround for some tailored suits and he absolutely executed. I purchased a 3 piece suit and a 2 piece suit along with 2 shirts. He had me hand select the fabric and color I wanted during the initial consultation. After selecting those, he had me come back next day for two different fitting sessions, one in evening, one in morning. The next day I came back in the morning for a final fitting. At night I came to pick up my very final product and I am beyond amazed. Oscar not only gave an outstanding price, but provided service, hospitality, and customization that is hard to find anywhere in the world. I am beyond amazed at the turnaround, customization, and fit. Truly an amazing person and store. HIGHLY recommend."
> **- Tonic Storyz (5/5/5)**

> "I had a suit made at Oscars Fashion and can only recommend going to Oscars if you need a suit or shirt - The whole process has been really professional, the measures was spot on from the first measurements. I had a tight schedule, as I had to leave Koh Samui in 4 days, but nonetheless Oscar performed and had a suit ready for me the night before leaving Koh Samui.  I have had a suit made in Phuket last year and can only say that Oscar has a higher quality and is much more professional through the process."
> **- Mathias Laustsen (5/5/5)**

> "Great experience!  Oscar helped me a lot to find the right color and material. The clothes were almost perfectly fitting at the first fitting. The service is outstanding. Contact through WhatsApp and they give helpful advices from their year long experience as a Taylor.  I can order stuff back home or get changes made."
> **- Philipp Lutz (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/oscars-fashion-1.jpg','062 630 6822','60, 3, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Koh Sa-Mui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/pages/category/Shopping---Retail/Oscars-Fashion-168459913918441/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 11:15 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 11:15 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 11:15 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 11:15 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 11:15 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 11:15 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 11:15 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.746+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.746+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/oscars-fashion-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/oscars-fashion-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8205634636550602962',NULL,NULL);
