> **- GT3 RS (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/outrigger-voyager-47-club-lounge-1.jpg','077 458 560','173, 41 Rob Koh Road, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.outrigger.com/thailand/outrigger-koh-samui-beach-resort','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.758+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.758+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/outrigger-voyager-47-club-lounge-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/outrigger-voyager-47-club-lounge-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16803426513922100969',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ovs-wine-cellarbar','standard','cmr07ihbt00l1q8xdadn6hpjn','OVS Wine Cellar/Bar','## Top Reviews
> "First of all the service here is simply amazing!!!!! We came here by chance and it turned out to be one of the places we enjoyed the most in Koh Samui. The wine was delicious and at a great price, the food was amazing, and the service was the best we have received in Thailand. Highly recommended!"
> **- דריה זליקמן (5/5/5)**

> "A Hidden Gem in Koh Samui – A Must-Visit for Wine Lovers!  We have just discovered a little gem on the island of Koh Samui that completely stole our hearts. As people who really like our wine and appreciate the history, location, and provenance of vineyards and producers, this place was an absolute find. We were lucky enough to meet the owner of this establishment, who gave us the warmest welcome imaginable. She was incredibly passionate and certainly knew the history of her wine, guiding us through their impressive selection with such care. What’s truly amazing is the diversity they offer—wines from over seven different countries, including France, Spain, Italy, South Africa, New Zealand, Chile, Austria, and Australia. It is rare to find such a curated global selection in one spot! You simply must visit this hidden gem to experience the most amazing decor. We were delighted to find "
> **- Anthony (5/5/5)**

> "*A Hidden Gem on Samui!*  "
> **- พีระพล สมบูรณ์มนต์ (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ovs-wine-cellarbar-1.jpg',NULL,'1/69 ถ. ทวีราษฎร์ภักดี Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.orientalvinesories.com/','["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.761+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.761+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ovs-wine-cellarbar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ovs-wine-cellarbar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10353163121544078451',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('owndays','standard','cmr07ihbx00l2q8xdbexdpoai','Owndays','## Top Reviews
> "I had a very good experience at Owndays.  The new glasses are nice. I returned after 1 week and  they did more tests and replaced one lens, now I can see very clearly again.  On top of that the staff  informed me how I could get a 10% discount. I''ll definitely use this optician again 😀"
> **- Eddie Corbyn (5/5/5)**

> "Walked in. Had a pair of new glasses in an hour. Bought 2 sets, other pair was specially ordered for me and was ready to be collected in 5 days.  As seamless process as can be 5/5"
> **- Rasmus Pyykkö (5/5/5)**

> "I walked in with a friend and we were met with such friendly service. We had been to a glasses store before, and were quoted about 4000 baht, where we were able to get beautiful frames, with fitted prescription lenses for 1790 (great price, including a newcomer discount). We were helped by Nudee, who was attentive, kind and very professional. Great experience!"
> **- Micayla Dennis (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/owndays-1.jpg','077 410 365','No. 209, 209/1 - 209/2 Moo 2, Central Samui, Unit No.148/2 1st Floor, G3J6+QM4 ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.owndays.com/th/th/shops/269','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.765+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.765+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/owndays-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/owndays-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17538468908037051654',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ozo-chaweng','standard','cmr07ihbz00l3q8xdzlow4ik7','OZO Chaweng','## Top Reviews
> "We stayed at the hotel for three nights and had a very nice experience. The staff was extremely kind, friendly, and helpful throughout our stay.  When we asked to change rooms because of some discomfort, the team was very attentive and helped us quickly. We really appreciated the fast response and the willingness to help.  A special thank you to the staff members Nikki, Pui, Nueng, and Beem for their great service and kindness. They made our stay even better.  We truly enjoyed our time at the hotel and would be happy to stay here again."
> **- Roi Sharet (5/5/5)**

> "Our stay at OZO Chaweng Hotel in Koh Samui was absolutely perfect! From the moment we arrived, we were warmly welcomed and immediately felt at home. The location right on the beautiful Chaweng Beach is perfect. The hotel is modern and very clean, and the breakfast was also good.  The pool area is a real highlight – clean, well-maintained, and ideal for relaxing. Especially great: the hotel is very child-friendly, so families can feel completely comfortable here.  A special thank you to Ti-Cha – she was incredibly friendly, attentive, and truly made our stay even more special.  We felt completely at ease and would love to come back!"
> **- Gilles Eich (5/5/5)**

> "⸻  I had an absolutely wonderful stay at OZO Chaweng Samui. From the moment I arrived, everything was seamless and welcoming.  The location is perfect—right on Chaweng Beach, with easy access to shops, restaurants, and nightlife, yet the resort itself feels peaceful and relaxing. Waking up to the sound of the ocean and stepping directly onto the beach was a highlight of my trip.  The rooms were modern, clean, and very comfortable, with thoughtful touches that made the stay even more enjoyable. The bed was especially comfortable, and I slept incredibly well every night.  The staff truly made the experience exceptional. They were friendly, attentive, and always ready to help with a smile, making me feel genuinely welcomed throughout my stay.  The pool area was beautiful and well-maintained, and the beachfront setting made it even more special. Breakfast had a great variety of options, and everything was fresh and delicious.  Overall, OZO Chaweng Samui offers fantastic value, combining comfort, great service, and an unbeatable location. I would definitely return and highly recommend it to anyone visiting Koh Samui."
> **- Lanz Vy (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ozo-chaweng-1.jpg','077 915 200','11 34 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.ozohotels.com/chaweng-samui/special-offers?utm_source=google&utm_medium=gmb&utm_campaign=ors','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.767+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.767+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ozo-chaweng-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ozo-chaweng-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14434538033368324755',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('padel-paradise','standard','cmr07ihc200l4q8xd9up5a2g9','Padel Paradise','## Top Reviews
> "I had a private lesson with Swan. I really liked the way he explained, demonstrated, and explained everything. We didn''t move on to other instructions until we were comfortable with what we were doing. The club is very comfortable and well-designed, and the staff responded quickly when I signed up for a lesson. I even managed to play once. The club has a group for different levels—I recommend it. I fell during a game, but at the end, the staff member offered me some ice, so I''m especially grateful for that."
> **- Ильдар Калимуллин (5/5/5)**

> "We had an amazing time at Padel Paradise Lamai! As total beginners, we really appreciated the friendly owners who gave us a quick and fun lesson with great tips. The courts are covered, so you can play rain or shine, and the atmosphere is super relaxed. . Whether you’re a first-timer or an experienced player, this place is a must-visit in Koh Samui. Highly recommended! ⭐"
> **- Hello Explorer Guide (5/5/5)**

> "Best padel club in Samui!!! Everything from the facilities to the team is fab. I extended my stay in Samui just to play padel here more. I travelled around Asia for 2 months and played padel in many clubs and so far this was my fav. Within just a few days, I felt so welcomes and part of the family. I cant recommend it enough and defo be visiting again ❤️❤️❤️"
> **- Deepika Bangarh (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/padel-paradise-1.jpg','080 126 8250','83 Sub-District 65 Thanon Had Lamai, Tambon Maret, Lamai Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.padellamai.com/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifuo0015q8xdfahzrsp4','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.770+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.770+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/padel-paradise-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/padel-paradise-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=201930833355624854',NULL,NULL);
