> "Great band! I went 2 different nights and then guitar players were in incredible. The lead singer was amazing also."
> **- steven lane (5/5/5)**

> "The best place for rock and heavy rock live music in Samui. The band did amazing covers especially of Rage Against the Machine."
> **- Frank KA (5/5/5)**

> "I wrote a review about this place a year ago from another account. Now, I''m writing a new one from this account. I was so happy to come back after a year and see the same talented band "
> **- Tanya Fanka (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/palm-terrace-1.jpg','093 659 6891','162/6 Moo 2, ตำบล บ่อผุด Koh Samui, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://thepalmssamui.com/','["Monday: 5:00 PM – 3:00 AM","Tuesday: 5:00 PM – 3:00 AM","Wednesday: 5:00 PM – 3:00 AM","Thursday: 5:00 PM – 3:00 AM","Friday: 5:00 PM – 3:00 AM","Saturday: 5:00 PM – 3:00 AM","Sunday: 5:00 PM – 3:00 AM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.774+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.774+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/palm-terrace-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/palm-terrace-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17326715799142459810',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('panacea-retreat','standard','cmr07ihc900l7q8xdw2lju6yf','Panacea Retreat','## Top Reviews
> "Sublime. 11/10. Out of this world.  We were 5 of us all adults in Purana villa. Purana in Hindi/Sanskrit means old/ancient- there wasn''t anything old about it.. 4 bedrooms- we occupied 3. All with ensuite washrooms. Both the rooms and the washrooms very spacious with at least 2 cupboards each. The living/dining area- is humongous - maybe 5k+ sq. ft. Huge sitting area, huge dining table with an open kitchen with every amenity possible- fridge, stove, coffee machine- everything.  You enter on the first floor and then walk down to the ground floor to the bedrooms and the pool. The pool, the pool, what a pool- large, easy to wade in, with a bar area on the side. There is also a barbeque area next to it with a large dining table, cooling cabinets and a barbeque grill.  The villa comes with a staff of three. They spoil you. Breakfast is included. If you want to get anything else cooked- you tell them what- they get the groceries and cook. We did dinner two nights like that and it was sumptuous. Amazing spread.  You can order in also- Grab works effortlessly.  For me personally the best thing was that the audio system. Sonos amp (old style ZP100/120). Speakers in the living/dining area and next to the pool. Spotify will work (not much else- as the Sonos amp is very old)- great sound quality. If you download the S1 app you can even sync both sets of speakers.  One thing: this place is not walkable from anything- but you don''t to get out - at least not for utilities. You need a car to move about - Grab works. If you need to get alcohol- there are online services though if you take a Grab you can reach multiple stores within 5 minutes.  Will surely go back-thinking of doing remote work from here. Special call out to Iew."
> **- Manu Kashyap (5/5/5)**

> "What an amazing experience having the opportunity to stay at Panacea Retreat. It was private, spacious and Noei and her team were friendly and professional. The villa’s view was stunning and the building architecturally beautifulZ Highly recommend this stay."
> **- Donnie Le (5/5/5)**

> "We had an unforgettable stay at the hillside  Villa Kalya! Perched high above the stunning landscape, the views were nothing short of spectacular. Each morning, we woke up to breathtaking sunrises and the gentle sounds of nature, making it the perfect retreat from our busy lives.  The private infinity pool was the cherry on top  swimming while taking in the incredible scenery was a dream come true!  The staff were exceptional, always exceeding our expectations with their warmth and attention to detail. Best part is my family loves to play Mahjong 🀄️ as part of our family activities even without proper table, staff manage to arrange for us, simply amazing. they were always there to help.  This hillside villa was the perfect getaway for our family, offering both relaxation and adventure. We can''t recommend it enough and can’t wait to return!"
> **- Patricia Ma (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/panacea-retreat-1.jpg','02 544 0162','51, 25, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.panacearetreatsamui.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.777+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.777+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/panacea-retreat-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/panacea-retreat-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6872400081199279129',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('pandanus-spa','standard','cmr07ihcc00l8q8xdnf1z7vc3','Pandanus Spa','## Top Reviews
> "Incredible spa. Tough to find a better massage/spa treatment on Samui. Sasi & Ben are amazing. Highly recommend"
> **- Peter Arm (5/5/5)**

> "I thought long and hard about how to describe it. I''ll keep it short: We''ve probably had over 100 massages at every opportunity. This one (Swedish / 90 minutes) was the best we''ve ever had. Simply fabulous. We immediately made another appointment. This time for a 90-minute aromatherapy massage. We''re looking forward to it!"
> **- Mark L (5/5/5)**

> "The options are numerous and the execution is truly outstanding. Everything is meticulously prepared and you are exceptionally well looked after. I''ve had many massages before, but I''ve never felt so relaxed afterward. Highly recommended!"
