INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('papillon-resort','standard','cmr07ihci00laq8xd1skpc1wl','Papillon Resort','## Top Reviews
> "We just left this sn amazing place !!! We stay two family in the family suite. We were looking for Thailand style resort , we find one !!! We had a wonderful stay at this hotel in Thailand and truly felt at home from the first day. The food was excellent — fresh, delicious, and with a great variety every day. Everything was beautifully prepared and full of flavor. The staff were outstanding: kind, attentive, and always smiling. They made us feel welcome and cared for, especially traveling as a family. This hotel is very family-oriented — comfortable, safe, and relaxed, with a warm atmosphere! The location is perfect: convenient, close to everything, yet peaceful and ideal for relaxation! Taxi service is available 24/7 We highly recommend this hotel and would happily return again! Valeria ypu did an amazing very welcoming place !!"
> **- Diana Drobchak (5/5/5)**

> "This resort is only looked after by one receptionist working and is very slow, my friend asked to see the 1,500 bht room and got shown the one for 2,000 when we went to pay we were confused and the owner came to say this is the wrong room for that price and the french old lady owner was sooo rude to us no customer service whatsoever when we said we did not want to pay that price and will go somewhere else, she called me strange to my friend, the receptionist kept my id card and told me to smile more. As managers ourselves if our reception staff made a mistake like this we would accept loosing 500bht in the name of customer service!! Absolutely poor customer service and buisness management especially leaving a receptionist incapable on her own."
> **- TuiNuy Monkey no.1 Thailand (1/5/5)**

> "Waste of money. It''s a very old resort, hardly any customers and the rooms lack of comfort. Door not close properly, therefore bugs inside. Bedsheets and towels worn out. For this price you get much better opportunities."
