> **- Digby Strong (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pis-premium-insurance-services-1.jpg','091 526 4241','124/16 Moo 1 Bophut, ตำบล บ่อผุด Koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/PremiumInsuranceServicesSamui/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.841+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.841+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pis-premium-insurance-services-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pis-premium-insurance-services-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16459449649121641325',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('pit-stop-bar','standard','cmr07ihe300lzq8xdckigfhtb','Pit Stop Bar','## Top Reviews
> "As a regular customer at The Pit Stop in Bangrak Beach, Koh Samui, I can''t say enough good things about this bar. The two-story layout offers a fantastic sea view from the top floor, providing a perfect spot to enjoy a game of pool and the cool breezes on hot days.  The staff at The Pit Stop is incredibly friendly and always goes above and beyond to make me feel at home. They serve super cold beers, which are perfect for enjoying while taking in the breathtaking views.  If you''re looking for a place to unwind and enjoy a drink with a view, The Pit Stop is the place to be. Whether you''re a regular like me or a first-time visitor, you''ll be sure to have a great time. Highly recommended!"
> **- Tony Jones (5/5/5)**

> "We had the best night with Barcycle Koh Samui Highly recommend , great people"
> **- Vanessa Baker (5/5/5)**

> "Had an awesome night out celebrating the sister in laws 60th birthday. Starting with a few games of pool upstairs and then on the bike we went The hosts were fantastic and even organized a birthday cake at one of the planned stops. Great night well worth doing"
> **- Jason Gill (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pit-stop-bar-1.jpg',NULL,'67, 15 Bangrak Reach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.843+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.843+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pit-stop-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pit-stop-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10447720017485246663',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('pizza-makmak','standard','cmr07ihe500m0q8xduisd0tgb','Pizza MakMak','## Top Reviews
> "I recently visited Pizza MakMak  with my friend and I have to say, it was one of the best pizza experiences I’ve had in a while! The crust was perfectly crispy on the outside and soft on the inside, with a wonderful balance of flavors in the sauce and toppings. They offer a great selection of pizzas, from classic margheritas to more unique and creative options.  The service was friendly and efficient, and the restaurant has a cozy, welcoming vibe. Pleasant place with perfect owner Bernard👌🏻delicious pizza and frozen limoncello . It’s a great spot for both a casual dinner or a gathering with friends. I highly recommend trying their ham  pizza and limoncello a must!  I will definitely be coming back for more. Highly recommend if you''re looking for quality pizza on the island."
> **- Maryanna Okhrimenko (5/5/5)**

> "Pizza by the slice that hits the spot.  I''m always wary of pizza in Asia but picture this - pizza by the Parthenon and also by the slice and you''ve got it here. Short stay, long stay, Take out?  It doesn''t matter.  The quality is worth it. Lemoncello too? Now I''m really back in Europe. Perfect for those days you need to have some familiarity."
> **- Doug Mackenzie (5/5/5)**

> "Bernard is a really nice owner and understands excellently how to treat customers and how to present the food. 😀"
> **- Dennis K. (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pizza-makmak-1.jpg','064 059 5557','124, 434 Thanon Had Lamai, Tambon Maret, Lamai, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/pizzamakmak',NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.845+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.845+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pizza-makmak-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pizza-makmak-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17529673133000366997',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('pizzeria-bellavita','standard','cmr07ihe800m1q8xdmp4oidjd','Pizzeria Bellavita','## Top Reviews
> "This place was genuinely so nice, the staff were so sweet, the food tasted absolutely amazing and came hot, we didn''t have to wait long. Overall would 100% recommend, it looks small from the outside but it''s really lovely inside and a peaceful little restaurant to sit in. we also got desserts (Italian cheesecake and apple pie) which were super delicious too."
> **- Monika Raisutyte (5/5/5)**

> "We watched a movie about an Italian restaurant and it got us salivating for some Italian food tonight. We literally nearly walked past the place, so slow down and make sure you don''t miss it. It is a gem! Pizza,  pasta and desserts were all sensational!! Finished with an Espresso ☕️. Thank you Bellavita... highly recommended."
> **- Tropicaltheo (5/5/5)**

> "Pizza was great! But I have had way better Tiramisu than this. Good ambience, staff were good, and good food.  Do ask the chef to understand what ingredients are there on the pizza as you might get confused."
> **- Manali Dev (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pizzeria-bellavita-1.jpg','081 296 9980','Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100092844150808','["Monday: 2:00 – 9:30 PM","Tuesday: 2:00 – 9:30 PM","Wednesday: 2:00 – 9:30 PM","Thursday: 2:00 – 9:30 PM","Friday: Closed","Saturday: 2:00 – 9:30 PM","Sunday: 2:00 – 9:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.848+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.848+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pizzeria-bellavita-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pizzeria-bellavita-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6212351952954463558',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('pizzeria-sorte','standard','cmr07iheb00m2q8xdnamp4ek4','Pizzeria Sorte','## Top Reviews
> "Very solid Neapolitan-style pizza spot in Koh Samui. From the moment you walk in you can see they take pizza seriously. The wood-fired oven is visible in the kitchen and you can watch the team preparing the pizzas fresh, which is always a good sign.  The pizzas were huge, much larger than expected. The dough had a nice airy crust with good charring from the oven, and the ingredients felt authentic and good quality. We tried the Napoli and the Diavola and both were very enjoyable. The tomato sauce and overall flavor could be slightly more intense or balanced, but overall it’s still a very good pizza, especially considering you’re on a tropical island.  The place itself is cozy and nicely decorated, with Italian flour bags on the walls and a relaxed dining atmosphere. Service was friendly and efficient.  Price-wise it’s a bit on the higher side for Thailand (around 400–420 baht per pizza), but the size definitely helps justify it.  Overall I’d rate it 8.5/10. A great option if you’re craving proper Neapolitan pizza while in Koh Samui."
> **- Alexander Cillan (5/5/5)**

> "I think this is one of the best Italian pizza places outside of Italy.  I can only review the food since I only ordered on delivery and never have been to the restaurant or ate at the restaurant.  The pizzas are incredible, taste like Italy and are all around amazing. I have tried 3 different pizzas across the menu: Diavola, Nduja and Mortadella e Straciatella.  I loved all of them. The dough is perfect, the ingredients taste Italian so I’m sure they are imported.  The crust is always perfect - the middle is a little weak after the delivery and I’m sure it’s because of the delivery.  This is the first time ever that I came from Grab to the Google page to review.  The only thing that made me a little unhappy is that the Nduja is used very economical and therefore the Nduja taste is not fully present. But this only a little note. All pizzas were tasting great and made me very happy."
> **- Fabian schär (5/5/5)**

> "Once a hidden gem- and now, one of the highly lauded, big names not to miss for the Neapolitan pizza lovers and fanatics on Koh Samui. The dough - all imported from Italy - was spot on, nicely executed and well prepared throughout all the different pizzas. Quality of the produce and ingredients are just as outstanding. Fresh, top-quality ingredients shine on every dish; although the tiramisu is not the best I''ve tasted, but their main show really are their pizzas. My personal pick would be the one with the sweet potato, and the other variation with green, pistachio paste. The pizzeria also serves calzones and incredibly refreshing salad options.  The restaurant features extensive beverage menus, as well as a comprehensive wine list.  Outdoor dining area also available.  The friendly and welcoming staff add a charming personal touch, as well as the hospitality from the owners who engage mostly in making the pizzas themselves.  A must try for all the pizza lovers when in Koh Samui. An establishment of true Neapolitan flavours proudly made by Thai hands."
> **- Wunda Stone (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pizzeria-sorte-1.jpg','097 939 9972','105 105, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://pizzeriasorte.com/bophut?utm_source=google&utm_medium=organic_gbp&utm_ca%20mpaign=bophut_branch','["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 1:00 – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 1:00 – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 1:00 – 11:00 PM","Friday: 1:00 – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 1:00 – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 1:00 – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.851+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.851+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pizzeria-sorte-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pizzeria-sorte-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13374061871836310877',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('pla-pla','standard','cmr07ihee00m3q8xdqtxwa0my','Pla Pla','## Top Reviews
> "The restaurant is located at the bottom of the resort at the beach level.  The best part of the whole experience was waiting in the top reception lobby with a breathtaking view (see image).  The service is exceptional as is the standard in the Four Seasons resort and as expected is also kept in the restaurant.  The staff was attentive and polite with meticulous setting of the table and serving us.  The presentation of the food and table setup were professional and elegant.  Sadly, the food itself was very disappointing and below our expectations.  The bread and spreas we got as the restaurant''s starter were ok, the breas felt not so fresh and stale / chewy.  We got a Wagyu salad starter which was nice and by far the best dish we had.  For mains we got the green curry with chicken and a club sandwich.  The curry was ok, nothing bad but we had much better curries in any of the modest family ran restaurants on the island that we visited.  The club sandwich was below our expectations for such a simple dish, it is not the local cuisine but you expect at least proper execution and fresh high quality ingredients especially when paying these prices. The bread felt cheap and rather dry, there was barely any sauce in the sandwich itself it was very dry. The french fries that were served with it felt stale and at best industrial from a bag.  It is not crazy expensive luxury dining but still given the reputation of the Four Seasons and very attractive low prices of food almost everywhere, it is hard to feel that it is not overpriced and under delivering for it''s cost."
> **- Ofri “HofLed” Herold (3/5/5)**

> "Food: Simple but well done. The burrata and the Dutch cocoa dessert especially stood out. Overall, better than flagship restaurants at the Four Seasons Whistler and Papagayo, which is already a high bar.  Service: Friendly and very attentive. The manager came out and checked in on us multiple times, and indulged our questions about the White Lotus shoot.  Atmosphere: Beautiful views, but since it is outdoors, there are a lot of bugs around sunset. The wonderful staff noticed me swatting them away and brought out some bug spray which really helped. They assured us the bugs would be gone shortly after sunset, and indeed they were gone."
> **- Shriraj Gandhi (5/5/5)**

> "Pla Pla is located in the four season which is beautiful and has the most stunning views and vibes. After a golf cart drive down you enter the restaurant and greeted with great service.  The menu had a solid balance of options i got the hummus and the pesto pasta which was great. The spaghetti ragu my cousin got wasn’t as good but besides that everything else was amazing. The shrimp starter was fresh and tasty with the sauce.  Overall was a great vibe and you can see the private beach the ocean and the pool area on the other side.  Definitely worth a trip for a fancy dinner or a cute lunch for a date as well.  the pricing wasn’t as bad as it could have been, which i was surprised about. roughly 1000baht a head minimum with starter and main."
> **- Jonathan Tuil (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pla-pla-1.jpg','077 243 000','219, Angthong, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.fourseasons.com/kohsamui/dining/restaurants/pla_pla/?utm_source=google&utm_medium=organicsearch&utm_campaign=tor-koh-fab-mid-seo-na&utm_content=na-na&utm_term=na','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifxh0027q8xde6xqk8o6','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.854+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.854+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pla-pla-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pla-pla-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2992580922129797546',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('planet-tacos','standard','cmr07iheg00m4q8xd3a4knmum','Planet Tacos','## Top Reviews
> "The food was so amazing I forgot to take a photo until halfway through my meal. We keep coming back here every time we are on Samui. The food is always outstanding and the young lady in charge of service is doing an amazing job. We will gladly be back next time."
> **- CH W (5/5/5)**

> "Went here for drink and food only, and it''s by far the best birria tacos I''ve had during my two years  and couple month in Thailand.  Young guys are brilliant💪. Sure They are fairly new to Thailand.  This is the first place in two years where tacos were really good, and tried numerous bars and restaurants and traveled a fair bit.  The owner (G) made me feel very welcomed and he was a great host. I only wished🙏 I''d found this place earlier .  Finally ,It was my birthday🎉🎊 that day, so I was very happy to be given a free food to take home. appreciate it😍!!  This is the Sunrise tacos samui!😍"
> **- Htun Zaw (5/5/5)**

> "Good as texmex goes Nice cheesy beef birria quesadillas & chimichangas  Pastor isn''t real pastor, skip the standard tacos and just order the texmex dishes  I''d give it 3.5 star for food but gave 4 because staff members were also nice  Would go back again but definitely not for tacos"
> **- Art Nuthariyatud (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/planet-tacos-1.jpg','061 673 8833','K131 209, 1st Floor, 209/1-2 หมู่ที่ 2 ตำบล บ่อผุด Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.sunrisetacos.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.856+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.856+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/planet-tacos-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/planet-tacos-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2835858762557563312',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('plunktone-cafe','standard','cmr07ihem00m5q8xd2oxhhcnz','PlunkTone Cafe','## Top Reviews
> "So glad I came here to eat and work! The place is a vibe. Tons of comfortable seating with outlets, cold AC, great WiFi, food and service. The lunch set with lentil cutlet was flavorful and a great value. The cottage cheese pancakes and coffees were also unique and delicious. After walking down the deserted street I was a little skeptical and even thought they were closed because the door was locked, but you use another door that looks like another place. I stayed for several hours, hardly anyone else was inside. Good peaceful environment!"
> **- Shannon Daly (5/5/5)**

> "Had a wonderful breakfast at Plunktone Café. The place has such a beautiful ambience with stunning views that make the whole experience even more special.  We ordered an omelette and a crepe, and both were absolutely delicious, fresh, flavorful, and perfectly prepared. What truly stood out was the warm hospitality. The staff was polite, attentive, and very courteous."
> **- Srishti Narula (5/5/5)**

> "Overall, everything was excellent. From the first visit, I really appreciated the variety and unique styles of food and drinks. The staff were well-trained, attentive, and provided great service throughout.  One small suggestion would be to consider having a designated smoking area. It would be nice for guests who prefer to sit outside to enjoy the atmosphere without losing their appetite due to cigarette smoke."
> **- Thitaphas K. (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/plunktone-cafe-1.jpg','092 828 8532','3 148 หมู 2 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://plunktonecafe.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.862+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.862+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/plunktone-cafe-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/plunktone-cafe-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5730901964877008326',NULL,NULL);
