> "Good advice"
> **- Alexandre Rosada (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pool-shop-1.jpg','+6677374599','44/34-35 Moo 1, ตำบล แม่น้ำ Koh Samui, Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 AM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.864+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.864+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pool-shop-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pool-shop-2.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pool-shop-3.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3925129917748582134',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('popsmile-nathon','standard','cmr07iher00m7q8xd4uc0fkmq','PopSmile','## Top Reviews
> "My son forgot his retainer while on holiday. We got a new one made as he couldn''t manage without one. It took one week which was fair however it cost 6000 baht (very expensive but we needed it so paid). Day of collection we advised the orthodontist we were on the way to collect it (via hotel reception). When we arrived just the receptionist was there, tried it retainer on it was too loose!! We left without complaining as there was no point, its not like they could make another retainer. A waste of 6000 baht. Would not recommend this orthodontist, very disappointing"
> **- Christina X (1/5/5)**

> "So happy I found this place! We went to the hospital because I was in pain with my wisdom tooth. They charged 1500 baht just to confirm I was right and offered me a appointment in 5 days(!) With costs of 10.000 baht! Because I couldn''t wait that long we were searching for a dentist the day after and found this office- lucky! They offered me an appointment on the same day! Of course I was scared as an foreign having a surgery in an other country- but the Dr. Was soo patient with me, and so lovely! She explained everything and helped me with my breathing to relax. She also did an amazing job, it was fast and without any pain! The total cost was like 3000 baht? Nothing in compare to the hospital! Friendly stuff, just awesome :)! Totally recommend it!"
> **- Michelle Lang (Shelly) (5/5/5)**

> "Had some issues with my teeth towards the end of my trip to Thailand. PopSmile provided very quick, easy, professional and friendly service. Thank you so much for your help!"
> **- Manuel Baumgartner (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/popsmile-nathon-1.jpg','093 581 5876','43/12 ถ. ทวีราษฎร์ภักดี Tambon Ang Thong, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 11:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 1:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ig1d003gq8xdfxkqj28w','cmr07ig1h003iq8xdb1g9nifo','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.867+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.867+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/popsmile-nathon-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/popsmile-nathon-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8135956938612087680',NULL,NULL);
