INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('posh','standard','cmr07ihex00m9q8xdm1s6mkvk','POSH','## Top Reviews
> "Amazing! We had such a lovely day!  So relaxing, chilled and nice. It was great to have a private boat experience, not having to visit the islands with loads of other people.  Being able to chill out and sunbath on deck, drink fresh coconut and eat fresh fruit in the sun, dive off the boat in the middle of nowhere, eat on a private jetty for lunch.... Yes it is relatively expensive, but it a extremely nice treat!  That said, there were 4 of us and if you paid for a individual trip on a tourist boat you would pay a fair bit and it would be nowhere near as nice! Well worth it!!"
> **- Martyn Symes (5/5/5)**

> "Great company, the tour was excellent! The boat was in reasonable condition, provided good shade and also great spots to lay down and chill out. We had two kids also and the driver and guide were excellent with them both! Great day out. Many thanks to Alain and the team!"
> **- Jason Edmunds (5/5/5)**

> "Fantastic day with the team from Posh.  From pick up through to dropping us back at our Villa everything was superb.  The crew looked after us all through the day and were helpful and knowledgeable.  Excellent lunch, quiet time to relax on secluded beaches and/or explore if the mood takes you.  Well done POSH, highly recommended.  Thank you"
> **- Mark Barlow (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/posh-1.jpg','095 503 6526','91, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://poshsamui.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.873+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.873+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/posh-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/posh-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2421474645136327415',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('power-bear-tattoo','standard','cmr07ihez00maq8xdm9gfjm4t','Power Bear Tattoo','## Top Reviews
> "An exceptional artist with world-class freehand skills. Powerbear didn’t just tattoo me — he brought my entire sleeve vision to life with precision, creativity, and absolute mastery. He guided me on what ideas would work best and seamlessly incorporated them onto the hand, making the design flow perfectly. His work ethic, patience, and attention to detail are on another level, and the care he puts into every line truly shows. If you’re looking for a top-tier tattoo artist in Koh Samui, I highly recommend Powerbear without hesitation."
> **- Krishneel Charan (5/5/5)**

> "I had my first Tattoo by Anan last year. I asked for a Penguin, in memory of my best friend who passed away, and it was absolutely perfect! 🐧🖤  I came back this year and asked for another Penguin, and a cover up of two old tattoos and I am so happy with it!  Anan''s line work is absolute precision, and the shading looks really cool. I want sleeve eventually, but have to come to Samui every time so Anan can do it!"
> **- Daniel Carberry (5/5/5)**

> "One of the best tattoo parlour I’ve been to. Clean, professional, precise. Really good people. Kap 🙏🏾"
> **- Brooke Isaac (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/power-bear-tattoo-1.jpg','081 060 9767','166, 29 หมู่ที่ 2 ตำบล บ่อผุด Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 2:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 2:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 2:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 2:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 2:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 2:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 2:00 PM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.875+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.875+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/power-bear-tattoo-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/power-bear-tattoo-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7840530763127240126',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('power-buy-central','standard','cmr07ihf200mbq8xd38ay36n6','Power Buy @ Central','## Top Reviews
> "Huge choice of products. The store is well organized, spacious, and easy to stroll in. Besides the AC works fine ;-) I didn''t really need any help or service as I had my mobile with me and could check specs and prices on google shopping. Bottom line: good store delivering what it is expected to."
> **- Dan M (4/5/5)**

> "terrible service!! to the point where we don’t want to buy anything because we don’t want to give them commission. From the moment u walked in, it felt like we were intruding them. We were looking for speakers, no assistance, just glares as they watch us struggle to connect device to our phone. One speaker in particular we were looking for but it wasn’t working, it took the sales person a good 10 minutes to realize it wasn’t broken just not charged and when he realized battery is out, just said “yeah battery die” and walked away… i had to ask him to charge it or find a another device so we can hear sound quality but they are less than interested in helping."
> **- Ari (1/5/5)**

> "Good sized store with big range of products,not the cheapest place to buy. Air conditioning was nice.  Nit served once while in the store for 20 minutes despite picking up products and looking for help. All major brands here"
> **- Matthew Hansen (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/power-buy-central-1.jpg','065 510 7296','209 209/1-2 ตำบล บ่อผุด Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,2.9,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.powerbuy.co.th/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.878+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.878+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/power-buy-central-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/power-buy-central-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10261589234296350438',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('pp-samui-tennis-padel-shop','standard','cmr07ihf400mcq8xdtziwto41','PP Samui Tennis & Padel Shop','## Top Reviews
> "As someone who plays tennis almost every day, I’m quite picky about my equipment. I’ve trusted this shop with my rackets many times, and the results are always outstanding. Consistent tension, professional workmanship, great advice, and friendly service. My rackets have never played better. Highly recommended to any tennis player in Samui! 🎾🔥"
> **- Shalom Sharabi (5/5/5)**

> "This store operates with the spirit of a big family; they are the best at what they do, offering the best stringing services, the best equipment, and the best prices. They are extremely honest, extremely fast, dedicated, and above all, they support the tennis community. They have been sponsors for many consecutive years without asking for anything in return. Without asking for anything in return, not even advertising, they do everything anonymously, discreetly, and with good intentions. Our dear friend, the owner, Mr. Pupa. He is an incredibly kind, helpful, honest, cheerful, and polite person; worth getting to know."
> **- Rodrigo Souza Pinto (5/5/5)**

> "Best shop on the island. I came one time to buy new racket string few months ago. They strung my racket perfectly and gave me some advices."
> **- julian renard (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pp-samui-tennis-padel-shop-1.jpg','085 956 6598','4, 4, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.1,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 10:00 AM – 7:30 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 7:30 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 7:30 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 7:30 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 7:30 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 7:30 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 7:30 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.880+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.880+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pp-samui-tennis-padel-shop-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pp-samui-tennis-padel-shop-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11077527567670083668',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('prana-resort-nandana','standard','cmr07ihf600mdq8xdbccsdmr4','Prana Resort Nandana','## Top Reviews
> "We had a wonderful stay at Prana Resort Nandana. The hotel is beautiful, clean, and relaxing, with great facilities and a lovely beach atmosphere.  A special thank you to James and Ton at the reception who were incredibly kind, professional, and always ready to help with a smile. They made everything easy for us, from check-in to recommendations around the island.  Also, Benz at breakfast was amazing—so warm, attentive, and friendly every morning. He made sure everything was perfect and started our day with great energy.  All three staff members were wonderful and truly made our stay special. We would definitely love to come back and highly recommend this resort to anyone visiting Koh Samui!"
> **- Anna Bendavid (5/5/5)**

> "We had an incredible stay at this hotel! If you’re traveling with a child but still want a relaxing, high-end experience, this is the place to be.  The Pool & Bar: The swimming pool area is a dream. It was the perfect setup for relaxing with our kid—safe, clean, and very inviting. The pool bar was a major highlight; the drinks were fantastic, and the service was quick, making it way too easy to spend the whole afternoon lounging by the water.  Location & Convenience: Having direct beach access made our mornings so much easier. We loved being able to hop between the ocean and the pool without any hassle.  Exceptional Service: What truly blew us away was the service. The staff is attentive and goes above and beyond. They even arranged a rental scooter for us on the spot, which was delivered directly to the hotel. It saved us so much time and effort!  Bottom Line: Great vibes, seamless amenities, and a staff that genuinely cares. We’ll definitely be back!"
> **- thiru N (5/5/5)**

> "I recently stayed at Prana Resort Nandana in Koh Samui, and it was an exceptional experience from start to finish.  Location: Perfectly situated on Bangrak Beach, just 10 minutes from the airport and close to Fisherman’s Village. It offers a peaceful retreat while still being accessible to local attractions.  Rooms: Spacious, modern, and immaculately clean. The beds were incredibly comfortable, and the air conditioning worked flawlessly. I especially appreciated the pool-access rooms, which made mornings feel indulgent and relaxing.  Facilities: The resort boasts two beautiful pools, including an infinity pool overlooking the beach. The spa and fitness center are well-maintained, and the beachfront restaurant is a highlight.  Dining: The food was consistently excellent, with a wide variety of Thai and international options. The happy hour cocktails were a fun bonus, especially enjoyed by the pool.  Service: The staff were warm, attentive, and genuinely committed to making the stay memorable. They went out of their way to accommodate requests and even surprised us with thoughtful touches during our visit.  Overall: Prana Resort Nandana is ideal for couples, families, or anyone seeking a tranquil yet well-connected stay in Koh Samui. The combination of location, facilities, and service makes it a resort I would happily return to."
> **- Vinoy Parakunnil (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/prana-resort-nandana-1.jpg','077 246 362','14, T. Bophut, 3, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.pranaresortsamui.com/','["Monday: 12:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Thursday: 12:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Friday: 12:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Saturday: 12:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Sunday: 12:00 AM – 11:30 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.882+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.882+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/prana-resort-nandana-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/prana-resort-nandana-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1983469678091890464',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('prasuthon','standard','cmr07ihf800meq8xdjkzdla2n','Prasuthon','## Top Reviews
> "Quality & Trust  Can’t be more pleased by the level of service and professionalism: We actually had a first experience that left us disappointed and explained it by sending an email. They emailed us back and asked for a second chance and because we were around for an event, we decided to go back again. We were greeted by the Manager “K. Joe” who gave us, with the staff, one of the most fabulous experience we’ve had in our stay. They made sure everything was right on for us from beginning til the end, and gave us a 5 star experience which we will remember. The food was great with GREAT selection of desserts.  I think the chef also came to apologize and made us feel appreciated.  This level of customer service was inspiring and should be shared because it’s not very present in Samui. We will gladly come back for more!"
> **- William Santoni (5/5/5)**

> "Delicious, vegan and vegetarian friendly, amazing view and excellent staff.  We stayed in the hotel for a few days and the staff remembered us and our diet restrictions.  The English of some of the staff is not perfect but they will always make it work and understand your request.  Prices of food are on the medium $$ end, beverages are a little expensive mostly with the alcoholic drinks and wines are too expensive.  Lovely vegetarian massaman curry, vegan Pad-Thai and smashed potatoes with tofu 🤤💛🙏🏽 oh and a few days a week they have live music and fire shows, watch out for those, they are really good!  Thank you again for the lovely experience ✨"
> **- Carla Carolina (5/5/5)**

> "Tasty food with a view. Complete menu with plenty of dishes to choose from. Thai or international options. Pasta was great and served in good portion. Average pizza dough, could have been better... Staff is attentive and polite. The restaurant is quiet and right in front of the beach. Pizza+pasta, 520THB. You cannot bit that view!"
> **- Carl Wallington (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/prasuthon-1.jpg',NULL,'G3WG+36C, Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.samuirestaurantguide.com/prasuthon7/','["Monday: 6:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Tuesday: 6:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Wednesday: 6:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Thursday: 6:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Friday: 6:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Saturday: 6:00 AM – 9:30 PM","Sunday: 6:00 AM – 9:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.884+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.884+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/prasuthon-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/prasuthon-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9921236154742222075',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('prego-italian-restaurant','standard','cmr07ihfb00mfq8xdu5l33iwh','Prego Italian Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "It''s been a long time since my last visit to the restaurant, probably 5-6 years or more. I''m glad we decided to come here for my friends’ last night on the island, as we enjoyed a great meal and a good time with superb service from the entire staff. We were well taken care of by Khun Karen, who was our main host for the night. Everyone who passed by our table checked in to ensure we had a wonderful time. The staff even recognized me even though it''s been a big while. Such warm and thoughtful service—I only wish I could have visited Prego more often in the past. Thanks to the whole team, from kitchen to the front, for such a great evening. We’ll definitely come back more often."
> **- pasruji poolsavasdi (5/5/5)**

> "We visited Prego around 6PM on a Sunday. It was a nice, relaxed time for an early dinner, so we were quickly seated in the comfortable air-conditioned section. ​A huge shout-out to our server, Ms. Aor 🏆💯 Before even offering the menu, she thoughtfully asked if we had any food allergies or dietary restrictions, which made us feel incredibly well taken care of from the start! She was friendly, attentive, and gave excellent recommendation. The Aperol Spritz was excellent and served in a much larger glass than other restaurants—definitely a win! We loved the complimentary bread, followed by our choice of appetizers calamari and arancini, which arrived fresh and hot. The Slow Roast Pork and Spaghetti Bolognese were both delicious and very generous portions. We were so full by the end that we had to skip dessert! Great food, wonderful service, and a lovely atmosphere. We''ll definitely be back."
> **- Lj Francisco (5/5/5)**

> "Lovey, the service was impeccable and very high quality - made you feel special. The food was delicious, the problem was choosing something off the menu because I wanted to order 5 different dishes they all looked so good. Also great gluten free options for my sister. I would love to come back  and try more. Aor also provided lovely friendly service with a great smile and that always makes the experience even better 😊"
> **- Carmen Golder (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/prego-italian-restaurant-1.jpg','077 300 317','Chaweng Beach, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://prego-samui.com/?utm_source=google&utm_medium=gmb&utm_campaign=aps&utm_content=home','["Monday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 12:00 PM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.887+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.887+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/prego-italian-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/prego-italian-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=776695141634929891',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('prima','standard','cmr07ihfd00mgq8xdqwwrpciq','Prima','## Top Reviews
> "amazing !!!"
> **- Benoit Asselin (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/prima-1.jpg','099 407 3146','G3J6+89V, Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.primagold.co.th/',NULL,'cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.889+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.889+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/prima-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/prima-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7999792476252505775',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('prime-burger-central','standard','cmr07ihff00mhq8xdjldppc22','Prime Burger @ Central','## Top Reviews
> "● June 2026 ● 4 Stars 🌟🌟🌟🌟 We went again to have a burgur fix here. Great service and burgers 🍔  definitely worth coming. We tried tiramisu but not a fan unfortunately. We''ve had better and home made one. So ... yes to burger and fries but not tiramisu. Thank you.  ● May2026 ● 4 Stars 🌟 🌟🌟🌟 We drove pass this burger joint and decided to give it a go.  When it said 100% Australian beef, I got excited. Lived there over 15 years and have been on a hunt for good burger 🍔 in Ko Samui. It tastes good, very familiar beef patty taste. Good service, speak very well English and friendly staff.  One star down only because I feel like the patty is little under seasoned, just a bit more touch of salt and pepper would bring out more flavor of the beef but I was quite happy with this meal. Fries 🍟 as Aussie calls chips was good too, thin and crunchy just the way we like it.  Would we come back? Yes, we would 👍 freshly ground beef everyday and they have daily promotion as well. Double burger was quite big but I finished it. Thank you for your service."
> **- Onnida T (4/5/5)**

> "I was really craving a burger and this one totally met my expectations. The ingredients and sauce were very flavorful, and the fries were super crispy. The service was great and the food came out really quickly.  Try the Stockholm and the Paris — both are really good."
> **- Guadalupe Martinez Lamas (5/5/5)**

> "Ohhh Boy! Talking about a good old smash burger with the outside being crispy and the burger being juicy! Big mention to their fries too! For once it fell like it wasn’t about these dull fries that you always have in other places. Simple menu, all burgers are the same price and the only difference is whether you choose to have a single, double, or Triple burger! 🍔 My 2 boys tried to follow their Daddy with the double even though it was the size of their faces! Guess who came after them to finish them up …."
> **- Felix Shuttleworth (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/prime-burger-central-1.jpg','080 089 6846','167, 12, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://primeburgersamui.com/','["Monday: 12:00 PM – 3:00 AM","Tuesday: 12:00 PM – 3:00 AM","Wednesday: 12:00 PM – 3:00 AM","Thursday: 12:00 PM – 3:00 AM","Friday: 12:00 PM – 3:00 AM","Saturday: 12:00 PM – 3:00 AM","Sunday: 12:00 PM – 3:00 AM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.891+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.891+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/prime-burger-central-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/prime-burger-central-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14457763468444815418',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('prime-burger','standard','cmr07ihfi00miq8xdqcw1yj1l','Prime Burger','## Top Reviews
> "Good quality smash burger with good flavor selection! Not the best one you’ll have but it’s worth the calories 😉 I’ve had the one with pineapple which was interesting to try, but it was supposed to be spicy but it didn’t so the flavors were not fully hitting the spot. Their truffle sauce is really good tho so I recommend getting that one. Fries were really good!"
> **- MH (4/5/5)**

> "Yep that’s me again! Different location same result! I like the one in Fisherman’s village better than the one in Chaweng, although they have the same taste. But the one in fisherman’s village has a more cozier vibe to it and fits the environment perfectly. The service is great too and the staff are attentive. I had the Paris Burger this time because it was the only one that comes with bacon. The other ones don’t but you can still add on top to it for an extra. Again, the fries are just great and reminds me of those from Burger King -> that’s really a compliment by the way"
> **- Felix Shuttleworth (5/5/5)**

> "Like a smash burger. Many options with daily specials. They will customize a burger to your liking. Their prime sauce is mayo and ketchup.  I ordered a single Stockholm which I couldn’t finish; I added caramelized onions, which were black, and they still included the red onion. Overall i thought my burger was overcooked, it looked like the smashed edges were burnt, not bursting with flavor. He ordered a modified New York double which he hoovered down! I guess Ketchup fixes all!  Large order of sweet potato fries perfect for two people Caesar salad was really a small side for one person. The milk shakes, yum! We had a caramel and an Oreo shake, such a sweet change from an alcoholic cocktail! 😉  We spent between 600-800THB each. They do accept credit cards."
> **- Kele Coloma (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/prime-burger-1.jpg','094 695 8187','Thanon Bo Phut Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'http://primeburgersamui.com/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.894+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.894+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/prime-burger-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/prime-burger-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7300492209589246804',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('psylo','standard','cmr07ihfk00mjq8xdkpi5e8wv','Psylo','## Top Reviews
> "Fantastic shop with original, unusual and very high-quality items. A must-visit every time I''m on holiday in Samui. It takes a toll on my budget. But "
> **- jacques (5/5/5)**

> "Cool boutique shop with alt clothing. Cool designs outside and funky clothes....."
> **- Paul (5/5/5)**

> "Come and meet Edward, what amazing experience of  buying some of the most amazing type clothes. The service was the best ever. Clothing that I have never ever seen in Australia. It was a pleasure to meet you Edward and have that golden service"
> **- Stephen Todarello (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/psylo-1.jpg','077 256 157','167 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, District, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://psylofashion.com/pages/chaweng-koh-samui-thailand','["Monday: 12:00 – 11:30 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 11:30 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 11:30 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 11:30 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 11:30 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 11:30 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 11:30 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.896+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.896+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/psylo-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/psylo-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6980859395980566350',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('pui-relax-restaurant-bar','standard','cmr07ihfl00mkq8xdn72xbpqd','Pui Relax Restaurant & Bar','## Top Reviews
> "Flavourful, freshly cooked Thai cuisine. We were in Samui for 5 days and we probably ate here 3 to 4 times. Incredible food each time, lovely service, and plenty of vegetarian options. I especially loved the crab salad and the stir fried morning glory. 10/10 recommend."
> **- Riddhi L (5/5/5)**

> "My friend and I ate here twice while staying nearby in Koh Samui. Highly recommend everything we had: papaya salad, broad noodles (drunken noodle), pineapple fried rice, steamed fish with soy/ginger. They give you a little fruit dessert plate at the end of the meal. CASH ONLY"
> **- Jane Lee (5/5/5)**

> "Visited here for the first time and need to tell you that the customer service was brilliant, not only friendly staff but quick and professional service and super tasty food.  Portion sizes were just on point and they way  how they delivered it was amazing.  One of the best local places around the area"
> **- Zimi Brown (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pui-relax-restaurant-bar-1.jpg','087 896 6357','63/148-149 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/puirelax','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifsv000nq8xdrwnu123q','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.897+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.897+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pui-relax-restaurant-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pui-relax-restaurant-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7801962250682635012',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('pulse-clinic','standard','cmr07ihfn00mlq8xd4tq43xuu','Pulse Clinic','## Top Reviews
> "I went there for the first time today to have a check-up as they’re currently running a promotion. I was given a very warm welcome and received excellent advice. I’d recommend everyone to pop in here. Top-notch service"
> **- cha.meleon743 (5/5/5)**

> "I recently visited Pulse Clinic for a health check-up. Being a foreigner, I was worried about the language barrier and explaining exactly what I needed.  However, the staff was incredibly professional and patient. They used translation apps to communicate and made sure they understood my specific request perfectly.  I was pleasantly surprised by the service and their support! The clinic is clean, discreet, and very efficient. I felt safe and understood. Highly recommend to anyone, especially expats or tourists who need peace of mind. Thank you!"
> **- Sergey K (5/5/5)**

> "I had a fantastic experience at Pulse Clinic on Koh Samui. From the moment I walked in, I was impressed by the clean, modern, and welcoming environment. There was no waiting time, which made the whole visit incredibly efficient and stress-free.  The staff were exceptionally professional—knowledgeable, approachable, and discreet. I really appreciated how they took the time to listen, making me feel both understood and respected throughout the entire process.  Pulse Clinic offers a very comprehensive range of services, and it’s clear that they prioritise both quality and confidentiality. It’s a great comfort to know a clinic like this exists on the island. Highly recommended!"
> **- Vanessa M (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pulse-clinic-1.jpg','083 904 2826','14, 51 4171, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.pulse-clinic.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 1:00 PM, 2:00 – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: Closed","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 1:00 PM, 2:00 – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 1:00 PM, 2:00 – 6:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 1:00 PM, 2:00 – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 1:00 PM, 2:00 – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 1:00 PM, 2:00 – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07ig1d003gq8xdfxkqj28w','cmr07ig6y005pq8xd4jrvheih','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.899+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.899+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pulse-clinic-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pulse-clinic-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2858544062172566096',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('punch-it-gym','standard','cmr07ihfq00mmq8xdi5duczr7','Punch It Gym','## Top Reviews
> "If you’re visiting Koh Samui, you should definitely try this at least once. It was an amazing experience and one of the best ways to start the day. The training is suitable for both beginners and people with experience in other martial arts. The coaches are professional, and everyone is very friendly and supportive. Highly recommended!"
> **- LxT LxTze (5/5/5)**

> "I started Muay Thai training with Coach Four, and I had no previous experience or knowledge at all. From day one, he has been incredibly patient, professional, and supportive. He knows how to explain techniques clearly and effectively, making it easy to learn and improve. What I appreciate most is how attentive he is—he quickly identifies weaknesses and knows exactly how to help strengthen them. I’m very happy with my training and the progress I’ve made with him. I’m usually not someone who sticks to going to the gym or training regularly, but thanks to his motivation and guidance, I consistently make it to training once or twice a week. He’s simply an outstanding coach. Highly recommended!"
> **- נטלי קדיש (5/5/5)**

> "I’ve been training Muay Thai since 2 weeks straight, in different parts of Thailand and must say, this one was my least fave one! It’s nothing against the gym/coaches itself, because everything is fine but I prefer a smaller, less crowded, more family vibes kind of Muay Thai training. I was at a group class with around 20 people. And usually I had max 6 other people joining a class. But the gym is clean, price is also super okay 400 baht for a group session of 1,5 h. They even have a little shop and a cafe there. It’s nice just not for me."
> **- Anita B. (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/punch-it-gym-1.jpg','061 661 5161','Maret, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.punchitgym.com/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 7:45 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 7:45 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 7:45 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 7:45 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 7:45 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 7:45 PM"]','cmr07ifuo0015q8xdfahzrsp4','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.902+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.902+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/punch-it-gym-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/punch-it-gym-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16086883954664192956',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('pure-vegan-heaven','standard','cmr07ihfs00mnq8xdr3h2m2j7','Pure Vegan Heaven','## Top Reviews
> "🌿✨ One of the best vegetarian restaurants on Koh Samui!  The food was absolutely incredible. The Smokey BBQ Bowl with Jackfruit was packed with flavor and perfectly balanced, and the Gluten Free Veggie Wrap was fresh, delicious, and surprisingly satisfying. And Cutest pancakes 🥞🥰💚  Everything tasted healthy without sacrificing flavor. The atmosphere is peaceful and cozy, and the staff are genuinely kind and welcoming.  A true vegetarian gem that even non-vegetarians will love. We can’t wait to come back! 🥹🌱🙏🏼"
> **- Elvira (5/5/5)**

> "Part of a chain with locations across Thailand. I’ve eaten at one of their other locations previously and the taste and presentation were very consistent. The offering is mostly western, bowls and sandwiches and some dishes with an American Mexican flair. The food feels clean, healthy and tasty, although really not overwhelming in any way. Extra points for being 100% vegan. Definitely recommended if you are around Lamai, but I wouldn’t make a special trip if elsewhere. Serving sizes are very generous, and prices although a little high, feel average for Koh Samui."
> **- Guy Braverman (4/5/5)**

> "Pure Vegan Heaven is an absolute must-visit! We had an incredible meal where every dish felt like a curated experience. The Food: The Burmese salad and tacos were standout stars—each bite was a complex, rich explosion of flavor. Also the waffles were divine. The Drinks: Their Kefir was refreshing and tangy, hitting just the right spot, and the coffee is excellent. Between the creative menu and the quality of the ingredients, this spot is a total gem. Already our second time here"
> **- Timon Koths (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pure-vegan-heaven-1.jpg','097 279 5769','131/1 Thanon Had Lamai, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: Closed","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.904+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.904+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pure-vegan-heaven-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/pure-vegan-heaven-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6179824989637758064',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('put-auto','standard','cmr07ihfu00moq8xdmbt0s2mz','PUT Auto','## Top Reviews
> "Exceptional Service at Put Auto – Highly Recommended!  I first stopped by Put Auto when my motorbike chain needed oil. Without hesitation, one of the crew grabbed the lubricant, tipped my bike to the side using his knee for balance, and sprayed the chain—all within two minutes.  A month later, I returned with a loose chain. Once again, the team sprang into action, adjusting everything necessary to get it back in perfect working order. They refused to charge me for the service, and their courtesy and professionalism stood out.  Just a few weeks ago, I found myself in the same situation. Without delay, they tightened the chain, and I was back on the road in under two minutes.  The staff at Put Auto, including the boss, are not only skilled but genuinely friendly. Their commitment to customer service is exceptional. While tips aren’t required, I consider it a privilege to show my appreciation for their outstanding work.  If you’re one of the many people scooting around Lamai Beach during high season, I highly recommend Put Auto for any servicing needs. The shop is run with efficiency and care, truly embodying the ‘Land of Smiles’ spirit."
> **- Nomadic Lotus (5/5/5)**

> "I had a fantastic experience at this motorcycle repair shop in Thailand! The mechanics are knowledgeable and really know their stuff. They serviced three of my bikes quickly and efficiently, and the prices were fair for the quality of work. Highly recommend for anyone needing reliable service! 👍🇹🇭"
> **- Tijat Pongsanmoon (5/5/5)**

> "If you’re a foreigner they will charge you 3 times more than a Thai. They’re so many better places for repairs in Samui than here."
> **- Joe Joe (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/put-auto-1.jpg','096 694 7389','36/6 ถ. ทวีราษฎร์ภักดี Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifui0012q8xdzn158clv','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.906+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.906+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/put-auto-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/put-auto-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2310992465541892487',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('queen-bee-nail-and-eyelash-chaweng','standard','cmr07ihfw00mpq8xd17tvy3fb','Queen Bee Nail And Eyelash','## Top Reviews
> "I got a french gel nail manicure at the start of our holiday and then a refill at the end of our holiday and both times the result is so beautiful. The ladies are so nice and talented. It took only an hour to do the whole set including filing old nails off. The price is also very affordable. Definetely coming here when we come to Koh Samui again. :)"
> **- Inka Borenius (5/5/5)**

> "I was there to do my nails, since they looked terrible. The employees were so kind and didn’t judge me for my short nails. After I showed them my inspirations and ideas for designs, they immediately agreed to do it. The service was fast, but very clean and professional. I’m very thankful, for what they have done and I would always come back and I can just tell you, that you have to go there. The 5/5 stars are well deserved. ❤️"
> **- Grell Sutcliff (5/5/5)**

> "Best manicure and nail art I’ve ever had! I went to the salon near fisherman village. Staff speak very clear English and completely exceeded my expectations. Exceptional attention to detail. Cuticles never looked better. Thank you so much. Worth the $and time."
> **- Michelle Bowden (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/queen-bee-nail-and-eyelash-chaweng-1.jpg','065 393 7192','45/1 moo1, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://queenbeesamui.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.908+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.908+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/queen-bee-nail-and-eyelash-chaweng-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/queen-bee-nail-and-eyelash-chaweng-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9074418580640560117',NULL,NULL);
