INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('rapheephan-clinic','standard','cmr07ihg800muq8xd4wezjd1a','Rapheephan Clinic','## Top Reviews
> "I really enjoyed my visit to this clinic , I was here today. I did the tests recommended by the doctor, and everything was smooth and comfortable. The doctor was very attentive, kind, and approachable , it was easy and pleasant to communicate with her.  I also used a Russian interpreter, which made the appointment even more convenient and clear.  Overall, it didn’t feel like a typical medical visit, but more like a place with genuine care and warmth. It’s rare to feel this way, not like you’re in a hospital, but somewhere people truly want to help ❤️"
> **- Darth Vader (5/5/5)**

> "I had the most wonderful experience with Rapheepan Clinic throughout my entire pregnancy and delivery.  Dr. Rapheepan guided my pregnancy from the very beginning, and I always felt safe, supported, and truly cared for. She is calm, highly professional, and very confident in her decisions — which gave me so much trust during such an important time in my life.  My labor was extremely long — 35 hours of contractions — and it was not easy. With another doctor, I am quite sure I would have ended up with a C-section. But Dr. Rapheepan gave me the opportunity to continue naturally. She monitored everything carefully, supported me patiently through the process, and when necessary, we made the decision to break my water. Thanks to her experience and steady guidance, I was able to give birth naturally.  I am deeply grateful for that.  Now I happily bring my daughter for regular pediatric checkups at the clinic as well. It feels comforting to stay with the same team who supported me throughout my pregnancy journey.  Highly recommended for any mother looking for professional care with genuine heart and dedication. 💛"
> **- Airgym Family (5/5/5)**

> "I have been going to this clinic for over 4 years, Dr Rapheephan delivered my daughter in 2023 with a natural (zero intervention birth -due to my demand) at Koh Samui Hospital in less than 8 hours.  They have helped me with multiple appointments at the government hospitals to see different specialists as well.  They are true professionals, with rich experience and most honest opinions and recommendations."
> **- Katalina Matus (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rapheephan-clinic-1.jpg','077 950 757','111 Moo 1, Nathon Tambon Ang Thong, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.rapheephanclinic.com/','["Monday: 12:00 – 1:00 PM, 5:00 – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 1:00 PM, 5:00 – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 1:00 PM, 5:00 – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 1:00 PM, 5:00 – 8:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 1:00 PM, 5:00 – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 1:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 1:00 PM"]','cmr07ig1d003gq8xdfxkqj28w','cmr07ig1h003iq8xdb1g9nifo','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.920+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.920+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rapheephan-clinic-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rapheephan-clinic-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5204622293908118069',NULL,NULL);
