> "I have been going to this clinic for over 4 years, Dr Rapheephan delivered my daughter in 2023 with a natural (zero intervention birth -due to my demand) at Koh Samui Hospital in less than 8 hours.  They have helped me with multiple appointments at the government hospitals to see different specialists as well.  They are true professionals, with rich experience and most honest opinions and recommendations."
> **- Katalina Matus (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rapheephan-pediatrist-1.jpg','077 950 757','111 Moo 1, Nathon Tambon Ang Thong, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.rapheephanclinic.com/','["Monday: 12:00 – 1:00 PM, 5:00 – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 1:00 PM, 5:00 – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 1:00 PM, 5:00 – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 1:00 PM, 5:00 – 8:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 1:00 PM, 5:00 – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 1:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 1:00 PM"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ig1h003iq8xdb1g9nifo','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.922+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.922+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rapheephan-pediatrist-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rapheephan-pediatrist-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5204622293908118069',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('raya-spa-by-sereeya','standard','cmr07ihgb00mwq8xdtif3il3u','Raya Spa By Sereeya','## Top Reviews
> "Very professional massage with a serene environment. Just wow! We started with a Roselle herbal tea, then we were walked up our massage room. There is a toilet in the room, we had to wash our feet and put on a robe. The masseuse was so good! It was pretty strong, just what I needed. They did back, shoulder and head massage for me. After we got hot ginger tea and some fresh fruit. Definitely a five star!!"
> **- Lexi Randazzo (5/5/5)**

> "I had an absolutely wonderful experience at Cave rai ra beach spa. The ambiance was serene, the facilities were spotless, and the massage was incredibly relaxing. It’s the perfect place to escape the hustle and bustle of the city."
> **- KEERADA (5/5/5)**

> "The massage was amazing! My wife and I went with our kids (aged 3.5 and 5); we did 90 minutes while the kids had a 60-minute session. The place looks like something out of a fairytale, a pleasant cave with cozy rooms and fragrant waterfalls.  The staff was highly professional, and the kids had a blast (they even got temporary tattoos!). To top it off, we were served tea and watermelon on a comfy sofa at the end.  The prices are affordable and fun is guaranteed for the whole family. Highly recommended!"
> **- Ron Vaisman (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/raya-spa-by-sereeya-1.jpg','077 429 700','Choengmon Beach 89 Aura Villa Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.muangsamui.com/royalmuangsamuivillas/wellness/cave-rai-ra/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.923+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.923+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/raya-spa-by-sereeya-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/raya-spa-by-sereeya-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8879011108443681596',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('rc-construction-island','standard','cmr07ihgd00mxq8xdtajdtb9q','RC Construction Island','## Top Reviews
> "serious company, quality work and very good follow-up.  Highly recommended"
> **- Laurent Olliver (5/5/5)**

> "This is a highly experienced and honest construction company on Koh Samui. They complete their work meticulously, on time, and provide excellent customer service."
> **- Lang Promjan (5/5/5)**

> "A reliable company, always available even after construction for follow-up. I highly recommend them!"
> **- Pascale (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rc-construction-island-1.jpg','+66892106079','12, 59, Tambon Mae Nam, Maenam, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/RC.ConstructionIsland/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.925+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.925+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rc-construction-island-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rc-construction-island-2.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rc-construction-island-3.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rc-construction-island-4.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10616869854883316009',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('red-elephant','standard','cmr07ihgg00myq8xdhdeiplz5','Red Elephant','## Top Reviews
> "Chill casual beach bar and restaurant on Lamai beach. You can sit on the beach in the comfortable bean bags or inside at the upstairs restaurant. Food was good and reasonable prices. There’s also a swimming pool and towels available at no extra charge. Friendly staff and quick service. Enjoyed it."
> **- City of Angels (5/5/5)**

> "Great service on the beach. Matthew is a star. WiFi. Free pool. Beach bean bags. Service to your bean bag. Often a DJ there. Great tunes. Sometimes fire shows as well."
> **- Richard Lycett (5/5/5)**

> "This place has it all! From the moment you walk through the big front doors you are greeted by a beautiful ocean view, ocean breeze and some perfect tunes. The food and beverages were delicious. I don’t drink alcohol but everything I ordered was affordable and freshly made. The staff is so cool. You have options of inside or outside dinning. I couldn’t choose because there were both gorgeous ❤️. I sat on the comfy bean chairs by the beach. You don’t like the sand, NO Problem! They have a pool and a wash off station which is perfect for cleaning up before you hit the road. Be sure to check them out if you’re in Lamai, Koh Samui . Check out the full video on Tik Tok ❤️ Always tip your servers, they work so hard to please you. Can’t wait to return next year!"
> **- Babie L M (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/red-elephant-1.jpg','065 236 4388','109 12, 109, 12 ตำบล มะเร็ต อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://redelephantsamui.com/index.html',NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.928+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.928+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/red-elephant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/red-elephant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12238647869986075201',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('red-fish-restaurant','standard','cmr07ihgi00mzq8xd6iuvnrny','Red Fish Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "I can really recommend the food. It was prepared very nice and the tasting, especially of the fish, was fantastic. Yes, you can get yor dinner cheaper somewhere else, but for me it was it worth. Also the Mango sticky rice, yummy!"
> **- Dirk L. (5/5/5)**

> "I think it is a bit overrated and overpriced. I went for seafood set A, and I can''t say anything too much special about it. Fish and prawns were even slightly overcooked, to my mind. Seeing the rating I expected something better than average, but you can for sure find same options in quality for a lower price in other places. Besides, when ordering seafood in such a place I would at least expect lemon water or aroma tissues to be offered by default."
> **- Tatiana Sergienia (3/5/5)**

> "A stylish Thai and seafood restaurant with quality ingredients, food, wine and professional service. We simply love the baked sea bass with vegetable fried rice, which goes perfectly with a dry Chardonnay. The service is excellent and the atmosphere is so beautiful and stylish that you feel like you are in any 3-star Michelin restaurant, the only difference is the lower prices."
> **- Timea Ivančová (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/red-fish-restaurant-1.jpg','081 979 5371','155, 4 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Koh Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://chawengregent.com/dining-resort-samui/red-fish-restaurant/','["Monday: 3:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 3:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 3:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 3:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Friday: Closed","Saturday: 3:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 3:00 PM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.930+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.930+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/red-fish-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/red-fish-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3371259318603847917',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('red-fish','standard','cmr07ihgl00n0q8xdywtq4nqv','Red Fish','## Top Reviews
> "I can really recommend the food. It was prepared very nice and the tasting, especially of the fish, was fantastic. Yes, you can get yor dinner cheaper somewhere else, but for me it was it worth. Also the Mango sticky rice, yummy!"
> **- Dirk L. (5/5/5)**

> "I think it is a bit overrated and overpriced. I went for seafood set A, and I can''t say anything too much special about it. Fish and prawns were even slightly overcooked, to my mind. Seeing the rating I expected something better than average, but you can for sure find same options in quality for a lower price in other places. Besides, when ordering seafood in such a place I would at least expect lemon water or aroma tissues to be offered by default."
> **- Tatiana Sergienia (3/5/5)**

> "A stylish Thai and seafood restaurant with quality ingredients, food, wine and professional service. We simply love the baked sea bass with vegetable fried rice, which goes perfectly with a dry Chardonnay. The service is excellent and the atmosphere is so beautiful and stylish that you feel like you are in any 3-star Michelin restaurant, the only difference is the lower prices."
> **- Timea Ivančová (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/red-fish-1.jpg','081 979 5371','155, 4 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Koh Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://chawengregent.com/dining-resort-samui/red-fish-restaurant/','["Monday: 3:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 3:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 3:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 3:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Friday: Closed","Saturday: 3:00 PM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 3:00 PM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.933+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.933+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/red-fish-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/red-fish-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3371259318603847917',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('red-moon','standard','cmr07ihgo00n1q8xd2e0vzzji','Red Moon','## Top Reviews
> "The owner/chef greet us with a big smile at the entrance. He was welcoming and made us feel like home straight away. The food was amazing. He made me on request the beef caparcio burrata full of flavor even half portion was enough. My husband got the deal of the day and had green seafood curry and was also super rich and delicious. We got free dessert (fried ice cream) and some drink for free as it was our honeymoon. Definetly one of the best experience we got in Koh Samui. If you are French the guy will chat with you all night, being from Nice himself. Go check it out"
> **- Sabrina Roussel (5/5/5)**

> "Restaurant looked lively, good background music. We opted for the Thai 390 thb fixed menu with a starter and a main. Overall: Bland. Nice presentation. Spring rolls were deep fried and overly crispy, so much so that they were tough to bite and even tougher to cut with a knife. I don’t think we’ve ever had a spring roll wrapper like these. Chicken satay was four nice size skewers but on the dry side; the “peanut sauce” was not. Was very thick and had no peanut flavor even through it looked like it was filled with bumpy bits. Pad Thai was average, nothing special.  Chicken with cashew not very exciting. Staff spoke English. They accept credit cards, you have to go up to the bar to pay with a card. All in all, even tho the restaurant is across the road from us, we’ll probably walk over to the Night Market for more flavorful Thai dishes."
> **- Kele Coloma (3/5/5)**

> "We had the prawn tempura, chicken satay, Thai mussels, beef/duck panang and a pasta dish. Starter and main for 390B.  Excellent food with real high quality ingredients and fantastic customer service.  Lots of great food spots in Koh samui and this is definitely one worth visiting for some authentic Thai food."
> **- Daniel Edney (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/red-moon-1.jpg','061 262 6141','12 Moo 1 Thanon Haad, Fisherman village, เทศบาลนครเกาะสมุย Suratthani, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 12:00 – 11:30 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 11:30 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 11:30 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 11:30 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 11:30 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 11:30 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 11:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.936+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.936+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/red-moon-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/red-moon-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15067349247591874705',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('remax-island-real-estate','standard','cmr07ihgq00n2q8xdfbes7xmx','Remax Island Real Estate','## Top Reviews
> "I had a very positive experience renting a villa through RE/MAX. The entire process was smooth, professional, and stress-free from the beginning. The agent Ms. Gem was extremely attentive to every detail and always responsive whenever I needed assistance or had special requests.  What I appreciated the most was the ongoing support even after moving into the villa, anytime I need help or have a question, I can always reach out and receive prompt assistance. It really made me feel taken care of as a tenant.  I highly recommend RE/MAX to anyone looking for reliable and professional real estate services."
> **- Violeta Martinkė (5/5/5)**

> "I entrusted my land for sale to Khun Anda, and the transaction was completed successfully and smoothly beyond my expectations. From the very beginning until the final closing, she demonstrated exceptional professionalism, integrity, and dedication. Her expertise in the market, strong negotiation skills, and attention to every detail truly impressed me. Khun Anda is not only highly knowledgeable and experienced, but she is also incredibly supportive and attentive. She kept me informed throughout the entire process and handled everything with confidence and care, making what could have been a stressful experience feel effortless and secure. I wholeheartedly and confidently recommend RE/MAX on Koh Samui. Without a doubt, this is one of the finest real estate companies on the island. Their service standards are outstanding, their team is professional, and their results speak for themselves. If you are looking to buy or sell property on Koh Samui, I strongly encourage you to work with RE/MAX. You will be in the best possible hands. Truly exceptional service, remarkable expertise, and an overall five-star experience from start to finish. ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐"
> **- Nongthanasaran Chotiwararan (5/5/5)**

> "Very professional and reliable real estate agency in Koh Samui. Great service, honest advice, and strong local market knowledge. Highly recommended."
> **- Paul Fitzpatrick (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/remax-island-real-estate-1.jpg','+66800410420','1, 39 Thaweerat Phakdee road, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://buysamui.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.939+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.939+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/remax-island-real-estate-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/remax-island-real-estate-2.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/remax-island-real-estate-3.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/remax-island-real-estate-4.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17584390879469291475',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('renaissance-banana-leaf','standard','cmr07ihgt00n3q8xdiqv9czmr','Renaissance Banana Leaf','## Top Reviews
> "Delicious food! Courteous and attentive service and pleasant setting. We were guests of the resort but highly recommend dining here even if you aren’t staying at the resort. Wonderful traditional Thai dishes. Thank you go Saii, Aum, and Woody for a lovely and delicious dining experience :)"
> **- Karlee Osman (5/5/5)**

> "We had breakfast at Banana Leaf every morning and had the pleasure of being looked after by Aod, Peace, Ningz, Faii, Palm and Tan during our five-day stay, and I truly can’t speak highly enough of them. Every single morning at the breakfast buffet, they greeted us with genuine warmth and kindness that never felt forced or routine.  What stood out most was their attentiveness. They remembered our preferences from the very first day—how we liked our coffee, or where we preferred to sit. It made each morning feel personal and welcoming, rather than just another hotel breakfast. Their care went beyond simple service. They were always one step ahead—clearing plates promptly, offering refills without being asked, and checking in just enough to make sure everything was perfect.  Over the course of five days, their consistency never wavered. Their positive energy, professionalism, and genuine hospitality made a lasting impression and truly elevated our overall experience at the Renaissance Koh Samui.  A heartfelt thank you to all of them for making our mornings something to look forward to. They are a credit to the hotel and a perfect example of what outstanding service is like.  Sincerely, Grace and Carmen"
> **- Chacha Laicha (5/5/5)**

> "Another great Restaurant at the Renaissance. Breakfast is served here, wich is amazing and the variety second to none. I also like it during hot days to enjoy a air conditioned meal for lunch when the pool bar is just too hot 😀 It also has great offers and events for the evenings. What is standing out at the Renaissance overall is the customer service and this goes without saying also for the Banana Leaf. Thank you Saii & Team!!!"
> **- M. G. (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/renaissance-banana-leaf-1.jpg','077 429 300','208/1 Moo 4, Laem Nan Beach, Lamai, T, Tambon Maret, Koh Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.renaissancekohsamui.com/','["Monday: 6:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 6:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 6:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 6:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 6:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 6:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 6:30 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.941+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.941+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/renaissance-banana-leaf-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/renaissance-banana-leaf-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6501766244823352135',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('renaissance-resort','standard','cmr07ihgv00n4q8xdgo2rfmgk','Renaissance Resort','## Top Reviews
> "3 nights at Renaissance Koh Samui Resort & Spa with our wife and toddler daughter, coinciding with my wife''s birthday, and the team delivered an exceptional experience from end to end. Pre-arrival, Hana from the Delighted to Serve team coordinated every detail across multiple emails: airport transfer with a baby seat, bottle steriliser in the room, hot water for formula, restaurant suggestions, local sightseeing guidance. Nothing felt like an effort.  The birthday setup in the room with the decoration and complimentary cake was a lovely touch. Alice gave us a warm and efficient check-in. The Lamai Beach setting is beautiful, and the resort blends relaxed island energy with Marriott service standards very well. The rooms were spacious and the spa was luxurious.  Highly recommend for families travelling with young children. Would return without hesitation. Special thanks to Hana, Sandy, and Alice."
> **- Abhijit Roy (5/5/5)**

> "What an absolutely incredible experience it was staying at Renaissance.  From the very first step out of our transport, we were welcomed with genuine warmth and comfort by the front desk and concierge team. Even though our room was not quite ready at check-in, the staff made sure we were comfortable and well taken care of within the premises. It immediately set the tone for the rest of our stay.  Everything throughout our visit was exceptional. The cleanliness of both our room and the entire property was immaculate. What truly elevated the experience were the little details. The team remembered our names, our morning coffee orders, and greeted us every single day with such sincerity and warmth. It made the entire stay feel incredibly personal and precious. A special thank you to Director Chin for ensuring our stay was nothing short of impeccable. To Lexi, thank you for the amazing recommendations and for making every conversation so easy and enjoyable. Alice, your attentiveness to every inquiry from check-in to our final moments did not go unnoticed. Bes, thank you for arranging all of our transports and excursions so seamlessly. Barry and Pook from the concierge team made every arrival and departure effortless, always ready to help with our bags and anything we needed.  To the F&B team, Ningz, Odd, the breakfast chefs, and the wonderfully funny Woody, thank you for making every morning something to look forward to.  To The Spa team, Pin for the amazing, absolutely best massage I’ve had in Thailand. And the Ploy for amazing morning stretching classes that boosts my energy during the stay.  And of course, to the unsung heroes in housekeeping and by the pool maintenance who kept our room spotless every single day, your hard work truly made a difference.  I am so sorry I cannot name everyone, but please know each of you contributed to making this stay so special.  From the beautiful design inspired by the old Siam era, to the flowers and trees thoughtfully maintained throughout the property, everything carries a unique charm. It may not be the most ultra modern resort, but it is by far one of the most unique and character filled stays we have ever experienced. If you appreciate rustic elegance and heritage inspired design, this place is truly magical.  This stay has completely raised my expectations for hospitality. What started as a perfect experience somehow ended even better than perfection.  We will absolutely be back."
> **- Akira Na Thalang (5/5/5)**

> "Our stay at Renaissance Koh Samui Resort & Spa was truly out of this world. Everything was absolutely beautiful, and what impressed us the most was the staff — their kindness, dedication, and level of care were unlike anything we have experienced before. A huge thank you to the entire team for making our stay so special.  The hotel is right on the beachfront, and we stayed in a beachfront villa with direct private access to the beach, which made the experience even more incredible. The room was spotless, and the bathroom in the villa was simply stunning — truly beyond words.  The pool was fantastic, the cocktails were excellent, and we highly recommend the spa program and massages. Dinner at the restaurant with the sunset view was amazing and one of the highlights of our stay. The only thing we found a bit average was the breakfast, but everything else was exceptional. All in all, a wonderful experience and a hotel we would absolutely recommend."
> **- Aleksandar Tasic (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/renaissance-resort-1.jpg','077 429 300','208/1 Moo 4, T. Maret, Lamai Beach, ตำบล มะเร็ต Koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.marriott.com/en-us/hotels/usmbr-renaissance-koh-samui-resort-and-spa/overview/?scid=f2ae0541-1279-4f24-b197-a979c79310b0',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.943+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.943+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/renaissance-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/renaissance-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11519271760306551367',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('replay-residence-pool-villa','standard','cmr07ihgx00n5q8xdxuuiyt4d','Replay Residence & Pool Villa','## Top Reviews
> "Smoothies are sold at the bar by the pool on your site for 90 baht. However, these smoothies are made with very little fruit and lots of ice and syrup.  These syrups, left in the sun, undergo a chemical reaction and pose a major health risk. I request that the use of these syrups be stopped immediately. I kindly request that management pay attention to the health of your guests."
> **- A S (1/5/5)**

> "I got here 1 year ago and everything was cool. But since then, the gym has fallen to pieces and nobody cares. Glass doors get smashed and don’t get replaced for weeks. The gym doesn’t get cleaned including the floor it’s dirty. The small sauna still works, I guess that’s cool but needs a good scrub 🧼 location is epic ! Love the location . Seems like they keep the pool clean and the tennis court . I love replay but replay doesn’t love me 😂"
> **- luke schembri (2/5/5)**

> "We''re staying at the Replay Pool Villa which is just across the street from the Replay Residence, but you have access to all the facilities that Replay Residence offers (gym, pool). The private villas are very modern and have their own private pool and lounge area which is very nice. The seaview never gets old, and the staff clean the room daily. I got this off AirBnB for a better price than Booking (almost have price!). Loving the life here."
> **- Michael Cebreiro (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/replay-residence-pool-villa-1.jpg','077 246 388','199, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.1,0,0,0,NULL,'https://replayresidence.site/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.945+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.945+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/replay-residence-pool-villa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/replay-residence-pool-villa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=18410322565361574567',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('restaurant-bali','standard','cmr07ihgz00n6q8xd6l5tg7tl','Restaurant Bali','## Top Reviews
> "Great restaurant! . The most delicious and high-quality meals I’ve had on my trip to Asia. If you haven’t tried them yet, you must try the doner, lahmacun, and ayran. They all taste exactly like the traditional versions. This restaurant offers all of the following at once:  High-quality food Great taste and flavor Very friendly service Generous portions Affordable prices  Thank you so much! Best of luck with your business!"
> **- E İyi Madem (5/5/5)**

> "When U arrive and the first taste you get is from homemade bread, you already feel right, then a wonderful turkish owner says hello, you like oookay.. so i took the iskender kebap to eat at home and it was delicious , there is only ine real kebap in samui for me.. now its two 🥰❤️👊👊👊 and i love his rosasted onions on top"
> **- Dennis Gluska (5/5/5)**

> "This place is amazing! 🤩 The food is very fresh and everything is homemade. They make their own bread and cook the meat and chicken perfectly. 🥖🍗 The portions are very big (even 400gr) you can eat a lot of delicious meat here! 😋  My favorite is the chicken sandwich. It is so tasty! 😍 Also, the small french fries (matchstick fries) are legendary. I can’t believe how such a small place makes such great food. 🍟✨  Note: Only cash is accepted here. 💵 You should definitely try it! ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐"
> **- Büşra Beşiroğlu (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/restaurant-bali-1.jpg','091 164 1421','Thanon Bond Kai, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.instagram.com/hamurkohsamui','["Monday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.947+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.947+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/restaurant-bali-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/restaurant-bali-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17315537153548023074',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('revo-podcast-studio','standard','cmr07ihh500n7q8xdvz6fsw34','Revo Podcast Studio','Discover Revo Podcast Studio, a premier local services located in Plai Laem, Koh Samui. Find reviews, hours, and contact information.',NULL,NULL,'H38M+99H, 45 ตำบล บ่อผุด, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,0.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.revostud.io/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifv2001aq8xdag7cvjgf','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.953+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.953+00:00',NULL,'https://maps.google.com/?cid=5189592856677118929',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ribbon-brand','standard','cmr07ihh800n8q8xdntwmij85','Ribbon Brand','Discover Ribbon Brand, a premier for kids located in Chaweng, Koh Samui. Find reviews, hours, and contact information.','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ribbon-brand-1.jpg','080 878 8591','ชั้น 2 BigC, super store, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,0.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.ribbonbrand.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.956+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.956+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ribbon-brand-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ribbon-brand-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14013404783648652632',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('rice-x-de-pier','standard','cmr07ihhb00n9q8xda42ha12t','Rice X De Pier','## Top Reviews
> "Loved this Italian Restaurant in Fisherman’s Village looking out onto the beach. The entry is quietly low key but you can watch pizzas go into the stone fire oven. The hostess was so gracious and welcoming.  Nice vibe!! Background music was perfect volume. Lighting set a relaxing ambiance. Big menu with good variety of Italian food including steaks, lobster and some Thai  dishes. We had a burrata pizza, pasta bolognese and pasta Aglio Olio all of which had so much flavor, they were Delicious! Portion size was enough to fill you up. We will definitely go back for more!!"
> **- Kele Coloma (5/5/5)**

> "Restaurant team especially p’tum was amazing!! Great View next to the fisherman village pier! Food was good but great cocktails which i loved the most!!!  Come with your date won’t be disappointed."
> **- Rp Riawpai (4/5/5)**

> "It was a beautiful place with an amazing view. The staff were very friendly, and our waitress, Tum, was especially sincere and kind. The food was also delicious."
> **- Renanah Kramer (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rice-x-de-pier-1.jpg','077 430 680','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.ricexdepier.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.959+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.959+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rice-x-de-pier-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rice-x-de-pier-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11810209782896490653',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('rice','standard','cmr07ihhh00naq8xdv2bzwqol','Rice','## Top Reviews
> "Cracking little restaurant with what looks like has a boutique hotel attached. Lovely and clean inside with attentive staff. Nice menu with a mix of Italian dishes and Thai dishes. The kids were supper happy to find an authentic pizza after ten days of Thai food. The Thai green curry and cashew chicken were fantastic. Very well priced and the 99bhat happy hour cocktail was a nice surprise."
> **- Fabio Vincenti (5/5/5)**

> "Had such a wonderful dinner at Rice on my 2nd night during my stay at Jalmin hotel. The staff made us feel right at home and they were super helpful, making sure we had plenty of space and never felt rushed.  The food was great and their homemade pizza was a highlight as well as their extensive cheese and cold cuts selections. We had tried a few different dishes like the rack of lamb, pesto spaghetti and tuna salad, and every bite was packed with flavour throughout the dishes.  The restaurant also houses extensive selections of wines and bar beverages.  The atmosphere and ambiance is thoughtfully decorated with Thai motifs and elements, featuring extensive teak furnishings and panels throughout the interiors. The setting is stylish and relaxed. If you''re on Koh Samui want a memorable Italian and Thai cuisine with warm service, this place is absolutely one of them."
> **- Wunda Stone (5/5/5)**

> "If you’re in Chaweng and craving amazing food, you have to try Rice Restaurant.  This place is not just about authentic Thai cuisine — it’s a perfect mix of Thai and Western favorites, making it ideal for every type of traveler.  From the moment you walk in, the vibe is warm, relaxed, and welcoming. But the real highlight? The food. Every dish is packed with flavor — from rich Thai curries and spicy Tom Yum to delicious pasta, spaghetti, and freshly made pizza. Whether you’re in the mood for Thai or something more familiar, they do both incredibly well."
> **- RE/MAX Island Real Estate (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rice-1.jpg','063 267 5920','Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://jalmin.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.965+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.965+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rice-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rice-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13750104560901490948',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('risto-luca','standard','cmr07ihhj00nbq8xd4nil4mci','Risto Luca','## Top Reviews
> "Poor and expensive. Staff were friendly but my dish tasted funny and when the bill came they had charged us 80 Bhat for bread we didn’t even order or want. It’s also noisy. Will deffo not be back. Roma is much better (and better value)"
> **- David shearer (2/5/5)**

> "We had a fantastic experience here. The food was outstanding and truly authentic – you can really taste the quality in every dish. The service was top-notch as well; the staff is incredibly friendly, attentive, and welcoming. A special shout-out goes to the Italian espresso – without a doubt the best I’ve had on Koh Samui! If you’re looking for genuine Italian cuisine and wonderful hospitality, this is the place to be. Highly recommended!"
> **- Angelo Palmitessa (5/5/5)**

> "Took my daughter out for an Italian today, she loves Spaghetti.  This restaurant is one of those unexpected little gems that just surprises you with the quality of the food.  If you are in Samui, and fancy an Italian, then don’t go anywhere else. This seriously was awesome.  I love pizza, this was hands down the best pizza I’ve had for a very long time.  Will be a regular treat for me now.  The only thing I would like to see, is maybe a small kids menu as the portions are far too big for kids, but they will box up any left and explain how best to reheat as well. 😉"
> **- Kevin H (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/risto-luca-1.jpg','098 518 4681','39 6 ตำบล บ่อผุด Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/ristoluca71/','["Monday: 1:00 – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 1:00 – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 1:00 – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 1:00 – 11:00 PM","Friday: 1:00 – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 1:00 – 11:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.967+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.967+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/risto-luca-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/risto-luca-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=846523861903015025',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('rockbar','standard','cmr07ihhm00ncq8xdhhmuk6cv','Rockbar','## Top Reviews
> "A really cool place. I didn''t try the food but enjoyed a cold beer and the relaxing atmosphere. Music was great. Lots of seating and at different levels, each turn revealed a surprise. The staff were a bit too cool for school and seemed very indifferent as to whether you stayed or left. This was the only downside."
> **- Barry Musgrave (5/5/5)**

> "The Rock Bar in Koh Samui offers a charming seaside experience with great hospitality and a relaxed atmosphere. The fried rice was well-prepared, and the banana with coconut milk made for a delightful local dessert. Combined with the scenic ocean views and calm setting, it’s an excellent spot to unwind and enjoy authentic Thai flavors. Highly recommended for travelers seeking a serene dining experience by the beach.  Rastafari Vibes!!"
> **- Modern Nomads (5/5/5)**

> "The best bar in Koh Samui! ☀️ What can we ask for more? You have the view, the wonderful drinks and food, the good music and the kindness of the owners 🥰 You can only feel relaxed when you’re in there, so natural and beautiful"
> **- Tiffany Ponsot (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rockbar-1.jpg',NULL,'92 84310 126/92 Moo 3 Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 11:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.970+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.970+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rockbar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rockbar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2673705013495027412',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('rockestra-music','standard','cmr07ihho00ndq8xdkyr5x43r','Rockestra Music','## Top Reviews
> "Beautiful selection of guitars, basses, keys and various other instruments. Top notch service and knowledge from the staff. They sell and also rent for short term use, which was perfect for my video shoot. Can’t say enough nice things about this shop and the staff!"
> **- Dave Menzo (5/5/5)**

> "This is the best music store in Samui. A very wide selection of products. Thank you very much 🙏"
> **- BLVCK JESUS / MJ MARLEY (5/5/5)**

> "professional musical instrument store where you will find guitars, keyboards, drums and anything you need from musical instruments. good and friendly service and a very wide range to choose from.  I recommend this store👍"
> **- Evgeniy Dobryanskiy (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rockestra-music-1.jpg','095 359 5988','24 แม่น้ำ 53 ถ. ทวีราษฎร์ภักดี Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 10:00 AM – 7:30 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 7:30 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 7:30 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 7:30 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 7:30 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 7:30 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifso000kq8xdfe9gpaon','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.973+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.973+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rockestra-music-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rockestra-music-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1826592982827931742',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('rockys-boutique-resort','standard','cmr07ihhr00neq8xdcxgdz9h3','Rocky''s Boutique Resort','## Top Reviews
> "We had a perfect stay at Rocky’s. The staff was very helpful and willing to help us with everything. The room left us speechless, as they gave us an upgrade. We stayed in a sea view room, with shared private pool, with all the necessities. We were lucky to be there in a Saturday and we booked the dinner by the sea activity. The food was very good, varied, and the evening included a fire show that amazed us. The massage was very relaxing and the ladies took care of us, to be an unforgettable experience. Overall, choosing Rocky’s boutique resort was the best ideea. Definitely recommend to book some nights there when in Samui."
> **- Ioana Dit (5/5/5)**

> "This is a fantastic resort, do yourself a favour and book your holiday here! We brought our 19 month old daughter and had an amazing time. The pools are great, the staff are friendly, our room was cool and spacious, the resort’s beach is great for adults and children. We liked that the beach and pools had shade to sit in. The staff are happy to organise anything you need such as a hire car, transfer, tour, activity. Our food was included with our package and was delicious. We also enjoyed the cocktail night and beach fire show. We loved that the resort was big enough that it had everything we needed, but small enough that it really was boutique and not overcrowded. Thank you Rocky’s for a truly memorable and enjoyable trip. We wish we had stayed longer than a week!!!"
> **- Claire H (5/5/5)**

> "We were lucky enough to book one of the beach view rooms with plunge pool and it was incredible! We loved the small private beach for relaxing and enjoying the beautiful sunrise and sunsets. The rocky scenery is so unique and beautiful. We read some reviews saying you couldn''t swim but we swam every day and it was beautiful. We also took out the kayaks they have for free and really enjoyed exploring the coastline around the area. The food at the restaurant is great and we also liked exploring outside the hotel around the grandfather rocks area which is walkable. Would absolutely stay again!"
> **- Bec Kilpatrick (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rockys-boutique-resort-1.jpg','077 332 888','438, T, 1, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.rockyresort.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.975+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.975+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rockys-boutique-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rockys-boutique-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=861385187080568873',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('roestiland','standard','cmr07ihhu00nfq8xdwz2e0qgg','Roestiland','## Top Reviews
> "It was truly a wonderful evening, filled with warmth and comfort — it felt like we were spending time among close friends. The atmosphere in the restaurant is incredibly cozy and inviting, perfect for relaxing and enjoying every moment.  The Swiss barbecue was absolutely fantastic: there was a great variety of dishes, and every single one of them was delicious. Everything was prepared with care and attention to detail.  We visited with my husband and daughter, and we were all absolutely delighted — with the food, the service, and the overall experience. This is definitely a place we would love to come back to again and again!"
> **- Hanna Immega (5/5/5)**

> "Had a meal at this perfect location. Everything on the menu looked great,  so I went for a recommendation from Thomas the owner. I''m moving to Koh Samui soon and this will definitely become a regular spot."
> **- Shahin Farjami (5/5/5)**

> "The food at Rostiland was pleasing to the palette.  However, we were taken back by the attitude of the owner when we were asking questions and ordering food.  My partner asked if we could share the raclette and the owner was flabbergasted that we would even suggest that we would share a meal.  We have been travelling for well over two months and we typically share a meal as we find the portions are generally too large.  He went on about  a portion is a portion and that is how we should order it, a portion for my partner and a portion for myself, or a meal apiece.  My partner than asked about sharing a different meal, the meat loaf, and would that be suitable to share.  At that point the owner asked if the sharing of meals was a financial issue.  What a rude, unacceptable thing to say to a paying customer.  The cost of the meal has never been the problem but rather portion size.  We felt extremely insulted by his accusation of it being the cost of the meal, not the fact that too large a portion is a waste of food.  The meat loaf, which we did share was very tasty, but I believe the owner should be careful with his accusatory statements."
> **- Steve Dempsey (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/roestiland-1.jpg','061 118 6732','Maret, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://noxamasamui.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.978+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.978+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/roestiland-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/roestiland-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15713714927372956411',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('royal-beach-boutique-resort','standard','cmr07ihhx00ngq8xdneo87r4l','Royal Beach Boutique Resort','## Top Reviews
> "We were very dissatisfied with our hotel in lamai so we saw a deal for this hotel and decided to drive up to check it out. Mint met us and was more than happy to show us around and answer any questions. she also showed us the room we would get if we booked. she provides the best customer service we received this whole trip! So, we ended up booking for 3 nights and was very happy with the cleanliness, the amenities and the views. the included breakfast is also very good. The only 2 cons would be the beach: its nice to look at but it is not a swimmable beach.but lamai beach is only 5mins drive. the gym needs more weights and newer cardio equipment. The best thing about this place was the customer service. we were very impressed."
> **- Shar (4/5/5)**

> "We booked a proposal package including four nights at this hotel – and it was simply perfect.  The entire team, including the manager, was exceptionally friendly, warm, and always helpful. We were especially impressed by the proactive support and flexibility in planning the proposal. My ideas were brought to life with great attention to detail and even exceeded our expectations.  The stay itself was also excellent – everything was comfortable and always clean. The staff was so lovely all the time!  We highly recommend this hotel!"
> **- Jonas Urbonait (5/5/5)**

> "Great of you wish a relaxing and on budget resort. Staff was more than 5 stars, incredible service. Sunrise can be seen from the beach. Pool area is usually pretty quiet and one can make the most of it since it’s a boutique resort with not a lot of guests. Bathrooms could use a little modernist touch up, but other than that, it was a perfect stay ☺️."
> **- Luana Maia (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/royal-beach-boutique-resort-1.jpg','077 418 080','438, Lamai, 2, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.royalbeachsamui.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.981+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.981+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/royal-beach-boutique-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/royal-beach-boutique-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16811852430127360449',NULL,NULL);
