> **- Luana Maia (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/royal-beach-weddings-1.jpg','077 418 080','438, Lamai, 2, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.royalbeachsamui.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.983+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.983+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/royal-beach-weddings-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/royal-beach-weddings-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16811852430127360449',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('royal-king-international-suits','standard','cmr07ihi200niq8xd1zr2340b','Royal King International Suits','## Top Reviews
> "I recently had a suit tailored and was thoroughly impressed with the quality of service. The customer service was knowledgeable, quick, and highly professional throughout the entire process.  Having the suit made was effortless, and the tailor guided me smoothly from start to finish. The materials used were first-class, and the final result exceeded my expectations.  I can highly recommend this tailor to anyone looking for exceptional craftsmanship and a seamless experience."
> **- Juuso Lehtinen (5/5/5)**

> "We were looking for a Tailor to create something bespoke and special for an up and coming important occasion for my wife.  plenty of Tailors to choose from on Koh Samui but after looking around we were drawn into Royal King. Turned out to be a very good decision. excellent service, a very fast turnaround and the quality of the dress is excellent. when changes to the design were asked for nothing was a problem. let s hope it brings her good luck at the dog show this week!"
> **- Tim Grimshaw (5/5/5)**

> "Couldn’t be happier with my experience at this bespoke tailor shop. At 6''5"
> **- Balram Sidh (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/royal-king-international-suits-1.jpg','085 061 0697','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.tripadvisor.com/Attraction_Review-g676072-d11903724-Reviews-Royal_King_International_Suits-Chaweng_Bophut_Ko_Samui_Surat_Thani_Province.html','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.986+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.986+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/royal-king-international-suits-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/royal-king-international-suits-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14318564828465093225',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('royal-muang-samui-villas','standard','cmr07ihi400njq8xdtcocl9q4','Royal Muang Samui Villas','## Top Reviews
> "Outstanding service and exceptional people  I would like to express my sincere appreciation for the amazing team, especially the manager of the Mars Restaurant and Catch from the reception. The manager of Mars Restaurant is an absolute professional – attentive, well-organized, and always present on the floor. You can clearly see the passion and dedication put into both the service and the team. Everything runs smoothly, the atmosphere is welcoming, and guests feel truly taken care of. It’s rare to see such strong leadership combined with genuine kindness.  Catch from the reception is equally impressive. Always friendly, calm, and extremely helpful, Catch creates a fantastic first impression and makes every guest feel welcome from the very first moment. Professionalism, efficiency, and a warm attitude perfectly combined.  Thank you for a wonderful stay and for making our experience truly memorable. We would gladly return and highly recommend this place.  Fam .Atanassov"
> **- Valentina Atanassova (5/5/5)**

> "This resort is a true gem. From the very first welcome, you feel the special atmosphere created by the entire staff. Everyone works with great dedication, kindness, and attention to detail. The beach is beautiful and lovingly cared for every morning. Particularly touching is the staff member who quietly sweeps the walkways of leaves each day.  We stayed in room 228, which was always spotlessly clean thanks to an exceptionally friendly and thorough housekeeper. Excellent breakfast, perfect service, and an atmosphere where you immediately feel at home. A place you don’t just visit – but one you truly want to recommend."
> **- Jonny (5/5/5)**

> "Nothing really to criticize. Huge rooms, very friendly staff, beautiful, lush green grounds. Beach was awesome, food was great. And you''ll get free drinking water bottles (glass!!) every day. Massage was good, pool area was good. Breakfast was brilliant, which was more like Brunch with daily changing warm Asian dishes. The area around is much quieter than Chaweng and offers plenty of eating out opportunities as well. Can highly recommend!"
> **- Zeljko Klaric (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/royal-muang-samui-villas-1.jpg','077 428 700','89 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://muangsamui.com/royalmuangsamuivillas/','["Monday: 12:01 AM – 12:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:01 AM – 12:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:01 AM – 12:00 PM","Thursday: 12:01 AM – 12:00 PM","Friday: 12:01 AM – 12:00 PM","Saturday: 12:01 AM – 12:00 PM","Sunday: 12:01 AM – 12:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifsv000nq8xdrwnu123q','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.988+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.988+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/royal-muang-samui-villas-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/royal-muang-samui-villas-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7449375259288403663',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('royal-spa','standard','cmr07ihi600nkq8xdl0xo3zs9','Royal Spa','## Top Reviews
> "I visited this salon for a manicure and pedicure. I was informed that the price would be 900 THB for the basic service with a light scrub or 1,200 THB for the full scrub and cleaning option. I agreed based on that information.  After the service was completed, I was presented with a total of 1,700 THB. When I asked for clarification, I was told that aromatherapy had been included. I did not request or agree to any additional aromatherapy service, and this was not explained to me in advance.  I am sharing this experience to inform others to clearly confirm all services and prices before the treatment begins. Clear communication and transparent pricing are important for customers to make informed decisions.  Be aware!"
> **- M. H. (1/5/5)**

> "My visit to Royal Spa was absolutely wonderful. The service and the overall approach were excellent, and I can highly recommend it. I visited this salon twice during my stay on Koh Samui. I’m definitely coming back next time—I already know which treatment I’ll choose!"
> **- Veronika Harbichova (5/5/5)**

> "Highly professional team as mention below, they are well trained and the staff really look after you. I felt their Thai hospitality and felt so welcomed! Highly recommend because of the value and experience must try. I was mildly sun burnt so this place was magical ;)"
> **- Sugar Sprink (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/royal-spa-1.jpg','077 963 883','209 1-2, Central Festival, 209 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.990+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.990+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/royal-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/royal-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3305620479672732684',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('rsbb-rongsong-barber','standard','cmr07ihi800nlq8xdtdyzcp4f','RSBB Rongsong Barber','## Top Reviews
> "I was recommended this barber (James) by my mate in Chaweng beach. I got a really good skin fade, a trim and my beard touched up. James paid a lot of attention to detail and I am stoked with the fresh cut.  Definitely see why I was recommended them and certainly pass that recommendation on! I just showed him a couple of photos and off we went. He is also fluent in English which makes it easier for people like me that can’t speak Thai  Cheers lads"
> **- Mick Parker (5/5/5)**

> "I came 30 minutes across the island to this barbershop because of the reviews and it was a complete waste of time.  They told me they can’t cut because “50% of the power is out.” That made no sense because the lights were on, the clippers were working, and one of them was literally cutting another customer’s hair right in front of me. The only thing not working was the AC and the door was open anyway.  So the shop was clearly operating. They just didn’t want to serve me.  When I asked why they could cut someone else’s hair but not mine, I didn’t get a real explanation, just attitude and dismissive behavior.  If you don’t want to work in the heat, just say that or close the shop. Don’t lie and say you “can’t operate” while you are actively operating for someone else. That’s dishonest and unprofessional.  It also didn’t sit right that the only person being served was a white customer while I was turned away with excuses. Take that however you want, but it raised a serious red flag for me.  They wasted my time, treated me with disrespect, and tried to play me like I’m stupid. I do not recommend this place."
> **- Albert Opoku (1/5/5)**

> "James is a very talented barber. He knew exactly what I was after with the same terminology as the UK which is hard to find. He did a great job and the best haircut I’ve had since being away travelling."
> **- Alex Tilley (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rsbb-rongsong-barber-1.jpg','091 815 5687','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.kohsamuibarbershop.com/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.992+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.992+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rsbb-rongsong-barber-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rsbb-rongsong-barber-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14316186951118819859',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('rudi-window-and-door','standard','cmr07ihia00nmq8xd3qjz106h','Rudi Window And Door','## Top Reviews
> "Great quality furniture. Pricy but reasonable for you get 👍🏻"
> **- Денис Макаренко (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rudi-window-and-door-1.jpg','+66818934936','134 5, Tambon Na Mueang, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ih4s00idq8xdbhwjttn6','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.995+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.995+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rudi-window-and-door-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rudi-window-and-door-2.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rudi-window-and-door-3.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6472856046877623923',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('rungrueng-restaurant','standard','cmr07ihid00nnq8xdc8ui6osk','RungRueng Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "The food is always so delicious and the staff are friendly and welcoming. They’ve made recent updates/renovations that are quite nice also. There are plenty of shakes/smoothies and cold beer on the menu to cool you off on the hot days. There are good music videos (most always in English) always playing on the tv and there is also a pool table for entertainment. It’s worth a visit up on Chaweng Hill, it’s not too far from main road. Just 2-3 minutes after turning by Caltex station. ⛽️"
> **- RJ (5/5/5)**

> "My group of 3 stayed at an Airbnb nearby and ended up eating here multiple times. It was just too convenient and too good to pass up. The staff were super friendly, the food came out quickly, and everything was both tasty and reasonably priced. Even if you’re not staying in the area, I’d definitely recommend making the trip for some authentic, family-run Thai food.  I even tried their pizza one night, and it was surprisingly delicious. A fun change of pace from the usual dishes. Honestly, you can’t go wrong with anything here. Highly recommend!"
> **- Taj Wortham (5/5/5)**

> "I had the cashew chicken with rice for lunch and it was to die for. The chicken was cooked perfectly and the flavors were amazing. The staff were so sweet and friendly, which made the experience even better. Honestly, everything on the menu looked delicious and it was hard to choose. Highly recommend stopping here if you’re in the area!"
> **- Grace Chizawsky (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rungrueng-restaurant-1.jpg','086 476 4905','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/share/1BH1z41Lxj/?mibextid=wwXIfr','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.997+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.997+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rungrueng-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/rungrueng-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1057501523818582932',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sabai','standard','cmr07ihif00noq8xdcb6uaf7c','Sabai','## Top Reviews
> "Down the China town part of town, all the prices are the same in the area. Service was efficient and professional, $300bhat for one hour hot oil massage. Air conditioning which makes it more comfortable and a nice little hot tea when finished. Good value for money"
> **- Matthew Hansen (4/5/5)**

> "Very thorough massage and they give 200%, both our massages were over an hour and a half. I had a medical massage which was very good and they showed me what to do at home.  Very courteous and if you have language problems, just use Google translate. They are lovely 🥰"
> **- Judy Stein (5/5/5)**

> "Excellent massage! Had both Thai and Oil Massage, they were both outstanding!"
> **- Philip Stein (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sabai-1.jpg','063 261 9097','แม่น้ำ, 117 หมู่1 Soi 4, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig5c0051q8xdykrbexft','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:12.999+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:12.999+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sabai-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sabai-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8769581707567095306',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sabienglae-restaurant-lamai','standard','cmr07ihij00npq8xd6nqnubkc','Sabienglae Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "The food was absolutely delicious, and the service was very polite and attentive.  Our family of four ordered seven dishes. Although the portions weren’t very large, together with four drinks, it came to about $70 USD — which was really great value."
> **- 唐有建 (5/5/5)**

> "Incredible seafood and great service. The signature spicy salad, the crab with Indian curry, the sweet and sour fish curry and the giant tiger prawns with tamarind sauce were absolutely amazing.  We celebrated my dad''s birthday and it was the perfect spot. Highly reccomended if you want authentic local seafood"
> **- Nadir Khan (5/5/5)**

> "Very good food in a great setting at a very good price. Staff is accommodating and willing to adapt spiciness levels 🌶️ Seafood is very fresh! You can see the lobsters and crabs in their respective tanks as you go in. Ended up going back the following day as there were too many good things to try!"
