INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sadanan-acupuncture-wellness','standard','cmr07ihin00nrq8xdhkzj2vyu','Sadanan Acupuncture & Wellness','## Top Reviews
> "⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐  I would like to thank the doctor for her prompt and professional care. It was very easy to get an appointment, and everything was handled smoothly and efficiently from the moment I arrived.  The doctor took the time to listen carefully to my concerns, thoroughly discussed my condition with me, and tailored the treatment accordingly. I especially appreciated her attention to detail and the fact that she answered all of my questions, making me feel comfortable and well cared for throughout the visit.  The clinic is clean, well organized, and highly professional. Everyone was kind, welcoming, and helpful.  Thank you for the excellent experience and the outstanding care. I would highly recommend this clinic to others."
> **- Tímea H. (5/5/5)**

> "I came to the clinic with leg and bark pain.Dr Arin took care of me perfectly. I had acupuncture and cups. Now I am after 5 sesions and I feel much better. Iam going to continoue my therapy. Thanks Dr Arin for Her treatment, knowledge and patience. Iam very grateful, indeed."
> **- Asia Zalewska (5/5/5)**

> "I had an excellent experience at this acupuncture and cupping center. The staff were very welcoming and professional from the moment I arrived. The practitioner took the time to listen carefully to my concerns and explained each step of the treatment clearly. The session was both relaxing and effective — I already felt noticeable improvement afterward. The place is clean, calm, and has a really peaceful atmosphere. I’ll definitely be coming back. Highly recommended."
