INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('safe-zone-glamping','standard','cmr07ihiq00nsq8xd3chp1l0l','Safe Zone Glamping','## Top Reviews
> "This was honestly the best place I have ever been to. 10 out of 10.  The property itself is absolutely gorgeous, with breathtaking views. I could have stayed there the whole day, simply immersed in nature and the beauty of the surroundings. The atmosphere is peaceful, soulful, and deeply relaxing.  What truly makes this place exceptional is the hospitality. The hosts are incredibly kind, warm, and genuinely helpful. You feel welcomed and cared for from the moment you arrive.  Breakfast was delicious every day – a freshly prepared Thai dish, coffee or tea, and fresh fruits. It’s such a beautiful way to start the morning.  They also rent motorbikes, which is a great option if you’re confident driving. It makes exploring Koh Samui very easy. The accommodation is located quite high on a hill, and the road is steep, but taxis and Grab do come up without problems.  If you’re looking for a place where you can truly relax and reconnect with nature, this is it. I would come back anytime."
> **- Andreja Gombač (5/5/5)**

> "One of the best places on Koh Samui. The owners are very pleasant, accommodating, and friendly. Above-standard service 10/10. Sunset view 10/10. Excellent accommodation! And there are no mosquitoes inside the glamping tents. Luxurious breakfast with a view. Accessible by scooter."
> **- David Ťuka (5/5/5)**

> "Great place up in the mountains with an amazing view! They have a really nice common area to relax and share with others, always with a calm and peaceful vibe. The rooms are big and comfortable, with fans inside and cool chairs outside to enjoy the scenery. The shared bathrooms are always clean—just note there’s no hot water. The breakfast included is incredible… every day a different and delicious surprise! The family in charge is always available, kind, and has a great attitude.  **Tip:** Rent a motorbike to get up here—there are some good climbs and it makes the trip much easier."
> **- Veronica Calvo (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/safe-zone-glamping-1.jpg','062 965 5224','Lipa Noi, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61552732766599','["Monday: 12:00 – 8:30 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 8:30 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 8:30 PM","Thursday: Closed","Friday: Closed","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: 10:30 AM – 8:30 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.010+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.010+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/safe-zone-glamping-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/safe-zone-glamping-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11113046844065638781',NULL,NULL);
