INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('saiyor-garden','standard','cmr07ihjc00nzq8xdz41bviv7','Saiyor Garden','## Top Reviews
> "The space is beautiful, large and shady.  I dropped a star because it is neglected and not maintained.  In my opinion, the place can be easily improved, some more facilities, spraying against mosquitoes, maintenance of the toilets.  It is possible to buy soft drinks, a small cafe would have added to the experience.   There is a lovely pool.  The children enjoyed themselves but the mosquitoes bothered them."
> **- יולי מזל טוב (4/5/5)**

> "Amazing place for kids, large compound with interesting statues and many playgrounds, slides and more. There are also ropes and some kind of climbing tarzan land. Museum and 3D history hall is fascinating. The best of all is swimming pool in the middle od the forest! You can easily spend whole day there. Food selection is limited, but sufficient."
> **- Marek Horyl (5/5/5)**

> "It is such a big place in the jungle with all kinds of playing areas for kids. The pool is so cool. Nothing fancy, simple, and fun."
> **- Jessi Heifets (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/saiyor-garden-1.jpg',NULL,'Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.2,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 10:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: Closed","Friday: 10:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.032+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.032+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/saiyor-garden-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/saiyor-garden-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11545550796001641982',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sakura-spa','standard','cmr07ihje00o0q8xdoa9hglye','Sakura Spa','## Top Reviews
> "Honestly, the best massage I’ve ever had.  Not only did they work through all my knots, but they also incorporated stretching—it was a full-body experience. I feel completely refreshed, more aligned, and even standing straighter after the session.  An incredible experience that I highly recommend."
> **- Jennifer Quintero Velez (5/5/5)**

> "I gotta be honest I was a bit reserved towards this place and the quality of massage you can get but it turn out really good. Very happy we actually decided to go for it. Lovely sea view, relaxed atmosphere and the woman who did my foot massage had magic hands, one of the best I''ve had so far in Thailand.  ขอบคุณค่ะ 🙏🏻"
> **- Krasimira Valkanova (5/5/5)**

> "Walked by this place to have a massage and they sat us in the two chairs next to the window. Nice view and we had a neck/shoulders and feet massage for 450baht for 60mins.  Happy with the massage, we went in the middle of the day so it wasn''t too busy."
> **- Michelle Nguyen (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sakura-spa-1.jpg','095 427 8526','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.034+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.034+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sakura-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sakura-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1348777786452405520',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sala-chaweng-beach-resort','standard','cmr07ihjg00o1q8xdatpobsnv','Sala Chaweng Beach Resort','## Top Reviews
> "We stayed at Sala Samui for three nights, and from the moment we checked in until the day we left, we felt incredibly well taken care of. A heartfelt thank you to all the staff for their warm hospitality and excellent service.  We stayed in the Garden Wing, and honestly, I preferred it over the beachfront area. The gardens are beautiful, very photogenic, and most of the resort’s facilities are conveniently located there. Whenever we wanted to visit the beach, it was just a short walk away.  Our room was comfortable, spotless, and well maintained. One feature that really stood out was Sala’s dedicated app. We could easily find information, make requests, and communicate with the staff through the app, and the responses were always quick and helpful. It’s such a fantastic feature and deserves special praise.  The location is also very convenient. The airport and Central Samui are both nearby, and there are plenty of restaurants, shops, and other amenities within easy reach.  My husband and I absolutely loved our stay here, and we hope to return again very soon."
> **- Wen-Ya Chen (5/5/5)**

> "We recently returned from our holiday in Thailand, where we stayed at SALA Samui Chaweng Beach Resort, and writing this review is truly emotional for us.  From the very first moment, what stood out the most were the people. The friendliness and warmth of the entire staff were beyond anything we have ever experienced. From the kind gentlemen who helped us cross the road every single day, to the reception team, to the incredible restaurant staff – waiters, managers, everyone – the level of care, kindness, and professionalism was exceptional.  There were moments during our stay when we genuinely needed their help. One morning, our little one had a fever, and the team immediately stepped in. They called a taxi for us, made sure we got to the clinic safely, and checked on us multiple times afterward to see if we needed anything. They were always there when we needed them – not just performing a service, but truly caring. That level of humanity is rare.  The gastronomy was absolutely outstanding. Breakfasts were fresh, beautifully prepared, and incredibly diverse, with an amazing selection of cold cuts, vegetables, fruits, and a varied à la carte menu that made every morning special. Lunches and dinners were just as perfect – high-quality dishes, great flavors, and impeccable service every single time.  We also want to highlight the wonderful team at the pool and beach. They took care of us all day long, bringing drinks, fresh coconuts, and making sure we were comfortable at all times. Their kindness and attention made our days by the water effortless and relaxing.  As parents, we must say that this hotel offers one of the best environments for children we have ever seen. There is so much open green space where kids can safely run and play, a beautiful large pool, and a fantastic kids’ corner with activities. Our child had an amazing program every single day. A special thank you goes to instructor Honey and instructor Chimn, who dedicated their time and energy with so much care and warmth. They made our little one feel happy, safe, and excited every day.  We would also like to give a very special thank you to the incredible people who made our stay unforgettable:  Erwin, Booki, New, Ooh, Amp, Cho, Mind, Nat, Mint, Am, Noom, Ice, Yod, Nim  From the Pool Team: Ter and Pitr  And also Sof and Bansan.  Each of you made us feel welcomed, cared for, and valued every single day. Your professionalism, kindness, and genuine smiles are the true reason this hotel stands out.  The hotel itself is stunning, but honestly, that is just the cherry on top. The rooms are elegant and extremely comfortable. We had a private pool, and the daily housekeeping was flawless. Everything was cleaned and prepared perfectly every day. And the bed… without exaggeration, it is the best bed we have ever slept in. Soft, luxurious, and unbelievably comfortable – we slept better there than anywhere else in our lives.  After a month with the team, we no longer felt like guests – we felt like family. It was genuinely difficult to say goodbye.  In our eyes, this is the best hotel in Thailand. Absolute professionals in every sense of the word, combining luxury with genuine warmth and heart. We are already planning to book our stay for next year, because the experience they create is something you simply want to live again.  We recommend it with the highest possible rating."
> **- Samuel Hoffman (5/5/5)**

> "We had the best stay at SALA Chaweng Beach Resort! We stayed on the Garden Side, and everything was amazing from start to finish. The room was beautiful, comfortable, and impeccably maintained. The facilities were excellent, and the entire resort was spotless and well cared for.  What truly made our stay special was the outstanding staff. Everyone was friendly, welcoming, and attentive, always going above and beyond to ensure we had a wonderful experience.  Everything was perfect, and we couldn''t have asked for a better vacation. We highly recommend this resort and would happily stay here again on our next visit to Koh Samui. Thank you to the entire team for such a memorable stay!"
> **- CPB Electrical and Gas (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sala-chaweng-beach-resort-1.jpg','077 905 888','99/10 Moo 2, Chaweng Beach, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.salahospitality.com/samui-chaweng/?utm_source=Google&utm_medium=GoogleMyBusiness&utm_campaign=Web_Link','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.036+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.036+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sala-chaweng-beach-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sala-chaweng-beach-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2520803605712367357',NULL,NULL);
