> **- CPB Electrical and Gas (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sala-chaweng-dinner-under-the-stars-1.jpg','077 905 888','99/10 Moo 2, Chaweng Beach, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.salahospitality.com/samui-chaweng/?utm_source=Google&utm_medium=GoogleMyBusiness&utm_campaign=Web_Link','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.039+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.039+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sala-chaweng-dinner-under-the-stars-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sala-chaweng-dinner-under-the-stars-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2520803605712367357',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sala-chaweng-spas','standard','cmr07ihjl00o3q8xd27csct9b','Sala Chaweng Spas','## Top Reviews
> "A fabulous spa experience. We were greeted with a drink, there was no rushing, however it’s good to be a bit early to relax. The attention to detail was evident when you walk into the treatment room and exceptionally clean. I had the head neck and shoulders for 90 minutes and my daughter had the signature massage. The massage was very relaxing in-fact one of the best I have ever had ."
> **- Tanya Collins (5/5/5)**

> "I went to SALA Spa in Chaweng, Koh Samui, and it was honestly the best massage I’ve ever had. I did their signature massage, which was around 90 minutes, and even though it’s a bit on the pricey side, it was absolutely worth it.  From the moment you walk in, the smell and atmosphere hit you in the best way. Everything is calm, warm, and luxurious without feeling intimidating. It really feels like they’re trying to engage all your senses, not just rush you through a treatment. The space is beautiful, quiet, and incredibly relaxing.  The therapist was amazing and clearly knew exactly what she was doing. You can tell the staff actually care about their work and take pride in it. It didn’t feel robotic or rushed at all, it felt very intentional and well paced. The pressure, technique, and flow of the massage were perfect, and I left feeling genuinely relaxed instead of sore or overstimulated.  Yes, it’s more expensive than your average Thai massage place, but the quality, environment, and overall experience completely justify the price. This is the kind of spa you go to when you want something special, not just a quick massage.  If you’re in Koh Samui and want a high end, sensory, genuinely relaxing spa experience, I would 100 percent recommend SALA Spa Chaweng. I’d go back in a heartbeat."
> **- Alex (5/5/5)**

> "We had an incredible experience at SALA Spa Koh Samui, truly one of the best spas we’ve ever been to.  From the moment we arrived, we loved all the sweet details and thoughtful touches throughout the experience: fresh tea, a flower under the bed, beautiful treatment rooms with private shower and toilets, and amazing bedding, towels, and bathrobes.  We chose the milk bath and signature massage experience and absolutely loved every part of the ritual, the oils, the peaceful atmosphere, and the meditation moments. Everything felt perfectly smooth and relaxing.  A special thank you to Rose and Milky for the amazing massages. The whole experience was flawless, we highly recommend!"
> **- Charlotte de Saint Périer (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sala-chaweng-spas-1.jpg','077 905 888','99, Beach, 10 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.salahospitality.com/samui-chaweng/wellness/sala-chaweng-spa/?utm_source=Google&utm_medium=GoogleMyBusiness&utm_campaign=Web_Link','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.041+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.041+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sala-chaweng-spas-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sala-chaweng-spas-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10269388805225229904',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sala-choengmon-beach-resort','standard','cmr07ihjo00o4q8xd49xtbrv3','SALA Choengmon Beach Resort','## Top Reviews
> "Another perfectly wonderful stay at the Sala Samui Choengmon Beach Hotel. This was already our fifth visit, and from the moment we arrived, we felt right at home again. Our anticipation was fulfilled in every way. The excellent service and the warmth of the staff once more put the crown on our holiday.  The entire resort is a small oasis of relaxation – very well maintained, peaceful, stylish, and perfect for completely unwinding.  A special compliment goes to the staff, who greet us every day with kindness and a heartfelt smile, making each morning start with joy. The beach bar crew – Looktan, Kran, Pui, and Beam – do an outstanding job and serve top‑quality drinks. Pui’s “Greenland” is truly exceptional.  As always, Noom made sure we could enjoy our days at the beach to the fullest, attentively providing us with every refreshing drink we could wish for. And the “new” team member – the well‑known Banja, who has transitioned to the beach boy team – is a real asset for the guests.  We were also delighted to meet a new, cheerful face: Ellie from the breakfast service. Her positive energy is contagious and a wonderful addition to Oom’s team.  We may have arrived as guests, but we left as friends – and we are already looking forward to our next encounter with this fantastic team at the 5‑star Sala Samui."
> **- Claudia Graf (5/5/5)**

> "Beautiful hotel in Koh Samui, we were absolutely delighted. The property is stunning and very well maintained, everything feels high quality and thoughtfully designed down to the smallest detail. Cleanliness is at an high standard.  The service is outstanding across all areas, always friendly, attentive and highly professional. Big big thanks to the whole team.  The hotel app is especially convenient, communication is fast, reliable and very easy.  The breakfast is delicious and varied, and we also really enjoyed the dinners.  There is a wide range of activities, so there is something for everyone.  The beach is beautiful, and there are great restaurants nearby for the evening.  A special thank you to Timo Kuenzli for the support and the very generous goodwill gesture regarding a medical issue.  We felt comfortable at all times and would come back anytime. Absolute recommendation. We would give 10 stars if we could :)"
> **- C. E. (5/5/5)**

> "This is by far one of the best hotels we have ever stayed at. The service and the entire team are exceptionally friendly and welcoming — from the very first moment, you truly feel comfortable and well taken care of.  The rooms with private pools make the stay even more relaxing and special. The design of the rooms is beautiful, stylish, and very thoughtfully done. We also rarely experienced food this good in a hotel — every meal was outstanding.  The private beach is absolutely beautiful, well maintained, and perfectly located. In general, the service throughout the resort is of the highest quality, and the hotel also offers a wide range of activities and programs.  The location is perfect if you want to relax and unwind. Even though we do not have children ourselves, we noticed several times how incredibly kind and caring the staff — and people in Thailand in general — are with children.  We stayed here for our honeymoon and will definitely come back again in the future. Highly recommended!"
> **- Melinda Inauen (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sala-choengmon-beach-resort-1.jpg','077 245 888','10 Baan Plai Laem 9, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.salahospitality.com/samui-choengmon/?utm_source=Google&utm_medium=GoogleMyBusiness&utm_campaign=Web_Link','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifv2001aq8xdag7cvjgf','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.044+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.044+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sala-choengmon-beach-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sala-choengmon-beach-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17680325667402300500',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sala-thai-santiburi-restaurant','standard','cmr07ihjq00o5q8xd9lg1k0gl','Sala Thai Santiburi Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "Absolutely the most beautiful and divine restaurant! We had a really special evening meal here and it was truly so wonderful. The food is to die for, huge portions, beautiful surroundings and the staff go out of their way to make your experience special. The kindest and sweetest waitresses. We can’t wait to bring our family back here for another meal! What a find!!"
> **- Sarah Craigie (5/5/5)**

> "the service was excellent, food is great but not that worth the price. surrounding is good, nice and peaceful. good for maybe once in a while or try it out but definitely not that spectacular yet."
> **- W alee (4/5/5)**

> "I normally don’t write reviews, but this place absolutely deserves one. If you’re in Koh Samui, this is a must-visit.  Hands down the best Thai food experience I’ve had on the island – maybe even anywhere in Thailand. Every dish was bursting with authentic flavors, perfectly balanced, and clearly prepared with real passion and skill. You can taste the quality in every bite.  The atmosphere, the service, and the attention to detail made the whole experience unforgettable. Nothing felt touristy or rushed – just genuine Thai cuisine at its absolute best.  If you’re even remotely serious about food, do not miss this place. I would come back to Koh Samui just to eat here again.—-"
> **- R L (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sala-thai-santiburi-restaurant-1.jpg','077 425 035','Sala Thai, ตำบล แม่น้ำ Maenam Beach, Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://salathaisamui.com/','["Monday: 6:00 – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 6:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 6:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 6:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 6:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 6:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 6:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.046+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.046+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sala-thai-santiburi-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sala-thai-santiburi-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6477891430468541587',NULL,NULL);
