> **- W alee (4/5/5)**

> "I normally don’t write reviews, but this place absolutely deserves one. If you’re in Koh Samui, this is a must-visit.  Hands down the best Thai food experience I’ve had on the island – maybe even anywhere in Thailand. Every dish was bursting with authentic flavors, perfectly balanced, and clearly prepared with real passion and skill. You can taste the quality in every bite.  The atmosphere, the service, and the attention to detail made the whole experience unforgettable. Nothing felt touristy or rushed – just genuine Thai cuisine at its absolute best.  If you’re even remotely serious about food, do not miss this place. I would come back to Koh Samui just to eat here again.—-"
> **- R L (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sala-thai-1.jpg','077 425 035','Sala Thai, ตำบล แม่น้ำ Maenam Beach, Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://salathaisamui.com/','["Monday: 6:00 – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 6:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 6:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 6:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 6:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 6:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 6:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.048+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.048+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sala-thai-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sala-thai-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6477891430468541587',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('salaraj-thai-wellness-spa','standard','cmr07ihju00o7q8xd77t364ki','Salaraj Thai Wellness & Spa','## Top Reviews
> "We had a wonderful experience at Salaraj Spa in Koh Samui. The staff were incredibly friendly and professional, and the spa itself was spotlessly clean and tastefully decorated. We were treated by three lovely ladies — Earth, Eva, and Bam — all of whom were warm, attentive, and highly skilled at what they do. I especially enjoyed the sports massage, which did wonders for releasing tension. I’d wholeheartedly recommend it to any athlete or active person looking to recover and unwind. We left feeling completely relaxed and well cared for. Highly recommended!"
> **- Anthony Ereme (5/5/5)**

> "Paid 1500 baht for hard nails but they kept falling off starting from the first day they were done. I went back to the shop 3 times when on Koh Samui with more nails falling off, but then I left the island and more fell off.. 8 in total. I kept in touch and told them I wasn’t happy. I asked for refund but they wouldn’t refund me. Do not get this done and beware they won’t give fair customer service / refund. Update : In response to your response - I have no idea what you’re talking about, I did not refuse any buffing. The nails were definitely buffed. You can actually SEE in the photos that the nails are buffed! If anything I think buffing makes them too smooth and that will help the nails fall off. I actually suggested rough buffing with a nail file instead of a smoother for extra texture to help the nails stick. Either way, your claim is incorrect and - the nails were buffed. This makes no sense about a guarantee period either, the nails fell off from day 1 and you fixed it. So why would I ask straight away. Then it kept happening so that’s when I asked for the refund. I never had a full set of 10 nails, not for one day. I reported the issues 4 times. Within a short space of time. You clearly should have refunded me."
> **- Madam Esmeralda (1/5/5)**

> "Great saloon with very kind staff. Very clean environment.  Beam has magic hands. Definitely coming back for another massage tomorrow. Amy and Kat were also great says my parents who had them.  Thank you!!"
> **- Ecenaz Albayrak (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/salaraj-thai-wellness-spa-1.jpg','083 828 9249','14 48, Tambon Bo Put, Koh Samul Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://salarajthaiwellnessspa.co.th/home/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.050+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.050+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/salaraj-thai-wellness-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/salaraj-thai-wellness-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7911484533374350194',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('salefino','standard','cmr07ihjx00o8q8xd6bh54xob','Salefino','## Top Reviews
> "We had dinner at Salefino Koh Samui during a business meeting. The service stood out — the lady who looked after us was very friendly and attentive, checking in to see if everything was okay, which we really appreciated.  As for the food, it was generally average. The lamb shank was the highlight of the meal and very enjoyable, but the other dishes could use some improvement to better match the overall dining experience. Since it was a business dinner and our partner kindly hosted, we didn’t raise any concerns at the time.  Overall, a pleasant experience with great service, but there’s definitely room to elevate the food quality."
> **- Zaza Meerveld (4/5/5)**

> "Salefino Koh Samui is one of those rare places that effortlessly combines breathtaking ocean views, exceptional cuisine, an impressive wine selection, and genuinely heartfelt hospitality. Located along the beautiful coastline of Bangrak Bay, this charming beachfront restaurant offers a setting that becomes even more magical at sunset. From the moment you arrive, you are welcomed into an atmosphere that feels elegant, relaxed, and inviting, making every visit a memorable experience.  The ambiance is truly outstanding. The stunning sea views, peaceful surroundings, and beautifully designed beachfront setting create the perfect environment to unwind and enjoy quality time with family, friends, or loved ones. Whether you are watching the sun dip below the horizon or simply enjoying the tranquil atmosphere, every moment at Salefino feels special.  The food is simply exceptional. Every dish is crafted with great attention to detail using premium-quality ingredients that are carefully selected to ensure the highest standards. The flavors are refined, authentic, and consistently outstanding, reflecting the passion and dedication behind the kitchen. It is easily some of the best food we have experienced on Koh Samui.  Complementing the dining experience is an extensive wine collection with an impressive variety of labels from different regions around the world. Whether you are a seasoned wine enthusiast or simply looking for the perfect pairing, the selection offers something for every taste and occasion.  What truly sets Salefino apart, however, is its remarkable service. The owners and staff are incredibly warm, welcoming, and genuinely friendly. Their hospitality goes far beyond professionalism—they make every guest feel valued, comfortable, and at home. The attention to detail, sincere care, and personal touch create an atmosphere that is both intimate and unforgettable.  Salefino is much more than a restaurant; it is a place that creates lasting memories through outstanding food, premium ingredients, an exceptional wine selection, stunning beachfront views, and truly remarkable hospitality. We absolutely love this place and always look forward to returning. Without a doubt, it is one of our favorite destinations on Koh Samui and a place we wholeheartedly recommend to anyone visiting the island. ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐"
> **- Chaiyo Jiarachaikul (5/5/5)**

> "Such a lovely place- they made a real fuss of my birthday and provided so many lovely extras. Also a rare spot in Thailand to get a decent glass of wine by the glass! Portions are huge and you can taste the quality. Highly recommend!"
> **- Lizzie Fussey (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/salefino-1.jpg','091 825 2190','ตําบล บ่อผุด Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.salefinosamui.com/','["Monday: 6:00 – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 6:00 – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 6:00 – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 6:00 – 11:00 PM","Friday: 6:00 – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 6:00 – 11:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.053+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.053+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/salefino-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/salefino-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13915182976157980389',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('salmon-samui','standard','cmr07ihk000o9q8xd06lo2bvh','Salmon Samui','## Top Reviews
> "We come here every day for one of our family members birthday. For 3 years straight we have been served excellent food which made us come back time and time again! The atmosphere here is great and super relaxing. The owners are extremely friendly and provide a good amount of info regarding any questions to the menu.  The burgers, which we have been ordering since the start of us coming here, have always been of top quality. Today, it was the french style burger which was paired with deliciously melted goat cheese!  The pasta is hand-pulled and made right before your eyes. They are perfectly Al Dente and the sauce with it fits like puzzle pieces.  The Marsala Chicken, served with our choice of mashed potatoes, is perfectly tender and delicious!  Overall, the general Atmosphere, the service and the food is worth always coming back. If you are a connoisseur of great meals, friendly people and good vibes then we would definitely recommend Samons Restaurant!"
> **- Dhom- Monthathip (5/5/5)**

> "Samons Restaurant - A Perfect Spot for a Special Occasion  I recently visited Samons Restaurant in Mae Nam, Koh Samui, for a birthday celebration, and I couldn''t have asked for a better experience. The atmosphere was warm and inviting, with a cozy yet elegant setup that made the evening feel extra special.  The staff went above and beyond to make the birthday celebration memorable. They were friendly, attentive, and even surprised us with a small treat for the occasion, which was a lovely touch. Their hospitality truly made us feel welcome.  Now, let''s talk about the food—absolutely delicious! Every dish was beautifully presented and full of authentic flavors. The ingredients were fresh, and you could tell a lot of care went into preparing each meal. The seafood, in particular, was outstanding—perfectly cooked and seasoned.  The service was prompt and professional, yet warm and personal, which made the whole dining experience even more enjoyable. The prices were reasonable for the quality, and I would highly recommend this place to anyone looking for a great meal in Koh Samui.  Overall, Samons Restaurant is a fantastic choice for a special occasion or just a great dinner out. I will definitely be coming back!  ⭐ 5/5 Highly recommended!"
> **- Luca Foschi (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing atmosphere, even better food and the staff and owner are super friendly. Highly recommended if you are looking for these qualities in a restaurant."
> **- Byron Giehl (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/salmon-samui-1.jpg','080 040 4612','40/6 Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 5:30 – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 5:30 – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 5:30 – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 5:30 – 9:00 PM","Friday: 5:30 – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 5:30 – 9:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.056+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.056+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/salmon-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/salmon-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10454665076202390277',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('salt-society','standard','cmr07ihk200oaq8xdj1htsmv1','Salt Society','## Top Reviews
> "What an amazing time we had at Salt Society brunch. The staff were incredible and couldn’t do enough for you. Cassey was so lovely and attended to our every need. Babe and  Peepo were equally friendly and attentive. Food was varied, lots of lovely choice and delicious, drinks flowed and the music was great. The female DJ played a great mix of tunes, plenty of us were up dancing. A fabulous way to spend a Sunday afternoon. Would come back again and again and highly recommend."
> **- Katie Leader (5/5/5)**

> "Food was amazing.nice option.happy hour is there. The beach is really pretty and quite. Great views and vibes. The right price. The staff is really cooperative and good. The vibe was perfect. It also has stay option resort option. It has a pool and private beach must come here to spend time with family friends, couples solo"
> **- Siddharth Kumar Das (5/5/5)**

> "Went for drinks. Excellent cocktails ~£10 but staff were very friendly and helpful when picking drinks. Friend got wine, very generous to let him try different types until he found the one he liked. Was a Sunday and therefore quiet but that in itself gave it a relaxing and calming vibe."
> **- Krishan Patel (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/salt-society-1.jpg','077 230 500','38/2 Moo 3 Borpud, Chaweng Beach, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.saltsocietysamui.com/','["Monday: 12:00 – 10:30 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 10:30 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 10:30 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 10:30 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 10:30 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 10:30 PM","Sunday: 12:30 – 3:30 PM, 6:00 – 10:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.058+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.058+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/salt-society-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/salt-society-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10596674132735609800',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samaya-activities','standard','cmr07ihk400obq8xddyait8ko','Samaya Activities','## Top Reviews
> "I visited yoga with for beginners and I’m in love with it. We started with some breath work, which is good and helps you to connect with your mind.  All asanas are so gentle! So if you’re not flexible like me, you’ll feel the difference after the class. Don’t worry if you’re more advanced, you gonna enjoy it anyways."
> **- Dina Makalova (5/5/5)**

> "I love that place! Classes and teachers are nice and professional 🙏🏻❤️ I go to yoga and qigong classes. In fact the whole Samaya resort is great! Lots of flowers and greens. Very natural 🍀 They also have beautiful events and master classes. Recommend ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️"
> **- ILove Magic (5/5/5)**

> "Thank you for gentle yoga with an experienced teacher. For beginners, this is a good opportunity to start practicing yoga in a harmonious atmosphere on the roof of the building! I recommend 🙏"
> **- Amrita Demidenko (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samaya-activities-1.jpg','062 183 7437','71/4-9 M.4, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.instagram.com/samayawellness/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifuo0015q8xdfahzrsp4','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.060+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.060+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samaya-activities-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samaya-activities-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14819423790425852818',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samaya-wellness-resort','standard','cmr07ihk700ocq8xdu21mwi68','Samaya Wellness Resort','## Top Reviews
> "My girlfriend and I stayed at Samaya Wellness Resort for six nights and overall had a mixed experience. Upon check-in, we encountered a leaking fridge in our room, which staff addressed promptly. However, we also discovered there was no hot water and had to report this separately; it was resolved the following morning. While the issues were handled efficiently, it was not ideal after a long day of travelling, particularly as one of us was feeling unwell and hoping for a hot shower.  The room itself was pleasant. While it is clear that some areas could benefit from a bit of TLC, this did not significantly detract from our stay. On our third night, we were unfortunately woken at around 4:30am by a neighbouring couple arguing loudly, which was both unsettling and frustrating, especially as we had an early boat trip the next morning and ended up with very little sleep. To their credit, the staff handled the situation quickly and professionally, and were very accommodating once we raised the issue. We were able to change rooms, experienced no further disturbances, and enjoyed a nicer view thereafter.  We had seen prior reviews mentioning an air conditioning smell, which we did notice slightly, though it was not severe. The staff throughout our stay were consistently friendly, welcoming, and helpful. The pool area was a lovely space to relax, the bed was comfortable, and the resort is well suited for a short stay or for guests who plan to be out exploring, as it provides all the essential amenities.  In terms of location, the resort is situated on a very busy road, which can make access a little challenging, and road noise may be a consideration for some. That said, from our room we did not experience any noticeable noise. Overall, the resort has a lot of potential, and with some maintenance upgrades, it could offer an even better guest experience."
> **- Tom Porter (3/5/5)**

> "Unfortunately, our experience at this hotel was very disappointing.  We were assigned a room facing a main road with constant and extremely loud traffic noise. It was impossible to sleep during our first night. For a hotel that promotes wellness and relaxation, this was unacceptable.  We immediately informed reception and politely requested a quieter room. We were not asking for an upgrade or a sea view, only a room where we could rest. The only alternative offered was another room in the same noisy area, and we were told that any quieter room would require paying extra.  We felt that our concerns were not taken seriously and no real solution was provided. Due to the lack of sleep and the way the situation was handled, we decided to check out early and relocate to another hotel.  This was a very stressful start to our vacation, and we lost valuable time dealing with an issue that should never happen in a wellness resort. We would not recommend this hotel to travelers who value rest, tranquility, or professional guest care."
> **- Victoria Rosado (1/5/5)**

> "Over all the hotel is beautiful with relaxing vibes. But... I arrived after a long day of flights, and unfortunately the experience started badly. The receptionist gave me a lower-category room, explaining that my original room had a water leakage issue. I had booked this room 5 months in advance, so this didn’t make sense, especially when the hotel clearly had availability.  After waiting about another 40 minutes while she spoke to her manager, I was finally given the room I originally booked. I specifically asked if everything was fine with it, and she assured me there was no issue.  The next night, I found out that wasn’t true. In the middle of the night, the entire bathroom flooded, and water spread into the entrance and carpet, likely from the neighboring room. It was actually dangerous, and I almost slipped.  Instead of relaxation, the stay felt frustrating. It’s a shame, because the hotel itself has good potential. the pool is nice and the beach is beautiful. But the management is clearly lacking.  I also didn’t receive any apology or compensation throughout my 8-night stay.  One more note: the bed is quite hard, so keep that in mind if you prefer a softer mattress."
> **- מגנטים ענבר איזנמן Inbar Eisenman Imagnetim (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samaya-wellness-resort-1.jpg','062 709 9317','171/4, ตำบล มะเร็ต Koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.1,0,0,0,NULL,'https://hotels.cloudbeds.com/reservation/NBcvnW','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.063+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.063+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samaya-wellness-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samaya-wellness-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15026479968915338345',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samphatao-tour','standard','cmr07ihk900odq8xd4tp124wv','Samphatao Tour','## Top Reviews
> "●Thanks for 2 awesome days of tours the service was excellent and attention to detail was perfect. Communication was on point. ●The 4x4 personalized jeep tour MAIKEI really made it super special he has an amazing personality.   The group just loved everything about him  ♡♡ #kudosMaikei"
> **- Jocelyn Van Der Vendt (5/5/5)**

> "Excellent professionals, which arrange for U everything what U need based to yours expectations & make your vacation in Koh Samui absolutely great. 👌😉 If You wants trips or transportation or….😊nothing is for them impossible. During our stay they cover 3 trips & transportations…which was really excellent & overestimated our expectation. Soo if You need absolutely friendly proffesionals which cover every yours needs Samphatao tour is best choice👌😎"
> **- Martin Letko (5/5/5)**

> "​I strongly advise anyone visiting Koh Samui to avoid booking with this operator. If you value your money and expect even a basic level of professional integrity, look elsewhere. ​I booked a tour with them three weeks in advance. Unfortunately, due to unforeseen circumstances, I had to cancel and provided 48 hours'' notice. Despite this reasonable timeframe, the company refused to provide a refund. ​Here is why you should be wary: ​Hidden Terms: Their website mentions nothing about a cancellation policy. However, when I asked for my money back, they suddenly claimed their policy requires a minimum of 72 hours'' notice for a refund. ​Zero Flexibility: They refused a partial refund and would not even provide a voucher for a future trip. ​Insulting "
> **- Ivan Milev (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samphatao-tour-1.jpg','098 334 5474','Lamai, 34/1 Soi Tavon, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://samphataotour.com/','["Monday: 12:00 – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: Closed","Wednesday: 12:00 – 8:00 PM","Thursday: Closed","Friday: 12:00 – 8:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.065+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.065+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samphatao-tour-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samphatao-tour-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=18168678451930881938',NULL,NULL);
