INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samsung','standard','cmr07ihkh00ofq8xd2mi63crf','Samsung','## Top Reviews
> "Had 2 mobile phones and 1 tablet, Minor screen problem on 2 and one device water damage. I asked if they could check how much it would be to repair and left the devices at the shop. They texted me the day after. Devices with screen problems were to expensive for it to make sense to repair. The water damaged device was irreparable. I went to the shop to pick up and the asked for 642 baht in service fee. This service fee was never mentioned before. Also, part of the service fee were for the irreparable phone."
> **- Martin (1/5/5)**

> "My wife''s Samsung S22 Ultra screen got damaged after a software update. A bright white line appeared on the screen, and after checking online, I realized the only solution was to replace it. The phone had never been dropped or damaged, but I still had to pay for the repair, which was frustrating.  I was told to take the phone to the Samsung Customer Service center, and honestly, I didn’t expect much from their service. But to my surprise, the staff was friendly and even helped us get a discount. They reminded us about our extended warranty, which gave us a 30% discount, and the repair was done within a few hours.  Although I’m disappointed with the product, I was happy with the service. The team was kind and helpful, so I’m giving them 5 stars for their excellent service.  A special shoutout to Ms.Charlita (Tang) & Ms. Ploypailin (Ploy) for this amazing experience.  Loy Machedo"
> **- Loy Machedo (LOYMACHEDO) (5/5/5)**

> "Consumer Beware  I had a frustrating experience with this repair service. Here’s what happened: •   I called them to fix my washing machine. When I went to check on the repair, I saw them replacing the motor, even though that wasn’t the issue. It made me wonder if they swapped out my good motor for another one. They claimed the motor was under warranty (how would they even know, since the machine is two years old?). Despite replacing the motor, the washing machine still wasn’t fixed. •   I called them back and had to pay additional money for further repairs.  Later, I asked them to repair my TV. They said it needed a new chip, so I paid for the replacement. However, the TV stopped working the very next day. When I called them again, they claimed a different issue was causing the problem and asked for more money. By this point, the total cost they demanded was equivalent to the price of a larger, brand-new TV.  My advice: If something is broken and the repair cost adds up, consider buying a new one instead of dealing with unreliable repairs."
> **- แอล Alex (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samsung-1.jpg','02 689 3232','108 33 หมู่1 ถ. ทวีราษฎร์ภักดี Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.9,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.samsung.com/th/support','["Monday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM","Thursday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM","Friday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.073+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.073+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samsung-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samsung-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9362566730350294057',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-airport-shuttle-service','standard','cmr07ihkj00ogq8xd692zh375','Samui Airport Shuttle Service','## Top Reviews
> "As a Thai traveler with direct experience using the shared van shuttle and ferry transfer service at Samui Airport to Koh Phangan, I had a very disappointing experience.  The van driver dropped me at the wrong pier. What made it even more frustrating was that before leaving the van, I specifically asked whether he wanted to check my ticket first, and he said there was no need. As a result, I ended up at the incorrect pier and had to urgently book a motorbike taxi myself just to make it to the correct ferry on time.  Afterward, I checked the company’s Google reviews and was not surprised to see a rating of only 1.7 stars. I have requested a refund for the van transfer and will continue pursuing the matter with the company.  More importantly, this service represents one of the very first experiences many tourists have upon arriving in Thailand. The tourism authorities should not allow a service provider with such consistently poor reviews to operate at the airport — especially not in a way that effectively monopolizes the service.  It damages Thailand’s image and reputation at a time when the country is working hard to elevate the quality of its tourism industry. Frankly, it is an embarrassment to the country and to the many Thai people who genuinely care about delivering warm, professional hospitality."
> **- Duangporn Leelalumlert (1/5/5)**

> "Disappointing service at KSM arrival airport exit. We were approached to use their service and paid for it for 2 pax (140THB each) and told to sit and wait. There was no further communication how long we had to wait. About 30 minutes later we asked only to find out it was a shared service and the had to wait for more people going to the same zone before we can drive off. The guy then told us to get a refund and go back to another location to do it at the same cost with a taxi leaving immediately. Then we were told we had to pay more to get a private hire.  All in a pretty frustrating experience with complete communication breakdown"
> **- Zoe Lee (1/5/5)**

> "Ok, we should’ve ordered the limo from the hotel, yes, but we didn’t think smackone would be this bad and gave it a shot. We paid for the 1500 limo to Conrad koh samui, guess what showed up to take us there, it was a minivan meant for 10 people. Oh god, the ride was painful as the seats were just horrible. You’d think that if we paid for 2 man ride at 1500 baht they’d give us a more comfy ride like a SUV or something, not the case.  I wanted to give it a 0 stars, but the driver was nice and friendly, he was also easy to communicate to and let us off at a 711 to grab some drinks and chips before we head to the hotel, so the 2 stars are given to the driver."
> **- Pohan Tsao (2/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-airport-shuttle-service-1.jpg','077 428 507','Samui Airport Koh Samui 99 Moo 4 Bophut Koh Samui, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,1.7,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.smackone.com/','["Monday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ig1n003kq8xd72v6yb3r','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.075+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.075+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-airport-shuttle-service-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-airport-shuttle-service-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12908190314031724709',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-aquarium-tiger-zoo','standard','cmr07ihkm00ohq8xdlkmtztkr','Samui Aquarium & Tiger Zoo','## Top Reviews
> "We visited Samui Aquarium & Tiger Zoo with mixed expectations after reading very different reviews.  On one hand, the place appears clean and there are many beautiful animals, including colorful fish, birds, raccoons, tigers, and otters. For children, it may seem like an exciting opportunity to see animals up close.  However, as someone who truly loves animals, this place broke my heart.  Seeing tigers kept in small cages, pacing in circles in the same spot, was deeply upsetting. The raccoon looked sad and lonely. The otters seemed desperately hungry, as if they would do anything for a small piece of food. At the end of the visit, tourists can take photos with tigers or tiger cubs. The cubs are placed in visitors'' arms for just a few quick photos and then taken away immediately, which felt very unnatural and uncomfortable.  I understand that many families and children may enjoy seeing these animals, but for adults who care deeply about animal welfare, this experience can be heartbreaking.  I do not want to leave a harsh review, because the staff may be doing their best within the circumstances. But in my honest opinion, wild animals belong in nature, where they can live freely and with dignity.  This visit left me feeling very sad and reminded me how cruel humans can sometimes be toward animals."
> **- Jakub Zahradnicek (2/5/5)**

> "The most creepiest animal house I''ve ever visited. One ticket offered you the thrill and wonder. How wonderful! This is actually the thrill house and prison not zoo or aquarium. You should make your understanding correctly in advance.  My kids relentlessly said he wants to leave immediately, which never happens before. The scare and uncomfortable feelings are real. These atmospheres are built into this thrill house from the inside out.  May god spares these poor lives and never falls into this hell in their reincarnation"
> **- C Y (5/5/5)**

> "I''m far from being an animal activist. Sometimes, animals are genuinely better off in zoos than in the wild. This place seems to be breeding animals; there are a lot of them, but they don''t have proper conditions. This place has good potential if it were developed and provides better food for the animals."
> **- maybetomorrow (2/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-aquarium-tiger-zoo-1.jpg','077 424 018','33 2 Laem-Set Rd, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,2.9,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.samuiaquariumandtigerzoo.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 4:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 4:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ig3v004fq8xdw6q7afhh','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.078+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.078+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-aquarium-tiger-zoo-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-aquarium-tiger-zoo-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9581546372122535024',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-automotive','standard','cmr07ihkp00oiq8xdf5ev9sif','Samui Automotive','## Top Reviews
> "I cannot recommend Samui Automotive Co. Ltd enough. After years of chasing a suspension rattle that kept getting worse, and after visiting three other workshops on Koh Samui with no results, David was the first person willing to properly diagnose my custom Profender suspension setup.  David’s mechanical knowledge is next level. You can immediately tell he is highly trained and extremely experienced. He identified the issue straight away but was honest that the specific parts needed had to come from Profender. Instead of sending me away, his wife Goong went above and beyond, calling around and finding a specialist 4x4 Profender workshop and even offering to take my car there for me due to my work schedule.  Both David and Goong speak excellent English, are incredibly friendly, and genuinely care about their customers. Professional, honest, and reliable. Rare to find on the island."
> **- Ken Drix (5/5/5)**

> "This was my second visit to Samui Automotive and it confirmed why they are the best on Koh Samui. After having suspension work done in Surat Thani, I still had a very faint rattling noise that was getting worse. I could not pinpoint it at all.  David heard it immediately. On the lift, he inspected everything and found multiple contact points and loose bolts that others had missed. The main culprit was a hidden side cover sitting between rubber mounts, causing an intermittent rattle that only happened on certain bumps.  That level of attention, hearing, and experience is something only a top mechanic has. In my opinion, David is the best mechanic on Koh Samui. Fair pricing, no upselling, and honest work."
> **- Ken McTernan (5/5/5)**

> "Samui Automotive is not just another repair shop. David is a true specialist with deep mechanical knowledge across modern cars, custom builds, engines, and suspension systems. He works with skilled Thai technicians, including an ex Ford mechanic, which shows in the quality of work.  Goong runs the office flawlessly and makes everything easy. Communication is clear, professional, and friendly. Both speak excellent English which makes the whole experience stress free.  They also work on rare, vintage, and performance vehicles. If you care about your car, this is the place."
> **- Calvin International (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-automotive-1.jpg','080 159 5576','69, 107, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100092551878114&mibextid=kFxxJD','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifui0012q8xdzn158clv','cmr07ifv2001aq8xdag7cvjgf','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.081+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.081+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-automotive-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-automotive-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4577128935105344823',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-bike-tour','standard','cmr07ihkr00ojq8xdpy9d7jzy','Samui Bike Tour','## Top Reviews
> "Very friendly owner. They even offer a service where the scooter is delivered directly to your hotel, which is super convenient.:)  The scooter was in excellent condition with outstanding quality. Honestly, the best scooter I’ve rented in Thailand so far. We rented a 125cc Honda for 250 THB per day, which is more than fair!  You can either leave a cash deposit or your passport. I left my passport and can honestly say there’s no need to worry at all. It’s completely safe and handled professionally.  I would definitely rent here again and can highly recommend this place! :)"
> **- Mira (5/5/5)**

> "Had a great experience with Samui Bike Tours, hired a bike for seven days and had an awesome look around.  The bike didn''t miss a beat and the staff were super helpful.  We dropped the bike back and they gave us a lift back to our hotel which was quite a way from Lamai, would definitely recommend these guys."
> **- Jodi Cockburn (5/5/5)**

> "Bike was in great shape, clean with full tank of petrol. They gived me a drive both to and from the rental office so it''s was really convenient for pickup and return."
> **- Toma Paunovic (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-bike-tour-1.jpg','098 669 7533','5, 17 หมู่ที่ 3 Thanon Had Lamai, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://samuibike-tour.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07ifui0012q8xdzn158clv','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.083+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.083+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-bike-tour-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-bike-tour-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11919033762829557982',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-boat-charter','standard','cmr07ihkt00okq8xdvohknico','Samui Boat Charter','## Top Reviews
> "Great day out boat crew are really knowledgeable. Recommend way to see the islands. They avoid the busy times with the big boats so you have a more relaxed time. And private tour."
> **- Michael Thompson (5/5/5)**

> "This tour company was incredible! Super friendly staff, very well organized… they thought of everything! We just got to kick back and enjoy and I’d highly recommend"
> **- Kelly Hogan (5/5/5)**

> "Wow, we had a really amazing day on the boat yesterday! The boat was beautiful & so clean .. & fast! There were 3 staff on board, Golf, Fame & Pow, they were fabulous, so friendly & looked after us very well. I thought Fame was a really good skipper, he was focussed & safe the whole time. Golf and Pow looked after us with drinks, beautiful melon & interesting information. They are great guys  ;)) The places we went to were so special .. empty, paradise beaches, a breath taking view point & stunning snorkelling  The lunch was beyond superb!  Absolutely delicious & plentiful .. a feast with tropical wild birds singing in the trees. The trip gave us a wonderful feel for the islands & we would recommend it to anyone wanting to have a unique, memorable and pampered time. Thank you so much again 🙏"
> **- Steph George (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-boat-charter-1.jpg','080 640 2123','30/30 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.085+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.085+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-boat-charter-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-boat-charter-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5405222491040188499',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-buri-beach-resort','standard','cmr07ihkw00olq8xd58msyzra','Samui Buri Beach Resort','## Top Reviews
> "Really impressed with this hotel for our family stay over Christmas. The staff went above and beyond to make the place feel festive, and the breakfast/lunch restaurant was brilliant with great service throughout our stay. Rooms were very spacious and clean, with nice touches like beach bag and towels, umbrellas etc. The pool area is also huge and right on the beach with more than enough sun loungers. The hotel has a massage spot on the beach too, which is worth a visit and reasonably priced.  Gym a little dilapidated and in need of some TLC, but has enough machines in there."
> **- Max Firman (5/5/5)**

> "We are 3 adults with 2 12yo children and absolutely loved it at the Samui Buri. The location is more local and away from the more touristy spots. The rooms are comfortable and very clean and the staff is super friendly. We initially booked a hotel on Lamai beach but it was nuts there, far more touristy and full of bars so we literally sucked up the full cancellation and moved here. The beach is wonderful with a view of Koh Pha Nangen and there are many local restaurants and an open market within walking distance."
> **- Christine Richardson (5/5/5)**

> "Here’s a more casual and friendly version of your review for Samui Buri Beach Resort:  We had such a great stay at Samui Buri Beach Resort! The service was really good, and the staff were super welcoming and friendly the whole time.  The beach is beautiful and very calm — perfect if you just want to relax and enjoy some peaceful time. Having a private beach makes it even better.  The resort area is well maintained and has a very relaxing vibe. There’s also a gym and a nice restaurant with a big variety of food, so you always have good options.  The rooms are spacious and cleaned very well every day.  Overall, a lovely place for a relaxing holiday. Would definitely come back! 🌴😊"
> **- E (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-buri-beach-resort-1.jpg','077 447 275','26/24, Moo4 Maenam, ตำบล แม่น้ำ อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.samuiburi.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.088+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.088+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-buri-beach-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-buri-beach-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4145339311537784242',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-business-services','standard','cmr07ihkz00omq8xdnxzm26h2','Samui-Business-Services','## Top Reviews
> "I use Samui Business Services for my company accounts as well as to facilitate a recent house purchase. Vicky and the team were extremely helpful and highly professional. They helped make the house purchase very easy and I would highly recommend the services for anyone looking for an accountant on Samui or to purchase a property."
> **- Sally Kirchell (5/5/5)**

> "Vicky and Assawin always did an amazing job for me and my company! She''s a badass and knows everything about the thai law, visas, paperwork and so on! Big plus is that she also speaks perfect English, which makes everything much clearer and smoother! Highly recommended!"
> **- Nicoletta Milanese (5/5/5)**

> "Thank you Vicky and Winnex for always providing our company with amazing service. For being professional and caring. We are thankful for all of your factual information at times when things have been so unclear. I am very appreciative of your proactive emails informing us always of changes and new rules/laws to expect coming. We feel you go above and beyond our expectations."
> **- Candis Meisner (5/5/5)**',NULL,'094 946 2896','60/66, ตำบล บ่อผุด Koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.samui-business-services.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifu0000zq8xdvll5tv7z','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.091+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.091+00:00',NULL,'https://maps.google.com/?cid=15898584187161905483',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-camping-farm','standard','cmr07ihl100onq8xd8ij58ufw','Samui Camping Farm','## Top Reviews
> "This is a great stay, we enjoyed it, only rating 4 stars because setting your expectation is the most important thing to enjoying the stay and a few minor things. We stayed in the farm view bungalow which was lovely, rustic and so close to nature, exactly what we wanted. The experience is closer to camping (as per the place name) than a bungalow. The hut didn’t have space for our backpacking bags inside when we slept and the mosquito net had lots of holes in (and the replacement one we asked for) so we used our own. Minor things but important to know going into it.  If you want to camp this is 5 stars! Massive value for money. Location is great if you want to enjoy the peaceful quiet side of Samui away from the parties and main towns. You can rent a scooter on site which you’ll definitely need (although confirm the price before you do as there was a miscommunication with ours). The staff are so friendly and helpful, they even do transfers to the local points which is good value. Ice creams on site is a big bonus!  All in all not perfect, but who is, and the staff try very hard to make it a really good stay, so I’d stay there again!"
> **- Robert Hyde (4/5/5)**

> "We stayed there for a week and it completely changed our vacation. You can truly feel Thailand there. We slept in the cottage and it has everything you need, plus sleeping with the sounds of nature in the background is priceless, something a 5-star hotel can''t match for anyone at the price you pay."
> **- Davide Garau (5/5/5)**

> "Just spent few days there. One of the best resorts I’ve been in Thailand so far, ok it’s a bit isolated but they have everything you need: restaurant, bar, taxi, motorbike rent, and all for cheap prices. The staff is lovely and accommodating. I recommend."
> **- Smoking Skills (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-camping-farm-1.jpg','081 942 4036','122/45 Namuang, ตำบล หน้าเมือง อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://live.ipms247.com/booking/book-rooms-samuicampingfarm','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ift8000pq8xd7yujz20i','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.093+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.093+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-camping-farm-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-camping-farm-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3357936025077534079',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-car-wash-station-maenam','standard','cmr07ihl400ooq8xdqyum89xg','Samui Car Wash Station','## Top Reviews
> "Easy ..conveninet and cheap .. yes need t o work by yourself but ready to go and get car cleaned quickly .good job"
