INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-caravans','standard','cmr07ihla00oqq8xdpxg2ahb7','Samui Caravans','## Top Reviews
> "We didn’t stay here, but visited for the day.  The beach is well maintained, soft sand, shallow waters and peaceful.  The bar serve delicious food & mouth watering fresh shakes.  It’s a little off the beaten track but definitely worth a visit.  And if your into caravan’s and tents, then you’ll be in paradise."
> **- emma rose (5/5/5)**

> "Love my stay This place is like you’re not in typical touristic Samui. It’s calm and relax. I have my weekend feels like vacation. The beach is not best to swim. We enjoyed cooking our seafood bbq for dinner with the ingredients and equipment provided by the place. They have mini projector with chill out vibe music. Bar has craft beer and easy drink( no cocktail). The staff are nice and welcoming. Really nice experience."
> **- Patcharapa P (Autobot) (5/5/5)**

> "Beautiful location, vibe and family! We spent 5 nights in our own tent, not far from the water!  Lovely Drinks (including craft beers) and food available whilst on the most quiet and relaxing environment you could imagine.  Smoking shops and restaurants a few minutes along to beach.  If you’re looking to get away from it all and enjoy the sound of silence, visit this beautifully maintained camp!"
> **- Nathan Jennings (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-caravans-1.jpg','082 483 0947','35, 2, Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://samuicaravans.com/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ig4i004oq8xdv207xuh2','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.102+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.102+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-caravans-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-caravans-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14324106708619581076',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-clinical-laboratory','standard','cmr07ihlc00orq8xdqh24941b','Samui Clinical Laboratory','## Top Reviews
> "Great email communication before my trip. Prices quoted upfront with no delays Walk in service for my INR test performed and finished within 10mins. Promised results by 3pm today. Super fast service. Would definitley reccomend Samui Clinic Lab on the service i received. Thanks"
> **- Steve Payne (5/5/5)**

> "Samui Clinical Laboratory is amazing for quick and reasonable blood tests. So affordable that you can easily do this once a year."
> **- Jenni Lipa (5/5/5)**

> "Efficient service. No queue. Staff very friendly and professional. Very reasonable and competitive price.  You don''t need referral to get a blood test nor a doctor to get the results. I went there for lipid profile and liver function checked. Arrived at before 9am and got the results through email before noon.  Highly recommended for routine tests."
> **- Martlet (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-clinical-laboratory-1.jpg','077 966 141','H22P+824, Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 7:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 7:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 7:30 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 7:30 AM – 4:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ig1d003gq8xdfxkqj28w','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.104+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.104+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-clinical-laboratory-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-clinical-laboratory-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13802554756286968724',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-coconut-soap','standard','cmr07ihlf00osq8xd83xk3vgh','Samui Coconut Soap','## Top Reviews
> "These products are exceptional.  We have used them for years.   Normally I buy in the Lamai shop but today I visited the factory show which was very nice inside and a seemingly endless amount other products I have not seen before.  You may think the prices can be a bit high but you find nothing else like this in Europe or elsewhere and without the nasty chemical we try to avoid.  When you come to Samui you must visit here. Coconuts are part of samui’s culture."
> **- Saintybaby (5/5/5)**

> "Had an exceptional experience learning how to make soap with Mike teaching us. He’s extremely knowledgeable and knows his oils. Excellent experience. A must do for anybody in Samui. Thanks Mike"
> **- Nick Gupta (5/5/5)**

> "Very nice shop with an amazing atmosphere. We also were present during the soap making demonstration, thanks Mike for the great explanation! It’s nice to see these kind of family runs businesses on koh samui. It’s a really special place!"
> **- Joris Lijzenga (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-coconut-soap-1.jpg','091 721 9528','109 7 ถ. ทวีราษฎร์ภักดี Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.samuicoco.co.th/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.107+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.107+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-coconut-soap-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-coconut-soap-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=676222553414446122',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-computer','standard','cmr07ihli00otq8xdrmlzco1w','Samui Computer','## Top Reviews
> "I initially paid a 3,000 THB deposit for a screen replacement. When the repair did not work, I was asked to pay another 3,000 THB.  At that point, I was told that the police would be contacted if I did not pay, even though the repair had failed and I had previously been told I would receive a refund if it did not work.  A lower-resolution, incompatible screen was installed by the technician on his own initiative, even though it was clearly stated beforehand that a lower-resolution screen would not be compatible. As a result, the display flickered and did not function correctly.  The technician also changed the display cable unnecessarily, which did not fix the problem.  When I asked for my original display cable to be returned, I was initially told it would not be given back because I “had not paid for it”. The cable was only returned later.  I also asked for a receipt, which the technician refused to provide.  This experience caused significant stress, extra cost, and loss of trust, as the original screen that has to be replaced now costs over 12.000 THB, without a service fee...  I would not recommend this technician for laptop repairs, especially for screen replacements that require basic technical knowledge and proper responsibility."
> **- Tawua mili (1/5/5)**

> "Just GO if you have electronic concerned problems. I’ve a laptop problem which doesn’t turn on. it’s magical! He did fix and solve another my request in front me. Even though my laptop couldn’t apply English, he did. This means he saves my life. Thank you so much. I attached his workroom to fix. If he’s not there, call him! He can speak English ^_^"
> **- MISEUNG KANG (5/5/5)**

> "The place to go to repair a computer in Ko Samui! The man was very professional, efficient and honest. Thanks you, i was desperate!"
> **- francois gautier (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-computer-1.jpg','063 194 7888','150/11 หมู่ 1 Tambon Lipa Noi, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.samuicomputer.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.110+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.110+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-computer-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-computer-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=395060168264341854',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-crocodile-farm','standard','cmr07ihlk00ouq8xdefzzdpai','Samui Crocodile Farm','## Top Reviews
> "Pretty interesting, the show is actually pretty scary and intense. Of course: do not compare it to a western standard zoo - this is Thailand. Nevertheless it''s worth visiting! There are no monkeys and cobras (at least not when we went there in July 2025)  Shows are at specific times... I remember 14:00h and 16:00h"
> **- Stefan Hosemann (5/5/5)**

> "Stumbled by accident. The enclosures were in very bad shape and the crocodiles looked miserable. Also snakes in their concrete enclosures with no water or greenery whatsoever. The crododile show was a hard watch and completely unneccesary."
> **- Hertta Siekkeli (1/5/5)**

> "Despite reading the reviews we went. Many crocodiles to observe. Pretty run down place.Total stay around 25 minutes. Paid 1200 baht (2 adults and 2 kids). Not worth the money I think but they do have a lot to maintain. Did not see a show. Could come back another day to see one. We were the only visitors. Bring repellent. Would not recommend going again. But the kids liked the crocodiles. Do think the owners are good people and do love the crocodiles."
> **- BA M (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-crocodile-farm-1.jpg','077 239 002','30, 24, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.4,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.samuicrocodilefarm.com/eng/engstart.htm',NULL,'cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.112+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.112+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-crocodile-farm-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-crocodile-farm-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17150151493737837474',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-custom-gift','standard','cmr07ihlo00ovq8xdey6ied67','Samui Custom Gift','Discover Samui Custom Gift, a premier local services located in Lamai, Koh Samui. Find reviews, hours, and contact information.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.116+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.116+00:00',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-cycle-hire','standard','cmr07ihlr00owq8xdiw6shdft','Samui Cycle Hire','## Top Reviews
> "If you come to Samui and you are looking for an honest, very service oriented bike rental shop this is the place you wanna go to. The shop offers both motorbike, bicycle and mountain bike rental for very reasonable prices. If you rent for a longer period or just more than 1 bike it’s often possible to get it delivered at your hotel but ask the owner for the options compared to your needs. The shop also sells flips flops and nice sandals even in big sizes. Full English speaking owners and also very welcoming attitude. Don’t take a risk and rent from a small local shop. Go here instead. The bikes are in super good conditions as they are serviced on a regular basis to ensure the quality of your rental experience will be to full satisfaction.. I have been coming here for many years and I would never consider going anywhere else. Just read the other reviews and you will only find 100% satisfied customers like myself. The flip flop section in the shop is also the biggest in Lamai so you can be sure to find a colorway that suits you. My best recommendations is hereby given"
> **- Kasper Hammer-Hansen (5/5/5)**

> "Absolutely best bicycle service rent. When I came with question I would like to rent some bicycle, next was immediately advice a suitable bike for me. I got a wonderful workout. Thank you."
> **- Ivan Khafizov (5/5/5)**

> "I don''t often write reviews unless I feel it''s warranted. I rented both a mountain bike and later a scooter. 3 days each. On day 2 of my mountain bike rental, I rode 19km from my hotel in Lamai Beach to Nathon on the other side of the island. I parked the bike and did a little business. Upon returning, I notice the bike didn''t roll well. Flat front tire! Well, I thought "
> **- Paul Aoki (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-cycle-hire-1.jpg','094 117 9360','169/8 Moo 4 Lamai, ตำบล มะเร็ต Koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.samuicyclehire.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: Closed","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ifui0012q8xdzn158clv','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.119+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.119+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-cycle-hire-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-cycle-hire-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10532326462414118447',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-deep-well','standard','cmr07ihlu00oxq8xdj5fo56ap','Samui Deep Well','## Top Reviews
> "Came home to fix my deep well providing not enough water. They removed the pump of the well and left leaving everything behind. Then quoted me crazy prices for further investigation. I found better service 75% cheaper (!!!!) and didn''t follow up with them. But they still ask 8000 for the 2h spent removing the pump. Now I need to dig a new deep well...  Go with them if you have too much money and enjoying giving it for nothing."
> **- jerome carlier (1/5/5)**

> "She refuse to return my deposit for 100K. Is this scammer???"
> **- Sutthapa Tarrant (1/5/5)**

> "He took 239000.- Bath and after one year i still don’t have water, the contract he signed is worth nothing. No honest businessman. His company also was destroying many plants unnecessary and making a newly build building so dirty that we can only repaint it and when I told his manager, the manager threatened me like mafia. So I loose more then 250000.- Bath and one year, plus a lot of trouble."
> **- Hansi Silbern (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-deep-well-1.jpg','+6677430546','18 5, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,2.6,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.samuideepwell.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.122+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.122+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-deep-well-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-deep-well-2.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-deep-well-3.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-deep-well-4.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14075911643850898007',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-dental-clinic','standard','cmr07ihlw00oyq8xd6nvmyce2','Samui Dental Clinic','## Top Reviews
> "I can highly recommend Dr. Alex. His spoken English is very good, and before starting he will explain what will be happening during your appointment. He is gentle and above all, his work is concise and meticulous. The assistants are also very kind and polite. After numerous appointments, I can say that my personal experience here has been excellent."
> **- Dave G (5/5/5)**

> "I had an amazing experience at Dental Clinic Samui! From the moment I walked in, the staff was friendly, professional, and made me feel completely at ease. But the real highlight was Dr. Alex — hands down the best dental doctor I’ve ever had.  He was incredibly gentle, patient, and explained everything clearly, making the whole process stress-free. You can tell he truly cares about his patients and takes pride in his work. My treatment was painless, efficient, and the results were better than I expected.  If you''re in Samui and need dental care, I highly recommend this clinic — and definitely ask for Dr. Alex."
> **- Kohtao Bikerental (5/5/5)**

> "The doctor here is a good doctor.he speak politely and has a very gentle touch. All the staff are lovely.I am very happy."
> **- Ohmmar Aung (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-dental-clinic-1.jpg','086 470 4247','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ig1d003gq8xdfxkqj28w','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.124+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.124+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-dental-clinic-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-dental-clinic-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9374550755083706640',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-disc-golf-football-golf','standard','cmr07ihlz00ozq8xd76arkdp9','Samui Disc Golf & Football Golf','## Top Reviews
> "Good disc golf course with a variety of shot types required.  Luke the owner is a good guy.  Must play if visiting Samui"
> **- Colin Filliter (5/5/5)**

> "Fantastic disc golf course with excellent facilities (and footy golf too). Widely known for hosting Thailand’s largest disc golf tournament each year, beginners and families will feel just as welcome as the professionals. There are discs to borrow if you are new to the sport and a well-stocked pro shop too."
> **- ReluctantAardvark (5/5/5)**

> "Looking for a fun activity while on Samui?  Check this out.  They have all you need to get started."
> **- Margaret Patterson (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-disc-golf-football-golf-1.jpg','062 425 9406','62, 5, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.127+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.127+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-disc-golf-football-golf-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-disc-golf-football-golf-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2289596324965448435',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-diving-resort','standard','cmr07ihm200p0q8xdo6w7m781','Samui Diving Resort','## Top Reviews
> "Hi samui diving resort . Are you still in business. Website now up , can’t call or message. We tried to book a date but no reply . Are you still in business??? Thanks"
> **- Jeff King (5/5/5)**

> "Very nice villa to stay. Hakan was so friendly and helpful. He provided a map for the area with somethings highlighted and a large cooler bottle of drinking water. The pool was nice to cool off in. Great location. Close to fishing village and 7-11. We would stop there to bring back drinks to put in the fridge back at the villa. The only drawback, but not that big of a deal, is there is only air conditioning in the bedrooms. Otherwise it is a ceiling fan. We also went diving with Hakan a couple of days. So nice and patient with us. We are newly certified and these were our first dives after. Would love to dive with him again."
> **- Jade Stephenson (5/5/5)**

> "I was in search of a dive shop for a 2 tank dive and this place did not disappoint! Hakan immediately responded to my request and after conversations he had a package set up for me. We had hotel pickup to the pier where we did the standard, but important, safety briefing. We then took a 1hr scenic speed boat ride to  Sail Rock, the team had all the equipment, perfectly sized wetsuits, and fins ready to go as soon as we arrived. My dive master Steve was great, he maintained our safety while keeping it fun! The trip was effortless with planning thanks to Hakan and a successful dive trip thanks to Steve."
> **- K T (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-diving-resort-1.jpg','092 714 3871','122/52, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.samuidivingresort.com/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.130+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.130+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-diving-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-diving-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4557997753326045122',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-elephant-haven','standard','cmr07ihm400p1q8xd8md4fi78','Samui Elephant Haven','## Top Reviews
> "We had the most amazing afternoon at Koh Samui Elephant Haven. We chose to visit the Haven specifically, after extensive research found it to be the most ethical sanctuary available. It’s clear that all the staff care deeply for the beautiful rescue elephants. Our guide, Mr Thai, was a fine example of this. He was knowledgeable, humorous and gentle mannered. He helped to elevate our already brilliant experience! At Samui Elephant Haven, they  practise showing the elephants the upmost respect and encourage guests to do the same- not to encroach on the elephants freedom.  We were able to prepare food and feed the elephants, have a tour around the sanctuary learning some fascinating facts about elephants as well as the sad stories that lead the elephants to be rescued. The tour was followed with the provision of a delicious, authentic vegetarian Thai meal including starter, main and dessert. We would highly recommend this experience and support of the sanctuary so that they can continue the important work that they do. Thanks, Ella & Luke (England)"
> **- Ella Saunders (5/5/5)**

> "We had the most heartwarming and unforgettable day at Samui Elephant Haven. From the moment we arrived, it was clear how deeply the staff care — not only about the elephants, but about sharing their stories with respect and compassion.  This is truly an ethical sanctuary. You can see how well the elephants are looked after and how much thought goes into their care, enrichment, and wellbeing. Hearing each elephant’s history was incredibly moving and gave us a deeper appreciation for the work this sanctuary is doing.  The tour was very informative and included plenty of hands-on experiences, all done in a way that clearly prioritizes the elephants’ comfort and dignity. The guides were knowledgeable, patient, and genuinely passionate.  For anyone with mobility issues, there is a bit of a hill to walk, but it felt very manageable. There were always shaded areas to wait, and at almost every stop where information was shared, there was also a place to sit and rest, which was really appreciated.  Lunch was absolutely delicious and thoughtfully prepared. One of the biggest highlights of the day was celebrating our friend’s birthday — we brought a birthday “cake” that was fed to the five girls (the elephants!) at the end of our visit, and it was such a joyful, unforgettable moment.  This experience was educational, emotional, and deeply uplifting. If you’re looking for an ethical, caring, and meaningful elephant experience in Koh Samui, Samui Elephant Haven is a must-visit. We left with full hearts and so much gratitude for the work they do.  🐘💚"
> **- Jessi Nessi (5/5/5)**

> "I highly recommend this Sanctuary for everyone wanting to meet an elephant but not knowing how to without exploiting them. The caregivers are amazing, the place is vast and it''s very clean. The elephants are all rescues and can''t live in the wild. Sanctuary is really ethical - you can''t touch them. You can feed them from a safe distance and the staff makes sure animals are well taken care of. Mr Thai was the best guide, with a kind heart and nice jokes 😄 he helped us learn about the rescued elephant''s, their history and hardships. While very sad, you can rest knowing they will never endure anything like this again ❤️"
> **- Anita N (kita051) (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-elephant-haven-1.jpg','095 628 6160','137/31 Tambon Bo Put, Koh Samui Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://samuielephanthaven.org/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.132+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.132+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-elephant-haven-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-elephant-haven-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=18219655523928613364',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-elephant-sanctuary','standard','cmr07ihm600p2q8xdym5l9l0k','Samui Elephant Sanctuary','## Top Reviews
> "What an incredible experience! The sanctuary clearly puts the elephants'' welfare first, and it was wonderful to see them living in such a caring and natural environment. The staff were friendly, knowledgeable, and passionate about conservation. Spending time with these gentle animals was truly unforgettable. Highly recommended for anyone looking for an ethical and meaningful elephant experience!"
> **- Jana (5/5/5)**

> "We had an absolutely great trip at this elephant sanctuary. I did quite a bit of research before settling on this one.  They treat the elephants very well. No riding or bathing them.  Preparing food for them and getting to see them. The guides know all the information and can answer all the questions.  Pick up and drop off was smooth and lunch was delicious. Definitely recommend this place.  The one small thing I wish they would change - there’s SO much plastic being used. I took my reusable water bottle with me (as it said on the email, but would’ve taken it anyway) but there was nowhere to refill it. I had to empty a plastic bottle into it - which defeats the whole point."
> **- Becky Walker (5/5/5)**

> "Fantastic ethical elephant sanctuary. All interactions are based on voluntary participation by the elephants, meaning they can walk away any time they want (which happened while we were about to watch two in the pool - people are NOT allowed to swim the elephants here, it''s an area that they get to bathe alone - these elephants decided to wander away so our group followed and watched them play in the mud from  a safe distance instead). There was an injured dog on the property, it had a very painful looking wound on the hind paw. I asked staff and was told the dog belonged to the neighbors, I sincerely hope the dog gets the medical attention it needs."
> **- Barbara Kozicki (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-elephant-sanctuary-1.jpg','095 269 8343','Samui Elephant Sanctuary 108/52 ถ. ทวีราษฎร์ภักดี Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.samuielephantsanctuary.org/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.134+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.134+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-elephant-sanctuary-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-elephant-sanctuary-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7917651528894174985',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-emerald-condotel','standard','cmr07ihm800p3q8xddx70vu7g','Samui Emerald Condotel','## Top Reviews
> "I visit Samui Emerald Condominiums regularly and I am always amazed about how well run and nice this little resort looks. It stands out from other condos on the island."
> **- Arthur van de Laak (5/5/5)**

> "The staff are amazing, lovely spacious, modern rooms. They have a pool, gym and washing machine all on-site!"
> **- Chloe New (5/5/5)**

> "I move in June 1st.."
> **- carl fredrickson (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-emerald-condotel-1.jpg','6174 6660','H3G9+373, Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifv2001aq8xdag7cvjgf','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.136+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.136+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-emerald-condotel-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-emerald-condotel-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7694338700540318821',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-exotic-park','standard','cmr07ihmb00p4q8xdp8gd6p1j','Samui Exotic Park','## Top Reviews
> "We visited around 12:00 PM, and it was pleasantly quiet. More visitors started arriving around 1:30 PM. We also bought a feeding basket, which we definitely recommend. Feeding the animals was a great experience, especially the turtles. It was fascinating to see so many different animals living together in one place. The staff were kind, helpful, and it was clear that they genuinely care about the animals. A lovely and memorable visit."
> **- Bohdana Kráľová (5/5/5)**

> "We had such a wonderful time at the exotic petting zoo. The animals were healthy, well-cared for, and surprisingly gentle. Each interaction felt unique, from feeding the smaller animals to getting up close with the more exotic species.  The staff were fantastic—knowledgeable, patient, and genuinely passionate about what they do. They took time to explain each animal’s personality and made sure everyone felt comfortable and safe throughout the visit.  The entire place was clean, well-organized, and beautifully maintained. You can really see the love and effort that goes into creating a great experience for visitors and providing a kind, enriching environment for the animals.  Highly recommended for families, couples, or anyone who wants a fun, memorable, and educational experience. We’ll definitely be back!"
> **- GOLAN TACTICAL (5/5/5)**

> "Small but well maintained little sanctuary for animals. Kids and adults would have a great time here.  The animals minglev with each other and play together which is great.  Highly recommend getting there as close to opening as possible. The animals are a little hungry and very playful.  There is a sign at the start which shows what animals eat what.  It would be good if a smaller sign on each enclosure showed it as well (just a suggestion) 😃  Only little thing that concerned me was the white tiger pacing alot.  Im not sure if that is a normal thing or not.  Overall, great little place to visit"
> **- Sharon Wagner (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-exotic-park-1.jpg','098 563 7114','Maenam soi 1, Maenam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.139+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.139+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-exotic-park-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-exotic-park-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9745500552326021950',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-fishing-club-and-resort','standard','cmr07ihmd00p5q8xdqp8p2ll6','Samui Fishing Club And Resort','## Top Reviews
> "Me and my brother have been lucky enough to of fished Canada,Spain, South Africa and lots more fishing holidays. And this place beats them all for the different species available we caught 10 different species and some monster fish too, the manager Tom what a star fella couldn''t of done more to make us welcome and make sure we were in the right spots and with the right baits and guides, a Big Thank too our amazing guides taki nyein win akar they were incredible guides and couldn''t of done more to make sure we were in the right locations to catch,the accommodation,  clean, modern, with great access to fish straight from your room, the staff are all helpful and lovely. Food in resturante was great, with veiws over the lake. I would recommend this place to everyone it''s amazing!! It''s dream fishing. I''ll add just a few pics of some of what we caught. Cheers Luke and Tom P.s Tight lines everyone !!!"
> **- Luke Askew (5/5/5)**

> "I’m definitely not a fisherman, but I really liked this place. My boyfriend and I came here for fishing. We were given a gazebo, and a Thai staff member sat with us and helped put bait on the fishing rods because we didn’t know how to do it ourselves. He also helped us remove the fish from the hook in the safest way possible, without harming the fish.  The lake is quite large, with more than 200 fish and over 20 different species. We managed to catch two types of fish — in total, we caught six huge fish. When you catch a fish, you’re allowed to go down and gently touch each one. It reminded me of a kind of interactive fish park.  I definitely recommend visiting this place if you have the chance.  There were a few downsides, though. Check-in took quite a long time — the staff needed about 15 minutes to find the correct key for our room. Also, in the morning they didn’t tell us that breakfast was available. When we came later, it turned out that breakfast had already ended. However, they made an exception for us and served breakfast anyway, which we really appreciated — thank you so much for that.  On the territory, there are also activities like darts, pool, billiards, and a café."
> **- Елена Макарова (5/5/5)**

> "The accommodations and fishing experience were outstanding. We fished for an afternoon and morning of the next day catching 20+ carp and catfish species. The local fishing guides setup the rods and baiting for each fishing hut or accommodation hut located on the water front. The fishing time period was from 7:00 am to 6:00 pm. I would definitely return for the fishing experience if we ever return to Ko Samui in our future travels."
> **- Glenn Nowosad (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-fishing-club-and-resort-1.jpg','065 651 6031','66, 16 Moo2, Tambon Na Mueang, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://samuifishingclubandresort.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ig4i004oq8xdv207xuh2','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.141+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.141+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-fishing-club-and-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-fishing-club-and-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4339565228506684333',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-float-centre','standard','cmr07ihmg00p6q8xd4w9ufegr','Samui Float Centre','## Top Reviews
> "Amazing spa experience. The place is beautiful, calm, and very well designed, with a relaxing atmosphere from the moment you arrive. The facilities are clean and luxurious, and everything is perfectly organized. It’s the ideal spot to fully relax and unwind. Highly recommended."
> **- Mister Benz (5/5/5)**

> "I understand the concept that it is like a Bali massage/workout place. The facilities are very westernized - made for foreigners in Thailand. As a local Thai, it was really “weird” to experience a spa where the staff was mediocre for the price that they charge. The vibes are filled with gym bros and instagram girls. The massage itself was odd, there was only a fan turned on. The therapists (if you can call them that) weren’t experienced in any way. As a local Thai, this was really just a place catered to foreigners visiting Thailand."
> **- V VV (2/5/5)**

> "Great experience at this relaxing spa. Neat, clean and cutting edge setup with lush greenery that adds to the island vibe. The cold and hot plunge pools are ample and thoughtfully designed, and well cared for with cleanliness and maintenance. The 2 sauna and steam rooms - as well as the ice baths and spacious bathrooms with lockers - are spanking new with serious, invigorating temperatures. The facility includes a bar serving healthy refreshments and more; a mezzanine level with extensive lounging areas and treatment rooms. An expansive space - great place to relax and recharge and like-minded healthy groups to bond."
> **- Wunda Stone (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-float-centre-1.jpg','092 896 0807','37, 45, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://legacyspakohsamui.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.144+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.144+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-float-centre-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-float-centre-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8328321338940858760',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-gourmet-lamai','standard','cmr07ihmj00p7q8xdkppiy64d','Samui Gourmet','## Top Reviews
> "It’s my favorite shop🫶 An excellent shop where I always buy sausages and cheeses. There is always a wide selection, and everything is fresh and high-quality — you can tell they really care about their products. The owner is wonderful: polite, friendly, and always ready to help you choose. The staff is great as well — welcoming and professional. Every visit is a pleasure! I highly recommend this place to anyone who values delicious, fresh products."
> **- Roxi Zai (5/5/5)**

> "We were super satisfied with this rental. We were able to rent a scooter for ourselves and two friends very quickly and easily. Everything was uncomplicated and smooth. As a deposit, you can either leave your passport or pay 3,000 Baht in cash, so if you don’t want to leave your passport, just plan for that. The owner is incredibly friendly and helpful. Prices were fair: 250 Baht for a small scooter and 350 Baht for a bigger one during the hot season. Would definitely rent here again."
> **- Anna Fischer (5/5/5)**

> "Truly a gourmet place. They have great meat for burgers and steaks. They offer European cheeses per weight."
> **- Samuel Leško (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-gourmet-lamai-1.jpg','090 156 5688','33 37, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/samuigourmet','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.147+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.147+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-gourmet-lamai-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-gourmet-lamai-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4568848642981944255',NULL,NULL);
