> **- Anna Fischer (5/5/5)**

> "Truly a gourmet place. They have great meat for burgers and steaks. They offer European cheeses per weight."
> **- Samuel Leško (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-gourmet-1.jpg','090 156 5688','33 37, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/samuigourmet','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.149+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.149+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-gourmet-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-gourmet-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4568848642981944255',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-grand-safari-tour','standard','cmr07ihmq00p9q8xdnhowz2vi','Samui Grand Safari Tour','## Top Reviews
> "What a day!!  Great tour staff. Shakey start people not showing etc but when finally on the way we had a terrific time. Riding the roof top looked amazing and the squeal''s from the girls we traveled with was so entertaining 🤣"
> **- Bin Nugent (4/5/5)**

> "Great and interesting tour with most of the highlights of the island, by 4x4 cars. Very professional staff, with special mention to our tour guide. I had a really good time and enjoyed the experience like a happy kid. The travel agency lady staff was also super kind and helpful. Highly recommended, don’t forget the sun screen protector!😎💪🏻"
> **- David Robatti (5/5/5)**

> "We had a fantastic experience when we did the city tour with this tour company. Jackie was a great tour guide. He is informative, professional and made sure that everybody was safe and was having fun. The whole tour was seemless from booking to pick up and drop off at the hotel. We enjoyed every stop on the itinerary but the highlight of the activities for us was the climb to the mountain when they let us (2 persons at a time) sit on top front of the 4x4. The view was breathtaking. Lunch was delicious. Overall this activity is highly recommended."
> **- Grace Angeles (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-grand-safari-tour-1.jpg','093 554 3765','154 5 ตำบล แม่น้ำ Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.154+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.154+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-grand-safari-tour-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-grand-safari-tour-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2948738765022694435',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-health-shop','standard','cmr07ihms00paq8xdxoftiuib','Samui Health Shop','## Top Reviews
> "I had such a wonderful experience at this store! The selection of organic and natural products is fantastic, and everything is beautifully organized, making it easy to find what you need. What really stood out to me, though, were the employees — they are incredibly friendly, approachable, and genuinely happy to help. They took the time to answer my questions with patience and knowledge, and you can tell they truly care about their customers. Shopping here feels welcoming and personal, and I always leave with a smile. Highly recommended for anyone who values both quality products and outstanding customer service! 🌱✨"
> **- Gwend F. (5/5/5)**

> "You can find everything you need here. I was amazed by all the selection of healthy products, from cosmetics to organic food. I was looking for a protein powder plant based as I’m allergic to lactose. Price was very reasonable comparing to Europe. The staff members were very sweet and helpful. We got a free hug !!! And a photo too :-) Thailand at very best!!!! Thank you so much."
> **- Caroline Decam (5/5/5)**

> "Such a good shop with many products that you won’t find anywhere else. From essential oils, to organic peanut butter to paleo santo sticks to burn."
> **- Allen T (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-health-shop-1.jpg','096 634 8752','130, 39 M.4, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.samuihealthshop.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.156+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.156+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-health-shop-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-health-shop-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8183155189393147512',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-home-clinic-chaweng','standard','cmr07ihmu00pbq8xdtuhrmrn6','Samui Home Clinic','## Top Reviews
> "I was scared and confused being injured whille traveling solo in a foreign land. They were extremely friendly and helpful and provided great care within an affordable expense. Highly recommended."
> **- JAWAD UL KABIR (5/5/5)**

> "I highly recommend making an online reservation for a specific time before visiting this clinic. The waiting room was crowded with people without reservations. We booked online, and although we were seen about 15 minutes later than scheduled, it wasn’t too bad. The online booking fee was around 10 euros, which is reasonable. They took a blood sample from my son, ran some tests, and administered antibiotics through an IV."
> **- Milan Kozicky (5/5/5)**

> "I had a very good experience with Samui Home Clinic in Bangrak.  The staff are professional, helpful, and take the time to explain everything clearly. They were also very flexible in putting together a customized health check package tailored to our specific needs, rather than just offering standard packages.  The pricing is transparent and very reasonable compared to larger hospitals, and the overall service feels personal and well-organized.  Highly recommended if you are looking for reliable and professional healthcare on Koh Samui."
> **- Johnny Erlandsen (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-home-clinic-chaweng-1.jpg','080 669 6915','Bangrak beach, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.samuihomeclinic.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ig1d003gq8xdfxkqj28w','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.158+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.158+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-home-clinic-chaweng-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-home-clinic-chaweng-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16867554664855442665',NULL,NULL);
