> "I highly recommend making an online reservation for a specific time before visiting this clinic. The waiting room was crowded with people without reservations. We booked online, and although we were seen about 15 minutes later than scheduled, it wasn’t too bad. The online booking fee was around 10 euros, which is reasonable. They took a blood sample from my son, ran some tests, and administered antibiotics through an IV."
> **- Milan Kozicky (5/5/5)**

> "I had a very good experience with Samui Home Clinic in Bangrak.  The staff are professional, helpful, and take the time to explain everything clearly. They were also very flexible in putting together a customized health check package tailored to our specific needs, rather than just offering standard packages.  The pricing is transparent and very reasonable compared to larger hospitals, and the overall service feels personal and well-organized.  Highly recommended if you are looking for reliable and professional healthcare on Koh Samui."
