INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-home-pharmacy','standard','cmr07ihn000pdq8xd6q0yrhn5','Samui Home Pharmacy','## Top Reviews
> "UPD:  Thanks for commenting but I would not drop such a review if new pharmacist been kind, helpful and supportive. She is being opposite and no English speaking, just few words. Sorry but it’s was true when I visited 7 or so month ago.  //  Huge loss for all of us, our lovely pharma lady whom we are all respect and praising do not come here anymore as I’ve been told by other stuff who is not helpful at all. Such a disappointment."
> **- Sonja Nova (1/5/5)**

> "SIRIWAN (One Mind) provides excellent customer service. She is really kind & helpful and helped me during a difficult situation with such professionalism & no judgement. Thank you. The clinic also have very fair prices. ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️🙏🏻"
> **- Gemma Westwick (5/5/5)**

> "Super professional and helpful people. Made ordering and collecting my medicines fast and easy. Can''t rate these guys highly enough."
> **- Mac Williams (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-home-pharmacy-1.jpg','093 651 2888','4171 2/31, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.samuihomeclinic.com/order-your-prescriptions','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ig1d003gq8xdfxkqj28w','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.164+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.164+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-home-pharmacy-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-home-pharmacy-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3748116752718840967',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-honey-cottages-beach-resort','standard','cmr07ihn200peq8xd12vm6jax','Samui Honey Cottages Beach Resort','## Top Reviews
> "It’s a really good hotel and really good vibes. We extended the stay up to almost 2 weeks. Can’t explain how much we like this place :-) The staffs, I would like to thank you them for providing such a nice service every day. They are all caring for the customers and really helpful. Thank you so much ka. ❤️ The rooms are all located in the middle of the beautiful garden. Everyday you would wake up and see the beautiful nature in front of you. The food at the restaurant is also great as well. Another thing we like is that it’s not noisy, it’s such a calm and relaxing place with the good vibe. Such a peaceful place to stay. So we would like to come back here next time. We hope to see you again 😄 Thank you so much!"
> **- Faii (5/5/5)**

> "This place has the potential to be great with some updating and more care for residents. I think the previous reviews are very flattering as we did not enjoy our stay. Rooms are very dated and bathrooms terrible, poor shower and you can’t flush paper. Shabby curtains, bedding etc. It has a small pool next to the restaurant, although small its quite nice and modern. It only has 7 loungers at the pool so you will be lucky to get one. Outside folk can use the facilities all day as long as they spend 250 Baht so you will find randoms using the loungers and in the pool, leaving no room for residents. There are loungers on the beach but they are filthy and not set up each day. There is very loud music at pool/ restaurant that plays all day. Owner sits about the bar/ restaurant playing loud videos on his phone. Felt dirty here the whole time as there are no proper paths round the resort and the sand just gets everywhere. My feet were black walking in the room with no shoes. Positives - it’s a nice setting and you get lots of bottled water each day in your room,  restaurant Kirati next door is good. Happy hour BOGOF  for certain cocktails is ok and they left a valentine gift in our room which was a nice touch I could not wait to leave and would not stay here again."
> **- Glasgow girl (2/5/5)**

> "Paid only 60 € per night but even that was too much. The room above the reception was very dated and dirty. Brownish stains all over the walls, layers of dust in places that would be extremely easy to clean etc. Plus the huge cockroach I had to evict from the room. The pool and the common areas were in a somewhat better condition apart from the plastic sunbeads that had seen better days. Also the smell of seweage in the reception was pretty nasty.  However, the bed in the room was the worst part of the experience. The matress was extremely bouncy and you could feel every spring. I woke up every time my partner moved even an inch. Impossible to get a good night’s sleep.  The staff at the reception weren’t exactly rude but didn’t say hello, didn’t ask how our stay was, didn’t offer to order a taxi to the airport, didn’t help with our luggage etc. I don’t necessarily need all that but in every other hotel in Thailand the staff at least bothered to say hello when passing by.  Couple of positives; the location on the beach was good, and the breakfast was decent. The pool itself was also okay."
> **- Joni Leinonen (2/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-honey-cottages-beach-resort-1.jpg','083 646 4188','24, 34, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.2,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.samuihoney.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifsv000nq8xdrwnu123q','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.166+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.166+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-honey-cottages-beach-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-honey-cottages-beach-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7189789517139626828',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-honey-seafood-restaurant','standard','cmr07ihn400pfq8xd6hv683kk','Samui Honey Seafood Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "5 stars to everything. The food is perfect! Also the staffs, the environment and the atmosphere are great as well. It is such a nice place. You will see the whole view of the beach from the left to the right, and see Koh Phangan from here. I would recommend this place so much!"
> **- Faii (5/5/5)**

> "A very chill beachfront restaurant. During the day, the beach is not very busy. You can sit and eat while enjoying the sea view. The food is delicious, the seafood is fresh, and the price is not expensive. At first I thought the price would be higher, but the price is okay compared to what I get."
> **- Mmhewy S (5/5/5)**

> "Friendly staff and great Thai food. Everything is delicious, and they can serve proper spicy food upon request. The prices are fair, and the portions are big."
> **- Helena Borges (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-honey-seafood-restaurant-1.jpg','064 004 1975','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/Honey-Seafood-Restaurant-Samui-Island-483214325044390','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifsv000nq8xdrwnu123q','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.168+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.168+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-honey-seafood-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-honey-seafood-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1071061366380958967',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-honey-tara-residence','standard','cmr07ihn700pgq8xd7cpdei9r','Samui Honey Tara Residence','## Top Reviews
> "Very nice place, great pool. We had a massive suite, the aircon and kitchen were great and worked well, and the bed was huge. The location isn’t the best as it’s quite far from any type of centre and beach, however across from the hotel there’s a 7-11 and a local Thai spot with the best Thai food in the world (nothing has come close to it so far). Also, the water pressure of the shower was quite low but fine. they also have a lovely dog on the property. They also have a generator on site for when there’s no central power, very good! And the balcony is great too. Overal we enjoyed our stay very much"
> **- Phoenix777q (4/5/5)**

> "We rented your 2 bedroom villa from 11 to 18 April. The villa is very nice and big rooms. The villa was a little broken down every where and dirty. For the price of this villa, you need to clean and update it to a higher standard. This is not acceptable for this price. We will share this with Booking. Com so next customer can see what they get for 3.500 Bath pr day at your Resort.  If you want to say something to us, just let me know.  Alexander ☺"
> **- Lindsethmo Alex (2/5/5)**

> "Not recommended! Right to Feb 2026 - there’s a building site right next to the property making horrible noise! Knocking and banging for hours. This is not mentioned anywhere online, I was very disappointed to know of this when I arrived !"
> **- Hailey M (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-honey-tara-residence-1.jpg','064 004 1975','19/1 M5 Baan Plai Laem Tambon Bo Put, koh samui Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.samuihoneytara.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifv2001aq8xdag7cvjgf','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.171+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.171+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-honey-tara-residence-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-honey-tara-residence-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10538345178173175342',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-international-hospital','standard','cmr07ihn900phq8xdu8pg0wfp','Samui International Hospital','## Top Reviews
> "We had to visit Samui International Hospital twice in one day, and I am truly grateful for the care we received.  In the morning, we brought our young son in due to significant swelling around his eye after what appeared to be a mosquito bite. The doctor examined him thoroughly, explained everything clearly, and reassured us calmly. The nursing staff was extremely gentle and kind with him, which meant a lot as parents. Later the same day, I unfortunately got stung by sea urchins in the ocean and had to return for treatment. Once again, the team was prompt, professional, and very attentive. The doctor handled the situation efficiently and the nurses were supportive throughout the procedure. What stood out most was their patience, clear communication, and genuine concern for patients. As travelers, that reassurance is priceless.  Thank you to the doctor and the entire nursing staff for your professionalism and compassion. Highly recommended for anyone visiting Koh Samui."
> **- Pankaj Parihar (5/5/5)**

> "I''m so thankful for the team at this hospital, they took such a good care of me! I had an accident and needed to come to this hospital multiple times during my trip, I was always welcomed with smile and kindness. They made the procedure as painless as possible, the hospital was very clean and sanitary, all doctors are very knowledgeable and understand English."
> **- Karolina Krawczyk (5/5/5)**

> "Went with a friend for swimmers ear - so not serious. As per other comments. Feels more like a clinic than hospital. But we were seen within 15 minutes. All sorted professionally"
> **- Sheelagh Bailey (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-international-hospital-1.jpg','098 013 5479','90 2, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.5,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.sih.co.th/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ig1d003gq8xdfxkqj28w','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.173+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.173+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-international-hospital-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-international-hospital-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14798299341098763529',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-international-meditation-center','standard','cmr07ihnb00piq8xdus158rr0','Samui International Meditation Center','## Top Reviews
> "So Grateful to be able to be emersed in the presence of the Monks and staff at the Samui International Meditation Center.  We were welcomed to listen, chat freely, ask questions and receive the wisdom of Monk Nate. We were guided through the stillness of mindfulness meditation to help  with inner peace. The amount of peace and stillness that I felt within, after my visit, lasted for hours. My husband and I only could only attend a one off meditation, although we will be returning to the Samui International Meditation Center for a longer period in the future. In the meantime we hope to make the most of Monk Nate''s online meditation guidance. Thank you x"
> **- Naomi Touzel (5/5/5)**

> "I spent 4 days at this meditation center. Nate was our monk/teacher during my stay. He was incredible… I learned so much about meditation and Buddhism. He was a very patient and kind teacher, and he shared his joy in teaching with us. I met Nicky, the woman who took care of the food and other maintenance tasks at the center. She was a very cheerful and extremely kind woman. Thank you very much Nate and Nicky. 🙏🏻  I thank the center for taking me with the monks each morning for the offering ritual. It''s a peaceful and well-maintained center.  Thank you for this wonderful experience. ✨"
> **- Angie Bricout (5/5/5)**

> "We spent a full day at this Samui international meditation center, it was one of my greatest experiences I’ve ever connected before. From that moment when we came to the compound, we felt a sense of peace that gently settled in to our mind. Everyone is so warmly welcome, smile and peaceful. We joined 45 minutes meditation with the control and guidance of the Monk, Tri ( Ko Kyi Lwin; Burmese name before ). Thank you so much for letting us to join this daily program. It’s super special for me. With full of gratitude!!"
> **- Elias Ryder (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-international-meditation-center-1.jpg',NULL,'106, 23 Moo1, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.samui-meditation.com/','["Monday: 6:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 6:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 6:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 6:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 6:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 6:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 6:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.175+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.175+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-international-meditation-center-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-international-meditation-center-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16751726046361594851',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-island-adventures','standard','cmr07ihne00pjq8xdzrwls461','Samui Island Adventures','## Top Reviews
> "I had a great time. This is good for all levels of riders. But you must notify them of your skill level.  There are easy paths, medium, and hard paths.  There are plenty of stops along the way in the mountains if you need a break.  My bike ran good and was set up good."
> **- Sterling LaPratt (5/5/5)**

> "We had a blast on our Enduro tour! We were equipped with great protective gear and bikes. The route (we chose the medium-level route) contained a good mix of challenging and fun dirt roads and back country roads. The guide did a great job as well, always making sure that we were fine and explaining how to get through tough sections."
> **- Philipp Andermatt (5/5/5)**

> "Absolute blast!!!! Highly recommended for anyone who wants that adrenaline kick. Did the full day(7 hours) tour around the mountains, ps- the routes change from narrow tracks to rocky hills in a blink of an eye. The guide was amazing, so enthusiastic towards everything and brought only good vibes which really made my day being a solo traveller as it was only me and the guide. He took me to temples, did the samui zip lines, took me to a waterfall for swimming which isn''t open to the public, and had food on top of the mountain in an amazing restaurant with a breath taking view. He took a lot of photos and videos for me and you can also rent a GoPro for your helmet for an extra 1000bht. I can''t say enough about this place and the staff..."
> **- Ashley Jackson (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-island-adventures-1.jpg','061 719 6887','49/15, ตำบล แม่น้ำ อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.samuiislandadventures.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.178+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.178+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-island-adventures-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-island-adventures-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16860727470160425775',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-jetski-safari','standard','cmr07ihni00pkq8xdsyzw1tl4','Samui Jetski Safari','## Top Reviews
> "Great day! Thanks to the amazing team and the great organisation!"
> **- Ivan Sincek (5/5/5)**

> "We went on a jet ski tour today, including a trip to Pig Island and snorkeling. The jet skiing was so much fun, I highly recommend it! The first stop and the snorkeling could have been skipped, and the jet ski ride could have been longer, as we didn''t see much anyway and the water was quite murky. Otherwise, we had plenty of time on Pig Island, and the guides were great. We would definitely book here again!"
> **- Caroline Be (5/5/5)**

> "I highly recommend buying jet ski goggles. Great trip, definitely recommendable."
> **- Thorsten Schultz (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-jetski-safari-1.jpg','098 668 8986','6, 2, Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifzl002uq8xdaadxjuc2','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.182+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.182+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-jetski-safari-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-jetski-safari-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5747364275451611008',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-karting','standard','cmr07ihnl00plq8xd54fpadvc','Samui Karting','## Top Reviews
> "Samui Karting opened its new location few days ago. It was our 12 yo daughter first time driving a karting and she absolutely loved it. The owner & the team were extremely friendly and made our daughter fell very comfortable. For those who hygiene matters, a disposable hair cap to wear under the helmets is provided and shoes (with new socks) are available for rent (extra cost).  Highly recommended !"
> **- Mathilde Wanderlust (5/5/5)**

> "Fun level: high! 🚦 Kart quality: pure lottery. You don’t race your friends — you race against which kart you randomly get. Some fly, others feel like they’re powered by hope and good memories. Only five karts on track at once, so expect short rounds and long waits. The place could use a little love (and maybe a wrench or two), but overall still a good laugh and bit of adrenaline on Samui."
> **- Frequent Traveller (3/5/5)**

> "Best Go-Karting Race ever seen! Great race, great karts, wonderful environment with palms everywhere, very friendly staff! Top!"
> **- Giorgio Carlo Roberto Albieri (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-karting-1.jpg','080 012 7149','101, Bophut Sub, 33, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://samuikarting.com/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.185+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.185+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-karting-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-karting-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12232377996692806789',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-kids-club','standard','cmr07ihno00pmq8xda4e1gs04','Samui Kids Club','## Top Reviews
> "Really great and important place because the swimming school is critical for children living in Thailand.i think the teachers are , I would say just fenomenal.its also not expensive (relatevly).can only recommend specially the swimming school."
> **- danny pipko (5/5/5)**

> "Best place on island to get yoir kids to high level of fitness amd swimming. I dont know about educational courses so cant commemt. But if you want fit competive kids in warm environment aok. English weak"
> **- South Samui Villas Koh Samui (4/5/5)**

> "The swimming instructor is excellent. They also offer tutoring in general subjects."
> **- KikDIY (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-kids-club-1.jpg','081 606 2501','9°31''17. 99°56''35.2"E, 9/23 ถนน บรมราชชนนี เขต ทวีวัฒนา อำเภอเกาะสมุย กรุงเทพมหานคร 10170, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/samui.kidsclub','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: Closed","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: Closed","Friday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ig1h003iq8xdb1g9nifo','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.188+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.188+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-kids-club-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-kids-club-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2490645303798836826',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-language-school','standard','cmr07ihnq00pnq8xd9gp28ehe','Samui Language School','## Top Reviews
> "A great language school for learning English or Thai. One of the nicest communities of teachers, staff and students at this center.  A great place learning languages even if you don''t need an education visa 🕊🕊"
> **- Kamolchanok Leelasarn (5/5/5)**

> "Every aspect of this Thai language  school suited me and the standard of the teaching was very high.  Whats more, it turned out to be a lot of fun as well as the teachers and all the staff were great ''craic'' and really went out of their way to make sure that my experience was laid back as well as effective.  The location ( Lamai town) was really convenient as I was living down the East coast of Samui and it saved me having to travel all the way to Bophut or Maenam. Highly recommended!"
> **- EamonnBlaney (5/5/5)**

> "I am very glad that I chose this English language school for my studies. The learning process was not only beneficial but also incredibly fun. The classes were interactive and engaging, making the language learning process a real adventure. Additionally, the admission process to the school was very easy. I particularly want to mention the help of the school''s employee P Toy, who assisted me with all the paperwork. Thanks to her support and professionalism, I was able to start my studies quickly and without any problems. I recommend this school to anyone who wants to learn English in a friendly and supportive atmosphere!"
> **- Disident (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-language-school-1.jpg','077 960 103','142/24-25, Moo 4, (opposite the IT Complex), ตำบล มะเร็ต Koh Samui, Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'http://samuilanguageschool.org/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.190+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.190+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-language-school-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-language-school-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8347516844266978508',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-lapidary','standard','cmr07ihns00poq8xd75tbwemv','Samui Lapidary','## Top Reviews
> "This shop are amazing and sells stunning top quality jewellery’s. Owner are very professional and helpfully!!! We purchased stunning 18k gold ring with Ruby’s & diamonds🤩🤩🤩 which looks so elegant and beautiful specially in day light on sun!!! Thanks again for warm welcoming and nice experience by choosing are beautiful stones ring 💍"
> **- Andrius Soliunas (5/5/5)**

> "Fantastic service.  Sent an email via the website and i was promptly contacted by Charlie.  I designed a custom diamond ring and the communication from Charlie throughout was brilliant.  I would definitely recommend and will use them again."
> **- Josh Jacobs (5/5/5)**

> "This review came from a friend who was incredibly happy with her choices of stacking ring set and a dainty emerald necklace, so I write her thoughts here- on her behalf.  The jewwelry pieces here are excellent; their workmanship is top quality and contemporary in style. My friend was especially pleased with the lovely 18k pendant and the rose gold stacking ring set. She was looking for delicate pieces set with emeralds, as emerald is her birthstone.  The staff and owner were professional and helpful; and accommodating while we looked over their selections and my friend making her decision. I cannot recommend enough stopping by this shop if you are looking for something special while you are in Samui. Their selections are truly vast, as they sell gold, silver, pearls and individual gemstones."
> **- Ceylon Soul (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-lapidary-1.jpg','081 861 4888','9, 1, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://samuilapidary.com/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.192+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.192+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-lapidary-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-lapidary-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2741355102259954324',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-lost-souls-scooter-club','standard','cmr07ihnv00ppq8xd07li66cf','Samui Lost Souls Scooter Club','Discover Samui Lost Souls Scooter Club, a premier activities located in Bang Rak, Koh Samui. Find reviews, hours, and contact information.',NULL,'099 000 3440','9 59, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,532,0,0,NULL,'https://samuiscooters.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.195+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.195+00:00',NULL,'https://maps.google.com/?cid=13818093895327759917&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-luggage-storage','standard','cmr07ihnx00pqq8xd29peur0s','Samui Luggage Storage','## Top Reviews
> "So happy that this place exists. Made my life so easy to travel to the islands for a week. I celebrated while I relaxed only having what I needed for my trip. Too easy! They''ll pick up before you leave and reunite you on your return to whichever Samui hotel you land at. 10/10 😁"
> **- dom hayden (5/5/5)**

> "The owners are super friendly and helpful. I left my things there for over 1 year, it’s super clean, air conditioned, very safe, if you want to leave your belongings in a safe place that does not have mold and is ideally air conditioned, this is the right place to go. They were very flexible with my contract, and even when I picked up my belongings 2 months after the contract finished, they kept my things safe and did not give me any pressure. The owner even helped me to sell my things on facebook, when I came back to pick up the leftovers and had only a few hours time on the island and didn’t have time to put an advertisement online at all. This storage place also has a coworking space upstairs. It’s an amazing location with amazing owners, 5 stars"
> **- Cupoftea Withouthoney (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing service! Extremely communicative with great prices. I was able to explore the islands without the hassle of dragging my large suitcase around. They offer pick up and drop off service as well. Made my traveling much easier and relaxing. Thank you so much!"
> **- Erin (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-luggage-storage-1.jpg','083 449 7940','10, 81 Maenam, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.197+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.197+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-luggage-storage-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-luggage-storage-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2924460923563705147',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-luxury-boats','standard','cmr07iho000prq8xdba16d6a9','Samui Luxury Boats','## Top Reviews
> "From start to finish, the service from Samui Luxury Boats was excellent, with great communication the whole way through. Chris and the team were fantastic — so friendly, professional and made everything effortless. The boat was perfect and spacious, the staff were wonderful, the food was amazing, and the personal bartender was such a fun touch. Truly the best hens day and such a memorable experience for all of us. Highly recommend! 🥂"
> **- Wanderlust Traveller (5/5/5)**

> "An absolutely amazing experience from start to finish. Chris and his team were communicative and understanding from my very first message enquiry. They were patient with every question asked and eased all anxiety for the day. The experience itself was absolutely phenomenal. Am & team made the day extra special and it exceeded all of my expectations. The team met all our needs and made sure we were comfortable and having fun the entire time. It was mine and my partners most magical memory in Thailand to date and we couldn’t recommend this company more! Thank you for everything Samui Luxury Boats!!!"
> **- jessica elsey (5/5/5)**

> "We chartered a private catamaran with Chris on 12/29/25. We had a family of 8 and it was my wife’s birthday and the entire crew was amazing. They decorated the boat with Happy Birthday decor. We visited Ang Thong and the crew guided us up the mountain and didn’t leave our side the entire hike. We have travelled to many destinations and have taken private day charters and this charter tops everything. From the attentive crew to the amazing captain, this was a trip my family will remember forever. Thank you Chris and the crew of Serenity for the highlight of our vacation. If you’re looking for top notch service, I definitely recommend booking with Samui Luxury Boats!"
> **- kevin leach (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-luxury-boats-1.jpg','080 535 9140','26, 23 Thanon Bond Kai, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://samuiluxuryboat.com/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.200+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.200+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-luxury-boats-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-luxury-boats-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14631051514427719190',NULL,NULL);
