> **- Lamphan Kaewtongkham (5/5/5)**

> "Hello  I wanted to thank you for the website you created for me!!  It''s exactly what I wanted and even more...  The first sales have started!  I''ll continue following your advice on SEO, but I didn''t expect to start getting orders already. Hehe  I recommend you to anyone who wants to create a French website in Koh Samui.  Thank you for everything and best of luck! Marissa"
