INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-natien-resort','standard','cmr07ihof00pxq8xdulsqvlje','Samui Natien Resort','## Top Reviews
> "I normally write reviews after I have left an establishment but I found this place perfect for me. The reception staff have been fantastic Got an early check-in that was great. Staying in a villa very nice modern clean and super comfortable. The whole place is so clean and well taken care of. You are right on Cheweng beach. Breakfast was good a variety of foods to choose from. I highly recomend this hotel for sure."
> **- Costas Kyriacou (5/5/5)**

> "The room (No.: 403) was dirty on arrival, but after we reported it to the reception, they cleaned it tomorrow morning and sincerely apologized for the inconvenience. After that, it was kept clean every day. The breakfast was delicious, with a great selection of fresh fruits and vegetables, and a nice mix of European and Thai dishes. We really enjoyed the variety and the beachside location of the restaurant. The staff was always helpful, kind and polite with us. The male receptionist spoke very good English and made check-in and check-out smooth and easy. The hotel team made us feel welcome throughout our stay. The à la carte food was also delicious, especially the Thai dishes we ordered. Presentation and portion size were both satisfying. The beach was clean and good, even though the water had a bit of algae. Compared to other beaches on the island, this one was still one of the better and calmer spots. We really appreciated being able to relax there. The happy hour cocktails were tasty and came with a good discount, a perfect way to enjoy the sunset by the sea. The only thing I didn’t like was the coffee at breakfast, it was quite bad, and there was no alternative milk (lactose-free or plant-based options). This would be easy to improve for guests with dietary needs. Altogether, it was a very good experience. A lovely hotel with a beautiful tropical garden, nice rooms, and friendly staff. I would definitely recommend it."
> **- Akos Korpaczy (4/5/5)**

> "Was slightly concerned reading the mixed reviews, However this Hotel was a Lovely find, right on the beach, and minutes from the "
> **- Alex Stuart (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-natien-resort-1.jpg','094 801 9754','101, 2 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Beach, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.samuinatien.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.215+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.215+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-natien-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-natien-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12938946091825990827',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-ocean-sports-and-yacht-charter','standard','cmr07ihoh00pyq8xdqj5rarm7','Samui Ocean Sports And Yacht Charter','## Top Reviews
> "We had an amazing experience with Samui Ocean Sports! The staff were incredibly lovely and welcoming, and the whole crew was truly professional.  Kunta, the owner, is very experienced in sailing around Samui. He explained everything clearly and made sure we understood all the details before we decided to go on the trip. His knowledge and professionalism made us feel completely safe and confident.  Highly recommended for anyone looking for a fun, safe, and unforgettable adventure on the water in Samui! 🌊⛵✨"
> **- Araya Lunta (5/5/5)**

> "I rented the 30ft sanora a few weeks ago for a leisurely sail around the samui islands. I had a splendid time. The boat was comfortable and well stocked with drinks, snacks and fruit. The boat was easy to rig and great to handle. And the crew Sun and Reef were excellent, friendly and very knowledgable about the waters, beaches and winds. I highly recommend it."
> **- Vinay Pinto (5/5/5)**

> "I had such an incredible day out on the boat — the crew was super friendly, welcoming, and made me feel completely safe the entire time. We stopped at a stunning, quiet beach far away from all the tourist spots, with crystal-clear water and beautiful viewpoints all around.  There was snorkel gear and even a SUP on board, which made the experience even better. And the sunset… absolutely breathtaking.  I couldn’t have wished for a more perfect day. Highly recommend!"
> **- Sunny Sun (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-ocean-sports-and-yacht-charter-1.jpg','081 940 1999','123/117, ตำบล บ่อผุด Koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://sailing-in-samui.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.217+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.217+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-ocean-sports-and-yacht-charter-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-ocean-sports-and-yacht-charter-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11043961999529322345',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-orchid-the-ocean-beach-resort','standard','cmr07ihok00pzq8xd37ygefu9','Samui Orchid The Ocean Beach Resort','## Top Reviews
> "There were problems with the water in the room — it was flowing very weakly or not at all, it was yellow and had a very bad smell. It may have been due to the heavy rain beforehand, hard to say. The beach is not suitable for swimming, as it is very shallow. No one takes care of the beach, even though it is basically only for the hotel and a few nearby houses. The hotel does not maintain it, so when the wind blows, there is a lot of trash everywhere. There is also a lot of mess around the resort."
> **- Jana Havelková (3/5/5)**

> "Basic rooms with air con. Needs some renos. Very quiet and spacious resort on the beach. Great restaurant close by. Great for those not seeking nightlife or who have scooters."
> **- Al (3/5/5)**

> "A nice hotel complex right by the sea with several swimming pools. Unfortunately, the complex is marginal maintained. Nevertheless, I liked it there because it is in a very quiet location. However, the hotel is a bit remote, so you need a motorcycle or car to get around."
> **- Markus A. Jegerlehner (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-orchid-the-ocean-beach-resort-1.jpg','077 424 018','33 หาด บ้านหาน, 2, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.samuiorchidtheoceanresort.com/','["Monday: 12:00 AM – 12:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 AM – 12:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 AM – 12:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 AM – 12:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 AM – 12:00 PM","Saturday: 12:00 AM – 12:00 PM","Sunday: 12:00 AM – 12:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ig3v004fq8xdw6q7afhh','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.220+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.220+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-orchid-the-ocean-beach-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-orchid-the-ocean-beach-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9022202162983097851',NULL,NULL);
