INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-photo-express','standard','cmr07ihor00q2q8xd8kcxqbhr','Samui Photo Express','## Top Reviews
> "The guy in this photo shop is the most unhelpful and grumpiest I''ve ever met in Thailand.. However I needed a job to be completed and the next shop was 30 minutes away. Work was satisfactory... However... I''ll never go back there again...This guy should never meet customers and should stay in the print room... You''ll know what I mean if you ever go there. Maybe he took an instant dislike to my happy approach or his instant dislike to western people. Who knows..  Needs Must 🤣🤣"
> **- Pogg Ma Hon (1/5/5)**

> "Unprofessional and less responsibility I came here bc of the good reviews and it seem professional. I took a photo for my visa and the owner said wait for 30 minutes but, I don’t have enough time. so, I said I will come to take it tmr after pay the amount. ( not just half, I paid total of the bill already ) Today, I came to take my photo and they can’t find it. They said they have kids and kids just play around so, they can’t find my photo and said I need to wait for 1 hours to do a new one. Do they let kids play with customers order? If it something happens with photo so, they just blame with the kids?"
> **- Jirapith Jantaramporn (1/5/5)**

> "Best in Samui. There''s another shop close to makro Chaweng."
