INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-physio-clinic','standard','cmr07ihou00q3q8xd0va4aa0o','Samui Physio Clinic','## Top Reviews
> "I’ve been dealing with chronic pain for over 2 years, and finding people who truly listen and take the time to understand can make a huge difference. The team here was very kind, patient, and professional. They took their time to listen carefully and really tried to understand every symptom and concern instead of rushing through the appointment. I already felt relief after just one assessment and one treatment session, which honestly gave me hope after struggling for a long time. I’m very grateful for the care and attention I received and I definitely plan on going back. Thank you again."
> **- Lara Nart (5/5/5)**

> "Having pulled my back and potentially inverted my back disc. I was treated by gift. All relieving my pain and helping get me comfortable again. I am so grateful. Also , good communication thru whatsapp for documents and ecercise advise. Always on hand for follow up and appointment queries. Easy to find and excellent service throughout. If you have serious muscle strain or pain dont suffer. Take a visit. Very affordable price and youll be amazed how effective it can be."
> **- Yocal FM (5/5/5)**

> "I received treatment for a muscle and spinal injury after repeated pain killer doses did not take. Feom the first treatment to the last. The aftercare. Simplicity of use, appointment,communication were all excellent. Gift is a great therapist , i received ultrasound and electric treatment. Also some exercises and stretch to help treat the problems and their cause. I felt the cost was very fair and was matched with a hogh level of service.  I recommend highly. If your suffering any pain or muscle injuries. They really are miracle workers."
> **- Thomas J (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-physio-clinic-1.jpg','080 010 5781','157/41, Samui heritage, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.samuiphysiotherapyclinic.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07ig1d003gq8xdfxkqj28w','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.230+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.230+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-physio-clinic-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-physio-clinic-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16115414481213377454',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-pier-beach-front-resort','standard','cmr07ihow00q4q8xdblyo008r','Samui Pier Beach Front Resort','## Top Reviews
> "Myself and 2 friends just stayed in 3 beachfront rooms at this resort. We found everything absolutely perfect - especially for the price you are paying.  Super clean rooms, right on the beach, excellent affordable and very budget friendly menu, plus excellent staff in the reception and restaurant.  We especially loved the facilities for the children and will be returning again with a friend’s family and children in a couple of weeks.  Excellent value for money, super clean and very budget friendly. Directly on the Beach ! Highly Recommended"
> **- Ed Jones (5/5/5)**

> "The hotel is nice. Good location. Clean, big rooms. On the beach. Clean pool. Sand pit for children.  Unfortunately for us (I know it''s not the hotels fault and the staff try hard to clean it up) but the large amount of trash in the sea and on the beach is very off putting and sad to see.  Also, we paid an extra 500 baht per person for the ninja water park in the sea. I believe if you are a hotel guest the water park should be free to use or atleast come at a discounted price to everyone else.  We found the food and drink at the hotel restaurant very expensive. But there is a microwave, fridge and cutlery in the room to cook something yourself."
> **- Bridie Blakeston (3/5/5)**

> "Staff are friendly and service around food and drinks is ok. Its a budget hotel  2 star as described by hotel on here its a 3 star. so not expecting too much. We arrived from flight early in morning. Was told room  will not be ready until 2pm will try to get it ready before. Ended up being ready at 2.30p  workmen drilling and sawing until 9.00pm when I went to complain at reception owner was talking to a builder and explained he did not know it was still going on! He did agree work would stop. Work started at 8am"
> **- Richard Price (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-pier-beach-front-resort-1.jpg',NULL,'30/5 Moo 4 Bophut, ตำบล บ่อผุด Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.2,0,0,0,NULL,'http://samuipier.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.232+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.232+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-pier-beach-front-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-pier-beach-front-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8963625536976565142',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-pier-boat-charter','standard','cmr07ihoy00q5q8xdow73urxh','Samui Pier Boat Charter','## Top Reviews
> "A fantastic all-day boat tour of the Koh Samui Ang Thong National Marine Park islands. Our tour guide Two was great, he was very approachable and spoke incredible English. We learnt a lot about the islands as well as being able to see so many of them. All soft drinks were included and there was no shortage available for everyone. Our group was about 25 people, which was ideal as it still felt personal but we had others to share the experience with. The food provided was fantastic, it was all cooked fresh on the boat and was some of the tastiest Thai food we had. They made sure to cater for everyone and provided plenty. The pick-up and drop off direct to our hotel, included in our ticket, worked smoothly without any issues. The additional activities of kayaking, snorkelling and going onto one the main islands to see the lagoon were well organised and managed. Certainly an experience that we would recommend as was great value and completely worth it."
> **- Hannah Price (5/5/5)**

> "⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ Absolutely Perfect Day in Koh Samui!  We had an incredible day on this luxurious yacht — truly one of the highlights of our trip! The whole experience felt so exclusive and peaceful; we didn’t encounter a single other cruise the entire day, which made it feel like we had the ocean all to ourselves.  The kayaking was so much fun, and the snorkeling was simply breathtaking. I’ve visited many beautiful places, but the sheer amount and variety of fish and corals here blew me away.  The atmosphere on board was wonderfully relaxed and fun for everyone — we had kids and adults of all ages, and everyone had a fantastic time. Meeting and chatting with people from all over the world added to the charm and made the day even more special.  The crew was amazing — so friendly, attentive, and genuinely eager to make sure we were happy. They constantly checked in, served drinks, and made everything effortless for us.  And the food… wow! Everything was freshly prepared and absolutely delicious — we even got fresh fruit and ice cream! I had the best green curry of my entire two weeks in Thailand. We felt blissfully spoilt from start to finish.  If you want a truly special experience away from the tourist crowds, this tour is an absolute must-do."
> **- Tine Schafhauser (5/5/5)**

> "Lovely day out Got to see some buddha whales briefly. Facilities good, nice relaxing day. Good safety instructions, equipment and team watching you as you kayaked and snorkelled. Food and snacks  were nice. Staff very pleasent and attentive. Nice long relaxing day."
> **- S Hampson (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-pier-boat-charter-1.jpg','081 535 7768','404, 68, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://kosamuiboatcharter.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.234+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.234+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-pier-boat-charter-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-pier-boat-charter-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3475962376345482163',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-pool-tables','standard','cmr07ihp100q6q8xdyt18k8sh','Samui Pool Tables','## Top Reviews
> "We were very impressed with the professionalism shown by Khun Tar and his team.  Communication was very prompt when we had some questions about the installation date and time.  Everything went really smoothly from point of sale to the day of delivery and installation.  They did such a great job installing and clearing up.  We highly recommend their services and products.  Thanks again guys."
> **- Priscilla Sailor (5/5/5)**

> "Great Service by K. Cherry. I bought Pool, table tennis and dart from Samui Pool tables.  Both are great quality. Service is fast and great. Very professional. Highly Recommended if Anyone looking for those kind of activity in your house, just go to the showroom and ask for K.Cherry. Five Stars Service."
> **- Danny Kai (5/5/5)**

> "Great buying experience! Very professional sales lady here in Koh Samui and a great delivery team 👍 We love our pool table!"
> **- Antonio Del Grosso (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-pool-tables-1.jpg','088 530 2929','119/16 Samui Town Center Moo 1 Bophut, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.thailandpooltables.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.237+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.237+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-pool-tables-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-pool-tables-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5424408590060671255',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-property-finder','standard','cmr07ihp300q7q8xdummb3bei','Samui Property Finder','## Top Reviews
> "Fast, efficient, excellent service. To the point, specific picking, and available whenever you need them. The website is very detailed and enables you to filter exactly what you want to find. Definitely my go to brokers in Koh Samui. I wouldn’t go to anyone else. Well done Bob. 👏👏"
> **- A Sab (5/5/5)**

> "Really can recommend that company... Smooth service, very professional and passionate brokers. Good luck to you guys! Bob did an amazing job for me."
> **- Yura Mistiukov (5/5/5)**

> ""
> **- steve Calvert (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-property-finder-1.jpg','+66994031426','22, 13, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.estate-samui-properties.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 1:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.239+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.239+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-property-finder-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-property-finder-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2148972337274670592',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-quad-motor','standard','cmr07ihp500q8q8xdn66w3mdv','Samui Quad Motor','## Top Reviews
> "Super fun. Good mix of technical and flat terrain. Even more fun if you''ve driven a quad bike before. We paid £62 approx for 1 hour (2 people on one quad) through Get Your Guide, which included pick up and drop off from our hotel.  We ended up having one guide take just us around, so private tour essentially.  Bit of advice: if there''s a dip, try and straddle it, so both wheels are either side of the dip, and that way the quad stays mostly flat"
> **- Michael O''Hagan (5/5/5)**

> "I booked the full two hours for like 70$ and it was absolutely worth it. It was a real experience and a lot of fun. Through the jungle and across rivers – it was a true adventure! It''s important to note that the route is very steep and bumpy in places. This makes the ride challenging. I wouldn''t necessarily recommend it for inexperienced riders or children."
> **- Marco B. (5/5/5)**

> "In 2023 we booked a 2-hour Jungle ATV tour and we had the best time of our lives on Koh Samui! We are coming back in 2025! The ATVs were fun and easy to operate, the jungle was amazing, we saw snakes, and went through rivers! This company is professional and good!"
> **- Ian W. (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-quad-motor-1.jpg','083 645 9881','28 32 ถนนแม่น้ำซอย1 Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.samuiquad.com/',NULL,'cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.241+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.241+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-quad-motor-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-quad-motor-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2949821919179407491',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-resotel-beach-resort','standard','cmr07ihp700q9q8xdv5nq248v','Samui Resotel Beach Resort','## Top Reviews
> "We had one of the Ocean Pool Villas for our stay. It was clean, bright, spacious, and comfortable. The beach view and easy access to the beach was great. It was very relaxing to lounge by your private pool while feeling like you''re on the beach.  The majority of the staff are quite friendly and pleasant. Anything we asked of them was done without hesitation or fuss. The breakfast buffet isn''t the best I have had, but was very good none the less and with quite a good selection.  The location of the resort is down the quieter end of Chaweng Beach which I didn''t really mind, but if you want to be closer to the action you may want to reconsider."
> **- Ben Ferrara (5/5/5)**

> "We had a great stay here, Rooms were kept clean and refreshed, Good size with a nice view. Service was excellent, Had met our needs. Pool was great, Small gym but good enough if you want to get a quick workout in! Very happy with beachfront access from the resort. It’s a great location to visit the city and Surrounding area. We rented scooters Tour of the city with no issue.  Boom is the hotel customer service rep, she is an absolute gem! She went above and beyond to help us with our needs. Always smiling and happy, her  Positivity is contagious. She and her colleagues made our stay all that much better! 💯"
> **- Domir Deanelle (4/5/5)**

> "I booked my hotel through Agoda. I had two nights stay at the hotel. The staff is very sweet especially the girls on the reception desk.  The room was very big and spacious however the bathroom had an unpleasant smell.  The only downside with regards to the food was lack of vegetarian and halal options in room service and breakfast buffet. The fruit quality in the breakfast isn’t good either so despite paying for breakfast you have to eat out.  The location is nice. Beach is accessible. Although lighting of the passageway leading to the beach at night should be present."
> **- Farwa Rizvi (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-resotel-beach-resort-1.jpg','077 422 374','17 Moo 3, Chaweng Beach, Koh Samui, Suratthani, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.samuiresotel.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.243+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.243+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-resotel-beach-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-resotel-beach-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13021383521100242362',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-robotics','standard','cmr07ihp900qaq8xddkvlnnr1','Samui Robotics','## Top Reviews
> "Really good law firm in Koh Samui.  I contacted them for legal consultation and they helped me understand my situation much better. Everything was explained clearly: what can be done, what documents are needed, what the process looks like, and what steps are better to take first.  I liked that there was no pressure and no confusing legal language. Just normal, clear advice and a very friendly attitude.  Professional, honest and easy to communicate with. I would recommend Sittipaisarn Law Firm if you need legal help or consultation in Samui."
> **- Павел (5/5/5)**

> "Very professional and well rounded organization. Informative and helpful throughout entire process"
> **- Keep Diving (5/5/5)**

> "Very good, very responsible, reassuring."
> **- Auychai Sukthorn (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-robotics-1.jpg',NULL,'Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://timeandmoney.io/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.245+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.245+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-robotics-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-robotics-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4279182836881867798',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-safety-box','standard','cmr07ihpb00qbq8xd6xw35ik3','Samui Safety Box','## Top Reviews
> "So happy that this place exists. Made my life so easy to travel to the islands for a week. I celebrated while I relaxed only having what I needed for my trip. Too easy! They''ll pick up before you leave and reunite you on your return to whichever Samui hotel you land at. 10/10 😁"
> **- dom hayden (5/5/5)**

> "The owners are super friendly and helpful. I left my things there for over 1 year, it’s super clean, air conditioned, very safe, if you want to leave your belongings in a safe place that does not have mold and is ideally air conditioned, this is the right place to go. They were very flexible with my contract, and even when I picked up my belongings 2 months after the contract finished, they kept my things safe and did not give me any pressure. The owner even helped me to sell my things on facebook, when I came back to pick up the leftovers and had only a few hours time on the island and didn’t have time to put an advertisement online at all. This storage place also has a coworking space upstairs. It’s an amazing location with amazing owners, 5 stars"
> **- Cupoftea Withouthoney (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing service! Extremely communicative with great prices. I was able to explore the islands without the hassle of dragging my large suitcase around. They offer pick up and drop off service as well. Made my traveling much easier and relaxing. Thank you so much!"
> **- Erin (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-safety-box-1.jpg','083 449 7940','10, 81 Maenam, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifu0000zq8xdvll5tv7z','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.247+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.247+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-safety-box-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-safety-box-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2924460923563705147',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-sailor-grill-restaurant','standard','cmr07ihpd00qcq8xdiw6j6rjv','Samui Sailor Grill & Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "Despite the mixed reviews, we decided to give this a try since we are staying at the hotel for two weeks.  It was a pleasant surprise! I loved the mango sticky rice, the fresh coconut was extremely tasty, and I loved the presentation. We also tried the curry, which was flavorful and delicious.  I’m glad that we gave this a try!"
> **- Zsófi Ruzsvánszky (5/5/5)**

> "Great cocktails and desserts. The live music creates a great atmosphere, and the excellent service keeps you coming back for more."
> **- Ebony “Ebb” Walsh (5/5/5)**

> "Excellent Food and super delicious Cocktails with an amazing view! We stayed at the beautiful CELES Beachfront Resort and loved it! The SeaGrille Restaurant serves incredible delicious food. We ate breakfast there every day: it was always fresh and there was a great variety of western and Thai food at the breakfast buffet! I really enjoyed all the fresh pressed juices, the coffee was excellent and the food was outstanding! We also tried the dinner and it was more than delicious! We had fresh seafood as well as meat! Don’t miss out on the best dessert I have ever had: COCONUT PARFAIT with fresh mango and strawberry!"
> **- Ina Abeyta (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-sailor-grill-restaurant-1.jpg','077 900 999','175/3 Thaveerat-Pakdee Bophut Beach, ตำบล แม่น้ำ Koh Samui, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.celessamui.com/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifsv000nq8xdrwnu123q','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.249+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.249+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-sailor-grill-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-sailor-grill-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2617018637583828023',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-scooters','standard','cmr07ihpf00qdq8xdkib8bys3','Samui Scooters','## Top Reviews
> "No complaints: delivers all around the island, takes cash deposit, good communication, the 155cc bike I had was new and ran smoothly with two people without any problems"
> **- Kastytis Štaras (5/5/5)**

> "Great experience, super responsive, scooter in excellent condition. They deliver directly to your home and pick it up. Thanks again!"
> **- Alma Viva (5/5/5)**

> "Fantastic rental agency! The owners are lovely: always smiling, honest, and very flexible. You can immediately tell they want their customers to have a great stay. In addition to the scooters being in excellent condition, they share lots of great tips and recommendations about Koh Samui, which is really appreciated. It''s a pleasure to find fellow French people like them abroad. Top-notch service from start to finish; I highly recommend them without hesitation."
> **- Bilel BOUHETTA (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-scooters-1.jpg','080 418 1588','9/31, Save House Resort, ตำบล แม่น้ำ อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/frenchykohsamui','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07ifui0012q8xdzn158clv','cmr07ifsv000nq8xdrwnu123q','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.251+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.251+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-scooters-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-scooters-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15527774505219626585',NULL,NULL);
