INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-social','standard','cmr07ihpn00qgq8xd3n9p4l5e','Samui Social','## Top Reviews
> "Loved this hostel. Really clean and easy to talk to and meet new people. It’s not too suitable if you are here for a quiet stay as the music is loud from the hostel."
> **- Isabelle king (4/5/5)**

> "We booked a private room through Agoda and loved it! I even recommend booking the rooms through their own website. They have lots of activities to meet other people and will do anything to amuse you. The only thing I think is a little bit heavy is the music during the night, you can hear it a little bit in the rooms. Overall a good experience in Koh Samui!!"
> **- kaat bruggeman (5/5/5)**

> "so the hostel looks really nice, and the rooms are nice and clean. Great bathrooms. So overall thats pretty good but ohh my the vibes are horrible. Yes its a party and social hostel but no one is socializing. Everyday there is a DJ playing all evening/night and there is absolutely no one. The pool is always empty, loud music, no one is dancing.  The staff was kind of weird not giving us enough keycards for everyone (we got 2 were with 4 people). We were out of toilet paper all day and the cleaners came at 5pm to clean the room. From all the hostels this was look wise one of the best but social wise the worst. (Beds are very comfortable tho)"
> **- Kara linde (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-social-1.jpg','077 235 888','168, Chaweng, 62 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.2,0,0,0,NULL,'https://socialtel.com/',NULL,'cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.259+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.259+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-social-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-social-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17130626150387794672',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-soul','standard','cmr07ihpp00qhq8xdj8dhhdgj','Samui Soul','## Top Reviews
> "Amazing food and service! We just ate here & this was mums favourite restaurant after eating at over 30+ places in Thailand! The chicken fried rice, service and soul shake were top tier! The 3 ladies that work there were super friendly and even gave my mum some fresh mango and banana from their garden which made her day! If you’re visiting Samui (especially near the Na Mueng Waterfall, this place is a must!) P.S. the glass bottle that they let you draw on is also a lovely touch! Thank you again ladies we will be back again 100%!❤️🫶🏽💐"
> **- Suraj Manandhar (5/5/5)**

> "The perfect place to stop on the way to the waterfall! A very cozy café with homemade food and incredible smoothies. The dishes are fresh, hearty, and absolutely delicious — all made with love! A wonderful spot to relax and recharge before continuing your journey ;)"
> **- Yuliia Kazmina (5/5/5)**

> "We came to eat before going to the waterfall (4 min walk) and it was a literal gem. It is a family business and the food was so authentic and absolutely delicious. We had the best Pad Thai!! The owner is so kind, generous and welcoming! We absolutely recommend this restaurant!"
> **- Justine Audelin-Rinfret (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-soul-1.jpg','089 490 8088','32, 3, Tambon Na Mueang, Waterfall1, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://web.facebook.com/SamuiSoul/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: Closed","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig4i004oq8xdv207xuh2','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.261+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.261+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-soul-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-soul-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2058789557361388242',NULL,NULL);
