> "I have used Samui Steam Clean on 2 separate occasions for sofas that were heavily soiled with oil stains, marker, grease and food. On both occasions the team has far exceeded my expectations and extended the shelf life of the sofas another year. Extremely fast, efficient, polite and courteous. Would highly recommend their competent team."
