INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-storage-moving-solutions-namueang','standard','cmr07ihpu00qjq8xdjr9zn8uu','Samui Storage & Moving Solutions','## Top Reviews
> "I had a really smooth experience with this moving team. They handled both the house move and furniture storage, and everything was done professionally and efficiently.  The team arrived on time, worked carefully, and treated my furniture with respect. Nothing was rushed, nothing was damaged, and the whole process felt organised from start to finish.  Moving can be stressful, but they made it easy. I would definitely use them again and highly recommend them to anyone looking for a reliable and professional moving company."
> **- arabelle (5/5/5)**

> "Efficient and friendly service. I have used their services twice, once for a cross-island move, once for a removal into storage. The staff are always knowledgeable, friendly, professional, and careful with belongings. Their English is also quite good. Many thanks again"
> **- Donna F (5/5/5)**

> "It was a very good service. The staff were hardworking and strong. Good service, everyone is polite and works quickly. The items moved are complete and not broken. If you need to move your house or belongings, whether small or large, this company can help you. I recommend it."
