INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-tailor','standard','cmr07ihq300qnq8xdgy2inbtk','Samui Tailor','## Top Reviews
> "I was only on Koh Samui for a few days but the guys in Tony Tailor did an awesome job making me a Nehru style vest. They were great with measurements and fit, and it was awesome being able to customise and tweak the design based on a photo I showed them. The quality is fantastic, with a great lining material, even with some extra pockets I hadn''t asked for. They were super helpful and a great price. Highly recommend!"
> **- Christopher Peck (5/5/5)**

> "I was helped by David 3 weeks ago. He was friendly, reliable and most important, an expert!  I am very happy with my 5 shirts and pants. I ordered in the past in Vietnam and I like the Quality, fabrics and service of David in Tony”s shop more.  Also after the first round the fit/ size was perfect. It didnt need more rounds of adjustmens, so good for the speed. (And Nice for the wow effect!)  I was happy with the price and will go 100% back.  Thank you David!  (Melvin and Finni)"
> **- Melvin Littel (5/5/5)**

> "Went to see Mr Tony at his branch on MaeNam across from Cocopalm Resort. I ended up ordering three different sets of coat and pants in pure linen. There were so many beautiful colours to choose from 🙈😍. I have added a photo of the colour samples...just in case anyone is already thinking... 🤔😅 The pants are fashioned after the traditional Thai fisherman pants and the coat is a copy of one of my favourite summer pieces with three quarter sleeves and big pockets. The photos are of the olive green set. Great quality and craftsmanship from a very knowledgeable tailor. An excellent experience from start to finish and I will be back next year for more bespoke wardrobe staples 😎 Thank you Mr Tony!"
> **- M H (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-tailor-1.jpg','062 942 4751','25/1 moo 1, Fisherman village,Bophut Koh Samui, suratthani TH 84320, บ่อผุด, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://tonytailorsamui.com/','["Monday: 9:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 9:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 9:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 9:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 9:30 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.275+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.275+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-tailor-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-tailor-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12959965001288606588',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-teerak-663','standard','cmr07ihq600qoq8xdqmus06j4','Samui Teerak 663','## Top Reviews
> "Just avoid this place – not worth it  I live 2 minutes away from Samui Teerak and still decided to stop going. That says a lot.  First of all, there’s no A/C. It gets ridiculously hot inside, especially during the day. You’ll be dripping with sweat before you even start your workout.  Second, the equipment is super old and barely works. Machines are often broken or just feel unsafe to use. It honestly felt like they haven’t updated anything in years.  But the worst part? The lady at the front desk. I’ve never felt so unwelcome at a gym before. She’s constantly giving people bad looks and acting like you’re a problem just for walking in. One time she told me I hadn’t paid when I absolutely had — then asked me to pay again. Total scam vibes. It was uncomfortable every single morning.  There are way better gyms in Koh Samui with decent equipment, A/C, and staff who actually treat you like a human being.  I wouldn’t recommend this place to anyone."
> **- Mark Meshe (1/5/5)**

> "Gym with great equipment to have a good workout. Due to not having proper AC, I''m giving four stars. Fans helped a bit in between the sets but it was still a very sweaty workout. 😁"
> **- Pipsa Ervasti (4/5/5)**

> "A great gym with all the equipment you need. The space is quite small but it never felt overcrowded, and I always managed to get the equipment I needed. Clean, loads of fans (although on a hot day they won’t help like an AC), and I also appreciate that the floor is hard and not covered with a gym mat-like material. No changing rooms though, I changed in the shower, plus nowhere to put a big bag"
> **- Anna Bell (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-teerak-663-1.jpg','081 893 9697','HX9X+G3G, Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://timesamui.com/place_samui-teerak-663-gym_308','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifuo0015q8xdfahzrsp4','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.278+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.278+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-teerak-663-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-teerak-663-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8633436713483331456',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-top-gun','standard','cmr07ihq800qpq8xd9brk2gqd','Samui Top Gun','## Top Reviews
> "Everybody agrees the prices were expensive, however we had a pleasant experience though very short (5 mins for me and my wife). We shot the glock and a smith and wesson gun 10 rounds each. The service was basic with smiling faces and helpful staff. They even allowed me to setup my gopro and film with ease! 5% plus if you want to pay by card."
> **- Rachad Koaik (4/5/5)**

> "We had a really fun day at Ko Samui Top Range Gun. The experience of shooting at the range was exciting and well-organised, and we never felt rushed at any point. The staff were friendly, professional, and even kindly took photos of us posing with the guns, which made the day even more memorable.  One thing that did surprise us was the pricing. We later found out that the actual cost of the bullets is around £3 which is quite expensive. That felt quite expensive so it’s something to be aware of before booking.  Overall though, it’s a good spot for shooting, especially if you’re looking for a fun and different experience while in Ko Samui"
> **- Adam D (4/5/5)**

> "Listen, this place is not cheap, but for shotgun and medium calibre rounds it’s probably as cheap as you’ll get here.  Good little range. Decent friendly staff.  Really good for beginners  But if you’re a shooter like myself peeper to rack up the $$$  Other than that, good selection of weapons. They let you handle most of them and have a look at the them."
> **- Gabriel (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-top-gun-1.jpg','089 874 5289','SamuiTopGun Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.280+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.280+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-top-gun-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-top-gun-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8130701302739721850',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-utopia','standard','cmr07ihqe00qqq8xdcy6xy2yp','Samui Utopia','## Top Reviews
> "Really nice place, check in was ok, room wasnt ready as we arrived early so sat by the beach. When room was ready, the receptionist showed us around. Spacious and clean. No faults. We were in the pool view room upstairs. Nice views no one over looking. Staff all attentive and looked after you. Quiet and no loud music, outside of resort is straight into the night life. They offered they''re own taxi service to various places, which we used as it was cheaper than grab. Definately recommend staying here, but get a room towards the beach"
> **- Paul F (5/5/5)**

> "Great location, and clean room. Staff were very friendly. Access to the beach was great! However a/c was not good and the shower pressure was bad."
> **- Ricqui Dickinson (4/5/5)**

> "Unfortunately our room starting smelling like sewage shortly after we arrived. We notified the staff that we would be leaving early and requested a refund and they agreed, but since then they claimed that they submitted the refund but booking.com has not received anything from them and will not refund us. This is really unfortunate since we now double paid to find a room at another hotel."
> **- Hana Sawanobori (2/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-utopia-1.jpg','088 244 2629','124, 105 Thanon Had Lamai, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/Utopia-Resort-Lamai-Beach-Koh-Samui-113554410019784/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.286+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.286+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-utopia-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-utopia-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9075390581503324500',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-verticolor','standard','cmr07ihqh00qrq8xdmqaijfpk','Samui Verticolor','## Top Reviews
> "The rooms are spacious with a nice bathroom all the staff is very friendly The included breakfast is great,you have a lot of choice and can get freshly cooked eggs Unfortunately the room cleaning was just changing towels,making the bed and give new water. Still dirt in the room.  Would recommend 👍"
> **- Niko (5/5/5)**

> "This is our second time staying at the Verticolor. The hotel is great value for money and located a short walk to Central Samui. The facilities are clean, there’s a large pool with plenty of sun beds, gym and lots of parking. The staff - front desk, housekeeping are all friendly and very welcoming. We look forward to staying here again"
> **- Sarah (5/5/5)**

> "AVOID THIS HOTEL AT ALL COSTS. I stayed here for one week in Koh Samui and it was one of the worst hotel experiences I’ve ever had.  From the moment you arrive, this place feels like a trap designed to charge you for absolutely everything. They try to monetize every tiny detail of your stay. They rent scooters without gasoline, meaning you pay to fill the tank — and of course, you leave fuel behind for the next guest. Pure scam.  In the room? Only three pillows. Need an extra one? You’ll be charged to rent a pillow for the week. Yes, you read that right. A pillow. Everything is an excuse to take more money from you.  The breakfast is frankly disgusting — low quality, poorly prepared, and absolutely not what you expect from a hotel in Thailand. Completely disappointing.  Now let’s talk about the staff, because this is the worst part. The majority of the staff is cold, unfriendly, and unpleasant. No smiles. No greetings. No “hello”, no “good morning”, no basic courtesy. You feel unwelcome every single day. The only exception is the manager, who is polite and smiling — sadly, she’s the only one. The rest of the staff behaves as if guests are a burden.  This hotel has zero hospitality, zero warmth, and zero respect for guests. Do yourself a favor: do not book this hotel, do not rent scooters here, do not book any activities through them. There are far better places in Koh Samui where you’ll be treated like a human being instead of a walking wallet.  I strongly regret staying here and would never come back."
> **- mohamed ghaouti (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-verticolor-1.jpg','077 914 000','Chaweng Beach Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.9,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.samuiverticolor.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.289+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.289+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-verticolor-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-verticolor-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1110481543297650587',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-vision','standard','cmr07ihqj00qsq8xddr1qtj9c','Samui Vision','## Top Reviews
> "The owner of the villa is a very serious and responsible person. As soon as we arrived at the hotel, she took us on a tour and introduced us to the design of each room. We stayed for 5 days, and we had breakfast and pick-up and drop-off services every day. The breakfast was very delicious, and it was all cooked by the chef. The driver was also very responsible, and his driving skills were first-class. There are 16 of us and we are very satisfied with the service and facilities of the hotel. I especially like the steam room, very comfortable. The biggest feature of the hotel is that the scenery is beautiful, and you can see a large beach, which is indeed the best world vision."
> **- Serena qian (5/5/5)**

> "We spend 4 night here and the host was so warm and kind to us! Indeed the road to the house is a bit difficult for some cars or drivers, but the host is always willing to give a helping hand! Just ask for their help! We have enjoy so much in Koh Samui, and the host have been part of it for giving us a enjoyable trip, as well as other staff, they are so nice. Hope to have another chance to stay at your house again!"
> **- Jesse Lau (5/5/5)**

> "I think this is the best villa in Koh Samui. The view is stunning, there was a problem with our apartments, but they gave for us the best one at the very top instead. We are very thankful for this opportunity to stay in the best apartments on the island at a good price. Manager Pom is very helpful and nice person."
> **- Rytis Puida (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-vision-1.jpg','062 329 0878','6/80 Moo3 Chaweng, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.bestworldvision.net/',NULL,'cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.291+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.291+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-vision-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-vision-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5449966863739260492',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-water-park','standard','cmr07ihqm00qtq8xdl5gdf0ce','Samui Water Park','## Top Reviews
> "We visited Samui water park today for the first time and we basically had the park to ourselves witch was nice the park had 3x big slides and 8x medium slides and 4x baby slides with a activity play Centre The park is very clean and tidy. The Staff are very welcoming and nice. We didn’t have any food because we had a restaurant booked for tonight but the Food is very reasonable price we had coffees cold drinks and ice creams All was very nice I feel like this waterpark is very underrated. We have come today and really enjoyed it and I will recommend to all my friends who is visiting Samui. if you have children this Park has stuff for all ages. Water is fresh not salt and warm. We will definitely be returning. Thank you Sami waterpark we really enjoyed it."
> **- Cotswolds Game And Meats Company (5/5/5)**

> "Two weeks ago i went to this waterpark with my two kids, 6 and 8 years old. Here is my feedback: The entry was 1.250 Baht per person, also for my small kids. So i paid 3.750 Baht. I was asking for free towels for my kids, but no chance. Only thing was to buy a towel for 250 Baht. The park was compleltly empty. Only 8 more guests inside. The slides, there are not so much, are not the best. At two of them to less water, so i couldn‘t slide, had to walk more or less. The wave pool was just on for 10min during the day and tbh the waves were nothing. Not a really wave pool. The kids area is okay, restaurant had also normal prices and the only good thing is the staff. Very friendly and helpful. Thanks for that. But overall no chance to go back, they don‘t even offer resident prices. Far too high! It‘s a shame, could be nice for kids and family but not with that prices. Much higher than a waterpark in europe and less slides. Don‘t understand this management. We will not go back. Even the waterpark in Pattaya, three times bigger was cheaper and included towels."
> **- Thierry Hegenbart (1/5/5)**

> "My kids had a blast!! There were like 10 other families there. It was a quiet and fun filled day. My girls loved all the slides there (big and small). We stayed from 10:30-16:30. The staff was super friendly and helpful. I highly recommend going there!"
> **- רחל אלמלח (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-water-park-1.jpg','077 423 548','28, 41 หมู่ที่ 1 ถนนแม่น้ำซอย1 Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.6,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.294+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.294+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-water-park-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-water-park-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6068970504459624580',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-wood-projects','standard','cmr07ihqp00quq8xdtnzsdfm8','Samui Wood Projects','## Top Reviews
> "Carpenters with 15 years experience? I don''t think so."
> **- Чингиз Садвакасов (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-wood-projects-1.jpg','+66822821565','108/12, Soi, 7 ตำบล แม่น้ำ อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,1.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.samuiwoodprojects.com/','["Monday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: Closed","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM","Sunday: 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.297+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.297+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-wood-projects-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-wood-projects-2.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-wood-projects-3.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8620724697180728225',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-wooden-hill-resort','standard','cmr07ihqr00qvq8xd0piyjwtc','Samui Wooden Hill Resort','## Top Reviews
> "Location: 15 minutes walk to Lamai beach and all bars, pubs and restaurants. On the main road, so you can hear every motorbike, car and truck driving by. And those ARE noisy. If you are looking for peace and quiet and relaxation, this is not the place. Breakfast: terrible. No food warmers, so everything was cold (eggs, omelet, spring rolls, bacon, french fries), burned soggy spring rolls and waffles. The quality of the coffee depended on who was preparing it, some days it was good, some other days it was not. In a paradise of fruits, they only offered watermelon and pineapple. I went out and bought cheese and other fruits. I don''t know who would find this breakfast "
> **- Camelia Rarinca (1/5/5)**

> "The rooms were huge and unique, set on quite a steep hill. We found the hotel a perfect base for Lamai, a short walk to the beach. The staff were super friendly and on hand to answer any questions we had.  Certain parts could do with some TLC, but all in all we had a lovely stay. Also, how could anyone complain about getting woken up with the sound of nature!"
> **- Siobhan O''Toole (4/5/5)**

> "Great staff, super location,  atmosphere is pleasant and feels like you are in the jungle.  Big separate houses for each family,  5 min from the beach by bike. Very clean,  close to center, just one thing I would change,  the furniture is made from wood and it''s makes a lot of noise and hard to sit on a wooden sofa and chairs.  Other than that  great place to stay."
> **- Alex (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-wooden-hill-resort-1.jpg','091 121 1661','F27R+74 127/60, ตำบล มะเร็ต อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'https://samuiwooden-hill.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.299+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.299+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-wooden-hill-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-wooden-hill-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11673558836222727543',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-zenity','standard','cmr07ihqt00qwq8xd7shn2uxb','Samui Zenity','## Top Reviews
> "We enjoyed our stay at Samui Zenity. The room was clean and comfortable. The breakfast was freshly made and good. The owners were very welcoming, friendly and helpful. The communal kitchen was a great feature, if you wanted to cook, be cooked for or take away, nothing was a problem, there was a nice relaxed atmosphere. A shuttle was provided 4 times daily + return to town which is close to the beach, which is lovely with white sand and turquoise water."
> **- stephanie morris (5/5/5)**

> "We stayed on this location few nights. The place is lovely, clean, confortable. Thw owners are doing their best to make us enjoying our stay. We enjoyed the stay. There is a shuttle bus few times on the day.  The downside is that you need to walk 20 min to the beach. I recommand to have a scooter or car. Thank you very much"
> **- Anca Iamnitchi (5/5/5)**

> "Hotel was very nice, large cleans rooms, plenty of fans and great AC. The pool was a good size with a slide which was great. The staff were all amazing particularly the French guy with long hair that I forgot to ask his name, super helpful and friendly and willing to go above and beyond. The location is a little bit out of the way but we noticed that they are building a lot around this hotel so would imagine within the next couple years this area will be booming. Would highly recommend this hotel and will definitely be back🏴󠁧󠁢󠁳󠁣󠁴󠁿🏴󠁧󠁢󠁳󠁣󠁴󠁿🏴󠁧󠁢󠁳󠁣󠁴󠁿"
> **- charlie dolan (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-zenity-1.jpg','084 226 0066','Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.301+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.301+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-zenity-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-zenity-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=355290232983127511',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samui-zipline','standard','cmr07ihqv00qxq8xd4prj94y6','Samui Zipline','## Top Reviews
> "เริ่ดดด Really fun zipline experience and mostly it’s because of the friendly instructors! (พี่นอสตลกมาก และพี่สวัสน่ารัก ใจดีมากกกค่ะ) 🫶🏽 Felt safe the whole time, and there’s insurance included too.  Quick tips: just listen respectfully and carefully to the instructors especially during the training, relax and enjoy, and be mindful of others in your group. Sunglasses help a lot during summer ☀️  For the ATV trip, I went during summer so I didn’t get to enjoy the waterfall much because it was pretty dry and dusty but at least it’s not muddy so light colored cloths should be skipped 🥹"
> **- Little Thai Bee (5/5/5)**

> "We had the best time celebrating our honeymoon at Samui Zipline! Takky and all the guides were so friendly and helpful and made sure everyone on the tour was safe and having fun! They made sure we got photos and even took videos of us going down the zip line to make sure we had those memories! The views were incredible and the staff took wonderful care of us! We’ll always remember how much fun we had here and would recommend it to anyone looking to have a great time!"
> **- Noah Camarena (5/5/5)**

> "What an incredible experience! The Samui Zipline and UTV adventure was unforgettable from start to finish. Yu and Aun were simply amazing—professional, fun, and made us feel completely safe while still keeping the excitement high.  The UTV drive up the mountain was exhilarating, with just the right mix of adrenaline and awe. And once we reached the top… wow. The view was absolutely special—one of those moments you just stop and take in.  Highly recommend this experience if you’re in Koh Samui. Adventure, stunning scenery, and fantastic guides all in one. 🌿"
> **- Shan Aboo (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-zipline-1.jpg','083 278 5058','17/3 หมู่ 4 Tambon Lipa Noi, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/samuiziplinelipanoi/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.303+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.303+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-zipline-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samui-zipline-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2576419069418800230',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samujana-villas','standard','cmr07ihqy00qyq8xd7pztw4ai','Samujana Villas','## Top Reviews
> "Our stay at Samujana Villa 30 was absolutely incredible — truly one of the most beautiful places we have ever stayed. The villa itself is breathtaking, with full 360-degree views across Koh Samui, stunning rooms, cold and comfortable bedrooms, and the most spectacular pool we have ever had at a villa. Everything about the property felt luxurious, peaceful, and unforgettable.  But what made the stay truly exceptional was Honey.  Honey was our house manager for the week, and she was without question the best part of our entire experience. From the moment we arrived, she made everything feel effortless. She arranged beautiful breakfasts, organized our trips and transportation, gave amazing recommendations, anticipated what we needed before we even asked, and made sure we never wanted for anything. She took such genuine care of us that by the end of the week, she felt like family.  As stunning as Villa 30 is, our stay would not have been the same without Honey. She brought so much warmth, thoughtfulness, and professionalism to every moment. We will absolutely be back — and honestly, Honey is a huge reason why.  An unforgettable stay from start to finish. No notes. Samujana Villa 30 is gorgeous, but Honey made it magical."
> **- Matthew Gustavson (5/5/5)**

> "Absolutely incredible experience at Samujana Villas! From the moment we arrived in villas 27 and 28, everything was pure luxury. The villa itself is stunning with unbeatable views - every sunrise and sunset felt magical. The staff were exceptional, always friendly, attentive, and went above and beyond to make our stay perfect. We felt completely pampered and private, yet everything we needed was taken care of. This was genuinely the best holiday of our lives, and we can’t wait to come back. Highly recommended for anyone wanting the ultimate luxury getaway!"
> **- Katrina Vandermeer (5/5/5)**

> "Stayed 3 nights at villa 28 and i must say it was amazing. The view from the villa was phenomenal with perfect natural lighting into the rooms. The villa manager and attendants are always in contact with you making sure your stay with them is the best it can be, from ordering food and massages, or booking a shuttle or golf cart for transportation, they are always there for you. Breakfast is served either thai or western style for you every morning, accompanied with fresh fruits, juices, and pastries. The whole villa also felt very secure as i was told by staff that security personnel does not let anyone other than guests into the compound. The villa also had an amazing cinema room, with beautiful hd projector and amazing surround sound, perfect for movie nights!"
> **- Jason “jasonc1231” Chiu (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samujana-villas-1.jpg','077 423 465','63/154 Plai Leam Soi 11, 154 Choeng Mon, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://samujana.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifsv000nq8xdrwnu123q','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.306+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.306+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samujana-villas-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samujana-villas-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11853452962372942458',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('samujana-weddings','standard','cmr07ihr000qzq8xd26hlgag1','Samujana Weddings','## Top Reviews
> "Our stay at Samujana Villa 30 was absolutely incredible — truly one of the most beautiful places we have ever stayed. The villa itself is breathtaking, with full 360-degree views across Koh Samui, stunning rooms, cold and comfortable bedrooms, and the most spectacular pool we have ever had at a villa. Everything about the property felt luxurious, peaceful, and unforgettable.  But what made the stay truly exceptional was Honey.  Honey was our house manager for the week, and she was without question the best part of our entire experience. From the moment we arrived, she made everything feel effortless. She arranged beautiful breakfasts, organized our trips and transportation, gave amazing recommendations, anticipated what we needed before we even asked, and made sure we never wanted for anything. She took such genuine care of us that by the end of the week, she felt like family.  As stunning as Villa 30 is, our stay would not have been the same without Honey. She brought so much warmth, thoughtfulness, and professionalism to every moment. We will absolutely be back — and honestly, Honey is a huge reason why.  An unforgettable stay from start to finish. No notes. Samujana Villa 30 is gorgeous, but Honey made it magical."
> **- Matthew Gustavson (5/5/5)**

> "Absolutely incredible experience at Samujana Villas! From the moment we arrived in villas 27 and 28, everything was pure luxury. The villa itself is stunning with unbeatable views - every sunrise and sunset felt magical. The staff were exceptional, always friendly, attentive, and went above and beyond to make our stay perfect. We felt completely pampered and private, yet everything we needed was taken care of. This was genuinely the best holiday of our lives, and we can’t wait to come back. Highly recommended for anyone wanting the ultimate luxury getaway!"
> **- Katrina Vandermeer (5/5/5)**

> "Stayed 3 nights at villa 28 and i must say it was amazing. The view from the villa was phenomenal with perfect natural lighting into the rooms. The villa manager and attendants are always in contact with you making sure your stay with them is the best it can be, from ordering food and massages, or booking a shuttle or golf cart for transportation, they are always there for you. Breakfast is served either thai or western style for you every morning, accompanied with fresh fruits, juices, and pastries. The whole villa also felt very secure as i was told by staff that security personnel does not let anyone other than guests into the compound. The villa also had an amazing cinema room, with beautiful hd projector and amazing surround sound, perfect for movie nights!"
> **- Jason “jasonc1231” Chiu (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samujana-weddings-1.jpg','077 423 465','63/154 Plai Leam Soi 11, 154 Choeng Mon, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://samujana.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifsv000nq8xdrwnu123q','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.308+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.308+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samujana-weddings-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/samujana-weddings-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11853452962372942458',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('san-remo-lounge','standard','cmr07ihr200r0q8xdb2lo6znm','San Remo Lounge','## Top Reviews
> "Good vibes and location. Pasta was a bit over cooked but still good. Pizza was great"
> **- Coco Dubs (4/5/5)**

> "San Remo on Koh Samui was an absolute highlight of our stay. The host, Lars, is incredibly friendly, welcoming, and makes you feel at home immediately. His hospitality truly stands out.  The food was excellent — easily 1A quality. After a long journey, it was exactly what we needed to rediscover our appetite for high-quality Western food. Everything tasted fresh, authentic, and prepared with great care.  We enjoyed it so much that we came back a second time during our stay, which says everything. I can highly recommend this place to anyone visiting Koh Samui. Thank you, Lars, for the wonderful experience!"
> **- Bünyamin Aksoy (5/5/5)**

> "Absolutely amazing food. Spaghetti Aglio e Olio and pork schnitzel are my favorite. The portion is big and the price is reasonable. Cozy atmosphere in a quiet area walking distance to the beach. Highly recommended."
> **- Thaia Paisansatan (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/san-remo-lounge-1.jpg',NULL,'Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/SanRemoKohSamui/','["Monday: 3:00 – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 3:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 3:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 3:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 3:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 3:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.310+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.310+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/san-remo-lounge-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/san-remo-lounge-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4401384318874737255',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sands','standard','cmr07ihr400r1q8xdvsgwzk01','Sands','## Top Reviews
> "The two gems of the restaurant are the view and Luukmee, one of the servers, unfortunately not the food. Besides being a pretty good waitress, Lukmee is an astonishing photographer. We actually came and ate here 4 times (ok ok, I drank 4 times) while the Ms’s and Luukmee ran around taking pictures. Well done Banyan Tree for having such a treasure working with you."
> **- P'' Da (4/5/5)**

> "We had fantastic BBQ night with live music and fire swirling show which is not to be missed. BBQ buffet includes lot of seafoods, pork, chicken, and different choices of salads , soup, hot dishes and more dessert.  Beach provides lots of activities, we special thanks to Banyan Tree staff, Nook who is our very kind personal coach brings us to morning jogging, sailing, house reef snorkeling class, soccer, he is very professional and always smile , a work hard friendly person also provides us pre and post services, such as towels, waters, mint water spray and more fruits!!!"
> **- IRIS CHUNG (5/5/5)**

> "I ordered the carpaccio and the prawn linguine. Both were great but very pricey.  In terms of service, it was relatively slow and all the food came at different times (like 30 minutes apart from one another). My friend and I saw our prepared food sitting on the counter for 20 minutes, with no waiter around or even bothering to attend to it. It came to the point where my friend and I had to walk to the counter ourselves and take the food back to our table. The waiter also didn’t know how to split the bill.  The atmosphere was nice at the beachfront until it hit 7PM… then all the flies from the jungle started attacking our table and the waiters barely did anything about it. We had to carry all our stuff to a table indoors by ourselves. Knowing that there is a massive fly problem at this hour, I encourage the staff to light more incense at that time and make sure guests aren’t placed right next to the jungle."
> **- Viveca (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sands-1.jpg',NULL,'Unnamed Road, F3F9+9VW ตำบล มะเร็ต อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.banyantree.com/en/thailand/samui/dining/sands','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.312+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.312+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sands-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sands-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17907660334592843669',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sankala','standard','cmr07ihr600r2q8xdfkq74qzt','Sankala','## Top Reviews
> "My stay at Shankara in Thailand was simply unforgettable. Everything about this place felt special, intentional, and deeply soulful.  Playing tennis with a breathtaking view over the sea was an experience I’ll never forget moments like that remind you how rare true luxury really is. The service was flawless, yet never intrusive. Every interaction felt genuine, warm, and perfectly timed.  What truly set Shankara apart were the small, thoughtful details. The team noticed my personal habits and even adapted the arrangement of my room to match how I naturally organize my belongings. Those subtle gestures made me feel truly seen and cared for, not just hosted.  Shankara is more than a beautiful place it has a soul. You feel it in the atmosphere, in the people, and in the way everything flows so naturally. It’s the kind of place that stays with you long after you leave.  I cannot recommend it enough. This is hospitality at its finest."
> **- raphael bauer (5/5/5)**

> "Shankara is as good as it gets. Truly as close as you could get to perfection. They have thought of everything from amenities to facilities. There is everything one would need for an exceptional holiday retreat. You could stay there the full week without ever leaving the premises.  The attention to details, from the staff to the decoration in the rooms and throughout the property is truly exceptional. It has been built and designed with impeccable taste.  The food (especially the Thai!) is the best I have had on the island.  Spy and Irufan along with the rest of the staffing team have made Shankara a real paradise."
> **- Marc (5/5/5)**

> "My husband, I and our friends had an amazing one week in Shankara Samui. It was our first time here on the island, and the stay was so wonderful that we honestly felt like home. Service and the team were top notch, thoughtful and well-organised. The food was very authentic, delicious but very healthy. Our room and the facilities were spectacular, especially the water pressure which is so stable and it’s rare on islands usually.  If we were to come back to Koh Samui again, Shankara would be our first choice"
> **- Sylvia Chenaux-Ng (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sankala-1.jpg','062 242 0028','79/12, ตำบล แม่น้ำ อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.shankarasamui.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.314+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.314+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sankala-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sankala-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8647970588730095136',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sans-souci-resort','standard','cmr07ihr800r3q8xd6hml6mc8','Sans Souci Resort','## Top Reviews
> "We booked Sans Souci Samui just one day before our arrival and couldn’t be happier with our choice. Initially, we thought Chaweng might be too touristy, but the hotel is perfectly located at the quiet end of the beach, away from noise and crowds.  The staff welcomed us warmly, the rooms are clean, beautifully designed, and very comfortable. Breakfast is à la carte, included in the price, and served right on the beach with the sound of the waves – simply magical.  From its charm, location, and service, we will definitely come back. A truly wonderful place for a relaxing stay!"
> **- Björn Wildung (5/5/5)**

> "Loved the dog that comes w the hotel!! Absolutely loved this hotel super cosy but luxurious at the same time. The private beach is a 20 sec walk from the room and breakfast was 10/10. The bed was very comfy. Staff a little awkward but sweet"
> **- Gabriella Enrico (5/5/5)**

> "We are currently trying to contact the staff regarding the possibility of rebooking our stay. Unfortunately, due to the recent flight cancellations in the Middle East, we are unable to reach the destination as planned.  We have made several attempts to contact the property to discuss possible options for moving our reservation to another date when travel becomes possible again. However, we have not received any response so far, and it has been very difficult to get in touch with anyone.  We completely understand that unexpected situations happen, but we would greatly appreciate any communication or assistance regarding the possibility of rescheduling our stay. At the moment, it feels like our messages are being ignored, which is quite frustrating given the circumstances."
> **- peter vajo (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sans-souci-resort-1.jpg','077 422 044','4, 4 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.sanssoucisamui.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.316+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.316+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sans-souci-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sans-souci-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2137236662258028059',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('santiburi-country-club','standard','cmr07ihra00r4q8xd6c9fcacc','Santiburi Country Club','## Top Reviews
> "Difficult course.  We took advantage of early morning special to try and beat the heat and so glad we did. Caddies were lovely and super helpful.  Would recommend as the views are fantastic and a great morning out."
> **- Amanda (4/5/5)**

> "Santiburi Samui is a good, honest golf course. It uses the hillside setting really well, giving you a mix of challenging and forgiving holes without overdoing the elevation. The greens were in good shape, and the course overall feels well looked after. It’s a nice place to spend a few hours if you enjoy a round that keeps you thinking.  I played here with some golfers on a Fairways of Eden trip, and everyone had a positive impression. The atmosphere is quiet and easygoing, and the course feels different enough from the typical resort layouts to make it stand out. A solid round and worth trying while on the island."
> **- Robert Müller (5/5/5)**

> "More than your typical resort course: Playing from Blue there are several intimidating tee shots. Fairways are firm and well kept so are the tricky greens, which are faster than they appear (and faster than the practice green which is sub-standard). I was grateful for the knowledgeable caddies giving advice on aim points and green slopes. Last but not least the selection of rental clubs is very good. All in all  very pleasant days in beautiful setting. And the view from the clubhouse terrace is something else."
> **- Erik Ballauff (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/santiburi-country-club-1.jpg','080 611 4195','ทางหลวงแผ่นดินหมายเลข 4169 Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.santiburigolfsamui.com/','["Monday: 6:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Tuesday: 6:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Wednesday: 6:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Thursday: 6:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Friday: 6:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Saturday: 6:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Sunday: 6:00 AM – 6:30 PM"]','cmr07ifuo0015q8xdfahzrsp4','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.318+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.318+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/santiburi-country-club-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/santiburi-country-club-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6307790118719778271',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('santiburi-koh-samui-resort','standard','cmr07ihrd00r5q8xd08v9fcr4','Santiburi Koh Samui Resort','## Top Reviews
> "WE actually stayed from May 26th to June 1st and liked it so much that we returend from June 5th to the 7th.  We had two wonderful stays at your hotel and felt truly welcome from the moment we arrived. The staff were exceptionally friendly and attentive throughout our visit. A special highlight was the Muay Thai trial training session for our 8-year-old son, which he thoroughly enjoyed.  We were also delighted by the appreciation that we returned to the resort very well recognized by the team and a hand-written welcome note by Director of Rooms, which added a very personal touch to our stay. The breakfast was excellent, offering a great selection and highest quality.  Overall, everything was simply wonderful, and we greatly appreciated the warm hospitality. Thank you for making our stay so memorable."
> **- heike schemberablum (5/5/5)**

> "We had a pleasant stay at Santiburi Koh Samui. The property itself is stunning, though there were a few service and dining hiccups that kept it from being a flawless 5-star experience.  The Highlights: * The Villa: Our villa was wonderful—very comfortable, beautifully maintained, and came with a fantastic, spacious outdoor area that was a highlight of our trip. * Breakfast: The breakfast buffet was quite good with a nice variety of tasty options to start the day. * The Staff: For the most part, the team here is friendly and welcoming, with a few exceptions. Areas for Improvement: * Pool Maintenance: We experienced a leak in our villa pool during our stay. While the team attempted to fix it, it wasn''t fully resolved, and we would have appreciated a small gesture or compensation for the inconvenience. Unfortunately nothing of the kind was ever offered to us. * Communication & Dining: The breakfast restaurant staff had a low level of English comprehension which made communication a bit tricky at times. We also felt the restaurants—particularly the beach restaurant—could be improved. The seafood was a bit disappointing and felt overpriced for the quality. * Beach Service & Spa: While most interactions were great, the beach service staff could be a bit more polite and welcoming. Additionally, the spa was just okay for the price; the massages were a bit inconsistent, turning out either too light or a bit too firm. Overall: It’s a gorgeous resort with excellent villas and a lot going for it. With a few adjustments to the dining and staff training, it could easily be a top-tier luxury stay!"
> **- Maggie Salak (4/5/5)**

> "Had to change hotels last minute as the one we booked wasn’t safe for our child. We drove around and looked at some options and this was a clear winner. Stayed 8 days. Stunning grounds, warm and professional staff, hotel food is outstanding and we had some of the best Thai food we had in Thailand at their lobby restaurant. Beautiful pool, beautiful clean beach. Just luxury. We travelled with an infant who also enjoyed the kids play room, pool and beach toys and playful attention from the staff. Thank you again for cleaning up after my messy baby after every meal 🙏 highly recommend."
> **- Olive Diaz (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/santiburi-koh-samui-resort-1.jpg','077 425 031','12 สุราษฏร์ธานี Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://santiburisamui.com/?utm_source=google&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=santiburikohsamui&utm_term=gbp','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.321+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.321+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/santiburi-koh-samui-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/santiburi-koh-samui-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13015706162977324589',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('santiburi-spa','standard','cmr07ihrf00r6q8xdk3zgfa2a','Santiburi Spa','## Top Reviews
> "I had a wonderful experience at the spa. The receptionist, Khun Yui, provided excellent service with great attention to detail and made me feel very welcome.  Additionally, Khun Praew was very friendly and attentive. She focused on the specific areas I needed and ensured I felt comfortable throughout the session.  Overall, I am very impressed with the service and would highly recommend this spa."
> **- กนกพร สินธุพาชี (5/5/5)**

> "This afternoon had the pleasure of experiencing a 90-minute aromatherapy massage at Santiburi Koh Samui, and I cannot recommend it enough! Therapists Cream and Mook were exceptional. From the moment I arrived, the serene ambiance set the perfect tone for relaxation. Yui at reception was warm and friendly welcoming us with a beautiful smile and explaining all the options available to us  Cream''s technique was incredible, expertly addressing my tension points while ensuring I felt comfortable throughout the session. Mook complemented this beautifully with a soothing touch, creating a harmonious balance that left me feeling rejuvenated. The choice of essential oils was delightful, enhancing the overall experience with calming scents that lingered pleasantly.  Both therapists were professional, attentive, and genuinely caring, making this one of the best spa experiences I''ve ever had. If you''re looking for a tranquil escape and top-notch service, definitely book with Cream and Mook at Santiburi!"
> **- Viila Sēcūra (5/5/5)**

> "I ordered elixir of love for me and my husband for his birthday! Saying good or even wonderful is nothing to tell you how it was! Really recommended to enjoy your life, your body and the man you love ❤️"
> **- Инна Якшина (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/santiburi-spa-1.jpg','077 425 031','12, Maenam Beach, 12, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://santiburispa.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.323+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.323+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/santiburi-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/santiburi-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12822812824313179268',NULL,NULL);
