> **- Tom Tom (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sareeraya-weddings-and-events-1.jpg','077 914 333','100, 1 Chaweng Beach Rd, Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.sareeraya.com/',NULL,'cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.348+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.348+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sareeraya-weddings-and-events-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sareeraya-weddings-and-events-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2676899578650604765',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sasatorn-koh-samui','standard','cmr07ihs600rgq8xdi87klinz','Sasatorn Koh Samui','## Top Reviews
> "This Cafe was recommended by our host for breakfast and we ate here most days. The coffee was excellent, we usually had an iced cappuccino. Every juice we tried was delicious and the meals were so full of flavour. There is a great choice of Thai foods with a bit of a Melbourne twist. The kids menu had lots of fun options, each kids drink came with marshmallows. The service was friendly and professional. The water and ice are filtered so you can drink without worry."
> **- Rebecca Smith (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing coffee places with an extraordinary large menu, full of never-seen-before drinks and dishes. As i took about 20 minutes upon deciding what i wanted, i was in a bit of a rush to grab breakfast before an appointment nearby, but they were very friendly and made my breakfast super quick (without judging me for taking so long to order 😆). I had a Melbourne style sourdough toast with a folded chili omelet, salmon, fermented cauliflower and a goatcheese espuma and it''s truly one of the best sourdough toast i''ve ever had! The coffee, as stated in lots of reviews, is fabulous indeed."
> **- Marie Laurence Demeyer (5/5/5)**

> "Well they have every type of coffee you can imagine and it''s bloody good!!!  Food - lovely, just a really. Nice relaxed place. Worth going to if you love coffee"
> **- Lee Markham (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sasatorn-koh-samui-1.jpg','082 692 8941','2, H24J+PGJ, 52, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.350+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.350+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sasatorn-koh-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sasatorn-koh-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9384109777729657467',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sasitara-residence','standard','cmr07ihs800rhq8xddtirjnyk','Sasitara Residence','## Top Reviews
> "Very good place, I kinda disagree on the negatives review but we got the bungalow (B5) and everything was excellent except the odors in the toilets due to the drain.  Also, a bit far from everything but you can rent scooters for 250-300 B.  The pool was great, and the bed comfortable.  The breakfast wasn’t that great but for 250 B you can have plenty of choice."
> **- Romain (4/5/5)**

> "The hotel is beautiful, with decent rooms and a swimming pool. Its location is convenient and close to local events. However, I noticed that most of the staff have limited English, which made communication somewhat challenging.  That said, the receptionist, Mimi, was excellent. Her English was very good, and she was easy to communicate with. She even assisted me in finding a motorbike to rent. She was professional, polite, and highly efficient."
> **- Samer Alhamwieh (El Patrón Samer) (4/5/5)**

> "I don''t get some reviews. I loved my stay, the room was great and clean. The staff was lovely, the pool was beautiful and nice. The only thing it is a bit far from chaweng central but the beaches are way more nicer here then in central. And within 15 min walk you are in the central or I take a grab scooter and for € 1,10 I was at the centre. But there are also some nice restaurants nereby. So I would definitly recommend it."
> **- M. (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sasitara-residence-1.jpg','077 601 167','9 Baan 90, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://hnyhotels.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.352+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.352+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sasitara-residence-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sasitara-residence-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5331949180940632086',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sasitara-thai-villas','standard','cmr07ihsb00riq8xdr7xvp4n0','Sasitara Thai Villas','## Top Reviews
> "I ❤️ this authentic Thai-style hotel. The resort is so beautiful surrounded by nature and seaside. Great location for quiet and peaceful relaxation. One of the very best Sunsets in Koh Samui. The staffs are very friendly and helpful. This is my third time returning and will be many more in the future for sure. Strongly recommended! 👍😍😁"
> **- Thammarat Limsawas (5/5/5)**

> "We stayed at Sasitara Thai Villas for a little over a month, and from the very first moment we arrived, it was clear that this place is something special. The atmosphere is warm and welcoming, largely thanks to the genuinely friendly and smiling staff. The hotel itself is beautifully designed in a traditional Thai style, with lots of wood, greenery, palm trees, and coconut trees, creating a calm and cozy environment that immediately helps you relax.  We stayed in several different rooms during our time there, and each one had its own unique and authentic character. This made our stay even more enjoyable, as every room felt like a slightly different experience while still maintaining the same level of comfort and care. It’s a great way to feel connected to Thai culture while enjoying all the conveniences needed for a comfortable stay.  One of the biggest advantages of this hotel is its quiet and secluded location. The area is very peaceful, and while airplanes do pass overhead during the day, it’s important to note that they do not fly at night. Since this is an island with a limited number of flights, you quickly get used to it, and it did not negatively affect the quality of our stay at all.  The hotel has a beautiful swimming pool and direct access to the beach. The beach itself is not very large and not ideal for long swimming sessions, but a big plus is the free access to kayaks, including double kayaks, which adds a lot of value and enjoyment.  The staff truly deserves special mention. Everyone is kind, attentive, and always willing to help. The administrator Ou is especially wonderful — incredibly caring, supportive, and professional. Many staff members speak very good English, which makes communication easy and ensures you can get all the information and help you might need.  After spending about a month and a half here, we can confidently recommend Sasitara Thai Villas both for short-term stays and for a longer winter stay. The hotel also offers the option to rent villas on a monthly basis at very reasonable prices compared to other parts of the island, which makes it an excellent choice for long-term living as well.  Overall, this is a place we would happily return to and sincerely recommend to others looking for a calm, authentic, and comfortable stay in Thailand."
> **- Anri Savinovsky (5/5/5)**

> "Looks a lovely villa, but there’s only air conditioning in your bedroom not the whole villa! There is no hot running water to wash your hands! No soap either to wash your hands,I had to ask for some!! No access to a beach only the sea where the dirty river runs into! The dirty river runs parallel with the villas so you can see it in its highlight (not welcoming)"
> **- steven smart (2/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sasitara-thai-villas-1.jpg','077 430 111','79 60 Plai Laem Soi 2, Tambon Bo Put, Bophut Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.sasitara.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifv2001aq8xdag7cvjgf','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.355+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.355+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sasitara-thai-villas-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sasitara-thai-villas-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7694617462471117578',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sassy-beach','standard','cmr07ihsd00rjq8xd7erk19g0','Sassy Beach','## Top Reviews
> "Sassy Beach presents itself as a wine bar and upscale restaurant. The location right by the beach is beautiful and the atmosphere is pleasant.  The service is very attentive and friendly. The menu focuses heavily on meat and steak dishes, which are well prepared and enjoyable.  Prices are noticeably higher compared to many restaurants in the surrounding area, but the quality is overall solid. A nice spot if you’re looking for a beachside dinner with good service."
> **- Oliver Kremers (4/5/5)**

> "My wife and I celebrated our wedding anniversary here! It was a fantastic evening with a great beachfront location. The food was superb—we had the steaks, tartare, and appetizers. By the way, they have a huge wine selection, which was our main criteria when choosing a restaurant for the occasion. There was a musician playing live music in the evening, which made for a great atmosphere. Huge thanks to the staff for the excellent service; everything was top-notch!"
> **- Stanislav Markov (5/5/5)**

> "We had an amazing dining experience at Sassy Beach. From the moment we arrived until our departure everything was top notch. First thing to note is the comfort of the chairs. We were a group of 5 and we started with 2 appetizers (appertivos) and a very nice, reasonably priced, bottle of wine. 4 of us got pasta dishes and we all were very impressed with the quality, taste and portion size. Desserts of creme brulee and Panettone with gelato were the perfect end to a perfect meal. If you''re looking for a restaurant for a special occasion or just a high end dining experience, this is the place!"
> **- David Moore (heynowdave47) (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sassy-beach-1.jpg','081 482 5193','52, Tambon Mae Nam, Maenam, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifs1000cq8xdfo2aau32','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.357+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.357+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sassy-beach-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sassy-beach-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8435857624029406455',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sassy','standard','cmr07ihsf00rkq8xdad8jn56a','Sassy','## Top Reviews
> "I’m a very picky eater, but this place made it. It was my first visit today, and definitely not my last.  The ambiance is beautiful and welcoming, and the staff is genuinely friendly. The food arrived quickly and exceeded my expectations. The steak was cooked to perfection, and the 24-hour slow-cooked beef was unbelievably tender.  I went for lunch, so it was calm and relaxed, exactly what I was looking for. They even turned on the air conditioning inside for us, which I really appreciated.  Highly recommended."
> **- S (5/5/5)**

> "First off the server was very sweet and attentive. It was a quiet night but the atmosphere was great with the setting and sax man (also great). Food looks pretty but is average at best, if you''re from the UK it''s like Zizi which is totally fine but couldn''t recommend based on food. I would avoid the tiramisu( if reading please change it), it''s genuinely gross but pizza and pasta all  fine but expensive for the quality."
> **- David P (3/5/5)**

> "The food is absolutely fantastic, incredibly fresh, packed with flavor, and beautifully presented. You can really tell they care about quality. On top of that, the vibe here is perfect; it is modern, stylish, yet super cozy and welcoming.  What really sets this place apart, though, is the service. The staff is extremely attentive, friendly, and goes above and beyond to make you feel welcome.  If you are in Chaweng and looking for amazing food in a great location, this place is a must-visit. We will definitely be back! Highly recommended!"
> **- Sebastian Linde (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sassy-1.jpg','081 482 5193','888, 2 nd floor, Haven Samui mall, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.sassysamui.com/','["Monday: 12:00 – 11:30 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 11:30 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 11:30 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 11:30 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 11:30 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 11:30 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 11:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.359+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.359+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sassy-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sassy-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4804876084844472868',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sativa-tattoo','standard','cmr07ihsh00rlq8xdhs597uua','Sativa Tattoo','## Top Reviews
> "I can’t say enough great things about this tattoo shop. The staff were so fun and friendly - the shop is super clean and comfortable. K took my vision and turned it into a perfect reality. This was a difficult design to execute an he did it perfectly. I’m already planning my next one for when we pass back through in a couple of week! HIGHLY RECOMMEND!"
> **- Vintage Gypsies (5/5/5)**

> "Awesome experience. Very clean studio and they created my tattoo out of two motives and added their own style to it - love it! Very detailed and superb service. We were lucky and everything worked out even we were walk-in customers (me and my brother). Highly recommended!"
> **- Joost Mentink (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing tattooist, great detail and care taken. Very very happy with the result! Thanks 😀"
> **- Scott Higgins (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sativa-tattoo-1.jpg','064 780 7305','200, 7 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/SativaTattooKohSamui/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.361+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.361+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sativa-tattoo-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sativa-tattoo-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11936121930102910965',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('satva-yoga-retreat','standard','cmr07ihsj00rmq8xd2tqsb6il','Satva Yoga Retreat','## Top Reviews
> "I didnt stay in their accomodation, but I lived near here, I went to join their communities where they throw Kirtan night every Sunday evening, there is free vegan light dinner afterwards, and Krishna Mantra Chanting music, and a little cute little dance when the live music gets groovy. You can sit, stand, dance, or not, all is welcome. I will miss living near Sattva! They also throw amazing Yoga+sound healing classes in the morning and evening by the beach every weekday except Wed; the evening classes especially are wonderful since it is by the beach where you see sunsetting. Beautiful, welcoming and peaceful. Their food is also very lovely and yummy, I had breakfast buffet right after the yoga class in the morning. Great experience! Thank you for everything."
> **- Winter Ray (5/5/5)**

> "A stunning resort right by the beach in Lipa Noi... The rooms need some renovation, but steel we loved the place. There are several kind of treatments there, together with the neighbor resort. Very recommended to try one of the panchakarma treatment."
> **- Neer Komm (neeros) (4/5/5)**

> "The Resort is really beautiful and the beach is awesome! Great offerings for yoga, sport and healthy live style. The rooms could use a little love but you have everything you need. Do not expect luxurious interior. The environment is full of beautiful plants and the 2 pools are great. They offer shuttle service and private tours to see some places on the island. Only the breakfast is a little bit disappointing. Eggs and things like Cappuccino are being charged extra. In general the restaurant is very good with a mix of local and western oriented food. We went there every day. Location and beach are stunning especially the sun set due to it being located in the west of the island. Definitely check out the yoga courses!!! In total we felt welcome and the stay was very pleasant!"
> **- Thilo Roh (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/satva-yoga-retreat-1.jpg','099 057 0467','95/4 M2, ตำบล ลิปะน้อย อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://satvasamui.ru/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.363+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.363+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/satva-yoga-retreat-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/satva-yoga-retreat-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6401486742497868238',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('savana-bar-restaurant','standard','cmr07ihsl00rnq8xdrd2t2593','Savana Bar Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "The foods is very good 👍 and the price was very cheap 👏🏻👏🏻👏🏻 Will visit again soon ❤️ I will recommended this restaurant ."
> **- Kitty Kat (5/5/5)**

> "It is a small, nicely decorated restaurant. We ordered a cheeseburger and a pepperoni pizza. The burger is generous and served with french fries. The pizza is also well garnished and the dough perfectly cooked. We liked the place for the quality of the food and also for the welcome of the staff. We will come back…"
> **- Nicolas Bourquin (5/5/5)**

> "Great place with great food and good prices"
> **- jean-louis franchi (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/savana-bar-restaurant-1.jpg','082 118 3794','Bophut, Chumchon Chaweng Yai Soi 4 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.365+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.365+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/savana-bar-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/savana-bar-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14373314217995092259',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('savor-catering','standard','cmr07ihsn00roq8xd16n95wu1','Savor Catering','## Top Reviews
> "Leo was fantastic from the very first meeting. He sat down with us to carefully discuss the buffet for our pre-wedding brunch and crafted a wonderful selection of finger foods and main dishes. The little burgers were an absolute highlight—awesome flavor and so delicious that several guests asked for the recipe! Beyond the food, Leo brought a beautiful sense of decor that transformed our parents’ villa into a truly elegant and inviting setting. The brunch looked stunning and felt perfectly cohesive with our overall wedding vibe. On the day itself, his team was impressive—they set up everything in lightning speed with professionalism and efficiency. The food was fantastic, fresh, and full of flavor, and our guests couldn’t stop raving about how much they enjoyed it. Leo and his team exceeded our expectations and played a big part in making our pre-wedding celebration relaxed, beautiful, and memorable. Highly recommend Leo for any event on Koh Samui—you won’t be disappointed!"
> **- Niko Bjelic (5/5/5)**

> "Спасибо за заботу🫶 Все прошло отлично! Ребята настоящие профессионалы, еда невероятная, гриль просто восторг. Все быстро, качественно, а главное как красиво!"
> **- Ksusha Lenkina (5/5/5)**

> "I''d like to express my gratitude for the wonderful catering! The food was simply magnificent! The guests especially loved the marinated mackerel with black bread and the pâté, which were delicious. And the grilled meat was simply amazing!"
> **- Анна Задорожная (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/savor-catering-1.jpg','083 496 7255','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://samuicatering.tilda.ws/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.367+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.367+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/savor-catering-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/savor-catering-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16306865366844748852',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sawai-home-resort','standard','cmr07ihsq00rpq8xdjzreuo2j','Sawai Home Resort','## Top Reviews
> "An extremely good, clean and friendly resort. Staff always pleasant and eager to assist. Rooms spacious and well serviced. Sunsets on the beach at Pu restaurant just a short stagger"
> **- Ian Murphy (5/5/5)**

> "Stayed here for 3 nights, the room was simple but clean and the beach nearby is beautiful.  The restaurant at the beach is also good, you have a few options what to eat and are back to your room within 3 minutes.  We also took the taxi from the hotel multiple times for 200 baht / Person. Easy planning with the service."
> **- Betty (5/5/5)**

> "Nice cozy place with very cheap price.All rooms literally got a seaview as the rooms are not very far from the beach.Stayed here for a month and it costs about 10,000THB!! Amazing sunset and restaurant also!! A family owned place and the services are not like 5 stars but all are nice and helpful."
> **- Bruce One (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sawai-home-resort-1.jpg','077 421 635','7 1, Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.2,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ig1h003iq8xdb1g9nifo','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.370+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.370+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sawai-home-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sawai-home-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8213138561292910812',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sawan-pool-villas-residence','standard','cmr07ihss00rqq8xdsmhjoqqa','SAWAN Pool Villas Residence','## Top Reviews
> "Sawan pool villas leaves much to be desired. That being said, the amenities present are good and work well. However, some of the cabinets were broken upon arrival, the living area had no blackout curtains like the rooms, and the fan in the living room had one speed, super sonic. Overall i would still recommend you give this place a try. P.S. you do have to pay for the electricity too, which is understandable"
> **- Hunter Oliver (4/5/5)**

> "Hii Melanie, I give you 1 star of your service and reply, I don''t know what are your position in Sawan, but you sounds like a superior with a vulga attitude.  By the way, your staff is very good, polite and much more professional and courteousness, anyone in this business would consider to grab your staff but isn''t you Melanie. If I remember your name still.  This is what we get staying in your Villa. Villa 18 if not mistaken, I have forgotten, wanna delete this 😭 memory in Koh Samui. Koh Samui is a Paradise anyway after early check out from your AGED Villa Melanie.  Don''t say or feel sorry anymore, I leave this comment here as I am returning to Samui again real soon."
> **- Ong Kok How (1/5/5)**

> "The staff are the shining stars here. We did run into some problems with spotty electricity in our villa but the staff was very kind and responsive to our concerns. They were able to move us to another villa and we are much more comfortable now.  The company would do well to add a couple of armchairs to the villas as indoor seating is limited. Outdoor seating is plentiful.  The pool has been wonderful. It’s quiet and private. Close proximity to good restaurants and beaches."
> **- Erin Farrar (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sawan-pool-villas-residence-1.jpg','081 787 9862','142/123 T., Lamai, ตำบล มะเร็ต Koh samui, Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.2,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.sawanresidence.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.372+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.372+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sawan-pool-villas-residence-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sawan-pool-villas-residence-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8922284555425364045',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sawasdee','standard','cmr07ihsv00rrq8xdcc413r4m','Sawasdee','## Top Reviews
> "We had a wonderful month long stay at Villa Baan Sawadee!  Emma was a fantastic host, very welcoming, always available to answer questions (leading up to our trip and during), and full of great local recommendations. She took the time to show us around, share her favourite places to eat and visit, and even helped arrange tours, which we really appreciated.  The villa is in a perfect location surrounded by beautiful palm trees, peaceful and quiet, yet close enough to the main road to get anywhere easily. We loved being in this part of Samui, as it offered a great balance of calm surroundings and easy access to markets, restaurants, and beaches.  Thank you again for such a lovely experience and for helping make our trip so special!"
> **- Intu Fitness TV (5/5/5)**

> "We found this place completely by chance and at the very last minute and it turned out to be a perfect choice! It’s quiet, peaceful, and surrounded by beautiful nature. Honestly, we’ve rarely stayed anywhere this clean and well maintained; you can really tell it’s run with passion and care.  On top of that, the accommodation is hosted by the lovely owner, Emma, who made our stay even better. She shared loads of helpful tips and recommendations for exploring Koh Samui, and she’s also happy to help you organize trips or plan your free time. If you need ideas, Emma will gladly recommend great places and activities.  This stay made our trip even better, we left feeling relaxed and would love to return! ☀️💛"
> **- Vanessa J (5/5/5)**

> "We spent 14 days in the villa and it was amazing. The rooms were beautifully clean, as was the pool. The owner Ema was very kind and helpful, she gave us lots of useful tips and advice on food and shopping. She also helped us with renting a scooter and arranged airport transfers. I highly recommend this accommodation. Jaroslav Řehoř"
> **- Jaroslav Řehoř (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sawasdee-1.jpg','084 381 2184','8/40 Santhitani Valley Moo 5, Ban Tai Maenam Maenam, ตำบล แม่น้ำ อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.baansawadeevillasamui.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.375+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.375+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sawasdee-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sawasdee-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3083975413878863441',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('say-sushi','standard','cmr07ihsx00rsq8xduml5m6io','Say Sushi','## Top Reviews
> "Tried the Philadelphia Special Roll and it was amazing! The salmon is so fresh and the cream cheese is rich and creamy. I love the crunchy almond flakes and fish roe on top. Everything tastes perfect and clean. Highly recommended for sushi lovers! 10/10."
> **- Arr Mang Htet (5/5/5)**

> "Didn’t expect much — overall it was good. The rolls were fresh and well balanced, without too much rice The salmon quality was decent and the presentation was clean. Service was quick even during busy hours. One small note: the pieces could be cut more evenly Overall, the price matches the"
> **- Matthew Young (5/5/5)**

> "It seems that new owner has done his work. Food quality and presentation are much more better than it was around 6 month ago.  Despite the fact we were waiting around half an hour, the spicy tuna rolls were delicious. And big thanks for the miso soup 🍲"
> **- Anastasiia Goncharenko (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/say-sushi-1.jpg','099 176 9616','25, 243, Tambon Bo Put, Sub-district, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://r.grab.com/o/zyuqUn6r','["Monday: 12:30 – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:30 – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:30 – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 12:30 – 11:00 PM","Friday: 12:30 – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 12:30 – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 12:30 – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.377+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.377+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/say-sushi-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/say-sushi-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3834151571417011310',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sea-la-vie','standard','cmr07ihsz00rtq8xdrbdcac8a','Sea La Vie','## Top Reviews
> "A beautiful seaside restaurant located within a villa resort — perfect for a romantic dinner.  We ordered a large seafood platter with fish, prawns, mussels, squid and baby octopus, and everything was fresh and delicious.  The staff were very attentive, and the manager was especially helpful — answering all questions and making sure we had a great experience.  I visited in the evening, and after 8pm it gets quite busy, so I recommend booking in advance.  Loved everything — the food, the atmosphere and the service. Highly recommended."
> **- Nora Vale (5/5/5)**

> "We had such a wonderful evening here. The food was a 10/10 – everything was absolutely delicious. The manager and the staff were incredibly kind, attentive, and made us feel very welcome throughout the whole evening. The location is also perfect for watching the sunset, which made the experience even more special. I would definitely recommend this place and would love to come back again!"
> **- Julie N (5/5/5)**

> "Went there this evening randomly and what a find. Right on the beach great atmosphere music good not too loud. Meet the owner moved us to a nicer table once one opened up. We had sangria & cocktails with 10 Japanese oysters 10/10 would recommend to anyone 😎"
> **- Matthew Groves (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sea-la-vie-1.jpg','077 960 252','79, 100 Plai leam, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/sealaviesamui','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifv2001aq8xdag7cvjgf','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.379+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.379+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sea-la-vie-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sea-la-vie-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15910035218498975641',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sea-sun-bed-beyond','standard','cmr07iht200ruq8xdta80j2ns','SEA SUN Bed & Beyond','## Top Reviews
> "I really enjoyed my stay at this hostel. It wasn’t social at all—most of my time it was literally just me in my room—but everything else was great. The facilities were very clean, the pool was spotless, and the view of the water was beautiful. It’s also an amazing spot to watch the sunset (at least in November when the sun goes down on this side).  The ensuite bathroom was super clean, the shower was great, and the locker in the room was big enough to fit all my stuff. The front desk staff were really friendly too. They provide both a beach towel and a room towel, and the beds were very comfortable.  The only issue I had was the Wi-Fi. Aside from my last day, it just wouldn’t stay connected for me. It got a bit annoying and I ended up using a lot of my own data, so that would be my only real complaint.  Overall, I’d definitely recommend this place.  It’s also a good location if you want to be halfway between fisherman’s village and chaweng beach area. A grab bike typically cost me 70 baht each way to either of these areas."
> **- Savannah (5/5/5)**

> "We stayed here twice during our trip, one night before heading to Koh Tao, and another six days later. Both times we were warmly welcomed by Nee, who was an absolutely wonderful host: attentive, genuine, and making us feel at home on both occasions.  The rooms are charming and well-decorated, the pool is a nice bonus, though the included breakfast we got was entirely skippable.  Now, the location is a double-edged sword: you’re perfectly placed near the airport, which is very convenient, but that also means planes fly directly overhead until late at night and start again early in the morning. They offer earplugs in the room but it’s not enough to cover the bass sound and vibrations.  Add to that the road noise (particularly loud in our second room), next to no water pressure and very little hot water, rock-hard mattresses, and an AC unit that blasted directly onto us all night in our second room, and you end up having a poor quality sleep, which is regrettable for a hotel..."
> **- SJ (3/5/5)**

> "Modern boutique hotel with great rooms and stunning views. We got the room right by the pool, and despite some privacy issues, we loved the beautiful design and sunset views. The only downside is that outsiders can easily sneak into the facilities, which worsens the lack of privacy. They should restrict access to guest-exclusive areas."
> **- Luis (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sea-sun-bed-beyond-1.jpg','077 423 641','14, 22, Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.seasunsamui.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ig6y005pq8xd4jrvheih','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.382+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.382+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sea-sun-bed-beyond-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sea-sun-bed-beyond-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5756830811615236459',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sea-valley','standard','cmr07iht700rvq8xd3hngcplv','Sea Valley','## Top Reviews
> "We had a wonderful experience at this hotel and especially at the restaurant, where we ate almost every day during our stay.  The servers were incredibly kind, friendly, and always smiling. They were just as warm and attentive with us as they were with our children, which truly meant a lot to us.  A special thank you to Dar Dar, Myo, BoBo, and Min — they were amazing throughout our stay.  We would also like to mention the housekeeping staff, who were absolutely lovely and did a wonderful job, as well as the reception team, who were always welcoming and helpful.  Their kindness and positive attitude really made a difference in how we experienced our vacation. Thanks to them, we had such an enjoyable and memorable stay.  We are very happy and grateful, as they truly contributed to making our holiday so special!"
> **- Tania Sobral-Ristic (5/5/5)**

> "We originally booked Sea Valley Hotel for just one week, but after only two days, we loved it so much that we decided to spend our entire remaining time, three weeks in total, right here until our flight back home. We enjoyed every single moment! ​The location is absolutely perfect if you are looking for peace, quiet, and privacy. The rooms are incredibly large and spacious with everything you could need, and you can really feel the amazing attention to detail and to the guests'' comfort throughout the resort. The pool is fantastic, and the food is wonderful with a great variety, especially the breakfast. ​But what truly makes this place unforgettable is the team. The lovely ladies at reception - Mos, Ying, Kate, and Boom. were all so helpful and charming and made us feel so welcome. The absolute highlight of our stay was the morning breakfast team; a huge personal thank you to Myo, Dar Dar, Bo Bo, and Ton Ton. They went above and beyond every single day, being so incredibly kind and constantly anticipating our every need before we even had to ask. I wish I knew the names of the entire waiting staff, because absolutely everyone was wonderful. We also want to thank Tan Tan from the maintenance team who was always so nice and kept the pool area flawless. ​Sea Valley Hotel combines professional hospitality with a warm, genuine touch. We will definitely be back!"
> **- tamar cohen (5/5/5)**

> "Way too expensive for what is it. Only good thing about resort is that beach is in front of your villa. Breakfast is very very poor ,super limited. Shocking if you think that fruit market is 4 min away from hotel and it’s ridiculously cheap,they could easily offer way better if they wanted. Rooms are very simple ,old style,with nothing complementary apart from water.(coffee you need to pay ) Cleaning is ok when happens,apparently they clean only on request and not on second day . Villa is nice and cold . Beach is really good and private,quiet. So I would say for 200/ night should be way better offer in terms of food and general feeling. Poor hospitality unfortunately. Not good value for money."
> **- Honeymoon 365 (2/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sea-valley-1.jpg','077 485 745','123/3 moo 2, ตำบล ลิปะน้อย koh samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.seavalleyhotel.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.387+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.387+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sea-valley-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sea-valley-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17800348520708837780',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('seara-sports-systems','standard','cmr07iht900rwq8xd3w8h6z21','SEARA Sports Systems','## Top Reviews
> "Horrible Service - I hate writing poor reviews but honestly this company have been horrible to deal with. Forgotten orders, wrong orders and the last time I emailed them they said they were on vacation and would get back to me. It never happened.  This is typical of company with exclusive distribution. It might be a better experience for you if you are a big business but for a solo operator with a few hundred thousand baht to spend, they don''t have much interest.  Sad that a few good brands like Life Fitness, Escape, Hammer are represented by this company. Good luck dealing with them..."
> **- K P (1/5/5)**

> "Absolutely brilliant customer service and a good range of high end sports equipment and knowledgeable staff.  Highly recommended!"
> **- Marie Wright (5/5/5)**

> "Excellent quality products and superb customer service, highly recommended."
> **- Marie Wright (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/seara-sports-systems-1.jpg','077 953 146','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.searasports.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 3:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifuo0015q8xdfahzrsp4','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.389+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.389+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/seara-sports-systems-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/seara-sports-systems-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1171545428299463814',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('searobin-dive-centre','standard','cmr07ihtc00rxq8xd6seupqev','Searobin Dive Centre','## Top Reviews
> "During my vacation in Koh Samui I booked 4 dive sessions with Searobin dive center. The 4 dives were absolutely amazing. Arek is professional, always punctual and an expert in the business. I can highly recommend him. Thanks again for the amazing dives and see you again next year."
> **- Peter van der Klooster (5/5/5)**

> "I did my PADI certification here. Great diving school, Arek is a very patient and well informed diver. I would highly recommend him to anyone who wants to get into diving. I now feel confident to go diving anywhere in the world. Thanks Arek!"
> **- Arthur Glowinski (5/5/5)**

> "I passed my PADI Open Water Diver certificate with the help of Arek and Searobin. From the initial inquiry to booking through to the lessons and diving itself, everything was incredibly smooth and efficient. Comms were crisp, pick ups were convenient and prompt, the chartered boats were clean and fast with tasty and free food. Most importantly despite being here in rainy season the dive spots were still full of marine life. Throughout the programme I felt that Arek was moving at my speed, and that I was in very safe hands. I would fully recommend Searobin for any aspiring diver, and will call them up when I come back to Koh Samui."
> **- Vincent Rebeix (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/searobin-dive-centre-1.jpg','084 868 4842','Tongsai Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://divesearobin.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifsv000nq8xdrwnu123q','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.392+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.392+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/searobin-dive-centre-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/searobin-dive-centre-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4616316883236720053',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('seatran-ferry-discovery','standard','cmr07ihte00ryq8xdob112n49','Seatran Ferry Discovery','## Top Reviews
> "Always punctual and professional I’ve used Seatran many times and they have always been on time and well-organized. The check-in is smooth, staff are helpful, and the boats are reliable. Great service for island transfers in Thailand — definitely recommended!"
> **- Luca Foschi (5/5/5)**

> "Great service, always on-time.  Their captains are actually “certified captains” understands the waves, weather and have a responsibility to maintain safety.  Some other boat services, have no registered captains in their operations."
> **- Ros C. (5/5/5)**

> "Very good experience, both times absolutely on time. Especially good for people who are getting easily seasick, because boats are quite big, so bigger waves are no problem at all. Staff was very friendly and helpful with the luggage."
> **- S K (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/seatran-ferry-discovery-1.jpg','086 476 4825','Koh Samui, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.seatrandiscovery.com/','["Monday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ig1n003kq8xd72v6yb3r','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.394+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.394+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/seatran-ferry-discovery-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/seatran-ferry-discovery-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2825802175855440429',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('seatran-ferry','standard','cmr07ihtg00rzq8xdry5il6g1','Seatran Ferry','## Top Reviews
> "Sharing my experience on getting over to Koh Samui by the ferry using van. We had a very unpleasant experience & it goes like this…we spent a night in Khanom & to get to the ferry terminal early the next morning. We arrived ( by the way, we hired a Thai van 10 seaters) at the dock at 8:45am. Because we didn’t ( couldn’t get online to purchase the van ticket) buy ferry tickets in advance, as for passengers tickets, there is no issue. But as for vehicles it is a first come first served. We got the van ticket at 13:30 schedule to go on board. The van didn’t board the ferry until 17:30. It is a 1 hour 30 minutes ferry ride to get across, it was a madness wait to go over to Koh Samui. So the lesson here is to buy pre booked van ticket online atleast 2 or 3 days ahead before travel. Pre-booked lane is a separate queue lane. Take my advice… travel safe & have a great trip."
> **- Paul Ooi (4/5/5)**

> "Seatran Ferry is the only company I wholeheartedly recommend, excelling in reliability, exceptional service, comfort, air-conditioned amenities, diverse food options, and a punctual schedule."
> **- Edward Smalley (5/5/5)**

> "You need to tell all passengers that their seats match their tickets.  Otherwise, they will just put their bags there, and some people won’t have a seat.  I booked the Seatran Ferry for both the outbound and return trips.  The outbound trip went smoothly, but on the return trip, many people didn’t have seats. 😱"
> **- WhoKnown19 Player (2/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/seatran-ferry-1.jpg','077 251 555','17, 1, Tambon Ang Thong, อำเภอ ดอนสัก, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84220, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.1,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.seatranferry.com/','["Monday: 5:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 5:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 5:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 5:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 5:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 5:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 5:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07ig1n003kq8xd72v6yb3r','cmr07ig1h003iq8xdb1g9nifo','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.396+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.396+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/seatran-ferry-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/seatran-ferry-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3097775462708222411',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('secret-garden-beach-resort','standard','cmr07ihti00s0q8xdbcsaf98d','Secret Garden Beach Resort','## Top Reviews
> "The hotel is located on a nice beach and is an easy access to the pier and airport. One thing I didn’t know about when we booked and just wanted to call out is that the bathrooms have some small openings to the outside that can’t be closed. It became a bit of a problem for me since lizards/bugs were coming in to the bathroom. The room itself was okay, so if you’re not afraid like me it would be worth the price."
> **- Dana Frid (3/5/5)**

> "We had dinner. There was live entertainment and dancing. The all you can eat ribs were delicious and at a great price. The wagyu burger was delicious too. There’s a resort here with nice rooms. The atmosphere next to the beach was magical."
> **- Shirden (5/5/5)**

> "We came here for dinner whilst staying in the area.  The service was good and the food was decent.  There was live music on during our visit which added to the nice vibe.  Would recommend visiting here."
> **- Charlie (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/secret-garden-beach-resort-1.jpg','077 332 661','22/1 Moo 4, Big Buddha Beach, Bophut, Bangrak, Koh Samui, Surat Thani Bophut เขตบางรัก Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'http://secretgardensamui.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.398+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.398+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/secret-garden-beach-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/secret-garden-beach-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13320571295124016525',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('secret-of-samui','standard','cmr07ihtk00s1q8xdjb3u3j9n','Secret Of Samui','## Top Reviews
> "The store is amazing, and has a lot of amazing and natural products. I couldn’t decide what to take because I would love to buy all!! Highly recommend 🥥🥰😍"
