INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('securitas-thailand','standard','cmr07ihtm00s2q8xdtqpf21qk','Securitas Thailand','## Top Reviews
> "Because Securitas is the best in the world"
> **- Petr Pracný (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/securitas-thailand-1.jpg','077 426 940','119/29 Moo 1, Bophut, ตำบล บ่อผุด Koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.securitas.co.th/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.402+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.402+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/securitas-thailand-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/securitas-thailand-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8967613994048555035',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('seedaeng-bungalows','standard','cmr07ihto00s3q8xd02ajwke7','Seedaeng Bungalows','## Top Reviews
> "We stayed here for a week and are looking forward to going back for another. The rooms are spacious with comfortable beds. The AC is excellent and so is the staff. Outstanding value and amazing location on the beach!  Marie is a laid back hostess and if you need anything all you have to do is ask. This has been our home away from home. The cocktails are made by a brilliant bartender, they are strong and taste lovely."
> **- Laura Williams (5/5/5)**

> "Then only good thing is the location. We walked in and out, payed 1 night but didn''t stay. Dirty, dusty, cat walking everywhere even the kitchen. I was glad there is a nice place to stay next door. The owner might be a nice lady (as told by some poeple)  but we didn''t get to meet her, the other ones were not very welcoming and they forgot about our booking. Total mess. I hope they improve the place and service because here is a lot of potential."
> **- Johana C. S. (1/5/5)**

> "We didn''t stay here this is solely based on the restaurant. I''ll start off by saying at least the beers were good because they were cold. We ordered shrimp with garlic and pepper and penang seafood. Both dishes weren''t even close to that. The shrimp was battered in way I can''t even describe, actually it wasn''t even supposed to be battered so I''m not sure what happened there. But even if it was the batter was disgusting; soggy, cold and obviously not fried properly. The penang wasn''t penang. Maybe a sweet coconut soup at best. Didn''t taste awful but shouldn''t have been labelled penang. Buuut all of this makes sense because we found out later the chef was a foreigner. Can''t expect amazing local food from a non native. Too bad the menu is only Thai food. The staff were a lot of fun though cause they were pretty much blackout drunk. Maybe a fun place to party but don''t eat here."
> **- Mags Hammill (2/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/seedaeng-bungalows-1.jpg','081 537 0302','Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.seedaengmaenam.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.404+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.404+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/seedaeng-bungalows-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/seedaeng-bungalows-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12616493512594100310',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('seen-beach-club','standard','cmr07ihtp00s4q8xde3kayrn6','SEEN Beach Club','## Top Reviews
> "We’ve been to SEEN club a few times, including three years ago, and this time during the Zamna Festival- and once again, it was amazing. We had a reservation for a lounge area with poufs, which made the whole experience even more comfortable and special.  Everything was wonderful: delicious sushi, great cocktails, and truly excellent service. The staff were attentive and professional, which made the night even better.  I also tried a truffle pizza from a friend, and it was probably the best pizza I’ve ever had in my life.  An unforgettable experience -we will definitely be back! ✨"
> **- Karolina Okrągła (5/5/5)**

> "We had an absolute amazing time at Seen Ko Samui!  The atmosphere was very energetic and felt like a beach club similar to Ibiza!  Prices were moderate and service was absolutely on point. Shoutout to Bow and Ton who made our time extra special and made the service outstanding.  We are definitely coming back."
> **- Tom Behn (5/5/5)**

> "First time in Thailand and I am amazed at the food here. The Seen restaurant has a broad range of food with asian twists and I just Love it! The staff as well is really nice and professional. I even bonded with Justina who is a wonderful host! Great to eat and relax, though as it''s a beach club, beware of the music loudness from 2pm onwards."
> **- Clarisse Benharoche (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/seen-beach-club-1.jpg','077 956 800','Sala Koy Road Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.seenbeachclubsamui.com/?utm_source=GoogleMyBusiness&utm_medium=GMB&utm%20_term=SEENSamui&utm_content=Home&utm_campaign=Google_GMB','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.405+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.405+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/seen-beach-club-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/seen-beach-club-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10043810101670973984',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('seetawaree','standard','cmr07ihts00s5q8xdcid1dogl','Seetawaree','## Top Reviews
> "We live close to this place and like to come here. The atmosphere is nice and there’s a sea view. Prices are good for this area. When it rains, it’s not so comfortable. The owners are kind and polite. The food is tasty and filling. In the evening, some music would make it better. We didn’t stay at the hotel, so can’t say about that."
