INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('serenity-yachting','standard','cmr07ihtw00s7q8xdtxwp8abx','Serenity Yachting','## Top Reviews
> "Don''t be fooled by this company.  On their site they show they have individual pricing 3250 baht/pp.  However, when you contact them they only want to sell the private tours 100,000 baht.  They tell you they are all sold out yet the boat has sat at the dock for over a week in front of the KOB.  I''m not sure what or how their business model works, but maybe best to look at other companies that provide a service rather than false information."
> **- John Johnson (1/5/5)**

> "Very impressive service and hospitality 🏝️🙏🏼"
> **- Chris (5/5/5)**

> "Perfect and best company of boat, very good services !"
> **- Malisa (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/serenity-yachting-1.jpg','094 498 6316','82/1, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.2,0,0,0,NULL,'https://linktr.ee/serenity_yachting','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.412+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.412+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/serenity-yachting-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/serenity-yachting-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=628239468408044288',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('seventy-fahrenheit','standard','cmr07ihtz00s8q8xdse6n4mey','Seventy Fahrenheit','## Top Reviews
> "We went here for dinner on 22nd May and the whole experience was lovely! We got a pasta and the Massaman curry which my husband has said was the best curry he has ever had. We also had the mango sticky rice for dessert and it was also one of the best ones we’ve had! Service was great, can’t rate this place higher."
> **- Mallory Bennett (5/5/5)**

> "We really enjoyed everything at this French-Thai fusion restaurant. From the first bite to the last, the experience was all about amazing flavors and perfectly balanced tastes. Each dish felt thoughtfully prepared and beautifully presented.  The absolute highlight for us was the Wellington steak — tender, juicy, and cooked to perfection, with an incredible combination of textures and aromas. It was honestly one of the best taste experiences we’ve had in a long time.  If you’re looking for something special and memorable, this place is definitely worth visiting. We’ll be coming back for sure!"
> **- Sabína Cepka (5/5/5)**

> "We went for dinner here last night and the service was amazing. The restaurant is clean, catchy and has a good atmosphere. The staff are welcoming, attentive and friendly. I had the best cocktails here - very balanced and tasty. The food was delicious and presented beautifully. I highly recommend coming here for a goot meal or even just for a few drinks :)"
> **- Bianca Katai (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/seventy-fahrenheit-1.jpg','084 513 5143','124, 314 Thanon Had Lamai, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://m.facebook.com/SEVENTYRESTAURANTLAMAIKOHSAMUI/','["Monday: 4:00 – 10:30 PM","Tuesday: 4:00 – 10:30 PM","Wednesday: 4:00 – 10:30 PM","Thursday: 4:00 – 10:30 PM","Friday: 4:00 – 10:30 PM","Saturday: 4:00 – 10:30 PM","Sunday: 4:00 – 10:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.415+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.415+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/seventy-fahrenheit-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/seventy-fahrenheit-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3010269035438568222',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sexy-fish','standard','cmr07ihu100s9q8xdh0z6u9a4','Sexy Fish','## Top Reviews
> "Absolutely loved my experience at Sexy Fish. The food was honestly incredible, every dish felt unique, flavorful, and beautifully presented. The desserts were just as impressive and definitely worth saving room for.  What really made the night even better was the service. May was amazing throughout the entire experience, supper attentive, friendly, and made us feel genuinely welcomed without being over the top. You can tell the team really cares about the experience they provide.  Definitely one of those places that lives up to the hype, both for the atmosphere and the quality of the food. Would happily come back again."
> **- Ali Ahmed (5/5/5)**

> "I dine at Sexy Fish twice on my recent vacation. I was very impressed from the fresh seafood, cocktails, service and special touches that made the experience special. Yes, it’s a killer more on the $ side, but well worth it and I felt is was value for money. I would recommend."
> **- Tom Fitzgerald (5/5/5)**

> "Simply amazing, 5 out of 5. Every dish we tried has been very, very good - it is clear that the chef and team put a lot of attention into every single detail.  From presentation to taste and quality of ingredients - it''s impossible to find anything we did not like.  We tried tuna maki, shrimp toasties, octopus and hazelnut seabass and oh my god - and we are really picky eaters.  Just come over and see for yourself. Totally worth it."
> **- Yaroslav Budlyansky (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sexy-fish-1.jpg','077 905 888','99/10 Moo 2, ถนน เลียบหาดเฉวง Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.salasamuichawengmenu.com/sexy-fish1.html','["Monday: 3:00 – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 3:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 3:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 3:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 3:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 3:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 3:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.417+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.417+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sexy-fish-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sexy-fish-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17940324119062666673',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('shahda-yoga-studio','standard','cmr07ihu300saq8xdr3u0kenb','Shahda Yoga Studio','## Top Reviews
> "Highly recommend this yoga class! Very welcoming environment and excellent yoga. The instructor did a really wonderful flow and was very quick to help us improve our own flow. She also was very aware of any bad patterns I kept repeating, which no other previous instructor has picked up on, which I found really useful."
> **- Monica Gupta (5/5/5)**

> "We came in as complete beginners, a little nervous and not knowing what to expect — and we left feeling absolutely amazing. From the moment we walked through the door, the welcome was so warm and genuine that any anxiety we had completely melted away. Our teacher was incredible. Patient, attentive, and passionate about what she does. Every pose was carefully explained and demonstrated, and we never once felt lost or out of place. For a first yoga experience, we honestly could not have asked for anything better. We left feeling relaxed, energised, and already excited to come back. This studio has gained two loyal new students — we will absolutely be returning very soon!"
> **- Adna Arslanovic (5/5/5)**

> "After two weeks of almost daily classes with Era, I feel safe to say that anyone can find themselves here. Era brings a rare combination of physical and spiritual. Her meticulous instruction helps you find with anatomical precision which muscle and body part is the focus of any movement, and yet serve your mind and your metal wellbeing through the practice. I finished every morning practice with a lightness and inner calm that carried me through the rest of the day. Thank you for a wonderful time!"
> **- Jonathan Grozovski (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/shahda-yoga-studio-1.jpg','061 996 9540','3/28 Moo 1, Fisherman''s Village, H25M+Q4 Bophut, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.shahdayoga.com/','["Monday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 9:30 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifuo0015q8xdfahzrsp4','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.419+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.419+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/shahda-yoga-studio-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/shahda-yoga-studio-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15468208294902044884',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('shangrilah-bungalow','standard','cmr07ihu500sbq8xd49v6fh24','Shangrilah Bungalow','## Top Reviews
> "We felt very comfortable at Shangrilah. Our bungalow was quite small, but cosy. The location is great, right next to the beach, and the pool with sun loungers overlooks the sea. The staff is very friendly and the breakfast is simple but adequate. There are several vegetarian/vegan restaurants in the area, which was also a great plus for us. Unfortunately, we had a cockroach in the bathroom one evening and several lizards also visited us. Of course, this cannot be ruled out due to the proximity to nature, but the door did not close completely because it was warped.  Two small bottles of water are provided daily, but a proper drinking water dispenser would be great."
> **- Jane (5/5/5)**

> "We stayed in a bungalow with faced the beach. We were amazed waking up every day and watch dancing tree palms in the wind. The bungalow is bright and very spacious with convinient pieces of furniture in thai style. Clean and well working bathroom. We felt there very comfortable. There is beautiful beach with spots of shade which we needed in hot days. Sometimes it can be really windy and the sea is rough these days. There is also a great swimming pool with many sunbeds around. Breakfasts are various and tasy in western and thai style. The restaurant is open all dayand offers delicious meals and drinks in reasonable prices. The memmbers of staff are kind and friendly, lovely and hilarious. There are different restaurants and mini markets not so far from the hotel. 7/11 is 800 m from the hotel. I reccommend the bungalows and every day walks along the beach watching beautiful sunrises."
> **- Monika Hildebrandt (5/5/5)**

> "The rooms are spacious and the AC is very strong. The Staff is very polite. The location is a bit remote (good if you like empty beaches, Bad if you want flexibility)."
> **- Jonathan E. (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/shangrilah-bungalow-1.jpg','077 425 189','1, หาดแม่น้ำ, 2, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.shangrilahbungalow.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.421+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.421+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/shangrilah-bungalow-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/shangrilah-bungalow-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13471683453000499218',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('shasa-resort-residences','standard','cmr07ihu700scq8xdpgdf8nwq','ShaSa Resort & Residences','## Top Reviews
> "We didn''t want to leave!  Our absolute best accommodation thus far in our 6 weeks in Thailand.  The whole suite was so comfortable.  We felt at home with so much living space and a well equipped kitchen.  The beds were very comfortable. The free breakfast was tasty and varied.  The restaurant food was good and we took advantage of room service a couple of times which was very convenient.   The pools are lovely and the views from anywhere on the property are stunning. It''s a little off the beaten path so we made use of the scooter rentals on-site or called a taxi for some exploration of the rest of Samui.  I will now be ruined for any other place we stay because Shasa was so incredible."
> **- Barb Sisson (5/5/5)**

> "We loved our stay here. Positives: Super friendly and helpful staff, especially Thanida and May on reception. Fantastic pool areas and gardens. Awesome location on the beach. Amazing huge apartment - felt like a palace. Wonderful breakfast and resteraunt area. Our family really enjoyed the breakfast each morning. Good gym. Everything super clean.  Things to keep in mind: They have been renovating, but this did not bother us significantly. The location is a bit out of town, but we loved being away from the hustle and bustle. I recommend to hire a car to make life easy. We hired one at the airport for US$31 per day. Scooters are also cheap to hire and you can hire them from reception for 400 baht per day.  We loved this place and definitely hope to return one day. Thanks for having us! 🙂👍"
> **- Bram Tibbs (5/5/5)**

> "The most beautiful view, amazing pools, and spacious rooms. The rooms came fully equipped with a kitchen and washer/dryer. Ordered room service from the restaurant a couple of times and everything was delicious. Location was great for relaxing but not great if you wanted to do anything else on the island as it’s a 20-40 minutes drive from any stores or activities. Worth the extra driving time though."
> **- katie sisson (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/shasa-resort-residences-1.jpg','065 525 8815','116, 1 Laem-Set Rd, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ig3v004fq8xdw6q7afhh','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.423+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.423+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/shasa-resort-residences-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/shasa-resort-residences-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14673952994763436044',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('shine-spa','standard','cmr07ihub00sdq8xdcwckikkj','Shine Spa','## Top Reviews
> "One of the best massages of my life, so I booked another session the next day. My masseuse MAY was beyond amazing, very professional, thorough, and found every knot and trouble spot. She checked in on pressure and adjusted if needed. A very pampered, elegant and relaxing experience all round. From the moment you walk in to the moment you leave top level execution at every point."
> **- M Sharpe (5/5/5)**

> "A very welcoming spa that feels very peaceful.Lovely staff. i had x 2,Thai massages whist staying atthee Bandara resort. Both were from lovely ,smiling MINT.Her veryskilfull hands and fingers ensured and resulted in an amazing  feeling of total relaxation.   Itwas a  great  experience 😊👌 Thank you kindly MINT 🤗"
> **- Pam Lockie (5/5/5)**

> "This was an amazing experience! Everyone was soo sweet and the massage was the best massage I’ve ever had!!"
