INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('siam-green','standard','cmr07ihuf00sfq8xdjw47kqwo','Siam Green','## Top Reviews
> "Excellent service and they are very helpful and insightful about each breed. This shop is a go to if you''re around Chaweng beach and want to have a good time and a light head. 😉 The shop has various packages and is quite affordable as well."
> **- Nehabul Haque Niloy (5/5/5)**

> "One of the more reputable canna stores in Thailand. There’s a few chains in Bangkok, glad to find one in Koh Samui. There’s service is super friendly. I love that there’s an upstairs lounge where you can puff & they provide b0ngs on the house for use  A great way to chill on the island. A bit on the pricier end, 400-900 baht a gram"
> **- Soul Munchie (5/5/5)**

