INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('silavadee-weddings','standard','cmr07ihv400skq8xdoc0t1vg8','Silavadee Weddings','## Top Reviews
> "I celebrated my 40th birthday at Silavadee Pool Spa Resort in Koh Samui, and it was truly unforgettable. The resort offers breathtaking ocean views, beautiful private villas, and a peaceful atmosphere that makes it perfect for relaxation. The staff were incredibly friendly and attentive, always going the extra mile to make our stay special. I would like to give a special mention to two staffs, Bee and Dream for their wonderful service and fun conversations we had with them. The breakfast was excellent with plenty of fresh options, and the infinity pools overlooking the sea were unforgettable. Overall, Silavadee is a stunning luxury retreat that combines natural beauty, comfort, and outstanding service. Highly recommended for a relaxing getaway."
> **- Noble Adu Agyapong (5/5/5)**

> "First time in Koh Samui with my high school friends, and we couldn''t have picked a better place! We planned and booked this trip a year in advance for a long holiday, and it was worth every single second of waiting. The resort just finished its renovation, and everything looked absolutely stunning. ​We stayed at the Silavadee Ocean Front Pool Villa Suite No.2, which has the absolute best view in the entire resort. At 30,000 THB a night, it was worth every single Baht—the view is worth millions! We were happy every second, from watching the sunrise to seeing the sunlight sparkle on the sea during the day, and swimming under a beautiful full moon at night in our huge private pool. ​The public areas and restaurants were excellent with delicious food, and the service was top-notch. They even have a dedicated app to chat and request anything you need, which was super convenient. The private beach was also incredibly relaxing. ​We will definitely be back if we get the chance! Highly recommended! ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ Special thanks to Khun Su, who gave us an incredible experience from the very first day she helped us book the villa, all the way through ensuring we were perfectly taken care of during our stay. Such amazing service🫶🏻🤍"
> **- A Dapawi (5/5/5)**

> "This is truly one of the most beautiful places I have ever stayed in my entire life! it felt like paradise. Everything about this resort is absolutely perfect.  The place is exceptionally clean, to the highest standards, and extremely elegant in every single detail. You can clearly feel the luxury and care throughout the entire property.  The staff are beyond amazing!! genuinely some of the best and most professional people I have ever encountered. Their hospitality, kindness, and attention to detail were outstanding and unforgettable.  The private beach is incredibly clean and easily one of the most beautiful beaches I’ve ever seen. I stayed with my family in a two-bedroom villa with a private pool, and it was excellent in every way.. spotless, beautifully designed, and absolutely comfortable.  Everything was perfect. I honestly wish I had stayed for more days, and I would return without any hesitation."
> **- Fatema Alminoo (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/silavadee-weddings-1.jpg','077 960 555','208/66 Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.silavadeeresort.com/?utm_source=GoogleMyBusiness','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.456+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.456+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/silavadee-weddings-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/silavadee-weddings-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15522095521303294624',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('silent-divers','standard','cmr07ihv700slq8xdp2cwtc7c','Silent Divers','## Top Reviews
> "I recently went on a private diving charter with Silent Divers in Koh Samui and honestly couldn’t fault a single part of the experience.  From the moment we booked, everything was seamless. Communication via WhatsApp was quick, clear, and easy, and the entire trip was extremely well organised. We were picked up and dropped off exactly on time, which made the day completely stress-free.  Our diving instructor, Riggert, was fantastic—knowledgeable, professional, funny, kind, and incredibly accommodating throughout the day. The crew on the boat were equally wonderful, always friendly and attentive, and they helped create a relaxed and enjoyable atmosphere from start to finish.  The diving itself was excellent, and I particularly appreciated the option to rent a GoPro directly through Silent Divers, which made capturing memories underwater very convenient. The food provided on board was also delicious and exceeded expectations.  Overall, the experience offered outstanding value for money and was one of the highlights of our time in Koh Samui. I would highly recommend Silent Divers for both private charters and group excursions. I’ll definitely be booking with them again the next time I’m back in Koh Samui.  Thank you to the entire team for such a memorable day! 🌊🤿"
> **- Conrad (5/5/5)**

> "It was very very great, no regrets. As a teenager this is very nice experience and great moments. Also, being with our instructor Jose makes me more confident, safe, and happy. By his guidance it helps me to stay calm every time and everywhere. For the silent divers, they were very gentle and helpful that makes me to be more motivated and focused. Overall experience was an 100% Excellent. Hope to see you again soon."
> **- Jewel Carpio (5/5/5)**

> "I had an absolutely fantastic experience with Silent Divers. From start to finish, everything was perfectly organized and the entire team was incredibly professional, friendly, and attentive. You can really feel that they are passionate about diving and about making sure every guest has a safe, enjoyable, and memorable experience.  The briefings were clear and reassuring, and the overall atmosphere was relaxed while still maintaining a very high level of professionalism.  A special thank you to our Divemaster Bjorn, who was simply outstanding. He was calm, knowledgeable, and always attentive to the group. His guidance underwater made the dives both safe and truly enjoyable. You can tell he has a lot of experience and a genuine passion for the ocean and for sharing it with others.  Thanks to Bjorn and the whole Silent Divers team, this was without a doubt one of the best diving experiences I’ve had. I highly recommend Silent Divers to anyone looking for a top-quality dive center with a great team and flawless organization.  I will definitely dive with them again.  ⸻"
> **- Marc Toledo (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/silent-divers-1.jpg','081 933 6641','39 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://silentdivers.com/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.459+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.459+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/silent-divers-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/silent-divers-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1156369873659742696',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('skandi-collection','standard','cmr07ihva00smq8xdwprktxf0','Skandi Collection','## Top Reviews
> "We were completely blown away by the Skandi team. From the moment we walked in, they made us feel genuinely welcome and at home.  In less than a week they made us two suits, a winter coat, pants, dress shirts, and a blouse. Every piece fits like it was engineered specifically for us. The quality is fantastic and the selection of fabrics was huge.  Even better, the price was incredibly reasonable for fully custom clothing. They also keep your measurements on file, so ordering again later is easy.  We honestly couldn’t be happier with our new wardrobe. Next time we need custom clothes… we might just have to come back to Koh Samui.  10/10 — would absolutely do this again. 👔✨"
> **- Jonathan White (5/5/5)**

> "My husband had a suit  and additional pants made. Perfect fitting suit. Would definitely recommend. Friendly and professional service and well priced for excellent quality."
> **- Rachel (5/5/5)**

> "I had a suit and two shirts tailored at Skandi Collection in Lamai and couldn’t be happier.  The consultation was professional and attentive, with great advice and a strong focus on the perfect fit. The quality and craftsmanship are outstanding – everything fits perfectly and feels premium.  Excellent service from start to finish. Highly recommended!"
> **- Boris Schmidtke (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/skandi-collection-1.jpg','062 065 7137','Lamai Beach Road, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://skandicollectionsamui.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.462+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.462+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/skandi-collection-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/skandi-collection-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1770352636578758998',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sky-lounge-jamaican-bar-grill','standard','cmr07ihvi00snq8xd3pyzh4cq','Sky Lounge - Jamaican Bar & Grill','## Top Reviews
> "Absolutely amazing experience at Trap House Samui!  From the moment we arrived, the team was incredible so welcoming, attentive, and genuinely friendly. You can really feel the positive energy and passion behind this place. The service was flawless and made us feel truly taken care of.  The food was outstanding: packed with flavor, beautifully presented, and perfectly prepared. Every dish we tried was a hit.  If you’re in Samui, this place is a must-visit. We’ll definitely be back highly, highly recommended!"
> **- Momentsoleil (5/5/5)**

> "This place has serious soul. The kind of spot you walk into and immediately feel the vibe — warm, genuine, no pretense. The Wray & Nephew speaks for itself — whoever is behind that bar truly respects the rum. And the rum punch? Dangerously good. The kind you’re still thinking about the next day. 🥃 Then the Jamaican patties arrive and suddenly you’re nowhere near Thailand anymore. Flaky, golden, packed with flavour — completely authentic and absolutely addictive. This isn’t just a restaurant, it’s a little piece of Jamaica dropped right into Samui. A total gem. Go. 🇯🇲🔥​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​​"
> **- Ingrida Allen (5/5/5)**

> "Because it was off-season, we were alone all evening... a shame because this place is highly recommended! The food was fantastic, the view is amazing, and the staff is incredibly friendly! We chose this spot to avoid being surrounded by Instagrammers ;) Tip: the shuttle taxi is waiting down the hill, don''t go up by motorbike!"
> **- N. Nieboer (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sky-lounge-jamaican-bar-grill-1.jpg','099 793 0232','5, Tambon Bo Put, Ko Samui District, District, ตำบล บ่อผุด Koh Smaui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig5c0051q8xdykrbexft','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.470+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.470+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sky-lounge-jamaican-bar-grill-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sky-lounge-jamaican-bar-grill-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3286921897821163778',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('skye-beach','standard','cmr07ihvn00soq8xdtdoq8de4','Skye Beach','## Top Reviews
> "We spent six wonderful days at Skye Beach Hotel in Koh Samui with our two children, and we can honestly say: it was one of the best vacations we’ve ever had! One of the absolute highlights was the breathtaking rooftop pool. The view from up there is simply stunning – the perfect place to relax and unwind. Both we and our kids absolutely loved it. Another big plus was the thoughtfully designed room layout. Our children had their own room, while we had a separate bedroom that could also be closed off. This setup was fantastic and ideal for us as a family – comfortable, practical, and very well designed. The cleanliness throughout the hotel was excellent. Our room was cleaned thoroughly every day – everything was always spotless. We would also like to give special praise to the reception team: always friendly, helpful, and truly dedicated. Whether it was booking activities, arranging transport, or giving recommendations, they supported us in every possible way. The nearby beach is also beautiful and pleasantly quiet – perfect for families and anyone looking to relax. All in all, it was a truly memorable stay that we won’t forget anytime soon. We highly recommend Skyt Beach Hotel and would absolutely love to come back!"
> **- Anna (5/5/5)**

> "We had the most fabulous one week holiday at Skye Beach Hotel situated in a quiet part of Samui on the pristine and uncrowded Plai Laem beach. We stayed in a 2-bedroom unit. The room is excellent, very spacious, very well maintained and clean, excellent sea view, excellent mattress and pillows, three bathrooms, good hot and cold water pressure, comfortable cinema room, coffee machine, very comfortable sofa for taking naps. The complimentary coconut candy in the room is really good. Sunset view from the room is beautiful and the best part is watching and relaxing in the infinity pool. And having a massage with seaview without leaving your room is something you gonna tell your friends.  Kudos to Skye Beach Hotel for having such efficient, helpful, and courteous staff. During our holiday here we made some very beautiful friends. Their friendly approach made us feel very welcome. You have truly shown the beauty of Thai culture of warm hospitality.  To our new friends, Aru, Ross, Whan, Ben, Nitty, Moolarn, Goh, you have made our family holiday a most enjoyable holiday everyday the whole week. Thank you."
> **- glyn sim (5/5/5)**

> "We spent two beautiful weeks at Skye Beach Hotel with our two boys in Koh Samui. The hotel is new and modern, the neighborhood is quiet. The hotel is on the beach so we could swim, the water was clean there. Our room was huge with two big bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, one TV room and a big living room with a balcony, and a pool. The view was spectacular from there! The staff well how can I say it…. We LOVE them!!!!❤️ Nitty, thank you for everything, your smile and kind heart made our vacation sooo much better!❤️ Anytime we passed the reception we got huge smiles and nice words from everybody!❤️ Thanks for cleaning our room every day, it was spotless, the towels were always changed and smelt so good! Spoon!❤️We loved everything you cooked for us!❤️"
> **- Mariann Csatári (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/skye-beach-1.jpg','064 923 4590','8, 135 Plai Laem Soi 2, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.skyebeachsamui.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifv2001aq8xdag7cvjgf','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.475+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.475+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/skye-beach-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/skye-beach-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1500650587374140838',NULL,NULL);
