> "Thank to all the team that has helped my stay in Thailand be smooth and sweet. From visa to setting up companies everything was perfect. Lana and team you''re the best"
> **- Jay Mathews (5/5/5)**

> "A very efficient office, a very nice woman, always with a smile... very fun to deal with. I recommend"
> **- M A (5/5/5)**

> "Excellent service. Very fast, very professional."
> **- Adios Upella (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sn-business-group-coltd-1.jpg','090 275 7357','23, Bonkai, 291, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61550661568345&mibextid=ZbWKwL',NULL,'cmr07ifu0000zq8xdvll5tv7z','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.480+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.480+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sn-business-group-coltd-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sn-business-group-coltd-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6425094675661166020',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('so-cafe','standard','cmr07ihvy00sqq8xdfs60gbuc','SO CAFE','## Top Reviews
> "We enjoyed our time at SO CAFE Samui — the setting is great and the vibe is nice. However, I found the prices a bit high and the wait for the food was longer than expected. The bowls I ordered weren’t quite convincing — good, but not memorable. Still, the café has promise and would be worth another visit if they speed things up and refine the menu a bit."
> **- Frequent Traveller (4/5/5)**

> "SO CAFE SAMUI is a delightful spot for coffee lovers and food enthusiasts alike! Serving very good coffee and a variety of beverages, it is a go-to place for those looking to enjoy a quality drink. The welcoming atmosphere adds to the overall experience, making it a perfect place to relax or catch up with friends. Additionally, the friendly staff likely enhances the environment, ensuring that every visit feels personal and enjoyable. Whether you''re there for a morning cup of coffee, an afternoon snack, or a cozy evening drink, SO CAFE SAMUI appears to offer a memorable experience, where customers feel valued and satisfied. It''s lovely to see establishments like this that prioritize taste, ambiance, and customer service."
> **- Nataliawtajlandii (4/5/5)**

> "This place I visited by chance and it surprised me a lot!!! I wish we had its branch in central or northern Samui🙏🏼 The food was amazing!!! The choice is not huge, but this is the point, you don’t need lots of courses to make a place successful and high level!!! I’ve tried a pasta with cream sauce with salmon. I think I made a weird sound of satisfaction right after the first bite😅🤣 awesome!!!! Coffee and other drinks are super well done!!!  They have a huge dessert cart!!! I was recommended to try an apple crumble and I didn’t regret that🤍👍🏼  There are so many things to try for my next visit of this part of the island, looking forward!!!!!  The service is perfect!! The prices are surprisingly not hight compared to other restaurant this level in the center. Wow, I hope you keep this place alive, I’m so happy to find it out🙌🏼🙏🏼🤍  Thank you!!!"
> **- eva zay (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/so-cafe-1.jpg','064 456 6246','266, Angthong, 20, Tambon Ang Thong, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.facebook.com/socafexsamui','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig1h003iq8xdb1g9nifo','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.486+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.486+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/so-cafe-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/so-cafe-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8546617593810572340',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('socialtel-sandbox','standard','cmr07ihw100srq8xdpjg0ktrt','Socialtel Sandbox','## Top Reviews
> "Loved this hostel. Really clean and easy to talk to and meet new people. It’s not too suitable if you are here for a quiet stay as the music is loud from the hostel."
> **- Isabelle king (4/5/5)**

> "We booked a private room through Agoda and loved it! I even recommend booking the rooms through their own website. They have lots of activities to meet other people and will do anything to amuse you. The only thing I think is a little bit heavy is the music during the night, you can hear it a little bit in the rooms. Overall a good experience in Koh Samui!!"
> **- kaat bruggeman (5/5/5)**

> "so the hostel looks really nice, and the rooms are nice and clean. Great bathrooms. So overall thats pretty good but ohh my the vibes are horrible. Yes its a party and social hostel but no one is socializing. Everyday there is a DJ playing all evening/night and there is absolutely no one. The pool is always empty, loud music, no one is dancing.  The staff was kind of weird not giving us enough keycards for everyone (we got 2 were with 4 people). We were out of toilet paper all day and the cleaners came at 5pm to clean the room. From all the hostels this was look wise one of the best but social wise the worst. (Beds are very comfortable tho)"
> **- Kara linde (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/socialtel-sandbox-1.jpg','077 235 888','168, Chaweng, 62 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.2,0,0,0,NULL,'https://socialtel.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.489+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.489+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/socialtel-sandbox-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/socialtel-sandbox-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17130626150387794672',NULL,NULL);
