INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('socialtel','standard','cmr07ihw500stq8xd861e8x46','Socialtel','## Top Reviews
> "Loved this hostel. Really clean and easy to talk to and meet new people. It’s not too suitable if you are here for a quiet stay as the music is loud from the hostel."
> **- Isabelle king (4/5/5)**

> "We booked a private room through Agoda and loved it! I even recommend booking the rooms through their own website. They have lots of activities to meet other people and will do anything to amuse you. The only thing I think is a little bit heavy is the music during the night, you can hear it a little bit in the rooms. Overall a good experience in Koh Samui!!"
> **- kaat bruggeman (5/5/5)**

> "so the hostel looks really nice, and the rooms are nice and clean. Great bathrooms. So overall thats pretty good but ohh my the vibes are horrible. Yes its a party and social hostel but no one is socializing. Everyday there is a DJ playing all evening/night and there is absolutely no one. The pool is always empty, loud music, no one is dancing.  The staff was kind of weird not giving us enough keycards for everyone (we got 2 were with 4 people). We were out of toilet paper all day and the cleaners came at 5pm to clean the room. From all the hostels this was look wise one of the best but social wise the worst. (Beds are very comfortable tho)"
> **- Kara linde (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/socialtel-1.jpg','077 235 888','168, Chaweng, 62 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.2,0,0,0,NULL,'https://socialtel.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.493+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.493+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/socialtel-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/socialtel-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17130626150387794672',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('soho-residence','standard','cmr07ihw900suq8xd8ez2uh1a','Soho Residence','## Top Reviews
> "The most luxurious hotels and beach clubs are just round the corner. Michelin restaurant is there as well. Perfect investment"
> **- Bralgina Yana (5/5/5)**

> "I had a great experience buying villa SOHO in Koh Samui their team was professional and attentive, helping me choose a villa that perfectly matched my layout preferences the buying process was well-organized, and their support continues even after the transaction is finalized"
> **- Эля Винс (5/5/5)**

> "This is one of the most beautiful and luxurious villa neighborhoods in Koh Samui, close to Sala, close to the sea and the neighborhood Big C, close to Big Buda and the Thai boxing gym. The place is quiet, beautiful and very luxurious."
> **- naor yanko (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/soho-residence-1.jpg','+66632734584','Plai Laem, Tambon Bo Put, Plai Laem, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://sohoresidence.asia/?utm_source=Gmaps','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ifv2001aq8xdag7cvjgf','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.497+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.497+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/soho-residence-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/soho-residence-2.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/soho-residence-3.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6403609960732779883',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sound-club','standard','cmr07ihwb00svq8xdo3oa0qtd','Sound Club','## Top Reviews
> "I had a very disappointing experience at this nightclub. While I was dancing, my money was stolen. Before entering, I exchanged $100, and by the end of the night all of it was gone. I immediately reported the theft to security, expecting them to take the matter seriously, but they completely ignored me and showed no interest in helping or investigating what happened.  As a tourist, this made me feel extremely unsafe and unsupported. When guests report theft, security should at least make an effort to assist rather than act as if they don’t care. Based on my experience, visitors should be very careful with their belongings in this venue. I left feeling frustrated, disappointed, and concerned about the lack of security and customer care."
> **- Syd (1/5/5)**

> "I visited Sound Club on January 17 at around 00:45, and it was one of the worst club experiences I’ve had in Koh Samui.  At the entrance, security claimed they required passports or IDs for entry, but this rule was clearly applied selectively. Non-white guests were stopped and questioned, while white customers were allowed inside without showing anything. It felt discriminatory and uncomfortable.  Things got worse when I took a simple photo of the front gate to send to my friend so they could pick me up outside. Security immediately approached me aggressively and demanded that I delete the photo. Their behavior was threatening and completely unprofessional.  Inside the club, the staff and servers were uninterested in helping customers and showed no basic hospitality. Overall, the environment felt unwelcoming, rude, and unfair.  I would not recommend this place to anyone expecting respectful treatment."
> **- Mark Lourence Catahan (1/5/5)**

> "Brilliant nights there. However last night, was playing pool upstairs and tapping cue to the music. The man behind the bar came up to me, slapped me and snatched the cue out of my hand. We continued to play and 10 mins later, the ball fell off of the table. Just a silly mistake? Once again, the man behind the bar came marching up, snatched out cues and potted all of the balls. Had an amazing time there (for most of the time) except form that night. 4/5 nights there were brilliant. I would 100% recommend sound club to anybody however just be careful if you’re playing pool upstairs."
> **- charlie Cooper 54 (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sound-club-1.jpg',NULL,'195 19 ตำบล บ่อผุด Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.soundclubsamui.co/','["Monday: 10:00 PM – 6:00 AM","Tuesday: 10:00 PM – 6:00 AM","Wednesday: 10:00 PM – 6:00 AM","Thursday: 10:00 PM – 6:00 AM","Friday: 10:00 PM – 6:00 AM","Saturday: 10:00 PM – 6:00 AM","Sunday: 10:00 PM – 6:00 AM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.499+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.499+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sound-club-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sound-club-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=313739122664095126',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sound-healing-sanctuary-shantika','standard','cmr07ihwc00swq8xddfm2cplo','Sound Healing Sanctuary - Shantika','## Top Reviews
> "Svetlana is a wonderful teacher! She covers everything a beginner needs to know with great clarity. The teamwork during the sessions was excellent, and the entire learning environment was very supportive. Highly recommended for anyone starting their journey"
> **- Lenin Lakmal Premarathne (5/5/5)**

> "I’m a certified sound healing therapist :) Lana is such a wonderful teacher, I could follow and understand everything she taught us, with such grace and amazing energy. Her school is warm and welcoming, and the sounds she creates are incredibly deep and moving.  I’m grateful for our time together. I had a wonderful experience learning and exploring the singing bowls, gong, and crystal bowls. Lana is very talented, she plays many different instruments, and each day was an incredible journey. She explains everything in such a peaceful and clear way.  Her passion and knowledge are truly inspiring. I highly recommend learning with her."
> **- מגנטים ענבר איזנמן Inbar Eisenman Imagnetim (5/5/5)**

> "Just had a 3 days sound healing course. All was amazing! Thank you Lana for sharing your great knowledge with us all with calm, kind, love and happiness approach. Totally recommend and will definitely join you on more courses somewhere in the world 🙏🏻❤️"
> **- Sharon Touring (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sound-healing-sanctuary-shantika-1.jpg','063 501 2769','22/1 Moo 5 Angthong 11, Tambon, ตำบล อ่างทอง อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://shantikasound.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifxh0027q8xde6xqk8o6','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.500+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.500+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sound-healing-sanctuary-shantika-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sound-healing-sanctuary-shantika-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4243418075427101247',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sourdough-bread-bakery','standard','cmr07ihwe00sxq8xdn2gom20p','Sourdough Bread Bakery','## Top Reviews
> "Thank you dear Veronika for your healthy yummy products! Your bread is the best I ever tried all over the world! The price corresponds the quality 100%! Pitas, strudel and lasagna - all is yummy!!! It''s a pity that we are leaving Samui soon, but we hope to come back soon again! You are very passionate about your business and take great care about you clients! We wish you all the best for the future!!! Hope to meet you in person next time!"
> **- Taisiya Fedyushkina (5/5/5)**

> "This place is a welcoming addition to the island since high quality bread is not available everywhere. We tried the dark bread and it sure is a heavy beast at 1,6 kg! It was absolutely delicious and well worth 160 baht! You need to preorder your bread and they bake twice a week. Highly recommended!  Update! Tried all 3 breads and the blueberry pie... it''s all good folks! Highly quality products!"
> **- Johnny Buchwald (5/5/5)**

> "We love this place. Amazing sourdough bread, vegan lasagna, strudels and many more. Everything that Veronika makes is delicious and made with heart and soul 😊 Must try when in Samui"
> **- Margarita Cherkasova (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sourdough-bread-bakery-1.jpg','084 509 7376','112 Pracharakpattana Rd, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/SourdoughBreadSamui/',NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.502+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.502+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sourdough-bread-bakery-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sourdough-bread-bakery-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=410549235678803134',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sp-villa-management','standard','cmr07ihwh00syq8xd43agbswa','S&P Villa Management','## Top Reviews
> "I don’t understand the reviews claiming this is an unreliable company. We’ve had a very good experience. The villa we had originally rented was unavailable due to power issues, so they arranged a different villa for us—one that was much more expensive—at no extra cost. The only cost we had to pay was for electricity usage, which had been clearly communicated in advance. And for 6 nights, only €100 with full use of airco’s and washing machine!"
> **- Nelle Bel (5/5/5)**

> "Worst experience ever. They do not honour any of their offerings. The management S&P is the problem. Avoid anything to do with them. Also make sure you always check reviews. If they do not have reviews for at least two years then use onother place. Common trick in Thailand is to claim the place is sold to goggle to cancel the old listing and start a new one hence the two year check."
> **- Leon Botes (1/5/5)**

> "BE AWARE! PLEASE! This is a very untrustworthy company, Dont belive what they say! They offer a good price, but demand for a big deposit, and just never return it to me, even that the house was left perfect! excuse it with bank problem .  Trust this review, dont ignore it.  There are plenty of vilas in koh samu, If you don’t want to lose money, find something else"
> **- Mark Meshe (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sp-villa-management-1.jpg','+66619584282','160, 2, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.sp-villa-management.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.505+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.505+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sp-villa-management-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sp-villa-management-2.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sp-villa-management-3.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sp-villa-management-4.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4898841730524786310',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('spa-cenvaree','standard','cmr07ihwj00szq8xd7slvpjpy','Spa Cenvaree','## Top Reviews
> "Best spa on island. We’ve tried “SOUND OF BAMBOO GROWING”and “WHISPERS OF THE WIND”. Absolutely the best spa treatment I’ve ever had. And highly recommend AE & Rung, they’re the pro!  The spa experience is designed with a profound sense of ritual. From the very beginning to the closing moments, the resonant tones of the singing bowls create a serene atmosphere, gently guiding the mind to flow in harmony with their rising and fading vibrations."
> **- 谢宜珈 (5/5/5)**

> "The highlight of my experience was the treatment itself. The therapist (Rung) was absolutely fantastic—attentive, skilled, and truly dedicated to my wellness. It was clear that she knew exactly how to tailor the experience to my needs, leaving me feeling rejuvenated and deeply relaxed.  Everything, from the customer service to the quality of the treatments, was exceptional. I left feeling completely renewed, both physically and mentally. This spa is truly a hidden gem, and I will definitely be returning soon. Highly recommend to anyone looking for a peaceful and rejuvenating experience!"
> **- Anutida T. (5/5/5)**

> "We recently enjoyed a couple’s aromatherapy massage at the spa in Centara Reserve, and it was absolutely amazing! The treatment lasted for an hour, and we both left feeling completely rejuvenated. The welcome drinks were refreshingly delicious, setting the perfect tone for our relaxation.  The treatment room was spacious and beautifully designed, creating a serene atmosphere. The staff were attentive and continually checked in on us to ensure we were comfortable and enjoying the experience. This thoughtful approach truly elevated our spa visit. We highly recommend the spa for anyone looking to unwind and indulge in a little luxury during their stay!"
> **- Anika Hoque (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/spa-cenvaree-1.jpg','077 230 500','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.centarahotelsresorts.com/reserve/crs/spa/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ig3v004fq8xdw6q7afhh','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.507+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.507+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/spa-cenvaree-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/spa-cenvaree-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5698289167269810236',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('spaicar-auto-detailing','standard','cmr07ihwl00t0q8xdeww57dus','Spaicar Auto Detailing','## Top Reviews
> "Big thanks to the Spaicar team for an amazing job! I had my car tinted and polished with a liquid glass coating, and the results exceeded all expectations. The car looks brand new — the shine is just incredible! Everything was done carefully, professionally, and on time. The staff was polite, attentive, and explained everything clearly while taking all my preferences into account. I’m really glad I chose this service — highly recommend to anyone who values quality and care for their car!"
> **- Kirill (5/5/5)**

> "I am a detail-obsessed person with an affinity for cars.  I brought my new car here to get a Ceramic Coating applied. I can honestly say that I am very impressed with the work that Spaicar did. I watched as they worked and noted how they applied masking tape to avoid overspray on certain parts and they removed the license plates to make sure the coating was applied properly at those spots. I did this mainly to protect the car from the hot Samui UV rays and I feel confident that this will keep the car looking good for a long time.  Highly recommended 👍."
> **- Daniel Gutin (5/5/5)**

> "Professional and very friendly. Good price. Always happy when my car is ready"
> **- Michael Jernberg (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/spaicar-auto-detailing-1.jpg','094 951 5659','44 130 Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/glasscoatingkohsamui/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifui0012q8xdzn158clv','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.509+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.509+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/spaicar-auto-detailing-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/spaicar-auto-detailing-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10178116161713996883',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('spavillion','standard','cmr07ihwr00t1q8xdofgvlxca','Spavillion','## Top Reviews
> "Beautiful property.  Our 3rd visit, close to great shopping (night market next door) and restaurants (try Nana Tam down the street - we ate there 6 times!!)!! The property bar has excellent "
> **- Christine Tivas (5/5/5)**

> "Just stayed at this resort earlier this May, and it was such a private, lush, and cozy getaway. We stayed in a massive 2-story Family Pool Villa right by the beach, the views every morning and evening were incredibly relaxing. It comes with a private pool right out front and a jacuzzi on the second floor. I honestly didn''t want to go home! The room was super comfortable, the breakfast buffet had an amazing variety, and the staff took such great care of us. It’s absolutely worth the money. Highly recommended!"
> **- tanatorn tangkachaiyanant (5/5/5)**

> "Terrific stay at Pavilion and highly recommend.  The resort was very clean, and the staff went above and beyond.  Such hard working people too. Thank you for your amazing services. I especially loved the pools and beach. They had a security guard too so I had no worries of my stuff getting stolen while I was swimming. My only con was that one staff member who always poked so unhappy whenever I saw him, especially on the steak night event on Thursday’s. I had taken a look at the meats they had laid out on display but noticed the rib eye had run out so I said “no more ribeye”?  There were three staff members anroind the grill and he yelled out with an angry tone “Coming, wait!). I just looked at him and left to my table.  The rest of the time he avoided our table and instead the older gentleman Thandi helped us. He was amazing. So attentive and knew what we needed even before we did lol.  This hardworking man deserves a huge kudos. He made the stay more memorable. Thank you Thandi."
> **- Troy Delfino (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/spavillion-1.jpg','077 424 030','124 Thanon Had Lamai, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.pavilionsamui.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.515+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.515+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/spavillion-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/spavillion-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1317692002939683795',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('specs-optic','standard','cmr07ihwv00t2q8xdjonyenal','Specs Optic','## Top Reviews
> "Best one on the island. If you need glasses or check up your eyes, specs optic is the one for you. Of course the service is excellent as well. Highly recommended"
> **- NAING WIN TUN (5/5/5)**

> "I am on Koh Samui island with my family for vacation, and one of my kids accidentally broke a nose piece off his glasses. We stopped by Specs Optics after driving by and seeing them!  The staff was very friendly, polite and professional. I asked if they could fix the nose piece. They said yes, and had it done in about 10 minutes. When I asked how much to fix them, the staff said free! I was so shocked.  Thank you so much for your kindness and generosity. This place is truly restored my faith in humanity, and reminded me that there are good businesses out there that genuinely care about people! Thank you so much, Specs Optics of Koh Samui! 💚"
> **- J. C. (5/5/5)**

> "Good place if you’re looking for the best optic shop"
> **- Valen .z (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/specs-optic-1.jpg','093 582 7840','83 สมุย 22 บ่อผุด Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.specs-optic.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.519+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.519+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/specs-optic-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/specs-optic-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4730031943133046713',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('spice-zone-beach-restaurant','standard','cmr07ihww00t3q8xdg3htoamx','Spice Zone Beach Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "The breakfast buffet line pretty decent. The food really tasty. I especially love their noodle soup section and their local Thai herb rice salad.  The room is really big, comfy and beautiful with Thai style decoration. Very unique and fascinating.  The staffs are supper friendly and helpful. Literally friendly and nice. The people here makes the stay more pleasant."
> **- Annette B (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing food and great choice Barbecue was incredible with so much variety and great customer service the whole time. The fire show was impressive too A real relaxed atmosphere dining on the beach with amazing views of the sea ."
> **- Bea Haysman (5/5/5)**

> "We were guests at the Royal Muang and dined twice @ their Beach Restaurant "
> **- Steffen Rademacher (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/spice-zone-beach-restaurant-1.jpg','077 428 700','89 Bontji Moo 4 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifsv000nq8xdrwnu123q','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.521+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.521+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/spice-zone-beach-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/spice-zone-beach-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14112128190266112414',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('spices-cafe','standard','cmr07ihwy00t4q8xd5j35nbch','Spices Cafe','## Top Reviews
> "I think I had dinner here but can''t remember. Ordered the khao SOI and veggie and fruit salad. Khao SOI was decent, the fruit and veggie salad was decent.  The servers spoke and understood English and were accommodating to not put fish sauce into my salad."
> **- David Tsui (4/5/5)**

> "Lovely restaurant with a phenomenal menu and delicious cocktails. Prices are very reasonable, and it’s conveniently located near the Santiburi Samui hotel.  We ate here twice and were impressed both times. We started with the chicken satay—perfectly seasoned and full of flavour.  The chicken Pad Thai was outstanding. Beautifully flavoured and cooked perfectly (not overcooked like it often is elsewhere). Spices Cafe absolutely nailed it.  The sea bass fillet with spicy mango salad was another highlight. Lightly battered and fried to perfection, with the mango salad adding a surprising burst of heat and flavour.  On our second visit, I had the Pad Krapraw with minimal spice—again, incredible flavour, with green beans adding great texture. I couldn’t stop eating it. Mind blown.  We also tried the Spices fried rice with prawns. The prawns were tempura-style, which was a pleasant surprise, and the rice itself was bursting with flavour.  Highly recommend—fantastic food, great value, and consistently excellent quality.  Happy hour- two for one cocktails. Margaritas- shaken. Goes down so smoothly. Too smooth!!"
> **- Amber McKain (5/5/5)**

> "One of the best restaurants in this area - although it is located near the busy main street it is very cosy. The owners have a very good sense for good design. The restaurant is beautifully decorated and the food is also exceptionally well presented. The best Prawn Tempura and Khao Soi we ever had! Very friendly service and Credit cards are accepted without additional charges. Thank you for this nice evening!"
> **- Mike Peters (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/spices-cafe-1.jpg','089 501 0116','45 32 4169 Maenam Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://m.facebook.com/Spices-Cafe-1188496967827012/','["Monday: 12:00 – 10:30 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 10:30 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 10:30 PM","Thursday: Closed","Friday: 12:00 – 10:30 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 10:30 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 10:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.522+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.522+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/spices-cafe-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/spices-cafe-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5552998812450669695',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('spliff-samui-dispensary','standard','cmr07ihx000t5q8xdnvzfzjss','Spliff Samui Dispensary','## Top Reviews
> "This vibrant cafe is the perfect spot to unwind—sip a cold beer, enjoy refreshing fresh juice, or chill in a lively cannabis lounge filled with great music. A must-visit break on a hot day! We will return ✨"
> **- Balanced Travel (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing shop with two TVs and two PS5 stations for fun and a large indoor and outdoor area to hang out. indoor smoke friendly which is great. The staff is amazing and very friendly.  for the quality stuff ask them what’s in the fridge ;)  great spot to hang and go overall.  Oh it’s all cash so make sure to have before you go. Also coffee is amazing !"
> **- Jonathan Tuil (5/5/5)**

> "Visited this evening and had a great experience. The shop is clean, modern, and welcoming, and the staff were friendly and helpful without being pushy.  I picked up the Buy 2 Get 1 Free deal — 3 grams for the price of 2 — which is excellent value. I went for the Juicy J, and it’s really good quality: smooth, uplifting, and exactly what I was after.  Overall, great selection, fair prices, and a relaxed vibe. I’ll definitely be coming back next time I’m in Koh Samui."
> **- Cool Guys (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/spliff-samui-dispensary-1.jpg',NULL,'26 2, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.spliffsamui.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 3:00 AM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 3:00 AM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 3:00 AM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 3:00 AM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 3:00 AM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 3:00 AM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 3:00 AM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.524+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.524+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/spliff-samui-dispensary-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/spliff-samui-dispensary-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14190494306015272401',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('spr-accounting-business','standard','cmr07ihx300t6q8xdl7c9mdpm','SPR Accounting & Business','## Top Reviews
> ""
> **- สุภาพร บุญทอง (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/spr-accounting-business-1.jpg','092 259 8687','151 33 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.spraccounting.co/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifu0000zq8xdvll5tv7z','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.527+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.527+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/spr-accounting-business-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/spr-accounting-business-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17040782750624821003',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('srifa-resort','standard','cmr07ihx600t7q8xdcz7gb3po','Srifa Resort','## Top Reviews
> "Very Nice Location near very beautiful beach! Excellent new 2 BDR houses! Suitable for families with kids. Very helpful and hospitable owners! Very recommended!"
> **- Tatiana Semenova (5/5/5)**

> "Great place to stay! Lovely owners/family keep the house and area looking fabulous. The beach is a 1 min walk away. Stunning!"
> **- Andrew McRae (5/5/5)**

> "New and clean houses. Very friendly owners. Fast Internet. To the nice swimmable beach 100 meters only. Very recommended!"
> **- Vitaly Semenov (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/srifa-resort-1.jpg','081 535 1388','84/3, ตำบล ลิปะน้อย อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.530+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.530+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/srifa-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/srifa-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1806844559072744343',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('srikwan-farm-camp','standard','cmr07ihx800t8q8xdo66qhtfp','Srikwan Farm & Camp','## Top Reviews
> "great area makes you feel more secluded than you actually are (2 minutes down the road from main road)  lovely service and nice living space.  has loads of friendly cats running around  outdoor pool  only let down was the consistency of hundreds of biting ants in the outdoor toilet (no inside toilet) and the huge spider outside our door😂"
> **- sned z (4/5/5)**

> "What a gem ! Beautiful spot seems like newly owned with the nicest accommodating stuff. Great atmosphere with nice music, views and little to no crowds. For the food we just asked the chef to bring us whatever he would like to. And everything tasted incredible and different one from another. We are coming back again for sure"
> **- Mária Žembery (5/5/5)**

> "Reccomended 💯👍👍👍 - Southern foods are really southern taste😉 - BBQ (moo ka ta) Evening time on the hill sound good - nice ventilation - perfect scenery and nice place🏕️ - good service mind - Parking ✅ available - Available price  200-300 /each  Because of location on the hill, Its a rough way to get on there"
> **- MR W (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/srikwan-farm-camp-1.jpg','061 017 7784','99 100 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.532+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.532+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/srikwan-farm-camp-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/srikwan-farm-camp-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=769158427315486366',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('stacked-burger','standard','cmr07ihxa00t9q8xdduijbzbj','Stacked Burger','## Top Reviews
> "Good burgers, comes with fries. They give you pop corn wike waiting. They have gluten free bun. For gluten free you have to take the classic burger and pay 125 extra for the gluten free bun. The gluten free bun us nice, a little bit heavy. I think the fries are made in a speciffic gluten free fryer, i am not sure.  FYI, you are not allowed to take away burger with gluten free buns, only burger with gluten buns."
> **- Oren Tocker (4/5/5)**

> "STACKed Burger is hands down one of the best spots in Samui for a proper, juicy burger. The patties are flavorful, the brioche buns are soft and buttery, and every bite feels satisfying without being overcomplicated. The loaded fries are a must-try, and the cold beers pair perfectly with the beach-town vibe.  What really makes it special is the atmosphere — relaxed, fun, and social. It’s the kind of place where you come for a burger and end up staying for the vibes. Friendly staff, generous portions, and great music make it easy to come back again and again."
> **- Wa Sun (5/5/5)**

> "We visited this burger place and overall we really enjoyed it. The burgers were genuinely tasty, fresh and filling, so we were happy with our order.  The only downside was that there were no gloves for eating the burgers — it would have been much more convenient. Also, the blue cheese sauce tasted store-bought and a bit too salty; we were expecting a more homemade flavor.  Apart from that, everything was great and we can definitely recommend this place."
> **- Оксана Солдатова (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/stacked-burger-1.jpg','077 915 222','11 34 ตำบล บ่อผุด Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.stacked-samui.com/','["Monday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.534+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.534+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/stacked-burger-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/stacked-burger-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3435131590641164072',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('star-gym-fitness-center','standard','cmr07ihxd00taq8xdp6h0ibhe','Star Gym & Fitness Center','## Top Reviews
> "Good size gym with quality equipment. Gym has no AC but it is well ventilated. Staff is friendly and helpful. Towels and lockers are available if needed. One of the staff has a promotions item for me and the next time I visit this gym I will get it. 🎆"
> **- Carlton Edwards (5/5/5)**

> "I really enjoy coming to this gym. The staff are very kind and helpful. If you don’t know anything about the gym or how to use the equipment, they are always happy to explain and guide you.  All the equipment is clean and well maintained, and the gym environment feels comfortable and welcoming. It’s a great place for both beginners and people who already have experience.  I also like that the staff pay attention to members and are always ready to help when needed. This gym makes working out feel easy and enjoyable. I definitely recommend this place to anyone who wants to start their fitness journey."
> **- M Htoo (5/5/5)**

> "I highly recommend Star Gym. The staff are genuinely kind and friendly. They always try their best to give helpful advice and solve any issues promptly.  As a hotel employee, I receive complimentary gym access as part of my benefits, but the staff treat me just like any regular customer — with the same warmth and professionalism.  The gym is fully equipped with a wide variety of machines, and everything is sufficient even during busy hours. There are also plenty of cardio machines with different options to choose from.  Great atmosphere and great service. 👍"
> **- sarawut chuyjan (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/star-gym-fitness-center-1.jpg','095 263 0626','14, 102 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Koh Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.stargymkohsamui.com/','["Monday: 6:30 AM – 9:30 PM","Tuesday: 6:30 AM – 9:30 PM","Wednesday: 6:30 AM – 9:30 PM","Thursday: 6:30 AM – 9:30 PM","Friday: 6:30 AM – 9:30 PM","Saturday: 6:30 AM – 9:30 PM","Sunday: 6:30 AM – 9:30 PM"]','cmr07ifuo0015q8xdfahzrsp4','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.537+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.537+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/star-gym-fitness-center-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/star-gym-fitness-center-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2085480785439901441',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('stay-inn','standard','cmr07ihxf00tbq8xdd5se3riw','Stay Inn','## Top Reviews
> "We arrived at midnight and just wanted to go to sleep. We had to wait an hour because they claimed we hadn''t paid… after a long discussion, our payment was confirmed. The staff was very unfriendly, and if you enjoy ants, mold, and stains all over your bed, then this is the perfect place for you."
> **- Peter Richter (1/5/5)**

> "A simple small room hotel but at least there is a fridge but there are mosquitos in the room. However, the staff is quick to spray the room with repellent after informing them. Staff is friendly & helpful. There is no dedicated parking, you can park your bike on the sidewalk and your car on the public parking area. Good thing is their staff is stationed at the entrance so they can look after your bike. Location is slightly away from the shops you''ll frequent so expect a slight walk. However, it is just in front of the sea so you get a good view whenever you leave or return to the hotel."
> **- Jimmy Chan (4/5/5)**

> "The location in front of the sea is unique, the room smells really stinky, and no have hot water, just only one temperature. We must ask to change the towels every day, because they are very environmental friendly. The service is a bit curious to ask personal stuff. I recommend if someone just wanna save money and wanna search some place for breakfast, who loves freedom you are welcome!!!!!!"
> **- Jupjup (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/stay-inn-1.jpg','063 547 1562','328/19 Moo 3 Chonvitee, ตำบล อ่างทอง Koh samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.1,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.stayinnsamui.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ig1h003iq8xdb1g9nifo','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.539+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.539+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/stay-inn-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/stay-inn-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16464172142413903003',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('stop-sopa','standard','cmr07ihxh00tcq8xdr206hdvg','Stop @ Sopa','## Top Reviews
> "We are staying at the tango luxe hotel just down the road and came here for dinner last night. Lovely place, absolutely delicious food and friendly staff. Great prices too."
> **- Tyler Gascoigne (5/5/5)**

> "The waiter was so funny and silly. He made so many good jokes and was really knowledgeable about the menu. The menu is also super extensive. You can find food for everyone here."
> **- April VanKirk (4/5/5)**

> "Absolutely delicious Thai food, so much flavour. Dont know about the western dishes (who orders that here anyway..) but the Thai food is straightforward but top notch, extensive and exactly what you want. Went there twice and tried different things (even re-ordered the fried squid twice in the same meal because it was so tasty) and everything was really good and tasted local."
> **- Matthijs K (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/stop-sopa-1.jpg','085 055 5877','68/16 หมู่ 5 Tongsai Rd, Tambon Bo Put, อำเภอ บ่อผุด Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.stopsopasamui.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifv2001aq8xdag7cvjgf','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.541+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.541+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/stop-sopa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/stop-sopa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16547938798960426309',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('studio-7-chaweng','standard','cmr07ihxj00tdq8xdxas7qgup','Studio 7','## Top Reviews
> "Terrible experience. I came to this Studio 7 with my MacBook Air for a warranty repair and they simply refused to accept it, claiming that “it can’t be repaired because it was bought in Spain.” That is completely false.  At Studio 7 Lotus (Samui) they actually did their job, registered it in the official iCare system without any issues, and my Mac is now on its way to Bangkok for repair.  Here, they just didn’t want to work. They wasted my time, gave me incorrect information, and made the whole process unnecessarily difficult. Very bad experience. I absolutely do not recommend this store."
> **- carlos rovira (1/5/5)**

> "The place is neat and the employees are friendly but they have a weird policy that If you buy a phone from them you need to buy 2 accessories from them. That’s plain scam right there."
> **- Hamza Mo (Hamza) (1/5/5)**

> "During my trip in Thailand, I unfortunately broke my iPhone, prompting me to visit a nearby shop in search of a replacement. (the damage was irreparable :D). Checking their website beforehand, I discovered they didn''t have the specific model I wanted, the iPhone 15 Pro 256GB in stock at their location. Nevertheless, I decided to visit them, perhaps considering alternative options. When I arrived there, they were just unpacking new stock :), and to my luck, they had the exact model I wanted:) they also took the initiative to prepare tax refund documents for me, a gesture I appreciated, especially since it was done without my prompting, so far my experience with them was quite positive."
> **- Mariyan Atanasov (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/studio-7-chaweng-1.jpg','083 842 5516','เซ็นทรัลเพสติวัล, เลขที่ 209 หมู่ที่ 2 ห้อง 250 ชั้น 2, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,2.2,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.studio7thailand.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.543+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.543+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/studio-7-chaweng-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/studio-7-chaweng-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12965018871887714398',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('studio-7','standard','cmr07ihxm00teq8xdr0jqg3ha','Studio 7','## Top Reviews
> "Terrible experience. I came to this Studio 7 with my MacBook Air for a warranty repair and they simply refused to accept it, claiming that “it can’t be repaired because it was bought in Spain.” That is completely false.  At Studio 7 Lotus (Samui) they actually did their job, registered it in the official iCare system without any issues, and my Mac is now on its way to Bangkok for repair.  Here, they just didn’t want to work. They wasted my time, gave me incorrect information, and made the whole process unnecessarily difficult. Very bad experience. I absolutely do not recommend this store."
> **- carlos rovira (1/5/5)**

> "The place is neat and the employees are friendly but they have a weird policy that If you buy a phone from them you need to buy 2 accessories from them. That’s plain scam right there."
> **- Hamza Mo (Hamza) (1/5/5)**

> "During my trip in Thailand, I unfortunately broke my iPhone, prompting me to visit a nearby shop in search of a replacement. (the damage was irreparable :D). Checking their website beforehand, I discovered they didn''t have the specific model I wanted, the iPhone 15 Pro 256GB in stock at their location. Nevertheless, I decided to visit them, perhaps considering alternative options. When I arrived there, they were just unpacking new stock :), and to my luck, they had the exact model I wanted:) they also took the initiative to prepare tax refund documents for me, a gesture I appreciated, especially since it was done without my prompting, so far my experience with them was quite positive."
> **- Mariyan Atanasov (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/studio-7-1.jpg','083 842 5516','เซ็นทรัลเพสติวัล, เลขที่ 209 หมู่ที่ 2 ห้อง 250 ชั้น 2, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,2.2,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.studio7thailand.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.546+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.546+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/studio-7-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/studio-7-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12965018871887714398',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('success-gym','standard','cmr07ihxo00tfq8xdjb1x2uks','Success Gym','## Top Reviews
> "Heard great things about this gym but ultimately left it pretty disappointed. First off, I have been to many gyms in Asia whilst travelling/on holiday (I live in Bangkok) so have a lot to compare against.  Firstly, this gym is very well equipped and covers most areas. There is a very large room with resistance machines and free weights etc. There is also a new small room at the back that has some select machines and more dumbbells etc. I think that space is a bit more open and also for mat work etc. There is another space which is a bit more Hyrox focused with sleds, wall balls etc. Finally there is the main cardio area.  The gym covers most equipment you''d want but the layout is odd. There is a Hyrox style area, but as you can see people end up using the sled track as a mat/stretching area. Also, the Hyrox ergs (ski, row) are very far away in the cardio room. Yes they are cardio machines but realistically most people using a ski erg are using it for a hyrox workout.  My main issue with this gym is it clearly thinks highly of itself, there are strict rules such as no going topless (fine but maybe they should ensure the whole gym is air conned as it was incredibly hot in the Hyrox style area). The price is about 400 baht a day (when I went in April 25) which I think is expensive but that is fine if all equipment is highly maintaned. The cardio area contained many treadmills with belts thst skipped when you ran on them, to the point that they advised you dont go fast (this is dangerous) and the ski ergs were clearly not calibrated, along with the rowers.  Overall, it is well equipped but not worth its price tag depending on what youre looking for. For purely weight lifting/body building i think its probably one of the best."
> **- jamesshogg (3/5/5)**

> "I''ve been going to Sucses Gym for several years and until now I''ve designed my own training based on my own experience. A month ago, I decided to get professional coaching. My coach during this time was Owen, one of many coaches at Sucses Gym. I chose Owen because he occasionally corrected my form and pointed out training errors without charging me anything. Now, after seven training sessions, I can say that I chose a very good coach in Owen. He created new training programs for me that target exactly the muscle groups I wanted. He motivated me and also showed me my physical limits. He''s a motivated and friendly person whom I can highly recommend. Thank you for your support Owen."
> **- Carmelo Pesenti (5/5/5)**

> "Success Gym in Koh Samui is an excellent spot for anyone looking to keep up with their fitness routine while on holiday. The gym has a great selection of equipment that caters to all types of workouts, from weightlifting to cardio. Everything is well-maintained, and the layout makes it easy to find what you need. Plus, their day passes are very affordable, making it perfect for travelers who want to train without committing to a long-term membership.  One of the highlights is the attached Muscle Food Cafe, which offers a range of healthy, protein-packed meals and shakes—ideal for refueling after a workout.  I came across Barry Lustig’s review, which mentioned the gym being “hotter inside than out.” From my experience, this is a bit of an exaggeration. While it’s warm (understandably so, given Koh Samui’s climate), the gym is equipped with fans and has good airflow, making it comfortable to train in.  Success Gym in Koh Samui is a fantastic place to train—if you’re here to actually work out, that is! In Barry Lustig’s review he’s complaining about some supposed “bro culture” and couldn’t help but laugh. Barry, my friend, if you’re looking for a chat, may I suggest a beach bar or a local social club? Gyms aren’t usually where people go to socialize; most of us are there to break a sweat, not break into conversation.  That said, I did meet a few friendly folks who were up for a quick chat between sets, so it''s far from an unapproachable place. And as for the "
> **- Leanne (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/success-gym-1.jpg','065 402 0088','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://bit.ly/3yHotjY','["Monday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifuo0015q8xdfahzrsp4','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.548+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.548+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/success-gym-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/success-gym-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16716299833723835170',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sues-ocean-restaurant','standard','cmr07ihxq00tgq8xdytbkpjo4','Sue''s Ocean Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "The best fish I''ve had on Koh Samui. Fantastic drinks. Very friendly and helpful staff. Wonderful atmosphere. A fantastic place for dinner and pre-party drinks. I highly recommend it."
> **- Dariusz Witkowski (5/5/5)**

> "A wonderful on the beach restaurant, part of the Chaweng Gardens Beach Resort. The menu covers Thai and European foods and there is a cook to order seafood bar for grilled, fried or baked fish. I thoroughly enjoyed a steak whilst my lady enjoyed squid from the seafood bar. The staff were all very friendly and added to the friendly, relaxed atmosphere. Prices were very competitive."
> **- Tony Marsden (5/5/5)**

> "We made a pit stop here after a walk along the beach. We had a late lunch and drinks while looking out over the sea and enjoying the view beneath their amazing tree, with small birds and squirrels around us. A bit more expensive than the alternatives, but absolutely worth it. Great food and great drinks."
> **- Gozzi Bråten (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sues-ocean-restaurant-1.jpg','077 960 394','162 8, Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.chawenggarden.com/sues-ocean-restaurant.php','["Monday: 6:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 6:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 6:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 6:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 6:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 6:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 6:30 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.550+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.550+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sues-ocean-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sues-ocean-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15056902299864073967',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sun-lounge','standard','cmr07ihxs00thq8xdm4hljhg7','Sun Lounge','## Top Reviews
> "This place is amazing! Food was delicious, staff attentive and friendly! 🥰🫶🏼 Great music, lovely atmosphere! 😍 Highly recommend a visit!! Hubby had the pork belly and I had the ribeye with beef tallow fried rice 👌🏼 Definitely coming back 😍"
> **- Nat Tom (5/5/5)**

> "Sun Sea is a hotel, hostel and restaurant in one. It’s awesome. I came here for dinner at sunset for the very reason of the views and to watch the airplanes come into the airport nearby. This place is clean and a big area for people to dine and work if they need to. There are bean bag chair tables as well but they are first come first serve. There is great table seating to watch the water, sunset and planes. If you love this type of thing this place is amazing! We came a Friday night and there was live music too! The menu is quite large, offering salads, burgers, pizzas, pastas, fish and large pints (with a great cocktail menu too!) For 2 people with a few beers and 2 dinners it was approx $68 CAD. The view alone is worth this! I’d like to thank the staff who served us, they were so friendly and awesome. Thanks for making this an even more memorable experience!"
> **- Elle DeKay (5/5/5)**

> "A group of about 25 Koh Samui expats visited SeaSun for group breakfast. Phenomenal! The view of the seashore, sailboats and beaches was so beautiful and the breakfasts were absolutely amazing! The chicken and waffles was so delicious with a generous portion — the best I’ve had in many years. The pancakes were excellent — the chocolate brownies with ice cream was legendary. I honestly couldn’t believe how excellent this breakfast was! We’ll be going back often. Thank you Sea Sun for such a great breakfast experience!"
> **- Jamie Knapp (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sun-lounge-1.jpg','077 423 641','Koh Samui, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.facebook.com/seasunsamui','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.552+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.552+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sun-lounge-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sun-lounge-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10812436509168356940',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sundays-brasserie','standard','cmr07ihxu00tiq8xdysi4uuq0','Sunday''s Brasserie','## Top Reviews
> "Came here to chill on the beach and lay out on their sun lounger which are free to use with drink/food purchase. My friend and I chilled there for several hours drinking. Prices are a bit high but the place is nice and right on the beach. Happy hour we got 3 ice cold beers in an ice bucket for 250b. Staff were friendly and attentive.didnt try their food menu but maybe next visit. Recommended"
> **- SICILIAN-AMERICAN (4/5/5)**

> "Dined here most days while staying at the weekender. The service was exceptional. They make a mean cocktail, the food presentation is amazing and tastes good. Thank you Lak for your wonderful care and service!"
> **- Paul Exeter (4/5/5)**

> "We stumbled upon this beachside restaurant in Lamai Beach - best dining choice of our trip. Good variety of tradition Koh Samui Thai and a few western comforts too. I had the yellow snapper and pineapple curry and it was delicious. Highly recommend!"
> **- Daniel DeRosha (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sundays-brasserie-1.jpg','077 424 012','124/19, ถนน หาดละไม ตำบล มะเร็ต Koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.weekenderresort.com/contact','["Monday: 6:30 AM – 10:30 PM","Tuesday: 6:30 AM – 10:30 PM","Wednesday: 6:30 AM – 10:30 PM","Thursday: 6:30 AM – 10:30 PM","Friday: 6:30 AM – 10:30 PM","Saturday: 6:30 AM – 10:30 PM","Sunday: 6:30 AM – 10:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.554+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.554+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sundays-brasserie-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sundays-brasserie-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2961318550779343829',NULL,NULL);
