INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sunidaporna-accounting-business','standard','cmr07ihxy00tkq8xdipo5alzv','Sunidaporna Accounting & Business','## Top Reviews
> "I highly recommend Sunidaporna. It is one of a kind. I will always feel lucky and grateful to have found them to carry out my businesses so much they are rigorous, responsive and attentive. With them, all the paperwork comes seamlessly and crystal clear. Thank you.🙏"
> **- peter owler (5/5/5)**

> "Yui is an amazing accountant with vast years of experience. She is always on hand to answer your questions. 5 star rating 🙏"
> **- James (5/5/5)**

> "Highly recommend this nice team: friendly , available and very professional, Nothing to say ; thanks for your good services 🙏🙏"
> **- g fg (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sunidaporna-accounting-business-1.jpg','063 085 9888','54, 21, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://sp-accounting-business.com/','["Monday: 8:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifu0000zq8xdvll5tv7z','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.558+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.558+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sunidaporna-accounting-business-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sunidaporna-accounting-business-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14164724436673936247',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sunrise-bites','standard','cmr07ihy000tlq8xdubm2kjmv','Sunrise Bites','## Top Reviews
> "Lovely little traditional Thai restaurant! We chose Thai food, and it tasted absolutely delicious.  The restaurant is located in a calm part of the street with very little traffic, creating a relaxing atmosphere. The staff were smiling, welcoming, and very friendly, and the prices were reasonable as well.  The restaurant itself was clean and nicely maintained, with comfortable chairs and cushions that made the dining experience even better.  Highly recommended!"
> **- Torje Jæger (5/5/5)**

> "Good food reasonable price, friendly staff"
> **- dal dir channel (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing food the best mango sticky rice and chicken fried rice ive had in Thailand MUST TRY!  Super friendly staff"
> **- Aaron Gallo (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sunrise-bites-1.jpg','094 919 0316','FW4P+C7X, 287/3 Nara-Taling-Ngam Rd, Tambon Taling Ngam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.560+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.560+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sunrise-bites-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sunrise-bites-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8025438145466213760',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sunrise-studio','standard','cmr07ihy400tmq8xdhes2wgrl','Sunrise Studio','## Top Reviews
> "6 stars!!!  A Hidden Gem for Musicians in Samui  As members of Mohanik, our experience at this studio in Samui was truly exceptional. From the moment we arrived, we were welcomed with genuine care and professionalism by Liam and Chloe.  The studio itself is beautifully designed—elegant, well-equipped, and thoughtfully laid out for both creativity and technical precision. No need to think about anything else other than music at this beautiful Villa.  What made the experience truly special was the warmth and hospitality of the hosts. They weren’t just accommodating; they were passionate about music and dedicated to helping us bring our vision to life. Liam’s experience, insights and attention to detail elevated our work in ways we didn’t expect.  For any musician or band seeking a professional, serene, and inspiring space to create, this studio in Samui is a rare find. We can’t recommend it highly enough. •	Mohanik"
> **- Enerelt Otgonbaatar (5/5/5)**

> "Honestly, THE BEST RECORDING STUDIO i''ve ever been in my entire life ! Liam and his wife Chloé owners of the studio/residency are such kind human beings and so professional ! Working with Liam to produce and record new tracks is so smooth/productive and put you in the best conditions to creat and express yourself as much as possible ! He is a multi instrumentalist musician full of talent a passion !  For every level , i higly recommend Sunrise Studio, such a beautiful place that will make your dreams come true ! ❤️❤️❤️"
> **- EFEX official (5/5/5)**

> "What an amazingly experience! Liam, Chloe and the Sunrise team are professional and kind. We were able to create 5 awe inspiring songs in 5 days.  Liam is an extremely talented musician, producer, teacher and composer. The hospitality I received during my stay was exquisite and I enjoyed our time together outside of the studio also. Thanks for bringing my songs to life 🤘🌞💛"
> **- Chris Byrne (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sunrise-studio-1.jpg','092 387 0997','Maret, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.recording-studio-thailand.com/','["Monday: 9:30 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:30 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:30 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 9:30 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 9:30 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 9:30 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.564+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.564+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sunrise-studio-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sunrise-studio-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8345006505072496796',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sunset-beach-weddings','standard','cmr07ihy600tnq8xdej0decl8','Sunset Beach Weddings','## Top Reviews
> "We had a lovely stay at this hotel. The staff are truly amazing — a special thank you to Joy, who made sure we were well taken care of throughout our stay. Her kindness and attentiveness made a big difference.  The location is fantastic! It’s far from the hustle and bustle, which makes it perfect for a relaxing getaway. I would definitely recommend renting a scooter, as there are plenty of great local restaurants nearby (some even within walking distance).  The rooms are spacious and clean, which we really appreciated."
> **- Honorata Janas (5/5/5)**

> "A true haven of peace. The hotel may be a bit dated, but it is very well maintained and spotlessly clean. The staff are exceptional, with a rare level of kindness. Located in a quieter area, away from the hustle and bustle of tourist hotspots, it is the perfect place to relax and experience Thailand in a different way."
> **- Cédric T (5/5/5)**

> "Beautiful sunset views in a quaint family owned resort. Our first impression was very good, they called us after our flight landed to ensure we found the shuttle and asked if we wanted anything from the kitchen as it was closing we would arrive. The breakfast had made-to-order eggs, fresh fruit, cereal, espresso coffee/cappuccino, and a variety of bread & croissants. There’s a few restaurants within walking distance. There’s good snorkeling off the beach & there’s a break in the coral right in front of the resort to allow for deeper swimming. The price is excellent for what you are getting. The location is on the quiet side of the island about 1 hour drive from the airport, however most boat tours to neighboring islands will pick up at this resort. Definitely go on the Red Baron to view the national park and take a Koh Tao tour for snorkeling. The staff is very friendly & helpful. The laundry service was nice and inexpensive. We loved that they packed a breakfast for us when we had an early flight for our departure.  Upon arriving there was a note on our bed that said the resort was doing a “soft opening”, which meant the spa was closed and the restaurant had limited menu. The toilet in the room has a glass door that limited privacy. No bidet. The rooms are not sound proof. We could hear some noise from the neighbors and street, but it was still very quiet."
> **- KB Brietzke (they them) (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sunset-beach-weddings-1.jpg','098 830 9940','126/9 Nara-Taling-Ngam Rd, Tambon Taling Ngam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.thesunsetbeachresort.com/',NULL,'cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ift8000pq8xd7yujz20i','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.566+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.566+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sunset-beach-weddings-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sunset-beach-weddings-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17399510601757250973',NULL,NULL);
