INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('superpro-gym','standard','cmr07ihyb00tpq8xd9mjub8z1','Superpro Gym','## Top Reviews
> "We spent a month at Superpro Samui and loved every moment of it. It’s so much more than a gym — it’s a community. We feel incredibly lucky to have found this place. From day one everyone was so welcoming.  The trainers are fantastic, and every single person contributes to the experience — from the reception team to housekeeping, the locals who train there, the visitors from around the world, and of course the coaches themselves. You can feel the positive energy everywhere.  I honestly can’t recommend Superpro highly enough. We will definitely be back. A huge thank you to the entire team!"
> **- Brittany Holder (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing facilities with world class coaching! Highly recommend booking a month stay! Friendly, professional environment and super clean mats! Worth it to stay onsite, train (jiu jitsu for me) and get fit with hyrox and S&C! Can’t say enough good things about the coaches!!! They truly make the experience!"
> **- K Q (5/5/5)**

> "The MOST complete gym in Koh Samui.  After 10 weeks at SPS I''m sad to leave. Ill never need to look further in Southe East Asia for something better for me. I hope to return soon.  I''ll try to keep it short and explain why for any interested.  I sayed alone on the premise in a superior queens room. Also I included one month health package. 8 kilos lighter and 16 cm waist gone. I have a six pack again!  Made lots of friends with guests and staff and trainers.  Reading some criticisms I understand. First I also looked and expected more structure from organization and trainers. I felt a bit lost.  Then I realised..because so many people come and go. from all levels....some beginners and some pro fighters.. it''s impossible to create structure so there is a platform of options.  SPS has so much to offer for everybody and it is up to the guest, you, to take what you need.  Can''t even say Muay Thai is the main focus. The partnership with Royal Fight Club for BJJ and MMA is 100% and then there is even more. Hyrox, Yoga, Underwater, breathwork and fitness.  Check out the daily schedule its mind boggling.  I was able to easily do three different things/ hours of training per dag and so could you.  What Is will remember most is the feeling of being home. This is a great accomplishment by the owner because it''s so massive.  High quality facilities for each sport. Cleanliness a constans priority and good food.  But the main unique selling point.  ALL the trainers and staff are really happy to be there. They make you feel welcome and respected (almost +25 people in total!!!). They all do their daily work all effort and a smile. Some already longer as 14 years at SPS.  There are hundred if not thousands people each year coming... but if you want, you can get real personal attention and they give it.  SPS for me ahs been life changing and I hope for you to. Go for it and jump in!"
> **- Martin Ockels (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/superpro-gym-1.jpg','077 414 393','48, 10, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.superprosamui.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifuo0015q8xdfahzrsp4','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.571+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.571+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/superpro-gym-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/superpro-gym-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5492277249900460978',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('suvarn','standard','cmr07ihyd00tqq8xdo726lh8l','Suvarn','## Top Reviews
> "Suvarn is easily the best cocktail experience I’ve had in Samui.  From the moment you walk in, the place feels beautifully elegant and refined, with an atmosphere that makes the whole evening feel a bit special. It’s stylish without being pretentious, and the setting really adds to the experience.  The staff are quick and professional, and the cocktails are honestly pure fantasy. The presentation, the balance of flavors, and the creativity behind each drink are on another level. You can really tell a lot of thought and skill goes into every glass.  What surprised me most is that the prices are more than reasonable considering the quality of the drinks and the fact that you’re in Southern Thailand at such a high level cocktail bar.  If you love great cocktails, this is a must visit spot in Koh Samui."
> **- Bruno Lončar (5/5/5)**

> "Cool vibe n music on the background is just perfect not too loud like other places in the area,great variety of good stuffs to choose. Delicious cocktail. Really enjoy it here. Will visit again next time when we r at Samui again."
> **- Nooty Noot (5/5/5)**

> "Absolutely worthy of 5 stars! We live in NYC and frequent cocktail bars as a hobby, and this spot in Koh Samui absolutely blew us away. The service was incredible - warm, attentive, and clearly passionate about what they do - but the cocktails were even better. The mixologist is truly a master of his craft.  We especially loved The Hidden Gem, and really appreciated how each signature cocktail was inspired by different areas of Koh Samui and featured unique Thai spirits. The attention to detail and creativity were unmatched.  The bar itself is beautifully designed and feels both luxurious and inviting — the perfect place to spend an evening in Koh Samui. A must-visit for any cocktail lover"
> **- Liz (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/suvarn-1.jpg','077 960 394','Chaweng Garden beach Resort 162 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.suvarnbars.com/','["Monday: 6:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Tuesday: 6:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Wednesday: 6:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Thursday: 6:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Friday: 6:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Saturday: 6:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Sunday: 6:00 PM – 1:00 AM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.573+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.573+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/suvarn-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/suvarn-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3975082078869744108',NULL,NULL);
