> **- Ankit Garani (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sweedish-delight-1.jpg','081 648 7661','142, 100, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.sweedishdelight.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 12:30 AM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 12:30 AM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 12:30 AM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 12:30 AM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 12:30 AM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 12:30 AM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 12:30 AM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.582+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.582+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sweedish-delight-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sweedish-delight-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14768887922970921561',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sweet-and-salty','standard','cmr07ihyp00tvq8xdttpoxfog','Sweet And Salty','## Top Reviews
> "Lovely spot serving delicious food, as well as delicious healthy options. The dishes are nicely prepared, fresh and well executed, and in good portion. Wonderful smoothie and enjoyable coffee. Pricing is slightly above average but the quality is great. Despite the busy busy atmosphere, staff were accommodating and polite.  The cozy, laidback establishment offers both airconditioned indoor and outdoor areas - great for socials and peaceful atmosphere for working. I especially like the outdoor area that overlooks the greenery and large fields beyond."
> **- Wunda Stone (5/5/5)**

> "The food and drinks are excellent, we enjoyed it so much we came back every morning during our vacation! The staff is attentive and kind, and the atmosphere is great. Highly reccomended! Especially enjoyed the lime basil tart and the hash browns."
> **- Levana Muskal (5/5/5)**

> "Overall, a well-run café with solid quality — but not one we’d go out of the way for, given the many options around Koh Samui.  - We dropped by during a slightly busy hour, but the staff were kind enough to slot us in with a time cap, which was appreciated - The raf coffee was excellent — rich, creamy, and one of the more reliable Russian-style coffees we’ve had across cafés - We also tried a watermelon juice (nice, refreshing) and the orange espresso, which had a bold, pulpy orange base that complemented the coffee well — raw, sharp, and quite enjoyable  - For food, we ordered the Draniki (Russian potato pancakes), which came as two thick stacks with veggies and salmon — the pancakes were hearty, but the salmon tasted a bit too strong or gamey for our liking - That said, it might just be the traditional prep — different from the smoked salmon we’re used to in places like Dubai, Singapore, or Switzerland - The big breakfast plate was a variation on the same theme — with eggs, bread, and the same pancakes; the scrambled eggs were fine, bread was unremarkable  ✅ Overall, we appreciated the effort and authenticity, but it didn’t fully land for our taste — probably more suited to those familiar with or craving Eastern European flavours"
> **- V A (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sweet-and-salty-1.jpg','091 043 0007','H284+7PM, 4169 18/63, ตำบล แม่น้ำ อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://sweetandsalty.clipshot.cc/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.585+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.585+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sweet-and-salty-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sweet-and-salty-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5901628765517689346',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('sweet-sisters-cafe','standard','cmr07ihyr00twq8xdq9325guk','Sweet Sisters Cafe','## Top Reviews
> "Oh my god! Such a lovely place! We went there for a brunch with a family. The atmosphere is just amazing 🤩 they have such special vibe! 3in 1 Green private yard, health shop, local pottery and clothes shop, and the restaurant. And the food is fresh and delicious, full of colourful spices. A mixture of India and Thailand. We loved it! Especially the cakes :)) Definitely worth the ride!"
> **- kiddie garden (5/5/5)**

> "I first time tried this place and I have to say—I was truly impressed! Every dish was delicious, perfectly seasoned, and made with fresh ingredients. The presentation was beautiful, and the atmosphere felt warm and welcoming. The staff were friendly and attentive, which made the dining experience even better.  The price is absolutely worth the quality. This place has definitely become one of my new favorites. If you’re looking for great food, I highly recommend giving it a try—you won’t be disappointed! 😍"
> **- Mint Ratchanan (5/5/5)**

> "Incredible! Somewhere nowhere we have found such an awesome place with cozy ambiance and delicious food! Banana cake was amazing!!! Very recommend to stop for a brunch! 👍"
> **- Natali Kilic (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sweet-sisters-cafe-1.jpg','065 953 8832','4170, Tambon Na Mueang, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig4i004oq8xdv207xuh2','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.587+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.587+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sweet-sisters-cafe-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/sweet-sisters-cafe-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10879957712243165068',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('synergy-samui','standard','cmr07ihyu00txq8xdyyiamtst','Synergy Samui','## Top Reviews
> "We stopped by to spend some time on the beach and enjoy a couple of drinks, and it turned out to be a great experience. Amazing place with a beautiful view, good service, and very attentive staff.  A big plus is that when you order drinks, you can use the sunbeds without any extra charge, which makes the whole experience even more enjoyable."
> **- Nadiya Bondarenko (5/5/5)**

> "Wow, a hotel of a very high standard. I absolutely loved everything — everything was beautifully designed and thoughtfully done. The pool is clean, the beach is just a short walk away, and there’s a private, comfortable gym with several machines. The breakfast is rich and varied. All the hotel staff are friendly and always smiling. The staff members Sira, Jimmy, and Bhon were wonderful. It was a lovely stay, and I will definitely come back again! Highly recommended."
> **- ירדן אדמסו (5/5/5)**

> "We are staying in Paradise here in Senergy Koh Samui. The rooms are little houses with huge comfortable beds, mini fridge, coffee tea facilities. The bathroom with a very big bath and walk-in shower has plenty of hot water plus lovely soft towels. All spotlessly clean. The breakfast has an egg station always a winner for us plus fruit yoghurt breads and so much more .. delicious. The 2 pools overlook the beach which has beautiful soft sands and warm clear sea…. Once you walk out onto the hustle and bustle of main road where shops restaurants money exchangers tour touts all vie for your attention . It’s a fun place but with calmness within the hotel ."
> **- Lindsay Lambert (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/synergy-samui-1.jpg','077 300 438','155 3 ตำบล บ่อผุด Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.synergysamui.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.590+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.590+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/synergy-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/synergy-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=746861598673043550',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('tabula-rasa','standard','cmr07ihyy00tyq8xdnj8tk814','Tabula Rasa','## Top Reviews
> "The restaurant is beautifully decorated with a pleasant atmosphere. The food is delicious and well worth the price. The staff provide excellent service and are very attentive. The location is also very convenient and easy to access. Overall, it is great value for money and highly recommended."
> **- Benya Na (5/5/5)**

> "Absolutely great restaurant, delicious food for very good price in my perspective. Friendly, but experienced staff. Very good choice of wine as well for reasonable prices. Strongly recommanded! 🙂 We had wagyu rib-eye and fish. Both were awesome."
> **- Jan Kolarcik (5/5/5)**

> "HIGHLY RECOMMEND!! This was one of my favorite places to eat at in Koh Samui.  Upon arrival we were greeted with cooling towels, bread appetizer and little welcome shots. The staff was amazing and the manager was going around checking all the tables.  Our food came out so fast as well! And it was busy so I know the kitchen was definitely working hard at serving everyone!  Food was so yummy and everyone loved it. Our cocktails were gorgeous too:) we were given another set of cooking towels after finishing up dinner!  The song vibes and atmosphere was so good and made us feel secluded off of the streets. If you’re thinking about coming you won’t regret it! Pricing was very affordable too!"
> **- adalyn currie (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tabula-rasa-1.jpg','081 156 5672','G3J7+PFR, Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://tabula-rasa-samui.com/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 2:00 AM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.594+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.594+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tabula-rasa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tabula-rasa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9216081152754723376',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('take-a-chef','standard','cmr07ihz000tzq8xdj7pj042c','Take A Chef','## Top Reviews
> "Thank you so much to Chef Dara and her team for an amazing New Year''s Eve dinner in Koh Samui! They came to our rental villa and prepared a private dining experience that was lovely and incredibly delicious. Both the presentation and flavors of the meal were top notch. The service was friendly and professional. They took care of everything from start to finish. We highly recommend Siri Dara Samui Chef for an excellent dining experience in Koh Samui."
> **- Ariya Lapan (5/5/5)**

> "Chef Dara exceeded all of our expectations. Every single dish was presented so beautifully and tasted amazing. Our best meal in Thailand!! She and her team were also so friendly and she explained each of her dishes so well. Would definitely recommend and well worth the money!"
> **- Sandy (5/5/5)**

> "Our cooking class with Dara at Siri Dara Chef’s Table was an absolute highlight of our trip to Koh Samui! From start to finish, the experience was immersive, educational, and so much fun. Dara is not only an incredibly skilled chef but also a warm and engaging host who made us feel right at home in her beautiful kitchen.  We learned to cook authentic Thai dishes using fresh, local ingredients, and Dara guided us through every step with patience and expertise. She shared so many valuable cooking tips, cultural insights, and personal stories that made the experience even more special. The best part? Enjoying our delicious creations in a cozy, intimate setting!  If you’re looking for a hands-on, unforgettable culinary experience in Koh Samui, this is the class to take. Whether you’re a beginner or a seasoned cook, Dara will make sure you leave with new skills, amazing memories, and a happy (and very full) stomach. Highly recommend!"
> **- Donna Buonanno (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/take-a-chef-1.jpg','094 517 8916','28, 143 Moo1 Soi Maenam 1, Tambon Mae Nam, Koh Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://instagram.com/siridarasamui?igshid=YmMyMTA2M2Y=',NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.596+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.596+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/take-a-chef-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/take-a-chef-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17451415552122429697',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('tamarind-springs-forest-spa','standard','cmr07ihz200u0q8xd5z8qojkd','Tamarind Springs Forest Spa','## Top Reviews
> "Extremely friendly and welcoming staff — truly some of the nicest people. I loved every part of the premises; it’s beautiful, peaceful, and very well designed in nature. The massage itself was very good and relaxing.  We booked a couple’s massage and also experienced the caves, natural spring areas, and body scrub treatments, which made the whole experience feel very complete and unique.  The only area I feel could be improved is hygiene standards in certain parts of the facility, which would make the experience perfect.  Overall, a wonderful experience and I would still recommend it for anyone looking for a relaxing spa day in nature."
> **- Ghada Mallah (4/5/5)**

> "We visited Tamarind Springs Samui as a wedding gift from our friends and chose the “Stoned on Samui” package — and it was absolutely worth it.  From start to finish, the experience was incredibly relaxing and thoughtfully curated. We really appreciated the no-phone policy, which allowed us to fully disconnect and enjoy the peaceful surroundings. It made the whole spa day feel even more special and immersive.  The treatments were amazing, and everything was beautifully set in nature. One thing to keep in mind is that there’s quite a bit of walking and stairs involved, so you do need to be reasonably fit. But honestly, it just adds to the charm of the place.  We loved every moment and would highly recommend it for a special occasion or a proper treat!"
> **- Zaza Meerveld (5/5/5)**

> "We had an absolutely wonderful experience at Tamarind Springs. We spent a beautiful afternoon immersed in nature, following a peaceful path through the forest that truly felt magical. The entire setting is unique, serene, and incredibly well integrated into the natural surroundings.  The spa itself is simply amazing and unlike anything we had ever seen before. The sauna carved directly into the rocks is something truly special – a one-of-a-kind experience that you won’t easily find elsewhere. It feels authentic, original, and perfectly in harmony with the forest. Without a doubt, the experience is worth every penny and absolutely justifies the price.  The massage was exceptional: deeply relaxing, professional, and perfectly executed. On top of that, all the staff were incredibly kind, welcoming, and attentive in every aspect, making us feel comfortable and well taken care of from start to finish.  This is not just a spa, but a complete experience in nature. Highly recommended for anyone looking for something unique, relaxing, and truly memorable.  Renato"
> **- Renato Rottmann (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tamarind-springs-forest-spa-1.jpg','085 926 4626','265, 1, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.tamarindsprings.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.598+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.598+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tamarind-springs-forest-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tamarind-springs-forest-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=363410939101283574',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('tamarind-springs-home-stay','standard','cmr07ihz400u1q8xd736ebv71','Tamarind Springs Home Stay','## Top Reviews
