> **- Ghada Mallah (4/5/5)**

> "We visited Tamarind Springs Samui as a wedding gift from our friends and chose the “Stoned on Samui” package — and it was absolutely worth it.  From start to finish, the experience was incredibly relaxing and thoughtfully curated. We really appreciated the no-phone policy, which allowed us to fully disconnect and enjoy the peaceful surroundings. It made the whole spa day feel even more special and immersive.  The treatments were amazing, and everything was beautifully set in nature. One thing to keep in mind is that there’s quite a bit of walking and stairs involved, so you do need to be reasonably fit. But honestly, it just adds to the charm of the place.  We loved every moment and would highly recommend it for a special occasion or a proper treat!"
