> "We had an absolutely wonderful experience at Tamarind Springs. We spent a beautiful afternoon immersed in nature, following a peaceful path through the forest that truly felt magical. The entire setting is unique, serene, and incredibly well integrated into the natural surroundings.  The spa itself is simply amazing and unlike anything we had ever seen before. The sauna carved directly into the rocks is something truly special – a one-of-a-kind experience that you won’t easily find elsewhere. It feels authentic, original, and perfectly in harmony with the forest. Without a doubt, the experience is worth every penny and absolutely justifies the price.  The massage was exceptional: deeply relaxing, professional, and perfectly executed. On top of that, all the staff were incredibly kind, welcoming, and attentive in every aspect, making us feel comfortable and well taken care of from start to finish.  This is not just a spa, but a complete experience in nature. Highly recommended for anyone looking for something unique, relaxing, and truly memorable.  Renato"
> **- Renato Rottmann (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tamarind-springs-home-stay-1.jpg','085 926 4626','265, 1, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.tamarindsprings.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.600+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.600+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tamarind-springs-home-stay-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tamarind-springs-home-stay-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=363410939101283574',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('tan-marina-bay-resort','standard','cmr07ihz700u2q8xdsdgc138k','Tan Marina Bay Resort','## Top Reviews
> "We stopped at a restaurant for lunch. The owner of the restaurant is very arrogant. She told us that we can only order simple dishes and only at 11 am. Later they will not serve us anymore because they have groups booked. Some of the portions were very small. If you are looking for lunch, go somewhere else. You are not welcome here."
> **- Thajsko Kambodza (1/5/5)**

> "We stopped here on our boat trip and there isn’t much good to say. The lady who runs the restaurant was so rude from the moment we arrived but the worst part was that they scammed us on lunch. 9 of us sat down for lunch and they charged us 9300 baht. When I asked to see the bill they tried to refuse to show me and when I insisted they had charged us double for each item we ordered!! Stay away!!"
> **- Chris Peel (1/5/5)**

> "We had a wonderful lunch here as part of our boat tour. The resort is no longer operating but the restaurant is and the food is amazing. $7AUD for a pad Thai with fresh seafood and a beer. Cool island experience too"
> **- Nick Black (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tan-marina-bay-resort-1.jpg','087 046 5744','99 M.2 T.Taling Ngam, Koh Samui, เทศบาลนครเกาะสมุย Koh Samui, Thailand 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.1,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifyr002lq8xdu4o1j1f1','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.603+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.603+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tan-marina-bay-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tan-marina-bay-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12523425106148786761',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('tanchote-house','standard','cmr07ihz900u3q8xdgckjhlwq','Tanchote House','## Top Reviews
> "I am extremely disappointed with this establishment. Despite having a direct path to a public beach, the management refuses to let anyone use it. In an area where public access points are non-existent, this feels like an intentional attempt to "
> **- Neon S. (2/5/5)**

> "The location of place ''LaOr Tanchote Samui House'' is quite charming. The hostess of this small lakeside complex is a wonderful woman, Or, who is ready to help you whenever you need help. Although the price is low, the lodges are clean and cosy, air-conditioning and a fan are working.  The place is on the one hand quiet and peaceful and on the other hand it is not very far from the main road. The beach is a 10-minute walk away, and a 2-3-minute walk to the fresh fruit stand and the Family Mart 24-hour shop.  Tanchote lodges are home to relaxed and friendly visitors from different countries, who are often ''house buddies''.  Despite the water problem on the island, Or''s tap water is clean enough, and for cooking and drinking we used the water stand nearby, where we can fill 10 litres of clean drinking water for 10 baht.  For a cheaper and better taxi service, you can ask Poo (the car, in contrast to Thailand''s typical unpunctuality, arrives in advance).  My heartfelt thanks to Or for the hospitality provided and hopefully this review will help you choose a quality place to live on the paradise island of Samui.  Address: Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani, Tanchote Samui House (nearby the Clever Kids Development Centre)."
> **- Samui Guitar Lessons (5/5/5)**

> "Cheap clean affordable place to stay."
> **- Paul May (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tanchote-house-1.jpg','081 747 7877','H286+HW5, Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 6:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.605+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.605+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tanchote-house-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tanchote-house-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13928860325821832746',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('tandoori-nights','standard','cmr07ihzc00u4q8xdvmbz2m8t','Tandoori Nights','## Top Reviews
> "Great Indian food at Koh Samui’s Lamai. Service rendered by there team - Rajan & Goli was great. We ordered Dal Tadka, Paneer Tikka Masala and Channa Masala. All were good. And their roti was aata roti. Both the staff members were extremely warm and courteous. If you desire Indian, this place is recommended ."
> **- Nitin Lall (5/5/5)**

> "Initially, we ordered takeaway and were blown away by how fresh and delicious the food was, so we decided to dine at the restaurant a few nights later. WOW! We’ve travelled all over Southeast Asia and tried countless Indian restaurants, but this one tops them all.  The food was incredibly fresh — the tandoori chicken and prawns came straight off the grill, sizzling hot and packed with flavour. The sauces were fragrant, rich, and tasted beautifully homemade. Every dish we tried was absolutely delicious.  The service was fast, attentive, and genuinely welcoming. They even treated us to a complimentary dessert at the end, which was a lovely touch.  No matter where you’re staying in Samui, it’s worth making the trip here. You won’t be disappointed."
> **- Arni Lochner (5/5/5)**

> "The best Indian food I had since ages, their Chicken Tikka Masala is absolutely perfect. 🤤 And the naan also tasted really delicious.  Went there for dinner on each day while spending my Holidays on Koh Samui.  The Employees were really nice and welcoming as well.  I will definitely be back the next time I''ll go to Lamai. ☺️👍"
> **- Andre (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tandoori-nights-1.jpg','099 901 1408','หมู่ที่ 3, 130/1 Thanon Had Lamai, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://tandoorinights.ewaiterqr.com/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.608+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.608+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tandoori-nights-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tandoori-nights-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11909787201894255851',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('tandoori-palace','standard','cmr07ihze00u5q8xdw20kl6qe','Tandoori Palace','## Top Reviews
> "Without a doubt THE BEST Indian restaurant you can find in all of Thailand!! We came back twice because it was that good. The onion bhajis are incredible, the crispiness and the flavour is so good!! Then the butter chicken… I’ve never had a butter chicken that tastes so beautiful, every mouthful the flavour got better, what a dish! Massive thank you to Rocky, a great restaurant, fantastic food and wonderful staff, would highly highly recommend!!"
> **- Hollie Anderson (5/5/5)**

> "I had the nicest Indian food in Koh Samui here! I got the butter chicken and fish pakora and they were both delicious, fresh and well seasoned. Prices were really good too. Overall I recommend this to anyone who wants nice and afforable Indian food"
> **- Mohib Shams (5/5/5)**

> "Our family of 5 quite enjoyed our dinner at this place. The tikka masala chicken and lamb were great and they do ask how spicy you want it; the madras chicken was good & I loved my lamb korma - yum! We also ordered cheese naan & lamb naan & lamb pakoras - with raita, these were delicious. Fries were decent size. My GnT was make-it-yourself, but that allowed me to combine how I wanted it. They also have a selection of beer & cocktails. Basically, we cleaned the table - everything went and it was delicious! Recommend this place this side of the island - a good alternative if you love spicy but want something different. Tysm!"
> **- Ilona Nurmela (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tandoori-palace-1.jpg','099 327 1727','17 49, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 12:30 – 10:30 PM","Tuesday: 12:30 – 10:30 PM","Wednesday: 12:30 – 10:30 PM","Thursday: 12:30 – 10:30 PM","Friday: 12:30 – 10:30 PM","Saturday: 12:30 – 10:30 PM","Sunday: 5:30 – 10:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.610+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.610+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tandoori-palace-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tandoori-palace-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12685925329598437699',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('tango-luxe-beach-villa','standard','cmr07ihzg00u6q8xde3o6uzs4','Tango Luxe Beach Villa','## Top Reviews
> "The rooms are well appointed  and true of descriptions on line. The location is quiet as it’s down a lane way. The rooms are private with leafy surrounds and walkway to the main pool and bar and  restaurant area. Turn down service was a nice surprise upon returning to room after dinner. The plunge pool is very refreshing at end of the day and it’s nice to return and chill out. If you want an outside couch upgrade from the base villa. We arranged transfer from airport via accommodation was efficient and air conditioning was lovely and driver friendly face on the crowd at airport. Highly recommend for a chill out so give it a crack"
> **- Haidee Fullard (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing stay with a truly unique tropical atmosphere. The staff were incredibly kind and welcoming, which made our stay even more special. The villas are slightly older but beautifully fit the tropical style and have a lot of charm.  The in-villa breakfast was excellent (highly recommend the chia pudding!), and both the private villa pool and the main pool with a view are stunning.  There is no beach directly at the hotel and it’s a bit remote, so renting a scooter is useful. The restaurant is more expensive, but food delivery works well and there is a 7-Eleven just a 5-minute walk away.  Overall, a very positive experience and a place we would happily return to."
> **- Nikola Neterderová (5/5/5)**

> "Can’t stop thinking about this place! It was calm , cozy , rustic and luxurious at the same time . The rooms and patios  are spacious and beautiful and the plunge pools are good size too. The staff are super friendly and welcoming. The oceanfront restaurant has a great ambience too. We had relaxing time here."
> **- Ahona Mutsuddi (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tango-luxe-beach-villa-1.jpg','086 944 3838','79, beach, 100 Plai leam, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.tangoluxe.com/','["Monday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifv2001aq8xdag7cvjgf','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.612+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.612+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tango-luxe-beach-villa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tango-luxe-beach-villa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6723723001724637504',NULL,NULL);
