> **- Ahona Mutsuddi (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tango-wedding-1.jpg','086 944 3838','79, beach, 100 Plai leam, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.tangoluxe.com/','["Monday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 6:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifv2001aq8xdag7cvjgf','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.617+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.617+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tango-wedding-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tango-wedding-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6723723001724637504',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('tara-bistro','standard','cmr07ihzn00u8q8xdebs0gf60','Tara Bistro','## Top Reviews
> "Absolutely and amazing and quite place to enjoy your dinner. Most vegetables are organic from their own garden. Huge portion of food, tasty and well prepared. Staff really friendly and the atmosphere is like a family."
> **- M. L. STARK (5/5/5)**

> "Tara Bistro is a real little gem on Koh Samui. The atmosphere is relaxed and welcoming – the kind of place where you immediately feel like you’re exactly where you’re supposed to be.  The prawns were absolutely delicious: fresh, juicy, and full of flavor without any unnecessary fuss. You can really taste the quality. It’s simple food done exactly right – which, in my opinion, is much harder to find than fancy dishes. The rest of the menu also looked amazing, but honestly… after those prawns, it was hard to think about anything else!  The service was friendly and professional, with just the right balance between being attentive and giving you space to enjoy your evening. I had a great time and will definitely be coming back. If you’re looking for a place to enjoy great seafood in a relaxed setting, Tara Bistro should be high on your list.  And a little tip: order the prawns. Trust me – your future self will thank you!"
> **- Batty On Tour (5/5/5)**

> "Beautiful location in the hills. The grounds are quiet and peaceful. Great spot to have a lunch and cocktail."
> **- Timothy Murtland (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tara-bistro-1.jpg','098 822 9566','FX8P+69, Na Mueang, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.tarabistrosamui.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 8:30 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 8:30 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 8:30 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 8:30 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 8:30 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 8:30 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 8:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig4i004oq8xdv207xuh2','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.619+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.619+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tara-bistro-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tara-bistro-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13234099709279400223',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('tarnim-magic-garden','standard','cmr07ihzq00u9q8xdp0sicmyi','Tarnim Magic Garden','## Top Reviews
> "Such a hidden gem! Visiting this garden was a lovely experience and something unique compared to other sights. It’s quiet, traditional, and very beautiful. I highly recommend it!"
> **- Veronika Harbichova (5/5/5)**

> "It''s nice manmade garden incorporated in the beautiful jungle spot. It''s beautiful, calm place but it''s not very big so it can be overviewed over half an hour. Having in mind the road up the hill and later downhill I am not still sure whether it was worth the time. The entrance 100 TBH per person."
> **- Vilma G. (4/5/5)**

> "Amazing little garden nestled in the mountains! Apparently it was built in 1976 by a single man. It is also connected to a 100 acre farm - though there is no access to it we could find. The man passed away in 1990, and his grandkids have since opened it to the public. Beautiful statues hiding everywhere the eye could see. The moss and overgrowth gives the place an ethereal feel - as though nature is reclaiming it''s own territory but can''t help appreciating the scenery. Small souvenir and snacks/drinks shop nearby. There is a ticket cost of 100 baht, but I can only assume it was included in our day trip cost as we didn''t pay a dime. We also highly  suggest going there as part of a day trip to begin with - seeing as it''s quite remote and going there specifically can easily end up being a logistical, financial nightmare. Highly recommended!"
> **- evy playz (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tarnim-magic-garden-1.jpg',NULL,'FXMV+5Q9, Na Mueang, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ig4i004oq8xdv207xuh2','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.622+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.622+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tarnim-magic-garden-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tarnim-magic-garden-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4274554202448473969',NULL,NULL);
