INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('tembo-beach-club-resort','standard','cmr07ihzw00ubq8xd5lc0fsni','Tembo Beach Club & Resort','## Top Reviews
> "In my opinion, this is the best beach club in the area - clean, great service, and a really good selection of drinks and food. You only pay 500 THB per person if you want a sunbed, which is honestly a great deal (it’s just a minimum spend). The beach and surroundings are beautiful too.  There are so many beach clubs nearby that we wanted to check out, but we ended up leaving most of them because of crazy minimum spends or because they were overcrowded. That has never happened here, and we’ve been coming regularly since November 2024.  Highly recommended, thank you 🤍"
> **- Alexandra Muhlova (5/5/5)**

> "⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ Tembo Beach Club and Resort is an absolute gem.  The vibe is boutique, stylish, and aesthetically beautiful—everything feels thoughtfully designed, spotlessly clean, and it even smells incredible the moment you walk in. It genuinely feels like excellent value for money for the experience you get and perfectly located overlooking the beach.  The staff truly make this place special. Everyone was incredibly friendly and welcoming, but James stood out in particular—he was hardworking, attentive, and took such great care of us while always being warm and friendly. Nong was also amazing and so kind, which made our stay feel extra personal and memorable.  The food and drinks were fantastic, with breakfast being a real highlight—delicious, fresh, and something we genuinely looked forward to each morning.  I would absolutely stay here again and highly recommend Tembo Beach Club and Resort to anyone looking for a stylish, relaxing, and well-run beach stay."
> **- Abbie Hutchinson (5/5/5)**

> "Our family stayed here last year, and on their recommendation, we joined them again this year and we weren’t disappointed.  Everything about Tembo exceeded our expectations. The service was excellent, and everyone was so welcoming. James, in particular, stood out, he was attentive, friendly, and made sure we had everything we needed.  The food is also a highlight, especially the French toast, which is the best we’ve ever had. It became a must-have every morning for us.  Tembo is a beautiful place to stay, and we will definitely be returning."
> **- ava b (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tembo-beach-club-resort-1.jpg','081 161 8828','23/2, Bangrak Beach, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.tembo-samui.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.628+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.628+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tembo-beach-club-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tembo-beach-club-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10492722920538455560',NULL,NULL);
