INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('terra-socialite','standard','cmr07ii0000udq8xdszaqt8cs','Terra Socialite','## Top Reviews
> "Wow!  What an incredible board from Terra Socialite!  We wanted a lazy evening by the pool, and some meat, cheese and fruit, and thought we''d try the platter!  It was incredible with the variety of fresh fruit, veggies, meats, cheese, dried fruits, nuts, and homemade marmalade!  Definitely a fan favorite for our fam!  Thank you for the fabulous food.  We highly recommend them for functions and home dinners!!!"
> **- Jessica Loots (5/5/5)**

> "Absolutely stunning fruit platter – beautifully arranged, fresh, and delicious! Every detail was perfect, from the vibrant colors to the tropical flavors. A true feast for the eyes and the taste buds. Highly recommend for any special occasion!"
> **- Avital Kaufman (5/5/5)**

> "We hired this team for a dinner event with less then 24 hours notice and they came and severed a multi course dinner that was amazing, highly professional and reliable I would highly reccomend 🙏"
> **- Jesse 11:11 (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/terra-socialite-1.jpg','082 531 3188','126, T, 56 Lamai , Ban Lamai, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.terrasocialite.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.632+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.632+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/terra-socialite-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/terra-socialite-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14242303836150695024',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('thai-fight-hotel','standard','cmr07ii0200ueq8xdysgdzv2x','Thai Fight Hotel','## Top Reviews
> "We were honestly a bit hesitant because of some mixed reviews, but decided to book this hotel anyway and we’re glad we did. We are both pretty critical, but this place genuinely surprised us. From the moment we arrived, we got such a warm welcome. Everyone working there is just incredibly kind, friendly, and genuinely welcoming: you feel it right away!  The room was beautiful as well. The Thai boxing theme runs throughout the whole hotel, which makes it a bit different in a really cool way, but still done with great taste and quality.  The location is great, the hotel itself is stunning, and the pool for us was great as well (with a nice view on the ocean). What stood out to us was how clean everything is: the public areas seem to be cleaned multiple times a day, and our room was spotless every single day. And also important: it was super quiet, no noise at all.  We’re not easily impressed, but we would 100% recommend this hotel to friends and family. Thanks for such a great stay. We’ll definitely be back!"
> **- Julie Pennings (5/5/5)**

> "I had a really great stay at this hotel! The breakfast was amazing with lots of options, and everything was fresh and delicious. Especially pancakes and egg section.🥐🍉  The staff were incredibly friendly and helpful.. always smiling and ready to assist with anything, which made the whole experience even better.🥹  The rooms were spotless, very comfortable, and had beautiful views. Waking up to that ocean view was honestly one of the highlights of the stay.🌅  The sea wasn’t the cleanest, it didn’t really bother me because the pool was huge, very clean, and more than enough for a great swim.🤗  Another fun part of the stay was the free Muay Thai and stretching classes🥊such a cool experience! If you want, you can also book extra classes for a fee, including things like a cooking class, which is a great idea if you want to try something different.🤪  The cocktails in happy hour were great too, perfect for relaxing after a long day.🍹  Overall, this is definitely a great value-for-money hotel, and I would happily recommend to anyone who comes to Samui!!!!🥰"
> **- Ece Mira Albayrak (5/5/5)**

> "Not only the hotel was conformed to all pf our expectations but went beyond. The staff is very attentive and helpful. The reviews about the staff not speaking English are just not true. Every single person we interacted with spoke English.  The room was clean and comfortable, only negative point to me is the double duvet instead of one for two. I know it’s a German thing but I didn’t particularly like sleeping with 2 duvets.  The breakfast was good and could satisfy every taste.  The pool and the access to the beach were really lovely. Only negative point is the beach not being the cleanest… but we could see the staff were cleaning it every day.. but with the sea there’s not much that can be done.. I think it’s more of a national issue than a Thai fight hotel issue.  The Muay thai class was really instructive and fun.  And the spa was impeccable, nothing to complain about. Very relaxing and competent staff.  Overall it was a very good stay, I’d recommend the hotel."
> **- Margaux Martin (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/thai-fight-hotel-1.jpg','081 247 6841','Lamai Beach, ตำบล มะเร็ต อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.thaifighthotel.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.634+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.634+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/thai-fight-hotel-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/thai-fight-hotel-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11001385463495249861',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('thai-fight-physports','standard','cmr07ii0300ufq8xdcbukutj4','Thai Fight Physports','## Top Reviews
> "Koh Fight is back bigger and better then ever. Located in a brand new fitness complex, probably the best in the South of Thailand, Koh Fight is now offering Muay Thai retreats for all levels of experience. So if you want to discover, learn or polish your muay Thai skills, Koh Fight is certainly the place to visit. It even has an onsite Onsen Spa, Health Cafe and 2 Swimming Pools, not to mention a multi-storey, multi area gym complex."
> **- Samui Web Solutions (5/5/5)**

> "Great place and great classes, accessible to all levels. The team is very welcoming and professional. I recommand !"
> **- Nesrine Loussaief (5/5/5)**

> "Best gym at island"
