INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('thai-house-beach-resort','standard','cmr07ii0700ugq8xd86x5kkul','Thai House Beach Resort','## Top Reviews
> "Love everything about this resort. Staffs were the best. Restaurant staffs are working so hard and extremely professional, they hv so much responsibilitirs.... They also need to  make sure guests are happy but still keep everything in order like no smoking around the common area. We appreciate so much these types rules because not everyone smoke especially weed. This resort is clean and not polluted by smoker toxic (there is smoking area near by in every area of the resort) . Food is good breakfast is excellent. Room is very clean, well maintained. Swimming pool is well taking care of. All Staffs are informative and well trained. Love the resort. Highly recommended. Good beach and not too close to those jet ski.... Good location, very close to convenience store, very short walk to everything ever"
> **- K Pha (5/5/5)**

> "This place is an excellent value for the cost. It’s not the most luxurious but it has everything you could need for a great price. The staff is very friendly, it’s right on the beach, has a nice pool and massages available right on the beach. Walkable to many restaurants/bars. Location and service make it a 10/10. Definitely will stay here again"
> **- Brett Reut (5/5/5)**

> "Location  is fabulous.  Best part of lamai beach x Rooms clean and comfy. Staff are lovely . Food and drink great. Breakfast has just enough choice. The massage ladies at the side of hotel are the best. Kids pool could have better access as hard to get in and out."
> **- Debbie Platten (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/thai-house-beach-resort-1.jpg','061 818 2988','131, Beach, Thanon Had Lamai, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84150, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.thaihouse-beachresort.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.639+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.639+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/thai-house-beach-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/thai-house-beach-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=465049578739376235',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('thai-international-hospital','standard','cmr07ii0800uhq8xdhnjrkhys','Thai International Hospital','## Top Reviews
> "I do not recommend this hospital.  I came in because something had bitten me and blood was running down my leg. I wanted a proper examination to understand what had happened, how serious it was, and whether anything was still left in the wound.  Instead, the wound was simply cleaned with antiseptic and covered with a bandage. No real effort was made to identify what caused the injury, no proper examination was performed, and no meaningful explanation was provided.  Then came the bill: more than 4,500 baht.  The invoice included a doctor fee, emergency room nursing fee, OPD service fee, plus charges for gloves, bandages, antiseptic, saline solution, and other supplies. It felt as if every possible item and service had been added to maximize the bill.  I understand that private hospitals charge more, but this felt less like healthcare and more like a money extraction scheme. Charging over 4,500 baht for what was essentially cleaning a wound and applying a bandage is outrageous.3300 from 4600 - just service charges  The most disappointing part is that when you come in worried and needing medical help, you trust that you’re being treated as a patient. Instead, I left feeling like I was being treated as a tourist to be overcharged.  If your insurance does not cover 100% of the cost, I strongly recommend avoiding this hospital. In my experience, the quality of care was nowhere near the price charged, and the entire process felt like an overpriced rip-off designed to squeeze as much money as possible out of patients."
> **- Liudmyla Topor (1/5/5)**

> "I recently had a medical checkup at Thai International Hospital, and the overall experience was good. The staff were helpful and assisted me throughout the process. The checkup was organized and didn’t take too long, which I appreciated.  Everyone I interacted with was polite and explained the steps clearly, so it was easy to follow what needed to be done. The environment was also clean and comfortable.  Overall, it was a smooth and straightforward experience, and I felt well assisted during my visit. 👍"
> **- Jas Cupid (5/5/5)**

> "I was there because of a scooter accident and they took such amazing care of me. My wound was treated very carefully and professionally, and it now looks really good. The staff was incredibly kind and we truly felt comfortable there. Since I had to stay for two nights, I was a bit worried at first, but the rooms were great, the food was really good, and the staff was super friendly. My girlfriend was also allowed to stay overnight with me. I can absolutely recommend this hospital 👍"
> **- David Gerspach (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/thai-international-hospital-1.jpg','077 332 654','25/25 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ig1d003gq8xdfxkqj28w','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.640+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.640+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/thai-international-hospital-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/thai-international-hospital-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4055598315051652976',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('thai-lamai-tattoo','standard','cmr07ii0a00uiq8xdl5qrp7wr','Thai Lamai Tattoo','## Top Reviews
> "Mr B was my guy, he did so well on my Tat and here are some pictures.  He comes from so many awards and completed this in 6hrs (30min I needed to stop for drink and pain break).  VERY. FAST AND $3500THB per hour.  I''ll come back and see him in Samui"
> **- Vikram C (5/5/5)**

> "Mr. Tak is the best Tattoo Artist I‘ve ever seen and he deserved each and every Award in his Tattoo Studios. His own style, which he shows in the way he decorated his studios is also nice and unique. He tattooed me for this one in 4 Hours. Most of the other tattoo artists will never get this level. When ever I’ll be coming back to Koh Samui, a trip to him will be part of my plans. Thank you."
> **- Domenic Krepela (5/5/5)**

> "Nice relaxed people who know their stuff. They helped me cover up an old tribal tattoo with something fantastic instead. Highly recommended."
> **- John Padgett (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/thai-lamai-tattoo-1.jpg','083 650 2527','127/219 M.3 Maret, ตำบล มะเร็ต Koh Samui, Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/thailamaitattoo/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 11:30 PM"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.642+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.642+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/thai-lamai-tattoo-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/thai-lamai-tattoo-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=443401467711469834',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-bagel','standard','cmr07ii0c00ujq8xdv2e285xr','The Bagel','## Top Reviews
> "In my opinion, this is the best hummus on the island! We tried several dishes with different hummus variations, as well as pizza and salads — everything was absolutely delicious. The portions are generous. Thank you for such an amazing place!"
> **- Oksana Kirillova (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing Falafel 🥰🥰🥰 One of the best place in the Island! 🤩Every time we come here, it''s delicious. The service is very friendly, the prices are very reasonable, and they have a huge selection of dishes. I highly recommend it ☺️"
> **- Lidia Szczerkowska (5/5/5)**

> "Very tasty food and a very friendly owner and staff overall. Beautiful presentation and a great combination of sauces, vegetables, and meat. They also have baked goods — bread, baguettes, and bagels. Excellent quality for a reasonable price. We’ve been here twice and were satisfied both times. Definitely recommend!"
> **- Serj (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-bagel-1.jpg','082 808 4890','47 1, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.644+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.644+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-bagel-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-bagel-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16627631311590588508',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-bamboo-rooms','standard','cmr07ii0e00ukq8xdnay334mq','The Bamboo Rooms','## Top Reviews
> "What an amazing tattoo studio. Por is the most welcoming and friendly manager there is. She really makes you at comfort and does everything with a smile!  Me and my partner had a bamboo tattoo with the Ohm symbol. Jay and Cheng are quite the artists. Make beautiful designs of our wishes and there work is as fine as a machine. Cheng even did a cover up of an older tattoo to match the new one. So thankfull for that.  We left the studio both with a big smile and a beautiful bamboo tattoo! Is you are on Samui and want a clean shop and the best tattoo artists? Bamboo Rooms is the place!"
> **- Sanne van Lieshout (5/5/5)**

> "This place has been amazing from the very 1st contact all the way to getting the work finished. I initially reached out to the UK location via WhatsApp on accident when I tried to reach Koh Samui, Thailand. They redirected me to the correct location and Por took the initiative to reach out to me. The communication was thorough and consistent. We were able to lock in a design and a date and time.  When I arrived at the shop, I was greeted by Por and the staff with smiles, then introduced to my artist Jay. Jay was quick and proficient. He constantly checked in on me during the work to ensure I was doing ok. Por was also very attentive and checked if I needed anything while I was there. After we finished, I was given time to ask any questions and I was given a bag with aftercare instructions and some aftercare balm. The art looks amazing!! I’m definitely in love with the work! THANK YOU Jay 🙏🏽. And THANK YOU Por for assisting with everything to get the work done smoothly, making me feel comfortable and welcome while I was there, and helping me find my way back to safety 😊 I would HIGHLY HIGHLY recommend coming here for a tattoo. Reach out to Por and the rest will be a very smoothly and memorable process!"
> **- El3vated 760 (5/5/5)**

> "My wife had a cover up by Keng 5 years ago in Otley after missing him on Samui as he was in Otley at the time returning to Samui this year I wanted to get a traditional Sak Yant.  After consultation with Keng and Lauren I decided on a design, what I like about The Bamboo rooms is that they will guide you as to the meaning and placement and these are not tourist tattoos.  The tattoo took six hours and the detail is amazing and has more in it than anything else I''d seen, a credit to Keng and his abilities and speed.  My wife also had a second lotus tattoo to compliment her cover up and this was carried out by Jay at the same time, somehow both tattos finished at exactly the same time even though Fi''s started nearly 4 hours later! These guys know what they are doing, how long it will take and the detail and precision in everything they do is top notch, highly recommend if you want a modern bamboo tattoo or traditional Sak Yant.  Update!  Haven''t had such a great experience with the first Sak Yant by Keng I returned and had 2 more.  These have both healed really quickly and with no blistering and minimal after care I can''t recommend Keng highly enough if you want a traditional bamboo tattoo or Sak Yant with someone who is extremely knowledgeable in the art."
> **- Mark Webster (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-bamboo-rooms-1.jpg','082 643 2520','30, Bophut (next to Samui Airport arrivals, 129, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.bambootattoo.co.uk/','["Monday: 12:30 – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:30 – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:30 – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 12:30 – 9:00 PM","Friday: 12:30 – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 12:30 – 6:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.646+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.646+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-bamboo-rooms-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-bamboo-rooms-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2744961994265500940',NULL,NULL);
