> "10/10 experience. The service was incredibly friendly and welcoming, and the poke bowls were absolutely delicious and fresh. Such a great spot for a healthy meal in Koh Samui. We’ll definitely be back."
> **- Aurea Brandes (5/5/5)**

> "This was my first time opening my mind to healthy food. Before ordering, I kept wondering if I would even like it. I always thought healthy food might not taste good. But after trying it for the first time, I told myself I could eat this every day. At least one healthy meal a day as a gift to my life. It tastes great and the ingredients are very good. Highly recommended.💜🫶"
> **- Meen KanyaMee (5/5/5)**

> "Yummy and high quality health conscious bowls! I got the keto bowl and it was delicious. Nice interior, WiFi is strong, and the most lovely staff! Cash only though."
