INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-barrel','standard','cmr07ii0o00uoq8xdtoa45fkh','The Barrel','## Top Reviews
> "Super nice place. We were served by Nikki, the manager from Italy.  Very knowledgeable on wine from different regions.  Prices were fair in comparison to similar places on Samui.  Plus they are the only place in Thailand where I’ve seen a Paulaner beer from Germany.  Top place!"
> **- jakob hamm (5/5/5)**

> "The 1st time I went there was because I needed advice for red wine. I had a very good advice and the staff was so friendly 😁 Second time : I went to buy some rose wine and some cheese and WOW I enjoyed it so much every thing is so tasteful, you get the bread, you get the fruits and the charcuterie with the cheese all nicely chopped I am so happy with that I really recommend this place 100%"
> **- Amélie Catherine Butel (5/5/5)**

> "Very disappointing customer service, knew nothing about wine & shop was very messy."
