INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-bay-ink','standard','cmr07ii0q00upq8xdcyh48zew','The Bay Ink','## Top Reviews
> "Walked in and showed them a small elephant design I wanted. They gave me the price and asked if i wanted it done there and then. They drew it up and I had it done and completed in 10 minutes. Very happy with the tattoo. A lovely little reminder of an amazing holiday to Thailand. Would definitely recommend 👌"
> **- Leanne Ritchie (5/5/5)**

> "what lovely dudes! me and my mum went in for matching and booked the same day, they replied super quick and let us take time with placement and size. the level of skill one of the artist has with fine line is amazing and i’ve never seen such great line work! thank you once again!!"
> **- Mollie Pratt (5/5/5)**

> "Excellent service throughout by these guys. They know what they are doing and would highly recommend visiting them directly to make a booking. They may even get you in straight away, which I was lucky to get, so even better! My requests were followed all the way throughout. Thank you 💯"
