INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-beach-house-bar','standard','cmr07ii0s00uqq8xdml6fk39l','The Beach House & Bar','## Top Reviews
> "European price with European service. Coffee was good and coconut panna cotta looked and tasted great!  Staff is friendly and helpful. Good view on the beach 🏝️  The only minus was the 10 % service bill addition (just include it in the price)."
> **- Vladislav Lenskii (5/5/5)**

> "Lovely meal overlooking the beech at night with both house singers as well as fire performers for entertainment - it was excellent. Particularly good Beef Cheek Rendang. Staff were very attentive but not overly so as to be in the way of a lovely chilled out evening."
> **- Paul Wilson (4/5/5)**

> "We had lunch, dinner, and lunch here again! It’s so delicious, the food is so fresh, the premises lovely, clean, lively and comfortable atmosphere. Ken is very attentive and went out of his way to make us and our little one feel right at home. Highly recommend!"
> **- carissa hope lynch (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-beach-house-bar-1.jpg','077 965 900','Santiburi Koh Samui 12/12, ตำบล แม่น้ำ อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://santiburisamui.com/dining/the-beach-house-restaurant/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 10:30 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 10:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.660+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.660+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-beach-house-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-beach-house-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4396423067955243090',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-beach-samui','standard','cmr07ii0u00urq8xdul8xxtxb','The Beach Samui','## Top Reviews
> "This is one of the most beautiful and luxurious places I’ve ever stayed to completely reset and recharge.  From the moment I arrived, the whole team went above and beyond to make sure I felt comfortable, supported and cared for throughout my stay.  A special thank you to Anya, who was absolutely incredible. She genuinely cared about making my experience the best it could be and her kindness, attention and warmth made such a difference.  The setting is peaceful, the wellness approach feels personalised and intentional, and I left feeling healthier, clearer and back on track again both mentally and physically.  If you are looking for somewhere to truly disconnect, reset and focus on yourself, I honestly couldn’t recommend enough"
> **- Joanne F (5/5/5)**

> "amazing hotel! I stayed here for three days and honestly loved every moment. The hotel is beautiful, super comfortable, and incredibly welcoming. The customer service was outstanding — the staff went above and beyond to make sure everything was perfect and made me feel truly valued as a guest. This was one of my best hotel experiences ever! I highly recommend this place and can’t wait to come back again."
> **- Rabeen Mohammedsaeed (5/5/5)**

> "My recent stay at The Beach Samui was, without exaggeration, one of the best life experiences I’ve ever had. From the moment I arrived, I felt a deep sense of peace. The property itself is stunning, offering incredible, panoramic views that truly embody the ''Art of Living Well''.  The level of service here is top-notch. The staff is remarkably attentive, ensuring every need is met before you even have to ask. What truly sets this place apart, however, is the owner, Bryan. He is an incredible host who takes genuine time out of his day to connect with and get to know every guest. It’s rare to find that level of personal care and authentic connection in luxury travel.  The culinary experience was another highlight. Chef New is a true artist—every meal was amazing, fresh, and beautifully presented. Beyond the property, there is so much to explore nearby, with a variety of great food and local culture just minutes away. As a wellness getaway, this place is unmatched. The breathwork treatments were transformative, and the massages were some of the best I’ve ever experienced. From the sunset herbal baths to the overall atmosphere, everything was executed to the highest standard. I am truly grateful for this experience and cannot recommend The Beach Samui enough for anyone looking to reset and rejuvenate in luxury."
> **- Travon Ridley-Evans (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-beach-samui-1.jpg','077 234 567','30/23 Moo 5 Thong Krut, Village, อําเภ, อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.thebeachsamui.com/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07igdj008fq8xdhc2mye6x','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.662+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.662+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-beach-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-beach-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8937419996500787501',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-beach-wellness-retreat','standard','cmr07ii0w00usq8xd85xzppgz','The Beach Wellness Retreat','## Top Reviews
> "I have just finished an 8 day detox health cleanse and I am feeling fantastic. Under the knowledgeable, caring, skilled, guidance of Dr Manta, this is a brilliant program. Dr Manta brings many years of education and experience and has created a program that has loads of health benefits. I will be back next year for this health and energy boost. Thanks Dr Manta"
> **- Susan G (5/5/5)**

> "As an acupuncturist on vacation, I was looking for TCM practitioner for self-care, and I’m so grateful my friend referred me to Dr. Manta! She and her Thai health massage colleague Lek were both very caring and knowledgeable therapists, treating my neck and back stiffness during my week on Samui (I stayed nearby, not on-site). I highly recommend them for anyone looking for expert holistic healthcare. I’ll certainly be back next time I visit!"
> **- W L (5/5/5)**

> "It was a great experience to make the detox 5 days Massage was really good. Detox Not easy to do . The room have to be better. Lot of things are broken or not OK in the bungalow. Beach not far but the Programm is really hard when you make it for the first time. For my body it s was enough 5 days... I wait for feeling all the benefits beacuse I a m really..... Empty and tired"
> **- Sophie Lecoq (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-beach-wellness-retreat-1.jpg','081 891 8607','32, 10 Moo 6 Soi 3, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.healthretreatsamui.com/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07igdj008fq8xdhc2mye6x','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.664+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.664+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-beach-wellness-retreat-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-beach-wellness-retreat-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16815280335366523772',NULL,NULL);
