INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-blooming-gallery','standard','cmr07ii1300uuq8xdh61wg051','The Blooming Gallery','## Top Reviews
> "This is such a cute lil gem! I really loved the chicken caesar salad & the matcha was delicious. I ate lunch here with a friend which was the perfect environment to chat and I also stayed and did work on my laptop which was super peaceful! 😌"
> **- Samantha Sweet Skin (5/5/5)**

> "What a great place! Yesterday we had lunch, today "
> **- Grace Hermarij (5/5/5)**

> "Beautiful place, really take care over the setting, food and service.  We stayed nearby and thought it was an art gallery (it looks that nice!) until our last day, wish we’d realised sooner.  Perfect for breakfast, brunch or early dinner."
> **- Phillip Walker (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-blooming-gallery-1.jpg','077 231 446','124-124/1 2, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.671+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.671+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-blooming-gallery-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-blooming-gallery-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5148176371560975703',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-boudoir','standard','cmr07ii1500uvq8xdco8xu7oe','The Boudoir','## Top Reviews
> "My girlfriend (French) and I (Norwegian) wanted a calm yet special dinner evening for New Years Eve 2025, and we had seen signs to The Budoir as it is close to where we live in Mae nam.  We booked a table, and discovered what a wonderful oasis of french delicacy this is, hidden between trees and away from the road. Lit up with serene and atmospheric lights and decorations giving it an exotic feel of south france, north africa and also asia, we were already convinced when entering. The very friendly french owner greeted us, explained the menu and recommended a great tasting bottle of red wine. The three course dinner was delicious. Loved the foie gras especially, though the menu changes frequently to keep it exciting coming back. High quality food and being a special occasion, the price is worth it, although it is in the upper tier compared to thai food, which is expected.  I can fully recommend this restaurant for an authentic and exciting french food experience, with an owner and a chief who knows what they want to present and how to present it :)"
> **- Morten Søbyskogen (5/5/5)**

> "Hidden gem in the middle of nowhere. Super nice owner who’s very welcoming and also helped my husband go withdraw cash. Food was really good and portions were big."
> **- Fatima Faour (5/5/5)**

> "Nice restaurant , with a unique style . Quiet place , feel good . Dishes are frenchy style , yummy with good portions . Wines also great value , reasonable prices . A place to discover"
> **- Sabai Glamping (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-boudoir-1.jpg','082 848 0986','ตำบล แม่น้ำ Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://fr.tripadvisor.be/Restaurant_Review-g1182465-d1099409-Reviews-The_Boudoir-Mae_Nam_Ko_Samui_Surat_Thani_Province.html','["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: Closed","Wednesday: 7:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.673+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.673+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-boudoir-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-boudoir-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13109410718184348418',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-breeza-beach-restaurant','standard','cmr07ii1600uwq8xdt3d3mmdc','The Breeza Beach Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "The staff provided excellent service, ( The driver send us to the restaurant ,  Restaurant team, including the restaurant manager who was very attentive and helpful in recommending and assisting with everything. The food was delicious. Highly recommended, and we will definitely come back again!"
> **- Varaporn Ritto (5/5/5)**

> "I had a wonderful lunch at Breeza Beach Restaurant today. The food was delicious and every dish looked beautiful. I personally prefer a bit more spice, but I guess the team keep it mild because most guests are Western. Cheong Mon Beach is super beautiful today, and it made me enjoy the meal even more 🥰  The team at Breeza is always warm and friendly. Their service makes me feel very welcome every time I visit.  Don’t miss visiting this beach and enjoying the food here at Breeza, Meliá Cheong Mon. A lovely place to relax and enjoy good food by the sea. Highly recommended!"
> **- Puniga Yawananon (5/5/5)**

> "Fantastic spot for a meal, right on the beach with incredible views across the bay. Super friendly and kind team working here as well. Great vegetarian and mocktail options. The poke bowl is so good I had it twice!"
> **- Brodie Lynch (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-breeza-beach-restaurant-1.jpg','077 938 899','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.melia.com/en/hotels/thailand/koh-samui/melia-koh-samui/restaurants','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifsv000nq8xdrwnu123q','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.674+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.674+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-breeza-beach-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-breeza-beach-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14350751678204263193',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-briza','standard','cmr07ii1900uxq8xdpxuhrp5l','The Briza','## Top Reviews
> "Our stay at the Briza Beach Resort was overall a pleasant experience, and the property itself is very সুন্দর and well-maintained. The location is convenient, making it easy to explore the surrounding area.  Our room was spacious and comfortable, and the private pool on the terrace was definitely the highlight of our stay – perfect for relaxing and enjoying some quiet time.  However, there are a few downsides worth mentioning. The bathroom facilities are somewhat outdated and could use renovation. Additionally, the resort does not provide its own sun loungers on the beach, and the section of beach directly next to the resort is not really suitable for swimming.  On the positive side, the staff were consistently friendly, attentive, and helpful, which made our stay more enjoyable. For a 4-star resort, we expected a bit more in some areas, but overall everything was fine and we had a nice stay."
> **- simona Cuomo (4/5/5)**

> "Two friends and I stayed at the Briza Beach Resort from March 20 to April 3, 2026, and had a wonderful time. We had two adjoining duplex suites, 109 and 110, with a small pool off our patios. The suites were spacious, bright, and clean. The pool was great. A few days after our arrival, I tripped while walking down the hill outside the resort, and broke a bone in my foot. I got stellar treatment at the Bangkok Hospital Samui, but had to spend the rest of the vacation in an air cast and on crutches. The staff at the resort were wonderfully helpful and accommodating, and I can’t say enough about Tom, Alai, and Mary (and others whose names I’m sorry I didn’t catch) who patiently and cheerfully ferried me in a golf cart to and from the restaurant, the beach, the front entrance, and my room several times every day. The staff here really go the extra mile (in this case, literally!) There was a tasty breakfast buffet each day, including a coffee machine that made fabulous lattes. The three of us took a cooking class from the chef,  and we enjoyed it so much we took another one the second week using a different menu. The cooking classes were very well organized and we even got nice aprons to take home. The food we made was enough for our dinner, as well as leftovers that the staff warmed up and served us for lunch the next day. I want to shout out to many of the other great staff at this place as well - Laila, Jessie, Nuda, Pat, Boobo, and many more. Kudos to the managers - Ken, Sak, and others whose names I wish I’d written down. The place is very well run.  To be honest, when we first arrived, we weren’t sure we were going to enjoy our stay. Given the name of the resort, we were disappointed to find that there isn’t really a “beach”per se. There is a raised concrete platform area overlooking the water, with lounge chairs, massage services, and a beach bar. There are steps down to the shore, and sometimes there is a small beach area and other times it is covered by the tide. (Maybe it’s better at other times of the year? I don’t know.)  But once we got over that and focused on the great features that the resort does have (including beautiful spacious suites, lovely pools, attractive grounds, nice ocean view, and beach areas just a short walk down the shore. And have I mentioned the great staff?) we enjoyed our stay very much."
> **- Allison Matichuk (5/5/5)**

> "Spent 5 nights here in Feb 2026.  As per other reviews the hotel could do with some touch up. However it was better than I expected - after reading some of the other reviews.  Didn’t start off too well - our room had windows South and East. So very warm when entering.  Was told give the a/c 5 minutes.  Then disaster - power cut (the whole island). Clearly not the hotels fault.  Power was soon restored to the island except the local area - apparently sub station issue.  It wasn’t until around 9 pm that power was restored and we could cool the room down a bit.  After that we made sure cleaning closed the curtains during the day. Breakfast is reasonable - the chef cooking eggs is really nice. We had room 32X with a plunge pool. This was great as not overlooked. Note some of the larger villas have pool but these are very open. The two largest villas nearest to the sea are very public !  One has the massage area adjacent to the Not recommended if steps are an issue. The majority of room will have some steps to access. For us it was 76 steps up and down to breakfast."
> **- Michael Godfrey (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-briza-1.jpg','077 231 997','173 22 หมู่ที่ 2 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.9,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.thebriza.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.677+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.677+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-briza-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-briza-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13859450015798529619',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-butcher-koh-samui','standard','cmr07ii1a00uyq8xd5i9yw0d4','The Butcher Koh Samui','## Top Reviews
> "The Butcher is easily one of the best Western restaurants in Lamai. The steaks were cooked properly, the meat quality was noticeably better than most places on the island, and the portions were generous. The atmosphere feels busy and lively without being too loud or pretentious, and the staff were friendly and efficient even when the restaurant was packed. Prices are higher than average for Lamai, but for imported beef and the overall quality, it feels justified. Definitely a great spot if you want a proper steak, burger, or comfort food meal in Koh Samui."
> **- Kyrio Azure (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing restaurant in Koh Samui with a great atmosphere, delicious food, and outstanding service. Our steak dinner was cooked perfectly. tender, juicy, and full of flavor. The staff were very friendly and attentive, making the whole experience even better. Definitely one of the best dining experiences we’ve had in Koh Samui. Highly recommended!"
> **- Kylian PONTE (5/5/5)**

> "A place with a very good appearance. The service is excellent. The food has a very good presentation, and the size is perfect. The taste is normal, we tried the two burgers and the meat tasted good but their cooking was a bit overdone. The prices are slightly high, but fair for the attention and the dishes you are receiving.  Excellent option to eat food different from Thai."
> **- Salvador Calderón A. (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-butcher-koh-samui-1.jpg','082 232 5292','122 Thanon Had Lamai, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100063718083692','["Monday: 5:00 – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 5:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 5:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 5:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 5:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 5:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 5:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.678+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.678+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-butcher-koh-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-butcher-koh-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10892179843563029260',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-chess-hotel','standard','cmr07ii1c00uzq8xd1x1r6x5m','The Chess Hotel','## Top Reviews
> "Perfect location. Right under the flight path so it’s dead loud when the planes are landing and taking off which does disturb rest.  Shower was poor, but the rooms were good.  Safety deposit box, very small doesn’t fit too much in."
> **- JordanIRL (4/5/5)**

> "The rooms were dingy, almost no toiletries provided. Rooms and washrooms have mo ventilation. Not staying here again"
> **- Stuti Jain (1/5/5)**

> "VERY thin walls….you can hear your neighbor at normal speaking volume. I had to kill about 30 mosquitoes in my room. Stayed 3 nights with no room cleaning and no fresh towels. Won’t stay here again"
> **- Shelton Clark (2/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-chess-hotel-1.jpg','094 579 4488','156 7, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.680+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.680+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-chess-hotel-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-chess-hotel-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13358999933892910325',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-clean-team-bangrak','standard','cmr07ii1e00v0q8xdi9l48d0v','The Clean Team','## Top Reviews
> "Great service, highly recommended! They deep cleaned my house and I was very satisfied. Very reasonably priced as well."
> **- John V. (5/5/5)**

> "So pleased ( and relieved) to have found Natalie and her super team. Thorough, fast, professional, trustworthy and a gleaming island home!  Have struggled to find someone who we feel confident enough with to care for our house when we return home to South Africa..... and finally we found the Clean Team! Well Done ladies! 👋👋"
> **- Susan Angenent (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing cleaning team ! I m so lucky to find them🙏🏻 completely different quality of cleaning 👌🏻 after 4 years in Thailand I m finally see such  a great job! the whole house shines😊"
> **- Evgeniia Gilman (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-clean-team-bangrak-1.jpg','+66644152078','7/82, ตำบล บ่อผุด Koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.thecleanteamsamui.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ihcv00lgq8xdi8o8a1wt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.682+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.682+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-clean-team-bangrak-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-clean-team-bangrak-2.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-clean-team-bangrak-3.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-clean-team-bangrak-4.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17106074829228136018',NULL,NULL);
