INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-cliff-bar-grill','standard','cmr07ii1j00v2q8xdu70ko4ul','The Cliff Bar & Grill','## Top Reviews
> "We were there on Christmas. The food was great and the view was absolutely stunning. The service was excellent my boyfriend said he felt truly spoiled as the staff always noticed when his drink was almost empty and refilled it for him before he even realized, even though it was a very busy night on Christmas.  We booked directly through the website which was very convenient and they reserved the best seats for us on Christmas. This place is one of our favorites and we will definitely come back."
> **- anw Anw (5/5/5)**

> "5-Star Service in a Stunning Location – Exceptional Management!  We had a memorable evening at The Cliff Bar and Grill. While the food was good, it was the outstanding service from the manager and the team that truly earned this 5-star rating. 1. Exceptional Management & Care: The manager was incredibly enthusiastic, attentive, and highly observant. We were dining with a small child, and the manager noticed our initial table near the kitchen was a bit noisy, so they immediately moved us to a quieter 2-person table further away. Even more impressive, while we were waiting for our main courses, the manager proactively moved us again to a more spacious 4-person table. They realized that having a toddler requires extra space, and this level of thoughtfulness and proactive care made our evening much more comfortable. A huge thank you to the manager for being so considerate! 2. Atmosphere & View: The location and the overall ambiance of the restaurant are stunning. It is the perfect spot for a beautiful evening out with a great view. 3. Food & Presentation: The food presentation was beautiful and very well-plated. Taste-wise, I would rate it around 3.5 stars given the price point—it was good, though perhaps not as extraordinary as the service.  I am giving this a 5-star review primarily because of the world-class service provided by the manager and the staff. If you value being well-taken care of in a beautiful setting, this is the place to be. We truly appreciated the hospitality! Rating: 5/5 Stars ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐"
> **- Vo Tung (5/5/5)**

> "The most amazing meal at the Cliff! Although a little expensive for Thailand, it was well worth it for the view alone and the food was even better! My partner is a coeliac and pescatarian. There were lots of options for her and the staff were very knowledgable about gluten-free food. She had a lovely gluten-free salmon pasta dish and I had a beautiful lasagna. We both got gorgeous gluten-free brownies for desert!"
> **- Mitchell Licata (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-cliff-bar-grill-1.jpg','077 448 508','124/2 Tambon Maret, Suratthani, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://thecliffsamui.com/','["Monday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.687+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.687+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-cliff-bar-grill-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-cliff-bar-grill-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6648868876780039089',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-club-by-zazen','standard','cmr07ii1l00v3q8xd4sgxcnc7','The Club By Zazen','## Top Reviews
> "Everything was really wonderful, the food delicious during breakfast and diner, the atmosphere fantastic and impecable design and great architecture all around, the staff are super kind, smiley and helpful.  The hotel offers a great deal of things for a 10/10 stay. The place itself it’s cleaned and maintained regularly, the whole venue is designed to walk around and discover, large towels are offered for the pool area, the sun beds linen get changed daily, the garden is lush and impeccably maintained.  We had a room with sea front and it was beautiful, towels and linen smelled good, the bathtub was a great idea (although no bath salts available), mattress and pillows of good quality and confortable + great taste for the decoration.  Nothing bad to say to be honest."
> **- Carolina Lopez (5/5/5)**

> "The food was amazing, the views were beautiful, and the atmosphere was truly special. We made a reservation for my friend’s birthday and informed the staff in advance — they prepared everything wonderfully and decorated the table beautifully, which made a great impression. The service was outstanding. It’s most beautiful during the day, but the evening atmosphere is just as incredible. We will definitely come back — highly recommended for anyone looking for delicious food and a truly special experience."
> **- Anna Golec (5/5/5)**

> "⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ I’ve never been to a place this beautiful before! The place is absolutely stunning, with an amazing view of the sea that makes the whole experience unforgettable. The vibe is incredible, everything is well organized, and you can really feel the quality in every detail. This place is truly something special!"
> **- Alaa Nas (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-club-by-zazen-1.jpg','077 425 177','177 หมู่ที่ 1 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://samuizazen.com/the-club-by-zazen/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.689+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.689+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-club-by-zazen-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-club-by-zazen-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2272020940156428661',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-cocoon-viewpoint-restaurant','standard','cmr07ii1o00v4q8xdach61s6v','The Cocoon: Viewpoint Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "This was an absolutely unforgettable experience! From the moment we arrived, we were struck by the stunning scenery—the atmosphere is perfectly curated and provides a breathtaking backdrop for a meal.  The food was phenomenal, with every dish arriving perfectly prepared and full of vibrant flavors. It is clear that the kitchen takes immense pride in their craft.  What truly elevated our visit, however, was the exceptional service. Our server, Pan, was the absolute highlight of the evening. Pan was incredibly attentive, anticipating our needs before we even had to ask, and delivered everything with such genuine warmth and professionalism. It is rare to find service this personalized and seamless. She even took a ton of pictures for us in 3 different restaurant locations! She is the definition of an amazing server.  If you are looking for a spot with a view, delicious cuisine, and a team that genuinely cares about your experience, look no further. Ask for Pan-she is The best!"
> **- Justin Yoshida (5/5/5)**

> "What a beautiful setting to eat! We had breakfast here one morning and had a great time....staff were super friendly and accommodating of our family and multiple young children. We mentioned it was my intention laws anniversary and they were kre than happy to help us celebrate with some appropriate music and cake (in the pics)...food was great and reasonably priced...I would look into booking for a sunset timed dinner as I suspect that is primetime!! A must for any couple or family!"
> **- max yeo (5/5/5)**

> "Absolutely stunning views. The wind was a tab bit strong. The service was fantastic. Even the social media team was so active. The wine and beers were fine but the Thai food was a little underwhelming. It''s probably catered to tourists hence they have toned down the flavour and spice profiles but definitely worth a visit for a drink and the view. Exceptional service."
> **- Gursheel Dhillon (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-cocoon-viewpoint-restaurant-1.jpg','093 586 1777','33, 67, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://cocoon-samui.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.692+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.692+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-cocoon-viewpoint-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-cocoon-viewpoint-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=900251576794148564',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-cosy-fisherman-apartments','standard','cmr07ii1q00v5q8xdq1g9qafg','The Cosy Fisherman Apartments','## Top Reviews
> "Great atmosphere right on the beach. Food and drinks were amazing (buy one get one free cocktail was definitely a bonus!). Staff was very kind and provided excellent service"
> **- Amy Victoria (5/5/5)**

> "We had an amazing Valentine’s Day dinner on the beach. The food was exquisite, truly next level. The atmosphere was super peaceful, beautiful, and romantic. The staff was very attentive and kind, and everyone was so friendly and lovely. The music was soft, the decoration was fantastic, and everything was perfectly timed and cooked just right. More than recommended, such a fantastic place! 👏🏼✨"
> **- Luz de los Milagros Mansilla (5/5/5)**

> "Nice beach restaurant in a great location, but it’s definitely more on the touristic side rather than a local experience. The food was good, nothing bad at all, just nothing particularly incredible or memorable either.  The main highlight is the setting — right on the beach — and a big bonus is that the place next door does fire shows, which you can easily enjoy from the terrace while having a drink or meal.  It’s a convenient spot and a pleasant place to stop, especially if you’re already in the area, just don’t come expecting authentic local food or a hidden gem. One practical downside: the restaurant is quite large but there’s only one shared toilet, which can be a bit inconvenient when it’s busy.  Overall, a decent, easy option for beachfront dining with a nice view and entertainment nearby."
> **- C. G. (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-cosy-fisherman-apartments-1.jpg','092 701 6391','The Cosy fisherman''s Restaurant, 79 2moo1, Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.2,0,0,0,NULL,'https://thecosybeachresort.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 11:30 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 11:30 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.694+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.694+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-cosy-fisherman-apartments-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-cosy-fisherman-apartments-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16346164936197606709',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-cosy-maenam-beach-resort-pool-bar-restaurant','standard','cmr07ii1t00v6q8xd3xay2i8d','The Cosy Maenam Beach Resort, Pool Bar & Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "Quiet place tucked away close to a few local food markets and many massage places. It consists of approx. 10 small detached bungalows, one per family. Our stay included breakfast (a choice of Thai, continental and English i think) served at the restaurant overlooking the sea. There is a small swimming pool which may be suitable for kids rather than adults. Beach beds with parasols are provided. Rooms are cleaned every day, all have ceiling fans, tv and air-conditioning, veranda. Bathrooms are modern. Make sure you close doors in the evening as there are some mosquitos especially towards evening hours. The service is great and accommodating.  There are 3/4 parking spaces which was plenty as we were the only guests with a car."
> **- Natalia Percival (5/5/5)**

> "What a wonderful resort. Great location, real standout is the amazing people. Special mention to King and Zaw who made me feel so welcome. Note the pool is small and not really for swimming - lovely however. Place seems French owned with a lot of French guests. As a Brit, what a pleasure :), met some great people here who I will visit in France. This place is so charming it could even be a viable alternative to the vastly more expensive 4S, RC etc. Bravo to this place. Staff culture world class."
> **- howard smith (5/5/5)**

> "Nice quite place to stay. Clean rooms, great pool on the beach, good food and quiet beach 🏖️. Good reception service- but I recommend every guest to check the TAXI prices before. Don’t pay 700 BHT !!! when Grab is 400 BHT."
> **- Ole Connor (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-cosy-maenam-beach-resort-pool-bar-restaurant-1.jpg','064 914 0035','82, 2 Soi 4, Tambon Mae Nam, Maenam, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://thecosybeachresort.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.697+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.697+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-cosy-maenam-beach-resort-pool-bar-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-cosy-maenam-beach-resort-pool-bar-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8053662933656000467',NULL,NULL);
