> **- Ole Connor (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-cosy-1.jpg','064 914 0035','82, 2 Soi 4, Tambon Mae Nam, Maenam, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://thecosybeachresort.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.699+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.699+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-cosy-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-cosy-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8053662933656000467',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-cove','standard','cmr07ii1w00v8q8xdk93ldfq1','The Cove','## Top Reviews
> "Everything was perfect 🙏 from the service to the very friendly ladies at reception – absolutely top-notch!  We''ll definitely be back 😄"
> **- Stefanie Jäger (5/5/5)**

> ""
> **- Supon Jakom (5/5/5)**

> ""
> **- 徐誰立 (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-cove-1.jpg','086 282 8872','11/7 Moo 1 Bophut, Koh Samui Thailand, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.700+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.700+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-cove-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-cove-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1976179815425685764',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-culture-get-married','standard','cmr07ii1y00v9q8xd8x2ypprs','The Culture Get Married','## Top Reviews
> "Brilliant hotel, would recommend to anyone and wished we stayed here longer! Rooms are clean and very modern and stylish, pretty much everything you would need is in this room. We was in a ground floor pool veiw room as this was very convenient to have to room right next to the pool! Breakfast was great, lots of different food choices. I am vegetarian and found it very good for me. We also ate at the restaurant of an evening and the meals were lovely! Same for bar, lots of choices. Hotel has a private beach area, pool is very nice also. Gym is good. Location of hotel is good, shops and restaurants very close by. Close to fishermans village and other good things. All staff across hotel are very friendly and helpful,  reception staff including Kwan, Ti, Lala are very helpful! Also Paul the cat is very cute, make sure you make a donation to the street cats and dogs"
> **- Charly Sedgley (5/5/5)**

> "We had a wonderful stay at Culture Samui Hotel during our honeymoon. The hotel is beautiful, peaceful, and perfectly located right by the beach. The rooms were clean, comfortable, and well maintained, and the overall atmosphere was relaxing and welcoming.  The staff were incredibly friendly and helpful throughout our stay, especially Lala ana Niga always greeting us with a smile and making sure we were comfortable. Their hospitality really made a difference and helped make our trip even more special.  The pool, beach views, and facilities were excellent, and the breakfast offered a good variety of options. We truly enjoyed our time here and would happily recommend Culture Samui Hotel to anyone looking for a relaxing stay in Koh Samui.  Thank you to the entire team for a memorable experience! ❤️🌴✨"
> **- Shooq Turaif (5/5/5)**

> "If we could, we would give six stars in a heartbeat! Our stay at Culture Samui was simply fantastic from the very first minute to the last. As soon as you arrive, you notice how incredibly modern, stylish, and beautifully designed the entire resort is. Plus, everything is absolutely spotless – you feel right at home immediately.  Our absolute favorite spot was definitely the gorgeous infinity pool. It’s just the perfect place to completely unwind.  But what truly made this hotel so special for us was the wonderful team. It''s rare to experience such warm, genuine friendliness and such attentive service. We also have to give a huge compliment to the kitchen: the food quality was absolutely top-notch!  Just a little wink and a shoutout to the bar: Sorry again that we emptied the entire bottle of Ricard! 😉 We just had to treat ourselves.  We absolutely loved our time with you and already know for sure: We will definitely be coming back!"
> **- André Scaramuzza (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-culture-get-married-1.jpg','077 238 828','Bangrak Beach, 86 moo4, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.theculturesamui.com/',NULL,'cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.702+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.702+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-culture-get-married-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-culture-get-married-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2270950898876790536',NULL,NULL);
