INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-cups-caf','standard','cmr07ii2300vbq8xdv864ha66','The Cups Café','## Top Reviews
> "The shabu buffet was absolutely delicious, the food was very fresh and good quality. The staff were attentive and helpful. The service quick and efficient. I would definitely recommend this place if you are hungry because you won’t leave disappointed. The music, atmosphere is relax and chilled. Open until 9:30pm for last orders. Serves cold beers and a selection of other drinks.  Highly recommend for couples, families and large groups but recommended making a reservation."
> **- Chris (5/5/5)**

> "The spicy Thai-style marinated raw shrimp and shabu-shabu were absolutely perfect. So satisfying I enjoyed every moment  Friendly staff :)"
> **- SuperDuperMegaUltra (5/5/5)**

> "Always  I saw good food on Facebook and I check it on Google Maps  !so today  i go try it and from 10 point I give 9.5 !heey people go and check it out"
> **- Kevin Baumgartner (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-cups-caf-1.jpg','063 987 9639','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/thecupscafesamui/','["Monday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: Closed","Friday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.707+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.707+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-cups-caf-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-cups-caf-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8013432439645016343',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-deck-beach-club','standard','cmr07ii2500vcq8xdqlmp8wiu','The Deck Beach Club','## Top Reviews
> "A Perfect Beachside Oasis (and the Ultimate Pre-Flight Stop!)  If you are looking for the perfect blend of a cozy atmosphere and chic design on Koh Samui, The Deck Beach Club is an absolute must-visit. From the moment you walk in, the "
> **- Bernhard R. (5/5/5)**

> "I had such a great experience at this place. The service was excellent, everyone was friendly, attentive, and made me feel really welcomed. The food was delicious and the prices are very affordable, which is amazing because there’s no minimum spend.  From the moment I arrived everything was smooth; no issues at all. You can relax, sit anywhere, and just enjoy the space. The atmosphere is beautiful, peaceful, and perfect for spending the day.  Overall, highly recommended if you want a comfortable and affordable place to chill, eat well, and be taken care of. I’ll definitely come back."
> **- Johanna Amaya Rubio (5/5/5)**

> "From the moment you arrive, you’re treated as an honoured guest. The service is impeccable and the food is sublime. For what you pay 1500/2000 baht per person, you get your monies worth, as you’re not overcharged compared to other beach clubs on the island. Such a friendly atmosphere and when the DJ kicks off, the party ramps up. 🤙🤙🤙. Personally, I’d like to say a massive thank you to Harry who looked after us all day. A lovely young lad, so polite and humble. 100% you need a day or 3 or 5 at this place, it’s fabulous."
> **- Gareth Carpenter (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-deck-beach-club-1.jpg','063 085 4087','147, 41, Tambon Bophut, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.thedeck-samui.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.709+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.709+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-deck-beach-club-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-deck-beach-club-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=890390207750410207',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-dining-room','standard','cmr07ii2b00vdq8xd6luaixt7','The Dining Room','## Top Reviews
> "The staff is very friendly and cheerful. The food offers a good variety. The setting is very pretty. The accommodations are quite modern and offer a view of the sea. I appreciate that this property keeps the pool facing the beach well-maintained. It’s a shame the jacuzzi isn’t working. Other than that, I recommend it 100%."
> **- serge restori (5/5/5)**

> "We had a truly wonderful time dining at Rocky''s Resort! The atmosphere is lovely, but what truly makes this restaurant stand out is the outstanding service and delicious food. The staff were incredibly friendly and competent throughout our stay. They were especially attentive to our needs as a family; every morning, they had a baby chair and baby cutlery ready for us without us even having to ask, which made our mornings so much easier and more relaxing. The breakfast buffet was fantastic—delicious and varied. Beyond the buffet, the made-to-order dishes and drinks were also excellent and offered great variety. We looked forward to breakfast every day! I also want to give a special mention to the service. Keaw, May and Eak are absolutely phenomenal! Also the service at the Pool was truly outstanding, with regular deliveries of fresh water and fruit right to our sun loungers. This kind of thoughtful, proactive service elevates the entire resort experience. We highly recommend it and will definitely be back!"
> **- Otis (5/5/5)**

> "We had a wonderful meal here for our wedding anniversary. The staff were soo lovely and really made an effort! The outdoor setting was beautiful, food and cocktails delicious, and they have happy hour from 6 to 8 which was great. Would highly recommend for a lovely meal in Samui."
> **- Georgia Parker (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-dining-room-1.jpg','077 332 888','Maret, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 6:00 – 10:30 AM, 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 6:00 – 10:30 AM, 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 6:00 – 10:30 AM, 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 6:00 – 10:30 AM, 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 6:00 – 10:30 AM, 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 6:00 – 10:30 AM, 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 6:00 – 10:30 AM, 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.715+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.715+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-dining-room-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-dining-room-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5627743116606370027',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-dive-academy','standard','cmr07ii2e00veq8xd9gnmszbp','The Dive Academy','## Top Reviews
> "My son and I had our first ever dive today with The Dive Academy. From the very beginning we felt safe and in good hands. Our instructor Bjørn made sure that we understood everything thoroughly before we got in the water and took his time to make us comfortable — both before we went under the surface and during the actual diving part. It was such an amazing experience for both my son and me. I would definitely recommend The Dive Academy to anyone who wants to experience the joy of diving while on Koh Samui. They are great for both adults and kids — I mean, my son would have us come back every year if it were up to him, because he had such a wonderful time thanks to the incredible team! 😊  Edited on October 14: The attached photos were taken by Leia while we were underwater. These are just a small selection of the many amazing pictures and videos she captured. She did an incredible job, and it’s so cool to have our trip immortalized this way!"
> **- Marlene Hansen (5/5/5)**

> "I went diving with the Dive Academy in Koh Samui at Sail Rock, and it was an absolutely fantastic experience.  Everything was perfectly organized and very well prepared. The briefing and debriefing were clear, structured, and helpful. The equipment was in excellent condition.  A special thanks to Dive Master José – with his calm and relaxed attitude, he made the dive truly enjoyable and ensured we felt safe at all times.  The dive itself was incredible – huge schools of fish like I had never seen before. Truly impressive!  Highly recommended – I would definitely dive with you again!"
> **- florian Stöckli (5/5/5)**

> "Very disappointing experience and highly unprofessional service.  Three days before my trip, I specifically asked whether Nitrox would be available and was assured that it would. On the actual dive day, however, I was told by the manager that the Nitrox machine was broken and that nobody was using Nitrox, except for me on one dive.  Once I boarded the boat, I discovered that this was not true. Almost everyone else was using Nitrox tanks for two of their dives, while I was the only diver who did not receive the Nitrox that had been promised during booking. Being given misleading information was extremely frustrating.  As a result, I had to end one of my dives after only 28 minutes due to air consumption limitations, which significantly impacted my diving experience.  The boat itself was dirty and poorly maintained. In addition, some of the guides appeared inexperienced. I was also picked up by a Myanmar driver who told me he was not allowed to drive me, which raised concerns about whether proper licensing and operational procedures were being followed.  Overall, the service was disorganized, misleading, and far below the standard I would expect from a professional dive operator. I would not recommend this company based on my experience."
> **- Ramita Mint (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-dive-academy-1.jpg','092 464 3264','157, 15, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.thediveacademysamui.com/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.718+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.718+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-dive-academy-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-dive-academy-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13359512355587780767',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-dogfather','standard','cmr07ii2h00vfq8xd35lh3emx','The Dogfather','## Top Reviews
> "We couldn’t recommend this dog hotel enough! Our dog absolutely loves staying here and gets excited every time we arrive, which says everything.  The owner is an experienced dog trainer who truly has the dogs’ best interests at heart. You can feel the care, knowledge, and attention that goes into everything they do. The staff are incredibly kind, attentive, and genuinely loving with all the dogs. It’s rare to find a place you can trust this much we always feel comfortable leaving our dog here. What we especially appreciate is that this place focuses on the well-being of the dogs above everything else. It feels so refreshing to find somewhere that prioritizes their happiness, comfort, and needs rather than just the aesthetic.  If you’re in Samui and need a dog hotel  this is definitely the place to go as it’s in the forest nice and cool plenty of odours for our furry friends, and they get to go on nice walks in nature ."
> **- MELISSA Aregger (5/5/5)**

> "A huge thank you to The Dogfather and team for looking after my two boys, Santi and Stout. From the moment we checked in, I could see how relaxed and comfortable they were with you — your calm, casual demeanor instantly showed your experience and care.  After two weeks away, I picked them up to find them both calm, happy, and clearly well looked after. Hearing your positive feedback about them made me proud, and it was reassuring to know they’d been in such good hands.  I would absolutely recommend The Dogfather and his team to anyone needing a safe, caring place to board or house their dogs while away. I’ll definitely be using your services again soon.  Once again, thank you from me, Santi, and Stout for your care and dedication. (Picture credit The Dogfather)"
> **- Steven Dicker (5/5/5)**

> "We boarded our dog Lola with Michael and his team at The Dogfather for a one-month board and train program. She’s an ex-street pup, sweet but boisterous, headstrong, chewing up everything in the house, barking a lot, escaping at every chance, and not responding to our training efforts.  When we visited her during the program, we were amazed. She was clearly happy, bonded with Michael, playing confidently with other dogs, and already responding to commands with consistency and discipline—even in the middle of play, which was incredible to see.  Since bringing her home, she’s like a new dog. She listens, follows commands, hardly tries to chew, and is overall calmer and more respectful of us as her leaders. It’s now up to us to maintain what she’s learned, but the foundation Michael gave her is rock solid.  If you’ve adopted a dog out of love but don’t have the time or skills to train properly, this training is the best gift you can give to your dog—and to yourself.  Happy dog owner here! 😁"
> **- A W (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-dogfather-1.jpg','081 787 3701','144/1 Moo 2 Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.thedogfathers.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 12:00 PM, 3:00 – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 12:00 PM, 3:00 – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 12:00 PM, 3:00 – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 12:00 PM, 3:00 – 6:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 12:00 PM, 3:00 – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 – 11:00 AM, 3:00 – 6:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.721+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.721+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-dogfather-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-dogfather-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2795697382315298991',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-dolphin-restaurant','standard','cmr07ii2m00vgq8xd4tnenowz','The Dolphin Restaurant','Discover The Dolphin Restaurant, a premier food and beverage located in Bang Rak, Koh Samui. Find reviews, hours, and contact information.',NULL,NULL,'FX6R+X8, Na Mueang, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,0.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.726+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.726+00:00',NULL,'https://maps.google.com/?cid=14597530513526450960',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-door','standard','cmr07ii2p00vhq8xdwz2qczuj','The Door','## Top Reviews
> "Absolutely the best beach bar in Koh Samui . The food is incredible . The DJ set almost also the best . The beach is clean and with a nice sea . The dessert to taste ! The Cheesecake ! We''ll be back !"
> **- Francesco baraldo sano (5/5/5)**

> "The Door is an exclusive place, a real treasure on Lamai Beach! Super DJ, great food, quality cocktails, friendly and professional staff! I’m happy that we found you! With love from Budapest: Noémi and Laci"
> **- Noémi (5/5/5)**

> "Very nice sunbeds next to the beach. You have to soend at least 2000baht to get a sunbed. We ate lunch and had a full day there, so the price was more expensive than other places, but their service and beds was also better than other places. Music was a bit too loud. The staff was always around, good service. The food was okay."
> **- Pablo Rosales (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-door-1.jpg','095 295 0606','33 14, Tambon Bo Put, koh samui Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.andabout.com/m/the-door-beach-bar-restaurant-829','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.729+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.729+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-door-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-door-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3639144185071627527',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-dreamcatcher-or-samui-sunset-hostel','standard','cmr07ii2r00viq8xdvtfduiss','The Dreamcatcher Or Samui Sunset Hostel','## Top Reviews
> "Such a great stay. Spent two nights here and had a chill time. The hostel is calm and right by the beach, and its a great place to start conversations with other travelers. Its not super fancy, but thats part of the charm. GG (the owner) is super kind and helpful, and she even offers cooking classes. The food was great too. There are also cats here, which are super friendly. Locationwise, its a walking distance to Nathon, however, I felt like there was not much to see in Nathon. My only negative about this hostel is that the matresses were a little bit too hard in my opinion. All in all, if you’re in the area, consider staying here."
> **- William (5/5/5)**

> "This is by FAR the best hostel I stayed at on the entire island—I’ve crashed on every side! It’s a spot where you can actually recharge, take it easy, breathe in the beautiful clean sea breeze, and soak up the good vibes. Gigi, the owner, is an absolute gem who goes out of her way to help and accommodate everyone. STAY HERE ❤️❤️❤️"
> **- Stefan Louw (5/5/5)**

> "Suuuch a cute, clean & cozy hostel ♡ perfect to relax and enjoy some quietness. Gigi and the whole staff is sooo nice and helps with any wish you have. A family feeling. Food also very good!"
> **- Lara-Sophie Weeber (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-dreamcatcher-or-samui-sunset-hostel-1.jpg','082 495 3988','179 3 ถ. ทวีราษฎร์ภักดี Tambon Ang Thong, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://dreamcatcher-hostel.com/room','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ig1h003iq8xdb1g9nifo','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.731+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.731+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-dreamcatcher-or-samui-sunset-hostel-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-dreamcatcher-or-samui-sunset-hostel-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8612015182830921871',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-driver-samui','standard','cmr07ii2u00vjq8xd3w126u9e','The Driver Samui','## Top Reviews
> "WOW! What an amazing, fun, informative tour we had. 100%! From the email/WhatsApp communications to the pick-up day, everything was excellent. We visited the sites that were of interest to us and even had time to explore others that our great guide suggested. I would DEFINTLY recommend Mr.Samui to anyone travel to Thailand"
> **- Ray M (5/5/5)**

> "Communication from booking, to the details and coordination of our tour was seamless. Mr Lam our tour guide/driver was very knowledgeable, kind and accommodating. He made sure that we were able to see our preferred spots when we’re in Koh Samui. The van was very comfortable, clean and water bottles as well as cold towels were provided. Highly recommended and will definitely book them again when I visit Koh Samui."
> **- Miche Mangio (5/5/5)**

> "Perfection! The best customised Koh Samui tour!  Fabulous customised tour for our 6 person family group! I specifically chose this tour because it was customisable for our mobility and location needs. We were not part of a cruise group, just wanted an island tour while on vacation in Koh Samui. From the beginning, communication and service was fantastic. The vehicle is absolutely luxe and seats super comfortable. All the amenities like chilled water, tissues, raincoats were provided. Our tour guide and driver, Mr. Thai was absolutely incredible and his 15+ years in the role made him a very adaptable and knowledgeable host. Mr. Thai was easily able to navigate my mum''s mobility restrictions and suggest experiences that would be easy access. We received lots of interesting information throughout and Mr. Thai was generous and considerate in every way! On our list were Capybara Cafe, Big Buddha, Wat Plai Laem, Guan Yu statue, Na Muang Waterfall 2 (flat entry) and local food markets and coconut grove. My family had a fantastic experience and everybody enjoyed the day. Thank you Mr. Thai and thank you Mr. Samui Tours. Highly recommend this family-owned and run business!  Tip: Make sure you take enough Thai baht for markets, food, temple donations etc. Mr. Thai helped us find an international ATM.  Tip: Mr. Thai knew all the best and cleanest (accommodating Western style) toilets on our trip!"
> **- Geraldine Zagallai (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-driver-samui-1.jpg','089 060 6440','18/8 Maenam beach, ตำบล แม่น้ำ Koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.mrsamui.com/?utm_source=google&utm_medium=wix_google_business_profile&utm_campaign=446829682331297474','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ig1n003kq8xd72v6yb3r','cmr07ig1h003iq8xdb1g9nifo','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.734+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.734+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-driver-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-driver-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8870519908725921201',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-edge','standard','cmr07ii2w00vkq8xdn9pvcvcz','The Edge','## Top Reviews
> "Great private dining experience at Six Senses by Ko Samui. A set tasting menu, but they will gladly cater for any dietary requirements or preferences. Option to either have champagne or sparkling wine included. Hopefully it isn''t cloudy and you will get an amazing sunset view."
> **- Martin Roberson (5/5/5)**

> "Perfect location for a romantic date night. Unobscured view of the ocean at the magic hours. There is only one table so there won’t be another else nearby. Staff members are awesome and provides great help. Both my partner and I really enjoyed the night. Highly recommend everyone to check this place out!"
> **- Rey Cheng (5/5/5)**

> "⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ The ultimate private dining in Samui  Came here for our anniversary and it was honestly perfect. I’ve tried quite a few high-end private dinners on the island, but this one is just on another level.  Most places say they’re "
> **- Chawisa NN (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-edge-1.jpg','077 245 678','Six Senses Samui Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.sixsenses.com/en/resorts/samui/dining/dining-by-the-edge/','["Monday: 5:00 – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 5:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 5:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 5:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 5:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 5:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 5:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.736+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.736+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-edge-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-edge-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5388459013983125975',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-fade-zone-barber-shop','standard','cmr07ii2y00vlq8xdik24o1gr','The Fade Zone Barber Shop','## Top Reviews
> "Ive been living in samui for over a year. The fade zone is definitely the best on the island and he cuts western hair perfectly. The owner is very professional and the haircuts are always consistent. Very well priced compared to other places and a much better service."
> **- Ollie Baglioni (5/5/5)**

> "My family member had an amazing experience; the results are stunning. The hairdresser really listened to his vision and offered expert advice on which fade and design would best suit his face. The salon was clean and had a very relaxing atmosphere with nice music in the background. He already received many compliments on the blend haircut! Highly recommend if you''re looking for high-quality service and a stylist who truly cares and is affordable!"
> **- ADAM TRAVIS (5/5/5)**

> "Very thorough and excellent haircut/moustache trim today.  Attention to detail was top notch and will go again."
> **- Dom Lanfear (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-fade-zone-barber-shop-1.jpg','063 964 9987','90 3, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.738+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.738+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-fade-zone-barber-shop-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-fade-zone-barber-shop-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5470395548103864753',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-fair-house-beach-resort-hotel','standard','cmr07ii3000vmq8xd590oykzv','The Fair House Beach Resort & Hotel','## Top Reviews
> "Not recommended at all. For this price you can find much better and more luxurious hotels. The rooms are indeed large but old and a little smelly. The staff is kind but that doesn''t make up for the tasteless food and the distance from good restaurants. We definitely won''t be back here. You can find a much better hotel"
> **- Tomer Levi (1/5/5)**

> "Good location, picturesque scenery. Landscape designer really did a great job, such a pleasure to look at.  The beach is wonderful, clear water and soft sand. Staff is nice and friendly. I would like to mention an amazing desk manager Nunna - you made our stay so much better ☺️ (sorry if i remembered your name wrong)  Would recommend for family vacation, there are a lot of amenities for kids and a lot of place to rest for adults."
> **- Мария Бурнашова (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing staff. I thank all the staff that served us, not even one person bring the staff quality less than 5 star. Everything is very cool in this hotel, but bring ear plugs for the night. We stayed in a bungalow and if the birds decide to chirp at 5 in the morning, you will hear it as it is near your bed. Unfortunately bungalows don’t have the best sound isolation."
> **- Sevket Sefer (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-fair-house-beach-resort-hotel-1.jpg','077 422 255','124-124/1-124/2, หาดเฉวงน้อย, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.fairhousesamui.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ig5c0051q8xdykrbexft','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.740+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.740+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-fair-house-beach-resort-hotel-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-fair-house-beach-resort-hotel-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6965945553677156190',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-fish-restaurant','standard','cmr07ii3200vnq8xd4op2kvgf','The Fish Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "Three years ago my wife and I tried this amazing Thai restaurant....and three years lately I returned with family to enjoy what I would say is the best Thai restaurant in Koh Samui.  The owner Chaw is the main chef at the restaurant, the food is truly a delicious experience and the presentation of all the different dishes is so elegant.  It''s so good we ate there twice in the 4 day trip.  The restaurant has a pretty seating area open air under the leaning bamboo trees which is so nice to eat in there.  Top picks are the Barracuda dish is expertly cooked and juicy, the king prawn dish has huge prawns and so tasty.  The sea bass with tamarind sauce is amazing, massaman curry is very rich and full of favor.  Out if the 10 or 12 dishes we tried, we would order them all again as each one is so unique and delicious.  Thank-you Chef Chaw for such an amazing dining experience.  You deserve a Michelin Star for the quality of food you make!  Amazing!"
> **- Derek (5/5/5)**

> "One of the best restaurants I’ve been to. I ordered the green curry, and it was amazing. I’m not usually a fan of spicy food, but I absolutely loved it. The flavor was rich, balanced, and mildly spicy. The staff were so nice and friendly. Highly recommended."
> **- Malikeh Salimi (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing food and the owner is so kind and friendly! We came here twice for dinner during our 4 night stay. If you have a bigger group, I would recommend making a reservation just to be safe!"
> **- Alyssa Victoria (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-fish-restaurant-1.jpg','087 472 4097','Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.tripadvisor.com/Restaurant_Review-g1182465-d7070856-Reviews-The_Fish_Restaurant_Mae_Nam-Mae_Nam_Ko_Samui_Surat_Thani_Province.html','["Monday: 11:30 AM – 10:30 PM","Tuesday: 11:30 AM – 10:30 PM","Wednesday: 11:30 AM – 10:30 PM","Thursday: 11:30 AM – 10:30 PM","Friday: 11:30 AM – 10:30 PM","Saturday: 11:30 AM – 10:30 PM","Sunday: 11:30 AM – 10:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.742+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.742+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-fish-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-fish-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12442503574477806568',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-florist-resort','standard','cmr07ii3400voq8xddauh8whw','The Florist Resort','## Top Reviews
> "First night we stayed in the 300 section, Unable to get cold water in the shower, pool was cooler. The next day we moved to 400’s, water was way too hot in the pool. The way the rooms are set up, if the neighbours have their lights on there is a door that connects the rooms and you see their light all night - so if lights are an issue for you this isn’t great. Pool is nice and deep though. The staff were friendly, price was right, cats were cute, nice and close to the beach and only ten min ride to fisherman’s village. There’s also a small food market every night near the hotel, it’s worth checking out!"
> **- Cathy (4/5/5)**

> "The staff are really friendly and make you feel at home, the beach guest house is literally right on the beach I can hear the waves!"
> **- Jehrone (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing place with a direct access to a nice beach. The staff was really nice and helpful in the réservation of some activities. I do recommend x3"
> **- Hugo Vinet (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-florist-resort-1.jpg','095 276 6981','195 3, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.744+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.744+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-florist-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-florist-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6754200968521867800',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-flow-samui-beach-resort','standard','cmr07ii3600vpq8xdsmh33geu','The Flow Samui Beach Resort','## Top Reviews
> "We really loved this place — honestly had such a great stay ❤️ The hotel is small, quiet, and right by the sea, which was a huge plus for us. We stayed for 9 days and had a really good, relaxing time.  To be honest, we didn’t expect much from a 3-star hotel, but the service was surprisingly great — that was a very nice surprise. The overall atmosphere and staff made it even better.  The food was tasty, and even though breakfast was quite simple, we genuinely enjoyed it — it had everything we needed.  The beach was good too: right in front of the hotel the entry is a bit rocky, but if you walk a little to the right, there’s a much nicer spot to get into the water. The water isn’t super clear because of the sandy/muddy bottom, but there were almost no waves, so it was still really enjoyable to swim.  Since the hotel is small, the level of quiet really depends on the guests. Most of the time it was very peaceful, but on our last day a noisy group arrived, which was a bit annoying — luckily, it was already our last day.  So just a small note for future guests: please be mindful of others and respect the quiet atmosphere — this isn’t a party hotel.  Overall, definitely a place we’d come back to 🌿"
> **- Sofia Maksimova (5/5/5)**

> "The sea view here is absolutely beautiful, with a full panoramic view that feels incredibly relaxing. It’s the perfect place to sit back, unwind, and enjoy the atmosphere. The food is delicious and of great quality. The pasta, in particular, was rich and flavorful, with fresh, well-cooked shrimp. Paired with crispy garlic bread, it was a perfect combination. The drinks were refreshing and easy to enjoy, making them ideal for a laid-back afternoon by the sea. What truly stood out was the service. Special thanks to Khun Korn and the entire team for the warm welcome from the moment we arrived. Everyone was polite, friendly, and attentive, which made the whole dining experience even more enjoyable. This is definitely one of the must-visit spots in Koh Samui, whether for the view, the food, or the overall ambiance. I’ll definitely be coming back next time to enjoy the day pass by the pool and spend more time relaxing here. 🌊✨"
> **- Supaporn Jamlek (5/5/5)**

> "Just wow. I’ve been visiting maenam beach for 10years and always enviously looked into the place!! Anyway fast forward to my first stay there. Beautiful rooms, all backing onto a slick pool. Really good food, happy hour cocktails. The highlight is the infinity pool looking out over the vast blue calm sea. Oh and at night the pool has beautiful sparkling lights in it! Will be back."
> **- Claire England (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-flow-samui-beach-resort-1.jpg','077 426 000','49, 35, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'http://theflowsamui.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.746+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.746+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-flow-samui-beach-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-flow-samui-beach-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4638705485493830439',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-frog-gecko-pub','standard','cmr07ii3900vqq8xdo5tbxjyo','The Frog & Gecko Pub','## Top Reviews
> "Draught beer for a great price. Seating at the bar and on the sea front. Really kind, fun service from all"
> **- Harry Morgan (5/5/5)**

> "We spent a couple weeks in Koh samui and this is our favourite pub by far. Great music and atmosphere. Drinks are well priced and has the best pool table we’ve found in Thailand bars. We will definitely be back one day !"
> **- Keaton Cook (5/5/5)**

> "Good for a social and casual food experience on the beach. Simple setting, plastic chairs. But huge food portions and the fish ‘n chips were good! The bar at street level can be a bit noisy and disturbing when having dinner but that’s up to each own to decide. Staff is friendly and price level very attractive for this area"
> **- Skycruiser Travel Channel (Eric) (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-frog-gecko-pub-1.jpg','098 023 8310','Thailand, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 3:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Tuesday: 3:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Wednesday: 3:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Thursday: 3:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Friday: 3:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Saturday: 3:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Sunday: 3:00 PM – 1:00 AM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.749+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.749+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-frog-gecko-pub-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-frog-gecko-pub-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2345259175963804590',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-gourmet-cookies','standard','cmr07ii3b00vrq8xdnq1jdll7','The Gourmet Cookies','## Top Reviews
> "A true hidden gem in Koh Samui! Weve had a variety of their cookies and their cinnamon rolls over the past 2 weeks we''ve been here and they never fail to disappoint! The nicest cookies and cinnamon rolls I''ve had, that good that we are taking some home with us.  When ordering pur baked goods  we had a quick response back confirming our order and great service when we went to collect them. The staff there are very polite and very helpful."
> **- Katie Norris-scott (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing, I recommend the birthday cake cookies even if it’s not your birthday. One bite and it will feel like it though. The owners speak very fluent Chinese so it was very easy for me, especially the male owner. I felt very safe in the area especially around the female owner, she looks like she does Jiu Jitsu, so felt very protected."
> **- Vaughn Friday (5/5/5)**

> "So yummy. I love this sweets. My favorite is the cinnamon roll. Best on Samui"
> **- Roza Toy (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-gourmet-cookies-1.jpg','081 078 0359','136 74 Thanon Had Lamai, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: Closed","Wednesday: Closed","Thursday: 9:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 9:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.751+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.751+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-gourmet-cookies-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-gourmet-cookies-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=18373878496867458669',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-halfway-house','standard','cmr07ii3c00vsq8xd2xlj66vp','The Halfway House','## Top Reviews
> "Perfect place for watching the football and cheap drinks. Ask John if you want a specific game and he’ll make it happen! 99 baht cocktails all night and a good crowd around you! Definitely recommend."
> **- Brendon Reynolds (5/5/5)**

> "Great spot for the sports, good selection of booze and great vibes"
> **- JD (5/5/5)**

> "Wonderful little pub which shows sport. Very friendly locals made us feel incredibly welcome."
> **- Jack Vaughn (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-halfway-house-1.jpg','099 401 5877','4169, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 4:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Tuesday: 4:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Wednesday: 4:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Thursday: 4:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Friday: 3:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Saturday: 4:00 PM – 1:00 AM","Sunday: 4:00 PM – 1:00 AM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.752+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.752+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-halfway-house-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-halfway-house-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11520425016724201571',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-hangout','standard','cmr07ii3e00vtq8xd4h9il9dj','The Hangout','## Top Reviews
> "You guys need to improve the live music band, before MHT had much better singers specially 2 girls (see photo attached), one very short and slim with an amazing voice she used to sing in Old School and also kongsiam and another one that likes to colour her hair pink or sometimes yellow. Give them a call, bring them back to HO, they were much better than the guys you have now. If you bring those female singers I will give 5 stars and tip accordingly to the quality of the singers and service ! If you have the best club you need the best singers!"
> **- Teng Mo (3/5/5)**

> "This is quite a cool little venue, staff are very welcome and friendly, I would say it''s more for Thia people or people who enjoy Thia music.  But I enjoyed my time"
> **- Stevo Success (4/5/5)**

> "I love to listen thai live music, yesterday I went there but unfortunately they didn''t let me entry saying "
> **- ALESSANDRO Fontana (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-hangout-1.jpg','092 516 8555','3, 226 หมู่ที่ 2 ตำบล บ่อผุด Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 PM – 3:30 AM","Tuesday: 9:00 PM – 3:30 AM","Wednesday: 9:00 PM – 3:30 AM","Thursday: 9:00 PM – 3:30 AM","Friday: 9:00 PM – 3:30 AM","Saturday: 9:00 PM – 3:30 AM","Sunday: 9:00 PM – 3:30 AM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.754+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.754+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-hangout-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-hangout-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15284105721333187316',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-height-restaurant','standard','cmr07ii3h00vuq8xd7hw9blmp','The Height Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "Absolutely great dining experience. We ate here twice and did a bit of the fixed menu the first night and changed it up for our final night. Chicken satay starter is extremely flavorful and perfectly prepared, we spooned the rest of the peanut and chili sauce when we finished. Beef massaman was fantastic, fried local greens and cashew chicken were a big hit also. Really fits the venue well and the executive chef went above and beyond both times we dined in. Going to miss this spot"
> **- Joe DeHart (5/5/5)**

> "We had an incredible experience at The Height. The traditional Thai cuisine was a delight, and Chef Manee took the time to provide insightful explanations about the dishes. The staff was friendly, and the service was of high quality. We found the best Thai food here, and the prices are reasonable compared to other places on the island. I highly recommend this restaurant for those seeking to savor traditional Thai cuisine with a culinary touch."
> **- Serhat Sozen (5/5/5)**

> "Perfect Thai food!  Top: fried rice with crab, Gang Poo Bai Cha Ploo, the soups and Massaman Gai / Nuea (it comes with roti)."
> **- J T (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-height-restaurant-1.jpg','077 960 555','F39C+739, Maret, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.silavadeeresort.com/dining/the-height-authentic-thai-cuisine-samui',NULL,'cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.757+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.757+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-height-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-height-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6680693055472519584',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-herbalist-dispensary-the-beach','standard','cmr07ii3k00vvq8xdg2pmwyih','The Herbalist Dispensary @ The Beach','## Top Reviews
> "Well the staff are very knowledgeable,  and the owner happened by and he too was into the science so to speak."
> **- Jono (5/5/5)**

> "An incredible spot for a great smoke herbal doctors at hand and all great smoke / they don’t serve you the display bud & you get a great service aswell.  Would love to come and stay at their hotel aswell."
> **- Kane Edwards (5/5/5)**

> "Great cannabis for great prices! The atmosphere is amazing. They are near the water and there are places to enjoy the products while you are there! Plus, they have regular meet and sample parties 🎉"
> **- Shirden (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-herbalist-dispensary-the-beach-1.jpg','077 234 657','30, Village, 23, Tambon Taling Ngam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.herbalist-samui.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07igdj008fq8xdhc2mye6x','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.760+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.760+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-herbalist-dispensary-the-beach-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-herbalist-dispensary-the-beach-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7705194640914413424',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-hideout-samui','standard','cmr07ii3l00vwq8xdfgoyxvub','The Hideout Samui','## Top Reviews
> "Really nice and modern place to stay with great owners! Lots of space outside to sit and enjoy and also an amazing pool. It''s also in a quiet area, so away from all the noise of the roads. Really peaceful!  For the price it''s a steal.  Be aware, though, that it''s a 20 min walk from the main road - so it''s a perfect place to stay when you have a scooter..."
> **- Magnus Meseck (5/5/5)**

> "Great hostel for the price!! Not sure what the bad reviews are about as we had a great stay. The hostel is really modern and clean and cosy. Clean towels provided, shared shower and bathroom equipped and also very clean.  The owner is very helpful - he got us a ped rental straight away for a good price, booked us transport for our next destination and was easily contactable through whatsapp.  The pool area is also vibes. It is also kept nice and clean. Even the cutest dogs.  Great stay for the price. Would recommend  Location is not too bad just a ped ride away"
> **- Katie Jackson (5/5/5)**

> "Beautiful place to stay, I stayed in 1bedroom villa whilst on Samui. Lovely rooms with facilities to cook, clean, cold aircon, smart TV. Pool is beautiful, place to sit in sun, owners sorted me out with everything - where to do laundry, had a bike delivered in 30mins, taxi to airport on departure. Can''t wait to stay here again, on top of it all, it is quiet set in the jungle (4mins ride to beach) and Is very well priced.  The backpackers accommodation looked nice too."
> **- Justin (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-hideout-samui-1.jpg','097 990 4176','15, 5, Tambon Mae Nam, Maenam, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.6,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.761+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.761+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-hideout-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-hideout-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4023221399818235281',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-hive','standard','cmr07ii3n00vxq8xdtygu095n','The Hive','## Top Reviews
> "We had a wonderful stay at this hotel in Koh Phangan. The location was perfect, making it easy to explore the island and enjoy the nearby beaches and attractions. The rooms were spotless, comfortable, and very well maintained throughout our stay.  The breakfast buffet was excellent, with a great variety of delicious options to choose from each morning. Most importantly, the staff were incredibly friendly, welcoming, and always happy to help with anything we needed.  We thoroughly enjoyed our stay and would happily return. Highly recommended!"
> **- Jana (5/5/5)**

> "The location on Lamai beach is according to us one of the beast. The restaurant is good. The breakfast is ok but could be better.. The rooms are ok, nothing special. Service is very good, friendly staaf and very helpful! We booked a standard double room, where the door was facing the Main Street. It was impossible to sleep without earplugs, the bars where playing music until 05:00 in the mornings.. I could stay here again but would have booked the villa instead! But If you take everything in to account, it’s very affordable."
> **- Adam Aasa (4/5/5)**

> "We loved staying at the Hive in Koh Samui. Am, Jamila and the team were so helpful. They helped us with everything from booking excursions, recommending restaurants, booking cars and so much more. Am went over and beyond for us, she is so helpful and we loved her seeing smiling face everyday. She even came to greet us the day we were leaving even though it was her day off.  The resort is perfect, the pool is right off the beach, the location is close to all of the restaurants, bars and shops in Lamai. The breakfast is excellent, we really enjoyed it everyday. The food and drinks at the restaurant and pool were also very good.  The rooms are set in a garden area with lots of birds and frogs. Our room was lovely, large and we could hear the waves from the ocean.  We will definitely stay at The Hive the next time we are in Koh Samui, which I hope is soon. We will also recommend to anyone we know who is going to Lamai Beach in Koh Samui."
> **- Rochelle Hussey (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-hive-1.jpg','077 424 550','124/264, Moo 3, Maret, Lamai Beach, ตำบล มะเร็ต อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.hivehotelsamui.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.763+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.763+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-hive-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-hive-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2935897918925938363',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-humble-villas','standard','cmr07ii3p00vyq8xdxlvteter','The Humble Villas','## Top Reviews
> "We had an absolutely wonderful stay at the Humble Villas in Koh Samui! We would especially like to highlight the incredibly friendly and attentive staff – both at the reception and during breakfast service. From the very first moment, you feel welcomed and well taken care of.  The rooms were very clean and well maintained. The small private pool was a real highlight – perfect for cooling off and simply relaxing.  The breakfast was also delicious and prepared with great care. Another big plus is the scooter rental service as well as the reliable taxi service, which makes exploring the island very convenient.  All in all, a clear recommendation – we would definitely come back anytime!"
> **- Antonio Graho (5/5/5)**

> "Everything was perfect expect the noise coming from the nearby road.  The people and service were  perfect. The room is perfect. The breakfast is perfect. It is very easy  to have a scooter delivered there.  But… the upper rooms are very noisy, we were in room 3 and we could hear the cars and scooters passing. I had to sleep with eat plugs all the time.  So my advice ask for any room but not rooms 1,2,3 and 4, as they are noisy."
> **- Joel Gros (4/5/5)**

> "I cannot stress enough how utterly awesome this place is. Each bungalow has a private plunge pool, a sunset view, and is right on the beach for quick access. The breakfast is absolutely spectacular, your choice of everything from Thai to eggs Benedict. The beds are very soft and the rooms have air conditioning. Will definitely come back here again. Btw if you enjoy good cooking and travel videos, please subscribe to cuisinequest on YouTube, no regrets!"
> **- Cuisine Quest (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-humble-villas-1.jpg','065 403 8552','The Humble Villas 57/87 หมู่ที่ 5 Tambon Ang Thong, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://thehumblevillas.top/','["Monday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 6:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifxh0027q8xde6xqk8o6','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.765+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.765+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-humble-villas-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-humble-villas-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=18286967250578995989',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-island-view-restaurant','standard','cmr07ii3s00vzq8xdpzb04xh5','The Island View Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "Wonderful lunch with an amazing view We had lunch at Island View Restaurant and it was a great experience. The setting is absolutely beautiful, right by the sea, with a stunning view that makes the meal even more enjoyable. The food was very good, fresh and flavorful, with well-prepared Thai dishes. The service was friendly and attentive, and the atmosphere was calm and relaxing. A perfect place for a pleasant lunch in Koh Samui. Highly recommended!"
> **- Tom Nodal (5/5/5)**

> "One of the most amazing places to watch the sunset in a chill atmosphere. Amazing food - the fish & chips was particularly tasty (which says a lot in my experience). The cocktails are also of a surprisingly high level, especialy for a reasonable price. And the staff is friendly and professional. This place is a hidden gem where you''ll want to come again and again !!"
> **- Frédéric Vieille (5/5/5)**

> "If you’re visiting Koh Samui, this spot is an absolute must-try! From the moment you arrive, you’re welcomed by a team that is genuinely warm, attentive, and thoughtful, making the whole experience even more special. The food is fantastic, and I especially recommend the seafood dishes — they’re fresh, flavorful, and beautifully prepared. They also offer a great happy hour every day from 5–6pm with a buy-one-get-one-free cocktail deal, and the cocktails are absolutely delicious.  What truly made our visit unforgettable, though, was the owner. She went above and beyond to make us feel at home, always taking the time to chat and share a laugh. Her kindness and hospitality really stole the show. We can’t wait to come back!"
> **- Bence Uzoni (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-island-view-restaurant-1.jpg','077 426 422','348 หมู่ที่ 3 Nara-Taling-Ngam Rd, Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://theislandviewrestaurant.com/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ift8000pq8xd7yujz20i','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.768+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.768+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-island-view-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-island-view-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14907548201526798785',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-jolly-fisherman','standard','cmr07ii3u00w0q8xd1pat6iwn','The Jolly Fisherman','## Top Reviews
> "Nice Service, Lovely Beer Garden with shade, a few craft ale cans in the Fridge, not as stocked as the Menu shows but I can understand supply chain issues out here, Punk IPA has been (I think) on DRAUGHT on the bar but sadly it had ran out (not featured in the current Menu as of Feb 25). You can see that the owners have invested in this place, lovely service, and lovely touch with cooled flannels in a hot 32 Degree day. Nice and Thanks The Jolly Fisherman, Thanks."
> **- TRAVEL MAN (5/5/5)**

> "Staying over road at B1 Beach Apartments and found this place quickly. Popped in for a quick Friday night drink and stayed for a few. The owner was very friendly and chatted with us. The drinks were great. Lots of choice and the bar man even made me a special one according to my taste. We even managed to get a shot of real tequila rose. Great live music from 8pm, but still able to sit and chat without too much noise (yes we are getting old). Will definitely be back, maybe to sample the fish and chips or the new cinema venture. Claire & Pete x"
> **- Claire Heywood (5/5/5)**

> "Popped in this afternoon to see some friends, always meant to stop in but never did, got to chat with the owner Luke, really pleasent and extremely likeable chap. The service was great, even with the torrential downpour it was still a great place to stop in, grab some food and have a beer."
> **- Kevin H (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-jolly-fisherman-1.jpg','083 459 6310','77, 3, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/JollyFishermanSamui',NULL,'cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.770+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.770+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-jolly-fisherman-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-jolly-fisherman-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1861876161781358679',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-jungle-club','standard','cmr07ii3x00w1q8xdt0mb6ipa','The Jungle Club','## Top Reviews
> "such amazing service and kindness from everyone! our waiter was so so lovely and very personal. Drinks were good and not watered down / weak at all 👏 and food was sooo good, ordered the pad thai and fried rice and was really really flavourful! the vibe was so nice , not loud music or distasteful music, we arrived around 6-7pm and didn’t have to wait / nor had to reserve! If you are thinking of going, do it! it was truly a highlight of our trip in Koh Samui 🤍  Do be mindful there is a shuttle for some grabs/bolts that can’t make it to the top."
> **- Manishka Sharma (5/5/5)**

> "The food was absolutely delicious. We chose Pad Thai and Tom Yum Goong soup – both were excellent. The spring rolls were also very good. The way up was a bit steep, but we managed it easily on the scooter with two people. For dessert, we had mango sticky rice, which was amazing. In total, we paid 1,500 baht. Overall, it is quite a touristy place, but I would definitely come back just for the food. It’s really highly recommended. In the evening, the view is absolutely stunning."
> **- Leni Skodi (5/5/5)**

> "A beautiful café with one of the best environments in Koh Samui! 😍 The jungle vibe, scenic seating, and peaceful atmosphere make this place really special.  I would highly recommend booking a seat before coming, otherwise you may have to wait a long time or sit at the bar table. 🪑  The sunset view is absolutely amazing, and it’s one of the few places near Chaweng Beach where you can enjoy such a perfect sunset view. 🌄 Definitely worth visiting at least once for the experience! ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐"
> **- Mehul Batra (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-jungle-club-1.jpg','081 894 2327','44, 11 หมู่ที่ 3 ตําบล, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.jungleclubsamui.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig5c0051q8xdykrbexft','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.773+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.773+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-jungle-club-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-jungle-club-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2672342747940986450',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-kids-club','standard','cmr07ii3z00w2q8xdx6fif58m','The Kids Club','## Top Reviews
> "I highly recommend Star Kids kindergarten! We''ve been living in Koh Samui for a long time; our daughter is 4.5 years old, and this kindergarten is now our second home! We started with half-day visits, but picking her up was incredibly difficult each time! She wanted to stay longer and longer, and all we could talk about was when to go home! Now we attend full-day visits, and even the evening shift, so we''re here from opening until the very end. The true heart of this kindergarten is its founders and teachers: Maryana, Sasha, Ksyusha, Olechka, and Seya! How much love must you have for what you do to turn a simple kindergarten into a place where we''ve practically become a family? 😍 The constant photo and video reports in the general parent chat are a soothing balm for me as an anxious mother! Any question can be asked in the chat, and the answer is instant! Special thanks for that! After all, the day is planned out so that the children have a truly interesting time at the kindergarten! And it''s not just games; it''s also preparation for school, English lessons with a native speaker from the US, learning about the world around us, dancing, gymnastics, acting, not to mention the endless crafts, drawing, modeling, and everything else! Overall, we''re absolutely thrilled with everything; I don''t even know what else we could want from the preschool! We wish the preschool prosperity, development, and all the very best to everyone involved in this wonderful place!"
> **- Olga Mazalova (5/5/5)**

> "My three-year-old adores StarKids preschool!!! Every morning he runs there with joy: "
> **- Виктория Мишланова (5/5/5)**

> "This kindergarten on Koh Samui was a real find for our family. Our daughter is three years old, and we decided to try enrolling her in a kindergarten while on vacation—it was a new and somewhat nerve-wracking experience. But from the very first day, it was clear we''d made the right choice. The atmosphere here is very warm and welcoming. The teachers genuinely love the children, treat them with care and respect, and help them adapt gently and feel confident. Our child was always surrounded by attention, support, and kindness. I really regret that we didn''t find out about this kindergarten sooner! 🥹🙌🏻"
> **- Виктория Ким (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-kids-club-1.jpg','093 835 3008','58 1 ตำบล แม่น้ำ Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.775+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.775+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-kids-club-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-kids-club-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4973328457932252144',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-library','standard','cmr07ii4200w3q8xd3n6l8me1','The Library','## Top Reviews
> "Our stay at The Library Koh Samui was absolutely exceptional. The hotel is beautifully designed, with a unique atmosphere and an amazing beachfront location. The rooms were spacious, comfortable, and impeccably maintained, making our stay truly relaxing.  A special thank you to Dear, who provided outstanding service throughout our visit. Dear was incredibly friendly, attentive, and always willing to help with a warm smile. Their professionalism and genuine hospitality made our experience even more memorable and made us feel truly valued as guests.  The food, facilities, and overall service exceeded our expectations. We highly recommend The Library Koh Samui to anyone looking for a luxurious and unforgettable stay in Koh Samui. We look forward to returning in the future."
> **- Saeed A (5/5/5)**

> "A super hotel with great service. I really appreciated two pools, one labeled «quiet pool» only surrounded by adults. Great and comfortable sun beds with generous amount of towels and complimentary servings of fruit and juice once per day. Breakfast is fantastic, not buffet style but orders taken from a rich menu with a lot to offer. Rooms are kept nice even if the hotel is old. The bed was comfortable and bathroom big and nice. I stayed at a Page room at second floor with a private balcony that was nice for early mornings and evenings. Library sits directly on the beach allowing for ocean swims and beach walks any time of day. I really enjoyed my stay and would love to come back."
> **- Mona Jensen (5/5/5)**

> "The Library Koh Samui is one of those rare places that feels like a concept and a real retreat — I’ve stayed three times now, and it keeps pulling me back. It’s a design hotel built like a book: the “content” starts at reception, the rooms are the “pages,” and the villas feel like secret chapters with their own special atmosphere. And then there’s the iconic red pool — alone worth the stay. An oasis right on Chaweng Beach, but tucked away from the noise and chaos.  What I love most is what it gives me: creative energy and the space to write. Breakfast is à la carte, which instantly brings calm to the morning — no buffet rush, just good coffee and a quiet start to the day. Service is attentive and exactly on point: present when you need it, never over the top.  It’s a small design hotel without the attitude of a big luxury brand — and that’s precisely the charm. Every time I leave, I feel genuinely rested, grounded, and already looking forward to coming back."
> **- Tominffm (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-library-1.jpg','077 422 767','14 1 ตำบล บ่อผุด Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.thelibrarysamui.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: 12:00 AM – 11:59 PM","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.778+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.778+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-library-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-library-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8684707748716364934',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-life-aquatic-dive-center','standard','cmr07ii4400w4q8xdhefrzu40','The Life Aquatic Dive Center','## Top Reviews
> "Me and my friends had an amazing experience diving with Life Aquatic! I booked two days of fun dive for myself and Open Water course for my friends who wanted to certify. Our instructor Tan was incredibly kind, calm and funny while being extremely experienced! He made my friends feeing relaxed and safe during all training in the sea, not to mention made us all laugh a lot ☺️ Diving through small caves was definitely a bonus we did not expect! The organisation by Jo was spotless start to finish, we really appreciated pick up and drop off service (even though we stayed on the other side of the island). Well deserved 5 stars ⭐️ highly recommend!"
> **- Maria Popravko (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing diving experience. Everything went smoothly and safely. The boat crew was extremely helpful and quick to assist, keeping everything organized. All the diving equipment was assembled and prepared for you in advance.  I dived near Koh Tao Island at two locations close to each other. We traveled to the dive sites by a comfortable speedboat.  Highly recommended!"
> **- Jakub Klata (5/5/5)**

> "I dived recently with Jo and his team at Sail Rock. It was a bit more on the expensive side compared to Koh Tao and even Australian prices but the level of service matched the cost. It’s a fair distance by boat to the dive site and we had a good quality boat and crew. Equipment was prepared in advance based on sizing, was good quality and set up and changed over for you which was an unexpected bonus. Lunch was delicious, prepackaged local Thai dishes I had Pad-sew and I think it might have been the best one I had all trip. After only recently completing my Advance Course I felt safe and well looked after. They didn’t automatically supply a dive watch but when I requested one they happily accommodated with a spare. The dive itself was worth the trip. By far my favourite dive to date with exceptional amounts of life at the rock. Jo shot GoPro footage and supplied quickly after which was another appreciated value add. I also really valued that when a fellow diver chewed through his air quickly (approx 20mins) Jo managed the situation professionally and took the diver back to the boat without cutting our dive short. Thanks for a great experience."
> **- Sarah Butler (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-life-aquatic-dive-center-1.jpg','061 209 3664','moo 1 2/86 TAMBON bophut, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.thelifeaquatic.asia/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.780+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.780+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-life-aquatic-dive-center-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-life-aquatic-dive-center-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1255022085943902831',NULL,NULL);
