INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-nanny','standard','cmr07ii4q00weq8xd7kf9utqh','The Nanny','## Top Reviews
> "Our 14-month-old twins found wonderful caregivers—and true friends—thanks to Rattana. Rattana and her assistants supported our family for three weeks during our stay in Ko Samui, and the experience was exceptional.  The boys genuinely loved spending time with them, which gave us complete peace of mind when leaving them in Rattana’s care. They enjoyed a wide variety of games and activities, all thoughtfully adapted to their interests and energy levels.  Rattana was consistently flexible and accommodating, readily adjusting to our changing schedule and needs. We are truly grateful to have met her and to have experienced such reliable, caring, and attentive childcare.  I highly recommend Rattana’s babysitting service to any family looking for a thoughtful, responsible, and trustworthy caregivers."
> **- Karina Collis (5/5/5)**

> "I had the service of Mam. The nanny service was for 8 days (8 hours/day) for my 11-month-old baby, and I couldn’t be happier. She was incredibly gentle, kind, and patient with my little one always positive and easygoing no matter the situation. My baby was in safe, loving hands. Highly recommend to any parent looking for a trustworthy and caring nanny! ❤️"
> **- Lienchi Lê (5/5/5)**

> "Exceptional Care from Samui Nanny Service - A Truly Heartfelt Experience  We had the most wonderful experience with Samui Nanny Service, entrusting our 1‑year‑old daughter to Nanny Mam. From the very first moment, we felt completely at ease. The entire process was smooth, professional, and incredibly kind.  Mam herself is a rare gem: warm, flexible, reliable, and deeply trustworthy. She cared for our daughter with genuine love, attention, and tenderness. It was clear every single day that she wasn’t just “doing a job” - she was giving her heart.  What touched us most was the emotional bond she built with our little girl."
> **- Friederike Rhein (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-nanny-1.jpg','093 962 6505','3, 88, Tambon Bo Put, Koh Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://samuinanny.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.802+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.802+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-nanny-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-nanny-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4237172628428763785',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-natives-samui','standard','cmr07ii4t00wfq8xd9c075831','The Natives Samui','## Top Reviews
> "Traditional villas set right next to the sea. Very spacious and high quality furnishings. Some minor points can be observed such as visible service areas around the grounds and a few screws and bolts could do with tightening up around the villa but over all an exceptional home from home in traditional Thai style. It’s like Samui probably was 30 years ago but with air conditioning, toilet roll, WiFi and Netflix. If you’re looking for a comfortable, spacious and private accommodation away from the busy areas then this is highly recommended."
> **- Alan Bond (4/5/5)**

> "Just a perfect and lovely place with full privacy. Thai style villa with own garden and entry to the sea plus shared pool (renovated). Amazing authentic breakfast. On top of that, they do their own sourdough bread. Nice and lovely people, fully recommended for couples as well as for the families. Thank you."
> **- Richard Král (5/5/5)**

> "So this place had a great view and location for a great price. The breakfast was amazing so I''d recommend opting for it. If you can, get the beach villa if you''re like me and want to have a deck looking at the ocean and within walking distance. Almost perfect, but you should know it''s not the best for swimming as there are rocks/(coral?) close to the beach, but it''s doable for kids and adults, just can''t go too far out. For a softer beach experience, you only need to walk about 50 meters to the left facing the ocean. I found a great "
> **- Nathan Johnson (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-natives-samui-1.jpg','086 670 0659','3 Maenam 25, Tambon Mae Nam, Koh Samui Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.thenativessamui.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifs1000cq8xdfo2aau32','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.805+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.805+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-natives-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-natives-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15975195379945354011',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-new-french-kiss','standard','cmr07ii4v00wgq8xdg1d0k38v','The New French Kiss','## Top Reviews
> "The New French Kiss sets a high bar—and clears it comfortably.  Tony is an exceptional host. No theatrics, just sharp awareness, good timing, and genuine care. You feel looked after without it ever becoming intrusive. That’s professional hospitality.  The food is superb. Well-balanced, properly executed, and clearly built on quality ingredients rather than gimmicks. Each plate lands exactly where it should—confident and clean.  The setting does a lot of heavy lifting too. The view is outstanding, and it elevates the whole experience from “good meal” to something more memorable. At one point I was even fishing directly from the restaurant—caught a squid, returned it (we’d already eaten and were heading out), but it says everything about the place. It’s not just dinner, it’s an experience.  Bottom line: The New French Kiss isn’t trying too hard—it just gets it right."
> **- Anura Hotel (5/5/5)**

> "Ate here one night after completing all of the restaurants at the Conrad.  The food was fresh, had nice flavours and came very quick.  If you want a nice location looking out to the ocean , good local food (with European options available) it’s worth popping down.  We had squid and spring rolls to start Chicken penang curry Chicken and cashew nut Noddles with shrimp Which came with 2 large portions of rice Profiterolls and the frozen macron  And a couple of drinks which came to B2100 which was quite pricy for local food but a lot cheaper than the Conrad"
> **- D B (4/5/5)**

> "This restaurant is amazing, the food is so so good. We tried a Pad Thai and French fries and were the best of all our trip. The place is so magic and authentic, you can have the bests sunsets there. Also, the staff is so nice and they have some little doggy’s super cute. I recommend a lot this restaurant, we will repeat for sure!"
> **- ainhoa Dorca (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-new-french-kiss-1.jpg','098 416 1211','Koh Samui, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 12:00 – 8:30 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 8:30 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 8:30 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 8:30 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 8:30 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: 12:00 – 8:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ihdd00loq8xde04nm02v','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.807+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.807+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-new-french-kiss-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-new-french-kiss-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10484961309190397221',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-outback-cafe','standard','cmr07ii4z00whq8xdh7qklkpq','The Outback Cafe','## Top Reviews
> "Probably the best full English breakfast on  the island, good coffee too."
> **- Darren Horrocks (5/5/5)**

> "We always enjoy coming here for delicious food and fabulous service. I highly recommend."
> **- Ruth Brock (5/5/5)**

> "Not a bad little place for breakfast. Prices are very similar to the rest of the area, not cheap but not silly expensive. The bacon and egg toast was good, the sausages were very good for Thailand. The outback coffee was nice, very sweet, and the strawberry smoothie was really nice. Decent cafe, lots of cats around too."
> **- Isaac Davy-Day (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-outback-cafe-1.jpg','089 727 7757','123, 1, Tambon Lipa Noi, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.811+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.811+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-outback-cafe-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-outback-cafe-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11554079797276232706',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-oyster-bar-x','standard','cmr07ii5100wiq8xdlzev4dhm','The Oyster Bar X','## Top Reviews
> "An absolute highlight on Koh Samui. The Oyster Bar is a true paradise for oyster lovers. The oysters are incredibly fresh, perfectly chilled, and full of flavor. You can really taste the quality with every bite. What makes the experience even better is the large selection of different toppings, from classic options to more creative combinations, which makes tasting the oysters especially fun.  The atmosphere is relaxed and welcoming, and the quality of the food speaks for itself. Without a doubt, the Oyster Bar is a must place to visit when you are on Koh Samui, especially if you love fresh seafood."
> **- Philipp Gärtner-Uszkai (5/5/5)**

> "I am used to go Samui for more than 20 years but this Oyster Bar is really amazing. Fresh Oyster, delicious escalope, a very good selection of wines and the staff is always kind and ready to assist you with any info you need regarding their excellent food. Even the Octopus was superlative 😍😍😍"
> **- Massimo Gobbi (5/5/5)**

> "Had a really enjoyable dinner here during our Samui trip 😊  The atmosphere was relaxing, staff were friendly and attentive, and the overall dining experience was very comfortable. Food quality was solid and nicely presented, especially the seafood dishes which were fresh and tasty.  A great place to chill with good food and nice vibes in Koh Samui. Would definitely consider coming back again next time!  Highly recommended 👍"
> **- Jerry Fung (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-oyster-bar-x-1.jpg','087 389 9989','84/34 M.3, ถนน หาดละไม ตำบล มะเร็ต Koh Samui, สุราษฎร์ธานี 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.theoysterbarx.com/','["Monday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Friday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 5:00 – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.813+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.813+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-oyster-bar-x-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-oyster-bar-x-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15871648718262463981',NULL,NULL);
