INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-pizza-company','standard','cmr07ii5f00wnq8xdqb9thtnz','The Pizza Company','## Top Reviews
> "Food was nice (but quite expensive) and the staff were nice and helpful. A medium (6 slices) meat pizza with a cheesy crust was 520 baht ... about AUD$25."
> **- Craig Gibbons (4/5/5)**

> "Don''t repeat my mistake. I don''t know what I was hoping for, thinking that it would be better to eat pizza in a pizzeria than at the food market nearby. This is definitely not pizza. You can''t eat this. The menu shows how the cheese stretches and clearly describes how many types of cheese are in this pizza. I think my photos show what you''ll actually get."
> **- Lana Panasenko (1/5/5)**

> "Nice pizza company branch, Nice Pizzas. Many things were finished, like large pizza and some toppings. Pork steak was nice. The kitchen staff did better than the waitress. Not that great service."
