INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-proud-therapeutic-massage','standard','cmr07ii5n00wqq8xdp288v97b','The Proud Therapeutic Massage','## Top Reviews
> "Mouse is probably the best massage therapist I’ve ever experienced. She’s extremely professional and will melt away any built-up pain and tension in your body. You won’t regret it—I promise. Go book an appointment with her!"
> **- Stefan Louw (5/5/5)**

> "Great place for massage. Nice clean clinic with AC. The lady who works there is true professional, my body felt so good after the massage which had very special techniques. You need to make an appointment, and it’s not always available for the same day appointment."
> **- Veronica Zauharodniaya (5/5/5)**

> "I had back pain for five months, and nothing helped—not physiotherapy, not other massages—until I came here. In just one session, she worked magic and completely fixed it. Before starting she really takes her time to ask about the issues and get an overview of the situation. Her technique is incredible, deep, and precise, and you can tell she really knows what she’s doing. I’m beyond grateful and would recommend her to anyone looking for real healing."
> **- Paula Schotte (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-proud-therapeutic-massage-1.jpg','094 969 5000','68 ตลิ่งงาม 4 ตำบล แม่น้ำ Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ig0w003aq8xdfi0rydaw','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.835+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.835+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-proud-therapeutic-massage-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-proud-therapeutic-massage-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7261068747638016238',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-pug-house-samui','standard','cmr07ii5p00wrq8xdwatx26d2','The Pug House Samui','## Top Reviews
> "Great place to chill with cute pugs running about. The owners really care about the pugs, it feels like it’s her own dogs, and not for show/business at all.  Entry price is 100 per person but you get to stay as much as you like and they have really great drinks as well you can buy (you are not required to)  The dogs seem very happy and clean and chill, and always happy to have guests to pet them.  We’ve been here twice and I would be every day if I could."
> **- Noam Akselbant (5/5/5)**

> "⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ Amazing experience for dog lovers!  The Pug House Samui is such a lovely place! The dogs are incredibly friendly, well cared for, and clearly loved. You can really see how happy and relaxed they are, which makes the whole experience even more special.  The staff are kind, welcoming, and very attentive. They take great care of both the dogs and the guests, and they are happy to answer any questions. The café itself is clean, cozy, and well organized.  If you love dogs (especially pugs), this place is an absolute must-visit when you’re in Koh Samui. It’s a heart-warming and unforgettable experience. Highly recommended!"
> **- Witek Ustijanowski (5/5/5)**

> "I’m a local from Samui and can’t believe I only just discovered this place, it’s absolutely amazing! A lovely dog café right by the beach with the cutest, friendliest pugs who are clearly well cared for.  The atmosphere is relaxed with a beautiful sea view, perfect for unwinding. Drinks and food are decent, and the staff are warm and welcoming.  Such a hidden gem and a must visit for dog lovers in Samui! 🤎🐶🐾🫶🏻"
> **- Mint Mint (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-pug-house-samui-1.jpg',NULL,'27, 14, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/thepughousesamui?mibextid=JRoKGi','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: Closed","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.837+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.837+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-pug-house-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-pug-house-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5487132329629290945',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-quienest-project','standard','cmr07ii5t00wsq8xdporsvjo6','The Quienest Project','## Top Reviews
> "I celebrated my birthday here, and you know it''s one of my happiest birthdays. I don''t regret that we chose this place for romantic dinner for me and my husband. Here is a lovely atmosphere, nice music, great food (I just recommend a seafood set with lobster, it''s so delicious) and amazing, very friendly staff. The manager is funny, very energetic, and charismatic. There is a high level of service here. You feel special here, really."
> **- Ksenia Okuntseva (5/5/5)**

> "Its absolutely amazing beach and this restaurant is right where it belongs. The food, the service is outstanding! I would highly recommend to visit it!"
> **- Markus V (5/5/5)**

> "We have been there twice and are absolutely amazed. Diner directly on the beach is great. Highly recommended 👍 👌"
> **- Lupo 25 (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-quienest-project-1.jpg','+66630761271','Bo Put, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'http://facebook.com/baydayproject','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.841+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.841+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-quienest-project-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-quienest-project-2.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-quienest-project-3.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-quienest-project-4.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7518224338280488296',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-rainbow-club','standard','cmr07ii5w00wtq8xdwy1ia44k','The Rainbow Club','## Top Reviews
> "A nice place to go there with your kids... The kids will like it... The facility is colorful and nicely done! 👍🏻 😊 There are some events, you should ask in advance when they be in progress! Also ask if the beverages shop is open, otherwise you have to bring your own drinks! 😉 Don''t forget a mosquito protection for you and the children!!! As a small criticism is allowed... but little renovation would be good in various places. Seen through the eyes of an adult. 😉  PS. Admission and playing is not all for free, you have to pay a contribution!"
> **- Michael W. (4/5/5)**

> "This place is the most magical, pure, and beautiful on this island! It''s an amazing spot with a stunning view on the beach . My kids loooove to spend their time there , so colourful and calm place ... they have art workshops for kids and adults . It''s just perfect.  This island needs this place ❤️🌈 thank you for the great time, Mulamati"
> **- מורן דדון (5/5/5)**

> "This place bring all the joy for kids and take my inner child out!  The location is the best for family and lovely people. Many interesting activities and event with creative and craft talent."
> **- MQ madamm (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-rainbow-club-1.jpg','083 970 0057','Taling Ngam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61552697826707','["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: Closed","Wednesday: Closed","Thursday: Closed","Friday: 11:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.844+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.844+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-rainbow-club-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-rainbow-club-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15919808211154930172',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-reef-bar-restaurant','standard','cmr07ii5y00wuq8xd8k519loz','The Reef Bar & Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "We find this place completely on accident, kind of. We looked on Google maps and picked this place and what a great choice it was. Wonderful secluded location and great staff. Don''t come here, it''s ours lol"
> **- Simon Walker (5/5/5)**

> "This is a hidden gem of Samui, secluded and peaceful bar by the beach  Staffs were friendly, they are newly opened.  If you love time away from the crowded places, don’t hesitate just come and chill here  This is truly a hidden gem"
> **- varin khanijou (5/5/5)**

> "You have to try the software shell tacos, ice cold beer, the bar is in a great spot on the beach. Great for families plenty of space for the kids to run around whilst mum and dad enjoy a relaxing drink"
> **- Peter Taggart (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-reef-bar-restaurant-1.jpg','098 047 4598','ชายหาดสาธารณะแหลมสอ Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 12:00 – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 9:00 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 12:00 – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifzl002uq8xdaadxjuc2','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.846+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.846+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-reef-bar-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-reef-bar-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5074108492363375166',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-road-less-travelled','standard','cmr07ii6000wvq8xdqdgjw618','The Road Less Travelled','## Top Reviews
> "Amazing brunch spot! I got the breakfast burrito and it was so delicious and filling. The pumpkin was a great add. The staff really makes the place though! Such amazing service all thoughout. They take card but there is a 3% charge. Totally a must if you are about to board a ferry or just got off!"
> **- Mariel C (5/5/5)**

> "A truly wonderful place! We really enjoyed everything. The interior is very interesting and the design is beautiful and well thought out. The atmosphere is cozy and very pleasant.  I would especially like to mention the service — it is at a very high level. The staff speak excellent English and are very attentive and friendly.  Also, the owner is a very pleasant and welcoming person — very friendly, neat, and professional, which creates a great impression of the place.  The food was delicious and the coffee was excellent. Overall, everything deserves the highest rating. We are very happy that we visited this place and will definitely come back many times!"
> **- Maxim Hiro (5/5/5)**

> "What a beautiful place to start the day. Food was delicious and served with love and attention. Peter your Team are an absolute inspiration, so pleasant and genuinely interested in your customers. Thanks for the chat, a girl from Liverpool always loves a good conversation. Definitely will be back. Ps the magic slice certainly lives up to its name."
> **- Jo Brown (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-road-less-travelled-1.jpg','061 196 9882','11/2 3 Angthong 11, Tambon Ang Thong, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/The-Road-Less-Travelled-Samui-2362963547261252/','["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig1h003iq8xdb1g9nifo','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.848+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.848+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-road-less-travelled-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-road-less-travelled-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17647424006701258157',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-roof-samui','standard','cmr07ii6200wwq8xd4bawfqd1','The Roof Samui','## Top Reviews
> "The drive up: saw some reviews talking about how terrifying it was and it almost put us off, but so glad we went. The 4x4 shuttle feels safe and the roads are smoothly paved - it’s just super steep up/down. Definitely don’t attempt the drive yourself.  Order immediately upon arrival if having food. Took 50 mins from we ordered and it wasn’t even busy. The food was mixed but I enjoyed my green curry dish. You can also go just for a drink, they have a huge selection.  Overall: The views are amazing and I recommend going for sunset to see it both in daylight and lit up. The restaurant itself is lovely and worth a visit if only for a drink.  Also: book in advance. Would be a shame to make it up there and have to turn around. We were a group of 11 (5 small kids under 5yo and they still gave us an amazing table with “proper” chairs - not bean bags)."
> **- H_barko (4/5/5)**

> "We had a lovely time at the bar - a little expensive but what you would expect for the view. Food was delicious. Our only issue was a large German family of maybe 14 who ruined the experience for a lot of people. They let their kids run around whilst they sat down having dinner, screaming into the fans and jumping on the netting and throwing cushions. My issue is 1 the parents were sitting at the table and there was more than enough adults to watch them and that the staff did nothing even though they spotted this behaviour ruining other dinners experience. To add to this when it came to leaving the whole family pushed in front of us when it came to getting the shuttle down the hill. They could also have easily put the children on their laps or scooted up but inconveniently chose not to. They then rudely advised us they were their first even though this was a lie, we had just been standing back next to reception as instructed to bu staff. Irritatingly the staff did not intervene. Only issue with this place is its not cheap compared to other dinners and restaurants in Koh samui so I would expect staff to hold other dinners to a certain level of behaviour and step in when it is not being shown. The staff then advised ‘there’s another one coming’ while there was also two spots in the front of the van which was then taken by two staff members finished work for the day… from our perspective having worked in hospitality I would’ve offered these two seats to the guests to make the situation better."
> **- Rose Scott (4/5/5)**

> "Beautiful place but the food wasn''t worth the price, good but expensive and nothing special. I''ve been in many restaurant and paying for food over 1,200THB i get same food and probably even better for 500THB. But the view,  atmosphere and everything was amazing. Staff very friendly. Gonna go there again but only to relax, get couple drinks and enjoy."
> **- Aleksandr Tikka (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-roof-samui-1.jpg','065 547 8898','55, 23, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.theroofsamui.com/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.850+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.850+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-roof-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-roof-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=523593708391484587',NULL,NULL);
