> **- Aleksandr Tikka (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-roof-1.jpg','065 547 8898','55, 23, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.theroofsamui.com/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.852+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.852+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-roof-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-roof-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=523593708391484587',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-salt-rooms','standard','cmr07ii6600wyq8xdwpvg6qs6','The Salt Rooms','## Top Reviews
> "What an amazing time we had at Salt Society brunch. The staff were incredible and couldn’t do enough for you. Cassey was so lovely and attended to our every need. Babe and  Peepo were equally friendly and attentive. Food was varied, lots of lovely choice and delicious, drinks flowed and the music was great. The female DJ played a great mix of tunes, plenty of us were up dancing. A fabulous way to spend a Sunday afternoon. Would come back again and again and highly recommend."
> **- Katie Leader (5/5/5)**

> "Food was amazing.nice option.happy hour is there. The beach is really pretty and quite. Great views and vibes. The right price. The staff is really cooperative and good. The vibe was perfect. It also has stay option resort option. It has a pool and private beach must come here to spend time with family friends, couples solo"
> **- Siddharth Kumar Das (5/5/5)**

> "Went for drinks. Excellent cocktails ~£10 but staff were very friendly and helpful when picking drinks. Friend got wine, very generous to let him try different types until he found the one he liked. Was a Sunday and therefore quiet but that in itself gave it a relaxing and calming vibe."
> **- Krishan Patel (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-salt-rooms-1.jpg','077 230 500','38/2 Moo 3 Borpud, Chaweng Beach, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.saltsocietysamui.com/','["Monday: 12:00 – 10:30 PM","Tuesday: 12:00 – 10:30 PM","Wednesday: 12:00 – 10:30 PM","Thursday: 12:00 – 10:30 PM","Friday: 12:00 – 10:30 PM","Saturday: 12:00 – 10:30 PM","Sunday: 12:30 – 3:30 PM, 6:00 – 10:30 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.854+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.854+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-salt-rooms-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-salt-rooms-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10596674132735609800',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-samui-beach-resort','standard','cmr07ii6800wzq8xdy8i7ocw3','The Samui Beach Resort','## Top Reviews
> "The hotel is falling apart, would not book again! The pictures do not show the condition this place is in. The only thing giving this place a star is their staff that is kind. Bedsheets with stains and holes, towels falling apart. The rooms did not work: keycard was not working, tv remote was gone, staff gave me the only key to the room, so cleaning could only be done when I was there. The place is noisy and you hear everything even the wind.  breakfast so boring and consisted of some scrambled eggs, toast , fried rice with eggs and 2 different fruits. In total should just be avoided,  the only thing giving this place a star is the staff that is super kind and helpful. The distance is not too bad, takes about 20 minutes to walk to the central part.  The hotel is falling apart, is noisy and in very bad condition. Do not trust the pictures, I would not book again!"
> **- Tim Nemler (1/5/5)**

> "Bad experience i have booked sea view room and paid premium price and after the check in i got no sea view.  Just trees are there I am on my honeymoon and you have made my experience very bad"
> **- Ali (1/5/5)**

> "A whole day has passed and we still have no water in the shower and the staff is not helping or solving the problem for us. We asked to change rooms or hotels and they are not helping and are ignoring us."
> **- שלומי אוחנה (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-samui-beach-resort-1.jpg','077 423 666','17 123 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,2.9,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.thesamuibeachresort.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.856+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.856+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-samui-beach-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-samui-beach-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1634688105327598911',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-samui-restaurant','standard','cmr07ii6b00x0q8xdyz6dqqhl','The Samui Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "Three years ago my wife and I tried this amazing Thai restaurant....and three years lately I returned with family to enjoy what I would say is the best Thai restaurant in Koh Samui.  The owner Chaw is the main chef at the restaurant, the food is truly a delicious experience and the presentation of all the different dishes is so elegant.  It''s so good we ate there twice in the 4 day trip.  The restaurant has a pretty seating area open air under the leaning bamboo trees which is so nice to eat in there.  Top picks are the Barracuda dish is expertly cooked and juicy, the king prawn dish has huge prawns and so tasty.  The sea bass with tamarind sauce is amazing, massaman curry is very rich and full of favor.  Out if the 10 or 12 dishes we tried, we would order them all again as each one is so unique and delicious.  Thank-you Chef Chaw for such an amazing dining experience.  You deserve a Michelin Star for the quality of food you make!  Amazing!"
> **- Derek (5/5/5)**

> "One of the best restaurants I’ve been to. I ordered the green curry, and it was amazing. I’m not usually a fan of spicy food, but I absolutely loved it. The flavor was rich, balanced, and mildly spicy. The staff were so nice and friendly. Highly recommended."
> **- Malikeh Salimi (5/5/5)**

> "Amazing food and the owner is so kind and friendly! We came here twice for dinner during our 4 night stay. If you have a bigger group, I would recommend making a reservation just to be safe!"
> **- Alyssa Victoria (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-samui-restaurant-1.jpg','087 472 4097','Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.tripadvisor.com/Restaurant_Review-g1182465-d7070856-Reviews-The_Fish_Restaurant_Mae_Nam-Mae_Nam_Ko_Samui_Surat_Thani_Province.html','["Monday: 11:30 AM – 10:30 PM","Tuesday: 11:30 AM – 10:30 PM","Wednesday: 11:30 AM – 10:30 PM","Thursday: 11:30 AM – 10:30 PM","Friday: 11:30 AM – 10:30 PM","Saturday: 11:30 AM – 10:30 PM","Sunday: 11:30 AM – 10:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.859+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.859+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-samui-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-samui-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12442503574477806568',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('the-sarann','standard','cmr07ii6d00x1q8xdwsomv7sz','The Sarann','## Top Reviews
> "Just spent 9 nights at the Sarann, and had the best stay! We booked through a travel agent so had an all inclusive package. We stayed in a pool villa (102)  and it was spacious, had  2 separate rooms in one villa-one living room with tv, couch, bar fridge) and one huge bed/bath room- and a huge deck with bean bags, our private pool, and a table setting. It was so lovely and private. The staff were absolutely amazing the whole stay, so helpful! If you want an amazing Thai massage- the spa is the place to get it! I walked out feeling like I was floating! The restaurant is good! Although limited with choices, if you are on the inclusive packaging. I feel like they may dumb down some Thai food, I had to ask for salt a few times to get some flavour. I read through some reviews before I left and would love to clear some things up- Yes there are no footpaths- but you can walk along the road safely- literally the traffic will move out of the way for you, and the 7/11 is like 10 mins walk up the road- we never felt unsafe walking Yes it may seem like you are in the middle of nowhere- but they have an amazing shuttle for free , can get a ride back for 400 baht- after 4-5 hours out and about - that was worth it for us . Also the stray dogs- they are so freaking polite- they just crave some interaction- I wanted to bring them home. They won’t bother you unless you want them to . There is absolutely no way they enter the resort We had a beautiful stay at the sarann. I could not praise the staff enough, they were helpful, friendly and attentive"
> **- Chelsea Polaschek (5/5/5)**

> "Small property but well laid out.  We got the ocean front villa with plunge pool right at the water''s Edge.  Approximately 1300.square feet.  Own sun bathing deck.  Well worth it.  Restaurant was serving very good food and the breakfast spread was all very good. Only difficulty was entering the driveway on fast road with a curve."
> **- GroNig 6paT (5/5/5)**

> "Best location for girls trip.. secluded with quiet beach n infinity pool.. their inhouse restaurant was really good. All housekeeping staffs are very nice. Only drawback is that this hotel is far from popular tourist n market areas so every time u hv to spend 300 thai baht one way just to go to restaurant or nearby 7 eleven"
> **- Pragati Dhanavade (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-sarann-1.jpg','077 448 540','95-96 Moo 3 Chaweng Noi Beach, เทศบาลนครเกาะสมุย อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.1,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.thesarann.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ig5c0051q8xdykrbexft','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.861+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.861+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-sarann-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/the-sarann-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=18089499863828166564',NULL,NULL);
