INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('think-retro-cafe','standard','cmr07ii7y00xpq8xd2gjju44i','THINK & Retro Cafe','## Top Reviews
> "Food is so so good! We came here both for lunch and dinner several times. All the dishes were amazing. We especially liked the noodle soup and the papaya salad. We also ordered quite a few coconut milkshakes and banana lassis. Great prices and very friendly staff. Views are nice too!"
> **- Pernilla (5/5/5)**

> "We came for a drink after a day at the beach and had a really lovely experience! It was 4 minutes before the end of happy hour and the staff quickly whipped up our cocktails and did them even cheaper than advertised!! We had piña coladas and a strawberry daiquiri and they were all delicious!"
> **- Georgia Eaton-Rennie (5/5/5)**

> "Stopped by for some food and drinks on a quiet Monday evening. Quick and attentive to take our order, provide mosquito repellent, and serve our drinks. 30 mins later, we asked where our food was - it turned out they’d forgotten to do it. They told us while laughing. Food came soon after, and was decent, but nothing special. When we paid with cash, they didn’t give us any change. Given that they forgot our order, I’d have expected them to give us free drinks, not just take the change we expected as a tip. Will not be visiting again."
> **- Nick Edwards (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/think-retro-cafe-1.jpg','081 721 3683','38 48, Tambon Lipa Noi, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifsb000gq8xdch1ib0om','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.918+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.918+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/think-retro-cafe-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/think-retro-cafe-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10751342122642249144',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('think-safe-international','standard','cmr07ii8000xqq8xd3mmhqn1p','Think Safe International','## Top Reviews
> "What a great service from think safe👌 Thx Nico and your team, without you i think it would be a problem, that they pay. But with your help, all your energy you put in my case, it was done. Great job, another time thx🙏"
> **- andre van de venne (5/5/5)**

> "I have been a customer of this broker for more than 2 years. Although their team is small, they are very responsive and attentive. They offer a comprehensive range of insurance coverage and will help you tailor it to your specific risks and requests. They are also conveniently located nearby the Thai Local Immigration  office so highly recommended for visa required insurances."
> **- Luca Probst (5/5/5)**

> "Very good service, always available. They followed me for my claim from the begging to the end. I feel safe with them. Thank you Think Safe"
> **- Waffle (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/think-safe-international-1.jpg','098 030 5058','27/24, ตำบล แม่น้ำ อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.thinksafeinternational.com/',NULL,'cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.920+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.920+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/think-safe-international-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/think-safe-international-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8681261155229578979',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('thiptara-resort','standard','cmr07ii8200xrq8xdwm998wqr','Thiptara Resort','## Top Reviews
> "We had an amazing stay at the Thiptara Resort and I can totally recommend staying here! The location is very convenient, there are great eating options just in walking distance and the beach is just 1 minute away (walking). The breakfast in house was also really good! The staff is so nice and very, very helpful and everyone made sure that we were comfortable. On our first day we got a whole explanation & recommendation on what to visit on the Island which was also very helpful. Thank you again for the lovely stay!"
> **- g B (5/5/5)**

> "Honestly the best! Such nice and clean Bungalows within walking distance from the beach! Great Pool and friendly french owners who are very helpful and give Tipps what to do around the area. A plus are their cute cats who are very well behaved and always up for a cuddle or a play! We love it and great value for money!"
> **- Laura Winter (5/5/5)**

> "AMAZING RESORT - very clean & quiet ! Sébastien and his wife are really great people. Open minded and always there for your questions or wishes. Helpful 24/7. Thank you !"
> **- Björn Gutermuth (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/thiptara-resort-1.jpg','062 290 5467','1 5, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://thiptara-resort.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.922+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.922+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/thiptara-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/thiptara-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3419967333020841970',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('thirteen-roots','standard','cmr07ii8400xsq8xdu50d7izw','Thirteen Roots','## Top Reviews
> "I’ve eaten really well here. An amazing place, the service was incredible and the staff were super friendly. It’s a charming spot, full of great vibes and a relaxed atmosphere, and the food was outstanding. I asked the waitress for a recommendation and she couldn’t have chosen better. The place has a lot of character and identity — I would definitely come back without hesitation. Best regards."
> **- Adrián Jiménez (5/5/5)**

> "Luckily, I found Roots Thirteen on Google Maps and decided to give it a try after reading the reviews — and I’m so glad I did. The menu is fantastic, and the Beef Massaman was absolutely delicious , so full of flavor. The service was excellent, friendly, and attentive, and everything was very clean. The setting is beautiful and relaxing as well. I’ll definitely be coming back and highly recommend this place."
> **- Jade Morlang (5/5/5)**

> "A truly excellent experience: outstanding food, fresh and perfectly balanced in flavor. The service was friendly and attentive, and the atmosphere warm and inviting. From start to finish, everything felt just right — a place you’ll happily return to and gladly recommend."
> **- Neil Güttner (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/thirteen-roots-1.jpg','064 832 3438','ุ69/6 หมู่ที่ 5, Plai Laem Soi 3, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61565194511603','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifv2001aq8xdag7cvjgf','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.924+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.924+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/thirteen-roots-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/thirteen-roots-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16627151299044677943',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('thomas-kart-studio','standard','cmr07ii8700xtq8xdpcmdftw2','Thomas Kart Studio','## Top Reviews
> "Thomas was absolutely amazing to work with! We reached out last minute to get some engagement photos done while we were in Thailand and they turned out even better than we could have imagined. Thomas had so many prompts to help keep us comfortable in front of the camera. Highly recommend his amazing work. Thank you so much, Thomas!"
> **- Gabriella (5/5/5)**

> "Thomas was extremely kind and professional from the beginning. I reached out via WhatsApp inquiring about rates and his availability. He responded quickly, clearly and transparently. We booked in advance and he kept us confident as the date arrived.  Day of the shoot, he arrived early based on the itinerary provided to him. He wasted no time taking beautiful scenic shots, as well as shots of myself while the bride got ready. From the start of the ceremony and onward, we never felt rushed. He wasted precise in his direction and extremely knowledgable of the venue, its scenic properties and aware of the sun and diminishing light. He captured amazing photos by camera and drone.  He was able to turn around the photos way faster than advertised, receiving them less than a week later fully edited and ready to share.  Would highly recommend booking him if you’re looking for a photographer in Ko Samui Thailand."
> **- Elies Moumena (5/5/5)**

> "We couldn’t be happier with our experience with Thomas Wedding Photography. Thomas was incredibly professional, made us feel completely comfortable, and captured the most beautiful, natural moments of our day. The photos turned out absolutely stunning. We’re so grateful to have these memories captured so perfectly and would highly recommend him to anyone looking for a talented wedding photographer"
> **- T’Lia Lovett (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/thomas-kart-studio-1.jpg','062 349 2430','2, จังหวัดสราษฎร์ธ, 20 หมู่ที่ 1 ตำบล บ่อผุด Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://photosamui.com/',NULL,'cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.927+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.927+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/thomas-kart-studio-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/thomas-kart-studio-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2314036932478602701',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('three-trees-samui-resort','standard','cmr07ii8900xuq8xdwnwu13te','Three Trees Samui Resort','## Top Reviews
> "Amazing place to stay! Beautiful pools and ocean views. Great location. Breakfast buffet on site was amazing! Good variety of western and Thai foods. The fire show on Friday is amazing! Wished we could have stayed here longer. The most luxurious stay we had in Thailand and for a really great price. The service and staff were also very attentive and kind.  The only problem we had was with hot water going to our room. Staff was very quick to fix the issue though. One small recommendation would be the shower head. The placement made it a bit difficult to stand under as it shot straight out into the far wall, so it was a bit annoying to have to hold the handle in your hand to get proper placement. Minor annoyance."
> **- Kate Matthews (5/5/5)**

> "My partner and I had a wonderful stay at Three Trees Samui Resort – Sarocha Villa. The villa was cozy, clean, and well-maintained, with a beautiful tropical atmosphere that made it perfect for a romantic escape. The staff were incredibly warm and welcoming, making us feel right at home throughout our stay. Lamai Beach is just steps away, and the peaceful surroundings made it ideal for unwinding together. A minor scope for improvement in a few amenities keeps it at four stars, but overall it was a delightful experience and we would love to come back!"
> **- Prakasam Mathaiyan (4/5/5)**

> "Just spent 4 days here in a garden pool Villa Absolutely loved it and was sad to leave. Staff were fantastic facilities awesome. Great food in the restaurant.  The room was spotless and the lounge pool was awesome after a hard  day of exploring.  If I had any complaint it would be that access to the pool is a little awkward for the elderly. Perhaps a step would be helpful  Minor complaint. This  place was awesome."
> **- Guy Basile (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/three-trees-samui-resort-1.jpg',NULL,'F22J+GJP, Maret, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.hotelssuratthani.com/three-trees-samui-resort-sarocha-villa/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.929+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.929+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/three-trees-samui-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/three-trees-samui-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3554734223916558267',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('tiramisu-restaurant-bar','standard','cmr07ii8b00xvq8xdxd77v6tu','Tiramisu Restaurant & Bar','## Top Reviews
> "I came here on 3 different occasions, each trying a new pasta dish and I was soo happy with the food, 10/10, just how I expected and more!! The service is excellent and you are always greeted with smiling faces and good vibes. There is a lot to choose from and lovely desserts - you’re spoilt for choice but I recommend the pesto pasta or the seafood spaghetti!! I also loved the ham & mushroom tagliatelle - if you’re in fisherman village then I 1000% recommend!"
> **- Zaphy Christoforou (5/5/5)**

> "After having tried different Western restaurants on the island we were absolutely blown away by the quality of the food here. We had pizza (probably the best one on the island), lasagna and a salad and were more than happy with everything. Paul the owner is a really nice guy who talked to us for a while at the end and had lots of interesting stories to tell. We highly recommend this place to anyone! :)"
> **- M Short (5/5/5)**

> "Probably one the the best restaurants in the fisherman’s village ; avd for sure the cleanest ! All best ingredients are selected to provide an excellent food . Wooden oven pizzas are so good , Caesar salad , amazing ( not easy to find a good one in samui ) . Very nice wines too , and all at very decent prices . Will go again"
> **- Sabai Glamping (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tiramisu-restaurant-bar-1.jpg','093 367 6482','The Villager Fisherman''s Village, 33 Thanon Bo Phut Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://tiramisusamui.com/?utm_source=google&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=gbp','["Monday: 3:00 – 11:30 PM","Tuesday: Closed","Wednesday: 3:00 – 11:30 PM","Thursday: 3:00 – 11:30 PM","Friday: 3:00 – 11:30 PM","Saturday: 3:00 – 11:30 PM","Sunday: 3:00 – 11:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifre0005q8xdxq1t2ih4','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.931+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.931+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tiramisu-restaurant-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tiramisu-restaurant-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7915772092356306621',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('tk-168-garage','standard','cmr07ii8e00xwq8xdrcmj75gf','Tk 168 Garage','Discover Tk 168 Garage, a premier transport located in Chaweng, Koh Samui. Find reviews, hours, and contact information.',NULL,'062 020 0868','97 8 ตำบล บ่อผุด Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,0.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100087577488396','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07ifui0012q8xdzn158clv','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.934+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.934+00:00',NULL,'https://maps.google.com/?cid=958150481839429816',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('toast-cafe-bar-lamai','standard','cmr07ii8h00xxq8xdivzz66p8','Toast Cafe Bar','## Top Reviews
> "We came to Toast Cafe Lamai expecting a fresh and healthy breakfast, but unfortunately the experience was very disappointing. The food felt heavily processed and low quality rather than fresh or homemade. The only things we actually enjoyed were the spinach and the eggs.  Everything else tasted artificial and overly processed — especially the sausage, the hash browns, and the piece of meat that came with the meal. Instead of feeling like a healthy breakfast, it felt more like frozen or pre-made food heated up and served quickly. The presentation online and the atmosphere gave us completely different expectations.  For the prices they charge, we expected much better ingredients and much fresher food. Sadly, the meal left us feeling disappointed and unsatisfied. We would not come back and cannot recommend this place if you are looking for a genuinely fresh and healthy breakfast experience."
> **- The Guy 007 (1/5/5)**

> "Toast is a great spot for brunch with a wide and varied menu. There are plenty of choices, including healthy options and delicious vegetarian dishes, so everyone can find something they’ll enjoy.  The food is fresh, well-prepared, and very tasty, making it a perfect place for a relaxed brunch. The atmosphere is pleasant and welcoming, and the service is friendly and attentive.  A lovely place to enjoy a quality brunch, whether you’re looking for something indulgent or healthy. Highly recommended!"
> **- Kiymet Duran (5/5/5)**

> "My family and I came into Toast for breakfast as we were staying in the hotel opposite. Everything was lovely! We all really enjoyed our food and drinks, the staff were friendly, and the cafe was very clean and modern. We would definitely return."
> **- Suzie Page (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/toast-cafe-bar-lamai-1.jpg','082 621 5758','173, 56, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.937+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.937+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/toast-cafe-bar-lamai-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/toast-cafe-bar-lamai-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=256747568263807296',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('toast-cafe-bar','standard','cmr07ii8j00xyq8xdwtima6jc','Toast Cafe Bar','## Top Reviews
> "We came to Toast Cafe Lamai expecting a fresh and healthy breakfast, but unfortunately the experience was very disappointing. The food felt heavily processed and low quality rather than fresh or homemade. The only things we actually enjoyed were the spinach and the eggs.  Everything else tasted artificial and overly processed — especially the sausage, the hash browns, and the piece of meat that came with the meal. Instead of feeling like a healthy breakfast, it felt more like frozen or pre-made food heated up and served quickly. The presentation online and the atmosphere gave us completely different expectations.  For the prices they charge, we expected much better ingredients and much fresher food. Sadly, the meal left us feeling disappointed and unsatisfied. We would not come back and cannot recommend this place if you are looking for a genuinely fresh and healthy breakfast experience."
> **- The Guy 007 (1/5/5)**

> "Toast is a great spot for brunch with a wide and varied menu. There are plenty of choices, including healthy options and delicious vegetarian dishes, so everyone can find something they’ll enjoy.  The food is fresh, well-prepared, and very tasty, making it a perfect place for a relaxed brunch. The atmosphere is pleasant and welcoming, and the service is friendly and attentive.  A lovely place to enjoy a quality brunch, whether you’re looking for something indulgent or healthy. Highly recommended!"
> **- Kiymet Duran (5/5/5)**

> "My family and I came into Toast for breakfast as we were staying in the hotel opposite. Everything was lovely! We all really enjoyed our food and drinks, the staff were friendly, and the cafe was very clean and modern. We would definitely return."
> **- Suzie Page (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/toast-cafe-bar-1.jpg','082 621 5758','173, 56, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.939+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.939+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/toast-cafe-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/toast-cafe-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=256747568263807296',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('tobi-teppanyaki-bar','standard','cmr07ii8l00xzq8xds8d6fu19','Tobi Teppanyaki & Bar','## Top Reviews
> "A Delightful Dining Experience  This restaurant offers a fantastic selection of beef dishes that are sure to impress any meat lover. The beef is tender, flavorful, and cooked to perfection, with just the right balance of seasoning. Whether you’re a fan of steak, teppanyaki, or slow-cooked beef, each bite is packed with taste and quality.  The atmosphere is cozy, creating the perfect setting for a relaxed meal. With warm lighting and comfortable seating, it’s an ideal spot for a casual dinner. If you’re looking for delicious beef and a welcoming ambiance, this place won’t disappoint."
> **- Thitaphas K. (5/5/5)**

> "ingredients were very fresh, especially the Hokkaido Scallop and Salmon. There are many interesting menus here, so I tried many dishes. My fav menu is the Picanha AUS, it was very delicious with the fat that was in it. When you eat it, it almost melts in your mouth. Chef was very meticulous in cooking so I will definitely invite my friends to eat it again."
> **- Naon Suwan (5/5/5)**

> "A nicely done Japanese dinner at this new cozy restaurant, just opposite Chi beach club in Bangrak. Felt welcomed by the accommodating staff here. The energy at this place is nothing but positive and friendly. The food here was great and tastes beyond expectation - very fresh and nicely executed. All the dishes were so enjoyable from the picanha to fresh sashimis of salmon, scallops and grilled tiger prawns. Beyond Japanese menus, there are the picanhas (as mentioned), pastas, salads and beef tartare - to name a few I''d say. All in all, another quality Japanese cuisine on the island with fusion sensibilities."
> **- Wunda Stone (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tobi-teppanyaki-bar-1.jpg','096 695 6595','16/45, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/tobi.samui','["Monday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: Closed","Friday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 1:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.941+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.941+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tobi-teppanyaki-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tobi-teppanyaki-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17182788490415060530',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('tolani-resort','standard','cmr07ii8n00y0q8xdyg94cpt7','Tolani Resort','## Top Reviews
> "Tolani was an amazing stay for my wife, my 9 month old son and I. We messaged them ahead of time asking if thye had a bottle sanitizer for our son''s milk bottles which they didn''t, however they organised a brand new one for our stay! The staff were so kind and helpful - we really loved staying here. Food was good, massages were great. Thank you Tolani staff for a great holiday"
> **- Aaron Thoo (5/5/5)**

> "It was a wonderful resort, quiet and warm place. The view was amazing next to the beach which the restaurant is there. The guys there were very nice and smiling all time. The food was very delicious😋, I would say best food in Thailand. I recommend it for those who look for a quiet and restful"
> **- Fadi Essa (5/5/5)**

> "I stayed at Tolani Hotel Samui with fairly high expectations, but unfortunately the experience didn’t quite match up.  The room I was given felt quite worn and “lived in” not in a charming way, but more like it hadn’t been properly refreshed in a long time. You could see signs of aging in several details, and overall it didn’t give that clean, well maintained feeling you’d expect at this level.  What was more surprising is that the hotel was practically empty during my stay, yet no upgrade or even small perks were offered. This is where the guest relations really fell short. Even basic gestures that make a guest feel welcomed or valued were missing, which made the experience feel a bit cold and transactional.  The property itself is huge, which on paper sounds great, but in reality it can feel a bit too spread out and lacking atmosphere when occupancy is low. It almost gives a slightly abandoned vibe in certain areas, especially during quieter times of the day.  The beach is another mixed point it’s wide and scenic, but during low tide the water goes very far out, making it difficult to actually swim or enjoy the sea for a good part of the day.  In terms of location, it’s quite far from the main hotspots in Samui. If you’re looking to be near the action like Chaweng or even the more relaxed Fisherman’s Village in Bophut, this isn’t ideal. You’ll definitely need a scooter or car to move around comfortably, otherwise you might feel a bit isolated.  Overall, the hotel has potential thanks to its space and setting, but the lack of attention to detail and guest experience really holds it back."
> **- Alessandro Xine (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tolani-resort-1.jpg','077 448 999','442, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.tolaniresortkohsamui.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifpz0001q8xd0aml2ucx','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.943+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.943+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tolani-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tolani-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13145783000663017909',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('tommy-black-ink','standard','cmr07ii8p00y1q8xd9n6wc56r','TOMMY BLACK INK','## Top Reviews
> "Had a half sleeve done here with the artist Base and had such a great experience. I dealt with Tommy to start with and sent all the designs through him and then it was all mapped out.  I had a previous sleeve done by someone else in Samui but my experience here was so much better. The detail and speed was fantastic and the staff are all so friendly.  I’m over the moon with the outcome and recommend Base if you’re planning on getting any tattoos in Samui!"
> **- Brandon (5/5/5)**

> "I had a fine line tattoo done at Tommy Black Ink.  The staff are so friendly and were really helpful.  They are perfectionists and took the time to get my vision right.  I am very grateful.  Thank you so much"
> **- Holly Roma (5/5/5)**

> "So incredible! I got two pieces of Man Tra''s flash and she was excellent. She was so careful about the placement and I''m so happy with how it turned out. It was super easy to schedule an appointment!"
> **- Nancy Haugh (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tommy-black-ink-1.jpg','062 518 1199','100/ 31 หมู่1 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 11:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.945+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.945+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tommy-black-ink-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tommy-black-ink-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4497794738197391090',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('tonkra-nursery-kindergarten','standard','cmr07ii8r00y2q8xdcapuii1x','Tonkra Nursery & Kindergarten','## Top Reviews
> "I couldn''t be happier with Tonkra for our daughter. She started in nursery and is now in Kindergarten. The children really enjoy the school, the teachers are wonderful and the students have developed into supportive friends.  The school is upbeat, set around a garden with many outdoor activities and overall has a very positive atmosphere."
> **- Alex Barksby (5/5/5)**

> "Very lovely place with very kind teachers. They have different activities each day, as a parent, it is a really nice feeling to know that my kid is well taking care of. They have a chat group set up where they share pictured of the kids with the parents every day. Also the facility is really nice and clean with a big yard."
> **- Róza Eisenberg (5/5/5)**

> "Tonkra Nursery is an outstanding nursery with well trained and happy staff. Our daughter, who is 15 months, really enjoys attending and her social skills and development has improved a lot. Tonkra has great and well maintained facilities both inside and out, and the little trips such as to the beach look fun and very safe. She enjoys the meals and snacks a lot too. Overall a happy place for early years learning with qualified and caring staff."
> **- Ian Corrigan (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tonkra-nursery-kindergarten-1.jpg','081 894 1329','67/23 M.1 Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://tonkrasamui.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 3:30 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 3:30 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 3:30 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 3:30 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 3:30 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.947+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.947+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tonkra-nursery-kindergarten-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tonkra-nursery-kindergarten-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9582166246204186899',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('top-charoen-optical','standard','cmr07ii8t00y3q8xdhd2a0il7','Top Charoen Optical','## Top Reviews
> "The staff provided excellent service and were very attentive. There’s a wide variety of glasses to choose from, and the prices are affordable. They also offer great after-sales services, such as adjustments for loose frames or cleaning assistance when needed. Highly recommended!"
> **- Ella Benchan (5/5/5)**

> "This is not a real optician. Watch out for the scam!  Unfortunately, we were lured in by the nice promotions and the professional-looking salon. However, once inside, it became clear that the person selling the glasses had absolutely no knowledge of what she was offering. When we inquired about the shades we were interested in—asking about polarization, UV filters, and lens properties—she had no idea what these terms even meant.  To verify the authenticity of the products, we requested the original packaging or certification for well-known brands like Ray-Ban, Playboy, and Fila, which we know always come with proper documentation and packaging. Shockingly, she was unable to provide anything besides a generic shop bag—no original cases, labels, or certificates to confirm the legitimacy of the items.  This strongly suggests that the store only claims to sell original products but has no real proof of authenticity. Be cautious before making any purchase here!"
> **- Małgorzata Pindych (1/5/5)**

> "We went to the Shop due to a loose screw on my Husbands sunglasses we had brought from germany. They fixed the Problem and without us asking for it adjusted the screws on the outside as well. When asked for compensation, they declined anything. Great Service, really friendly! Highly recommend."
> **- Cathrin Zielinski (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/top-charoen-optical-1.jpg','077 962 327','เลขที่ 248/39 หมู่ที่ 1 ตำบล แม่น้ำ Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://topcharoen.co.th/','["Monday: 8:30 AM – 8:30 PM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 8:30 PM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 8:30 PM","Thursday: 8:30 AM – 8:30 PM","Friday: 8:30 AM – 8:30 PM","Saturday: 8:30 AM – 8:30 PM","Sunday: 8:30 AM – 8:30 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.949+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.949+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/top-charoen-optical-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/top-charoen-optical-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7635729717790864883',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('topcats-fishing-resort','standard','cmr07ii8w00y4q8xdoigxjbxw','Topcats Fishing Resort','## Top Reviews
> "If you are looking to book an amazing fishing experience on Koh Samui look no further! This place is absolutely amazing. Simon, Larry and Sarah make you feel so welcome from the moment you walk in the door, nothing was too much trouble. The atmosphere is professional but fun at the same time, you quickly feel like part of the Top Cats family there. The guides know really their stuff, are enthusiastic and good fun to spend time with (thank you Doi, Tadpole and Mai Mai). The gear is good quality branded kit and stands up to the goliaths in the lake really well. The variety and size of the fish stocked is amazing and they are all in such great condition due to the care that the guides take with them. We all understand fish care is important, you only have to see the state of some of the fish in European commercial fisheries, but these guys take proper care of their stock and it shows in the quality of the fish you will catch. They have taught me a few lessons to take back to my own club in the UK for sure. Three of us fished over 3 days and had over 3,200lb of fish including a 180lb Arapaima, 100lb Mekong Cats, 90lb Siamese Carp, Asian and Amazonian Redtail Cats, Alligator Gar, Leopard Cats, Ripsaw Cats & Pacu. We stayed on site and our accommodation was lovely and clean, with everything we needed. The onsite catering is delicious, portion sizes are generous, great Thai and English options, the staff friendly and attentive and the bar is well stocked. The pool is a bonus to cool off in after a hard fight in the sun. What more could you ask for? As a family we have fished 4 continents and Top Cats stands out by far as the best place we have ever been. We can''t wait to go back!"
> **- Adrian Morgan (5/5/5)**

> "We had such a great 3-day stay at Top Cats Fishery and honestly can’t thank the owners and staff enough for how well they looked after us.  From the moment we arrived, the owners came out to greet us and were so friendly the whole time we were there. They kept popping down during the day to chat and check in, which was a really nice touch. Nothing ever felt like too much trouble - they really went out of their way to make sure we had everything we needed.  The guides were brilliant and clearly know their stuff. Tadpole was my partner’s guide and she was amazing; super knowledgeable, really easy to chat to, and just genuinely lovely. My partner had the best time and caught around 36 fish across 8 species over the 3 days, including the one he really wanted - an Amazon Redtail catfish!  The food was also really good - tasty, big portions, and very reasonably priced. We stayed on-site too and the rooms were clean and comfortable, with everything you need. The beds were comfy (which is appreciated after long days!), and it was a nice touch having tea and coffee facilities with proper English Yorkshire tea.  While my partner was busy fishing, I spent some time by the pool which was perfect - really quiet during the day as most people are down by the lake, so it was a great spot to relax and cool off.  Even though I didn’t fish myself, I still felt really welcome and looked after the whole time. You can tell a lot of effort goes into the place. It might seem a bit pricey when you first book, but it’s 100% worth it for the level of service, the quality of the guides and equipment, and the overall experience.  We’d definitely come back!"
> **- aimee jade (5/5/5)**

> "Simon, Larry and Sarah and all the team at TopCats, what a wonderful resort you have created, we''ve loved every second spent here!  We won the AAC''s (Anglers Against Cancer''s) auction of this holiday back in september and from the first interaction, youve been nothing but accomodating.  From the first email to the moment we left, we felt welcome and that nothing was too much trouble.  The team you have are a real credit to you, all so lovely and accommodating and a joy to be around.  The food, was out of this world, with a mix of Thai and Western, all freshly cooked and delivered to our swim, although sometimes the portion sizes were too much for us but to the average fisherman, im sure they appreciate it (I just hate wasted food).  We were visited throughout the day with the offer of refreshments, we never felt forgotten.  I was especially touched by the fact that TJ learned to make Pina Coladas for me, they were out of this world, you''ll just have to restock the rum for our next visit!  Our room was spacious and very comfortable had ample supplies of water, tea, coffee, sugar etc, the bed and bedding really comfy, and air conditioning kept us lovely and cool.  Thanks to Sarah who extended her time to take me and another guest for a massage on the beach and some sightseeing, it really did make the trip more meaningful and was good to see more of the island.  Simon, thank you for dropping us into Lamai''s night market on a number of ocassions, which was a really nice gesture, we had some great evenings on our Honeymoon!  The pool was a great bonus for us non fisherman, a welcomed break from the heat to cool down.  Finally the guides, they really know their stuff and work consistently to make sure those fishing, catch well.  What a lovely bunch too, we on several occasions had some great banter with them, hopefully Tom knows that "
> **- Sarah Corbett (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/topcats-fishing-resort-1.jpg','084 184 1011','100, 1, Tambon Taling Ngam, Ban Saket, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84140, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.topcats.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ig0w003aq8xdfi0rydaw','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.952+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.952+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/topcats-fishing-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/topcats-fishing-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12866475531498762608',NULL,NULL);
