INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('toysgame-samui','standard','cmr07ii9200y6q8xdj0uf5hn7','ToysGame @ Samui','## Top Reviews
> "Flim is so lovely; she gave me great advice and took good care of me 🥰"
> **- สกาย. (5/5/5)**

> "Bought PS5, Very good price very good service, love it!  Thank you!!❤️"
> **- Nuur Sebastian Khalil (5/5/5)**

> "Friendly and very helpful even i not buy my xbox console there they try to help in anyway, 2 hours the owner tried to help, thank you"
> **- Patrick Desmet (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/toysgame-samui-1.jpg','077 426 919','124 8, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/Toysgamesamui/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.958+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.958+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/toysgame-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/toysgame-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9755174203735618903',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('trade-winds','standard','cmr07ii9400y7q8xd36vxevoi','Trade Winds','## Top Reviews
> "Outstanding breakfast experience! The variety of food is extensive. You can find both Western and Thai dishes as well. The staff is very helpful, and they were especially warm and engaging with our baby."
> **- Zsófi Ruzsvánszky (5/5/5)**

> "This is my 3rd hotel in Thailand and we found the food very bland. Of course there are the regular eggs hash bacon pancakes some  fruits  basic juices. They offer some thai as well what tasted very average. Im comparing this to the other hotels 1 in Bangkok 1 in Phuket  and those were superior to this. The Latte is also very poor i stopped drinking it. 3 star Max!! Nice view of the ocean though unfortunately is not for swimming , murky water."
> **- K K (4/5/5)**

> "I didn’t like it that they didn’t let us take the food out of the restaurant. We had a 20 for breakfast before we needed to check out, but they didn’t let us take a small bag with some bagels for the way because of hotel policy. Very bad. The breakfast looked nice."
> **- May Nir (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/trade-winds-1.jpg','077 900 999','175 3 Thaveeratpakdee road Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.1,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.celessamui.com/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.960+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.960+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/trade-winds-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/trade-winds-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2052252300498782842',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('tree-bridge-zipline-samui','standard','cmr07ii9600y8q8xdd6w3utjk','Tree Bridge Zipline Samui','## Top Reviews
> "PLEASE DON’T MISS THIS EXPERIENCE  This is one of the best experience you can have in Samui. We got picked up at hotel and reached the spot on time. Every person there was very polite and staffs were very helpful and amazing. The guides there are so friendly and they’re the best. They make you feel comfortable, make jokes and try to scare in a fun way for the adrenaline rush.  Please don’t fall for all the negative reviews since you never know what actually happened which made the staff to behave that way with them. The guides were even friendly to take videos of you for free when you’re doing zipline. Such a wonderful day and wonderful experience. Will visit again."
> **- Benny Richard Dickson (5/5/5)**

> "Unforgettable experience. All the staff are super friendly and welcoming. The professional caregivers are very professional, caring and attentive on the customers. They will let you fully enjoy this adventure without worry. The absolute stunning view is on every line and the breathtaking surrounding is thrilling. They open a cafe and have chill areas to relax after your exciting moment is over. Highly recommended for everyone’s activity in Koh Samui."
> **- Hein Satt Nyein (5/5/5)**

> "Absolutely breathtaking experience. The zipline through the jungle was unreal — the views, the lookout points, the waterfall hidden in the middle of nature… OMG. Everything felt magical. The scenery was straight out of a movie. The café was also such a vibe after the adventure. I had the strawberry smoothie and it was SO good and refreshing. Between the jungle atmosphere, the peaceful waterfall, and the incredible staff and setup, this was easily a 5-star experience. Highly recommend if you love nature and adventure 🌿✨"
> **- Par Nmv (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tree-bridge-zipline-samui-1.jpg','081 952 9855','12/79 หมู่ 1แม่น้ำ แม่น้ำ Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.treebridgezipline.com/','["Monday: 9:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 9:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 9:30 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.962+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.962+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tree-bridge-zipline-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tree-bridge-zipline-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5318274669031826952',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('tree-tops','standard','cmr07ii9800y9q8xd4dwwfi0b','Tree Tops','## Top Reviews
> "What an absolutely delightful experience! We did one Earth and Ocean (meat and fish) and one Earth and Bloom (vegetarian) - and the eight course set menu was incredible. Such interesting presentation, textures and thought put into each dish. Our Hosts Maya and Golf were so very attentive and made our evening there so very special. Going for the earlier sitting at 6 was excellent as we saw the sun setting as well as the night. My wife chose this venue for our special Honeymoon dinner as it’s a filming location for the tv show White Lotus, which we love so that was very exciting!"
> **- Sarah Williams (5/5/5)**

> "We visited Tree Tops on Friday, June 12, to celebrate our 30th wedding anniversary.  We are a Japanese couple visiting Koh Samui from Japan, and this was one of the most memorable dining experiences of our lives.  The restaurant itself is absolutely stunning. Surrounded by nature and overlooking the sea, everything felt special and far removed from our everyday lives.  Every dish was beautifully prepared, and we could truly appreciate the quality of the ingredients and the attention to detail. The food was exceptional.  What touched us most was the way the team helped celebrate our 30th wedding anniversary. We could feel their warm wishes and thoughtful touches throughout the evening, which made the experience even more meaningful and emotional.  A special thank you to Pukpik, who took care of us during our dinner. Her warm smile, kindness, and genuine hospitality made us feel incredibly welcome and comfortable. We are sincerely grateful to her.  If you are reading this review and wondering whether you should visit Tree Tops, stop wondering. If you come to Koh Samui, this is a restaurant you should not miss.  We sincerely hope Tree Tops continues to thrive and that many more guests will experience the same joy and unforgettable memories that we did.  We wish all the wonderful staff the very best for the future.  Thank you from the bottom of our hearts."
> **- Naoki Shima (5/5/5)**

> "I dined at Tree Tops to celebrate my 28th birthday, and I couldn’t have asked for a better experience. This was truly the best fine dining experience I’ve ever had. From the ambiance of the dining space to the presentation of each course, everything was absolutely phenomenal. I had the Earth and Ocean 8-course meal, and “delicious” doesn’t even begin to describe it. Every dish was crafted with so much detail and care. What made the evening truly unforgettable, though, was the genuine hospitality I received from Dada and Eric. They made my birthday extra special and took such wonderful care of me. I usually celebrate my birthday on my own, so having such a warm, attentive staff made the night feel incredibly meaningful. I left feeling happy, appreciated, and grateful for an experience I’ll never forget. Highly, highly recommend Tree Tops! 🌟"
> **- Taylor Bonds (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tree-tops-1.jpg','077 960 333','92, 1, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.treetopsrestaurantsamui.com/?utm_source=GoogleMyBusiness&utm_medium=GMB&utm_term=TreeTopsSamui&utm_content=Home&utm_campaign=Google_GMB','["Monday: 6:00 – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 6:00 – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 6:00 – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 6:00 – 11:00 PM","Friday: 6:00 – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 6:00 – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 6:00 – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.964+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.964+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tree-tops-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tree-tops-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12284024830948517553',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('tree-yard-international-school','standard','cmr07ii9a00yaq8xdqflsppce','Tree Yard International School','## Top Reviews
> "We adore TreeYard International Montessori Nursery in Koh Samui! The caring environment and creative activities make it a perfect start for our little ones. The staff''s warmth adds a lovely touch. We appreciate the international and Montessori focus, creating a fantastic place for our children to grow."
> **- Marcela Mota (5/5/5)**

> "My kid spent a month at TreeYard''s Montessori kindergarten, and it was truly wonderful. I never imagined finding such a good place for him. The experience has been fantastic, and I''m grateful for the positive environment and care he received there. Not only that, my boy immediately connected with the teachers. Their warmth and dedication made him feel right at home, and the bond they formed was heartwarming. In just a short time, he learned so much, and his enthusiasm for learning has truly blossomed. Thank you, for making every moment a valuable step in his educational journey!"
> **- Maria Heifets (5/5/5)**

> "TreeYard in Koh Samui is a delight for both my kids. The international preschool has sparked a love for learning in my preschooler, while my kindergartener thrives in the Montessori environment. It''s heartwarming to see them flourish in a school that values individual growth with an international and Montessori touch. Grateful for TreeYard!"
> **- Yuli Mazal tov (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tree-yard-international-school-1.jpg','088 110 6600','131, 35 Moo1, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'http://treeyardinternational.com/','["Monday: 8:30 AM – 4:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 4:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 4:00 PM","Thursday: 8:30 AM – 4:00 PM","Friday: 8:30 AM – 4:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.966+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.966+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tree-yard-international-school-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tree-yard-international-school-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=7697347785606795185',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('treehouse-silent-beach','standard','cmr07ii9c00ybq8xdjd0svbjs','Treehouse Silent Beach','## Top Reviews
> "This restaurant was one of the most memorable dining experiences I had in Koh Samui. My driver told me I had to check this place out and wow… what an absolute hidden gem. Tucked away in the jungle right on the beach, this spot has one of the most peaceful and magical atmospheres I’ve experienced in Koh Samui.  The ambience here is unreal. Beautiful decor, incredible beachfront setting, calm tranquil waters, and the most amazing ocean breeze that honestly made me never want to leave. It feels completely off the beaten path in the best possible way… quiet, relaxing, authentic, and surrounded by nature. At one point I swear I heard at least 15 different languages being spoken around me, which somehow made the whole experience feel even more special and connected.  The food was absolutely amazing too. Everything tasted fresh and full of flavor, and the entire experience just felt special from start to finish.  Leo loved it as much as I did 🐾 The staff were welcoming, the vibe was calm and cozy, and it’s the kind of place you accidentally spend hours at because you simply don’t want to leave.  One of my favorite discoveries on the island. If you’re looking for a peaceful beachfront escape away from the crowds, this place is a must visit."
> **- Clayton (5/5/5)**

> "We stumbled here for supper from our nearby hotel and what a beautiful surprise. Gorgeous seaside setting, fun design and smiling staff. I recommend reserving ahead of time if you’re coming for supper since it was quite busy, and we didnt get a table outside by the sea because we didn''t have one. We will most definitely be back again before we leave."
> **- Katherine Tar (5/5/5)**

> "Restaurant review: The food and drinks are good here, but definitely don''t order the children''s spaghetti with butter and a little cheese. For 120 baht, you get such a small portion that no child will be satisfied. I spent a total of 2,700 baht here and consulted with the manager, who refused to give me a 20 baht discount for the insufficient portion. The highlight was that they ended up charging 200 baht for this portion. No willingness to satisfy the customer, on the contrary, they will laugh at you by trying to charge you even more."
> **- Martin Alexander (2/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/treehouse-silent-beach-1.jpg','062 240 4305','12 2, Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.tree-house.org/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.968+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.968+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/treehouse-silent-beach-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/treehouse-silent-beach-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=10682323818536507784',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('tropical-kaleidoscop','standard','cmr07ii9f00ycq8xduz7wzdic','Tropical Kaleidoscop','## Top Reviews
> "My 8-year-old son recently attended this camp, and it was absolutely amazing! From start to finish, the entire experience was full of fun and excitement. The camp organizes a fantastic variety of activities that keep the kids entertained and engaged.  One of the highlights for my son was visiting an island and exploring a National Marine Park. He saw so many animals and learned a lot about nature, which he couldn''t stop talking about when he got home. He also made so many new friends, which made the experience even more special for him.  The staff were incredibly kind, professional, and attentive, ensuring every child had a great time. As parents, we felt confident knowing he was in good hands.  We’ll definitely be coming back, and I would highly recommend this camp to anyone looking for an unforgettable adventure for their kids!"
> **- Julia DAG (5/5/5)**

> "Finally, a normal summer camp has appeared on the island that helps to raise children, and not a club with the task of entertaining children for a few hours.  Very close to what we had in childhood: a camp with an overnight stay, the need to build long-term communication and relationships, team sports activities, hikes, normal nutrition, exercise and discipline.  The camp is run by experienced adult women with the best combination of education: a leader and a teacher.  This allows them to lead the children, and not merge under their destructive injections. Children monitor the cleanliness of their rooms, their own hygiene, work, develop independence, learn to be friends, communicate freshly, build a team, overcome difficulties, help each other in close contact.  The camp is based on a travel agency, which gives it good capacity: children regularly go on excursions and sports events by minibus, go to the sea, spend the night in a hotel, eat well. Master classes are conducted by invited competent teachers, it is not just "
> **- Svetlana Katson (5/5/5)**

> "Great service! My wife and I booked our transfers to Surat Thani airport from here and we found them to be very friendly, well organised and easy to deal with. They collected us from our accommodation the following day and dropped us to the ferry terminal making sure we got there safely. Excellent service, great value would highly recommend 👍"
> **- Donal Gorman (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tropical-kaleidoscop-1.jpg','099 000 3584','154, 28, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://kids-samui.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 6:30 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 5:30 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.971+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.971+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tropical-kaleidoscop-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tropical-kaleidoscop-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11137208377568351912',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('tropical-murphys-irish-pub','standard','cmr07ii9h00ydq8xd87n03p4w','Tropical Murphy''s Irish Pub','## Top Reviews
> "What a spot. Spent the week in Koh Samui and spent four nights here for food and drinks. I would recommend the spice bag, 10/10!! As well as every other dish!! Service was amazing and thank you Jeff/Geoff for being so welcoming!  Very sad to be leaving"
> **- Lúcás Ó Cuirrín (5/5/5)**

> "Food was great and very reasonably priced. Service wonderful. There was a band on when we dropped in followed by a guy playing a guitar with a singer. The guitar player was brilliant and he had a great interaction with the audience. Worth a visit"
> **- Jackie Fawcett (5/5/5)**

> "Quality Irish bar in a great location, food and service were fantastic. Owner Paul is very welcoming. A definite place to visit if you''re on Samui."
> **- Chris (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tropical-murphys-irish-pub-1.jpg','077 945 187','14, 40 หมู่ที่ 2 ถนน เฉวงบีช, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 12:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Tuesday: 12:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Wednesday: 12:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Thursday: 12:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Friday: 12:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Saturday: 12:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Sunday: 12:00 PM – 2:00 AM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.973+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.973+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tropical-murphys-irish-pub-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tropical-murphys-irish-pub-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17073593463441811721',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('tropical-tonys-sport-bar-diner','standard','cmr07ii9j00yeq8xdhsmp9cl2','Tropical Tony''s Sport Bar & Diner','## Top Reviews
> "Officially one of my favourite places. We came for dinner and had the fish and chips, and the beef and mash. It was delicious. The staff was friendly and lively and the setting was nice and relaxed. Massive portions with great prices. 10/10"
> **- Alrike Coetzee (5/5/5)**

> "The best home comfort British food I’ve had since travelling. I had steak and onion pie and it was amazing. The mash potato was some of the best mash I’ve ever had. Was even better than most pie and mash I’ve had in England. The service was great and the staff are so friendly. We will definitely be coming back before we leave. Thank you so much"
> **- Becca James (5/5/5)**

> "I was recommended this by a friend who lives in Koh Samui. I have to say it was the best value meal I have ever had. Such good food at such a good price. The ribs are slow cooked for 12 hours, the pies are homemade and that was just what we had. I have been told by other locals in the bar that all the food is just as good. My only disappointment is that I live in Australia so can’t come here every week. If you are in Koh Samui, you HAVE to visit Tropical Tony’s !!"
> **- Steve Foote (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tropical-tonys-sport-bar-diner-1.jpg','081 087 8918','124 holiday park 64 Soi Aumpai Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 4:00 – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 4:00 – 9:30 PM","Thursday: 4:00 – 9:30 PM","Friday: 4:00 – 9:30 PM","Saturday: 4:00 – 9:30 PM","Sunday: 4:00 – 9:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.975+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.975+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tropical-tonys-sport-bar-diner-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tropical-tonys-sport-bar-diner-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16403201790010779462',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('tropikana-beach-bistro','standard','cmr07ii9l00yfq8xdd90o1m7i','Tropikana Beach Bistro','## Top Reviews
> "We had breakfast, lunch, and dinner here. Also took cooking class. Food were delicious, staff were great, and beautiful view. Highly recommended to try their Massaman Beef Curry and Coconut Crème Brulee. It’s worth visiting just for the Crème Brulee itself."
> **- Shelly C (5/5/5)**

> "A very nice resort in Koh Samui, it’s placement is perfect, near to the airport and fisherman village and many many places.. everything is like 5 mins away: Thai massage, good restaurants. The highlight of my stay, was the personal, they are genuinely and truly nice people and friendly, I ask for a pool view on my birthday and they change a room and gave me a cake and that was very sweet. I’d like to thank James, Ton and actually everyone of the staff for their service and kindness and the egg chef? Because you’ll get the best breakfast with the perfect omelette ❤️❤️❤️"
> **- Eya Barkaoui (5/5/5)**

> "Such a great experience here!! Wonderful selection of Western and Thai foods—fantastic happy hour! Mhok and his team made breakfast a wonderful experience every morning! We had the best stay and meals—highly recommend!"
> **- Kate Huggins (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tropikana-beach-bistro-1.jpg','077 246 362','14, T, 3, Thesaban Nakhon Ko Samui, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://pranaresortsamui.com/dining/','["Monday: 10:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 10:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 10:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 10:30 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 10:30 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.977+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.977+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tropikana-beach-bistro-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/tropikana-beach-bistro-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17560782288169813432',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('two-palms-beach-club','standard','cmr07ii9n00ygq8xdz8rworlj','Two Palms Beach Club','## Top Reviews
> "The place is newly open (I think) all the facilities are very well maintained and clean. Staffs are mostly Myanma so they cannot speak Thai. So if you are Thai or locals you might need to speak English with them.  I tried their signature drink today and it’s very enjoyable and refreshing.  Pool is nice and clean.  The only downside in my opinion is that they have no parking lots but plenty of street parking available. :)"
> **- Setthaporn Junhavitthaya (5/5/5)**

> "Enjoyable lunch with a view at this chillaxing beach club in Bang Por. Coffee is good as well as their range of cocktails. The place is readily equipped with set of loungers and seating areas to relax and immerse in the beach side ambience.  There is also bathroom available for showers; although I must describe the shower room could be better equipped / designed for areas to stow bags and towels, and places to put personal amenities on, despite the spacious interior - for true convenience of things.  Otherwise, a chic beach club serving good menus and drinks; with friendly staff and beautiful seafront setting in Bang Por beach."
> **- Wunda Stone (4/5/5)**

> "Amazing place to go for the day! Sun loungers, pool & beach! Fresh food and drinks with no minimum spend or a cost for sunloungers like a lot of places!  Pizza was yummy! And caesar salad was lovely and full of chicken! Owner and staff are lovely and super friendly! Will return many times!  Family day on a Sunday is fab! Bubble machine, DJ & inflatable water slide!"
> **- Aimee Chaplin (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/two-palms-beach-club-1.jpg','094 335 7008','73/8 Moo 6 Beach Tambon Mae Nam, Bangpor Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'https://karmacommunity.karmagroup.com/experience-karma/two-palms-samui-beach-club-magic/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifs1000cq8xdfo2aau32','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.979+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.979+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/two-palms-beach-club-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/two-palms-beach-club-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4871182331227905499',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('two-sister-burger','standard','cmr07ii9p00yhq8xdc28fcqlb','Two Sister Burger','## Top Reviews
> "⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐☆  I go into this review wanting to be fair — there were good moments, but some things didn’t live up to the expectations set by earlier reviews. The service was friendly and the ambiance pleasant, and that’s worth credit.  However, the fried rice was nothing special — just average, not really memorable. And the acai bowl I ordered also fell short; I was hoping it would be exceptional given the glowing reviews I had seen, but it was simply okay.  Overall, I’d still give it 4 stars — it’s a good place, and there are definite positives, but I can’t say it wowed me in every dish."
> **- Stefan Pichler (4/5/5)**

> "such a sweet little spot with the best vegan food. The chili basil with Tempe was delicious - make sure to add the soy sauce with ginger and fresh chillies 🌶️ and the vegan carrot cake sooooo yum"
> **- Hannah whittington (5/5/5)**

> "Best place to eat in all of MaeNam. I had breakfast and lunch here a couple times. Amazing selection of food.  With some Thai and western options.  Def check out their breakfasts. I’m not vegan but I do love good vegan food.  And they have a great selection of it."
> **- Eddy (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/two-sister-burger-1.jpg','082 806 3710','Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://m.facebook.com/pages/category/Burger-Restaurant/Two-SisterBurger-878608755854536/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.981+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.981+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/two-sister-burger-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/two-sister-burger-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12006225351697893367',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ubox-samui-hostel','standard','cmr07ii9q00yiq8xdxnj6ihfc','UBOX Samui Hostel','## Top Reviews
> "I had a serious safety incident during my stay at Ubox Samui Hostel. A glass shower door shattered while I was using the bathroom, causing severe injuries to my wrist, including damage to an artery, tendon, and nerve. I required emergency medical treatment and surgery, and I spent two days in the hospital.  After the incident, I noticed that other glass shower doors on the property had visible cracks, which raised further concerns about guest safety and maintenance. I have photos documenting the shattered door, my injury, staff cleaning the area, and other damaged shower doors.  I contacted the hostel three separate times through WhatsApp to request reimbursement for my medical expenses, but my messages were ignored. The hostel also did not refund my stay or reimburse me for the days I missed while I was hospitalized. Instead, I was told that I was “lucky” the owner was not making me pay for the broken door.  Additionally, after the incident, staff threw away my shoes because they were covered in blood, and my silver Cuban link bracelet was removed and never recovered. The hostel denied knowledge of the bracelet and did not reimburse me for the shoes.  Based on my experience, I cannot recommend this hostel. The lack of safety, accountability, and communication after a major injury was extremely concerning. Please see the attached photos showing the shattered glass door that exploded under normal use and the condition of another shower door we found."
> **- abrahim benzina (1/5/5)**

> "At first I liked the place, staff was really nice. But on the last morning I was the only one in the dorm and went to take a shower. I saw that the cleaning team went into my room while I brushed my teeth. When I came back 1000 Baht were stolen. Glad I didn''t have more money.. I went to the staff and told them what just happened but they told my that their cleaning personell would never steal money. I read the reviews and I''m one of alot people where that happened, even in private rooms."
> **- Sophia (1/5/5)**

> "The staff were very helpful with upgrading our room as we had problems with cockroaches, they made sure to be very accommodating and checked in with us though out our stay. However upon checking out the lady at reception tried keeping our 500baht deposit and kept saying she already gave it to us"
> **- Jarrod White (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ubox-samui-hostel-1.jpg','083 898 2858','162/212 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'https://call.whatsapp.com/voice/cAIbZemzQ713iBnKXzpmyx',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.982+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.982+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ubox-samui-hostel-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ubox-samui-hostel-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14823058623952006401',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('ultra-bodies-gym','standard','cmr07ii9s00yjq8xdoefsgr05','Ultra Bodies Gym','## Top Reviews
> "It’s a really great gym with very friendly staff who keep things organized and make sure everyone follows the rules. The gym has a wide variety of good equipment, though the selection is understandably limited given the size of the facility. As a result, it can get a bit crowded in the mornings. Overall, it’s very clean and tidy. Towels are included. For a daily rate of 300 THB, it’s a great deal."
> **- Jaan R9 (4/5/5)**

> "Great gym located in an easy to find area and with lots of scooter parking.  Definitely on the smaller side size wise, but packed with everything you need for a great workout. Day pass was 250baht which was very fair for the facilities.  Gym was spotless and machines well maintained, 2 floors with cardio upstairs and weights downstairs, and fully air conditioned!  Worth a visit if you want to workout on holidays."
> **- Tazio Lai (4/5/5)**

> "Small community older well used gym with a good selection of machines and freeweights. Dumbbells to 50kg. Overall, I feel lucky this gym is here and use it almost every day. So this isn''t complaining... it''s merely suggesting.  The equipment needs some serious help. Cut my leg just barely brushing against the leg curl squeezing by. Judging by the electrical tape... I wasn''t the first victim. The lateral raise for delts, as well as the abductor and adductor machines are all seriously misaligned. The standing calf looks about to have an "
> **- Michael Wolff (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ultra-bodies-gym-1.jpg','077 963 393','139 / 48-49 Moo 4 Thambon Maret Lamai Thambon Maret Lamai, ตำบล มะเร็ต อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifuo0015q8xdfahzrsp4','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.984+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.984+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ultra-bodies-gym-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/ultra-bodies-gym-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4805393603583735600',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('uniqlo-central-samui','standard','cmr07ii9t00ykq8xdt7z8nbko','UNIQLO @ Central Samui','## Top Reviews
> "You''d think you''re in Europe or the US. Not the authentic Thai experience ;-) But if you like brand stores, this one is the one to visit. Spacious, beautifully decorated and organized, like all the Uniqlo stores, as you can judge on the photos. As usual, a very wide choice of Uniqlo products of all kind and at prices which seemed to me cheaper than in Europe (although, I confess, I was unable to really compare).. The attendants were nice and so the service was good.  Bottom line: worth the visit."
> **- Dan M (5/5/5)**

> "Clean and organized store, good service. They have tax free."
> **- Shani Bar Yosef (5/5/5)**

> "Good quality linen which is what you would expect from Uniqlo. Store was clean and easy enough to find what you are after. Did not get greated or approached during entire time. Pricing is good as the quality is good, standard Uniqlo store."
> **- Matthew Hansen (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/uniqlo-central-samui-1.jpg','077 410 348','209, 209/1, 209/2 Moo 2, Bophut, Koh Samui, Suratthani, 1st floor, Room no. 143, 144, CentralFestival Samui, ตำบล บ่อผุด Koh Samui, Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.uniqlo.com/th/th/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.985+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.985+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/uniqlo-central-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/uniqlo-central-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=4437431518001124805',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('unique-boutique-resort','standard','cmr07ii9v00ylq8xd2iwsta8p','UniQue Boutique Resort','## Top Reviews
> "We were blown away, having booked the sunset suite, from the moment we arrived we were treated like VIP’s l. The concierge Wan was fantastic, she gave us a guided tour of the resort and then took us to the room.  Where she had taken the liberty of placing one of the keys in the room to set the a/c. When she drew back the curtains, we were left breathless by the stunning view that lay before us. Looking out over the bay towards the setting sun, was astonishing. The room is large, the bed oh so comfy and the ceiling fan above the bed was just a small bonus. These suites are sleek and modern, with a massive balcony to sit and watch the glorious sunsets as they disappear into the sea. Then there is the pool…. This is an OMG pool, looking towards the setting sun and to watch the planes as they glide in on their approach to the airport, never grew old. The restaurant butts up along side, where you can order drinks and food to eat while enjoying the relaxing time poolside. The staff here are amazing, nothing seemed to be any trouble. The property is perched high on a hill, which affords its stunning views. A lot of people had cars or motorbikes, but the resort also offers a free courtesy shuttle, to take you to the lower edge and will collect you if needed, just a text on WhatsApp and the friendly driver will be there. We loved it so much that we canceled our extra nights back on the mainland to stay longer.  The Breakfast is à la carte, which offers variety.  People actually book the restaurant just for its amazing sunset view.  Maithy restaurant which is a part of the resort, offers a wide variety of cuisine and will be sure to have something to whet your appetite. We loved it and we are talking about our next visit already."
> **- Stephen Barber (5/5/5)**

> "Thank you to the lovely staff for all the kindness & helpfulness. Japan saved the day on our last night when I lost my AirPods and she went out of her way to help me, a hero! The housekeeping team was incredible, our room was always spotless and organized everyday. The security guards were also very kind. Thank you!  We rented a car so the hills weren’t that big of a deal for us. But we did find trying to come home everyday was a struggle because there’s 2 entrances but the one they want you to enter isn’t on the maps & very hard to find on the street. Very hidden, so that was frustrating. And the gym didn’t open till 8 which was very frustrating because we wanted to workout in the morning but it was too late. Other than that I think the staff & the room was the best part!"
> **- Cali Schwetz (4/5/5)**

> "My family and I stayed on the residence side for one week. The room was spacious, and the air conditioning worked very well. However, the water heater and water pressure were poor. Maintenance came to fix the heater, but the next day water was leaking everywhere. I believe this was not the maintenance team’s fault, but rather due to an old water heater.  During our stay, the shower alternated between hot and cold water with no warm option. Washing my long hair was especially difficult.  If you stay on the residence side, you do not receive the same level of service as on the hotel side. It feels like being treated as second-class guests. On the hotel side, there is shuttle service to take you down the hill, which is not available for residence guests.  I agree that the view from the room is amazing, but due to the difficult location, I would not recommend staying on this property. Even if you have a car, the road is very narrow with tight turns, making it stressful to drive in and out. Taxis charge at least 300 baht even for short trips nearby.  Overall, the cost of living in Samui in 2026 is at least 30% higher than the past year. P.S. We have visited Samui almost every year."
> **- thi vit (2/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/unique-boutique-resort-1.jpg','096 792 1675','เลขที่ 30/209, H388+98V ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.1,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.uniquekohsamui.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 12:00 PM, 1:00 – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 12:00 PM, 1:00 – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 12:00 PM, 1:00 – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 12:00 PM, 1:00 – 5:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 12:00 PM, 1:00 – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 12:00 PM, 1:00 – 5:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.987+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.987+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/unique-boutique-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/unique-boutique-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11424494049894312737',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('unique-samui-travel','standard','cmr07ii9y00ymq8xdgq5icesw','Unique Samui Travel','## Top Reviews
> "This company was so easy to deal with and so helpful. I dealt with Kenya who helped me arrange the half day trip to pig island and Koh Tan. They had a great selection of boats that she sent photos and I was able to select the boat we wanted. Transfer pickup from hotel was included. The company is very organised and the captain and our guide Jing on the boat were lovely and so helpful. We enjoyed several snorkeling and fishing spots during the trip. We felt extremely safe and comfortable on this boat. They were also great with the kids. When I mentioned it was my husbands birthday when booking, they organised a birthday cake for him on board which was so lovely. We also had snacks, fruit, water and soft drinks included. Thank you Unique Samui travel and our guide Jing for a fantastic day."
> **- Jessica B (5/5/5)**

> "An absolute 10/10 experience! We opted for the VIP private charter for a sunset cruise and it was breathtaking. The agency handled every detail perfectly, allowing us to just relax and enjoy the stunning views. Highly recommend for anyone wanting an intimate and luxurious island-hopping adventure in Samui."
> **- Madam Chalita (5/5/5)**

> "We had a fantastic experience booking with Bammy, she’s so easy to deal with, has a great personality and made sure everything was booked properly so our trip ran smoothly, from excursions to transfers and ferries. Would highly recommend booking with Bammy and team in the future. ❤️"
> **- Anand (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/unique-samui-travel-1.jpg','095 412 1145','160, 12 หมู่ที่ 2 ตำบล บ่อผุด Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://uniquesamuitravel.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ig1n003kq8xd72v6yb3r','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.990+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.990+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/unique-samui-travel-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/unique-samui-travel-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16915376207308642746',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('us-hostel','standard','cmr07iia000ynq8xdefak37ov','US Hostel','## Top Reviews
> "I spent five lovely days at the Us Hostel and would highly recommend it. It''s certainly not a party hostel, but it''s well located and quiet. It''s also quick and easy to get to lively places. I would also recommend hiring a scooter (if you feel confident enough). As a guest, you can even rent one without a deposit for 250 baht per day. The return was also very straightforward."
> **- Sebastian Wagner (5/5/5)**

> "Enjoyed my stay in Koh Samui! The common areas and pool are brilliant and the food is great. I didn’t find it the most social hostel but I may have just been unlucky, I did still make a couple of friends but people didn’t interact with each other much and vibes were very chill. The rooms are small and the beds are a little creaky with no curtains and limited storage space. During my stay the water went off one night but it was fixed by the morning. The staff were really friendly and helpful! I’d stay again."
> **- Lauren Pascolutti (4/5/5)**

> "We originally only booked for 1 night but extended without hesitation! The hostel has such a warm and welcoming atmosphere and the staff are so friendly! There is plenty of social space but is big enough if you do just want to sit by yourself to chill too. We rented a bike from the hostel (super easy) and had breakfast here both mornings. A great menu with lots of choices of different things to eat, and so tasty! A great location too, a 10 minute walk to the food market and walking street!Would 100% recommend! ❤️🙏🏼"
> **- Mia Ellahee (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/us-hostel-1.jpg','095 427 1525','165/192, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'http://ushostelsamui.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.992+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.992+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/us-hostel-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/us-hostel-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14992108303026300862',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('vaedana-clinic','standard','cmr07iia200yoq8xdwlwnzay7','Vaedana Clinic','## Top Reviews
> "⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐  I recently visited Vaedana Clinic Samui for Ultrafirmer III treatment and full body laser hair removal, and I couldn''t be more impressed with the experience.  From the moment I arrived, the staff were welcoming, professional, and attentive. The clinic is modern, spotless, and has a very relaxing atmosphere. The team took the time to explain each treatment thoroughly, answer all of my questions, and ensure I was comfortable throughout the entire process.  The Ultrafirmer III treatment was performed with great care and professionalism, and the laser hair removal treatment was efficient and surprisingly comfortable. The attention to detail and level of customer service were exceptional from start to finish.  What really sets Vaedana Clinic apart is the genuine care they show their clients. Everyone was friendly, knowledgeable, and highly skilled, making the whole experience feel effortless and enjoyable.  I would highly recommend Vaedana Clinic Samui to anyone looking for high-quality aesthetic treatments and outstanding service. I will definitely be returning for future treatments.  Thank you to the entire team for such a fantastic experience."
> **- Neil Thorpe (5/5/5)**

> "I had a facial treatment at this clinic, and really enjoyed the experience. The treatment included 9 different steps, which made it feel very thorough and professional. The place is clean, pleasant, and beautiful design. The treatment included the use of advanced technology equipment during the treatment. Overall, I had a great experience and would definitely recommend this clinic."
> **- מגנטים ענבר איזנמן Inbar Eisenman Imagnetim (5/5/5)**

> "This place is a delight from the first glance! Stylish interior, impeccable cleanliness, incredibly friendly receptionists. The staff is very caring and attentive! You will be provided with professional service and surrounded by comfort 😍👍."
> **- Alexandra Shi (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/vaedana-clinic-1.jpg','095 038 6363','Vaedanaclinic 128/105-6 เวดาน่า คลินิก หมู่ที่ 1 ซอยโรงพยาบาลบ้านดอน Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://vaedanaclinic.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.994+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.994+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/vaedana-clinic-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/vaedana-clinic-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17589635441062927824',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('vana-belle-kiree-international-restaurant','standard','cmr07iia500ypq8xdfmg0w5wc','Vana Belle - Kiree International Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "We ate breakfast at Kiree as part of our stay at the resort. Overall, the breakfast spread was excellent, with plenty of options to suit different tastes and cuisines. The à la carte menu was particularly strong and, in my opinion, better than the buffet. Incredible ocean views as well, both inside and out.  On our first morning, I ordered the açaí bowl from the menu. It was delicious but surprisingly small. Since no one explained on the first day that we could continue ordering from the menu or offered additional items, I ended up supplementing with the buffet, which wasn’t nearly as good.  On our second morning, I ordered the avocado toast, which was excellent. Unfortunately, while I was still eating it, a staff member attempted to clear my plate (I was only 1/3 of the way finished). I repeatedly said that I was not finished and asked them not to take it, but it was removed anyway.  Thankfully they told us this day that we could order more, so I tried (twice) to reorder so I could finish my breakfast, but neither replacement matched what I had originally been served. The eggs were undercooked, the toast wasn’t toasted (just bread), and I ultimately never got the chance to finish my meal.  It seemed possible that the staff were trying to rush the end of breakfast service, which may explain why my food was taken before I had finished eating and both replacements were undercooked in multiple ways. However, regardless of the reason, it was frustrating to have my meal removed after clearly stating that I was still eating.  Had I been allowed to finish the original avocado toast, this easily would have been a 5-star breakfast experience. The food quality was very good and the service was attentive, but not listening when a guest clearly says they are still eating put a significant damper on the experience. I left hungry and disappointed, which was unfortunate given how strong the (original) food itself was."
> **- Tierney Becton (3/5/5)**

> "Dined here after their impressive catering at the hotel''s wine event. Food was good. Flavours and freshness of the produce were nice, and so were the presentation. Hospitality and service active and thorough.  Although some hiccups with the food: I found my seabass to be under portioned, while my companion went for the salmon and it''s just so sumptuous in comparison. The prawn bisque had two scallops in there - fresh and nicely flavoured - but, the soup itself lacks this dense, fatty texture of the bisque and the one here is just a little too water down. Companions had very positive feedbacks on the salmon steak and the spaghetti aglio olio.  Ambiance is calm and intimate. We dined indoors, cooly airconditioned, which I''d say is perfect to enjoy glasses of red with the meal.  Their extensive wine list features some very nice bottles. I especially enjoyed one of the Chianti here."
> **- Wunda Stone (4/5/5)**

> "This restaurant is the main restaurant in Vana Belle resort. It''s on hillside facing to the sea.  There are both Thai and Eastern menu. All of them are delicious. Staffs are kind and polite. I would like to acknowledge to one of the waitress namely "
> **- Kritsana Potsatian (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/vana-belle-kiree-international-restaurant-1.jpg','077 915 555','9/99 Moo 3, Chaweng Noi Beach Koh Samui 9 99 Chaweng Noi Beach Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.4,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.marriott.com/en-us/dining/restaurant-bar/usmvl-vana-belle-a-luxury-collection-resort-koh-samui/6968706-kiree.mi','["Monday: 7:00 – 10:30 AM, 6:00 – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 – 10:30 AM, 6:00 – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 – 10:30 AM, 6:00 – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 – 10:30 AM, 6:00 – 10:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 – 10:30 AM, 6:00 – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 – 10:30 AM, 6:00 – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 – 10:30 AM, 6:00 – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig5c0051q8xdykrbexft','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:13.997+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:13.997+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/vana-belle-kiree-international-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/vana-belle-kiree-international-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=18190373101371361752',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('vana-belle-luxury-resort','standard','cmr07iia800yqq8xdksbfcp5i','Vana Belle Luxury Resort','## Top Reviews
> "Absolutely wonderful experience!!! We were traveling as a family of 9 and celebrating milestones for our parents. The staff went out of their way to make the stay memorable for all of us, taking care of our every request and going over and beyond without even asking. The rooms are indeed old, but whatever lacks there is enough and more compensated with the unmatched service and the tranquil surroundings.  A special shout-out to Tik, our butler, who took care of our every request with the brightest smile and truly delighted us with a wonderful surprise during the milestone celebration. Chef Freddie and his team were brilliant with coming up with creative solutions for our dietary preferences, Song at the check-in was great with problem-solving and accommodating our room requests and Alex at Concierge got us great recommendations for excursions.  Vana Belle team, you have won our hearts with your hospitality."
> **- Anushree Agarwal (5/5/5)**

> "Our stay at Vana Belle was nothing short of exceptional. From the moment we arrived, the hospitality and level of care from the team truly exceeded every expectation.  The resort graciously upgraded our room for our birthday and anniversary celebration, accommodated an early check-in, and prepared the most beautiful welcome set-up in our suite that instantly made the trip feel so special and memorable.  Every single staff member we encountered was warm, friendly, attentive, and always greeted us with a genuine smile. The service throughout the stay was flawless.  A very special thank you to C, who took incredible care of us from beginning to end. She checked in with us daily both in person and through messages, ensuring that everything was perfect throughout our stay. She was professional, thoughtful, precise, and delivered truly spotless service with such warmth and grace.  Another special shout out to Romi for the wonderful and smooth check-in experience that immediately made us feel welcomed and valued.  The breakfast each morning was excellent, the room was beautifully maintained, and the beach and pool area were absolutely stunning—peaceful, relaxing, and everything you would hope for in Koh Samui.  Amazing, amazing, amazing. This was genuinely one of the most memorable hotel experiences we’ve had, and honestly, we would return to Koh Samui just to stay at Vana Belle again."
> **- Branden Z (5/5/5)**

> "Our stay at Vana Belle, a Luxury Collection Resort, Koh Samui was absolutely exceptional. From the moment we arrived, everything felt truly luxurious.  A special thank you to Zidan, who went above and beyond to make sure we had the best stay possible. His attention to detail and genuine hospitality made a huge difference to our experience.  We would also like to thank our housekeeper, Ally, whose kindness and care kept our room spotless throughout our stay. Everything was immaculate, and it was clear that great pride is taken in maintaining the resort to such a high standard.  The beds were incredibly comfortable, the pool was beautiful, and the service throughout the resort was outstanding. Every member of the team made us feel welcome and well cared for.  A true 5-star experience from start to finish. We can’t wait to return! 🌴✨"
> **- Melissa Gonzalez (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/vana-belle-luxury-resort-1.jpg','077 915 555','9 Noi Beach, 99 Chaweng Beach Rd, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.marriott.com/en-us/hotels/usmvl-vana-belle-a-luxury-collection-resort-koh-samui/overview/?scid=f2ae0541-1279-4f24-b197-a979c79310b0',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ig5c0051q8xdykrbexft','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.000+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.000+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/vana-belle-luxury-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/vana-belle-luxury-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=8355706030719100549',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('vana-belle-panali-restaurant','standard','cmr07iiaa00yrq8xd27rz9e63','Vana Belle - Panali Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "The Thai food here is good, but not quite memorable enough to justify the price. Everything was well prepared, but the bill seemed more enthusiastic than the flavors. Worth a try, though I wouldn’t call it a great value.  Also, be prepared to share your dining experience with a surprisingly large number of mosquitoes. They seemed to enjoy the restaurant even more than I did."
> **- Carpe Diem Pirate (5/5/5)**

> "We ate at Panali for lunch after spending the morning on the beach while staying at the resort. My husband tends to prefer more traditional American and western food, while I’ll happily eat just about anything, so we appreciated how broad the menu was.  At least at lunch, there were essentially two full menus. One focused on traditional Thai dishes, while the poolside menu offered more western favorites. It made it easy for both of us to find something we were excited about.  My husband ordered the pepperoni pizza, and I had the Phad Thai Koh Samui with soft-shell crab. He really enjoyed his pizza, and I thought mine was very good. My only criticism was that I would have expected the soft-shell crab to be cleaned a bit better before serving. It still contained some of the internal organs and gills, which made it more work to eat than I would have preferred.  The setting is beautiful. We sat on the open-air deck beneath the trees overlooking the ocean. The entire restaurant is beachfront with fantastic views. We also walked by in the evening and loved the atmosphere created by the lights hanging from the trees, which gave the space a warm and inviting feel.  Service throughout our meal was attentive and friendly. Between the variety of menu options, the oceanfront setting, and the quality of the food, Panali was a great lunch spot and one we would happily visit again."
> **- Tierney Becton (5/5/5)**

> "The service was extremely friendly and attentive, making us feel very welcome from start to finish.  The highlight for me was the Tom Yum Goong – honestly the best I’ve had so far. Perfectly balanced, rich in flavor, and exactly how this iconic dish should taste.  Highly recommended if you’re staying at the hotel or looking for great Thai cuisine in a beautiful setting."
> **- Steven Neyer (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/vana-belle-panali-restaurant-1.jpg','077 915 555','9 99, Tambon Bo Put, Koh Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.marriott.com/en-us/hotels/usmvl-vana-belle-a-luxury-collection-resort-koh-samui/dining/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig5c0051q8xdykrbexft','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.002+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.002+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/vana-belle-panali-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/vana-belle-panali-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13425553026322416573',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('vanilla-restaurant','standard','cmr07iiac00ysq8xday7vqvfc','Vanilla Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "Daeng, Kikky and the whole team were amazing. This is by far one of the best experience we had in Thailand. The hotel was fantastic, the swimming pool and the view a dream. Thank you all for making our 10 days stay so wonderful."
> **- Aziza van der Hoek (5/5/5)**

> "Absolutely impeccable service, amazing food selection, reasonably priced, above and beyond Thai hospitality, and of course -- breathtaking view!  We stayed at the resort for two weeks and had dinner here on 3 separate occasions, each better than the last."
> **- Rob MacDonald (5/5/5)**

> "I had such an amazing time at the View kitchen & bar. Cocktails were amazing and food so delicious, so many choices for everyone. The staff is awesome. They are always smiling and willing to help you with anything. Nothing is a problem for them. Pin and Two miu have been really great and helpful throughout my stay at the hotel. Definitely recommend it, totally worth it. And the view from the restaurant is just stunning!!!"
> **- Mary Stamouli (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/vanilla-restaurant-1.jpg','081 137 9897','9/123-124, ตำบล แม่น้ำ อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://mantrasamui.com/dining/','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 7:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifs1000cq8xdfo2aau32','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.004+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.004+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/vanilla-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/vanilla-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16310127494321869678',NULL,NULL);
