INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('weddings-and-events-by-zazen','standard','cmr07iidq00zpq8xdhd6yz5r3','Weddings And Events By Zazen','## Top Reviews
> "Back in 2016, while visiting family in Koh Samui, we had a wonderful stay at Zazen Boutique Resort & Spa. The property was beautifully maintained, surrounded by lush tropical gardens that gave it a peaceful and private atmosphere. Our villa was spacious and comfortable—perfect for our family of four—and felt like a true island retreat.  The restaurant was outstanding, offering delicious Thai and international dishes, with a terrace overlooking the sea that made every meal feel special. Breakfast and dinners there were a highlight of our trip.  We also loved that the hotel was within easy walking distance to Bo Phut Fisherman’s Village, where we could explore local shops, beachside bars, and night markets.  Overall, it was a fantastic, relaxing stay, and one we still remember fondly. Highly recommended for families and couples looking for a peaceful, authentic Koh Samui experience."
> **- Sven Dutoit (5/5/5)**

> "The atmosphere was excellent, and the service was outstanding. The staff paid close attention to every detail, regularly checking on us regarding the service and the quality of the food. Most importantly, the food was absolutely delicious, especially the spaghetti dish. I would give it a perfect 10/10! I will definitely be coming back again. 😊"
> **- ดนยา เตียวสกุล (5/5/5)**

> "Zazen omg it’s amazing.Koh Samui must do ! This venue came highly recommended to us and it lived up to all expectations.On walking in through the magnificent gardens  to the restaurant you are met by the most attentive staff .You will be captivated by the restaurant which is absolutely gorgeous.We had a table on the waterfront it was magnificent. We chose the seafood banquet omg to die for ….yes it was so fresh ,delicious and the presentation (see pics ) The wine list was extensive as well ,we chose a Pinot Grigio from Italy paired beautifully. Dessert was amazing Zazen has absolutely nailed it …the attention to detail,the food choices ,the atmosphere and the decor which I believe was updated maybe a year ago. I found the staff to be so engaging and happy to help with dietary requirements and above all very attentive without over doing it Not forgetting the incredible backdrop This would be an amazing venue for a function On another note I was fortunate to have their Signature Aromatherapy massage let me tell you if you can just do it !!!! Bliss so professional One last thing the gift shop was great for those last minute gifts for home"
> **- Glynda Curtin (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/weddings-and-events-by-zazen-1.jpg','077 425 085','177 Beach Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.samuizazen.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.126+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.126+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/weddings-and-events-by-zazen-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/weddings-and-events-by-zazen-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3328826799020832534',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('weddings-by-code','standard','cmr07iids00zqq8xdyag67lk6','Weddings By Code','## Top Reviews
> "Juliette was the wedding planner for our wedding in Koh Samui in February 2025. She was a great help in many areas, from finding the right location to our amazing floral decorations, she has a fantastic network of partners. No matter how weird your request is, Juliette will pull out all the stops and make it happen, in my case it was a flamingo for the bar decoration.  Thanks to her and her team, we were able to enjoy the day to the fullest and sit back and relax. The wedding was perfect for us in every way and nothing was left to be desired.  Once again a huge thank you to Juliette and her great team, we can highly recommend them."
> **- Anda Blume (5/5/5)**

> "Wow, we has the pleasure of working with Juliette and her amazing team who truely made our special day unforgettable. From the very first meeting, she took the time to understand our vision and preferences, making us feel supported and excited about the planning process.  On the day of the wedding, Juliette and her team managed and coordinated everything seamlessly including the logistics, the amazing vendors and the timeline, ensuring that every aspect of the wedding was perfect, which allowed us to enjoy our time in the moment and celebrate with our loved ones.  Our wedding day was truely amazing and we cannot thank Juliette and her team enough for putting it all together! So if you are looking for a professional and creative team who are dedicated to making your special day as perfect as ours was, we would highly recommend Weddings on Samui!  Laura & Blayne - From Australia"
> **- Laura Abela (5/5/5)**

> "We highly recommend Weddings on Samui! Genuine, honest and trustworthy! Juliette created the most magical weddingday for us and our family. If you’re looking for a wedding planner in Thailand you can stop looking now, just contact Weddings on Samui! You will forever have a place in our hearts Juliette, thank you so much for everything you did for us from our first contact, all the way to the altar and beyond!"
> **- Jennie Hübinette (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/weddings-by-code-1.jpg','090 094 6583','69/55 Beach Plai Laem Soi 2, Tambon Bo Put, Koh Samui Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.weddingsonsamui.com/?utm_source=google&utm_medium=wix_google_business_profile&utm_campaign=14521569900628409327','["Monday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 7:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 2:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifs1000cq8xdfo2aau32','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.128+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.128+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/weddings-by-code-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/weddings-by-code-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3094828982989142783',NULL,NULL);
