INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('weekender-resort','standard','cmr07iidy00zsq8xdluxf0wun','Weekender Resort','## Top Reviews
> "First place in Thailand were staff blatanly ignored us. We had a lot of problems with our rooms. In the main building renovation was activly taking place, there was a constant smell of paint. Nobody mentioned that, nobody offered us different room.  Thankfully the next day the manager upgraded for free to bungalow, but there were still problems with sewer. I called to reception and nothing happened, i guess the staff wanted us to resolve it by ourselfes.  And most importantly, water in rooms is salty, i couldn''t wash anyting while i stayed here. Somehow the shower at the beach was normal.  The beach is fine, water is deep, green and somewhat clean, very warm. It has a strange smell of wet cellar somehow. Near hotel''s beach located water scouters and stuff like that, that was very annoying, constant noise.  The breakfast was ok, sufficent enough, not many to choose from.  There are many places to eat and massage, the nigh market withing 5 minutes walking  Also hotel has an option to book a minibus for 2400 baht for 4 hours and driver will take you around the island, wherever you ask to. Driver was amazing. Great deal, definetly recommend."
> **- Мария Бурнашова (2/5/5)**

> "I stayed here for 3 nights and paid 10,000 baht. Unfortunately, the room condition was not very good, but I still decided to stay in the same room. One issue I faced was in the bathroom—when taking a shower, water would leak outside the bathtub and make the floor wet. The breakfast was average, nothing special. However, the swimming pool was very nice and well-maintained, which I really enjoyed. Overall, the stay was okay, but the room condition and bathroom setup could definitely be improved."
> **- abhishek sunder lal (3/5/5)**

> "The Weekender is a great affordable option. Rooms are basic, but have everything you need. The only issue was the bathroom. The water goes all over the floor and its constantly wet, but once you get used to its all good. The grounds, beach, pool, restaurant, location are all absolutely awesome and the staff were so welcoming and friendly. We will definitely be coming back!"
> **- Maria Sap (4/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/weekender-resort-1.jpg','077 424 429','124/19, ตำบล มะเร็ต อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.1,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.weekenderresort.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.134+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.134+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/weekender-resort-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/weekender-resort-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9664132677335006388',NULL,NULL);
