> **- Kim K (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/white-sand-weddings-1.jpg','095 284 6999','124, F23R+V7R, 5 ตําบล, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.1,0,0,0,NULL,'https://whitesandsamuiresort.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.152+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.152+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/white-sand-weddings-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/white-sand-weddings-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6459144622647052808',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('white-whale-beachfront-pool-villa','standard','cmr07iiej00zzq8xd282ih7rq','White Whale Beachfront Pool Villa','## Top Reviews
> "If you crave a peaceful, serene and rustic stay then this ticks all the boxes.  The staff were exceptional- smiley and friendly and always ready to help. They never said no to customising my breakfast and also gifted me with the whale soft toy at the end of my stay because i mentioned its comfy to hug to sleep!  Area is perfect for local and quiet vibes but has walkable dining options along the stretch of beach. 7-11 across the street! You can tell the love, care and.  thoughtfulness that the owner and team has put into this place. For example, the room came with nespresso, plenty of free water, complimentary mini bar of drinks and snacks! Such a lovely thoughtful touch to ensure the guests feel comfortable.  Also, they provide bath robes, beach sarong, beach bag and indoor slippers.  One thing to note is if you’re sharing the room, the toilet and shower doors are clear glass."
> **- Rina R (5/5/5)**

> "White Whale has honestly been one of the highlights of our stay in Koh Samui. The villas are stunning with such a clean, luxe feel and waking up to that ocean view every morning is unreal. It’s peaceful, private and feels like your own little escape while still being close to everything."
> **- Renee Houston (5/5/5)**

> "Beautiful beautiful property. The rooms are tastefully made,the view was fantastic. The staff were extremely polite and helpful. Every person we met was very kind and welcoming. The breakfast was very good. Room amenities were good.  I have absolutely nothing to complain about. Our holiday was perfect and I was happy I chose white whale :)"
> **- Lakshmi Bhat (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/white-whale-beachfront-pool-villa-1.jpg','062 205 7676','56/24, ตำบล แม่น้ำ อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/share/18tYBhP7tD/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifs1000cq8xdfo2aau32','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.155+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.155+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/white-whale-beachfront-pool-villa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/white-whale-beachfront-pool-villa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5035246925883925814',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('wild-action-samui','standard','cmr07iiel0100q8xdot1as0we','Wild Action Samui','## Top Reviews
> "We did the 2 hour trip which was awesome. The guides  supportive and really make the trip wonderful. We had a very inexperienced rider on our trip and they assisted her the whole time. My partner even managed to fit in a zip line from the Tree Bridge which was a great spot. Thankyou team you were very patient and accomodating to the whole group."
> **- Sam McBride (5/5/5)**

> "Great tour, nice gear and the guides are fantastic! They’re good people and go out of their way to show you a good time 👍 I highly recommend."
> **- van Dijk (5/5/5)**

> "I was last year in Thailand and had a good ATV trip but listen to me Aiman and the staff made it a great trip, we had so much fun, new and maintained ATV’s and the buggy is something extreme that you must try if you love  5/5"
> **- IGD CARS רכבי יוקרה (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wild-action-samui-1.jpg','092 170 4448','HX3R+P99, Mae Nam, Ko Samui District, Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.wildactionsamui.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.157+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.157+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wild-action-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wild-action-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6318822645928168279',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('wild-child-organic-kitchen','standard','cmr07iieq0101q8xdluedlkas','Wild Child Organic Kitchen','## Top Reviews
> "This was truly a wonderful and unique experience for the whole family. The location is absolutely beautiful, the atmosphere is amazing, and the food was delicious. Every dish was prepared with great care and tasted fantastic.  The service was outstanding — all the staff were very friendly, attentive, and accommodating, making us feel very welcome throughout our visit. The pool area is also beautiful and added even more to this special experience.  We can highly recommend this place to everyone. It is something truly unique that you will remember for a long time and an experience you should not miss. Thank you for creating such a memorable time for us!"
> **- Sina Bambina (5/5/5)**

> "What a beautiful place. So relaxing! Watching the elephants roam around doing their own thing was so delightful. And feeding them was lovely too. The staff, the location, the food, all just absolutely outstanding. We spent 6 hours here at the pool and its worth every penny. 100% recommend a visit!"
> **- Laura Newman (5/5/5)**

> "I booked the Day Pass with pool access and was truly impressed from the moment I arrived. The location is stunning, and the food exceeded all expectations – and that''s saying something, considering the 1,500 THB minimum spend is included in the package. You get incredible value: the menu is delicious, fresh, and more than satisfying. What makes it even more special is that at least part of the ingredients are grown organically in their own on-site garden – you can really taste the difference.  What makes this place truly unique, though, is being able to watch the elephants directly from the pool. I''ve never experienced anything like it. The enclosure is spacious and thoughtfully designed – plenty of room for the two elephants to roam freely and simply be themselves.  Once a day, guests get the chance to feed them melons for around 30 to 60 minutes, which is a wonderful and memorable experience. What I appreciated most is the ethical approach: the elephants are never forced to interact. They do their own thing, move at their own pace, and if they disappear for an hour, that''s completely fine – and honestly, that''s exactly how it should be. No riding, no bathing sessions, no touching. Just elephants living as elephants.  If you want to be close to elephants in a responsible, ethical way – without exploiting them – this is the place to be. Highly recommended!"
> **- Habs No (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wild-child-organic-kitchen-1.jpg','062 375 5786','137/31, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.wildchild-samui.com/','["Monday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.163+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.163+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wild-child-organic-kitchen-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wild-child-organic-kitchen-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16850097400230483963',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('wild-cottages-sanctuary','standard','cmr07iiez0102q8xdpifhibj3','Wild Cottages Sanctuary','## Top Reviews
> "We had an absolutely amazing stay at White Cottage. The hotel itself is beautiful, peaceful, and feels truly special, but what made the experience unforgettable was the staff. Every single person was incredibly kind, warm, and genuinely cared that we felt comfortable and enjoyed every moment of our stay. You can really feel how much effort they put into making guests happy.  The service was outstanding from beginning to end, always with a smile and positive attitude. The restaurant was excellent as well — delicious food, great atmosphere, and everything felt fresh and high quality.  The elephants were adorable, and it was clear they are being cared for with love and attention, which was very important for us to see.  Highly, highly recommended. We would gladly come back again."
> **- The Guy 007 (5/5/5)**

> "Everything about this hotel is perfect. So magical that you can be in your beautifully designed room and see the most amazing creatures down below you. Being able to feed the elephants as a part of your stay is an unbelievable memory to have. Every member of staff is amazing, they work so hard and put their guests first. The restaurant is very reasonable with amazingly presented food and the spa massage was incredible."
> **- Brad Mayes (5/5/5)**

> "It’s a beautiful resort, truly. It’s amazing to be able to be so close to the elephants. The room was beautiful.  The room pool was beautiful but just a little cold.  However, they have some major issues with their checkout system. I came to the lobby to checkout, when they told me I needed to wait so they could go check the room to make sure we didn’t take any of their items for purchase. My husband was in the room with our toddler since it was up 7 flights of stairs and he couldn’t leave to take all of our bags down by himself. They told me I would have to wait until my husband left the room to settle our bill. In every other hotel I’ve stayed at, this is why they take a deposit. Instead, we were made to wait while rushing to get a taxi for our ferry. Worst of all, the owners were speaking rudely about my situation in French (saying it was our fault) and I could understand every word."
> **- Caitlyn Kim (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wild-cottages-sanctuary-1.jpg','065 574 5241','137/31, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.wild-cottages.com/',NULL,'cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.171+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.171+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wild-cottages-sanctuary-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wild-cottages-sanctuary-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9111876331836960836',NULL,NULL);
