> **- Caitlyn Kim (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wild-cottages-spa-1.jpg','065 574 5241','137/31, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.wild-cottages.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.173+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.173+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wild-cottages-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wild-cottages-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9111876331836960836',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('wild-cottages','standard','cmr07iif40104q8xdxudeozte','Wild Cottages','## Top Reviews
> "We had an absolutely amazing stay at White Cottage. The hotel itself is beautiful, peaceful, and feels truly special, but what made the experience unforgettable was the staff. Every single person was incredibly kind, warm, and genuinely cared that we felt comfortable and enjoyed every moment of our stay. You can really feel how much effort they put into making guests happy.  The service was outstanding from beginning to end, always with a smile and positive attitude. The restaurant was excellent as well — delicious food, great atmosphere, and everything felt fresh and high quality.  The elephants were adorable, and it was clear they are being cared for with love and attention, which was very important for us to see.  Highly, highly recommended. We would gladly come back again."
> **- The Guy 007 (5/5/5)**

> "Everything about this hotel is perfect. So magical that you can be in your beautifully designed room and see the most amazing creatures down below you. Being able to feed the elephants as a part of your stay is an unbelievable memory to have. Every member of staff is amazing, they work so hard and put their guests first. The restaurant is very reasonable with amazingly presented food and the spa massage was incredible."
> **- Brad Mayes (5/5/5)**

> "It’s a beautiful resort, truly. It’s amazing to be able to be so close to the elephants. The room was beautiful.  The room pool was beautiful but just a little cold.  However, they have some major issues with their checkout system. I came to the lobby to checkout, when they told me I needed to wait so they could go check the room to make sure we didn’t take any of their items for purchase. My husband was in the room with our toddler since it was up 7 flights of stairs and he couldn’t leave to take all of our bags down by himself. They told me I would have to wait until my husband left the room to settle our bill. In every other hotel I’ve stayed at, this is why they take a deposit. Instead, we were made to wait while rushing to get a taxi for our ferry. Worst of all, the owners were speaking rudely about my situation in French (saying it was our fault) and I could understand every word."
> **- Caitlyn Kim (3/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wild-cottages-1.jpg','065 574 5241','137/31, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.wild-cottages.com/',NULL,'cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.176+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.176+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wild-cottages-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wild-cottages-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=9111876331836960836',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('wild-ginger-restaurant-and-bar','standard','cmr07iif70105q8xdqxlxdykm','Wild Ginger Restaurant And Bar','## Top Reviews
> "Was on the set menu but it had both Thai and Western options. Everything I had was great. The normal options looked interesting also. Breakfast was varied and good"
> **- John Bain (4/5/5)**

> "We ate at this wonderful place for a week. A restaurant with a terrace overlooking the sea, excellent food, impeccable service, and friendly staff. Highly recommended."
> **- Alessandro Cesca (5/5/5)**

> "From pick up to end of the first week, the Chefs to waiter''s were excellent. Service with a smile, no food suggestions were a problem and every taste a sensation. Special shout out to Mr Joe, Koko and Ang who were our constant waiter''s from breakfast, through lunch and into dinner. And if you like Bloody Mary''s then Mr Joe is your man. Sensational. Thank you Wild Ginger. Michael, Julie, Andy and Janine."
> **- Michael Carney (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wild-ginger-restaurant-and-bar-1.jpg','077 448 540','95, 96 Chaweng Noi Beach, Bophut, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.thesarann.com/our-restaurant/','["Monday: 11:30 AM – 9:30 PM","Tuesday: 11:30 AM – 9:30 PM","Wednesday: 11:30 AM – 9:30 PM","Thursday: 11:30 AM – 9:30 PM","Friday: 11:30 AM – 9:30 PM","Saturday: 11:30 AM – 9:30 PM","Sunday: 11:30 AM – 9:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig5c0051q8xdykrbexft','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.179+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.179+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wild-ginger-restaurant-and-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wild-ginger-restaurant-and-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=1638942831223938010',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('wild-tribe-superfood-cafe','standard','cmr07iif90106q8xdduk2jucp','Wild Tribe Superfood Cafe','## Top Reviews
> "🩷🩷🩷 It felt like one of those places people truly fall in love with 🥹🌿 so green, so calm… like a little escape  You can really feel why everyone loves it such a peaceful, gentle atmosphere  We had falafel, Japanese soba with vegetables, Indian samosa, and a beans roll and Cadadilia 😋 simple, fresh, and made with care  And the kombucha with lemongrass… so refreshing ✨  The girls there are so kind and sweet you feel it right away 🤍"
> **- Elvira (5/5/5)**

> "The best food!!!! SO fresh. SO delicious. YUMM. I think the best we had in Thailand. Had the wrap it up with guacamole, the quesadillas in vegan, the pink passion roles with tofu and the spicy mushroom tofu salad. think the favourite were the quesadillas but the wrap it up were SO fresh 😍 100% recommend. Also free drinks a plus as it’s quite pricey but worth it."
> **- Magdalena Ros (5/5/5)**

> "10/10 for the food and drinks here. It was all really tasty. I''d recommend it all - I had the Viva Burrito which was a really excellent vegan burrito even compared to London standards. I loved that it had beans, tofu, peppers, lettuce, rice AND guac!  I also had the herby salad - I didn''t care for the dressing so I asked for lime and olive oil which went brilliantly.  And then finally I had the tofu satay skewers which came with a satay sauce and pickled veg.  We also a decaf iced latte which was excellent coffee.  The staff are nice and speak good English. Portions and prices are good."
> **- Charlotte Owen (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wild-tribe-superfood-cafe-1.jpg','082 383 5983','129, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,'https://visitnaturaldetoxresort.com/wild-tribe-superfood-cafe/','["Monday: 8:30 AM – 8:30 PM","Tuesday: 8:30 AM – 8:30 PM","Wednesday: 8:30 AM – 8:30 PM","Thursday: 8:30 AM – 8:30 PM","Friday: 8:30 AM – 8:30 PM","Saturday: 8:30 AM – 8:30 PM","Sunday: 8:30 AM – 8:30 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.181+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.181+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wild-tribe-superfood-cafe-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wild-tribe-superfood-cafe-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=13367706396263897282',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('wilsons-beach-bar-restaurant','standard','cmr07iifb0107q8xdwc3lbf7q','Wilson’s Beach Bar & Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "One of the best meals we had in Thailand – easily a 10/10. We arrived just before closing time, and instead of rushing us out, the staff welcomed us with genuine kindness and still served us with a smile.  The food was absolutely outstanding – fresh, full of flavor, and clearly made with passion. You could taste the quality in every bite.  Amazing service, great atmosphere, and unforgettable food. A must-visit – don’t leave without eating here. Highly recommended! 🍽️✨"
> **- Philipp Szendzina (5/5/5)**

> "A very pleasant experience. A location on the beach, with attentive staff and very good food."
> **- Luncasu C (5/5/5)**

> "First visit and a big disappointment. Especially since we live close by and were counting to find a place to visit daily.  At first it looked promising as two of the male staff were trying to be nice. But we ordered two dishes, and one of them only because it looked great in the photo. We even showed that exact photo when ordering. What we got was completely different - not even close.  When we pointed it out, a woman from the staff reacted in a very rude way and said it’s “obvious” dishes don’t look like in photos. (Also different ingredients?!)  We refused to eat it and ordered pad kra pao instead. What came was just oily meat overloaded with seasoning/MSG, with no Thai basil and nothing that resembles real pad kra pao. We live in Thailand and know how it should taste, this had nothing to do with Thai cuisine beside similar look.  Very disappointing overall - for the rude service and for serving dishes that are completely different from what’s advertised. 1/5."
> **- Jakub Kotuła Fit on Trip (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wilsons-beach-bar-restaurant-1.jpg','094 946 5887','11 แม่น้ำ 3, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84330, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61558376861969&mibextid=LQQJ4d','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 10:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifs1000cq8xdfo2aau32','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.183+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.183+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wilsons-beach-bar-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wilsons-beach-bar-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=6096345997551827546',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('windfield-international-school','standard','cmr07iife0108q8xdjbkouhxd','Windfield International School','Discover Windfield International School, a premier for kids located in Lamai, Koh Samui. Find reviews, hours, and contact information.','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/windfield-international-school-1.jpg','077 332 420','67/7 Thanon Had Lamai, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,0.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://windfield.ac.th/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 4:30 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 4:30 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 4:30 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 4:30 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 4:30 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifwy001zq8xdppgaj2cs','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.186+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.186+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/windfield-international-school-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/windfield-international-school-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3864473859433141014',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('wing-samui-condominium','standard','cmr07iifg0109q8xd04xuihbi','Wing Samui Condominium','## Top Reviews
> "Amazing facilities. Ideal location for visiting the island or daily living. Facilities are part of the Wyndham hotel so everyone can enjoy the gym, sauna, pool with swim up bar, restaurant, etc. Staff and reception folks are super nice. I stayed here for a week and fell in love with the place. I highly recommend."
> **- imi mosaheb (5/5/5)**

> "Honestly, this place is a bit of a shambles right now. It’s giving ''unfinished hotel'' rather than a cozy condo. The units are tiny and way too cramped—even for one person, the kitchen and bathroom are basically a joke. Plus, the sink faucet is weirdly long? It literally blocks the whole basin, making it a pain just to wash your face.  Also, a major heads-up: the water smells like a straight-up swimming pool. The chlorine is insane. If you’re moving in, you 100% need a filtered shower head or a proper water purifier, otherwise your hair and skin are going to be absolutely trashed.  If you''re in Building 6 or 7, good luck. You’re basically living on a construction site. Constant noise, workers singing at the top of their lungs, and dust everywhere. The walls/ceilings are paper-thin too; if you''re on the first floor, you’ll hear every single footstep from upstairs.  Pros: It''s new, has a washer/stove, and the ground floor garden is chill... until the smell of cigarettes and weed hits you.  The management needs to make up its mind. It functions okay for short-term hotel guests, but for anyone actually living here? It’s a mess. The hybrid ''hotel-meets-condo'' setup just doesn''t work for residents."
> **- Penelopé (2/5/5)**

> "I would like to raise several concerns regarding the current condition and management of the condominium facilities.  The public staircase appears incomplete, with paint stains visible throughout, and the windows in the stairway have not been properly cleaned. At the pool area, there are insufficient sun loungers, and music from the pool bar is played at an excessively loud volume in the mornings. Overall, many aspects of the property give the impression of being rushed or unfinished, including landscaping, where a number of plants and trees appear unhealthy or poorly maintained.  It also seems that the condominium units were delivered overdue and in a rushed condition. The gym facilities require attention: the treadmill machines are not adequate for running, the sauna is very small and unclean, and there are no lockers available. In addition, the gym equipment does not appear to be cleaned regularly. Finally, the metal gates near the pool are already showing signs of rust, which raises concerns about maintenance and durability.  I hope these issues can be addressed promptly to improve the overall standard of the property."
> **- Digzz Digzz (2/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wing-samui-condominium-1.jpg','+66888877877','124, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://wingsamuicondo.com/','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 5:00 PM"]','cmr07ifrn0007q8xdq29pgizw','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.188+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.188+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wing-samui-condominium-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wing-samui-condominium-2.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wing-samui-condominium-3.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wing-samui-condominium-4.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3354849229183438387',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('winmac-computer-shop','standard','cmr07iifi010aq8xdosj1k6j8','WinMac Computer Shop','## Top Reviews
> "I had a problem with my 2019 MacBookPro and this store was able to diagnose the problem very quickly. Since I was no longer in Samui they shipped it to me, they were very kind and helpful! Top quality price!!!"
> **- Anastassia Prada (5/5/5)**

> "Very professional and fast help for my MacBook! My MacBook Pro suddenly didn’t boot anymore and the fan became loud when I tried charging it. They fixed it quickly, charged a very fair price, and even sent it to me by ferry from Koh Samui to Koh Phangan (where I’m staying). Absolutely recommended! Top service all around — thank you so much! Khob khun kha ❤️"
> **- Constanze (5/5/5)**

> "I purchased a used iPhone Pro Max from this shop in good faith, but within hours the screen went completely black. After several hard resets, the issue briefly resolved, but the screen ultimately failed and had to be replaced within a week.  When I contacted the shop, I was advised that the warranty did not cover the issue. Given how quickly the screen failed, I question whether the phone received a thorough inspection prior to sale. Unfortunately, my experience was disappointing, and based on this, I would be cautious about purchasing a used iPhone from this store."
> **- Timothy MacDonald (1/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/winmac-computer-shop-1.jpg','084 690 4968','109 ถ. ทวีราษฎร์ภักดี Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.facebook.com/marketplace/profile/100012497625131/?ref=permalink&mibextid=dXMIcH','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.190+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.190+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/winmac-computer-shop-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/winmac-computer-shop-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14979011001905319548',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('wirason-residence','standard','cmr07iifk010bq8xd60zes15y','Wirason Residence','## Top Reviews
> "Overall our stay in this hotel was nice. Location is perfect for those who like peace and quiet. The owner of the hotel is very friendly and helpful, and really gives you the impression that you can ask him anything. Also all hotel staff is very nice, polite and makes you feel welcomed in this hotel. There was very intense smell of the air freshener in the 2nd floor room when we moved in and since I am very sensitive to the smells the hotel owner kindly moved us to another room on the first floor. Room on the first floor was much bigger and also looked much better. Only room minus was that during the heavy rain whole bathroom was wet, because in a place of large window area is a fine mesh. There were also lot of ants, but they don''t do any harm to the hotel guests, so it is ok to share the room with these neighbors. Rooms were clean, but I would recommend to the hotel staff to change the towels for the guests each day, because especially during the rainy days there is no option for guests to dry them and by the end of the second day those towels already start to have bad smell. Breakfast offer is very tasty, but each day the same. Pool was very clean and we liked the fact that it was private. By private I mean, that we were almost the only ones who used it. And this hotel is definitely a very family friendly place."
> **- Ieva Vilcāne (4/5/5)**

> "I was here with my son and my mom and we all loved it. The pool is very nice to relax and the restaurant has good food too. The breakfast is good and healthy. The Location is not perfect but by motorbike or foot you can go to the nice spots within 10-20 min. (Lamai Beach/night market/ grandfather Rock etc.)  We will come again !"
> **- Emre San (5/5/5)**

> "This place is fabulous. Great size rooms, both family and doubles. Really relaxed environment and the owners are truly amazing with guests. Would recommend if you are travelling with kids. Only minus is the location, takes about 15-20 min to walk to the beach. For us it was worth it since we felt very welcomed and taken care of. Highly recommend"
> **- Josie Holmgren (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wirason-residence-1.jpg','093 348 7544','lamai 119/8 119/8 Thanon Had Lamai, Tambon Maret, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84310, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.7,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.wirasonresidencesamui.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifrp0008q8xde8dk7pdm','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.192+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.192+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wirason-residence-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wirason-residence-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3894564159055947777',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('wokstar-express-samui','standard','cmr07iifm010cq8xd8tn8gfds','Wokstar Express Samui','## Top Reviews
> "Came to eat and drink here the other day with my sisters and it is a great place. The staff are really friendly and the food is tasty. Only needed a couple of dishes to share between us. Played some pool with the pretty staff and was made to feel very welcome. Will be going back again sometime."
> **- Sirilak Yosrungruang (5/5/5)**

> "Food was decent. Large portions and filling but flavor is lacking a bit. Also, no fortune cookies came with my take-out meal. The staff are very nice and the restaurant itself is spacious and good for groups."
> **- Bobby Shaftoe (4/5/5)**

> "I genuinely think this is the best Chinese restaurant in Koh Samui. It’s not just a Chinese restaurant though as it does amazing Western food. Best burgers on the island at a reasonable price. It also has a pool table and outdoor seating. A/c inside if it’s too hot. Ticks all the boxes"
> **- Steve Cromie (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wokstar-express-samui-1.jpg','092 742 9841','23, 106 Thanon Bond Kai, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.3,0,0,0,NULL,'https://wokstarexpress.com/?page_id=265','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 2:00 AM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 2:00 AM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifv2001aq8xdag7cvjgf','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.194+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.194+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wokstar-express-samui-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/wokstar-express-samui-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=16779250535649346640',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('workshop-sport-design','standard','cmr07iifo010dq8xdsi925ho5','Workshop Sport Design','## Top Reviews
> "Apparently, basic manners are optional in this shop. No greeting, no thank you, and definitely no help when it comes to finding the right jersey size. The owner seemed far too important to acknowledge customers. Thailand is famous for being the land of smiles — sadly, this store didn’t get the memo. If you’re looking for arrogance instead of customer service, you’re in the right place."
> **- Sam Sam (1/5/5)**

> "This jersey store has been great for me. I am a girl and finding shirts is a headache cuz the sizes and shape. The shop itself has cold AC, plenty of jerseys from Nba to all the football leagues. The owner has the machine for printing names and numbers. Idk why everyone complains about him... grow up, the prices are clearly there, no room for scam or taking advantage, he is not next to you pushing, like ALL the other shops. I had my time to check every single jersey and try them on. If any question ask but YOU are the visitor in Thailand so don''t expect perfect english. Don''t be that IDIOT. Everything is there clearly. Thanks a lot for let me have my time checking !!!!"
> **- Lu La (5/5/5)**

> "Excellent variety of Football shirts from all major football leagues, national teams and Thai teams. However, the owner and his store excels in custom made shirts which are unique, original and with the very best materials. If in Chaweng Samui or even Lamai, visit this store before you leave."
> **- Leonardo Di Carlo (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/workshop-sport-design-1.jpg','093 642 9645','112, 17 moo6, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,3.9,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 10:00 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07ifs5000eq8xdeu148200','cmr07ifuw0018q8xd0skvb1rt','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.196+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.196+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/workshop-sport-design-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/workshop-sport-design-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=2907534685633578377',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('x-quad-samui-atv-tour','standard','cmr07iifq010eq8xdsnerusar','X-Quad Samui ATV Tour','## Top Reviews
> "My family and I booked a 4-hour ATV and buggy tour, and it turned out to be a truly unforgettable experience. The tour was organized at the highest level — everything was perfectly planned from start to finish. The route was very diverse and rich in impressions: • a stunning viewpoint overlooking the northeast coast of Samui, • a high-altitude viewpoint with panoramic views of the east coast, • a stop at a beautiful and cozy bar for refreshing drinks, • lunch at the top of one of the mountains with breathtaking views, • and, of course, a visit to one of the most beautiful places on the island — Tan Rua Waterfall. The emotions and sensations from the tour are simply indescribable. It is a perfect combination of adrenaline, nature, and comfort. I would also like to especially highlight the excellent safety standards — the briefing, equipment, and professional guidance were outstanding, which is extremely important when traveling with family. Many thanks to the X-Quad Samui team for their professionalism, attention to detail, and for providing such an amazing experience. I highly recommend this tour to anyone who wants to see Samui from a new perspective and enjoy truly unforgettable moments."
> **- Евгений Рябченко (5/5/5)**

> "We booked the 4 hour tour and had the most amazing time from the pick-up to the last moment. The guides and whole team is amazing and has the best kind of humor and they are really good at explaining nature. Our guides showed us snakes and spiders and it was so much fun to learn more about Samui. Hands down the best experience ever!!! We even stopped at a temple and a super cute restaurant spot, lunch was fantastic! Would do it again tomorrow; worth every penny!"
> **- Hannah Bahl (5/5/5)**

> "This was by far the best experience we had on Koh Samui! Trip through the jungle to view points with lunch in a Xquad which was loads of fun. Instructors were very clear with the controls, knowledgable about the area and information and generally made the whole day fun and enjoyable! Chris was following at the back on a scrambler and Cala (i think that was his name) guided at the front on a quad to set the pace and make sure it’s safe for everyone!  You will get dirty so dont wear nice clothes, lunch provided which was nice, waterfall dried up due to no rain but that cant be helped!  100% recommend this, well worth it!!"
> **- Charlie Anne Grimes (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/x-quad-samui-atv-tour-1.jpg','090 980 5401','Soi 4, Tambon Mae Nam, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.9,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.xquad-samui.com/','["Monday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Tuesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Wednesday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Thursday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Friday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Saturday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM","Sunday: 8:00 AM – 9:00 PM"]','cmr07iftx000xq8xdn0s5qzbi','cmr07ifte000sq8xdidrd81na','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.198+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.198+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/x-quad-samui-atv-tour-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/x-quad-samui-atv-tour-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=115468433998374567',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('yada-beach-bar-restaurant','standard','cmr07iifr010fq8xdi7npjo8e','Yada Beach Bar & Restaurant','## Top Reviews
> "Great place with very nice staff. We had great food and lot of choices. It was a rainy day and we were able to play pool and games almost the whole afternoon. Thanks !"
> **- Victor SALLES (5/5/5)**

> "The nicest meal ever, yummy cocktails, sweetest workers and fun games!!! Everyone is so kind and attentive and I had the best evening here!!!!"
> **- cait gannon (5/5/5)**

> "Fantastic food, best Panang curry we’ve had on Samui, really good happy hour on beers and cocktails. Well worth a visit"
> **- Stephen Turnbull (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/yada-beach-bar-restaurant-1.jpg','098 053 1681','32/36 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Tuesday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Wednesday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Thursday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Friday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Saturday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM","Sunday: 11:00 AM – 12:00 AM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.199+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.199+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/yada-beach-bar-restaurant-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/yada-beach-bar-restaurant-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=12857519538867910669',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('yansa-studio','standard','cmr07iifv010gq8xd614s38mx','Yansa Studio','## Top Reviews
> "A must-visit spot in Koh Samui! Valérie’s kindness and professionalism are truly incredible. Her radiant smile and her absolute passion for teaching dance are second to none. Having traveled extensively and trained at various studios around the world, I can confidently say this was my absolute best experience. Valérie managed to elevate my salsa to a whole new level—something no other instructor has ever been able to do. ​I am infinitely grateful. A thousand thanks!"
> **- Brice (5/5/5)**

> "A Transformative Sound Healing Experience at Yansa Studio ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️  I stumbled upon Yansa Studio in the most serendipitous way over lunch at my favorite restaurant. I met Kathy, one of the teachers, and we struck up a conversation that quickly turned to health and healing. Through that exchange, she mentioned a sound healing session happening that very evening.  I’ve always been curious about sound healing but had put it on hold since moving to Thailand. That night felt like a nudge from the universe, and I decided to attend.  I arrived a few minutes early and was warmly welcomed, invited in from the heat, and told to make myself comfortable. The atmosphere inside was calm and inviting. I laid down on my back and closed my eyes as the team finished setting up a beautiful array of instruments crystal bowls, metal singing bowls, an ocean drum, a rain stick, and two mid-sized gongs.  As more participants arrived, I shifted into a lotus position to quietly observe the space and energy. When the session began, Valerie, the instructor, gently introduced what we were about to experience. Her voice was steady and soothing. She explained the basics of sound healing and how different frequencies interact with our brain waves, creating opportunities to move from Beta (our busy, thinking mind) into Alpha, Theta, and even Delta states the deeper waves where restoration and insight often occur.  For someone like me, whose mind is usually buzzing in high Beta due to a thirst for learning and a tendency toward overthinking, finding inner stillness is a challenge. But just minutes into the session, with the help of my breath and the surrounding resonance, I felt my mind soften and release. My body melted into the floor, grounded by the earth, and for the first time in a long while, I felt true peace.  With my eyes closed, I drifted into a dreamlike state, oscillating between Alpha and deeper waves of consciousness. I even brushed up against Theta and Delta moments. What truly surprised me were the visions that came vivid, spontaneous, and full of meaning. Insights surfaced that my waking mind had long buried or blocked. It felt like a gentle unlocking of something deeper.  This was more than a relaxing experience it was transformative. I’ve never had anything quite like it.  I’ll absolutely be making this part of my weekly routine. Sessions are held every Sunday at 7 PM, and because space is limited, I recommend reserving in advance.  If you’ve ever been curious about sound healing, frequency, or simply want to reconnect with yourself through nature and vibration, Yansa Studio is a beautiful place to begin. Whether you’re looking for peace, insight, or simply rest, I highly recommend giving it a try."
> **- Nomadic Lotus (5/5/5)**

> "Hey people If you are reading this to help determine if the dance classes here and sound healing sessions are worth checking out, my vote is a very solid yes!.. Valerie is exceptionally capable and personable. Has been teaching for many years and is connected with a great community of people on and off of Samui.  Dance classes; Beginners classes are easy going, fun and I think possibly the most progressive beginners classes I’ve attended before. Intermediate classes, partner work varied and designed to meet levels of attendees and the solo work at the beginning tends to yield a healthy amount of laughter. Students attending are welcoming, good, fun people as well. A healthy number of socials available within the group each week.  Sound healing; Aside from the wonderful benefits we know about - calming the internal systems (sometimes to the point of falling asleep), and tuning the body and mind towards healthy vibrations, Valerie provides a very grounding and peaceful energy in this environment. Also with a wider array of instruments here than I recall seeing before.  An absolute treasure!"
> **- Andy Banks (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/yansa-studio-1.jpg','063 325 6392','Bophut, 248 Had Chaweng 6 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,5.0,0,0,0,NULL,'https://yansastudio.wordpress.com/','["Monday: 10:00 AM – 1:00 PM, 5:30 – 7:30 PM","Tuesday: 6:00 – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 6:00 – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 6:00 – 8:00 PM","Friday: 10:00 – 11:00 AM, 6:30 – 8:30 PM","Saturday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: 6:30 – 8:30 PM"]','cmr07ifuo0015q8xdfahzrsp4','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.203+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.203+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/yansa-studio-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/yansa-studio-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=14882627952872579302',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('yellow-beach','standard','cmr07iifx010hq8xd61h3yyyn','Yellow Beach','## Top Reviews
> "Beautiful place. Long wide beach to stroll along. Comfy bed. Restaurant serves nice delicious food. Best dessert they have. Friendly,  helpful staffs from all over the hotel who greet you with wide smile. Khun JJ, their GM is a gem."
> **- Boey Mey (5/5/5)**

> "Lovely bar and restaurant right on the beach. The overall atmosphere is wonderful. Besides the beach there are also two pools there one of which has a bar in it, so you can sit in pool and order from bar.  Food was very good there. One night we brought our own food and manager very politely asked us not to do that again. We were in the wrong but he was still very polite.  There are also tables and deckchairs right on beach where on can chill."
> **- Kenny (5/5/5)**

> "We have a chance to join in the yellow beach market fireshow event last 17th August and it was amazing !! They gonna hold this special event again at the end of this month. We so exciting to be there again. cant wait !!!"
> **- suriya thonsamor (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/yellow-beach-1.jpg','077 422 255','124/1 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.2,0,0,0,NULL,'https://www.fairhousesamui.com/culinary-restaurant.html','["Monday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 11:00 PM"]','cmr07ifpj0000q8xdet31f7qd','cmr07ig5c0051q8xdykrbexft','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.205+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.205+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/yellow-beach-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/yellow-beach-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=17415501572012367784',NULL,NULL);
