INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('yokthip-massage-and-spa-school','standard','cmr07iig0010jq8xdq0q8rvky','Yokthip Massage And Spa School','## Top Reviews
> "A wonderful traditional experience! I had the old-fashioned traditional massage with oil and it was absolutely excellent. The therapist was skilled, attentive, and used the perfect pressure throughout. The atmosphere was calm and relaxing, and I left feeling completely refreshed and rejuvenated. Highly recommended for anyone looking for a genuine, professional massage experience."
> **- Luca Foschi (5/5/5)**

> "I did Thai massage and reflexology training, it was very interesting and instructive, many thanks to the team (everybody was absolutely adorable), wishing you all a great year 🫶🏻🙏🏻"
> **- Maya Bizel (5/5/5)**

> "Accomplished 60hr sport massage and 30 hr thai massage in this great samui spa school. Being super grateful for this wonderful knowledge and amazing people around me for the past two weeks. Highly recommend the school if anyone would like to learn the art of massage. Everyone was very professional, kind and understanding. Many varieties of courses and flexible terms for students.  thai massage aroma oil massage face massage sport massage reflexology massage herbal massage  And probably many more..."
> **- Dominika Urbańska (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/yokthip-massage-and-spa-school-1.jpg','095 013 9095','33/36 Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.5,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM"]','cmr07iftc000rq8xdiyhsa78o','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.208+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.208+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/yokthip-massage-and-spa-school-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/yokthip-massage-and-spa-school-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=5645403152433136419',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('youngnum-pet-hospital','standard','cmr07iig2010kq8xdpob7tujk','Youngnum Pet Hospital','## Top Reviews
> "The hospital’s tactic is to provide services quickly without mentioning the cost — using any excuse to avoid talking about it. Afterwards, they tell you a big bill. For example, the price for medicines was five times higher than in a regular pharmacy.  This isn’t something I made up — I read several reviews with the same story.  I brought in a kitten I found on the street, and after the treatment they prescribed, it died. Business is business, but karma is real."
> **- Оля Мазалова (1/5/5)**

> "Always a great experience there! They are very good with animals and some of the doctors are pretty friendly. They helped to treat our new member of the family, that was bit by a dog and couldn’t walk. They have experience and good quality products."
> **- Angelica Meditation (5/5/5)**

> "We had a very positive experience here when our dog needed surgery to remove cancerous growths. The staff was prepared, professional & caring. We will be returning for follow up care even though this office is a bit further away. Thank you! 🙏🏽 ขอบคุณครับ 🙏🏽"
