> "Second year visiting, quality establishment. Friendly owners. Highly recommend. I can confirm the food is top drawer. Will certainty return on next visit."
> **- paul lewis (5/5/5)**

> "Fantastic! Excellent cocktails, atmosphere and a free pool table 🎱🤩🍹When I ordered food, staff were happy to make me a vegetarian meal that wasn’t on the menu 💚 AND it was super tasty. Everyone in my group was happy with their food and we’ll definitely be back ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️"
> **- Nina Whiteman (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/yoyo-bar-1.jpg','064 696 3035','21, 2, Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: Closed","Tuesday: 4:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Wednesday: 4:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Thursday: 4:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Friday: 4:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Saturday: 4:00 PM – 2:00 AM","Sunday: 4:00 PM – 2:00 AM"]','cmr07ifx90024q8xdg1rcf50m','cmr07ifrv000aq8xdn6zpp33d','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.215+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.215+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/yoyo-bar-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/yoyo-bar-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=11721325395710151087',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('zasinar-clinic','standard','cmr07iig8010nq8xdqbo7gfr8','Zasinar Clinic','## Top Reviews
> "💯❤️🙌 I found this clinic after being really disappointed by how some of the more “famous” and fancy clinics on the island treat their clients—and not to mention their jaw-dropping prices. I was honestly starting to lose hope… until I discovered this little gem.  From the very beginning, I felt like I was exactly where I needed to be. The whole team speaks perfect English, they were so warm and welcoming, and you could really feel they were happy to see a client walk through the door. That kind of genuine energy is rare and meant a lot to me.  The procedure was explained clearly and thoroughly, and after a quick consultation with the doctor, I was able to get everything done right away—no waiting, no nonsense. I had Botox, Liftera, and a few other treatments, and all of them were performed by the doctor herself, not a nurse (which is honestly so rare, unless you pay extra in most other clinics). I felt super safe and taken care of the entire time.  The doctor and the nurse assisting her were not only professional but also so sweet and funny. They turned what’s usually a slightly uncomfortable experience into something that actually made me smile. I left feeling more like I came from a spa than a clinic!  I’m honestly in love with this place. I can’t imagine going anywhere else from now on. If you’re looking to have any beauty procedures done, I wholeheartedly recommend this clinic. It’s a hidden treasure on the island."
> **- Małgorzata Pindych (5/5/5)**

> "I had a great experience at this clinic! The laser treatment is much cheaper than in Europe, with the same high-quality equipment. The clinic is clean, the staff are friendly and speak English, and the promotion prices are unbeatable. Highly recommend!"
> **- Serena Harrington (5/5/5)**

> "The staff are so polite. Im here with my friend when he needs to clean his wounds from an accident. Might be the most polite hospital i have ever been in!"
> **- Ajdin Puskar (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/zasinar-clinic-1.jpg','082 859 4591','25/25, ตำบล บ่อผุด อำเภอเกาะสมุย สุราษฎร์ธานี 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.8,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,'["Monday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM","Sunday: 9:00 AM – 7:00 PM"]','cmr07ifst000mq8xdudn7dwk1','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.216+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.216+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/zasinar-clinic-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/zasinar-clinic-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=15132047045808779712',NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO "Listing" VALUES('zazen-boutique-resort-spa','standard','cmr07iiga010oq8xddq4t5rar','Zazen Boutique Resort & Spa','## Top Reviews
> "Back in 2016, while visiting family in Koh Samui, we had a wonderful stay at Zazen Boutique Resort & Spa. The property was beautifully maintained, surrounded by lush tropical gardens that gave it a peaceful and private atmosphere. Our villa was spacious and comfortable—perfect for our family of four—and felt like a true island retreat.  The restaurant was outstanding, offering delicious Thai and international dishes, with a terrace overlooking the sea that made every meal feel special. Breakfast and dinners there were a highlight of our trip.  We also loved that the hotel was within easy walking distance to Bo Phut Fisherman’s Village, where we could explore local shops, beachside bars, and night markets.  Overall, it was a fantastic, relaxing stay, and one we still remember fondly. Highly recommended for families and couples looking for a peaceful, authentic Koh Samui experience."
> **- Sven Dutoit (5/5/5)**

> "The atmosphere was excellent, and the service was outstanding. The staff paid close attention to every detail, regularly checking on us regarding the service and the quality of the food. Most importantly, the food was absolutely delicious, especially the spaghetti dish. I would give it a perfect 10/10! I will definitely be coming back again. 😊"
> **- ดนยา เตียวสกุล (5/5/5)**

> "Zazen omg it’s amazing.Koh Samui must do ! This venue came highly recommended to us and it lived up to all expectations.On walking in through the magnificent gardens  to the restaurant you are met by the most attentive staff .You will be captivated by the restaurant which is absolutely gorgeous.We had a table on the waterfront it was magnificent. We chose the seafood banquet omg to die for ….yes it was so fresh ,delicious and the presentation (see pics ) The wine list was extensive as well ,we chose a Pinot Grigio from Italy paired beautifully. Dessert was amazing Zazen has absolutely nailed it …the attention to detail,the food choices ,the atmosphere and the decor which I believe was updated maybe a year ago. I found the staff to be so engaging and happy to help with dietary requirements and above all very attentive without over doing it Not forgetting the incredible backdrop This would be an amazing venue for a function On another note I was fortunate to have their Signature Aromatherapy massage let me tell you if you can just do it !!!! Bliss so professional One last thing the gift shop was great for those last minute gifts for home"
> **- Glynda Curtin (5/5/5)**','https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/zazen-boutique-resort-spa-1.jpg','077 425 085','177 Beach Tambon Bo Put, Amphoe Ko Samui, Chang Wat Surat Thani 84320, Thailand',NULL,NULL,4.6,0,0,0,NULL,'http://www.samuizazen.com/','["Monday: Open 24 hours","Tuesday: Open 24 hours","Wednesday: Open 24 hours","Thursday: Open 24 hours","Friday: Open 24 hours","Saturday: Open 24 hours","Sunday: Open 24 hours"]','cmr07ifv6001cq8xd5vsyfm44','cmr07ifqw0003q8xdu2hrq6e7','cmqyzwjmd0000iuxdbv41llnf','2026-06-30T05:29:14.218+00:00','2026-06-30T05:29:14.218+00:00','["https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/zazen-boutique-resort-spa-1.jpg","https://pub-3433478e81804444ae052b8316ad0d83.r2.dev/images/businesses/zazen-boutique-resort-spa-2.jpg"]','https://maps.google.com/?cid=3328826799020832534',NULL,NULL);
